#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Laser_None
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 02070897
msgctxt "002255"
msgid "Empty laser sight attachment."
msgstr "레이저 표적 지시기 미부착."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Optics_ReflexSight
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 02070898
msgctxt "002256"
msgid "Reflex sights for quicker target acquisition and visibility."
msgstr "반사식 조준기. 목표 포착 능력, 가시성 증가."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Optics_ShortScope
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 02070899
msgctxt "002257"
msgid "Short scope for 2x magnified view."
msgstr "배율 2배의 저배율 조준경."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_LaserRifle_Mag_EM
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 0207087F
msgctxt "002258"
msgid "Electromagnetic rounds that can knockout living creatures as well as disable robotic units for a time."
msgstr "전자기탄. 일정 시간 동안 생물을 기절시키고 로봇 기체를 무력화시킴."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Internal_HighPowered
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 0207086D
msgctxt "002259"
msgid "Increases Damage done."
msgstr "적에게 가하는 피해 증가."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Internal_HighVelocity
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
#. FormID: 0207086E
msgctxt "00225A"
msgid "Internal module that increases accuracy and range."
msgstr "내장 부품. 명중률, 사거리 증가."

#. List: 1
#. EDID: SFBGS050_co_gun_mod_MGP_BallisticRifle_Mag_Large
#. REC: COBJ:DESC
