#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 006F1844, 002B6108, 00E39118
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 02005AD2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene:02005AF6
msgctxt "0000C8"
msgid "It also goes against the very beliefs that drove us to leave in the first place."
msgstr "그건 애초에 우리가 떠나게 만든 바로 그 신념에도 어긋나는 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 006F1844, 002B6108, 00E39118
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 02005AD2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene:02005AF6
msgctxt "0000C9"
msgid "It's a ridiculous notion that started out as the ideals of a few powerful people and was pushed on to the rest of us."
msgstr "힘 있는 몇몇의 이상에서 시작되어 나머지 모두에게 강요된 터무니없는 생각이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 006F1844, 002B6108, 00E39118
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 02005AD2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene:02005AF6
msgctxt "0000CA"
msgid "The Terrans think they are somehow superior and can subjugate the Settled Systems."
msgstr "테란은 자신들이 어쩐지 우월해서 개척 성계를 지배할 수 있다고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0035E5DA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005AD6/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF9
msgctxt "0000CB"
msgid "Do you think losing your mother is what made your father stay with the Terrans?"
msgstr "네 아버지가 테란에 남은 건 네 어머니를 잃었기 때문이라고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00DE0F1F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005AD8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B0C
msgctxt "0000CC"
msgid "I would be fed up, too, if I lost someone."
msgstr "나라도 누군가를 잃었다면 진절머리가 났을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00AF9B6D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005ADA/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF7
msgctxt "0000CD"
msgid "A lot of atrocities came out of that war."
msgstr "그 전쟁에서는 수많은 잔혹한 일이 벌어졌어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007077F9, 0062624E, 00124CF9
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 어머니를 잃었다니 유감이야., Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking, Proud with slight sadness. / Confident / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005ADB/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF1
msgctxt "0000CE"
msgid "It's over twenty years ago now. I've made my peace with it, but the occasional memory will still catch me off guard."
msgstr "이제 20년도 더 지난 일이야. 나는 받아들였지만, 가끔은 기억이 느닷없이 나를 흔들어 놓아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0010CC26
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005ADC/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFB
msgctxt "0000CF"
msgid "I'm sorry you lost your mother."
msgstr "어머니를 잃었다니 유감이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00F8ED03
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005ADE/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF0
msgctxt "0000D0"
msgid "War is pointless."
msgstr "전쟁은 무의미해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B02
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00CC1395, 00D17D7A, 00FDB563
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 테란 함대가 어떻게 그를 망가뜨렸지?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 02005ADF/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B02
msgctxt "0000D1"
msgid "He took on their ideals, their disgust with the Settled Systems... and before I knew it, I'd lost him."
msgstr "그는 그들의 사상, 개척 성계에 대한 혐오를 받아들였고... 어느새 나는 그를 잃어버렸어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B02
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00CC1395, 00D17D7A, 00FDB563
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 테란 함대가 어떻게 그를 망가뜨렸지?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 02005ADF/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B02
msgctxt "0000D2"
msgid "So as the people in authority became more extreme, like he said, he blindly followed."
msgstr "그러니까 그가 말한 대로, 당국자들이 점점 극단적으로 변하자 그도 맹목적으로 따른 거군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B02
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00CC1395, 00D17D7A, 00FDB563
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 테란 함대가 어떻게 그를 망가뜨렸지?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 02005ADF/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B02
msgctxt "0000D3"
msgid "My father's never been one to think on his own. He's a soldier at heart."
msgstr "아버지는 원래 자기 머리로 판단하는 사람이 아니었어. 마음속까지 군인이었지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF3
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 004293E9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005AE0/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF3
msgctxt "0000D4"
msgid "How did the Terran Armada ruin him?"
msgstr "테란 함대가 어떻게 그를 망가뜨렸지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B07
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00790C45, 005B88E3, 003E6ED6
#. Notes = Slight anger. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 식민지 전쟁에 진절머리를 냈던 거야?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Sad / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005AE1/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B07
msgctxt "0000D5"
msgid "It's fruitless. "
msgstr "헛된 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B07
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00790C45, 005B88E3, 003E6ED6
#. Notes = Slight anger. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 식민지 전쟁에 진절머리를 냈던 거야?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Sad / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005AE1/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B07
msgctxt "0000D6"
msgid "A war over territory when humanity has the entirety of space to explore? "
msgstr "인류가 우주 전체를 탐험할 수 있는데, 영토를 두고 전쟁이라니?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B07
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00790C45, 005B88E3, 003E6ED6
#. Notes = Slight anger. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 식민지 전쟁에 진절머리를 냈던 거야?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Sad / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005AE1/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B07
msgctxt "0000D7"
msgid "My mother died in that war, alongside countless others. And for what?"
msgstr "우리 어머니도 수많은 사람들과 함께 그 전쟁에서 죽었어. 대체 뭘 위해서?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B00
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F2CEA9
#. Notes = / to Connor
#: 02005AE3/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_TerranScene:02005B00
msgctxt "0000DB"
msgid "What can you tell me about the Terrans?"
msgstr "테란에 대해 뭘 알고 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001CC5F4, 00BEECF3
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02005AE4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B09
msgctxt "0000DC"
msgid "He was a UC lieutenant back then, back when we were fed up with the Colony War and I was fresh out of training."
msgstr "그는 그때 식민지 연합 대위였어. 우리가 식민지 전쟁에 진절머리를 내던 때였고, 나는 훈련을 막 마친 참이었지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001CC5F4, 00BEECF3
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02005AE4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B09
msgctxt "0000DD"
msgid "My father was a great man, a great dad, until the Terran Armada ruined him."
msgstr "내 아버지는 훌륭한 사람이자 훌륭한 아빠였어. 테란 함대가 그를 망가뜨리기 전까지는."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C3B2F6
#. Notes = / to Connor
#: 02005AE5/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF4
msgctxt "0000DE"
msgid "Can you tell me about your father?"
msgstr "아버지에 대해 말해 줄 수 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00194816
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005AE6/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF8
msgctxt "0000DF"
msgid "Why were you fed up with the Colony War?"
msgstr "왜 식민지 전쟁에 진절머리를 냈던 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 004FF215
#. Notes = Terrans broadcast threats over SSNN. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 02005AE7/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B0A
msgctxt "0000E2"
msgid "I didn't think I'd hear from him ever again, but after those threats over SSNN... a part of me knew it was a possibility."
msgstr "아버지에게서 다시 연락이 올 줄은 몰랐어. 하지만 SSNN에서 그 협박이 방송된 뒤로는... 마음 한구석에서는 그럴 수도 있다고 알고 있었지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00ACC591, 0002D440
#. Notes = Concerned, reserved shock. Hasn't heard from his father in over 10 years. / Shocked, Face: Shocked, Reading that his father is dead. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 02005AE8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005AFE
msgctxt "0000E3"
msgid "He's... he's gone."
msgstr "아버지는... 돌아가셨어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00ACC591, 0002D440
#. Notes = Concerned, reserved shock. Hasn't heard from his father in over 10 years. / Shocked, Face: Shocked, Reading that his father is dead. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 02005AE8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005AFE
msgctxt "0000E4"
msgid "It's from my father..."
msgstr "아버지가 보낸 거야..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00FE2FC2
#. Notes = Puzzled, Face: Puzzled
#: 02005AE9/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005AFA
msgctxt "0000E5"
msgid "Let's see here..."
msgstr "어디 보자..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0054B011
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Connor, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: [슬레이트 건네기] 코너 월리스에게 특별 배달입니다.
#: 02005AEA/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B0B
msgctxt "0000E6"
msgid "That's me, but I'm not sure who'd be contacting me, especially like this."
msgstr "그건 내가 맞는데, 누가 나한테 연락하는 건지 모르겠군. 그것도 이런 방식으로."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B08
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00114B97
#. Notes = / to Connor
#: 02005AEB/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B08
msgctxt "0000E7"
msgid "[Give Slate] Special delivery for Connor Wallace."
msgstr "[슬레이트 건네기] 코너 월리스에게 특별 배달입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B06
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0019FE86
#. Notes = That feeling you get when you get a package and you aren't sure what it is. / Surprised / to Connor, Face: Surprised, Prompt: [슬레이트 건네기] 이건 당신에게 온 겁니다.
#: 02005AEC/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B06
msgctxt "0000E8"
msgid "A slate? This is a surprise."
msgstr "슬레이트라고? 뜻밖이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B04
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E8D1F0
#. Notes = / to Connor
#: 02005AED/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B04
msgctxt "0000E9"
msgid "[Give Slate] This is for you."
msgstr "[슬레이트 건네기] 이건 당신에게 온 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B01
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00C15550
#. Notes = Curious as to what the player wants. / Question / to Player Default, Face: Question
#: 02005AEE/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_200_SlateScene:02005B01
msgctxt "0000EA"
msgid "Can I help you?"
msgstr "무슨 일이시죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A88
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_06
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 0063228B
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Afraid / to Actor2, Face: Afraid
#: 02005A63/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06:02005A88
msgctxt "0000EE"
msgid "Yeah. You're probably right."
msgstr "그래. 네 말이 맞는 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A83
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_06
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00D6BDE9
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Serious / to Actor1, Face: Serious
#: 02005A64/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06:02005A83
msgctxt "0000EF"
msgid "You're overreacting. That broadcast was clearly a hoax. I don't believe these \"Terrans\" exist."
msgstr "너무 과민 반응이야. 그 방송은 딱 봐도 가짜였어. 난 그 '테란'이라는 자들이 존재한다고 믿지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A84
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_06
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 005BE2CB
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Confident / to Actor2, Face: Confident
#: 02005A65/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene06:02005A84
msgctxt "0000F0"
msgid "We should start loading up on emergency supplies. Just in case."
msgstr "비상 물자를 챙겨 두기 시작해야겠어. 만일을 대비해서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A82
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_04
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 003DCEFE
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor1, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A69/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04:02005A82
msgctxt "0000F2"
msgid "I don't know. But I have a feeling we're gonna find out."
msgstr "모르겠어. 하지만 곧 알게 될 것 같은 느낌이 들어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_04
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 009B721B
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Afraid / to Actor2, Face: Afraid
#: 02005A6A/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04:02005A7A
msgctxt "0000F3"
msgid "That's a scary thought. But why are they attacking us? What do they want?"
msgstr "생각만 해도 무섭네. 그런데 왜 우리를 공격하는 거지? 원하는 게 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A87
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_04
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00E4B0D3
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Serious / to Actor1, Face: Serious
#: 02005A6B/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04:02005A87
msgctxt "0000F4"
msgid "Hard to say. Humanity left Earth centuries ago. It could be anyone. Assuming they're even human."
msgstr "단정하긴 어려워. 인류가 지구를 떠난 지 수 세기가 지났잖아. 누구든 될 수 있어. 애초에 인간이라면 말이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_04
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 005C31BB
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Afraid / to Actor2, Face: Afraid
#: 02005A6C/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene04:02005A7B
msgctxt "0000F5"
msgid "Who do you think these Terrans are? They called themselves \"The true children of Earth.\""
msgstr "이 테란들이 누구라고 생각해? 스스로를 '지구의 진정한 자손'이라고 불렀잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A81
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00FB23F5
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Serious / to Actor1, Face: Serious
#: 02005A6D/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene03:02005A81
msgctxt "0000F7"
msgid "They were never safe. It's just one more thing to worry about."
msgstr "원래 안전했던 적이 없어. 걱정거리가 하나 더 늘었을 뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 0070E411
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor2, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A6E/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene03:02005A7E
msgctxt "0000F8"
msgid "Between the Fleet, Spacers, and the Terran Armada, the spacelanes aren't safe anymore."
msgstr "함대에, 스페이서에, 테란 함대까지 있으니 우주항로는 더 이상 안전하지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A77
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 004308FC
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor2, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A73/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01:02005A77
msgctxt "0000FA"
msgid "Those poor passengers..."
msgstr "가엾은 승객들..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A79
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00865EB7
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor1, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A74/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01:02005A79
msgctxt "0000FB"
msgid "Oh god, yeah. It sounded terrifying."
msgstr "세상에, 맞아. 정말 끔찍하게 들렸어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 0091A673
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor2, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A75/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene01:02005A7D
msgctxt "0000FC"
msgid "Did you hear the news about the cruise ship?"
msgstr "그 유람선 소식 들었어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A86
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 009AA6A6
#. Notes = Somber / to Actor1, Face: Somber
#: 02005A6F/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02:02005A86
msgctxt "0000FE"
msgid "I love you too."
msgstr "나도 사랑해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A78
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 0087B856
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor2, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A70/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02:02005A78
msgctxt "0000FF"
msgid "I know. Just, try and be safe. I love you."
msgstr "알아. 그냥, 몸조심해. 사랑해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A76
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 0069BBED
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Nervous / to Actor2, Face: Nervous
#: 02005A72/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02:02005A76
msgctxt "000100"
msgid "I'm worried about you joining the search party. What if those... Terrans are still there?"
msgstr "네가 수색대에 합류한다니 걱정돼. 그... 테란들이 아직 거기 있으면 어떡해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A80
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00703C2E
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Serious / to Actor1, Face: Serious
#: 02005A71/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene02:02005A80
msgctxt "000101"
msgid "That's why I have to go. There could be survivors. "
msgstr "그래서 가야 해. 생존자가 있을지도 모르잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_05
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 00C9C7E6
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Afraid / to Actor2, Face: Afraid
#: 02005A66/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05:02005A7F
msgctxt "000103"
msgid "I have to believe we can."
msgstr "우리가 할 수 있다고 믿어야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A7C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_05
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor2
#. SoundFileID = 00624947
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Serious / to Actor1, Face: Serious
#: 02005A67/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05:02005A7C
msgctxt "000104"
msgid "That sounds nice in theory, but can you imagine getting Freestar and UC forces to agree on anything?"
msgstr "말로는 그럴듯하지만, 자유항성과 식민지 연합 병력이 무슨 일이든 합의하는 모습을 상상이나 할 수 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A85
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro_CrowdConvo_05
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Actor1
#. SoundFileID = 003DED6F
#. Notes = there was a broadcast about a warning from a scary, possible alien species attacking a cruise ship / Confident / to Actor2, Face: Confident
#: 02005A68/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene05:02005A85
msgctxt "000105"
msgid "If these Terrans are a real threat, humanity needs to unite to fight them."
msgstr "이 테란들이 진짜 위협이라면, 인류는 힘을 합쳐 맞서야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 007506CD
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked
#: 0203D937:02005A1D
msgctxt "000107"
msgid "That voice... it sounded like some kind of machine..."
msgstr "그 목소리... 꼭 기계 같았어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00237541
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked
#: 0203D937:02005A1C
msgctxt "000108"
msgid "Terran Armada? Was that broadcast even real? "
msgstr "테란 함대? 방송이, 진짜였던 거야? "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00417E34
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked
#: 0203D937:02005A1B
msgctxt "000109"
msgid "Wow. My wife and I were planning on taking a cruise, but our tickets got canceled last minute."
msgstr "와. 아내랑 유람선을 타려고 했는데, 막판에 표가 취소됐거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00E58BAC
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked
#: 0203D937:02005A1A
msgctxt "00010A"
msgid "What do they mean, true children of Earth?"
msgstr "지구의 진정한 자손이라니 무슨 뜻이지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A19
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00A03C41
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 0203D937:02005A19
msgctxt "00010B"
msgid "What if there are survivors? Is anyone going to save them?"
msgstr "생존자가 있으면 어떡해? 누군가는 구하러 가는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A18
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00623EF3
#. Notes = Worried, Face: Worried
#: 0203D937:02005A18
msgctxt "00010C"
msgid "I know how these things go. Big as space is, searching for that ship is like trying to find a grain of sand in a desert."
msgstr "이런 일이 어떻게 돌아가는지 알아. 우주가 워낙 넓으니, 그 함선을 찾는 건 사막에서 모래 한 알을 찾는 것과 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A17
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02 (+4 more)
#. SoundFileID = 004CFF73
#. Notes = Worried, Face: Worried
#: 0203D937:02005A17
msgctxt "00010D"
msgid "All those people, stranded. I can't imagine what that's like."
msgstr "그 많은 사람들이 고립됐다니. 어떤 기분일지 상상도 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember05_Female
#. SoundFileID = 00DFABA5
#. Notes = Different than the previous 2. You're still reacting tot he same news but getting more for variety / Shocked / to XMarker, Face: Shocked
#: 020059CC/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059FC
msgctxt "00010E"
msgid "*Gasps*"
msgstr "*숨막힘*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_Terran_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00AE4EF9
#: 020059CB/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:02005A02
msgctxt "00010F"
msgid "You have lost your way. Scattered among the stars, fighting amongst yourselves like vermin. Worthless. Irredeemable. "
msgstr "너희는 길을 잃었다. 별들 사이에 흩어져 벌레처럼 서로 싸우고 있다. 쓸모없고, 구제할 가치도 없다. "

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember02_Male
#. SoundFileID = 0023F8EF
#. Notes = Shocked / to XMarker, Face: Shocked
#: 020059CD/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059F6
msgctxt "000110"
msgid "What the..."
msgstr "뭐야..."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember01_Female
#. SoundFileID = 000447C1
#. Notes = Surprised / to CurrentKiosk, Face: Surprised
#: 020059CE/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059F0
msgctxt "000111"
msgid "*Gasps*"
msgstr "*숨막힘*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A05
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F2A543
#: 020059D4/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:02005A05
msgctxt "000112"
msgid "The luxury liner, Opulence of the Stars, has been hijacked in the Nirvana System, by a group calling themselves the Terran Armada."
msgstr "호화 유람선 오퓰런스 오브 더 스타가 니르바나 성계에서 납치되었습니다. 납치범들은 자신들의 이름이 테란 함대라고 밝혔습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember04_Male
#. SoundFileID = 000B18CF
#. Notes = Afraid / to CrowdMember03_Female, Face: Afraid
#: 020059D0/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast:020059E3
msgctxt "000113"
msgid "And do what? Everyone on that cruise liner is dead."
msgstr "가서 뭘 하게? 그 유람선에 탄 사람들은 모두 죽은 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember04_Male
#. SoundFileID = 004DEED1
#. Notes = Shocked / to XMarker, Face: Shocked
#: 020059D1/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059DD
msgctxt "000114"
msgid "Oh my god..."
msgstr "세상에..."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A11
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember01_Female
#. SoundFileID = 0068B349
#. Notes = Shocked / to CurrentKiosk, Face: Shocked
#: 020059D2/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast:02005A11
msgctxt "000115"
msgid "Oh my god, what was that?"
msgstr "세상에, 방금 뭐였어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0050993C
#: 020059D3/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:02005A0B
msgctxt "000116"
msgid "Hours after receipt of this recording, a search and rescue team was dispatched to the liner's last known coordinates. "
msgstr "이 녹음을 입수한 지 몇 시간 뒤, 유람선이 마지막으로 확인된 좌표로 수색 구조팀이 파견되었습니다. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00DE42B8
#: 020059D5/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059FF
msgctxt "000117"
msgid "We'll have more on this breaking news story as additional information comes in."
msgstr "추가 정보가 들어오는 대로 긴급 뉴스로 전해 드리겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00981E30
#: 020059CF/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059E9
msgctxt "000118"
msgid "The following is a recording captured by our intrepid reporters on the scene."
msgstr "다음 들려드릴 음성은 현장의 용감한 기자들이 녹음한 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0075A843
#: 020059D6/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059F9
msgctxt "000119"
msgid "In addition, authorities have asked all available pilots to aid in the search for survivors."
msgstr "이에 당국은 지원 가능한 조종사라면 누구든 생존자 수색을 지원해달라고 요청했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember03_Female
#. SoundFileID = 00B7EAE0
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020059D7/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast:020059F3
msgctxt "00011A"
msgid "They said they were looking for pilots who can help."
msgstr "도움을 줄 수 있는 조종사를 찾는다고 했잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059ED
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_Terran_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F8C6CC
#: 020059D8/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:020059ED
msgctxt "00011B"
msgid "You have forgotten who you are. We shall remind you. We are the Terran Armada. We are the true children of Earth. And none shall stand in our way."
msgstr ""
"너희는 자신이 누구인지 잊었다. 우리가 상기시켜 주겠다. 우리는 테란 함대다. 우리는 지구의 진정한 자손이다. 그 누구도 우리의 앞길을 "
"막을 수 없다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember02_Male
#. SoundFileID = 00661FA7
#. Notes = Shocked / to CurrentKiosk, Face: Shocked
#: 020059D9/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast:020059E6
msgctxt "00011C"
msgid "Holy hell..."
msgstr "맙소사..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_Terran_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 002585B1
#: 020059DC/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:02005A0D
msgctxt "00011D"
msgid "Humans of the Settled Systems. "
msgstr "개척 성계의 인간들이여. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_SSNN_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00472641
#: 020059DB/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_010_SSNNKiosk:02005A1E
msgctxt "00011E"
msgid "Warning, what you are about to hear is graphic in nature."
msgstr "경고합니다. 지금부터 들려드릴 내용은 매우 잔혹할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQIntroSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = CrowdMember05_Female
#. SoundFileID = 009C7623
#. Notes = Nervous / to CurrentKiosk, Face: Nervous
#: 020059DA/00000/SFTER_MQIntro_Scene_020_PostBroadcast:020059DF
msgctxt "00011F"
msgid "That sounded like a threat..."
msgstr "협박처럼 들렸어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00FBB2DD, 00CFB91B
#: 020059A1/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03:020059E0
msgctxt "000123"
msgid "When Aegis told me I'd be doing most of my assignments out in the black, the name seemed like a natural fit."
msgstr "이지스가 내 임무 대부분을 저 시꺼먼 우주에서 수행하게 될 거라고 했을 때, 그 이름이 딱 맞는 것 같았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00FBB2DD, 00CFB91B
#: 020059A1/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03:020059E0
msgctxt "000124"
msgid "In the old Yoruba culture, Yemoja's the goddess of rivers and seas. "
msgstr "옛 요루바 문화에서 예모자는 강과 바다의 여신이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BBE828
#: 020059A2/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04:02005A1F
msgctxt "000125"
msgid "Do you not spend a lot of time on land?"
msgstr "땅 위에서 지내는 시간이 많지 않은가 보네?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00FAE194, 00191A20
#: 020059A3/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04:02005A0E
msgctxt "000126"
msgid "You can get up to way more mischief on your own."
msgstr "혼자 있으면 훨씬 더 많은 사고를 칠 수 있거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00FAE194, 00191A20
#: 020059A3/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL04:02005A0E
msgctxt "000127"
msgid "No, but I don't mind it. I'm a people pleaser, but not a people person, if that makes sense."
msgstr "아니, 그래도 괜찮아. 남들 비위는 잘 맞추지만 사람들과 어울리는 걸 좋아하진 않거든. 무슨 말인지 알지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A08
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 008B528B
#: 020059A4/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03:02005A08
msgctxt "000128"
msgid "Now's not the time for small talk. But I'll tell you what, you find that cruise ship, and I'll give you the lore."
msgstr "지금은 잡담할 때가 아니야. 대신 이렇게 하자. 네가 그 유람선을 찾아내면, 그때 그 이야기를 들려줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A03
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00425EB9
#: 020059A5/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL03:02005A03
msgctxt "000129"
msgid "Where'd your Agent name come from?"
msgstr "요원명은 어디서 따온 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 004EBF33
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059AE/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A06
msgctxt "00012A"
msgid "So, here's the details. We're looking for a Trident Luxury Liner."
msgstr "자, 세부 사항은 이렇습니다. 우리는 트라이던트 사의 호화 유람선을 찾아야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FD
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0091127A
#: 020059A6/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01:020059FD
msgctxt "00012B"
msgid "But I've got a starchart of places we've already explored, so I can guide you a little if you go off course."
msgstr "하지만 이미 수색한 장소들의 항성 좌표가 있으니, 항로를 벗어나면 어느 정도 안내해 줄 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A598EB, 0037B9E6, 006DF993
#: 020059A7/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02:020059F7
msgctxt "00012C"
msgid "Finding that ship is the first piece of a much larger puzzle."
msgstr "그 함선을 찾는 건 훨씬 더 큰 퍼즐의 첫 조각이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A598EB, 0037B9E6, 006DF993
#: 020059A7/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02:020059F7
msgctxt "00012D"
msgid "We don't know who the Terran Armada is, or what they want."
msgstr "테란 함대가 누구인지, 뭘 원하는지 아직 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A598EB, 0037B9E6, 006DF993
#: 020059A7/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02:020059F7
msgctxt "00012E"
msgid "If you heard the broadcast, we could be dealing with a lot more than a missing cruise ship. "
msgstr "그 방송을 들으셨다면, 단순히 실종된 유람선 하나보다 훨씬 큰 문제일 수도 있다는 걸 아실 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C3852A
#: 020059A8/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL02:020059F1
msgctxt "00012F"
msgid "Is it going to be dangerous?"
msgstr "위험할까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059EA
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0028359B
#: 020059A9/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01:020059EA
msgctxt "000130"
msgid "I would, but I need to stay here and brief any new volunteers."
msgstr "저도 그러고 싶지만, 새로 오는 지원자들에게 상황을 설명하려면 여기 남아 있어야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E6FEB6
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059AB/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059DE
msgctxt "000131"
msgid "The Vanguard always answers the call."
msgstr "뱅가드는 언제나 부름에 응답합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002E0231
#: 020059AA/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL01:020059E4
msgctxt "000132"
msgid "Care to join me in searching for the ship?"
msgstr "저와 함께 그 함선을 찾아보시겠습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00CD4516
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059AD/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A0C
msgctxt "000133"
msgid "She's a big girl, but space is bigger, and it's definitely been a challenge to canvass the area."
msgstr "그 배가 큰 녀석이긴 하지만, 우주는 더 넓죠. 이 일대를 샅샅이 뒤지는 건 확실히 쉽지 않았습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A12
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0031A8D2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 지금까지 뭐라도 찾으셨습니까?
#: 020059AC/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A12
msgctxt "000134"
msgid "No, but every parsec we scan, we get that much closer to finding it."
msgstr "아뇨. 하지만 1파섹을 스캔할 때마다 그만큼 더 가까워지고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A00
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00622C2B
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059AF/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A00
msgctxt "000135"
msgid "Agent?"
msgstr "요원?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL00
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 006238EE
#: 020059B0/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL00:020059FA
msgctxt "000136"
msgid "If you're comfortable, I say go for it. There may be survivors on board, so time is of the essence."
msgstr "괜찮으시다면, 해보시는 게 좋겠습니다. 안에 생존자가 있을지도 모르니 시간이 중요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 007E3FDE, 00E183EF
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B1/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F4
msgctxt "000137"
msgid "A few ships have peeked around there, but haven't stuck their heads in."
msgstr "몇 척이 그 근처를 살짝 둘러보긴 했지만, 깊숙이 들어가진 않았습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 007E3FDE, 00E183EF
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B1/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F4
msgctxt "000138"
msgid "One place we haven't explored a ton is the asteroid field up ahead."
msgstr "아직 충분히 탐색하지 못한 곳이 하나 있는데, 바로 앞쪽의 소행성 지대입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00B41E16
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 그 방송을 듣고도 이 정도는 해야죠.
#: 020059B3/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059E7
msgctxt "000139"
msgid "Glad to hear it. We could use the extra set of eyes."
msgstr "다행이군요. 눈이 하나라도 더 필요하던 참입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004D3965
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B4/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059E1
msgctxt "00013A"
msgid "I'll help you."
msgstr "도와드리겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A04
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailRefused
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0010166D
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B8/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailRefused:02005A04
msgctxt "00013B"
msgid "All right, but it'll be easier if we work together."
msgstr "좋습니다. 다만 같이 움직이면 더 수월할 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00596F75
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B9/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059FE
msgctxt "00013C"
msgid "It's the least I can do after hearing that broadcast."
msgstr "그 방송을 듣고도 이 정도는 해야죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A20
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 002B5354
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 우주가 워낙 넓으니 놀랄 일도 아니죠.
#: 020059B5/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A20
msgctxt "00013D"
msgid "You're not wrong. We're mapping things as we go, so we need every volunteer we can get."
msgstr "틀린 말은 아닙니다. 저희도 움직이면서 지도를 만들어 가는 중이라, 지원자가 한 명이라도 더 필요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0099E888
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 분명 단서가 있을 텐데요.
#: 020059B6/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A0F
msgctxt "00013E"
msgid "We've made estimates based on the ship's trajectory and last known position. So, we're not totally blind."
msgstr "함선의 항적과 마지막 확인 위치를 바탕으로 추정해 두었습니다. 완전히 막막한 상황은 아닙니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A09
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00D98884
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059B7/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A09
msgctxt "00013F"
msgid "I just want the reward."
msgstr "보상만 받으면 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00BB581F, 00D62AB7
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 당신을 도우러 온 게 아닙니다.
#: 020059BA/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F8
msgctxt "000140"
msgid "And since you're already here, maybe the creds are enough to change your mind."
msgstr "이미 여기까지 오셨으니, 크레딧 정도면 마음을 바꾸기에 충분할지도 모르겠군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00BB581F, 00D62AB7
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 당신을 도우러 온 게 아닙니다.
#: 020059BA/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F8
msgctxt "000141"
msgid "That's too bad, but there IS a reward for finding it."
msgstr "유감이군요. 그래도 그 함선을 찾으면 보상이 있긴 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0016D7F4
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059C3/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F5
msgctxt "000142"
msgid "Surely you must have a lead."
msgstr "분명 단서가 있을 텐데요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00EEDFD2
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059BB/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059F2
msgctxt "000143"
msgid "I'm not here to help you."
msgstr "당신을 도우러 온 게 아닙니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A23F46
#. Notes = Ship dialogue no FaceFX / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059BD/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059E5
msgctxt "000144"
msgid "Welcome to the search party. My name's Agent Yemoja. Happy to have your help."
msgstr "수색대에 합류하신 걸 환영합니다. 저는 이지스 소속 예모자 요원입니다. 도와주신다니 기쁘군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059EC
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00CEC286
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 요원?
#: 020059C2/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059EC
msgctxt "000145"
msgid "I'm with Aegis. I know this isn't technically UC space, but given the circumstances, I don't think that matters."
msgstr "저는 이지스 소속입니다. 엄밀히 말해 여기가 식민지 연합 영역은 아니지만, 상황이 상황인 만큼 그건 중요하지 않다고 봅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A15
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_Hail
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0011140F
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059BE/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_Hail:02005A15
msgctxt "000146"
msgid "Unknown vessel, this is Agent Yemoja with Aegis. If you open your comms, I can brief you on the situation."
msgstr "미확인 함선, 여기는 이지스 소속 예모자 요원입니다. 통신을 열어 주시면 상황을 설명드리겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A14
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_Hail
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00FCCBD8
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059BE/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_Hail:02005A14
msgctxt "000147"
msgid "Hey, Vanguard, this is Agent Yemoja with Aegis. If you open your comms, I can brief you on the situation."
msgstr "뱅가드, 여기는 이지스 소속 예모자 요원입니다. 통신을 열어 주시면 상황을 설명드리겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 005DB02C, 0050EF0F
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 보상만 받으면 됩니다.
#: 020059C1/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059FB
msgctxt "000148"
msgid "But for both of us to get what we want, we'll first need to find that cruise ship."
msgstr "하지만 우리 둘 다 원하는 걸 얻으려면, 먼저 그 유람선을 찾아야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 005DB02C, 0050EF0F
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 보상만 받으면 됩니다.
#: 020059C1/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059FB
msgctxt "000149"
msgid "Fair play. I just want to find any survivors."
msgstr "공평하군요. 저는 그저 생존자를 찾고 싶을 뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A07
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 002DC2A9
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059BF/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A07
msgctxt "00014A"
msgid "Have you found anything so far?"
msgstr "지금까지 뭐라도 찾으셨습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A01
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C34486
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 도와드리겠습니다.
#: 020059C0/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A01
msgctxt "00014B"
msgid "Then you have my gratitude."
msgstr "그럼 감사드립니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005ABC
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 004CDA28
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02005AB7/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005ABC
msgctxt "00014C"
msgid "You're back. Did you change your mind?"
msgstr "돌아오셨군요. 마음이 바뀌셨습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A10
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0099E63F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059C8/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A10
msgctxt "00014D"
msgid "I'm not surprised, given how big space is."
msgstr "우주가 워낙 넓으니 놀랄 일도 아니죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A21
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0072CF5D
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 괜찮습니다. 이제 제가 있잖습니까.
#: 020059C7/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005A21
msgctxt "00014E"
msgid "We do. Let's hope that bravado pays off."
msgstr "그렇습니다. 그 배짱이 성과로 이어지길 바라죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0013EB55
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059C4/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059EF
msgctxt "000150"
msgid "Let me send you the telemetry data on where to scout. "
msgstr "정찰할 위치의 원격 측정 데이터를 보내드리겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 009C6EA1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 020059C6/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059E2
msgctxt "000151"
msgid "That's all right. Now you have me."
msgstr "괜찮습니다. 이제 제가 있잖습니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020059E8
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002ABB9D
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 뱅가드는 언제나 부름에 응답합니다.
#: 020059C5/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:020059E8
msgctxt "000152"
msgid "Don't I know it. You guys go above and beyond. Supra et Ultra."
msgstr "모를 리가 있나요. 여러분은 늘 더 높이, 더 너머로 나아가잖습니까. 수프라 엣 울트라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005A0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL00
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009D5D3E
#: 020059C9/00000/SFTER_SE_MQIntro_TL00:02005A0A
msgctxt "000153"
msgid "Should I dock with the ship or wait for backup?"
msgstr "그 함선에 도킹할까요, 아니면 지원을 기다릴까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005ABB
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 002125E1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 지금은 안 됩니다.
#: 02005AB8/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005ABB
msgctxt "000154"
msgid "That's too bad, but let me know if you change your mind."
msgstr "아쉽군요. 마음이 바뀌면 알려 주십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005ABA
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_MQIntro
#. SceneName = SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00B4172A
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02005AB9/00000/SFTER_HailTemplate_HailAccepted:02005ABA
msgctxt "000155"
msgid "I can't right now."
msgstr "지금은 안 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
