#: 0200FA2C/00006/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_06_System_GiveItem:0200FAF0
msgctxt "000245"
msgid "Confused. Definition of \"companion\" did not include internal hierarchy."
msgstr "혼란. \"동료\"의 정의에 내부 서열은 포함되지 않았음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FADF
