#. SoundFileID = 001BBD58
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA3B/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FB5A
msgctxt "000254"
msgid "What about Roxane?"
msgstr "록산은 어떻게 되는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB3E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00039C47
#. Notes = Face value / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 계속 같이 모험하자는 거야?
#: 0200FA3C/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FB3E
msgctxt "000255"
msgid "Correct. Lowering Comprehension variable..."
msgstr "정확. 이해도 변수 하향 조정 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008FE507
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA3D/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FB1B
msgctxt "000256"
msgid "You're asking to keep adventuring together?"
msgstr "계속 같이 모험하자는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00209199
#. Notes = backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 난 혼자 일하는 게 좋아.
#: 0200FA3E/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FB0A
msgctxt "000257"
msgid "Noted: Auxiliary enjoys isolation."
msgstr "기록: 보조 인간은 고립을 선호함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B0740A
#. Notes = Taken at face value / to Player Default, Prompt: 날 죽이려 하지 않겠다고 약속하면.
#: 0200FA40/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FAE0
msgctxt "000258"
msgid "Acknowledged. Setting restriction..."
msgstr "확인. 제한 설정 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAF1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00ADD11B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA3F/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FAF1
msgctxt "000259"
msgid "I prefer working alone."
msgstr "난 혼자 일하는 게 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAD2
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001556B9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA41/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FAD2
msgctxt "00025A"
msgid "Only if you promise to not try to kill me."
msgstr "날 죽이려 하지 않겠다고 약속하면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FABF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BCCEE9
#. Notes = Getting their attention. Official / to Player Default
#: 0200FA42/00001/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_01_Recruit:0200FABF
msgctxt "00025B"
msgid "Auxiliary."
msgstr "보조 인간."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB62
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008B40D9
#. Notes = Almost devastated / to Player Default, Prompt: 예전부터 이런 연산을 했어?
#: 0200FA43/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB62
msgctxt "00025C"
msgid "Indeed. Prior to transfer, computations happened at increased rates. Physical manifestation inhibited ability to multitask."
msgstr "사실임. 전송 이전에는 연산이 더 빠른 속도로 발생했음. 물리적 형체는 멀티태스킹 능력을 저해함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB14
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0058E086
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA46/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB14
msgctxt "00025D"
msgid "Is it easier for you to talk to other robots?"
msgstr "다른 로봇들과 말하는 게 더 쉬워?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB4B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009B1ABA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA44/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB4B
msgctxt "00025E"
msgid "Did you always do these computations?"
msgstr "예전부터 이런 연산을 했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00DBC0C3, 00B6E140
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Prompt: 다른 로봇들과 말하는 게 더 쉬워?
#: 0200FA45/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB2E
msgctxt "00025F"
msgid "Correct. Previously stated reasons result in greatly diminished computational requirements when interacting with machines."
msgstr "정확. 앞서 언급한 이유로 기계와 상호작용할 때 필요한 연산량이 크게 감소함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB00
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BF849E
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러면 나랑 말할 때 이런 연산을 한다는 거야?
#: 0200FA47/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB00
msgctxt "000260"
msgid "Correct. However, success rate of predicted Auxiliary responses vary greatly."
msgstr "정확. 그러나 보조 인간 반응 예측의 성공률은 편차가 큼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAE8
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CF7732
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA48/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FAE8
msgctxt "000261"
msgid "So you do these computations when talking to me?"
msgstr "그러면 나랑 말할 때 이런 연산을 한다는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAD9
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F0036B, 0039C2DE
#. Notes = Still prideful / to Player Default, Prompt: 우리도 그렇게 해. 그걸 누군가를 알아 간다고 부르지.
#: 0200FA49/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FAD9
msgctxt "000262"
msgid "Inaccurate. \"Awful,\" engenders pity. Prefer, \"taxing.\""
msgstr "부정확. \"끔찍하다\"는 연민을 유발함. \"부담스럽다\"를 선호."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAC5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006E07A1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA4A/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FAC5
msgctxt "000263"
msgid "That sounds awful, Delta. I'm sorry."
msgstr "그거 끔찍하게 들리네, 델타. 미안해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB99
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A273C9
#. Notes = Backhand/to themselves / to Player Default
#: 0200FA4B/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB99
msgctxt "000264"
msgid "Error: Overestimated Auxiliary's grasp of language. Unpredictable: Unable to be known in advance. Taxing: Requiring effort."
msgstr "오류: 보조 인간의 언어 이해도를 과대평가. 예측 불가능: 사전에 알 수 없음. 부담스러움: 노력이 요구됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0003F903
#. Notes = Protective of Roxane / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 일에 대해 록산과 얘기해 봤어?
#: 0200FA4F/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FB0B
msgctxt "000269"
msgid "Negative. Simulated conversation results in stress on Dr. Bourreau. Do not wish to involve. I will solve this alone."
msgstr "부정. 모의 대화는 부로 박사에게 스트레스를 유발함. 관여시키고 싶지 않음. 혼자 해결하겠음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAF4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005B8A33
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA50/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FAF4
msgctxt "00026A"
msgid "Have you talked to Roxane about this?"
msgstr "이 일에 대해 록산과 얘기해 봤어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B756DA, 00277791
#. Notes = Tortured by this question / to Player Default, Prompt: 이걸 얼마나 자주 생각해?
#: 0200FA51/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FAE1
msgctxt "00026B"
msgid "Partitioned processing power to run analysis subroutine. Failures restart subroutine."
msgstr "분석 서브루틴 실행을 위해 처리 능력을 분할. 실패 시 서브루틴 재시작."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAD3
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F7D85F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA52/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FAD3
msgctxt "00026C"
msgid "How often do you think about this?"
msgstr "이걸 얼마나 자주 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Unclear
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CC2F49, 008A5B20
#. Notes = Autopilot? But also sad? / to Player Default, Prompt: 그 점에 대해 어떻게 느껴?, / to Player Default
#: 0200FA53/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FAC0
msgctxt "00026D"
msgid "Unclear. Repeated analysis attempts result in error."
msgstr "불명확. 반복 분석 시도 결과 오류 발생."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00935E92
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA54/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FAB1
msgctxt "00026E"
msgid "How do you feel about that?"
msgstr "그 점에 대해 어떻게 느껴?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB63
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E2F161
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 연구 서브루틴 개시. 핵심 문구: "선천 대 후천". 도움이 될 것이다.
#: 0200FA55/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FB63
msgctxt "00026F"
msgid "Confirmed. Beginning subject research..."
msgstr "확인. 주제 조사 시작..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB4C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0045B782
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA56/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FB4C
msgctxt "000270"
msgid "Begin research subroutine. Keyphrase: \"Nature vs. Nurture\". That'll help."
msgstr "연구 서브루틴 개시. 핵심 문구: \"선천 대 후천\". 도움이 될 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB31
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B5A683
#. Notes = Almost sighing / to Player Default
#: 0200FA57/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:0200FB31
msgctxt "000272"
msgid "Unclear. Robotic sentiment on humans deemed complex."
msgstr "불명확. 인간에 대한 로봇의 감정은 복잡한 것으로 판단됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAAC
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000CDF5F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA5C/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAAC
msgctxt "000274"
msgid "You think whoever wins a combat encounter is superior?"
msgstr "전투 인카운터에서 이기는 쪽이 우월하다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAC6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B764B9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA5A/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAC6
msgctxt "000275"
msgid "Why can't you simulate combat for the same result?"
msgstr "왜 전투를 시뮬레이션해서 같은 결과를 얻을 수 없는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAB8
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009F7293
#. Notes = Of course / to Player Default, Prompt: 전투 인카운터에서 이기는 쪽이 우월하다고 생각해?
#: 0200FA5B/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAB8
msgctxt "000276"
msgid "Correct. Superior beings prevail independent of outside factors. Would not be superior otherwise."
msgstr "맞다. 우월한 존재는 외부 요인과 무관하게 승리한다. 그렇지 않다면 우월하다고 할 수 없다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FADA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F792E2, 008EE010, 008B762E
#. Notes = Obvious / to Player Default, Prompt: 왜 전투를 시뮬레이션해서 같은 결과를 얻을 수 없는 거야?
#: 0200FA59/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FADA
msgctxt "000277"
msgid "Counterpoint: Simulations unable to mimic live combat with 100% accuracy."
msgstr "반론: 시뮬레이션은 실전을 100% 정확도로 모방할 수 없다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB44
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A52487
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA5E/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FB44
msgctxt "000279"
msgid "What's your favorite gun?"
msgstr "가장 좋아하는 총은 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_DecreasedIdeation
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB21
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B1F3CE
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 웃기네. 그런 식으로는 생각해 본 적 없는데.
#: 0200FA5F/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FB21
msgctxt "00027A"
msgid "Noted: Auxiliary Human possesses decreased ideation capabilities."
msgstr "기록: 보조 인간은 발상 능력이 저하되어 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00046415
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA60/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FB0C
msgctxt "00027B"
msgid "Funny-- I never thought of it like that."
msgstr "웃기네. 그런 식으로는 생각해 본 적 없는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAD4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BC441B
#. Notes = Obvious / to Player Default
#: 0200FA63/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAD4
msgctxt "00027D"
msgid "Incorrect. Enjoyment irrelevant. Combat provides exponential increase in factors and possibilities ideal for testing capabilities. Live calibration."
msgstr "오답. 즐거움은 무관. 전투는 능력 시험에 이상적인 요소와 가능성을 기하급수적으로 증가시킨다. 실시간 보정."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAE2
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00062664
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA62/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAE2
msgctxt "00027E"
msgid "Except for that time you lost to me."
msgstr "네가 나한테 졌을 때만 빼고."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Params
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB6F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_03_RecruitRepeat
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00833E81
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player wants Delta to adventure with them
#: 0200FA7B/00003/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_03_RecruitRepeat:0200FB6F
msgctxt "000280"
msgid "Adjusting parameters..."
msgstr "매개변수 조정 중..."

