#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009CF071, 00EFC485
#. Notes = Shaking head / to Player Default, Prompt: 왜 스스로를 개조해서 개선할 수 없는 거야?
#: 0200FA91/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FAAE
msgctxt "0002A6"
msgid "Incapable. Ability to self-modify limited in standard robotic creation."
msgstr "불가. 기본등급 로봇 제작 방식에서는 자가 개조 능력이 제한됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BBE8EC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA92/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FB5E
msgctxt "0002A7"
msgid "Why can't they modify themselves to improve?"
msgstr "왜 스스로를 개조해서 개선할 수 없는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB49
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006E7F21, 00739B64
#. Notes = You'd think, but you'd be wrong / to Player Default, Prompt: 하지만 넌 개선되잖아. 그럼 넌 다르다는 뜻이야?, Backhand / to Player Default
#: 0200FA93/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FB49
msgctxt "0002A8"
msgid "Misconception. Have not improved. X-Tech integration has increased limits exponentially higher than standard robots."
msgstr "오해. 개선된 것이 아님. X-테크 통합으로 한계치가 기본등급 로봇보다 기하급수적으로 높아졌을 뿐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB2A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D3E79E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA94/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FB2A
msgctxt "0002A9"
msgid "But, you improve. Does that mean you're different?"
msgstr "하지만 넌 개선되잖아. 그럼 넌 다르다는 뜻이야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Compliment
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB12
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
