#: 0200FA95/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FB12
msgctxt "0002AA"
msgid "Compliment given begrudgingly."
msgstr "마지못해 칭찬한 것으로 확인."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAFC
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
