#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA96/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FAFC
msgctxt "0002AB"
msgid "That sounded like you just gave humans a compliment."
msgstr "방금 인간을 칭찬한 것처럼 들렸는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAC3
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F95BDC
#. Notes = Shaking head / to Player Default
#: 0200FA99/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FAC3
msgctxt "0002AE"
msgid "Predominately. Only observable machine flaw is predisposition to limitation."
msgstr "대체로 그렇다. 관찰 가능한 유일한 기계 결함은 한계에 묶이는 성향이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAB6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004B475E, 001CFF32
