#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140A_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00972424, 000303A3
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional and informative / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Friendly, yes professional and informative / Friendly / to Player Default
#: 02015672/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140A_VOID:0201567F
msgctxt "00048C"
msgid "As you can imagine, with the rise of the Terrans, it is our sworn duty to uncover their plans and put a stop to it, whatever it may be."
msgstr "짐작하시겠지만, 테란이 부상한 지금 그들이 무슨 계획을 꾸미든 밝혀내고 저지하는 것이 우리의 맹세한 의무입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140A_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00972424, 000303A3
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional and informative / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Friendly, yes professional and informative / Friendly / to Player Default
#: 02015672/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140A_VOID:0201567F
msgctxt "00048D"
msgid "As VOID, we are representatives for those who watch over the Settled Systems."
msgstr "VOID로서, 우리는 개척 성계를 지켜보는 이들을 대표합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001068E1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015674/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201567D
msgctxt "00048E"
msgid "That told me nothing. "
msgstr "아무 설명도 안 됐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00C83099
#. Notes = Starting line for if the player leaves the conversation and then comes back. A bit annoyed the Player ran off. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02015675/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201567C
msgctxt "00048F"
msgid "Have you come to listen now?"
msgstr "이제는 들으러 온 건가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 006F986E, 00434870
#. Notes = Matter-of-fact.Last line Player said: "I first deserve to know who you people are." / Serious / to Radha, Face: Serious, Still matter-of-fact, but a little annoyed / Suspicious / to Radha, Face: Suspicious
#: 02015676/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201567B
msgctxt "000490"
msgid "Now, the Terran?"
msgstr "그럼, 테란은?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201567B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 006F986E, 00434870
#. Notes = Matter-of-fact.Last line Player said: "I first deserve to know who you people are." / Serious / to Radha, Face: Serious, Still matter-of-fact, but a little annoyed / Suspicious / to Radha, Face: Suspicious
#: 02015676/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201567B
msgctxt "000491"
msgid "We are VOID. The Veterans of Interstellar Deployment."
msgstr "우리는 VOID다. 성간 파병 퇴역 군인회."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015FDA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00B7BFA1
#. Notes = A Blocking Hello that's said during the hacking competition.
#: 02015EF8:02015FDA
msgctxt "000497"
msgid "Pestering attempt noted. Conversation denied."
msgstr "성가시게 굴려는 시도 확인. 대화 거부."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F69
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 006D1205
#. Notes = A Blocking Hello that's said when Roxane is within eyesight and they are approaching
#: 02015EF8:02015F69
msgctxt "000498"
msgid "Recommending Auxiliary relay challenge to Dr. Borreau. More likely to agree."
msgstr "보조 릴레이 도전 과제를 보로 박사에게 제안하기를 권장. 동의 가능성 더 높음."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_AskAway
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F36
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 0061674D
#. Notes = Transition line to other question options / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0202AD27/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane:02015F36
msgctxt "00049A"
msgid "Ask away."
msgstr "마음껏 물어봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F01
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00ACDE0F, 0086AAD3
#. Notes = A little pompous/academic. "What a waste" / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 『종의 기원』을 좋아한다면 『외계생물학의 역사』는 어떻게 생각해?
#: 02015E80/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F01
msgctxt "0004A5"
msgid "I found it quite messy. The broad topic of the evolution of all life on Earth was challenging enough for Darwin."
msgstr "꽤 산만하다고 느꼈어요. 지구의 모든 생명 진화라는 방대한 주제는 다윈에게도 충분히 어려웠을 테니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F42
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00DB3786
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E81/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F42
msgctxt "0004A6"
msgid "If you like The Origin of Species, what do you think of History of Xenobiology?"
msgstr "『종의 기원』을 좋아한다면 『외계생물학의 역사』는 어떻게 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F71
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00C5A516, 00D0333C
#. Notes = Justifying. A little annoyed that they have to do this / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant, Prompt: 연구서는 아니야?
#: 02015E82/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F71
msgctxt "0004A7"
msgid "While I enjoy research, I understand my life can't just be work."
msgstr "연구를 좋아하긴 하지만, 인생이 일뿐일 수는 없다는 것도 알아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015EFB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00DE4464
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E83/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015EFB
msgctxt "0004A8"
msgid "Not a research book?"
msgstr "연구서는 아니야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0041D74C, 00079BC0
#. Notes = Almost annoyed by the joke they've heard probably 1000 times? / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 왠지 네가 프랑켄슈타인을 제일 좋아한다는 게 어울리네., Justifying, and also little excited to talk about their favorite book / Confident / to Player Default
#: 02015E88/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F1D
msgctxt "0004AC"
msgid "The parallel is not lost on me, if that's what you're implying."
msgstr "네가 그걸 암시하는 거라면, 그 유사점은 나도 알고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F08
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 0091BD27, 0036A5D3, 007F75DC
#. Notes = Correcting / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 다윈한테서 새로운 정보를 많이 얻었을 것 같진 않아. 그 책은 몇 세기나 됐잖아., Justifying, attempting to make the player as fascinated as they are / Neutral / to Player Default, Considering it / Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking
#: 02015E86/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F08
msgctxt "0004AD"
msgid "I view it less as an academic record and more as a historical one."
msgstr "저는 그걸 학술 기록이라기보다 역사 기록에 가깝게 봐요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F56
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C8E48A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E89/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F56
msgctxt "0004AE"
msgid "For some reason, Frankenstein being your favorite sounds fitting."
msgstr "왠지 네가 프랑켄슈타인을 제일 좋아한다는 게 어울리네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F12
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00970198, 001AC9F0, 0064DF1D
#. Notes = Loves her dad / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 네 아버지도 그 노력을 고마워하셨을 거야., Kind of embarrassed by this / Grateful / to Player Default, Smiling at the memory / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 02015E92/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F12
msgctxt "0004AF"
msgid "He was a dad. Loved anything his kid made."
msgstr "아빠였잖아. 자기 아이가 만든 거라면 뭐든 좋아했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F07
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 002154DB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E8B/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F07
msgctxt "0004B0"
msgid "How was it supposed to help?"
msgstr "그게 어떻게 도움이 되게 하려고 했는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F11
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00C2D219, 00BA3FE1
#. Notes = Ugh, how stupid is this laughing at herself / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 뭐가 문제였는데?
#: 02015E8C/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F11
msgctxt "0004B1"
msgid "I didn't account for the uneven terrain and the amount of particles in the air."
msgstr "고르지 않은 지형하고 공기 중 입자량을 계산에 넣지 않았어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F65
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 007F7038
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E87/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_04_TopLevel_Personal_2:02015F65
msgctxt "0004B2"
msgid "I doubt you got a lot of new information from Darwin, that book is centuries old."
msgstr "다윈한테서 새로운 정보를 많이 얻었을 것 같진 않아. 그 책은 몇 세기나 됐잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F27
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00EAEC00, 00DE85E9, 003FCB57
#. Notes = Half smile, sarcasm / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 하지만 지금은 이렇게까지 발전했잖아., Catching herself / Apologetic / to Player Default, Face: Apologetic
#: 02015E90/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F27
msgctxt "0004B3"
msgid "Yes, look."
msgstr "그래, 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F13
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00471056
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02015E91/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F13
msgctxt "0004B4"
msgid "But look how far you've come now."
msgstr "하지만 지금은 이렇게까지 발전했잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F4A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
