#. Notes = Nodding / to Player Default, Prompt: 여기 있는 건 뭐든 써도 돼?
#: 02016635/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:02016685
msgctxt "000619"
msgid "Correct. Corpse must speak again, no additional requirements."
msgstr "맞음. 시체가 다시 말하면 됨, 추가 조건 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201668A
