#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016636/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:0201668A
msgctxt "00061A"
msgid "Can we use anything here?"
msgstr "여기 있는 건 뭐든 써도 돼?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016687
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00A7F0A3, 00C19232
#. Notes = Justifying/Logical / to Player Default, Prompt: 그런 걸 할 거라고 왜 말 안 했어?
#: 02016640/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:02016687
msgctxt "00061B"
msgid "Concerned with reaction to information."
msgstr "정보에 대한 반응 우려."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016683
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00F807EC, 0004ACD2
#. Notes = Absolutely, 100% believes this / to Player Default, Prompt: 정말 이 사람들을 되살릴 수 있다고 생각해?
#: 02016637/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:02016683
msgctxt "00061C"
msgid "Correct. Qualifications for life relatively simple."
msgstr "맞음. 생명의 자격 조건은 비교적 단순함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201667A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00518F53, 005C9E37, 00744630
#. Notes = Don't be ridiculous / to Player Default, Prompt: 누가 우리가 이 사람들을 죽였다는 걸 알아내면 어떡하지?
#: 02016642/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:0201667A
msgctxt "00061D"
msgid "Unlikely. Terran Database identified Santos Homestead as relatively isolated."
msgstr "가능성 낮음. 테란 데이터베이스에서 산토스 정착지를 비교적 고립된 곳으로 식별."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016697
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0039CF7F, 00C2356A
#. Notes = Almost shrugging. Doesn't care how long it takes. They could work on this until the end of time and be satisfied / to Player Default, Prompt: 시간이 얼마나 있어?
#: 02016633/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:02016697
msgctxt "00061E"
msgid "Indefinite. Until challenge completion."
msgstr "무기한. 도전 과제 완료까지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016692
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 003686FF
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 준비되면 시작하죠.
#: 02016648/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:02016692
msgctxt "00061F"
msgid "Confirmed. Noted: Analyze moral framework of Auxiliary Human. Compare divergence from average Human..."
msgstr "확인. 기록: 보조 인간의 도덕 체계 분석. 평균 인간과의 차이 비교..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016694
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 001B2E49, 00EFD4B9
#. Notes = Leading to conclusion / to Player Default
#: 0201663E/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:02016694
msgctxt "000620"
msgid "Searched more human texts. Discovered fascination with dichotomy of life and death."
msgstr "인간 문헌 추가 검색. 삶과 죽음의 이분법에 대한 집착 발견."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201669A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 007C0EAE
#. Notes = Official / to Player Default
#: 0201663D/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:0201669A
msgctxt "000621"
msgid "Third Challenge: Make your corpse speak again."
msgstr "세 번째 도전 과제: 네 시체가 다시 말하게 만들어라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00C20B9D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201663C/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:020166A0
msgctxt "000622"
msgid "You can't be serious."
msgstr "진심일 리가 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00162FB4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201663A/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:020166AE
msgctxt "000623"
msgid "This is impossible. No one's been able to revitalize a corpse successfully before."
msgstr "이건 불가능해. 지금까지 시체 소생에 성공한 사람은 아무도 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201667D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00213507
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201664B/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:0201667D
msgctxt "000624"
msgid "I can't believe it! You just shot those people in cold blood!"
msgstr "믿을 수가 없어! 방금 그 사람들을 냉혹하게 쏴 죽였잖아!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016680
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0062A2CC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016641/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:02016680
msgctxt "000625"
msgid "Why didn't you tell me we were doing that?"
msgstr "그런 걸 할 거라고 왜 말 안 했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016676
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 002654F7
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 이건 불가능해. 지금까지 시체 소생에 성공한 사람은 아무도 없었어.
#: 02016639/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:02016676
msgctxt "000626"
msgid "Counterpoint: All tasks begin as impossible. Only requires correct combination of minds and methods."
msgstr "반론: 모든 과제는 불가능에서 시작함. 필요한 것은 지성과 방법의 올바른 조합뿐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0064FD4A, 009AB270
#. Notes = DUH "What else was I supposed to do?" / to Player Default, Prompt: 대체 왜 그런 거야?
#: 02016644/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:020166AB
msgctxt "000627"
msgid "Required 2 dead bodies for Third Challenge. Fresh. Minimal damage to flesh."
msgstr "세 번째 도전 과제에는 시체 2구 필요. 신선함. 육체 손상 최소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00F63592, 00949138
#. Notes = Deadpan / to Player Default, Prompt: 우리가 그들을 상대로 신 행세를 할 수 있게 무고한 사람들을 쐈잖아.
#: 0201663B/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:020166A6
msgctxt "000628"
msgid "I can only be serious. Dr. Bourreau removed comedic protocols."
msgstr "나는 진지할 수밖에 없음. 부로 박사가 희극 프로토콜을 제거."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
