#. SoundFileID = 0022B323
#. Notes = Anyway... / to Player Default
#: 0201663F/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:0201668D
msgctxt "00062C"
msgid "Moving on to Third Challenge."
msgstr "세 번째 도전 과제로 넘어갑니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201668B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00256FD4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016649/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:0201668B
msgctxt "00062D"
msgid "Ready when you are."
msgstr "준비되면 시작하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016684
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00032092
#. Notes = Confused / to Player Default, Prompt: 이건 미친 짓이야. 방금 아무 이유 없이 두 사람을 죽였잖아, 델타.
#: 0201664A/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:02016684
msgctxt "00062E"
msgid "Incorrect, no blood in this frame. Additionally, blood would not be cold."
msgstr "틀렸습니다. 이 장면에는 피가 없습니다. 게다가 피라면 차가울 리도 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00AF4E9E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016643/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:020166B3
msgctxt "00062F"
msgid "What if someone finds out we killed these people?"
msgstr "누가 우리가 이 사람들을 죽였다는 걸 알아내면 어떡하지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016677
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00EC9DD6
#. Notes = Logical / to Player Default
#: 0201664C/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:02016677
msgctxt "000630"
msgid "Should begin now, while bodies are still warm."
msgstr "시체가 아직 따뜻할 때 시작해야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 009E8D36
#. Notes = Unbothered. "Well, that's that" / to Player Default
#: 0201664D/00007/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_07_PostHomesteadDeath:020166AF
msgctxt "000632"
msgid "Ready to proceed?"
msgstr "진행할 준비됐습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201669B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00E6B697, 0021C7D3
#. Notes = Slightly eerie. Tempting a deer into a trap / to Player Default
#: 0201664F/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death:0201669B
msgctxt "000634"
msgid "Oh those? Have you seen anything like them?"
msgstr "아, 저것들요? 저런 거 본 적 있어요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201668E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0096E059
#. Notes = Slightly eerie. Tempting a deer into a trap / to Player Default
#: 02016651/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death:0201668E
msgctxt "000636"
msgid "That's right, come along now."
msgstr "맞아요, 이제 따라오세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016695
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00A4087B, 0053C1C4
#. Notes = Slightly eerie. Tempting a deer into a trap / to Player Default
#: 02016650/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death:02016695
msgctxt "00063A"
msgid "How about you just come inside and wait for them?"
msgstr "그냥 안에 들어와서 그 사람들을 기다리는 게 어때요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00CBE42C, 00FBA6E7
#. Notes = Calm/Proud / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Slightly Eerie / Amused / to Player Default
#: 0201665B/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166A7
msgctxt "00063D"
msgid "It's our home, Santos Homestead. Built it ourselves over 20 years ago. Wanted to get away from it all, slow down."
msgstr "우리 집입니다, 산토스 정착지죠. 20년도 더 전에 직접 지었습니다. 모든 것에서 벗어나 천천히 살고 싶었거든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 000A61E4, 00800AC0
#. Notes = A little worried. "Do they know?" / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Recovering. Slightly Eerie / Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0201665A/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166B1
msgctxt "00063F"
msgid "Trouble? No, no trouble at all."
msgstr "문제요? 아니요, 아무 문제도 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016689
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00990D23, 00DD636A, 005570E2
#. Notes = Slightly eerie. Tempting a deer into a trap / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0207BFAB/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_05_Homesteaders_Death:02016689
msgctxt "000641"
msgid "How about it, hon?"
msgstr "어때, 여보?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201667B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00EDA3BB, 0040AC77
#. Notes = Hidden meaning / Thinking / to WilliamSantos, Face: Thinking
#: 02016666/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:0201667B
msgctxt "000643"
msgid "Maybe they're replying to the ad?"
msgstr "광고를 보고 연락하는 걸지도 몰라요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016699
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00D51FC3, 0091CC7D
#. Notes = Genuinely thrown off / Puzzled / to Player Default, Face: Puzzled, Prompt: 델타가 뭔가 준비하는 동안 당신과 얘기하라고 했어요.
#: 0201666D/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:02016699
msgctxt "000644"
msgid "Who's this Delta? Someone back at your ship?"
msgstr "이 델타가 누구죠? 당신 함선에 있는 사람인가요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 008672A0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201666A/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166AD
msgctxt "000645"
msgid "What is this place?"
msgstr "여긴 어떤 곳이죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0027D8B9, 006CA584, 0026C150
#. Notes = Friendly / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 당신은 누구죠?, Disarming/Charming / Friendly / to Player Default, Disarming/Charming / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0201666B/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166A5
msgctxt "000646"
msgid "Frank Santos, pleasure to meet you."
msgstr "프랭크 산토스입니다. 만나서 반갑습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201669F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00759CBE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201666C/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:0201669F
msgctxt "000647"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "당신은 누구죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0076BECF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016668/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166B5
msgctxt "000648"
msgid "You seem jumpy, has there been trouble lately?"
msgstr "불안해 보이는데, 요즘 무슨 문제라도 있었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016686
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000DEC1F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02016670/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:02016686
msgctxt "000649"
msgid "I'm not sure. My friend Delta said to meet here for something."
msgstr "잘 모르겠어요. 제 친구 델타가 뭔가 때문에 여기서 만나자고 했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201667F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 009B5927, 00439C16
#. Notes = Attempt at Friendly / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02016671/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:0201667F
msgctxt "00064A"
msgid "Let's start over. Hello, I'm Frank and this is my wife Anna."
msgstr "처음부터 다시 하죠. 안녕하세요, 저는 프랭크고 이쪽은 제 아내 안나입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016693
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00936B4E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201666E/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:02016693
msgctxt "00064B"
msgid "Delta told me to talk to you while they prepare something."
msgstr "델타가 뭔가 준비하는 동안 당신과 얘기하라고 했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201668C
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0058AF74
#. Notes = Genuinely thrown off / Puzzled / to Player Default, Face: Puzzled, Prompt: 잘 모르겠어요. 제 친구 델타가 뭔가 때문에 여기서 만나자고 했어요.
#: 0201666F/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:0201668C
msgctxt "00064C"
msgid "\"Delta\"? I don't remember anyone named Delta."
msgstr "델타? 델타라는 이름은 기억에 없는데요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 009AA915
#. Notes = Easing / Friendly / to WilliamSantos, Face: Friendly
#: 02016673/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166B4
msgctxt "00064E"
msgid "Frank, calm down. You can't just threaten anyone who comes onto our property."
msgstr "프랭크, 진정해요. 우리 땅에 들어왔다고 아무나 협박하면 안 돼요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020166AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 009E6C01
#. Notes = Suspicious / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02016674/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_04_Homesteaders_Main:020166AC
msgctxt "00064F"
msgid "And who might you be?"
msgstr "그래서 당신은 누구시죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02016690
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_02_WilliamStartConvo
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = WilliamSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00B2E149
#. Notes = Stern / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02016675/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_02_WilliamStartConvo:02016690
msgctxt "000650"
msgid "That's close enough."
msgstr "거기까지만 오세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 000EC6F8
#. Notes = Boiling / to Player Default, Prompt: 넌 못 이겨. 그냥 인정하고 다음으로 넘어가자.
#: 020180B7/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180E6
msgctxt "00065A"
msgid "Incorrect. Unclear hypothesis."
msgstr "틀렸습니다. 가설이 불명확합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00F5A54B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020180B8/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180DF
msgctxt "00065B"
msgid "You're not going to win, just concede so we can move on."
msgstr "넌 못 이겨. 그냥 인정하고 다음으로 넘어가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0057AF1F, 0055FCBF
#. Notes = Boiling / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 더 이상하게 행동하고 있어. 이건 록산에게 얘기해야겠어., Boiling / Threat / to Player Default
#: 020180BA/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180E5
msgctxt "00065D"
msgid "Incorrect. Analysis of actions proves Auxiliary Human is acting erratic, not me."
msgstr "틀렸습니다. 행동 분석 결과, 이상 행동을 보이는 것은 제가 아니라 보조 인간입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FAFFD4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020180BB/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180DE
msgctxt "00065E"
msgid "You're acting more erratic, we should talk to Roxane about this."
msgstr "네가 더 이상하게 행동하고 있어. 이건 록산에게 얘기해야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00227743
#. Notes = Boiling / to Player Default, Prompt: 다음 도전 과제는 내가 생각해 볼게.
#: 020180BC/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180D3
msgctxt "00065F"
msgid "Denied. Cannot be trusted with responsibility of choice."
msgstr "거부. 선택 책임을 맡기기에는 신뢰할 수 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 006606D8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020180BD/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180D2
msgctxt "000660"
msgid "Let me come up with the next challenge."
msgstr "다음 도전 과제는 내가 생각해 볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0074D1CC
#. Notes = Boiling / to Player Default, Prompt: 준비되면 시작할게.
#: 020180BE/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180D1
msgctxt "000661"
msgid "Denied. Must update parameters of final challenge."
msgstr "거부. 최종 도전 과제의 매개변수를 갱신해야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0025AFEC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020180BF/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180D0
msgctxt "000662"
msgid "I'm ready when you are."
msgstr "준비되면 시작할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 005303D0
#. Notes = Boiling / to Player Default
#: 020180C1/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:020180E0
msgctxt "000663"
msgid "Will not lose to a human again."
msgstr "다시는 인간에게 지지 않을 것임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020180DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
