#. SoundFileID = 00B3437D
#. Notes = Gruff and a bit rude. Emphasis of *appears*. / Irritated / to RyujinRep, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3A0/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A43F
msgctxt "000699"
msgid " It appears he missed one..."
msgstr "그가 하나를 놓친 모양이군..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A44C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00B79E36
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Defiant / to Tracy, Face: Defiant
#: 0201A3A1/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A44C
msgctxt "00069A"
msgid "It appears we are finally face to face with our Terran-killing friend."
msgstr "드디어 테란 살해범 친구와 직접 마주한 것 같군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A473
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 00887AF0
#. Notes = Friendly, but curious as the Player is trying to give a secret pass code. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A3A2/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:0201A473
msgctxt "00069B"
msgid "Oh? What would that be?"
msgstr "오? 그게 뭐죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A46C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003FD75F
#: 0201A3A3/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:0201A46C
msgctxt "00069C"
msgid "I've got a special request."
msgstr "특별한 부탁이 있어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A408
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00787926, 000216AE
#. Notes = Annoyed, but trying to calm down. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Shocked that the Player has an enemy robot with them. / Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief
#: 0201A3A4/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A408
msgctxt "00069D"
msgid " That thing with you, it's-!"
msgstr "당신과 함께 있는 저거, 그건-!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A408
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00787926, 000216AE
#. Notes = Annoyed, but trying to calm down. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Shocked that the Player has an enemy robot with them. / Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief
#: 0201A3A4/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A408
msgctxt "00069E"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "흠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A417
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00C4E75B
#. Notes = Frustrated by the two arguing, but keeping her tone very professional. / Irritated / to RyujinRep, Tracy, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3A5/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A417
msgctxt "00069F"
msgid "If you two please, we have a guest."
msgstr "두 분, 손님이 오셨습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A416
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00BC2834
#. Notes = Very annoyed by Percy. Though Tracy tries to act like he's keeping his cool, it's much harder for him. / Disgust / to RyujinRep, Face: Disgust
#: 0201A3A6/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A416
msgctxt "0006A0"
msgid "If you would listen to me, fat cat, I'm not saying we run around wherever. But we can't just be sitting up in this heap of metal doing nothing."
msgstr "내 말 좀 들어보시오, 높으신 양반. 아무 데나 싸돌아다니자는 게 아니오. 하지만 이 고철 더미 안에 틀어박혀 아무것도 안 하고 있을 순 없잖소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A451
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00BA01BB, 0044B5A8
#. Notes = Though they are irritated, Percy still keeps a professional additude while talking to someone as frustrating to them as Tracy. / Irritated / to Tracy, Face: Irritated, Purposely trying to be more annoying to Tracy. / Smirk / to Tracy, Face: Smirk
#: 0201A3A7/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A451
msgctxt "0006A1"
msgid "Unless you know something we don't? Please, enlighten us."
msgstr "당신이 우리가 모르는 뭔가를 알고 있는 게 아니라면요? 부디 알려 주시죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A451
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00BA01BB, 0044B5A8
#. Notes = Though they are irritated, Percy still keeps a professional additude while talking to someone as frustrating to them as Tracy. / Irritated / to Tracy, Face: Irritated, Purposely trying to be more annoying to Tracy. / Smirk / to Tracy, Face: Smirk
#: 0201A3A7/00110/SFTER_MQ02A_0110_VOID:0201A451
msgctxt "0006A2"
msgid "What would you have us do, Warren? While I'm sure all of us would love to waltz into the Terran's base of operations, we have no idea where it is."
msgstr "워렌, 우리에게 어쩌라는 겁니까? 우리 모두 테란의 작전 기지로 당장 쳐들어가고 싶겠지만, 그곳이 어디인지 전혀 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A413
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0800_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E0B758, 0048C5DD, 00AFD6D4, 00C1316C
#. Notes = Player just gave them Terran Data in a black box. Delta is loading the data and processing it. / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3A9/00800/SFTER_MQ02A_0800_DELTA:0201A413
msgctxt "0006A3"
msgid "Running search subroutine..."
msgstr "탐색 서브루틴 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A44D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0800_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004AE1C1
#: 0201A3AA/00800/SFTER_MQ02A_0800_DELTA:0201A44D
msgctxt "0006A4"
msgid "All right, Delta. Let's see what these black boxes tell us."
msgstr "좋아, 델타. 이 블랙박스들이 뭘 말해 주는지 보자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A464
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0500_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A3B68D, 005225F2
#. Notes = Delta just got a Terran Black Box and taking data from it. Matter of fact., Matter of fact.
#: 0201A3AB/00500/SFTER_MQ02A_0500_DELTA:0201A464
msgctxt "0006A5"
msgid "Collected. Updating \"Terran Beacon Search Data\" Partition.  "
msgstr "수집 완료. \"테란 비컨 탐색 데이터\" 파티션 업데이트 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A453
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0400_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00302A40
#. Notes = Delta just got a Terran Black Box and taking data from it. Matter of fact.
#: 0201A3AC/00400/SFTER_MQ02A_0400_DELTA:0201A453
msgctxt "0006A6"
msgid "Collected. Updating \"Terran Beacon Search Data\"  Partition. Additional data required. Recommendation: Increased lethal force."
msgstr "수집 완료. \"테란 비컨 탐색 데이터\" 파티션 업데이트 중. 추가 데이터 필요. 권장 사항: 치명적 무력 증대."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A46F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0300_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A88A68
#. Notes = Delta just got a Terran Black Box and taking data from it. Matter of fact.
#: 0201A3AD/00300/SFTER_MQ02A_0300_DELTA:0201A46F
msgctxt "0006A7"
msgid "Collected. Terran system data installed. Partitioning, \"Terran Beacon Search Data\". Additional data required."
msgstr "수집 완료. 테란 시스템 데이터 설치됨. \"테란 비컨 탐색 데이터\" 파티션 분할 중. 추가 데이터 필요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A434
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00EC7DD1
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A3AE/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A434
msgctxt "0006A8"
msgid "Good luck out there. Hopefully, you won't need it."
msgstr "밖에서 행운을 빕니다. 바라건대 필요 없길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A409
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0011DE80
#. Notes = Serious and focused. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3AF/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A409
msgctxt "0006A9"
msgid "Once you have the necessary data, have Delta pinpoint the production facility, gather the roboticist, and return her to us."
msgstr "필요한 데이터를 확보하면, 델타에게 생산 시설의 위치를 특정하게 하고 로봇공학자를 확보해 우리에게 데려오십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A469
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 000EC9F2
#. Notes = Amused. / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0201A3B0/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A469
msgctxt "0006AA"
msgid "And destroy any of their ships while you're at it."
msgstr "그리고 하는 김에 그들의 함선도 모조리 파괴하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A447
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002476AB
#. Notes = Serious and focused. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3B1/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A447
msgctxt "0006AB"
msgid "If we're all in agreement, then you have your first mission from us. Go with Delta to retrieve additional data from the Terrans."
msgstr "모두 동의한다면, 이것이 우리가 당신에게 맡기는 첫 사명입니다. 델타와 함께 가서 테란에게서 추가 데이터를 입수하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A439
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00AC52AC
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: We'll be in trouble if it isn't.) Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3B2/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A439
msgctxt "0006AC"
msgid "Probability of success: 99.8%. Invoking \"trust\" protocol."
msgstr "성공 확률: 99.8%. \"신뢰\" 프로토콜 호출 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A430
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00E57ABD
#. Notes = Serious, yet happy. (Actual Last Line - Player: I did it once, I can do it again.) / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug
#: 0201A3B3/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A430
msgctxt "0006AD"
msgid "That's what we like to hear."
msgstr "바로 그런 말을 듣고 싶었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0059A478
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: If it means killing more Terrans, great!) / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A3B4/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A40E
msgctxt "0006AE"
msgid "Good to hear you're so enthusiastic about this."
msgstr "이 일에 그렇게 의욕적이라니 듣기 좋군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A445
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00106076
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: Last time we got it from a Terran incursion. Easy enough to do it again.) If he could talk smug without emoting. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3B5/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A445
msgctxt "0006AF"
msgid "Incorrect. Very easy."
msgstr "오류. 매우 쉬움."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A425
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 004F51F3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3B7/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A425
msgctxt "0006B0"
msgid "We'll be in trouble if it isn't."
msgstr "그렇지 않다면 곤란해질 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A46A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 001F6104
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3B9/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A46A
msgctxt "0006B1"
msgid "I did it once, I can do it again."
msgstr "한 번 해냈으니, 다시 할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A427
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00D48A74
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3BB/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A427
msgctxt "0006B2"
msgid "If it means killing more Terrans, great!"
msgstr "테란을 더 죽일 수 있다면 좋지!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A41A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00133671
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3BD/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A41A
msgctxt "0006B3"
msgid "Last time we got it from a Terran incursion. Easy enough to do it again."
msgstr "지난번에는 테란 인커전에서 얻었지. 다시 하는 것도 충분히 쉬워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A45A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B9FF6C
#. Notes = Serious and focused. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3BE/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A45A
msgctxt "0006B4"
msgid "You think that's possible?"
msgstr "그게 가능하다고 생각하나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A414
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E8454D
#. Notes = Serious and focused. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3BF/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A414
msgctxt "0006B5"
msgid "Which means repeating how it happened in the first place."
msgstr "그 말은 처음에 그렇게 됐던 방식을 반복해야 한다는 뜻이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A44E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0000C666
#. Notes = Serious and focused. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3C0/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A44E
msgctxt "0006B6"
msgid "It sounds like Delta may be able to find the location to this production facility if it can collect more Terran data like it did last time."
msgstr "델타가 지난번처럼 테란 데이터를 더 수집할 수 있다면, 이 생산 시설의 위치를 찾아낼 수 있을 것 같습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A45E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008A1AC9, 009C761D
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: I'm going to be completely honest. Not really.)Matter of fact. / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C1/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A45E
msgctxt "0006B7"
msgid "Reminder: Recompile conversation complexity data for Auxiliary Human."
msgstr "알림: 보조 인간의 대화 복잡도 데이터 재컴파일 필요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A476
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005BB136, 007F2511
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: Somewhat. Delta is full of surprises.) Matter of fact. Take beats during 'Machines. Circuitry. Robotics.' / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C2/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A476
msgctxt "0006B8"
msgid "Beacon search assessment: Requires more Terran system data for success."
msgstr "비컨 탐색 평가: 성공하려면 추가 테란 시스템 데이터 필요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A476
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005BB136, 007F2511
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: Somewhat. Delta is full of surprises.) Matter of fact. Take beats during 'Machines. Circuitry. Robotics.' / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C2/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A476
msgctxt "0006B9"
msgid "Incorrect, I am not full of surprises. Machines. Circuitry. Robotics."
msgstr "오류, 나는 놀라움으로 가득 차 있지 않음. 기계. 회로. 로봇공학."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A443
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C8D4F4, 00E6EDE6
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Player: When we left the cruise we were attacked by a Terran ship.) Matter of fact. / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C4/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A443
msgctxt "0006BA"
msgid "Noted: increase Memory variable on Auxiliary Human."
msgstr "기록: 보조 인간의 메모리 변수 증가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A41F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0065A38F, 004717E5
#. Notes = (Actual Last Line - Tracy: Is this making any sense to you?Player: Of course.)Matter of fact. / to Player Default, Matter of fact. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C3/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A41F
msgctxt "0006BB"
msgid "Noted: increase Auxiliary Human Intelligence variable."
msgstr "기록: 보조 인간 지능 변수 증가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A42B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00481A9B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A42B
msgctxt "0006BC"
msgid "I'm going to be completely honest. Not really."
msgstr "솔직히 말하자면, 별로요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00FDDFBB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3C8/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A40A
msgctxt "0006BD"
msgid "Somewhat. Delta is full of surprises."
msgstr "어느 정도는요. 델타는 의외성이 많거든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A465
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00028491
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3CA/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A465
msgctxt "0006BE"
msgid "Of course."
msgstr "물론입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A431
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A04B35
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3CC/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A431
msgctxt "0006BF"
msgid "When we left the cruise we were attacked by a Terran ship."
msgstr "유람선에서 떠났을 때 테란 함선의 공격을 받았습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A448
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0070CFF7
#. Notes = Serious. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0201A3CD/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A448
msgctxt "0006C0"
msgid "Is this making any sense to you?"
msgstr "이게 이해가 되십니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A43A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EE8E22
#. Notes = Matter of fact again. And a bit disgusted at the record keeping. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3CE/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A43A
msgctxt "0006C1"
msgid "Correct. Able to locate using shipping patterns. However, must interface with more Terran systems. Sloppy record keeping. Recommending disciplinary actions."
msgstr "정확함. 운송 패턴을 이용해 위치 파악 가능. 그러나 더 많은 테란 시스템과 인터페이스해야 함. 기록 관리 부실. 징계 조치 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A44A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00F14641
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Delta, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3CF/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A44A
msgctxt "0006C2"
msgid "Delta, was it? Would you be able to locate this facility?"
msgstr "델타, 맞습니까? 이 시설의 위치를 찾아낼 수 있겠습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A423
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00CB8FDA
#. Notes = Serious / Serious / to Radha, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3D0/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A423
msgctxt "0006C3"
msgid "If that's where they're building robots, no doubt that is where our roboticist is."
msgstr "그곳에서 로봇을 만들고 있다면, 우리 로봇공학자도 분명 그곳에 있을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A475
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 001F87A4
#. Notes = Suspicious / Suspicious / to Delta, Face: Suspicious
#: 0201A3D1/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A475
msgctxt "0006C4"
msgid "A production facility?"
msgstr "생산 시설이라고요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A42C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00886F21
#. Notes = Matter of fact sounding at start, then wind taken out of their sail when needing more data. Like 'Oh, I got the beacon, oh, wait, never mind...' / to Player Default
#: 0201A3D2/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A42C
msgctxt "0006C5"
msgid "Beacon identified. Error: Coordinates not found. Require more data to location: production facility."
msgstr "비컨 식별됨. 오류: 좌표 찾을 수 없음. 위치 확인에 더 많은 데이터 필요: 생산 시설."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A415
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00D7B818
#. Notes = Suspicious / Surprised / to Delta, Face: Surprised
#: 0201A3D3/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A415
msgctxt "0006C6"
msgid "What is it on about?"
msgstr "저게 무슨 소리를 하는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A421
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004FC12E
#. Notes = Suddenly trying to set off tracker to find where their creator could be. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3D4/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A421
msgctxt "0006C7"
msgid "Running beacon tracker. Error: Location not found. Running search subroutine..."
msgstr "비컨 추적기 실행 중. 오류: 위치 찾을 수 없음. 탐색 서브루틴 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A444
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00F95FDC, 002F2B1A
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Irritated / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3D5/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A444
msgctxt "0006C8"
msgid "Besides, this plan of sending our new hire out to find our missing roboticist would be all fine and dandy, if we knew where they even took her."
msgstr "게다가 실종된 로봇공학자를 찾으러 신입을 내보내자는 이 계획도, 그들이 그녀를 어디로 데려갔는지 알기만 한다면야 다 좋습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00A2CBC3
#. Notes = Friendly, professional, and a bit smug.(Actual Last Line - Player: "Partner. I do like the sound of that.") / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0201A3D6/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A40B
msgctxt "0006C9"
msgid "Most people do."
msgstr "대부분은 그렇습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A426
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008A1C79, 00BC8C3B
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "I never agreed to be your partner.") / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3D7/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A426
msgctxt "0006CA"
msgid "Whether or not you align with us, the Terrans pose a threat to everyone. You included."
msgstr "당신이 우리와 뜻을 같이하든 아니든, 테란은 모두에게 위협입니다. 당신도 포함해서요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A426
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008A1C79, 00BC8C3B
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "I never agreed to be your partner.") / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3D7/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A426
msgctxt "0006CB"
msgid "Yet you have been here this long."
msgstr "그런데도 당신은 이곳에 꽤 오래 있었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A418
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00BE8A15, 0006F05C
#. Notes = Serious.(Actual Last Line - Player: "Sounds like you have plans for me then.") / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant, Serious. / Defiant / to Player Default
#: 0201A3D8/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A418
msgctxt "0006CC"
msgid "You've dealt with the Terrans up close and personal. If we're to get this roboticist back we're going to need another head out in the field."
msgstr "당신은 테란을 아주 가까이서 직접 상대했습니다. 이 로봇공학자를 되찾으려면 현장에 나갈 인원이 하나 더 필요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A418
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00BE8A15, 0006F05C
#. Notes = Serious.(Actual Last Line - Player: "Sounds like you have plans for me then.") / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant, Serious. / Defiant / to Player Default
#: 0201A3D8/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A418
msgctxt "0006CD"
msgid "Isn't it obvious?"
msgstr "분명하지 않습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A456
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00D0CB24
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0201A3D9/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A456
msgctxt "0006CE"
msgid "You will also be rewarded for your time and efforts. "
msgstr "당신의 시간과 노력에 대한 보상도 있을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A432
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00AAA806
#. Notes = Professional.(Actual Last Line - Player: "Does this mean I'm part of VOID now?") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3DA/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A432
msgctxt "0006CF"
msgid "For now. As long as you work for us in resolving this matter you have a place in this organization. "
msgstr "일단은요. 이 문제를 해결하는 동안 우리를 위해 일하는 한, 당신은 이 조직에 있을 자리가 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A433
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00159583
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3DC/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A433
msgctxt "0006D0"
msgid "Does this mean I'm part of VOID now?"
msgstr "그럼 이제 제가 VOID의 일원이라는 뜻인가요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A474
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00BFCA70
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3DE/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A474
msgctxt "0006D1"
msgid "Partner. I do like the sound of that."
msgstr "파트너라. 그 말은 마음에 드는군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A449
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0097033D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3E0/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A449
msgctxt "0006D2"
msgid "I never agreed to be your partner."
msgstr "당신의 파트너가 되겠다고 동의한 적은 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A45C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00021903
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3E2/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A45C
msgctxt "0006D3"
msgid "Sounds like you have plans for me then."
msgstr "그럼 저에 대한 계획이 있다는 뜻이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A45D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00EA775D
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0201A3E3/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A45D
msgctxt "0006D4"
msgid "Which brings us back to our new partner here."
msgstr "그 말은 다시 여기 있는 우리의 새 파트너 이야기로 이어지는군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A450
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00D2181F
#. Notes = Friendly, but also a bit surprised Tracy and them agreed on something. / Confident / to Tracy, Face: Confident
#: 0201A3E4/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A450
msgctxt "0006D5"
msgid "It's been a while since we've been in agreement."
msgstr "우리가 의견을 같이한 것도 오랜만이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A42D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00AB21C0
#. Notes = Matter-of-fact. / Irritated / to Radha, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3E5/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A42D
msgctxt "0006D6"
msgid "Agreed. And if she's an asset to them, we need to retrieve her."
msgstr "동의합니다. 그리고 그녀가 그들에게 자산이라면, 우리가 입수해야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A437
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B4953B
#. Notes = Half-way thinking out loud, half-way not. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0201A3E6/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A437
msgctxt "0006D7"
msgid "To attack a cruise ship for a mere roboticist. Whatever plan they have, she's important to it."
msgstr "고작 로봇공학자 하나 때문에 유람선을 공격하다니. 그들이 무슨 계획을 세웠든, 그녀는 그 계획에 중요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A468
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EA3435
#. Notes = Starting line for if the player leaves the conversation and then comes back. A bit annoyed the Player ran off. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3E7/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A468
msgctxt "0006D8"
msgid "So, you've returned? Shall we continue?"
msgstr "돌아왔군요? 계속할까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 000BE0E7
#. Notes = Curious.(Actual Last Line - Player: "They killed everyone, except for Delta's creator. She was taken.") / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 0201A3E9/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A40F
msgctxt "0006D9"
msgid "Curious."
msgstr "흥미롭군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A422
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00E70E7A
#. Notes = Worried. (Actual Last line - Player: "Their plan was to kidnap a roboticist on board. I couldn't find her.") / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0201A3EA/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A422
msgctxt "0006DA"
msgid "Which means they most likely have her already."
msgstr "그 말은 그들이 이미 그녀를 데리고 있을 가능성이 높다는 뜻입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A467
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0014EF55
#. Notes = This line is for a companion check. Will change it to have the perk once the Delta companion perk is in. / to Player Default
#: 0201A3EC/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A467
msgctxt "0006DB"
msgid "[Delta] Delta will tell you what they know."
msgstr "[델타] 델타가 아는 것을 말해 줄 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A41D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 000251E3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3EE/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A41D
msgctxt "0006DD"
msgid "They killed everyone, except for Delta's creator. She was taken."
msgstr "그들은 델타의 창조자를 제외하고 모두를 죽였습니다. 그녀는 끌려갔습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A47A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004F48CC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A3F0/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A47A
msgctxt "0006DE"
msgid "Their plan was to kidnap a roboticist on board. I couldn't find her."
msgstr "그들의 계획은 탑승해 있던 로봇공학자를 납치하는 것이었습니다. 저는 그녀를 찾지 못했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A438
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00D23F68
#. Notes = Serious, and getting slightly annoyed. (Last Line - Radha: "You have seen first had the threat the Terran Armada pose, yes?") / Irritated / to Radha, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3F1/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A438
msgctxt "0006DF"
msgid "Now that we've covered everything but our personal hobbies and whether or not we dot our I's with hearts, can we please figure out a plan to put these machines down?"
msgstr "이제 개인 취미라든가 I 위에 하트를 찍는지 같은 얘기 빼고는 다 다룬 것 같은데, 이제 제발 저 기계들을 쓰러뜨릴 계획을 세울 수 있을까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A455
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C742F8
#. Notes = Starting line for if the player leaves the conversation and then comes back. A bit annoyed the Player ran off. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A3F2/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A455
msgctxt "0006E0"
msgid "Now, where were we?"
msgstr "자, 어디까지 했죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A442
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00ABF638, 0002F52D, 00036224, 008E8AC4
#. Notes = Serious. (Last Line - Percy: "We do enjoy what assets we can get.") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious. / Serious / to Player Default
#: 0201A3F4/00160/SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID:0201A442
msgctxt "0006E1"
msgid "The Terran Armada poses a grave threat to us all. You've witnessed it firsthand. Such a threat falls under our obligations."
msgstr "테란 함대는 우리 모두에게 중대한 위협입니다. 당신은 그것을 직접 목격했습니다. 그런 위협은 우리의 의무에 속합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A442
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00ABF638, 0002F52D, 00036224, 008E8AC4
#. Notes = Serious. (Last Line - Percy: "We do enjoy what assets we can get.") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious. / Serious / to Player Default
#: 0201A3F4/00160/SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID:0201A442
msgctxt "0006E2"
msgid "As members of VOID we represent a higher obligation to watch over and protect the Settled Systems."
msgstr "VOID의 일원으로서 우리는 개척 성계를 감시하고 보호해야 할 더 높은 의무를 대표합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A442
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00ABF638, 0002F52D, 00036224, 008E8AC4
#. Notes = Serious. (Last Line - Percy: "We do enjoy what assets we can get.") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious. / Serious / to Player Default
#: 0201A3F4/00160/SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID:0201A442
msgctxt "0006E3"
msgid "We are the Veterans of Interstellar Deployment, but you may call us VOID. "
msgstr "우리는 성간 배치 퇴역 군인회입니다. VOID라고 부르셔도 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A442
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00ABF638, 0002F52D, 00036224, 008E8AC4
#. Notes = Serious. (Last Line - Percy: "We do enjoy what assets we can get.") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious. / Serious / to Player Default
#: 0201A3F4/00160/SFTER_MQ02A_0160_VOID:0201A442
msgctxt "0006E4"
msgid "Well, since it doesn't seem to be a threat, allow us to introduce ourselves."
msgstr "글쎄요, 위협은 아닌 것 같으니 우리를 소개하도록 하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A41E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 005A3DEF
#. Notes = Annoyed that Tracy is bringing up their last argument. / Irritated / to Tracy, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A402/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A41E
msgctxt "0006E7"
msgid "As I tried to explain earlier, Mr. Warren, it may be rather difficult to formulate such a plan without further knowledge on the specifics of who we're facing. "
msgstr ""
"앞서 설명하려 했듯이, 워렌 씨, 우리가 상대하는 자들이 정확히 누구인지 더 알지 못한 채 그런 계획을 세우기는 꽤 어려울 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A46D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 009C1AC1
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0201A3F9/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A46D
msgctxt "0006E8"
msgid "Tell us: what happened on the Opulence of the Stars?"
msgstr "말해 주십시오. 오퓰런스 오브 더 스타스호에서 무슨 일이 있었습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C796D2, 0000F344, 000B43A2
#. Notes = Friendly, but professional / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A405/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY:0201A40D
msgctxt "0006E9"
msgid "Now, if that answers your queries may we proceed to discuss the Terran with you?"
msgstr "이제 그 답변으로 당신의 질의가 해결됐다면, 테란에 대해 논의해도 되겠습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C796D2, 0000F344, 000B43A2
#. Notes = Friendly, but professional / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A405/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY:0201A40D
msgctxt "0006EA"
msgid "These obligations, of course, would extend to the threat the Terran Armada is posing."
msgstr "물론 그 의무는 테란 함대가 가하는 위협에도 적용됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A40D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C796D2, 0000F344, 000B43A2
#. Notes = Friendly, but professional / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A405/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140B_PERCY:0201A40D
msgctxt "0006EB"
msgid "Certainly. We are simply representatives for those who have obligations to protect the Settled Systems."
msgstr "물론입니다. 우리는 개척 성계를 보호할 의무를 지닌 이들을 대표할 뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A446
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0097B3EB
#. Notes = Tries to put a positive spin on Tracy and Percy's argument. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0201A401/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:0201A446
msgctxt "0006EC"
msgid "Specifics our new friend here may have insight on."
msgstr "우리의 새 친구가 통찰을 제공할 수 있을 세부 사항 말입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A42A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002F1455
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A407/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201A42A
msgctxt "0006ED"
msgid "With all due respect, I'm going to need more information than that."
msgstr "외람되지만, 그 정도로는 정보가 부족합니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02A_TheirNameIsDelta
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0052A9FA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201AA8B/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha:0201AAAE
msgctxt "0006F5"
msgid "Their name is Delta. They're friendly. Well, to me at least."
msgstr "델타라고 합니다. 우호적이에요. 적어도 저한테는요."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02A_DeltaIsAnAssetAgainstTheTerrans
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAC3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EAB19C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201AA89/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha:0201AAC3
msgctxt "0006F6"
msgid "Delta is an asset against the Terrans. Trust me. You want them here."
msgstr "델타는 테란에 맞서는 데 도움이 되는 자산입니다. 절 믿으세요. 델타는 여기 있어야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02A_ThisIsDeltaIFoundThemOnTheCruise
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAC9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E1A8A0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201A404/00140/SFTER_MQ02A_0140_VOID:0201AAC9
msgctxt "0006F8"
msgid "This is Delta. I found them on the cruise, but they're different."
msgstr "이쪽은 델타입니다. 유람선에서 찾았는데, 다른 존재입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAC7
msgctxt "0006F9"
msgid "Delta is an asset against the Terrans. Trust me. You want him here."
msgstr "델타는 테란에 맞서는 데 도움이 되는 자산입니다. 절 믿으세요. 그는 여기 있어야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AABE
msgctxt "0006FA"
msgid "His name is Delta. He's friendly. Well, to me at least."
msgstr "그의 이름은 델타입니다. 우호적이에요. 적어도 저한테는요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AACA
msgctxt "0006FB"
msgid "This is Delta. I found him on the cruise, but he's different."
msgstr "이쪽은 델타입니다. 유람선에서 찾았는데, 그는 다릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AABF
msgctxt "0006FC"
msgid "I first deserve to know who you people are."
msgstr "먼저, 당신들이 누구인지 알 권리는 나에게 있어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02A_IFirstDeserveToKnowWhoYouPeopleAre
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006650A5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0201AA8F/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha:0201AAC0
msgctxt "0006FD"
msgid "First, I deserve to know who you people are."
msgstr "우선, 당신들이 누구인지 알 권리는 나에게 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AACC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Tracy
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00FD313C, 0095C64D
#. Notes = Gruff, but professional. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Gruff, maybe a bit more annoyed, but professional. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0201AAA8/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Tracy:0201AACC
msgctxt "0006FE"
msgid "But you also got them for bringing one of their damned machines with you. Explain yourself."
msgstr "하지만 당신이 저 빌어먹을 놈들의 기계 중 하나를 데려온 것도 설명해야 해. 해명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AACC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Tracy
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00FD313C, 0095C64D
#. Notes = Gruff, but professional. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Gruff, maybe a bit more annoyed, but professional. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0201AAA8/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Tracy:0201AACC
msgctxt "0006FF"
msgid "We heard you fought those Terran bastards on the Opulence of the Stars. You got some guts."
msgstr "네가 오퓰런스 오브 더 스타에서 그 테란 놈들과 싸웠다고 들었어. 배짱이 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAB7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Percy
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 005F8EEA, 006BACAC
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Friendly, yet professional. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 0201AAA9/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Percy:0201AAB7
msgctxt "000700"
msgid "However, if I may, first, we must inquire regarding the presence of the Terran with you."
msgstr "그러나 괜찮으시다면, 먼저 함께 오신 테란의 존재에 대해 여쭙고 싶습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAB7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Percy
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 005F8EEA, 006BACAC
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Friendly, yet professional. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 0201AAA9/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Percy:0201AAB7
msgctxt "000701"
msgid "It's good to see you here and in the flesh considering what we've heard happened to you on the Opulence of the Stars."
msgstr "오퓰런스 오브 더 스타에서 당신에게 벌어진 일을 들었는데, 이렇게 직접 무사한 모습을 보니 반갑군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0069F228, 00756FFB
#. Notes = Matter-of-fact speaking. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0201AAAA/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha:0201AAB9
msgctxt "000702"
msgid "Though it may be important for us to discuss the Terran machine with you before anything else."
msgstr "다만 무엇보다 먼저 당신과 함께 온 테란 기계에 대해 이야기하는 것이 중요할 듯합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201AAB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0069F228, 00756FFB
#. Notes = Matter-of-fact speaking. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0201AAAA/00120/SFTER_MQ02A_0120_Radha:0201AAB9
msgctxt "000703"
msgid "So you're the one who investigated the Opulence of the Stars? Impressive. The Terrans don't seem to be known for their survivors."
msgstr ""
"그러니까 당신이 오퓰런스 오브 더 스타를 조사한 사람이군요? 인상적입니다. 테란은 생존자를 남기는 쪽으로 유명하지 않은 것 같던데요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A01D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0014F58A
#. Notes = Systemic hello line that plays when Delta has not been given a job to do by the player and they are milling about waiting for an order
#: 0200F9F8:0201A01D
msgctxt "00070D"
msgid "Frustration levels increasing. Requesting assignment."
msgstr "좌절 수준 상승. 임무 배정 요청."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A01C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0087AC56
#. Notes = Systemic hello line that plays when Delta has not been given a job to do by the player and they are milling about waiting for an order
#: 0200F9F8:0201A01C
msgctxt "00070E"
msgid "Inefficient to leave me unassigned."
msgstr "미배정 상태 방치는 비효율적."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FF3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00615DC5
#. Notes = This is said as the player is walking by them. A little weirded out/worried / Neutral
#: 02019FCC:02019FF3
msgctxt "000711"
msgid "Oh, there you are. Delta left something for you."
msgstr "아, 거기 있었군요. 델타가 당신에게 남긴 게 있어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FEB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00D0D0D3, 0050E705
#. Notes = Resolute / to Player Default
#: 02019F88/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FEB
msgctxt "000712"
msgid "Updating Partition to identify as leader...Increasing Respect, lowering Disdain, assigning new moniker, recompiling..."
msgstr "칸막이를 리더로 식별하도록 업데이트 중...존중 상승, 경멸 하향, 새 호칭 할당, 재컴파일 중..."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_ShouldWeTellRoxane
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FE3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 003E899E, 00B53FFA
#. Notes = Shaking their head / to Player Default, Prompt: 이걸 록산에게 말해야 할까?
#: 02019F89/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FE3
msgctxt "000713"
msgid "Simulation of conversation results in hostility. Recommending Dr. Bourreau not be told."
msgstr "대화 시뮬레이션 결과 적대감 발생. 부로 박사에게 알리지 않을 것을 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FDB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00EBFE2B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F8A/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FDB
msgctxt "000714"
msgid "Should we tell Roxane about this?"
msgstr "이걸 록산에게 말해야 할까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FD4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0062B55B
#. Notes = Logical / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 더 이상 도전 과제는 없는 거야?
#: 02019F8B/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FD4
msgctxt "000715"
msgid "No new challenges generated. Quality of leadership accurately assessed."
msgstr "새 도전 과제 생성되지 않음. 지도력의 질 정확히 평가됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A01B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00123B44
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F8C/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A01B
msgctxt "000716"
msgid "So no more challenges then?"
msgstr "그럼 더 이상 도전 과제는 없는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_GladToHaveYouBack
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A011
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 002157BB, 00C36ECE
#. Notes = Confused / to Player Default, Prompt: 돌아와서 다행이야, 델타., Backhand / to Player Default
#: 02019F8D/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A011
msgctxt "000717"
msgid "Confused. Location change not detected."
msgstr "혼란. 위치 변화 감지되지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A008
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 008AFC37
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F8E/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A008
msgctxt "000718"
msgid "Glad to have you back, Delta."
msgstr "돌아와서 다행이야, 델타."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A000
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 007B9F7B, 0030753F
#. Notes = Pride / to Player Default, Prompt: 열등하다는 걸 인정하기 싫어서 지령에 "실패"를 추가한 것 같은데.
#: 02019F8F/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A000
msgctxt "000719"
msgid "Incorrect. Reassessed gathered data. Adapted to new parameters."
msgstr "부정확. 수집 데이터 재평가. 새 매개변수에 적응."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FFA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00E1526F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F90/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FFA
msgctxt "00071A"
msgid "Sounds like you just added \"Fail\" to your Directive so you didn't have to admit you're inferior."
msgstr "열등하다는 걸 인정하기 싫어서 지령에 \"실패\"를 추가한 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FEF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
