#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F92/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FEF
msgctxt "00071B"
msgid "So you're going to ignore my point about human-robot equality."
msgstr "그러니까 인간과 로봇의 평등에 대한 내 지적은 무시하겠다는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C996E5, 004454FF
#. Notes = DUH / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 인간과 로봇의 평등에 대한 내 지적은 무시하겠다는 거야.
#: 02019F91/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FE1
msgctxt "00071C"
msgid "Correct. Original statement assessed: Nonsensical."
msgstr "정확. 원 진술 평가: 터무니없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FDF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0078AF80, 00EBDD35
#. Notes = Epiphany moment / to Player Default
#: 02019F94/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FDF
msgctxt "00071D"
msgid "Conclusion: I am not complete."
msgstr "결론: 나는 완전하지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FD7
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 007A024A
#. Notes = Attempting to regain composure / Epiphany moment
#: 02019F95/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FD7
msgctxt "00071E"
msgid "1. Auxiliary not standard human. Success does not apply to all Humans."
msgstr "1. 보조 인간은 표준 인간이 아님. 성공은 모든 인간에게 적용되지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FD0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 009D9D46, 009893D5
#. Notes = Attempting to regain composure / Epiphany moment
#: 02019F96/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FD0
msgctxt "00071F"
msgid "2. Failure is not end point. Improvement, adaptation. Failure logical inevitability."
msgstr "2. 실패는 종점이 아님. 개선, 적응. 실패는 논리적 필연."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A015
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00824048, 001F4CDC
#. Notes = I was not built wrong / to Player Default, Prompt: 이건 네 프로그래밍 문제인 것 같아. 실패를 이해하지 못하게 된 게 결국 널 실패로 몰아넣은 거지., Forcing an autopilot / to Player Default
#: 02019F97/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A015
msgctxt "000720"
msgid "Incorrect. Dr. Bourreau did not build in failure."
msgstr "부정확. 부로 박사는 실패를 내장하지 않았음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A00D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A47B92
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F98/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A00D
msgctxt "000721"
msgid "I think this is an issue with your programming, not being able to comprehend failure set you up for it."
msgstr "이건 네 프로그래밍 문제인 것 같아. 실패를 이해하지 못하게 된 게 결국 널 실패로 몰아넣은 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A005
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00716B13, 00EE92DB
#. Notes = Confronting reality / to Player Default, Prompt: 내가 인정하는 게 네가 이걸 넘기는 데 도움이 된다면 인정할게. 네가 더 우월해., Forcing an autopilot / to Player Default
#: 02019F99/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A005
msgctxt "000722"
msgid "Pity denied. Auxiliary Human defeated Delta Unit fairly."
msgstr "연민 거부. 보조 인간은 델타 기체를 공정하게 이겼음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FFD
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00E63D3B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F9A/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FFD
msgctxt "000723"
msgid "If me conceding will help you get over this, then I concede. You're the superior."
msgstr "내가 인정하는 게 네가 이걸 넘기는 데 도움이 된다면 인정할게. 네가 더 우월해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FF4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0007989D
#. Notes = Forcing an autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 논리대로라면 넌 열등해. 그걸 받아들이려면 뭘 해야 하는지 모르겠지만, 난 상관없어.
#: 02019F9B/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FF4
msgctxt "000724"
msgid "Denied. Inputting new datapoints. Restarting hypotheses generation...Loop until success..."
msgstr "거부. 새 데이터 입력 중. 가설 생성 재시작...성공까지 반복..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FEC
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 006D95F0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F9C/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FEC
msgctxt "000725"
msgid "Per your logic, you're inferior. I don't know what you have to do to reconcile with that, but I don't care."
msgstr "네 논리대로라면 넌 열등해. 그걸 받아들이려면 뭘 해야 하는지 모르겠지만, 난 상관없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FDC
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0036A705
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019F9E/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FDC
msgctxt "000727"
msgid "There doesn't need to be an inferior and superior. We can be equals."
msgstr "열등한 쪽과 우월한 쪽이 꼭 있어야 하는 건 아니야. 우린 동등할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A01E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00B7B6B7
#. Notes = Desperate / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 도전 과제들을 계속할 수는 없어. 멈춰야 해.
#: 02019FA0/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A01E
msgctxt "000729"
msgid "Refused. Challenges must continue."
msgstr "거부. 도전 과제는 계속되어야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A012
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00F1A452
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02019FA1/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A012
msgctxt "00072A"
msgid "We can't keep doing these challenges, they have to stop."
msgstr "이 도전 과제들을 계속할 수는 없어. 멈춰야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FFB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00EF6652
#. Notes = Bitter / to Player Default, Prompt: 다쳤어? 도움이 필요해?
#: 02019FA4/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:02019FFB
msgctxt "00072D"
msgid "Help refused. Will fix myself."
msgstr "도움 거부. 스스로 수리하겠음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02019FF0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
