#. Notes = Desperately searching for an answer
#: 02019FAA/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A018
msgctxt "000733"
msgid "Method: Unknown. Potential trick. Sabotage of sensors. Perceived failure. Scanning..."
msgstr "방법: 불명. 잠재적 속임수. 센서 방해공작. 인지된 실패. 스캔 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A00E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
