#. Notes = Losing their marbles
#: 02019FAB/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0201A00E
msgctxt "000734"
msgid "Error: \"No Failure\" protocol terminated. Incoming data incorrect. Cannot be defeated by human."
msgstr "오류: \"실패 없음\" 프로토콜 종료됨. 수신 데이터 부정확. 인간에게 패배할 수 없음."

