#. SoundFileID = 00F5826A
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:0202176E
msgctxt "00082E"
msgid "Error... catastrophic damage to cranium... "
msgstr "오류... 두개부에 치명적 피해..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202176D
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueGenericTerranRobots
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric01, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric02, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric03
#. SoundFileID = 001D3BC3
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:0202176D
msgctxt "00082F"
msgid "Audio-visual detection has been compromised... "
msgstr "시청각 감지 기능이 손상되었다..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202176C
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueGenericTerranRobots
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric01, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric02, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric03
#. SoundFileID = 0070E5A9
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:0202176C
msgctxt "000830"
msgid "Heavy damage to cranial processor..."
msgstr "두개부 프로세서에 심각한 피해..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202176A
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueGenericTerranRobots
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric01, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric02, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric03
#. SoundFileID = 0043085F
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:0202176A
msgctxt "000831"
msgid "Catastrophic damage to arms."
msgstr "팔에 치명적 피해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02021769
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueGenericTerranRobots
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric01, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric02, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric03
#. SoundFileID = 00B6588D
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:02021769
msgctxt "000832"
msgid "Arms damaged."
msgstr "팔 손상."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02021766
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueGenericTerranRobots
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric01, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric02, SFTER_TerranRobotGeneric03
#. SoundFileID = 009F5DD4
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02021764:02021766
msgctxt "000833"
msgid "Warning: weapon accuracy reduced. "
msgstr "경고: 무기 명중률 감소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200D9A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 003FCA13
#. Notes = Trying to shake off the horrors she just heard Delta said and is trying to put her attention back to the Player. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 0200D9A2/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:0200D9A4
msgctxt "000838"
msgid "No. Never mind. We can talk about this later."
msgstr "아니. 됐어. 이 얘긴 나중에 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A44B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B71463
#. Notes = Angry, but scared. Trying to sound threatening, however she isn't at all. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:0201A44B
msgctxt "000839"
msgid "Hold it right there! Don't come any closer! Or I'll... I'll..."
msgstr "거기 서! 더 가까이 오지 마! 안 그러면 내가... 내가..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A52
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650A_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0001D802
#: 020238E6/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650A_ROX:02023A52
msgctxt "00083A"
msgid "Here is that X-Tech you asked for."
msgstr "요청하신 X-테크 여기 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A36
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F8BA67, 000D7B39, 00A0E0FD, 00922AE5
#. Notes = Sad and scared. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 후회하는 거죠?, Worried and regretful. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Regretful and angry at herself. / Depressed / to Player Default (+3 more)
#: 020238E7/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A36
msgctxt "00083B"
msgid "But I've already given Delta the upgrade, and if we're going to defeat the Terrans we need them at their best."
msgstr "하지만 이미 델타에게 업그레이드를 적용했고, 우리가 테란을 물리치려면 델타가 최상의 상태여야 해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A36
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F8BA67, 000D7B39, 00A0E0FD, 00922AE5
#. Notes = Sad and scared. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 후회하는 거죠?, Worried and regretful. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Regretful and angry at herself. / Depressed / to Player Default (+3 more)
#: 020238E7/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A36
msgctxt "00083C"
msgid "Just like that person at the factory. I've been making decisions without fully calculating the risks. "
msgstr "공장의 그 사람 때처럼요. 전 위험을 제대로 계산하지 않은 채 결정을 내려 왔어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A36
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F8BA67, 000D7B39, 00A0E0FD, 00922AE5
#. Notes = Sad and scared. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 후회하는 거죠?, Worried and regretful. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Regretful and angry at herself. / Depressed / to Player Default (+3 more)
#: 020238E7/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A36
msgctxt "00083D"
msgid "It's my own fault. I knew the risks of placing them in that machine back on the Opulence. But the full weight didn't hit me back then. I thought of how they could save me; I didn't think of the means."
msgstr ""
"제 잘못이에요. 오퓰런스에서 델타를 그 기계에 넣는 게 위험하다는 건 알고 있었어요. 그런데 그때는 그 무게가 제대로 와닿지 않았죠. 델타가 날 구할 수 있다는 것만 생각했고, 어떤 방식으로 그렇게 되는지는 생각하지 않았어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A36
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F8BA67, 000D7B39, 00A0E0FD, 00922AE5
#. Notes = Sad and scared. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 왜 후회하는 거죠?, Worried and regretful. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Regretful and angry at herself. / Depressed / to Player Default (+3 more)
#: 020238E7/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A36
msgctxt "00083E"
msgid "You heard them in battle. I built Delta to be a creation of peace. To help mankind. Not... this."
msgstr "전투 중 델타의 말을 들었잖아요. 저는 델타를 평화의 창조물로 만들었어요. 인류를 돕도록요. 이런... 모습이 아니라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A21
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0028C8F8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238E8/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A21
msgctxt "00083F"
msgid "Why would you regret it?"
msgstr "왜 후회하는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000BB530
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 지금은 업그레이드 계획을 세울 때가 아닌 것 같아요.
#: 020238E9/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A0D
msgctxt "000841"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr "그렇죠..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004046F5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238EA/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239F9
msgctxt "000842"
msgid "I don't think you should be planning any upgrades right now."
msgstr "지금은 업그레이드 계획을 세울 때가 아닌 것 같아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 006740F3
#. Notes = Worried, and emotionally exhausted. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 델타가 강해질수록 우리 모두에게 더 좋아요.
#: 020238EB/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239E5
msgctxt "000844"
msgid "That's what I'm worried about."
msgstr "그게 제가 걱정하는 점이에요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EB7C14
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238EC/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239D1
msgctxt "000845"
msgid "The stronger we make Delta, the better for all of us."
msgstr "델타가 강해질수록 우리 모두에게 더 좋아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0066A22F
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but trying to crack a faint joke. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 당신에게 보상을 받을 필요는 없지만, 고마워요.
#: 020238ED/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239BD
msgctxt "000847"
msgid "I could always make it Delta's reward. "
msgstr "언제든 델타의 보상으로 삼을 수도 있겠죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A22061
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238EE/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239AA
msgctxt "000848"
msgid "I don't need a reward from you, but I appreciate it."
msgstr "당신에게 보상을 받을 필요는 없지만, 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A58
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001D663E
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but trying to crack a faint bit of sarcasm. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 델타라면 또 한 번 업그레이드받는 걸 정말 좋아할 거예요. 지난번 것도 무척 기뻐하는 것 같았잖아요.
#: 020238EF/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A58
msgctxt "00084A"
msgid "I don't know about that."
msgstr "그건 잘 모르겠어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A42
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00562D71
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238F0/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A42
msgctxt "00084B"
msgid "I'm sure Delta would love another upgrade. They sounded really happy about that last one."
msgstr "델타라면 또 한 번 업그레이드받는 걸 정말 좋아할 거예요. 지난번 것도 무척 기뻐하는 것 같았잖아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA6434, 008AC966, 005EFA53, 00613ACF
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Emotionally exhausted. Though a hint of gratefulness at the end. / Depressed / to Player Default, Emotionally exhausted, and maybe a little scared of Delta. / Depressed / to Player Default
#: 020238F1/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A2D
msgctxt "00084F"
msgid "For my final note, while it was nice to work on Delta before at the facility, I will admit it wasn't my best work."
msgstr "마지막으로 덧붙이자면, 전에 시설에서 델타를 작업할 수 있었던 건 좋았지만 솔직히 제 최고의 결과물은 아니었어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A19
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00BE9C72
#. Notes = Concerned. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating, Prompt: 결국 다 잘돼서 그저 감사할 뿐이에요.
#: 020238F2/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A19
msgctxt "000850"
msgid "Yes. It was a miracle we even got out of there."
msgstr "네. 거기서 빠져나온 것만 해도 기적이었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A04
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CFF819
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238F3/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A04
msgctxt "000851"
msgid "I'm just thankful it all worked out in the end."
msgstr "결국 다 잘돼서 그저 감사할 뿐이에요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C24131
#. Notes = Concerned. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 음. 델타는 당신을 정말 그리워했던 것 같아요.
#: 020238F4/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239F0
msgctxt "000852"
msgid "Right... About Delta..."
msgstr "맞아요... 델타에 대해서는..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007DDB7E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238F5/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239DC
msgctxt "000853"
msgid "Eh. Delta seemed like they really missed you."
msgstr "음. 델타는 당신을 정말 그리워했던 것 같아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 002DE999
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 별일 아니었습니다, 부로 씨.
#: 020238F6/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239C8
msgctxt "000854"
msgid "Still, thank you."
msgstr "그래도 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A80FAF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238F7/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239B4
msgctxt "000855"
msgid "It was no problem, Ms. Bourreau."
msgstr "별일 아니었습니다, 부로 씨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A64
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008E51BD
#. Notes = Disappointed. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: VOID가 보수를 잘 줬으니까, 옳은 선택처럼 느껴졌어요.
#: 020238F8/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A64
msgctxt "000856"
msgid "I see... Well, I hope you enjoy your reward."
msgstr "그렇군요... 그럼 보상을 즐기시길 바라요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007F2660
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238F9/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A4F
msgctxt "000857"
msgid "VOID paid me well, so it felt like the right choice."
msgstr "VOID가 보수를 잘 줬으니까, 옳은 선택처럼 느껴졌어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A38
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EB2862
#. Notes = Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 그냥 테란과 싸우고 싶었을 뿐입니다.
#: 020238FA/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A38
msgctxt "000858"
msgid "That's understandable. But the 'thank you' stands nevertheless."
msgstr "이해돼요. 하지만 그래도 '고마워요'라는 말은 변함없어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A23
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D88B0B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238FB/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A23
msgctxt "000859"
msgid "I simply wanted to fight the Terrans."
msgstr "그냥 테란과 싸우고 싶었을 뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 002CE078
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020238FF/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239D3
msgctxt "00085A"
msgid "Just keep yourself out of trouble."
msgstr "문제에 휘말리지 않게 조심해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00461CD9, 001BB0E2, 002EDB60
#. Notes = Though she is still annoyed, she wants to lighten the mood and be grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 020238FD/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239FB
msgctxt "00085B"
msgid "So no matter what your motivations were for getting me out of there, thanks."
msgstr "그러니 절 거기서 빼낸 동기가 뭐였든, 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00461CD9, 001BB0E2, 002EDB60
#. Notes = Though she is still annoyed, she wants to lighten the mood and be grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 020238FD/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239FB
msgctxt "00085C"
msgid "Despite my efforts, I don't think I would have gotten out of that facility alone."
msgstr "제 노력에도 불구하고, 혼자서는 그 시설에서 빠져나오지 못했을 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00461CD9, 001BB0E2, 002EDB60
#. Notes = Though she is still annoyed, she wants to lighten the mood and be grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Sad/Emotionally exhausted, but grateful. / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 020238FD/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239FB
msgctxt "00085D"
msgid "Before anything else, there were a few more things I wanted to say. First off: thank you."
msgstr "다른 것보다 먼저, 하고 싶은 말이 몇 가지 더 있었어요. 첫째로: 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004A0501
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but trying to crack a small joke. Half-smug about it. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 문제에 휘말리지 않게 조심해요.
#: 020238FE/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239E7
msgctxt "00085E"
msgid "What is VOID going to do? Kick me out?"
msgstr "VOID가 뭘 할 건데요? 날 쫓아낼까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FE2FBD
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but annoyed. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 테란을 막을 수 있는 최고의 희망은 VOID예요.
#: 02023900/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239BF
msgctxt "00085F"
msgid "It appears so. But that doesn't mean we can't question them."
msgstr "그런 것 같아요. 하지만 그렇다고 우리가 그들에게 따져 묻지 못하는 건 아니죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C55C64
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023901/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239AC
msgctxt "000860"
msgid "VOID is the best hope we have to stop the Terrans."
msgstr "테란을 막을 수 있는 최고의 희망은 VOID예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008CB6DC
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 함께 일하려면 서로를 믿어야 해요.
#: 02023902/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A5A
msgctxt "000861"
msgid "You say that, but even they don't trust one another. VOID is built on distrust. That's their game."
msgstr "그렇게 말하지만, 그들조차 서로를 믿지 않아요. VOID는 불신 위에 세워졌어요. 그게 그들의 방식이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A44
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000797F7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023903/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A44
msgctxt "000862"
msgid "If we're going to work together, we need to trust each other."
msgstr "함께 일하려면 서로를 믿어야 해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A1C89C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023905/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A1B
msgctxt "000863"
msgid "That would be smart."
msgstr "그게 현명하겠군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000EE844, 0054D1E5, 00487639, 00D83F79
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, yet annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Emotionally exhausted, but visible upset/mad. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Emotionally exhausted, but now disgusted thinking about VOID. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust (+2 more)
#: 02023906/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A06
msgctxt "000864"
msgid "They only serve one thing. We both know it. Perhaps I can be the one to curb whatever danger they pose."
msgstr "그들의 목적은 하나뿐입니다. 우리 둘 다 알잖습니까. 어쩌면 그들이 끼칠 위험을 제가 억제할 수 있을지도 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000EE844, 0054D1E5, 00487639, 00D83F79
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, yet annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Emotionally exhausted, but visible upset/mad. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Emotionally exhausted, but now disgusted thinking about VOID. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust (+2 more)
#: 02023906/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A06
msgctxt "000865"
msgid "Besides, I don't trust VOID. I've seen people like them plenty of times. You think they care about the public? The Settled Systems? The very thing they swear their protection to?"
msgstr "게다가 저는 VOID를 믿지 않습니다. 그런 자들은 숱하게 봐 왔습니다. 그들이 대중을 신경 쓴다고 생각하십니까? 개척 성계를요? 자기들이 지키겠다고 맹세한 바로 그것을요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000EE844, 0054D1E5, 00487639, 00D83F79
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, yet annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Emotionally exhausted, but visible upset/mad. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Emotionally exhausted, but now disgusted thinking about VOID. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust (+2 more)
#: 02023906/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A06
msgctxt "000866"
msgid "The machines and Terran military must be stopped. The longer they're out there, the greater danger they pose."
msgstr "기계들과 테란 군은 반드시 막아야 합니다. 저들이 밖에 오래 있을수록 더 큰 위험이 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000EE844, 0054D1E5, 00487639, 00D83F79
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, yet annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Emotionally exhausted, but visible upset/mad. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Emotionally exhausted, but now disgusted thinking about VOID. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust (+2 more)
#: 02023906/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A06
msgctxt "000867"
msgid "I will stay, for now. Not much I can do about it anyway."
msgstr "당분간은 남아 있겠습니다. 어차피 제가 할 수 있는 일도 별로 없으니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0077B759
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 테란을 막고 싶다면 여기가 가장 좋은 곳입니다.
#: 02023907/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239F2
msgctxt "000868"
msgid "Is that the line you're still toeing? I didn't just kill Terrans. I killed someone. Someone innocent!"
msgstr "아직도 그런 입장을 고수하는 거야? 난 테란만 죽인 게 아니야. 사람을 죽였어. 죄 없는 사람을!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B2D660
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023908/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239DE
msgctxt "000869"
msgid "If you want to stop the Terrans this is the best place to be."
msgstr "테란을 막고 싶다면 여기가 가장 좋은 곳입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B1315C
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, yet regretful. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 그들이 당신을 여기 붙잡아 둘 줄은 몰랐습니다.
#: 02023909/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239CA
msgctxt "00086A"
msgid "Sounds like both of us have made some foolish judgements as of late."
msgstr "최근에는 우리 둘 다 어리석은 판단을 좀 했던 것 같군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00072A32
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202390A/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239B6
msgctxt "00086B"
msgid "I didn't think they would keep you here."
msgstr "그들이 당신을 여기 붙잡아 둘 줄은 몰랐습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A11
msgctxt "00086C"
msgid "You should have expected something like this."
msgstr "이런 일쯤은 예상했어야죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A51
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004D6219
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202390C/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A51
msgctxt "00086D"
msgid "I'm just doing my job."
msgstr "전 그저 제 일을 하고 있을 뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001475E0
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but also annoyed. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 이런 일쯤은 예상했어야죠.
#: 0202390D/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A3A
msgctxt "00086E"
msgid "Forgive me for not noticing, my mind was a bit preoccupied."
msgstr "알아차리지 못해 죄송합니다. 다른 생각으로 머리가 좀 복잡했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A25
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00D6279C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202390E/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A25
msgctxt "00086F"
msgid "You should have expected something like this."
msgstr "이런 일쯤은 예상했어야죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A66
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004F7D96
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but also annoyed. / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant, Prompt: 전 그저 제 일을 하고 있을 뿐입니다.
#: 0202390B/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A66
msgctxt "000870"
msgid "You could have at least warned me."
msgstr "적어도 미리 경고는 해 줄 수 있었잖아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00BB5216
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted, but also annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02023910/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020239FD
msgctxt "000872"
msgid "Escaped one prison to be confined to another. Did you know about this?"
msgstr "감옥 하나에서 탈출했더니 또 다른 감옥에 갇힌 셈이군. 이거 알고 있었어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00454575
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "Roxane has been confined enough. At least let her have free range of Anchorpoint.") / to Player Default
#: 02023914/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020239AD
msgctxt "000873"
msgid "We wouldn't want to confine her to this room. While she can't leave Anchorpoint, she's free to roam the station."
msgstr "그녀를 이 방에만 가둬 두려는 건 아닙니다. 앵커포인트를 떠날 수는 없지만, 기지 안에서는 자유롭게 돌아다닐 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A2B2FF
#. Notes = Angry, but trying to keep it mostly to herself. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02023913/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020239C1
msgctxt "000874"
msgid "Never mind. We can talk about this later."
msgstr "됐습니다. 이 얘기는 나중에 하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0001EB8A
#. Notes = Angry, but trying to keep it mostly to herself.(Actual Last Line - Player: "That is for the best.") / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 02023915/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A5C
msgctxt "000875"
msgid "As you say."
msgstr "말씀하신 대로 하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0086324A, 00BFB50D
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / to Player Default
#: 02023912/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020239D5
msgctxt "000876"
msgid "Well done on bringing Ms. Bourreau to us. As we promised before, your reward."
msgstr "부로 씨를 데려오느라 수고했습니다. 앞서 약속드린 보상입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0086324A, 00BFB50D
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / to Player Default
#: 02023912/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020239D5
msgctxt "000877"
msgid "Well, now that we have the Terrans' much wanted roboticist, we find ourselves with a bit of an upper hand."
msgstr "자, 이제 테란이 그토록 원하던 로봇공학자를 확보했으니 우리가 조금은 우위를 점하게 됐군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A46
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00E1ACD9
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "It was risky saving her the first time. Don't make me have to do it again.") / to Player Default
#: 02023916/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A46
msgctxt "000878"
msgid "It's in all of our best interest that you don't take such a risk again."
msgstr "다시는 그런 위험을 감수하지 않는 것이 우리 모두에게 최선입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A31
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00D0B6C5
#. Notes = Angry, but trying to keep it mostly to herself. / Disgust / to Radha, Face: Disgust
#: 02023917/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A31
msgctxt "000879"
msgid "Do I really not have a choice?"
msgstr "정말 나한테 선택권은 없는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E1D478, 00BB762D, 006DBB18
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "She's been held hostage enough. She doesn't need to be held any longer.") / to Player Default, Professional. / to Player Default
#: 02023918/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A1C
msgctxt "00087A"
msgid "You both must understand."
msgstr "두 분 모두 이해해 주셔야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E1D478, 00BB762D, 006DBB18
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "She's been held hostage enough. She doesn't need to be held any longer.") / to Player Default, Professional. / to Player Default
#: 02023918/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A1C
msgctxt "00087B"
msgid "Right now we have to think of what's best for everyone."
msgstr "지금은 모두에게 최선인 일을 생각해야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E1D478, 00BB762D, 006DBB18
#. Notes = Professional. (Actual Last Line - Player: "She's been held hostage enough. She doesn't need to be held any longer.") / to Player Default, Professional. / to Player Default
#: 02023918/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02023A1C
msgctxt "00087C"
msgid "There is little we can do in this matter."
msgstr "이 문제에 관해서는 저희가 할 수 있는 일이 거의 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0079F0A3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202391A/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239F3
msgctxt "00087D"
msgid "Roxane has been confined enough. At least let her have free range of Anchorpoint."
msgstr "로잔은 이미 충분히 갇혀 있었어요. 적어도 앵커포인트 안에서는 자유롭게 다니게 해 주세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 000083E5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202391C/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239CB
msgctxt "00087E"
msgid "That is for the best."
msgstr "그게 최선입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A67
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 007FB254
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202391E/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A67
msgctxt "00087F"
msgid "It was risky saving her the first time. Don't make me have to do it again."
msgstr "처음 그녀를 구한 것도 위험한 일이었습니다. 제가 또다시 구하러 나서게 만들지는 마십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008477AA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023920/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A3C
msgctxt "000880"
msgid "She's been held hostage enough. She doesn't need to be held any longer."
msgstr "그녀는 인질로 잡혀 있던 것만으로도 충분합니다. 더 붙잡아 둘 필요는 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A27
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00C90942, 00798737
#. Notes = Professional. / to Roxane
#: 02023921/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A27
msgctxt "000881"
msgid "You will be staying here."
msgstr "당신은 여기에 머무르게 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A27
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00C90942, 00798737
#. Notes = Professional. / to Roxane
#: 02023921/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A27
msgctxt "000882"
msgid "The matter of you staying here is not up for debate. If you leave, the Terrans will capture you once again."
msgstr "당신이 여기 머무는 문제는 논의의 대상이 아닙니다. 떠나면 테란에게 다시 붙잡힐 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A13
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002FD370, 003EBA5A
#. Notes = Professional, however, she is trying to show a little empathy to what Roxane just said. / to Roxane, Professional, however, she is trying to show a little empathy to what Roxane just said. / Stern / to Roxane, Face: Stern
#: 02023922/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A13
msgctxt "000883"
msgid "Unfortunately, Ms. Bourreau, we cannot always distinguish the lines between soldier and civilians here due to the way they've been assimilating people into their forces."
msgstr "안타깝게도 부로 씨, 그들이 사람들을 병력으로 흡수하는 방식 때문에 여기서는 군인과 민간인의 경계를 늘 구분할 수가 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008DD8D7, 005C3AF9
#. Notes = Angry at herself. / Disgust / to RyujinRep, Face: Disgust, Angry, now at VOID. / Angry / to RyujinRep, Face: Angry
#: 02023923/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239FE
msgctxt "000884"
msgid "I wish to stop the Terrans as much as you, maybe even more, but to cause the death of innocents? I can't be part of that."
msgstr "저도 당신만큼, 어쩌면 그 이상으로 테란을 막고 싶습니다. 하지만 무고한 이들의 죽음을 초래하는 일이라면? 저는 함께할 수 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008DD8D7, 005C3AF9
#. Notes = Angry at herself. / Disgust / to RyujinRep, Face: Disgust, Angry, now at VOID. / Angry / to RyujinRep, Face: Angry
#: 02023923/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239FE
msgctxt "000885"
msgid "We may have stopped the Terrans at the production facility. But you didn't see it. I killed civilians. Just... people."
msgstr "생산 시설에서 테란을 막아냈을지는 몰라. 하지만 넌 못 봤잖아. 난 민간인들을 죽였어. 그냥... 평범한 사람들을."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00483611
#. Notes = Confused. / Worried / to Roxane, Face: Worried
#: 02023924/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239EA
msgctxt "000886"
msgid "I'm afraid we don't understand what you mean."
msgstr "죄송하지만 무슨 뜻인지 잘 모르겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A47
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0004C74F
#. Notes = Suspicious., but unsure how to even react to what the player just said / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 내 새 친구를 그들에게 소개해 주고 싶었을지도 모르지.
#: 0202392A/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A47
msgctxt "000887"
msgid "That's, mmm..."
msgstr "그건, 음..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DDF99A, 008B7162, 0055CECE
#. Notes = Professional. / to Roxane
#: 02023926/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239C2
msgctxt "000888"
msgid "On top of this, you can help us better understand the Terrans. Their strengths. Their quirks. Their weak spots. Anything worthy of note."
msgstr "게다가 당신은 저희가 테란을 더 잘 이해하도록 도울 수 있습니다. 그들의 강점, 특이점, 약점. 기록할 만한 것이라면 무엇이든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DDF99A, 008B7162, 0055CECE
#. Notes = Professional. / to Roxane
#: 02023926/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239C2
msgctxt "000889"
msgid "Anchorpoint is most likely the safest place you can be right now."
msgstr "앵커포인트는 지금 당신이 있을 수 있는 가장 안전한 곳일 가능성이 큽니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DDF99A, 008B7162, 0055CECE
#. Notes = Professional. / to Roxane
#: 02023926/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239C2
msgctxt "00088A"
msgid "We have decided the best course of action is for you to remain here while the Terrans still pose a threat."
msgstr "테란이 아직 위협이 되는 동안에는 당신이 여기 머무는 것이 최선이라고 결정했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00208EBB
#. Notes = Suspicious. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 우리는 당신의 안전을 확인하고 싶었습니다.
#: 02023928/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239AE
msgctxt "00088B"
msgid "That's it?"
msgstr "그게 다야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00234E28
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023929/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A5D
msgctxt "00088C"
msgid "We wanted to make sure you were safe."
msgstr "우리는 당신의 안전을 확인하고 싶었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0045D620
#. Notes = Though she is still emotionally exhausted, Roxane still is angered and has the strength to show it. / Defiant / to Tracy, Face: Defiant
#: 02023925/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239D6
msgctxt "00088D"
msgid "And what Terrans would those be?"
msgstr "그 테란들이라니, 어떤 테란을 말하는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0014BAC7
#. Notes = Suspicious. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: VOID는 당신이 테란 손에 들어가는 걸 원치 않았습니다.
#: 0202392E/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239F4
msgctxt "00088E"
msgid "How very kind..."
msgstr "참 친절하시네요..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00686D47
#. Notes = Suspicious. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 당신의 도움이 필요합니다.
#: 0202392C/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A1D
msgctxt "00088F"
msgid "Is that so..."
msgstr "그런가요..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A32
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA3B8A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202392B/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A32
msgctxt "000890"
msgid "Maybe I wanted them to meet my new friend."
msgstr "내 새 친구를 그들에게 소개해 주고 싶었을지도 모르지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A08
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0094CC4C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202392D/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A08
msgctxt "000891"
msgid "We need your help."
msgstr "당신의 도움이 필요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C8C195
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202392F/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239E0
msgctxt "000892"
msgid "VOID didn't want you in the Terrans' hands."
msgstr "VOID는 당신이 테란 손에 들어가는 걸 원치 않았습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A49620
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023937/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239FF
msgctxt "000893"
msgid "With the help of Roxane, we shut down the whole production facility."
msgstr "로잔의 도움으로 생산 시설 전체를 폐쇄했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A68
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00BEF10F
#. Notes = Professional. / to Player Default, Prompt: 네.
#: 02023932/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A68
msgctxt "000894"
msgid "Good."
msgstr "좋습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A54
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002A876B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023933/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A54
msgctxt "000895"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 006636B8
#. Notes = Professional. / to Player Default, Prompt: 로잔을 무사히 여기 데려왔고, 테란 시설은 이제 가동 중지됐습니다.
#: 02023934/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A3D
msgctxt "000896"
msgid "It sounds like you've accomplished more than VOID could have hoped. Well done."
msgstr "VOID가 바라던 것 이상을 해낸 것 같군요. 훌륭합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A28
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0081D0D7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023935/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A28
msgctxt "000897"
msgid "I got Roxane here safely and the Terran's facility is now offline."
msgstr "로잔을 무사히 여기 데려왔고, 테란 시설은 이제 가동 중지됐습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A14
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009760C6
#. Notes = Professional. / to Player Default, Prompt: 로잔의 도움으로 생산 시설 전체를 폐쇄했습니다.
#: 02023936/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A14
msgctxt "000898"
msgid "Well done to both of you then."
msgstr "그렇다면 두 분 모두 수고하셨습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CC0C13
#. Notes = Suspicious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02023931/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239B8
msgctxt "000899"
msgid "All right. Say it. Why am I here?"
msgstr "좋아. 말해 봐. 내가 왜 여기 있는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0030CFF1
#. Notes = Professional.(Actual Last Line - Radha: "Either way, it is good to have you here.") / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02023938/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:020239EB
msgctxt "00089A"
msgid "I assume this mission was a complete success then?"
msgstr "그럼 이번 임무는 완전한 성공이었다고 봐도 되겠습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00D858BF
#. Notes = Professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02023939/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:020239D7
msgctxt "00089B"
msgid "Either way, it is good to have you here."
msgstr "어느 쪽이든, 당신이 여기 와 주셔서 다행입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00B9E95B
#. Notes = Professional, but also poking fun at the fact the Player could be doing all this just for the money. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0202393A/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:020239C3
msgctxt "00089C"
msgid "But, who's to say."
msgstr "하지만, 누가 알겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DEDA26
#. Notes = Professional. / Serious / to Roxane, Face: Serious
#: 0202393B/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:020239AF
msgctxt "00089D"
msgid "And the goal to destroy the Terrans."
msgstr "그리고 테란을 파괴한다는 목표도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00A69CCB
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / Friendly / to Roxane, Face: Friendly
#: 0202393C/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:02023A5E
msgctxt "00089E"
msgid "There was pay involved."
msgstr "보수가 걸려 있었거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000EDA18
#. Notes = Though Roxane is suspicious of VOID, this line is to the player, giving a light jab in feeling disappointed the Player. Still exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202393D/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:02023A4A
msgctxt "00089F"
msgid "Though, part of me hopes he did come get me out of the kindness of his heart."
msgstr "그래도 한편으로는 그 사람이 정말 순수한 호의로 날 구하러 온 거였으면 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A49
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 003222AE
#. Notes = Though Roxane is suspicious of VOID, this line is to the player, giving a light jab in feeling disappointed the Player. Still exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202393D/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:02023A49
msgctxt "0008A0"
msgid "Though, part of me hopes she did come get me out of the kindness of her heart."
msgstr "그래도 한편으로는 그 사람이 정말 순수한 호의로 날 구하러 온 거였으면 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A48
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00286C2E
#. Notes = Though Roxane is suspicious of VOID, this line is to the player, giving a light jab in feeling disappointed the Player. Still exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202393D/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:02023A48
msgctxt "0008A1"
msgid "Though, part of me hopes they did come get me out of the kindness of their heart."
msgstr "그래도 한편으로는 그 사람이 정말 순수한 호의로 날 구하러 온 거였으면 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A09
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00542AE9
#. Notes = Suspicious of VOID, but still just emotionally exhausted from the facility. / Nervous / to Percy, Face: Nervous
#: 0202393E/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:02023A09
msgctxt "0008A2"
msgid "Should have known my savior wasn't working alone against the Terrans."
msgstr "날 구해준 사람이 혼자 테란에 맞서던 게 아니라는 걸 진작 알았어야 했는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 008FC0B3
#. Notes = Friendly, yet professional. / to Roxane
#: 0202393F/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000A_VOID_ROX:020239F5
msgctxt "0008A3"
msgid "Ms. Roxane Bourreau, it's such a pleasure to see you alive and well."
msgstr "로잔 부로 씨, 무사한 모습을 보니 정말 반갑습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F9AB7D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023945/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A3E
msgctxt "0008A4"
msgid "There's no point crying over a dead man."
msgstr "죽은 사람을 두고 울어 봐야 소용없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A69
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C529D0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023943/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A69
msgctxt "0008A5"
msgid "Think about this on the ride out of here. Reinforcements could be here at any moment."
msgstr "여기서 나가는 길에 잘 생각해 봐. 지원군이 언제 도착할지 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A55
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 003638A4
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 죽은 사람을 두고 울어 봐야 소용없어.
#: 02023944/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A55
msgctxt "0008A6"
msgid "Let's just go..."
msgstr "그냥 가자..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0096169A
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 여기서 나가는 길에 잘 생각해 봐. 지원군이 언제 도착할지 몰라.
#: 02023942/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239B9
msgctxt "0008A7"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00923149
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023941/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239CD
msgctxt "0008A8"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr "가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FA1264
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 가자.
#: 02023940/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239E1
msgctxt "0008A9"
msgid "I'm right behind you..."
msgstr "바로 뒤따라갈게..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000913AE, 00570919, 005BB5F7
#. Notes = Very angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 델타 말대로, 그들은 그저 희생자였어., Angry at herself. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Angry at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202394B/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239C4
msgctxt "0008AA"
msgid "Dammit!"
msgstr "젠장!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000913AE, 00570919, 005BB5F7
#. Notes = Very angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 델타 말대로, 그들은 그저 희생자였어., Angry at herself. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Angry at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202394B/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239C4
msgctxt "0008AB"
msgid "I didn't mean for people, just people, to get caught up in this."
msgstr "사람들이, 그냥 평범한 사람들이, 이 일에 휘말리게 하려던 게 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000913AE, 00570919, 005BB5F7
#. Notes = Very angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 델타 말대로, 그들은 그저 희생자였어., Angry at herself. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Angry at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202394B/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239C4
msgctxt "0008AC"
msgid "No one should be 'just a casualty'!"
msgstr "그 누구도 '그냥 희생자'로 치부돼선 안 돼!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A00
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C976BC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023948/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A00
msgctxt "0008AD"
msgid "You couldn't have known."
msgstr "네가 알 수 있었을 리 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A15
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C11861
#. Notes = Angry and sad. / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant, Prompt: 네가 알 수 있었을 리 없어.
#: 02023947/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A15
msgctxt "0008AE"
msgid "Couldn't I?"
msgstr "정말 그랬을까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A77132, 0029A101
#. Notes = Sad and horrified. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 다음부턴 행동하기 전에 생각부터 해., Sad, but now more emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default
#: 02023949/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239EC
msgctxt "0008AF"
msgid "*Sigh* You are right. I did this..."
msgstr "*한숨* 네 말이 맞아. 내가 한 짓이야..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A77132, 0029A101
#. Notes = Sad and horrified. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 다음부턴 행동하기 전에 생각부터 해., Sad, but now more emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default
#: 02023949/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239EC
msgctxt "0008B0"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr "네 말이 맞아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DC3C87
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202394A/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239D8
msgctxt "0008B1"
msgid "Next time you should think before you act."
msgstr "다음부턴 행동하기 전에 생각부터 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001E465F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202394C/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020239B0
msgctxt "0008B2"
msgid "Like Delta said, they were just a casualty."
msgstr "델타 말대로, 그들은 그저 희생자였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A60
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007D8CFF, 00E1D699, 00ED94D0
#. Notes = Angry, sad, and regretful. Emphasis on 'they'. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 이 사람은 테란 함대 소속이었어., Angry and regretful. Emphasis on the 'I's. / Sad / to Player Default, Sad and horrified. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 0202394D/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A60
msgctxt "0008B3"
msgid "I wanted the Terrans to pay. I didn't think..."
msgstr "테란에게 대가를 치르게 하고 싶었어. 생각을 못 했어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A60
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007D8CFF, 00E1D699, 00ED94D0
#. Notes = Angry, sad, and regretful. Emphasis on 'they'. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 이 사람은 테란 함대 소속이었어., Angry and regretful. Emphasis on the 'I's. / Sad / to Player Default, Sad and horrified. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 0202394D/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A60
msgctxt "0008B4"
msgid "I was here. I didn't ask for it."
msgstr "난 여기 있었어. 원해서 그런 게 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A60
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007D8CFF, 00E1D699, 00ED94D0
#. Notes = Angry, sad, and regretful. Emphasis on 'they'. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 이 사람은 테란 함대 소속이었어., Angry and regretful. Emphasis on the 'I's. / Sad / to Player Default, Sad and horrified. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 0202394D/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A60
msgctxt "0008B5"
msgid "But what control did they have?"
msgstr "하지만 그들이 뭘 어쩔 수 있었겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00340366
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202394E/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A4B
msgctxt "0008B6"
msgid "This person was part of the Terran Armada."
msgstr "이 사람은 테란 함대 소속이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A33
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001BED4F, 00819C54
#. Notes = Sad and horrified as Roxane's actions to save herself caused the death of, possibly, an innocent man. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Sad and horrified. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202394F/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A33
msgctxt "0008B7"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr "그래..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A33
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001BED4F, 00819C54
#. Notes = Sad and horrified as Roxane's actions to save herself caused the death of, possibly, an innocent man. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Sad and horrified. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202394F/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:02023A33
msgctxt "0008B8"
msgid "I hijacked the Terrans' machinery to escape, not this... Not to gun down just- Someone."
msgstr "난 도망치려고 테란 기계들을 탈취한 거지, 이런 걸 하려던 게 아니야... 그냥 사람을 쏴 죽이려고 한 게 아니라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E9D356
#. Notes = Angry and horrified. / VeryAngry / to Delta, Face: VeryAngry
#: 02023951/00950/SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA:02023A0A
msgctxt "0008B9"
msgid "Delta!"
msgstr "델타!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0033496F, 00C03B4A
#. Notes = Straight forward. No empathy for the dead or Roxane. / to Roxane
#: 02023952/00950/SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA:020239F6
msgctxt "0008BA"
msgid "Assessment: Human did not fight. Scared. Failure. Typical emotional response. Easily killed when fleeing. A casualty."
msgstr "평가: 인간은 싸우지 않았다. 겁에 질림. 실패. 전형적인 감정 반응. 도주 중 쉽게 사망. 사상자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0033496F, 00C03B4A
#. Notes = Straight forward. No empathy for the dead or Roxane. / to Roxane
#: 02023952/00950/SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA:020239F6
msgctxt "0008BB"
msgid "Occupation: Janitor. No weapons detected. Minimal damage inflicted."
msgstr "직업: 관리원. 무기 감지 안 됨. 입힌 피해 미미."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A56
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 006D4BF6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023957/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A56
msgctxt "0008BC"
msgid "You don't look well."
msgstr "안색이 안 좋아 보여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0006766C
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 안색이 안 좋아 보여.
#: 02023956/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239A7
msgctxt "0008BD"
msgid "I'm just tired... I'll be better once I'm away from this hell."
msgstr "그냥 피곤해서 그래... 이 지옥 같은 곳에서 벗어나면 괜찮아질 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DF7189
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 가자.
#: 02023958/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A4C
msgctxt "0008BE"
msgid "Right. Let's."
msgstr "그래. 가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 006A0CAE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023955/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239BA
msgctxt "0008BF"
msgid "You did a lot of good here, Roxane."
msgstr "여기서 정말 많은 선한 일을 했어, 록산."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00087EB1
#. Notes = Horrified. / Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief
#: 02023953/00950/SFTER_MQ02B_0950_ROX_DELTA:020239E2
msgctxt "0008C0"
msgid "Who's this? They aren't a Terran, are they?"
msgstr "누구야? 테란은 아니겠지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A10
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009E8D05
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202395F/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A10
msgctxt "0008C1"
msgid "I'll live. But that was a close one."
msgstr "살 순 있어. 하지만 정말 아슬아슬했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005EF5E3, 0072D86E
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 여기서 정말 많은 선한 일을 했어, 록산.
#: 02023954/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239CE
msgctxt "0008C2"
msgid "Can we go now?"
msgstr "이제 가도 돼?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005EF5E3, 0072D86E
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 여기서 정말 많은 선한 일을 했어, 록산.
#: 02023954/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239CE
msgctxt "0008C3"
msgid "Hm, right, good."
msgstr "흠, 그래, 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DBADD6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023959/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A1F
msgctxt "0008C4"
msgid "Let's go."
msgstr "가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A65
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00919417
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202395B/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A65
msgctxt "0008C5"
msgid "You cut that pretty close."
msgstr "정말 아슬아슬했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A12
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E09604, 00B86DDE
#. Notes = Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 좀 더 나을 수도 있겠지만..., Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad
#: 0202395C/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A12
msgctxt "0008C6"
msgid "Though, that may not make up for the fact that you risked so much."
msgstr "그래도 네가 그렇게 큰 위험을 감수했다는 사실이 덮이진 않을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A12
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E09604, 00B86DDE
#. Notes = Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 좀 더 나을 수도 있겠지만..., Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad
#: 0202395C/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A12
msgctxt "0008C7"
msgid "I'm sorry. But know you've stopped these monster's facility. It will be near impossible for them to get it back and running."
msgstr "미안해. 하지만 알아 둬, 넌 이 괴물들의 시설을 멈췄어. 놈들이 다시 가동시키기는 거의 불가능할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A01
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 002EC86A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202395D/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A01
msgctxt "0008C8"
msgid "I could be better..."
msgstr "좀 더 나을 수도 있겠지만..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FBFD80, 002763BB
#. Notes = Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 살 순 있어. 하지만 정말 아슬아슬했어., Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad
#: 0202395E/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239FA
msgctxt "0008C9"
msgid "But it's over, for here, for now, at least. I'm sorry..."
msgstr "그래도 여기서는, 적어도 지금은 끝났어. 미안해..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FBFD80, 002763BB
#. Notes = Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 살 순 있어. 하지만 정말 아슬아슬했어., Emotionally exhausted. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad
#: 0202395E/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239FA
msgctxt "0008CA"
msgid "The system was harder to crack than I expected."
msgstr "시스템을 뚫는 게 생각보다 더 어려웠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A39
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00677395
#. Notes = Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 정말 아슬아슬했어.
#: 0202395A/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A39
msgctxt "0008CB"
msgid "The system was trickier than the last one. Every system has their safety measure, but this one... Gods, the Terrans are cautious bastards."
msgstr "지난번 시스템보다 더 까다로웠어. 시스템마다 안전장치는 있지만, 이건... 세상에, 테란 놈들 정말 조심성도 많더군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A24
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00539B8F, 00C3AC49, 00A09C62
#. Notes = Touched, and surprised by the praise. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Prompt: 정말 때맞춰 끝냈군. 훌륭했어, 부로!, A little nervous to praise Delta, but still wants to say kind words to the Player and Delta. Soft and sweet. / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02023960/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A24
msgctxt "0008CC"
msgid "So, let's get out of here?"
msgstr "그럼, 여기서 나갈까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A24
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00539B8F, 00C3AC49, 00A09C62
#. Notes = Touched, and surprised by the praise. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Prompt: 정말 때맞춰 끝냈군. 훌륭했어, 부로!, A little nervous to praise Delta, but still wants to say kind words to the Player and Delta. Soft and sweet. / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02023960/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A24
msgctxt "0008CD"
msgid "You and... Delta, did well too..."
msgstr "너랑... 델타도 잘해 줬어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A24
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00539B8F, 00C3AC49, 00A09C62
#. Notes = Touched, and surprised by the praise. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Prompt: 정말 때맞춰 끝냈군. 훌륭했어, 부로!, A little nervous to praise Delta, but still wants to say kind words to the Player and Delta. Soft and sweet. / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Returning to reality somewhat and starting to get nervous over their situation / Adrenaline of situation wearing off. Growing emotionally exhausted. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02023960/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A24
msgctxt "0008CE"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D34A6D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023961/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:020239C5
msgctxt "0008CF"
msgid "Not a moment too soon. Wonderful job, Bourreau!"
msgstr "정말 때맞춰 끝냈군. 훌륭했어, 부로!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0079E685
#. Notes = Determined. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired, Prompt: 그런 예상이라면, 네가 끝내기 전에 내가 전부 죽여 버렸을지도 모르겠네.
#: 02023963/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239DB
msgctxt "0008D0"
msgid "At least one of us is optimistic. Keep it up."
msgstr "우리 중 한 명이라도 낙관적이라 다행이네. 계속 그렇게 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009313AC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023964/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239B5
msgctxt "0008D1"
msgid "With those estimates, I may have killed them all before you're done."
msgstr "그런 예상이라면, 네가 끝내기 전에 내가 전부 죽여 버렸을지도 모르겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A59
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00AD7442
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023968/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A59
msgctxt "0008D2"
msgid "Roxane... I don't feel good about this."
msgstr "록산... 이거 느낌이 좋지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E24AF2, 00D58697, 00430DCD
#. Notes = Worried. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired, Prompt: 이제 남은 건 좀 쉬워지길 바라야지., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396A/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A3F
msgctxt "0008D3"
msgid "I'll just need a minute. Or two... Maybe three. I'll be honest, this system is most likely different than the one I hijacked before."
msgstr "잠깐이면 돼. 아니면 둘... 어쩌면 셋. 솔직히 말하면, 이 시스템은 전에 탈취했던 것과 다를 가능성이 커."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E24AF2, 00D58697, 00430DCD
#. Notes = Worried. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired, Prompt: 이제 남은 건 좀 쉬워지길 바라야지., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396A/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A3F
msgctxt "0008D4"
msgid "Those Terran machines probably already know our location. Which means, while I'm hacking into their system, I need you to keep them off me, and for you to stay alive, obviously."
msgstr "그 테란 기계들이 이미 우리 위치를 알고 있을 거야. 그러니까 내가 놈들 시스템에 침투하는 동안, 네가 놈들이 내게 접근하지 못하게 막아 줘야 해. 물론 너도 살아 있어야 하고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E24AF2, 00D58697, 00430DCD
#. Notes = Worried. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired, Prompt: 이제 남은 건 좀 쉬워지길 바라야지., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Afraid / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396A/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A3F
msgctxt "0008D5"
msgid "No. Unfortunately not."
msgstr "아니. 안타깝지만 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A30
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C8D966
#. Notes = Determined. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 록산... 이거 느낌이 좋지 않아.
#: 02023967/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A30
msgctxt "0008D6"
msgid "We'll be fine! And if we die, we died taking down these monsters!"
msgstr "우린 괜찮을 거야! 그리고 죽더라도, 이 괴물들을 쓰러뜨리다 죽는 거잖아!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A50
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DFAD2B
#. Notes = Determined. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 내가 맡을게. 천천히 해.
#: 02023965/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A50
msgctxt "0008D7"
msgid "I'll try not to."
msgstr "그러지 않도록 해 볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A03
msgctxt "0008D8"
msgid "Roxane... I don't feel good about this."
msgstr "록산... 이거 느낌이 좋지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A43
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0054A4A5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023966/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A43
msgctxt "0008D9"
msgid "I got this. Take your time."
msgstr "내가 맡을게. 천천히 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00178345
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202396B/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239C9
msgctxt "0008DA"
msgid "Hopefully the rest will be easy here on out."
msgstr "이제 남은 건 좀 쉬워지길 바라야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00BA8CB9
#. Notes = Determined. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 02023970/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239EE
msgctxt "0008DB"
msgid "We're here."
msgstr "도착했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DAE68D, 00D7883E
#. Notes = Serious and explaining what she did. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Back to serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02023972/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:020239F1
msgctxt "0008DC"
msgid "If we're going to defeat the Terrans, we're going to need to use their own weapons against them."
msgstr "테란을 물리치려면, 놈들의 무기를 놈들 상대로 써야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000A0EE3
#. Notes = Playful with Delta, though the gravity of their situation is still slightly there. / Smug / to Delta, Face: Smug
#: 02023973/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:020239E6
msgctxt "0008DD"
msgid "That's the idea."
msgstr "그게 계획이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_ROX_NowThenLetsKeepMovingFoward
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650C_ROX_NULL
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00275F44
#. Notes = Serious / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 02023971/00000/SFTER_MQ02B_0650C_ROX_NULL:02023A1A
msgctxt "0008DE"
msgid "Now then, let's keep moving forward."
msgstr "그럼 이제, 계속 앞으로 가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CFCC8B, 00629498
#. Notes = Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 02023974/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:02023A5B
msgctxt "0008E0"
msgid "Running diagnostics..."
msgstr "진단 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FCC63, 006F65ED, 00C1B16F, 00002E93
#. Notes = Worried. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 네가 뭘 하는 건지 알고 있길 바라., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0202396C/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239D2
msgctxt "0008E1"
msgid "Got it?"
msgstr "알겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FCC63, 006F65ED, 00C1B16F, 00002E93
#. Notes = Worried. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 네가 뭘 하는 건지 알고 있길 바라., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0202396C/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239D2
msgctxt "0008E2"
msgid "There's a strong likelihood, however, that the Terrans know where we are. Meaning, if they get in here, I need you to take care of them."
msgstr "하지만 테란이 우리 위치를 알고 있을 가능성이 높아. 그러니까 놈들이 여기로 들어오면, 네가 처리해 줘야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FCC63, 006F65ED, 00C1B16F, 00002E93
#. Notes = Worried. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 네가 뭘 하는 건지 알고 있길 바라., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0202396C/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239D2
msgctxt "0008E3"
msgid "I've never seen what this system looks like. But, if all goes well, it'll only take me a few minutes to hijack the system."
msgstr "이 시스템이 어떻게 생겼는지는 나도 본 적 없어. 그래도 모든 게 순조로우면, 시스템을 탈취하는 데 몇 분이면 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FCC63, 006F65ED, 00C1B16F, 00002E93
#. Notes = Worried. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 네가 뭘 하는 건지 알고 있길 바라., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0202396C/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239D2
msgctxt "0008E4"
msgid "More or less."
msgstr "대충은."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A61
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007DD61A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202396D/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A61
msgctxt "0008E5"
msgid "I hope you know what you're doing."
msgstr "네가 뭘 하는 건지 알고 있길 바라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0079A68A, 0096530F, 00B01472
#. Notes = Worried. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 이제 네가 실력 발휘할 시간이야., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Afraid / to Player Default, Face: Afraid, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396E/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239DD
msgctxt "0008E6"
msgid "If they start coming in, I need you to watch my back and make sure my work is not interrupted. I only need a few minutes."
msgstr "놈들이 들어오기 시작하면 날 엄호해 주고, 내 작업이 방해받지 않게 해 줘. 몇 분이면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0079A68A, 0096530F, 00B01472
#. Notes = Worried. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 이제 네가 실력 발휘할 시간이야., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Afraid / to Player Default, Face: Afraid, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396E/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239DD
msgctxt "0008E7"
msgid "And the Terrans probably know our location already."
msgstr "그리고 테란은 이미 우리 위치를 알고 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0079A68A, 0096530F, 00B01472
#. Notes = Worried. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 이제 네가 실력 발휘할 시간이야., Trying to be more determined, but still nervous. / Afraid / to Player Default, Face: Afraid, Determined again. / Angry / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0202396E/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020239DD
msgctxt "0008E8"
msgid "About that. To be honest, I'm not sure how long this will take. I've never been in this system before. "
msgstr "그 말인데. 솔직히 얼마나 걸릴지 모르겠어. 이 시스템은 처음이거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B417D3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202396F/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02023A4D
msgctxt "0008E9"
msgid "Time for you to do your thing."
msgstr "이제 네가 실력 발휘할 시간이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 003116F6
#. Notes = Softer, not as angry, and much happier/kinder tone to Delta. She's proud of what she just upgraded on them. / Smirk / to Delta, Face: Smirk
#: 02023975/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:020239A8
msgctxt "0008EA"
msgid "How do you feel?"
msgstr "기분은 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A05
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C30263
#. Notes = Happier now that she can work on robots on her own terms. / Happy / to Delta, Face: Happy
#: 02023976/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:02023A05
msgctxt "0008EB"
msgid "Ah, there we are!"
msgstr "아, 됐다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 003A932C
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Delta, Face: Serious
#: 02023978/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:02023A2A
msgctxt "0008EC"
msgid "Delta, come here."
msgstr "델타, 이리 와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA2B67
#. Notes = Serious / Concentrating, Face: Concentrating
#: 02023977/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:020239AB
msgctxt "0008ED"
msgid "Stand still for a moment."
msgstr "잠깐 가만히 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A37
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002B1517
#. Notes = Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 0202397C/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:02023A37
msgctxt "0008EE"
msgid "Correct. Increased lethality and coordination by 40%. Increased awareness by 24%. Decreased patience and empathetic response 78%. Increased knowledge of superiority 62%."
msgstr "정확함. 살상력 및 협동성 40% 증가. 인지력 24% 증가. 인내심 및 공감 반응 78% 감소. 우월성 인식 62% 증가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A3B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003DFC6D
#. Notes = Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 0202397E/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:02023A3B
msgctxt "0008EF"
msgid "Correct. Delta Unit fully operational. Full Terran robotic chassis takeover succeeded."
msgstr "정확함. 델타 개체 완전 가동. 테란 로봇 동체 완전 장악 성공."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A18
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0091A5F2
#. Notes = Softly to herself. Horrified at what Delta just said. / Worried / to Delta, Face: Worried
#: 02023981/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A18
msgctxt "0008F0"
msgid "This can't be happening."
msgstr "이럴 리가 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000AC88C
#. Notes = This line is for a companion check. Will change it to have the perk once the Delta companion perk is in. / to Player Default
#: 02023984/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239DA
msgctxt "0008F4"
msgid "[Delta] What do you think, Delta?"
msgstr "[델타] 델타, 어떻게 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008EA0EA
#. Notes = Determined / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 마음이 정해졌다면, 빨리 끝내자.
#: 02023985/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A0C
msgctxt "0008F5"
msgid "I won't leave 'til I put an end to this place. The sooner we get this done, the better."
msgstr "이곳을 끝장내기 전엔 떠나지 않을 거야. 빨리 끝낼수록 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A63
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007F968A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023986/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A63
msgctxt "0008F6"
msgid "If your mind is set on it, then let's get it over with."
msgstr "마음이 정해졌다면, 빨리 끝내자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A4E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00ABCF89
#. Notes = Determined / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 필요한 건 뭐든지, 록산.
#: 02023987/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A4E
msgctxt "0008F7"
msgid "Thank you. Now, let's go stop these bastards!"
msgstr "고마워. 이제 이 자식들을 막으러 가자!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000B130C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023988/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239B3
msgctxt "0008F8"
msgid "Whatever you need, Roxane."
msgstr "필요한 건 뭐든지, 록산."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0029416D
#. Notes = Determined / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 자식들을 완전히 막을 수 있다면 나도 함께할게.
#: 02023989/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239EF
msgctxt "0008F9"
msgid "Good. Let's get going then."
msgstr "좋아. 그럼 출발하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0013DE9E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202398A/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A2C
msgctxt "0008FA"
msgid "If it stops these bastards for good, then I'm in."
msgstr "이 자식들을 완전히 막을 수 있다면 나도 함께할게."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F21FE6, 00FBDB87, 0062D776, 005301DD
#. Notes = Angry, but now trying to remain calm to explain stuff to the player. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined. Emphasize on 'X-tech robots'. / Angry / to Player Default, Determined. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A02
msgctxt "0008FB"
msgid "If I'm gone they may not have X-Tech robots, but they'll still have robots. We're going to change that."
msgstr "내가 사라지면 놈들에게 X-테크 로봇은 없을지 몰라도, 여전히 로봇은 남아 있을 거야. 그걸 바꾸려는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F21FE6, 00FBDB87, 0062D776, 005301DD
#. Notes = Angry, but now trying to remain calm to explain stuff to the player. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined. Emphasize on 'X-tech robots'. / Angry / to Player Default, Determined. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A02
msgctxt "0008FC"
msgid "See, the Terrans don't need me to make their robots. Not really. They just don't know how to fuse X-Tech properly with their machines. That's where I come in."
msgstr "봐, 테란이 로봇을 만드는 데 꼭 내가 필요한 건 아니야. 사실은 아니지. 놈들은 X-테크를 자기 기계에 제대로 융합하는 법을 모를 뿐이야. 그래서 내가 필요한 거고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001FA4E8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202398C/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A0E
msgctxt "0008FE"
msgid "We should go before reinforcements arrive."
msgstr "지원군이 도착하기 전에 가야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00AC690F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202398E/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239A9
msgctxt "000902"
msgid "What you've done here won't put much of a dent in their plans."
msgstr "네가 여기서 한 일로는 놈들의 계획에 큰 타격을 주진 못할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A2630E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023990/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239C7
msgctxt "000906"
msgid "You've made a big mess for the Terrans here."
msgstr "여기서 테란에게 큰 혼란을 안겨 줬군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0047CB92, 005EDA5C
#. Notes = Very angry. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 너한테 그리 잘 먹히는 것 같진 않은데., Very angry. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 02023991/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239D4
msgctxt "000907"
msgid "I couldn't just keep 'perfecting', as they put it, their machines of destruction."
msgstr "놈들이 말하던 '완성'을 계속해 가며 파괴 기계를 다듬을 수는 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0047CB92, 005EDA5C
#. Notes = Very angry. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 너한테 그리 잘 먹히는 것 같진 않은데., Very angry. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 02023991/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239D4
msgctxt "000908"
msgid "I had hoped to use it all as a distraction to escape or something, but as you can see, things didn't go as planned."
msgstr "전부 탈출할 틈을 만들 미끼로 쓰거나 뭐라도 해 보려고 했는데, 보다시피 계획대로 되지 않았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A40
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CD6A43
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023992/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A40
msgctxt "000909"
msgid "That doesn't seem to be working out for you very well."
msgstr "너한테 그리 잘 먹히는 것 같진 않은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A41
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F038BB
#. Notes = Very angry. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 네 입장에서는 영리한 수였네.
#: 02023993/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A41
msgctxt "00090A"
msgid "The Terrans had me working on their robots. I couldn't do it anymore, knowing these machines are out there killing innocents!"
msgstr "테란은 내게 자기들 로봇을 만들게 했어. 그 기계들이 밖에서 무고한 사람들을 죽이고 있다는 걸 알면서 더는 못 하겠더라고!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A26
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FF4087
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023994/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:02023A26
msgctxt "00090B"
msgid "Sounds clever on your part."
msgstr "네 입장에서는 영리한 수였네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BEF8B9
#. Notes = Very angry. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 그건 알겠어. 여긴 완전히 난장판이야.
#: 02023995/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239D0
msgctxt "00090C"
msgid "What else was I suppose to do? They had me working, perfecting their damn machines. I couldn't let it go on any further."
msgstr "내가 달리 뭘 어떻게 했어야 했는데? 놈들은 나를 부려서, 그 망할 기계들을 완성하게 했어. 더는 그대로 둘 수 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C4EE6F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02023996/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239E4
msgctxt "00090D"
msgid "I can see that. It's absolute chaos in here."
msgstr "그건 알겠어. 여긴 완전히 난장판이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000D91A7
#. Notes = Serious and angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:020239B2
msgctxt "00090E"
msgid "I've rigged the facility's code to sabotage the robots programing. If any of them see any humans, besides me, they'll attack. That includes you."
msgstr "시설 코드를 조작해서 로봇 프로그램에 방해공작을 해 놨어. 놈들 중 하나라도 나 말고 다른 인간을 보면 공격할 거야. 너도 포함해서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A378F4
#. Notes = Absolutely shocked! / Shocked / to Delta, Face: Shocked
#: 02023998/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239C0
msgctxt "00090F"
msgid "Decimation? What?!"
msgstr "말살이라고? 뭐?!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C4443C, 003855CB
#. Notes = Very nonchalant / to Roxane, Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 02023999/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239F7
msgctxt "000910"
msgid "Assessment: Decimation of Terrans justified."
msgstr "평가: 테란 말살은 정당함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C4443C, 003855CB
#. Notes = Very nonchalant / to Roxane, Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 02023999/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020239F7
msgctxt "000911"
msgid "Roxane Bourreau identified. Running damage diagnostics. Physical: Fair. Psychological: Marginal."
msgstr "록산 부로 식별됨. 피해 진단 실행 중. 신체: 양호. 심리: 경계선."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008F9B0F
#. Notes = Shocked and scared / Confused / to Player Default, Face: Confused, Prompt: 부로 씨. 드디어 찾게 되어 기쁩니다.
#: 0202399A/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:020239BB
msgctxt "000912"
msgid "You were looking for me? Does that mean you're- wait..."
msgstr "나를 찾고 있었다고요? 그럼 당신은- 잠깐..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0014912D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202399B/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A0B
msgctxt "000913"
msgid "Ms. Bourreau. A pleasure to have finally found you."
msgstr "부로 씨. 드디어 찾게 되어 기쁩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A3944F
#. Notes = Shocked and scared / Shocked / to Player Default, Face: Shocked, Prompt: 네 창조자를 찾은 것 같아, 델타.
#: 0202399C/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:020239BC
msgctxt "000914"
msgid "What?! Delta? I..."
msgstr "뭐?! 델타? 나는..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A57
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0008AD0E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202399D/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A57
msgctxt "000915"
msgid "Looks like I've found your maker, Delta."
msgstr "네 창조자를 찾은 것 같아, 델타."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A62
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0048A5D4
#. Notes = Soft, gentle, and worried / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A62
msgctxt "000916"
msgid " Delta...?"
msgstr "델타...?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
