#: 020238E5/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650A_ROX:02023A5F
msgctxt "000A11"
msgid "Wonderful."
msgstr "훌륭해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0072FA3D
#. Notes = Worried for the player. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02023962/00900/SFTER_MQ02B_0900_ROX:02023A2E
msgctxt "000A12"
msgid "Let me see you. Spin around. Are you okay?"
msgstr "어디 좀 보자. 한 바퀴 돌아봐. 괜찮아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0600_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E06AEE
#. Notes = Serious. Trying to speak a bit fast so the three can get what she needs here. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 02023979/00600/SFTER_MQ02B_0600_ROX:020239B1
msgctxt "000A13"
msgid "I remember this area. The Terrans were mining X-Tech around here. See if you can find some. But be quick about it. We haven't much time."
msgstr "이 지역 기억나. 테란들이 이 주변에서 X-테크를 채굴하고 있었어. 좀 찾아볼 수 있는지 봐. 하지만 서둘러. 시간이 별로 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A17
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0600_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0061D21F
#. Notes = Surprised and remembering the location she's in. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202397A/00600/SFTER_MQ02B_0600_ROX:02023A17
msgctxt "000A14"
msgid "Wait. Come here for a moment. "
msgstr "잠깐. 이리 와 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
