#: 0202397B/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:020239BE
msgctxt "000A15"
msgid "Delta... I never meant for this to happen..."
msgstr "델타... 이렇게 되길 바란 건 아니었어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00C3B287
#. Notes = Nervous, and slightly defeated. Coming to understanding that her machine has turned into a monster. / Defiant / to Delta, Face: Defiant
#: 0202397D/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:020239E3
msgctxt "000A16"
msgid "You do seem different..."
msgstr "정말 달라 보이긴 하네..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CD4B8D
#. Notes = Soft and gentle. Speaking as if she's trying to reach to some version of Delta deep down. / Somber / to Delta, Face: Somber
#: 0202397F/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:020239D9
msgctxt "000A17"
msgid "Delta, is that really you?"
msgstr "델타, 정말 너야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A34
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0023CF1F
#. Notes = Talking to the Player, but concerned thinking about how her instructions led to Delta turning into a killing machine. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 02023980/00550/SFTER_MQ02B_0550_ROX_DELTA:02023A34
msgctxt "000A18"
msgid "I see you followed my instructions back on the Opulence?"
msgstr "오퓰런스에서 내가 한 지시를 따랐나 보네?"

