#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 0051712B, 0049512A
#. Notes = Excited / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy, Prompt: 그게 어떻게 도움이 되게 하려고 했는데?
#: 02015E8A/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F4A
msgctxt "000A31"
msgid "The idea was it would follow behind my dad and hold anything it was handed, allowing my dad to better focus on the work in front of him."
msgstr "원래는 아빠 뒤를 따라다니면서 건네받은 물건을 뭐든 들어 주고, 아빠가 눈앞의 작업에 더 집중할 수 있게 하려는 거였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F11
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00C2D219, 00BA3FE1
#. Notes = Ugh, how stupid is this laughing at herself / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 뭐가 문제였는데?
#: 02015E8C/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F11
msgctxt "000A32"
msgid "It tripped over itself and was blinded the moment it went inside."
msgstr "들어가자마자 제 발에 걸려 넘어지고 시야가 가려졌어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F27
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00EAEC00, 00DE85E9, 003FCB57
#. Notes = Half smile, sarcasm / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 하지만 지금은 이렇게까지 발전했잖아., Catching herself / Apologetic / to Player Default, Face: Apologetic
#: 02015E90/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F27
msgctxt "000A33"
msgid "Sorry, it's just hard to believe sometimes."
msgstr "미안, 가끔은 믿기 어려워서 그래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F27
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00EAEC00, 00DE85E9, 003FCB57
#. Notes = Half smile, sarcasm / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 하지만 지금은 이렇게까지 발전했잖아., Catching herself / Apologetic / to Player Default, Face: Apologetic
#: 02015E90/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F27
msgctxt "000A34"
msgid "In a derelict space station, held against my will with only a secret organization and my murderous creation to keep me company."
msgstr "버려진 우주정거장에, 내 의지와 상관없이 붙잡혀서, 비밀 조직과 내가 만든 살인 창조물만 곁에 있는 상태라니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F12
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00970198, 001AC9F0, 0064DF1D
#. Notes = Loves her dad / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 네 아버지도 그 노력을 고마워하셨을 거야., Kind of embarrassed by this / Grateful / to Player Default, Smiling at the memory / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 02015E92/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F12
msgctxt "000A35"
msgid "Funny enough, later his coworkers were all using \"Roxizzmo 2.0\"."
msgstr "웃기게도, 나중엔 아빠 동료들이 모두 \"록시즈모 2.0\"을 쓰고 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F12
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00970198, 001AC9F0, 0064DF1D
#. Notes = Loves her dad / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 네 아버지도 그 노력을 고마워하셨을 거야., Kind of embarrassed by this / Grateful / to Player Default, Smiling at the memory / Grateful / to Player Default
#: 02015E92/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_05_TopLevel_Personal_3:02015F12
msgctxt "000A36"
msgid "He was nothing but supportive. He would brag about me at work to anyone who would listen to him."
msgstr "아빠는 늘 날 응원해 줬어. 직장에서는 들어 주는 사람만 있으면 누구에게나 내 자랑을 했고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00CAB4BC, 00D7C2F6, 009BC82E
#. Notes = Smiling at her younger self / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy, Prompt: 네 첫 프로젝트 이름이 록시즈모였지?
#: 02015ED2/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane:02015F1A
msgctxt "000A37"
msgid "Didn't work though. I was still little, and way over my head."
msgstr "그래도 잘 안됐어. 난 아직 어렸고, 감당하기엔 너무 벅찼거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02015F1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
