msgid "Well, here we are. Home sweet home."
msgstr "자, 도착했네. 즐거운 우리 집이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02025A1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0000B8EC
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Pretending to give a grand speech. Can be intentionally stilted cause he's bad at public speaking
#: 02025A0D/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:02025A1B
msgctxt "000A97"
msgid "\"My goal was simple: To improve human beings. I wanted to help humanity adapt to our new astral homes.\""
msgstr "내 목표는 단순했다. 인간을 개선하는 것. 인류가 우리의 새로운 별의 터전에 적응하도록 돕고 싶었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02025A18
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00571E5D
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Not taking it seriously
#: 02025A10/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02:02025A18
msgctxt "000A99"
msgid "And what would you have me do, darling? We're already the biggest buyers at the Farmer's Market. Anymore and it'd be cheaper to grow our own."
msgstr "그럼 나더러 어떡하라는 거야, 여보? 우린 이미 파머스 마켓에서 제일 큰손이야. 더 사느니 직접 기르는 게 더 싸게 먹히겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02025A16
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00A666D9
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED At their wits end
#: 02025A11/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02:02025A16
msgctxt "000A9B"
msgid "I cannot work with subpar materials! Not anymore!"
msgstr "수준 미달 재료로는 작업 못 해! 더는 안 돼!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02025A14
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
