#: 0202756C/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02:0202757F
msgctxt "000ACD"
msgid "Oh, alright. You win. Again."
msgstr "아, 알았어. 당신이 이겼어. 또."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202757D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
