#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Attempt to inspire
#: 0202756F/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_02:0202757C
msgctxt "000AD1"
msgid "Just think of how amazed everyone will be when they see how much you were able to do with so little."
msgstr "이렇게 부족한 재료로 얼마나 많은 걸 해냈는지 사람들이 보면 얼마나 놀랄지 생각해 봐."

