#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D931F7
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 02028092/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281AB
msgctxt "000B10"
msgid "But I'm not letting you two off that easily. If you're vouching for this thing, there are going to be conditions."
msgstr "하지만 너희 둘을 그렇게 쉽게 봐주진 않을 거야. 이 물건을 보증하겠다면 조건이 붙을 거다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028179
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ECE332
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 넌 대체 누구야?
#: 02028095/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028179
msgctxt "000B11"
msgid "And what happens next depends on how you answer them, so let's save the attitude."
msgstr "그리고 그 대답에 따라 다음 일이 정해질 테니, 그 태도는 접어 둬."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1540_Delta_TerranWaveReady
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D2BB83
#: 0202809C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1540_Delta_TerranWaveReady:0202816A
msgctxt "000B12"
msgid "Faith in companion low, but still initiating access stream. Time to completion... variable."
msgstr "동료에 대한 신뢰도 낮음. 하지만 접속 스트림 개시. 완료까지 남은 시간... 변수."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D69695, 002DA060
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 우리가 안에 있는 동안 쓸 만한 건 좀 다운로드했어?
#: 0202809D/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202815A
msgctxt "000B13"
msgid "Let us continue mission, will revisit query at later time."
msgstr "임무를 계속하자. 질의어는 나중에 다시 검토하겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D69695, 002DA060
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 우리가 안에 있는 동안 쓸 만한 건 좀 다운로드했어?
#: 0202809D/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202815A
msgctxt "000B14"
msgid "Data has been duplicated and stored, but will take time to sort and analyze."
msgstr "데이터는 복제되어 저장되었지만, 분류와 분석에는 시간이 걸릴 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003B21BA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202809E/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202814A
msgctxt "000B15"
msgid "Manage to download anything useful while we were in there?"
msgstr "우리가 안에 있는 동안 쓸 만한 건 좀 다운로드했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C1984D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280A1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281C4
msgctxt "000B16"
msgid "So we did it? Grav Drives are back online?"
msgstr "그럼 해낸 거야? 중력 구동기가 다시 온라인 상태야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007B27CB, 00458AFA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 해낸 거야? 중력 구동기가 다시 온라인 상태야?
#: 020280A0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281D4
msgctxt "000B17"
msgid "No further external issues here should restrict ability to utilize spatial jump technology."
msgstr "이곳의 추가 외부 문제로 공간 도약 기술 활용 능력이 제한되지는 않을 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007B27CB, 00458AFA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 해낸 거야? 중력 구동기가 다시 온라인 상태야?
#: 020280A0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281D4
msgctxt "000B18"
msgid "Perhaps difficult for human comprehension, but Terran gravitational disrupter no longer functional."
msgstr "인간이 이해하기는 어려울 수 있으나, 테란 중력 교란기는 더 이상 작동하지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D38574
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 대체 뭘 분석하고 있는 거야?
#: 020280AB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281BC
msgctxt "000B19"
msgid "Request specimen refrain from interruptions. Security logs, damage reports, current status and chance of survival being scanned and assimilated."
msgstr "표본에게 방해 행위 중단 요청. 보안 기록, 피해 보고서, 현재 상태 및 생존 확률 스캔 및 동화 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EDFF43
#. Notes = Smirk / to Delta, Face: Smirk
#: 020280A2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B4
msgctxt "000B1A"
msgid "Best to keep friends close, and potential enemies closer."
msgstr "친구는 가까이, 잠재적 적은 더 가까이 두는 편이 최선이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0350_TerranExecutionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Terran01Scene01
#. SoundFileID = 00036EF2
#: 020280A3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0350_TerranExecutionScene:020281A3
msgctxt "000B1B"
msgid "Resistance ended."
msgstr "저항 종료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028171
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00253731, 001A7E77
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 너도 그냥 저 테란들 중 하나야?
#: 020280A6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028171
msgctxt "000B1C"
msgid "Terrans are limited. Technology: inefficient. Comparison rejected. Displeasure... ongoing."
msgstr "테란은 한계가 있음. 기술: 비효율적. 비교 거부. 불쾌감... 지속 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028171
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00253731, 001A7E77
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 너도 그냥 저 테란들 중 하나야?
#: 020280A6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028171
msgctxt "000B1D"
msgid "Not \"another\" anything. Unit is one of a kind. Special."
msgstr "또 다른 무엇도 아님. 이 기체는 유일무이함. 특별함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028162
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00DC233A
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280A7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028162
msgctxt "000B1E"
msgid "Are you just another one of these Terrans?"
msgstr "너도 그냥 저 테란들 중 하나야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028192
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0990_Delta_Unlock
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00403904
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280A4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0990_Delta_Unlock:02028192
msgctxt "000B1F"
msgid "Stand back during local interface."
msgstr "로컬 인터페이스 중에는 물러서라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028182
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002601F0
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280A5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028182
msgctxt "000B20"
msgid "Current occupant. Designation as \"enemy\"... status pending."
msgstr "현재 점유자. \"적\" 지정... 상태 보류 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003E356F
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280AA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281CC
msgctxt "000B21"
msgid "Aggression protocols... deferred. Control routed to processor."
msgstr "공격 프로토콜... 보류. 제어가 프로세서로 라우팅됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028141
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001B89F7
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280A9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028141
msgctxt "000B22"
msgid "I don't have time for this. We need to get moving."
msgstr "이럴 시간 없어. 움직여야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028152
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B1A3C1, 000AD117
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 이럴 시간 없어. 움직여야 해.
#: 020280A8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028152
msgctxt "000B23"
msgid "Claim irrelevant to objective delineation of concept -- \"time\"."
msgstr "해당 주장은 개념 -- \"시간\"의 객관적 정의와 무관."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028152
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B1A3C1, 000AD117
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 이럴 시간 없어. 움직여야 해.
#: 020280A8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028152
msgctxt "000B24"
msgid "Time is function of relative measurement. Variable possessed in large quantities."
msgstr "시간은 상대적 측정의 함수. 해당 변수는 대량 보유 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0045369E
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280B1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202815B
msgctxt "000B25"
msgid "Current frame... registered as \"Terran\". Aggression levels... elevated."
msgstr "현재 프레임... \"테란\"으로 등록됨. 공격성 수준... 상승."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A94DB3
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 처음부터 좀 꼬였나 봐. 이건 같이 해결하자.
#: 020280AD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202819B
msgctxt "000B26"
msgid "Permissions pending. Cooperation with Terran affiliates is restricted."
msgstr "권한 보류 중. 테란 관련자와의 협력은 제한됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00181967
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 좋든 싫든 여기서 나갈 방법을 찾아야 해.
#: 020280AF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202817A
msgctxt "000B27"
msgid "Concern is secondary. Must deal with current specimen before proceeding."
msgstr "우려는 부차적. 진행 전 현재 표본을 처리해야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00626B29
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280AE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202818B
msgctxt "000B28"
msgid "Maybe we got off on the wrong foot. Let's work together on this."
msgstr "처음부터 좀 꼬였나 봐. 이건 같이 해결하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0036D0E0
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280AC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281AC
msgctxt "000B29"
msgid "What exactly are you analyzing?"
msgstr "대체 뭘 분석하고 있는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CE67AA
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280B0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202816B
msgctxt "000B2A"
msgid "Like it or not, we need to find a way out of here."
msgstr "좋든 싫든 여기서 나갈 방법을 찾아야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0021F918, 00906F8A, 005E916E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 정확히 나한테 무슨 이득이 있는데?
#: 020280B2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202814B
msgctxt "000B2B"
msgid "Additional points. Creator led to Delta, can provide further advantages."
msgstr "추가 논거. 창조자는 델타를 탄생시켰고, 추가 이점을 제공할 수 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0021F918, 00906F8A, 005E916E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 정확히 나한테 무슨 이득이 있는데?
#: 020280B2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202814B
msgctxt "000B2C"
msgid "Objective benefit as ally rather than enemy."
msgstr "적으로 두는 것보다 아군으로 두는 편이 객관적으로 이득."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0021F918, 00906F8A, 005E916E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 정확히 나한테 무슨 이득이 있는데?
#: 020280B2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202814B
msgctxt "000B2D"
msgid "Physical prowess and observed intellect appear... rudimentary. Terran frame and Delta processor allow far greater efficiency in combat than yours."
msgstr "신체 능력 및 관찰된 지능... 기초 수준으로 보임. 테란 프레임과 델타 프로세서는 당신보다 전투 효율이 훨씬 높음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020A4B75
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0091920D
#. Notes = Prompt: 불꽃놀이 만드는 건 좋아하지.
#: 0205D09D/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020A4B75
msgctxt "000B2E"
msgid "If explosions were used, the combined intensity would have rendered your ocular nerves permanently disabled."
msgstr "폭발을 사용했다면, 결합 강도로 인해 당신의 시신경은 영구적으로 기능 정지되었을 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0033BEB1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 불꽃놀이 만드는 건 좋아하지.
#: 020280B3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281D5
msgctxt "000B2F"
msgid "Metaphor not apt. No explosions of that magnitude recorded. Electromagnetic pulses that resulted run on a different visual spectrum."
msgstr "비유 부적절. 해당 규모의 폭발은 기록되지 않음. 발생한 전자기 펄스는 다른 시각 스펙트럼에서 작동함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028172
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00436AC1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 생각보다 잘 풀렸어. 운이 좋았네.
#: 020280B9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:02028172
msgctxt "000B30"
msgid "Luck not a factor. System did as it was programmed to do. Terran forces were accordingly nullified."
msgstr "운은 요인이 아님. 시스템은 프로그램된 대로 작동. 이에 따라 테란 병력 무력화."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00821F0D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280B5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281B5
msgctxt "000B31"
msgid "Creator? You mean the one who made that chip?"
msgstr "창조자? 그 칩을 만든 사람 말이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000214D5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280B6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281A4
msgctxt "000B32"
msgid "How will this benefit me exactly?"
msgstr "그래서 정확히 나한테 무슨 이득이 있는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028193
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0011D99D
#: 020280B7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:02028193
msgctxt "000B33"
msgid "I love making fireworks."
msgstr "불꽃놀이 만드는 건 좋아하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00040DA1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 잠깐, 너 뭔가 한 거야?
#: 020280B4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281C5
msgctxt "000B34"
msgid "Set frequency to match hostile signatures as device was sent into overload. Simple adjustment."
msgstr "장치가 과부하에 들어갈 때 주파수를 적대 신호와 일치하도록 설정. 간단한 조정."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028142
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B10EB0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280BC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028142
msgctxt "000B35"
msgid "This is the only lead we've got to go on here."
msgstr "지금 우리가 따라갈 단서는 이것뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028153
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E4B95C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280BB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028153
msgctxt "000B36"
msgid "You might be right. But it's worth the risk."
msgstr "네 말이 맞을지도 몰라. 그래도 위험을 감수할 가치는 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028183
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0033C0E0, 0025857E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 아직 네가 누구인지, 뭐인지도 모르겠어.
#: 020280B8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028183
msgctxt "000B37"
msgid "Full capabilities would overwhelm your cognition. \"Superior in every way to you\" is likely sufficient. Though your presence not entirely without use."
msgstr "전체 능력을 설명하면 당신의 인지가 과부하될 것. \"모든 면에서 당신보다 우월함\" 정도면 충분할 듯. 다만 당신의 존재가 완전히 무용한 것은 아님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028183
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0033C0E0, 0025857E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 아직 네가 누구인지, 뭐인지도 모르겠어.
#: 020280B8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028183
msgctxt "000B38"
msgid "Constrained by Terran frame, but enhanced mobility and calculations present unique advantages."
msgstr "테란 프레임의 제약은 있으나, 향상된 기동성과 연산 능력은 고유한 이점을 제공함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009D5F5D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280BD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281CD
msgctxt "000B39"
msgid "I'm not even sure who or what you are yet."
msgstr "아직 네가 누구인지, 뭐인지도 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F64661
#. Notes = / to Yemoja, Prompt: 왜 내가 테란과 협력한다고 생각하는 거지?
#: 020280BE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281BD
msgctxt "000B3A"
msgid "Logical speculation. Based on superiority of Delta Unit, one would assume you to be... subjugated."
msgstr "논리적 추측. 델타 기체의 우월성을 기준으로 하면, 당신은... 종속된 것으로 보는 것이 타당."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0007347F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202817B
msgctxt "000B3B"
msgid "This arrangement benefits all involved. Sufficient?"
msgstr "이 구도는 관련자 전원에게 이득. 충분한가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A2F8CD
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 나랑 같이 오면, 내가 뭘 할 수 있는지 알아볼게.
#: 020280C7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281C6
msgctxt "000B3C"
msgid "Minimum requirements for agreement have been met. Terms acceptable."
msgstr "합의의 최소 조건 충족. 조건 수락 가능."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00369D93
#: 020280C0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202819C
msgctxt "000B3D"
msgid "Whoa, did you do something?"
msgstr "잠깐, 너 뭔가 한 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001D7FBF, 00FB65FC
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 저 문을 열 방법 생각나는 거 있어?
#: 020280C3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202816C
msgctxt "000B3E"
msgid "Array will not proceed until current process has finished running."
msgstr "어레이는 현재 프로세스 실행이 완료될 때까지 진행하지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001D7FBF, 00FB65FC
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 저 문을 열 방법 생각나는 거 있어?
#: 020280C3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202816C
msgctxt "000B3F"
msgid "Full list of effective measures arranged by decreasing probability of success already compiled."
msgstr "성공 확률 내림차순으로 정렬된 유효 조치 전체 목록 이미 컴파일됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00152DA2, 00C7A7DE, 0099E17C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202818C
msgctxt "000B40"
msgid "Simply collect black box separately for later uplink."
msgstr "이후 업링크를 위해 블랙박스를 따로 수집하면 됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00152DA2, 00C7A7DE, 0099E17C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202818C
msgctxt "000B41"
msgid "Subroutine to forcefully disable this Terran system can be run automatically when needed for future incursions."
msgstr "향후 인커전에서 필요 시 이 테란 시스템을 강제로 비활성화하는 서브루틴을 자동 실행 가능."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00152DA2, 00C7A7DE, 0099E17C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202818C
msgctxt "000B42"
msgid "In addition, this user has now been added to Terran's access exception list."
msgstr "또한 이 사용자는 이제 테란의 접속 예외 목록에 추가됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0079FF83, 0038D6C2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 창조자? 그 칩을 만든 사람 말이야?
#: 020280C5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202814C
msgctxt "000B43"
msgid "Delta Unit can provide further data if you assist. This arrangement will lead to completion of mission."
msgstr "지원하면 델타 기체가 추가 데이터를 제공 가능. 이 구도는 사명 완수로 이어질 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0079FF83, 0038D6C2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 창조자? 그 칩을 만든 사람 말이야?
#: 020280C5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202814C
msgctxt "000B44"
msgid "Led to my creation, but datachip origin incidental. True achievement in evolving beyond designed potential."
msgstr "내 창조로 이어졌으나, 데이터칩의 기원은 부차적. 진정한 성취는 설계된 잠재력을 넘어 진화한 데 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028194
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A4B36C, 00943BB4
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 도움이 필요해? 내가 너무 "열등"하진 않고?
#: 020280CA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028194
msgctxt "000B45"
msgid "Transportation and makeshift shielding rank highly."
msgstr "이동 수단과 임시 차폐는 높은 순위."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028194
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A4B36C, 00943BB4
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 도움이 필요해? 내가 너무 "열등"하진 않고?
#: 020280CA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028194
msgctxt "000B46"
msgid "Despite purported inferiority, there are uses even in non-efficient beings."
msgstr "열등하다고 알려졌음에도, 비효율적 존재에게도 용도는 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003EE853
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281B6
msgctxt "000B47"
msgid "You come with me, I'll see what I can do."
msgstr "나랑 같이 오면, 내가 뭘 할 수 있는지 알아볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00678A33
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202815C
msgctxt "000B48"
msgid "Attempt at awareness requires improvement. Lowering Appreciation variable."
msgstr "인식 시도에 개선 필요. 감탄 변수 감소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B981F1
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 여기서 나갈 수 있다면 좋아. 하지만 이 얘기는 아직 안 끝났어.
#: 020280D1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281BE
msgctxt "000B49"
msgid "Incorrect. Conversation has concluded. However, further inquiries will be allowed at a later date."
msgstr "부정확. 대화는 종료됨. 단, 추가 문의는 추후 허용될 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005A446D, 00D6A861
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 잘 들어, 간단하게 말하지. 이제 넌 내 명령을 따라.
#: 020280C6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281D6
msgctxt "000B4A"
msgid "Attempts to override will be met with hostility."
msgstr "재정의 설정 시도는 적대 행위로 대응할 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005A446D, 00D6A861
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 잘 들어, 간단하게 말하지. 이제 넌 내 명령을 따라.
#: 020280C6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281D6
msgctxt "000B4B"
msgid "Evaluating speech. Tone, not approved. Orders not yours to dictate."
msgstr "발화 평가 중. 어조, 승인되지 않음. 명령권은 당신에게 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D6B5B2
#. Notes = Sarcastic / to Delta, Face: Sarcastic
#: 020280D2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281AE
msgctxt "000B4C"
msgid "Right, uh... \"Delta\". Quite the ego it's got."
msgstr "그래, 어... \"델타\". 자존심 한번 대단하네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028173
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0080C673
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280CC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028173
msgctxt "000B4D"
msgid "You want my help? I'm not too \"inferior\" for you?"
msgstr "내 도움이 필요해? 내가 너무 \"열등\"하진 않고?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028164
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008CF97E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280CD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028164
msgctxt "000B4E"
msgid "Scans indicate present human is non-Terran. Updating interaction accordingly."
msgstr "스캔 결과 현재 인간은 비테란으로 표시. 이에 따라 상호작용 업데이트."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0040246A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280C9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281A5
msgctxt "000B4F"
msgid "Require auxiliary support to retrieve creator. Human opposes Terrans, can obtain further vantage through Delta Unit."
msgstr "창조자 회수를 위해 보조 지원 필요. 인간은 테란에 반대하며, 델타 기체를 통해 추가 우위를 확보 가능."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028184
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C5870C
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280CB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028184
msgctxt "000B50"
msgid "Listen up, I'll make this easy. You take orders from me now."
msgstr "잘 들어, 간단하게 말하지. 이제 넌 내 명령을 따라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028154
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0066DC58
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280CE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028154
msgctxt "000B51"
msgid "It fought off its own kind. We should give it a chance."
msgstr "자기 동족과 싸웠잖아. 기회를 줘야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ECFC0E, 009839CF, 00FE324A
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 항상 그렇게 사람을 잘 믿어?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 020280D3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202819D
msgctxt "000B52"
msgid "We might be better off tearing this thing down and getting the truth that way, instead of waiting for it to turn on us."
msgstr "이게 우리를 배신할 때까지 기다리느니, 차라리 뜯어내서 진실을 알아내는 편이 나을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ECFC0E, 009839CF, 00FE324A
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 항상 그렇게 사람을 잘 믿어?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 020280D3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202819D
msgctxt "000B53"
msgid "I don't even trust the partners I work with, let alone foreign death machines making universal declarations of war."
msgstr "같이 일하는 파트너들도 못 믿는데, 온 우주에 선전포고하는 정체 모를 살인 기계는 말할 것도 없지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ECFC0E, 009839CF, 00FE324A
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 항상 그렇게 사람을 잘 믿어?, Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 020280D3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202819D
msgctxt "000B54"
msgid "In my line of work you don't have the luxury of believing things the way they're presented."
msgstr "내 일에서는 눈앞에 보이는 그대로 믿는 사치를 부릴 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020A52E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0025B69C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020A52E0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020A52E1
msgctxt "000B55"
msgid "Seems to be playing along as an ally for now, but you think that's going to last forever?"
msgstr "지금은 아군인 척 장단을 맞추는 것 같지만, 그게 영원히 갈 거라고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028143
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0023C04F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 테란과 협력한다고? 난 그놈들과 싸우다 죽을 뻔했어.
#: 020280CF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028143
msgctxt "000B56"
msgid "What, and you believed it? These Terrans have already shown their true colors."
msgstr "뭐, 그걸 믿었다고? 이 테란들은 이미 본색을 드러냈어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0054EDE8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280D0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281CE
msgctxt "000B57"
msgid "The beginnings of a conspiracy. I'm in."
msgstr "음모의 시작이군. 나도 끼지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00230FA4
#. Notes = ah-jey yoruba word: witch / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 넌 대체 누구야?
#: 020280D5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202817D
msgctxt "000B58"
msgid "Aegis, aje. That means I'm the one asking the questions here."
msgstr "이지스, 아제. 그러니까 여기서 질문하는 건 나라는 뜻이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E5F8D6
#. Notes = o-LOHW-doh yoruba word: dumb person / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 넌 대체 누구야?
#: 020280D5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202817C
msgctxt "000B59"
msgid "Aegis, olodo. That means I'm the one asking the questions here."
msgstr "이지스, 올로도. 그러니까 여기서 질문하는 건 나라는 뜻이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000B36B3
#: 020280D6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202815D
msgctxt "000B5A"
msgid "That went better than expected, we got lucky."
msgstr "생각보다 잘 풀렸어. 운이 좋았네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EB4CED
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 음모의 시작이군. 나도 끼지.
#: 020280D7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202814D
msgctxt "000B5B"
msgid "Then you'll love what's to come."
msgstr "그럼 앞으로 벌어질 일은 아주 마음에 들겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00838C0E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 지금 우리가 따라갈 단서는 이것뿐이야.
#: 020280E6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202819E
msgctxt "000B5C"
msgid "I guess we just have to deal with the hand we're dealt."
msgstr "결국 받은 패로 버티는 수밖에 없겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EF327C, 0041D373
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: [배지 제시] 쏘지 마! 난 레인저스 소속이야. 진정하자고., / to Player Default
#: 020280D9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281C7
msgctxt "000B5D"
msgid "That answers the question of who you are, but still leaves a pretty big one."
msgstr "네가 누구인지는 답이 됐지만, 아직 큰 의문 하나가 남아 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EF327C, 0041D373
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: [배지 제시] 쏘지 마! 난 레인저스 소속이야. 진정하자고., / to Player Default
#: 020280D9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281C7
msgctxt "000B5E"
msgid "You move that hand again and my finger might just slip."
msgstr "그 손 또 움직이면 내 손가락이 미끄러질지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001736D7, 00DEC96C, 0006CEE7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 어떤 사람들을 말하는 거야?, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 020280DA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B7
msgctxt "000B5F"
msgid "You should feel honored. Not that you have much of a choice."
msgstr "영광으로 알아. 선택권이 많지는 않겠지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001736D7, 00DEC96C, 0006CEE7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 어떤 사람들을 말하는 거야?, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 020280DA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B7
msgctxt "000B60"
msgid "The kind with powerful interests, some sure to align with yours."
msgstr "강력한 이해관계를 가진 쪽이지. 그중 일부는 분명 네 이해와도 맞아떨어질 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001736D7, 00DEC96C, 0006CEE7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 어떤 사람들을 말하는 거야?, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 020280DA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B7
msgctxt "000B61"
msgid "The kind who have their fingers attached to a lot of strings, and who pull them when necessary."
msgstr "여러 줄에 손가락을 걸고 있다가, 필요하면 그 줄을 당기는 부류지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00BC3B38
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280DB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281A6
msgctxt "000B62"
msgid "All the more reason to keep an eye on it."
msgstr "그러니까 더더욱 지켜봐야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202813C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009B8AEA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 앵커포인트로 날아가기 전에 할 일이 좀 있어.
#: 020280D8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202813C
msgctxt "000B63"
msgid "A smaller delay would be advantageous. Mission cannot be deferred indefinitely."
msgstr "지연은 짧을수록 유리. 사명은 무기한 연기될 수 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028185
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0093638E
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280DE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028185
msgctxt "000B64"
msgid "Any ideas to get that door open?"
msgstr "저 문을 열 방법 생각나는 거 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028174
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00FFEE76
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280DF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028174
msgctxt "000B65"
msgid "If they can help against these Terrans, I should pay them a visit."
msgstr "그들이 이 테란들을 상대하는 데 도움이 된다면, 한번 찾아가 봐야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028165
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00199448
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280E0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028165
msgctxt "000B66"
msgid "I'll send you the coordinates. And make sure you don't forget to bring our rogue Terran there."
msgstr "좌표를 보내 줄게. 그리고 우리 변절 테란도 잊지 말고 데려와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028145
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 003ADD11
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그들이 이 테란들을 상대하는 데 도움이 된다면, 한번 찾아가 봐야겠어.
#: 020280E2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028145
msgctxt "000B67"
msgid "I think you'll find the relationship mutually beneficial."
msgstr "서로에게 이로운 관계라는 걸 알게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 003987F9
#. Notes = emphasis on a corrected "delta" name / to Player Default
#: 020280E4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281BF
msgctxt "000B68"
msgid "I get the feeling you and this Delta are going to end up tipping the scales in all this. We'll see in which direction that ends up being soon enough."
msgstr "왠지 당신과 이 델타가 이번 일의 판도를 뒤집게 될 것 같아. 어느 쪽으로 뒤집힐지는 머지않아 알게 되겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D76C5C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280E7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202818E
msgctxt "000B6A"
msgid "Either way, the people heading up this operation are going to want to see you about it -- both of you."
msgstr "어쨌든 이 작전을 지휘하는 사람들이 그 일로 당신을 만나고 싶어 할 거야. 둘 다 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E6F1A3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280E8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202817E
msgctxt "000B6B"
msgid "Working with the Terrans? I almost died fighting them off."
msgstr "테란과 협력한다고? 난 그놈들과 싸우다 죽을 뻔했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 006FA3C9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280E5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281AF
msgctxt "000B6C"
msgid "No, this one's not with them. It's got a special chip the Terrans were after. See, there was this scientist..."
msgstr "아니, 얘는 그쪽이 아니야. 테란이 노리던 특수 칩을 갖고 있어. 그러니까, 어떤 과학자가 있었는데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003524CA
#. Notes = / to Yemoja, Prompt: 테란과 협력한다고? 난 그놈들과 싸우다 죽을 뻔했어.
#: 020280EA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202815E
msgctxt "000B6D"
msgid "Clarification. Human is subordinate, not friend. Current status, temporary alliance."
msgstr "정정. 인간은 친구가 아니라 종속 개체. 현재 상태, 임시 동맹."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0089F431
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280EB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202814E
msgctxt "000B6E"
msgid "Meet them at Anchorpoint, dingy dive out on the Free Lanes. When you get there, order a \"Vocatis Vacuos\" at the bar."
msgstr "앵커포인트에서 만나. 프리 레인스 외곽에 있는 허름한 술집이야. 도착하면 바에서 \"보카티스 바쿠오스\"를 주문해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0064CB1A, 00436903
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 아니, 얘는 그쪽이 아니야. 테란이 노리던 특수 칩을 갖고 있어. 그러니까, 어떤 과학자가 있었는데...
#: 020280ED/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281C8
msgctxt "000B6F"
msgid "But you're saying somehow this thing's different, huh?"
msgstr "근데 어쨌든 이게 좀 다르다는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0064CB1A, 00436903
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 아니, 얘는 그쪽이 아니야. 테란이 노리던 특수 칩을 갖고 있어. 그러니까, 어떤 과학자가 있었는데...
#: 020280ED/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281C8
msgctxt "000B70"
msgid "Hey, slow down. That's a lot to unpack."
msgstr "잠깐, 천천히. 한 번에 받아들이기엔 이야기가 너무 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 002DE02D
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 020280E9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202816D
msgctxt "000B71"
msgid "Different how? From what I've seen they all seem to have a one-track mind. For all you know this is just a ploy until you turn your back."
msgstr "어떻게 다른데? 내가 본 바로는 다 하나같이 한 가지 생각밖에 없는 것 같던데. 네가 등을 돌리는 순간까지 꾸미는 술수일 수도 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028166
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0099DED0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280F3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028166
msgctxt "000B72"
msgid "If it's all the same to you, I don't really want to get involved."
msgstr "괜찮다면 난 이 일에 끼고 싶지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028196
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F0EF87
#. Notes = / to Yemoja, Prompt: 델타 말이야? 걱정 마, 이쪽은 달라.
#: 020280F0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028196
msgctxt "000B73"
msgid "Peace not currently an acceptable option. Terrans must be eliminated."
msgstr "평화는 현재 허용 가능한 선택지가 아니다. 테란은 제거되어야 한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028146
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 006DE051, 00EF3CCB
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 델타 말이야? 걱정 마, 이쪽은 달라.
#: 020280F5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028146
msgctxt "000B74"
msgid "How long until it starts feeling that way about you?"
msgstr "저게 너까지 그렇게 판단하기 시작하는 데 얼마나 걸릴까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028146
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 006DE051, 00EF3CCB
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 델타 말이야? 걱정 마, 이쪽은 달라.
#: 020280F5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028146
msgctxt "000B75"
msgid "Wanting to eliminate its own allies, huh."
msgstr "자기 동맹까지 제거하려 든다, 이거군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028175
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00C970B3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280F2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028175
msgctxt "000B76"
msgid "You'd better stow that weapon before you end up hurt."
msgstr "다치기 전에 그 무기 집어넣는 게 좋을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028156
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B48ED0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280F4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028156
msgctxt "000B77"
msgid "If it gets us out of here, fine. But this conversation isn't over."
msgstr "여기서 나갈 수 있다면 좋아. 하지만 이 얘기는 아직 안 끝났어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DC7D2E, 0004FBF5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 테란과 협력한다고? 난 그놈들과 싸우다 죽을 뻔했어.
#: 020280EF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281A7
msgctxt "000B78"
msgid "Wouldn't think you'd be palling around with it like it's your best friend if that were true."
msgstr "그게 사실이면 네 절친이라도 된 것처럼 저거랑 어울리진 않을 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DC7D2E, 0004FBF5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 테란과 협력한다고? 난 그놈들과 싸우다 죽을 뻔했어.
#: 020280EF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281A7
msgctxt "000B79"
msgid "Well it looks like you missed one."
msgstr "뭐, 하나 놓친 모양이네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028186
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DCC117
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280F1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028186
msgctxt "000B7A"
msgid "Are you always this trusting?"
msgstr "항상 그렇게 사람을 잘 믿어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202819F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0030E1BB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280FB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202819F
msgctxt "000B7B"
msgid "You mean Delta? Don't worry, they're different."
msgstr "델타 말이야? 걱정 마, 이쪽은 달라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 004DE2F2
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: 델타 말이야? 걱정 마, 이쪽은 달라.
#: 020280FA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B0
msgctxt "000B7C"
msgid "Isn't that convenient. The Terrans declare war on humanity and they - what - send this thing as a peace ambassador?"
msgstr "참 편리하네. 테란이 인류에게 선전포고를 해놓고, 뭐, 이걸 평화 대사로 보냈다고?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DFAD94
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280F8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281C0
msgctxt "000B7D"
msgid "Why would you think I'm working with the Terrans?"
msgstr "왜 내가 테란과 협력한다고 생각하는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202817F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007E08CC
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 020280FD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0202817F
msgctxt "000B7F"
msgid "One wrong move and I'm shutting you down again."
msgstr "수상한 짓 한 번만 해도 다시 꺼 버리겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00C3804A
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 다치기 전에 그 무기 집어넣는 게 좋을 거야.
#: 020280FE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202816E
msgctxt "000B80"
msgid "So your little friend can shoot me anyway? Not a chance."
msgstr "그러면 네 꼬맹이 친구가 어차피 날 쏘게? 어림없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028157
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00AFA4F4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028109/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028157
msgctxt "000B81"
msgid "If you can take down this Grav Jammer, then it seems like our best shot."
msgstr "이 중력 재머를 처리할 수 있다면 그게 우리한텐 최선 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00063037
#. Notes = / to Yemoja
#: 02028104/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281A8
msgctxt "000B82"
msgid "Incorrect. Not thing. Delta."
msgstr "부정확. 물건 아님. 델타."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028187
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0064D2D2
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 02028106/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028187
msgctxt "000B83"
msgid "Booting up... Initializing."
msgstr "부팅 중... 초기화 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202815F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0085D475
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020280FF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202815F
msgctxt "000B84"
msgid "[Lie] I'm not, this robot's taken me hostage! Help!"
msgstr "[거짓말] 아니야, 이 로봇이 날 인질로 잡았어! 도와줘!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028176
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EFF51B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028107/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028176
msgctxt "000B85"
msgid "Let's just take it easy. No problems here."
msgstr "진정하자고. 여기선 문제 일으킬 생각 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202814F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DCD13B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028100/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202814F
msgctxt "000B86"
msgid "Who the hell are you?"
msgstr "넌 대체 누구야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202813E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009DBCAB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028101/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0202813E
msgctxt "000B87"
msgid "I've got some things to do before we fly to Anchorpoint."
msgstr "앵커포인트로 날아가기 전에 할 일이 좀 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A00B23
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이제 다시 중력 도약을 할 수 있으니 앵커포인트로 가자.
#: 02028102/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281C9
msgctxt "000B88"
msgid "If beneficial to completion of current mission, will comply. For now."
msgstr "현재 임무 완료에 유익하다면 따르겠다. 지금은."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0002914A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202810D/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281C1
msgctxt "000B89"
msgid "Now that we can grav jump again, let's head to Anchorpoint."
msgstr "이제 다시 중력 도약을 할 수 있으니 앵커포인트로 가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00F13051
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 왜 내가 테란과 협력한다고 생각하는 거지?
#: 02028103/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281B9
msgctxt "000B8A"
msgid "You have the nerve to play dumb with that thing following you?"
msgstr "저걸 뒤에 달고 다니면서 시치미 뗄 배짱이 있네?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028147
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0016050D
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 진정하자고. 여기선 문제 일으킬 생각 없어.
#: 0202810B/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028147
msgctxt "000B8B"
msgid "Hostile weapon assessed as problem for Auxiliary Human."
msgstr "적대 무기가 보조 인간에게 문제로 평가됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00198B58
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202810C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281D1
msgctxt "000B8C"
msgid "[Show Badge] Don't shoot! I'm with the Rangers, let's calm down."
msgstr "[배지 제시] 쏘지 마! 난 레인저스 소속이야. 진정하자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028167
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 002537E3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028108/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028167
msgctxt "000B8D"
msgid "What kind of people are we talking about?"
msgstr "어떤 사람들을 말하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0040AF98
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202810E/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281B1
msgctxt "000B8E"
msgid "That's, uh... Thanks. I guess."
msgstr "그건, 어... 고마워. 아마도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FEEECF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 난 공짜로 일 안 해.
#: 02028110/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281A0
msgctxt "000B8F"
msgid "Familiar with idiom #406 -- \"quid pro quo\". Preferred by those bound by biological id. Will compensate appropriately if assistance is adequate."
msgstr "관용구 #406 -- \"quid pro quo\" 인지. 생물학적 원초아에 종속된 자들이 선호. 지원이 충분할 경우 적절히 보상하겠다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_SI_Yemoja_Exit01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028190
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00AEECDC
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 02028111/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028190
msgctxt "000B90"
msgid "Freeze! Right where you are!"
msgstr "꼼짝 마! 그 자리에서 움직이지 마!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028180
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001DB210, 000A95A6
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 수상한 짓 한 번만 해도 다시 꺼 버리겠어.
#: 02028112/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028180
msgctxt "000B91"
msgid "Violence will be dealt with and neutralized accordingly."
msgstr "폭력은 그에 맞춰 처리 및 무력화될 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028180
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001DB210, 000A95A6
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 수상한 짓 한 번만 해도 다시 꺼 버리겠어.
#: 02028112/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028180
msgctxt "000B92"
msgid "Issuing warning. Attempt at action will be considered hostile attack."
msgstr "경고 발령. 행동 시도는 적대 공격으로 간주된다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202816F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00846213
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028114/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202816F
msgctxt "000B93"
msgid "You've got a very short window to tell me why you're working with the Terrans."
msgstr "네가 왜 테란과 협력하는지 설명할 시간은 아주 짧아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028160
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0065DF09
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028115/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028160
msgctxt "000B94"
msgid "Alright, go ahead and crack it. I've got your back."
msgstr "좋아, 어서 뚫어. 뒤는 내가 봐줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028150
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D82234, 00FFCBC0
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그들이 일은 너한테 맡기라고 하긴 했지.
#: 02028116/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028150
msgctxt "000B95"
msgid "Therefore, you must defer other objectives to assist Delta Unit."
msgstr "따라서 다른 목표는 보류하고 델타 기체를 보조해야 한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028150
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D82234, 00FFCBC0
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그들이 일은 너한테 맡기라고 하긴 했지.
#: 02028116/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028150
msgctxt "000B96"
msgid "Affirmative. Recovery of creator is highest priority. Usefulness several magnitudes greater than yours."
msgstr "긍정. 창조자 회수가 최우선. 유용성은 귀하보다 몇 자릿수 더 큼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202813F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00637FD3
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 다치기 전에 그 무기 집어넣는 게 좋을 거야.
#: 02028117/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202813F
msgctxt "000B97"
msgid "Intention to shoot dependent on threat level to self, not Auxiliary Human."
msgstr "사격 의도는 보조 인간이 아니라 자체 위협 수준에 따라 결정됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00008206
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그건, 어... 고마워. 아마도.
#: 02028119/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281BA
msgctxt "000B98"
msgid "Any further hindrances would only delay my mission. Gratitude is unnecessary."
msgstr "추가 방해는 내 임무를 지연시킬 뿐. 감사는 불필요하다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002CF10F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202811A/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281A9
msgctxt "000B99"
msgid "Aegis? So that makes you the same Agent Yemoja that sent me here."
msgstr "이지스? 그럼 당신이 날 여기 보낸 바로 그 예모자 요원인가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A14253
#: 02028118/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:020281CA
msgctxt "000B9A"
msgid "Given enough time unimpeded, device should be shut down with low probability of fallout."
msgstr "방해받지 않고 충분한 시간이 주어지면, 여파 발생 확률을 낮게 유지한 채 장치를 정지할 수 있을 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028198
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0035EA9D, 0074E805
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 잠깐, 여파라고? 위험이 뭐야?
#: 0202811B/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028198
msgctxt "000B9B"
msgid "Risk to self, negligible. To others in the vicinity... non-zero chance of fatalities in case of system overload."
msgstr "자체 위험은 무시 가능. 인근 타인에게는... 시스템 과부하 시 사망 발생 확률이 0이 아님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028168
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E54336, 00AF8798
#. Notes = EyesClosed / to Player Default, Face: EyesClosed, Prompt: [거짓말] 아니야, 이 로봇이 날 인질로 잡았어! 도와줘!, Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking
#: 0202811F/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028168
msgctxt "000B9C"
msgid "Which means you've stumbled on something different here. Probably defective."
msgstr "그 말은 여기서 네가 다른 걸 발견했다는 뜻이지. 아마 결함품일 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028168
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E54336, 00AF8798
#. Notes = EyesClosed / to Player Default, Face: EyesClosed, Prompt: [거짓말] 아니야, 이 로봇이 날 인질로 잡았어! 도와줘!, Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking
#: 0202811F/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028168
msgctxt "000B9D"
msgid "*sigh* I doubt you'd be this relaxed if you were actually under threat right now."
msgstr "*한숨* 지금 진짜 위협받는 상황이라면 그렇게 여유롭진 않을 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028188
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002F4636, 003DBADC
#. Notes = confirming a hunch since she would have recognized the player's ship / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 이지스? 그럼 당신이 날 여기 보낸 바로 그 예모자 요원인가., / to Player Default
#: 0202811C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028188
msgctxt "000B9E"
msgid "Thought the ship docked outside might've lost its captain what with all the hostiles around, but you and your friend look just fine to me."
msgstr "밖에 정박한 함선은 주변 적대 세력 때문에 선장을 잃은 줄 알았는데, 너랑 네 친구는 내 눈엔 멀쩡해 보이는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028188
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002F4636, 003DBADC
#. Notes = confirming a hunch since she would have recognized the player's ship / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, Prompt: 이지스? 그럼 당신이 날 여기 보낸 바로 그 예모자 요원인가., / to Player Default
#: 0202811C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028188
msgctxt "000B9F"
msgid "That's right. Tracked your tags after our meeting in orbit."
msgstr "맞아. 궤도에서 만난 뒤 네 식별 태그를 추적했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028177
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00AB3AF8
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 드디어 쓸모가 생긴 모양이군.
#: 0202811E/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:02028177
msgctxt "000BA0"
msgid "Definition of \"useful\" appears lacking. Would not be able to proceed without my capabilities."
msgstr "유용함의 정의가 부족한 것으로 보임. 내 능력 없이는 진행할 수 없을 것임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028158
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007966EA
#: 02028120/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028158
msgctxt "000BA1"
msgid "Analyzing. Security appears rudimentary. Utilizing current frame, bypassing protocols should be simple process."
msgstr "분석 중. 보안은 초보적인 수준으로 보임. 현재 기체를 활용하면 프로토콜 우회는 단순한 과정일 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028148
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D45EB4, 005B332B
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 우린 모두 친구야. 난 적이 아니야.
#: 02028121/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028148
msgctxt "000BA2"
msgid "Classification \"enemy\"... status pending."
msgstr "분류 \"적\"... 상태 보류 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028148
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D45EB4, 005B332B
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 우린 모두 친구야. 난 적이 아니야.
#: 02028121/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028148
msgctxt "000BA3"
msgid "Designation \"friend\" not accepted. Only relations \"primary\" and \"secondary\"."
msgstr "지정 \"친구\"는 수락되지 않음. 관계는 \"주\" 및 \"보조\"만 존재."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028144
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004CECB2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 좋아, 어서 뚫어. 뒤는 내가 봐줄게.
#: 02028124/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028144
msgctxt "000BA4"
msgid "Even if Auxiliary Human cannot hold them off, simply serving as distraction will be enough."
msgstr "보조 인간이 저들을 막아내지 못하더라도, 단순히 주의를 끄는 것만으로 충분할 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0045088D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028126/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281B2
msgctxt "000BA5"
msgid "Good job, Delta. Good thing you were here."
msgstr "잘했어, 델타. 네가 있어서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001A4C71
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 잘했어, 델타. 네가 있어서 다행이야.
#: 02028125/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:020281C2
msgctxt "000BA6"
msgid "Programming beyond need for praise. Results were expected."
msgstr "칭찬은 필요 없도록 프로그래밍됨. 결과는 예상된 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0072EF1D
#. Notes = / to Delta
#: 02028123/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281D2
msgctxt "000BA7"
msgid "At the very least, the fact we're even having a conversation right now means it's worth entertaining... for the moment."
msgstr "최소한 지금 우리가 이렇게 대화하고 있다는 사실만 봐도 검토해 볼 가치는 있다는 뜻이야... 당장은."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0035C8D1
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 02028127/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281A2
msgctxt "000BA8"
msgid "We're all friends here. I'm not an enemy."
msgstr "우린 모두 친구야. 난 적이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028181
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007132A6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028129/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:02028181
msgctxt "000BA9"
msgid "Wait, fallout? What's the risk here?"
msgstr "잠깐, 여파라고? 위험이 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028191
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00674290
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028128/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028191
msgctxt "000BAA"
msgid "Proposal. Assist me as secondary. Creator's mission must be completed."
msgstr "제안. 보조자로서 나를 지원하라. 창조자의 임무는 완료되어야 한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028170
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00935B31
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202812A/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028170
msgctxt "000BAB"
msgid "\"Delta Unit\"? That supposed to be your name?"
msgstr "델타 기체? 그게 네 이름이라는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028161
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005D7EFE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202812B/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028161
msgctxt "000BAC"
msgid "They did say I should leave things to you."
msgstr "그들이 일은 너한테 맡기라고 하긴 했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028151
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0011E77A
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 0202812C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028151
msgctxt "000BAD"
msgid "You don't look hostile. It's a start."
msgstr "적대적으로 보이진 않네. 일단 그건 시작점이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028140
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004C7B27
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 공격성 수준? 걱정해야 해?
#: 0202812D/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028140
msgctxt "000BAE"
msgid "Do not interrupt diagnostics process."
msgstr "진단 과정을 방해하지 마라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00008D64
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202812F/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281CB
msgctxt "000BAF"
msgid "I don't do things for free."
msgstr "난 공짜로 일 안 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BB4ED7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 중력 재머를 처리할 수 있다면 그게 우리한텐 최선 같아.
#: 02028131/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1400_Delta_TerranEnd:020281AA
msgctxt "000BB0"
msgid "Variable not \"if\", only \"when\". I will perform function if you perform yours."
msgstr "변수는 \"만약\"이 아니라 \"언제\"뿐. 네가 기능을 수행하면 나도 내 기능을 수행하겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00368568
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 적대적으로 보이진 않네. 일단 그건 시작점이군.
#: 02028130/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:020281BB
msgctxt "000BB1"
msgid "Behavior dependent on target. According to observations, target at biological disadvantage."
msgstr "행동은 대상에 따라 달라짐. 관찰 결과 대상은 생물학적 불리함에 처해 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028199
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0025BE9D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028132/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:02028199
msgctxt "000BB2"
msgid "Process... complete."
msgstr "처리... 완료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028178
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E39D5A, 00AB07CA, 00E155BF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 괜찮다면 난 이 일에 끼고 싶지 않아., Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02028134/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028178
msgctxt "000BB3"
msgid "Take your time, though. I have a feeling you'll make the right choice eventually. When you do, you can go see my associates."
msgstr "그래도 천천히 생각해. 결국 옳은 선택을 할 것 같은 느낌이 들어. 그렇게 되면 내 동료들을 만나러 가면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028178
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E39D5A, 00AB07CA, 00E155BF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 괜찮다면 난 이 일에 끼고 싶지 않아., Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02028134/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028178
msgctxt "000BB4"
msgid "But even if you try and ignore this thing, sooner or later it's going to catch up to you."
msgstr "하지만 저걸 무시하려 해도 조만간 널 따라잡을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028178
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E39D5A, 00AB07CA, 00E155BF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 괜찮다면 난 이 일에 끼고 싶지 않아., Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02028134/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028178
msgctxt "000BB5"
msgid "You're not the first one to get wrapped up in something you didn't sign up for."
msgstr "원치 않던 일에 휘말린 사람이 네가 처음은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028189
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00375FCB
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 02028133/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028189
msgctxt "000BB6"
msgid "Aggression levels? Should I be worried?"
msgstr "공격성 수준? 걱정해야 해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028169
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B700B9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02028135/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:02028169
