msgstr "안 돼. 안 돼. 안 돼. 안 돼. 안 돼!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202804F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 009427A5
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Supportive
#: 02028042/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:0202804F
msgctxt "000BCE"
msgid "Oh, but we were just getting to the good part! We can try again later."
msgstr "오, 이제 막 재미있는 부분이었는데! 나중에 다시 해보면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202804C
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 007B78B2
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED That kind of embarrassment that's angry
#: 02028043/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:0202804C
msgctxt "000BCF"
msgid "*Sigh* I lost my place. Anna, this is embarrassing. Stop the recording."
msgstr "*한숨* 어디까지 했는지 잊었군. 안나, 이거 창피하군. 녹음 멈춰."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202804A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0048C485
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Pretending to give a grand speech. Can be intentionally stilted cause he's bad at public speaking
#: 02028044/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:0202804A
msgctxt "000BD0"
msgid "\"Why couldn't humanity adopt from creatures who already solved these problems? Why-\""
msgstr "인류는 이미 이런 문제를 해결한 생물들에게서 왜 받아들이지 못했는가? 왜-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028049
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0030F8BA
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Pretending to give a grand speech. Can be intentionally stilted cause he's bad at public speaking
#: 02028045/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:02028049
msgctxt "000BD1"
msgid "\"Like all the scientists I stand upon the shoulders of, I took it upon myself to solve this problem. And, like those before me. I took inspiration from my surroundings.\""
msgstr "내가 그 어깨 위에 올라선 모든 과학자들처럼, 나도 이 문제를 직접 해결하기로 했다. 그리고 선구자들이 그랬듯, 내 주변에서 영감을 얻었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202804E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0055F751
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Pretending to give a grand speech. Can be intentionally stilted cause he's bad at public speaking
#: 02028046/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:0202804E
msgctxt "000BD2"
msgid "\"In my opinion, we didn't have hundreds of thousands of years to waste. Nor could we afford a half-measure. What we needed was perfection.\""
msgstr "내 생각에 우리에게는 수십만 년을 낭비할 시간이 없었다. 어설픈 절충안을 택할 여유도 없었다. 우리에게 필요한 것은 완벽함이었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202804D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00E4475E
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Pretending to give a grand speech. Can be intentionally stilted cause he's bad at public speaking
#: 02028047/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_03:0202804D
msgctxt "000BD3"
msgid "\"Evolution is slow, unfocused. It weaves in and out of solutions over hundreds of thousands of years before arriving at something in between.\""
msgstr "진화는 느리고, 방향성이 없다. 수십만 년에 걸쳐 여러 해결책 사이를 오가다 결국 어중간한 결과에 도달한다."

