#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B295
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009C963F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0202B257/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B295
msgctxt "000E33"
msgid "Well, just wanted to make sure you're all right. "
msgstr "그냥 네가 괜찮은지 확인하고 싶었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B28C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0049FD7E
#: 02036D9C/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B28C
msgctxt "000E42"
msgid "Not at all. If I could I would kill them all again, with a smile."
msgstr "전혀. 할 수만 있다면 웃으면서 전부 다시 죽였을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B283
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 001777C1, 005DB837
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Neutral
#: 0202B266/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B283
msgctxt "000E45"
msgid "But outside of the choice itself, how are you feeling? "
msgstr "하지만 그 선택 자체를 제외하고, 지금 기분은 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B281
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00EF2A24
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Prompt: 모르겠어, 다시 생각하게 돼.
#: 0202B267/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B281
msgctxt "000E4A"
msgid "Nah, you did the right thing. Don't second guess it, or you'll drive yourself nuts."
msgstr "아니, 넌 옳은 일을 했어. 괜히 의심하지 마. 그러다 미쳐 버려."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B27E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00BE4FF9
#: 0202B268/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B27E
msgctxt "000E4B"
msgid "I don't know, I'm having second thoughts."
msgstr "모르겠어, 다시 생각하게 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B29A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00F3DB04
#: 0202B26A/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B29A
msgctxt "000E4C"
msgid "I actually enjoy the idea of wiping them all out."
msgstr "난 사실 그들을 모조리 쓸어버린다는 생각이 즐거워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B27B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00B7D1B3, 00B64BB1
#. Notes = Suspicious, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 난 사실 그들을 모조리 쓸어버린다는 생각이 즐거워.
#: 0202B269/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B27B
msgctxt "000E4D"
msgid "Creepy. That's going a little too far, but yeah. It was the right move."
msgstr "소름 돋네. 그건 좀 지나치지만, 그래. 옳은 선택이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B294
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00B45BB4
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 우리와 그들 중에서, 난 우리를 택했어.
#: 0202B26B/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B294
msgctxt "000E4F"
msgid "Amen. "
msgstr "아멘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B290
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0009B39F
#: 0202B26C/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B290
msgctxt "000E50"
msgid "It's us against them, and I chose us."
msgstr "우리와 그들 중에서, 난 우리를 택했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B28D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F5573C
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 개척 성계를 안전하게 지키는 게 최우선이었어.
#: 0202B26D/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B28D
msgctxt "000E51"
msgid "Damn straight."
msgstr "당연하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B289
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FBD724
#: 0202B26E/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B289
msgctxt "000E52"
msgid "Keeping the Settled Systems safe was the priority."
msgstr "개척 성계를 안전하게 지키는 게 최우선이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B27D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00676240
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 어려울 것 없는 선택이었어.
#: 0202B271/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B27D
msgctxt "000E58"
msgid "Maybe, if you don't think about the big picture. Ignorance is bliss, right?"
msgstr "큰 그림을 생각하지 않으면 그럴 수도 있지. 모르는 게 약이라잖아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B29C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 006FB412
#: 0202B272/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B29C
msgctxt "000E59"
msgid "It was an easy choice to make."
msgstr "어려울 것 없는 선택이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B298
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00496A93
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 그냥 동전이나 던질 걸 그랬어.
#: 0202B273/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B298
msgctxt "000E5B"
msgid "Honestly, I just might have. Let Lady Luck make the call, you can blame her after."
msgstr "솔직히, 나라도 그랬을지 몰라. 행운의 여신에게 맡기고, 나중에 그녀를 탓하면 되잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B27A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002989A2
#: 0202B274/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B27A
msgctxt "000E5C"
msgid "I should've just flipped a coin."
msgstr "그냥 동전이나 던질 걸 그랬어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B299
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0054EDBB
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 불가능한 선택이었어.
#: 0202B275/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B299
msgctxt "000E5D"
msgid "Yeah. And it's fine to over agonize it."
msgstr "그래. 그리고 너무 괴로워해도 괜찮아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B29D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 006BF06B
#: 0202B276/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B29D
msgctxt "000E5E"
msgid "It was an impossible choice."
msgstr "불가능한 선택이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B291
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00AD2D50
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed, Prompt: 결국 역사는 내 편을 들어줄 거야.
#: 0202B277/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B291
msgctxt "000E5F"
msgid "Glad you're confident about it."
msgstr "네가 확신해서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B28A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00DB5466
#: 0202B278/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B28A
msgctxt "000E60"
msgid "History will side with me in the end."
msgstr "결국 역사는 내 편을 들어줄 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B297
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00146778
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0202B279/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B297
msgctxt "000E63"
msgid "Hey, I just wanted to have a chat about what happened with the Terrans."
msgstr "있잖아, 테란과 있었던 일에 대해 좀 얘기하고 싶었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00A74B43
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Doesn't know who can hear them
#: 0202B0A5/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B7
msgctxt "000E65"
msgid "Frank. It's Frank now. And you're Anna."
msgstr "프랭크. 이제 프랭크야. 그리고 넌 안나야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 001CEC0E
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED She's burying her old life
#: 0202B09C/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B0
msgctxt "000E66"
msgid "It's hard to understand sometimes why they don't believe us."
msgstr "가끔은 사람들이 왜 우릴 믿지 않는지 이해하기 어려워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00F4BF56
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Comfort Wife Mode
#: 0202B09B/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B5
msgctxt "000E67"
msgid "I know. But we can't let them win. All we can do now is keep moving forward and prove them wrong. Together."
msgstr "알아. 하지만 그들이 이기게 둘 순 없어. 지금 우리가 할 수 있는 건 계속 나아가서 그들이 틀렸다는 걸 증명하는 것뿐이야. 함께."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 004DA549
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED She's burying her old life
#: 0202B09F/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B8
msgctxt "000E69"
msgid "I know. I know that. It's just..."
msgstr "알아. 나도 알아. 그냥..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 003D2E66
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Hit that "Anna"
#: 0202B098/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B6
msgctxt "000E6A"
msgid "I love you too, Anna."
msgstr "나도 사랑해, 안나."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 005BA308
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED She's burying her old life
#: 0202B09D/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0AC
msgctxt "000E6B"
msgid "And to think that they looked at our work and turned on us? What we're doing will change everything."
msgstr "그들이 우리 연구를 보고도 등을 돌렸다는 게 말이 돼? 우리가 하는 일은 모든 걸 바꿀 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00D2F7AE
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Hit that "Frank"
#: 0202B099/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B1
msgctxt "000E6C"
msgid "I love you, Frank."
msgstr "사랑해, 프랭크."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 008BF8C7
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Comfort Wife Mode
#: 0202B0A0/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B4
msgctxt "000E6D"
msgid "You know what they would've done to us. We had to leave."
msgstr "그들이 우리한테 무슨 짓을 했을지 알잖아. 우린 떠날 수밖에 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00F80C91
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Comfort Wife Mode
#: 0202B0A1/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B2
msgctxt "000E6E"
msgid "Hey, it's ok. We're gonna be ok."
msgstr "괜찮아. 우린 괜찮을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 002BFD7D
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Trying to keep it together and then loses it
#: 0202B0A3/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0A9
msgctxt "000E6F"
msgid "Right. Frank. Frank...*sobbing*"
msgstr "맞아. 프랭크. 프랭크...*흐느낌*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00671203
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED She's burying her old life
#: 0202B09E/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0AA
msgctxt "000E70"
msgid "I was so happy being Lauren Espinoza. And I was so proud of my husband, William."
msgstr "로렌 에스피노자로 사는 게 정말 행복했어. 그리고 내 남편 윌리엄이 정말 자랑스러웠고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 0049C79A
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Doesn't know who can hear them
#: 0202B0A4/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B9
msgctxt "000E72"
msgid "We've been over this: Frank and Anna Santos. We built this homestead when we were young and only now have been able to retire here."
msgstr "이미 얘기했잖아. 프랭크와 안나 산토스. 우린 젊었을 때 이 정착지를 지었고 이제서야 여기서 은퇴 생활을 하게 된 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 001E9F5E
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Starting the breakdown
#: 0202B0A6/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0B3
msgctxt "000E73"
msgid "Oh, William-"
msgstr "오, 윌리엄-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00B9D0C2
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED SO overwhelmed. Hasn't been able to sit down for so long
#: 0202B0A8/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0AF
msgctxt "000E74"
msgid "Gross? Disgusting?"
msgstr "징그러워? 역겨워?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00C4DC08
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Recognition of her weariness
#: 0202B0A7/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0AE
msgctxt "000E75"
msgid "I was going to say \"cozy\"."
msgstr "난 \"아늑하다\"고 하려고 했는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_FrankSantos
#. SoundFileID = 00AA3BB8
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED Attempt at being cheerful
#: 0202B0BA/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0BD
msgctxt "000E76"
msgid "I told you, historians will want to know everything about us. Why not give them what they want?"
msgstr "말했잖아, 역사가들은 우리에 관한 모든 걸 알고 싶어 할 거야. 원하는 걸 줘서 나쁠 게 없지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B0BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_AnnaSantos
#. SoundFileID = 008F07D3
#. Notes = NO FACE DATA NEEDED So done with his shit
#: 0202B0BB/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot01_AL_04:0202B0BF
msgctxt "000E77"
msgid "Why're you recording this?"
msgstr "이건 왜 녹음하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_ExplosivePawns
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B247
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_03_MinibotWave00
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 001936C8
#. Notes = Said as they're pressing a button to unleash robot minions RIGHT before combat
#: 0202B246/00003/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_03_MinibotWave00:0202B247
msgctxt "000E79"
msgid "Deploying Explosive Pawns."
msgstr "폭발 폰 전개 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2DB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_08_DeltaIntercom
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_Crew_Elite_Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A3927D
#. Notes = Grim
#: 0202B2A3/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_08_DeltaIntercom:0202B2DB
msgctxt "000E7A"
msgid "Alert: Must enter alone. Leave potential assistants behind."
msgstr "경보: 단독으로 입장해야 함. 잠재적 보조 인력은 뒤에 두고 올 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_08_DeltaIntercom
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_Crew_Elite_Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009C4507
#. Notes = Grim
#: 0202B2A5/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_08_DeltaIntercom:0202B2D0
msgctxt "000E7C"
msgid "Auxiliary Human detected. Proceed to Final Challenge."
msgstr "보조 인간 감지. 최종 도전 과제로 진행."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00FD905B, 000667D0
#. Notes = To themselves / to Player Default, Smug / to Player Default
#: 0202B2A6/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2DA
msgctxt "000E7D"
msgid "Updating \"Auxiliary Human\" Partition...Assigning new moniker...Recompiling..."
msgstr "보조 인간 파티션 업데이트 중...새 별칭 할당 중...재컴파일 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00C0FB90
#. Notes = Resolute / to Player Default
#: 0202B2A7/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2D4
msgctxt "000E7E"
msgid "Historical texts showed exchanging of gifts for ceremonial purposes. Here."
msgstr "역사 문헌에 따르면 의례적 목적으로 선물을 교환함. 여기."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00CC760A
#. Notes = SMUG / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q04
#: 0202B2A8/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2CF
msgctxt "000E7F"
msgid "Addendum: Perishable only leader at Delta Unit's behest. I am still the superior being."
msgstr "추가 사항: 부패성 개체는 델타 기체의 명령에 의해서만 지도자임. 나는 여전히 우월한 존재임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 003C3633
#. Notes = Um, actually / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 이긴다는 건 말이 안 돼. 대부분은 아직 내가 이겼잖아.
#: 0202B2AB/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2DF
msgctxt "000E82"
msgid "Counterpoint:  As established, \"Winner takes all.\""
msgstr "반론:  합의된 바에 따르면, \"승자가 모든 것을 갖는다.\""

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00F680CE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B2AC/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2D9
msgctxt "000E83"
msgid "It doesn't make sense for you to win, I still won the majority."
msgstr "네가 이긴다는 건 말이 안 돼. 대부분은 아직 내가 이겼잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00A3126C
#. Notes = HA, no. / to Player Default, Prompt: 재대결하자. 이기면 두 배, 지면 무효로.
#: 0202B2AD/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2D6
msgctxt "000E84"
msgid "Attempt at trickery acknowledged and denied."
msgstr "속임수 시도 확인 및 거부."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00C18FF2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B2AE/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2D1
msgctxt "000E85"
msgid "Let's have a rematch, double or nothing."
msgstr "재대결하자. 이기면 두 배, 지면 무효로."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00BE5D83
#. Notes = You're not getting out of this that easily / to Player Default, Prompt: 그냥 지금 쏴 죽여.
#: 0202B2AF/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2CC
msgctxt "000E86"
msgid "Denied. Auxiliary no longer able to give orders."
msgstr "거부. 보조 인간은 더 이상 명령을 내릴 수 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00A0A5D2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B2B0/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2CA
msgctxt "000E87"
msgid "Just shoot me now."
msgstr "그냥 지금 쏴 죽여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004703BE
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: ...명령 대기 중...선장...
#: 0202B2B1/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2C7
msgctxt "000E88"
msgid "Acknowledged. Increasing Servility variable..."
msgstr "확인. 노예 근성 변수 증가 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00843B6F
#. Notes = SMUG / to Player Default
#: 0202B2B4/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2E0
msgctxt "000E89"
msgid "Final Score: Auxiliary Human: 3, Delta Unit: 1. Delta Victory."
msgstr "최종 점수: 보조 인간: 3, 델타 기체: 1. 델타 승리."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0080929D
#. Notes = SMUG / to Player Default
#: 0202B2B3/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2E2
msgctxt "000E8A"
msgid "Delta Unit determined to be superior being. And leader. As agreed."
msgstr "델타 기체이 우월한 존재로 판정됨. 그리고 지도자임. 합의한 대로."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00793F7C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B2B2/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2C4
msgctxt "000E8B"
msgid "...Awaiting orders...Captain..."
msgstr "...명령 대기 중...선장..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00170BD0
#. Notes = Of course / to Player Default, Prompt: 이제 네가 리더라는 뜻이야?
#: 0202B2B5/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2D2
msgctxt "000E8C"
msgid "According to the rules agreed."
msgstr "합의한 규칙에 따라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0069E593
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B2B6/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2CD
msgctxt "000E8D"
msgid "Does this mean you're in charge?"
msgstr "이제 네가 리더라는 뜻이야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_PawnsCounterpoint
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 003B4F86, 00DCEB05
#. Notes = Um, actually / to Player Default, Prompt: I thought this was one on one, how come you used explosive drones?
#: 02093F48/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_06_PostCombat_DeltaLose:0202B2CB
msgctxt "000E8E"
msgid "Counterpoint: Stated stipulation, \"Solo combat. No assistance from other intelligent entities.\""
msgstr "반론: 명시된 조건, \"단독 전투. 다른 지성체의 지원 없음.\""

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2C9
