#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 다시 리더가 된 내가 내리는 첫 명령은 네가 날 이겼다는 걸 아무에게도 말하지 말라는 거야.
#: 0202B994/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9B1
msgctxt "000ED0"
msgid "Acknowledged. Archiving and encrypting data..."
msgstr "확인. 데이터 아카이브 및 암호화 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B9AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 009949FC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B995/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9AE
msgctxt "000ED1"
msgid "My first order as leader again is to not tell anyone you beat me."
msgstr "다시 리더가 된 내가 내리는 첫 명령은 네가 날 이겼다는 걸 아무에게도 말하지 말라는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B9B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0002878A, 00817A6B
#. Notes = Genuinely intrigued / to Player Default, Prompt: 날 동물처럼 관찰하고 싶다는 거야?
#: 0202B992/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9B8
msgctxt "000ED2"
msgid "Observation begets data. Data begets understanding."
msgstr "관찰은 데이터를 낳고, 데이터는 이해를 낳음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B9B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0002878A, 00817A6B
#. Notes = Genuinely intrigued / to Player Default, Prompt: 날 동물처럼 관찰하고 싶다는 거야?
#: 0202B992/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9B8
msgctxt "000ED3"
msgid "Correct. Most humans are predictable. Strange to encounter an anomaly."
msgstr "정확함. 대부분의 인간은 예측 가능함. 이상 현상과 마주치는 것은 이례적임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B9C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0052EA7A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B997/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9C4
msgctxt "000ED4"
msgid "Well, I'm glad it all worked out."
msgstr "그래, 다 잘 풀려서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B9B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
