#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202B99D/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B9B6
msgctxt "000EDE"
msgid "I can keep going."
msgstr "난 계속할 수 있어."

