#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDC9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00CC9DF5, 0012B20A
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202CDA2/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDC9
msgctxt "000F44"
msgid "I have a guarantee from one of our militia generals that you'll have reinforcements against the Terrans when the time comes."
msgstr "때가 오면 테란을 상대로 지원군을 보내 주겠다는 보증을 우리 민병대 장군 중 한 명에게 받아 두었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDC6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009D3FE6
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 테르니온 III 전초기지는 준비됐습니다.
#: 0202CDA3/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDC6
msgctxt "000F47"
msgid "Good. I'll let my contacts know it's ready so they can prep a team."
msgstr "좋아. 준비됐다고 내 연락책들에게 알려서 팀을 꾸리게 하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDBF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 007E4078
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 이제 거래에서 네 몫을 지킬 차례야.
#: 0202CDA5/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDBF
msgctxt "000F48"
msgid "Of course. "
msgstr "물론입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDBC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00DE7585
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202CDA6/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDBC
msgctxt "000F49"
msgid "Time to hold up your end of the deal."
msgstr "이제 거래에서 네 몫을 지킬 차례야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDB6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B6E203
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 마음에 드셨으면 좋겠군요.
#: 0202CDA7/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDB6
msgctxt "000F4A"
msgid "I'm certain it will be adequate."
msgstr "충분할 거라 확신합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0032C1B5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202CDA8/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDB1
msgctxt "000F4B"
msgid "I hope it's to your liking."
msgstr "마음에 드셨으면 좋겠군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 009CF854
#. Notes = Question / to Player Default, Face: Question
#: 0202CDA9/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:0202CDAA
msgctxt "000F4C"
msgid "The outpost. Is it finally complete?"
msgstr "전초기지. 드디어 완성된 겁니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDC4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E47EF2
#: 0202CD86/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDC4
msgctxt "000F53"
msgid "The Strix I outpost is ready."
msgstr "스트릭스 I 전초기지는 준비됐습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0067C540, 00FEEA47, 00259BCE
#. Notes = Changing the subject with the word "Now" / Confident, Face: Confident, Confident
#: 0202CD84/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDCA
msgctxt "000F54"
msgid "We'll do all we can to clear a path, you have my word."
msgstr "길을 열기 위해 할 수 있는 건 전부 하겠습니다. 약속드리죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0067C540, 00FEEA47, 00259BCE
#. Notes = Changing the subject with the word "Now" / Confident, Face: Confident, Confident
#: 0202CD84/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDCA
msgctxt "000F55"
msgid "And once we take that final fight to those Terrans, you'll have UC ships by your side."
msgstr "그리고 테란과의 최후의 전투에 나서게 되면, 식민지 연합 함선들이 당신 곁에 있을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0067C540, 00FEEA47, 00259BCE
#. Notes = Changing the subject with the word "Now" / Confident, Face: Confident, Confident
#: 0202CD84/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDCA
msgctxt "000F56"
msgid "Now, I owe you one X-Tech power core to do with as you please..."
msgstr "자, 이제 원하는 대로 쓸 X-테크 동력 코어 하나를 드려야겠군요..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDC7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005079D6
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Prompt: 스트릭스 I 전초기지는 준비됐습니다.
#: 0202CD85/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDC7
msgctxt "000F58"
msgid "Good. I got a team just raring to go."
msgstr "좋아. 당장 출동하고 싶어 안달 난 팀이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDC1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 002B43E7
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Prompt: 모두 준비됐어. 이제 네 차례야.
#: 0202CD87/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDC1
msgctxt "000F59"
msgid "And I have every intention of making good."
msgstr "그리고 난 반드시 약속을 지킬 생각입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 006FA963
#: 0202CD88/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDB9
msgctxt "000F5A"
msgid "It's all set. Now it's your turn."
msgstr "모두 준비됐어. 이제 네 차례야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 005BDD4B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Prompt: 이미 끝난 거나 다름없습니다.
#: 0202CD89/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDAE
msgctxt "000F5B"
msgid "Music to my ears."
msgstr "듣던 중 반가운 말이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDD2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00613978
#: 0202CD8A/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDD2
msgctxt "000F5C"
msgid "It's as good as done."
msgstr "이미 끝난 거나 다름없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202CDCD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 006C043C
#. Notes = Question, Face: Question
#: 0202CD8B/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:0202CDCD
msgctxt "000F5D"
msgid "You wrap up that outpost?"
msgstr "그 전초기지는 마무리했나?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ03_DeltaArgument
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C526
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000CCF84
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C54A/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C526
msgctxt "000F5E"
msgid "Pushing software update deemed most effective action to destroy Terran Armada. Cost-benefit analysis determines potential resulting loss of civilian life justifiable."
msgstr ""
"소프트웨어 업데이트 배포가 테란 함대를 파괴하는 데 가장 효과적인 조치로 판단됨. 비용 편익 분석 결과, 그로 인해 발생할 수 있는 "
"민간인 생명 손실은 정당화 가능하다고 판단됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02029367
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0064A15A
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 다른 지휘 센터도 찾을 수 있어?
#: 02029351/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:02029367
msgctxt "000F5F"
msgid "Unable to identify. Total knowledge of command structure inaccessible from this location."
msgstr "식별 불가. 이 위치에서는 지휘 구조 전체에 대한 지식에 접근할 수 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02029368
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0096B4D5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 요점만 말해.
#: 02029353/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:02029368
msgctxt "000F60"
msgid "Acknowledged."
msgstr "확인."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02029362
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009B059E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 유니파이어가 모든 로봇을 통제한다는 거군.
#: 02029355/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:02029362
msgctxt "000F61"
msgid "Potentially. Unable to draw conclusive statement regarding full chain of command."
msgstr "가능성 있음. 전체 지휘 계통에 관한 확정적 진술은 도출 불가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202936B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = UCOfficer_FB_0500_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00338D15, 004795FA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02029360/00000/UCOfficer_FB_0500_SFTER_MQ03:0202936B
msgctxt "000F62"
msgid "Recommend beginning combat maneuvers."
msgstr "전투 기동 시작 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 0062D85C, 009682E4, 005DE3AF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 최종 목적이 뭐야? 무력으로 개척 성계 전체를 병합하려는 거야?
#: 0202AC2F/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3C
msgctxt "000F63"
msgid "That right there is the difference between me and those you work for. I don't hide behind platitudes."
msgstr "바로 그게 나와 네 상관들의 차이다. 나는 듣기 좋은 빈말 뒤에 숨지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 0062D85C, 009682E4, 005DE3AF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 최종 목적이 뭐야? 무력으로 개척 성계 전체를 병합하려는 거야?
#: 0202AC2F/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3C
msgctxt "000F64"
msgid "You yourself answer to backroom oligarchs, yet you have the audacity to question my cause?"
msgstr "너 자신도 밀실의 과두 지배자들에게 복종하면서, 감히 내 대의를 의심하나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 0062D85C, 009682E4, 005DE3AF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 최종 목적이 뭐야? 무력으로 개척 성계 전체를 병합하려는 거야?
#: 0202AC2F/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3C
msgctxt "000F65"
msgid "If that's what it takes to dismantle this dystopian hellscape, then yes."
msgstr "이 디스토피아적 지옥도를 해체하는 데 그게 필요하다면, 그렇다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00D8AD2F, 00891678
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 솔직히 난 밤에 꽤 잘 자...
#: 0202AC31/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3A
msgctxt "000F66"
msgid "Someone with your abilities could have made a real difference, yet you choose to do grunt work for crooks?"
msgstr "너 정도 능력이면 정말 큰 차이를 만들 수 있었을 텐데, 고작 범죄자들 심부름이나 하기로 한 건가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00D8AD2F, 00891678
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 솔직히 난 밤에 꽤 잘 자...
#: 0202AC31/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3A
msgctxt "000F67"
msgid "I don't put it past a mercenary to be so thoughtless. What a waste."
msgstr "용병이 그렇게 생각 없게 굴어도 놀랍진 않군. 참 아까워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00BDC3B9, 002021BA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 오늘은 이미 충분히 피를 흘렸습니다, 제독. 병력에게 물러서라고 명령하면 대화할 수 있습니다.
#: 0202AC35/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3F
msgctxt "000F68"
msgid "Either this armada stands victorious today, or is obliterated completely."
msgstr "오늘 이 테란 함대가 승리하거나, 완전히 궤멸하거나 둘 중 하나다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00BDC3B9, 002021BA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 오늘은 이미 충분히 피를 흘렸습니다, 제독. 병력에게 물러서라고 명령하면 대화할 수 있습니다.
#: 0202AC35/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3F
msgctxt "000F69"
msgid "There's nothing to discuss. You're looking for compromise, while working for crooks."
msgstr "논의할 건 없다. 넌 범죄자들 밑에서 일하면서 타협점을 찾고 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 006D0D4D, 00E4B8DC, 00CE6209
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202AC37/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3D
msgctxt "000F6A"
msgid "How many of those politicians, are here fighting beside you today?"
msgstr "그 정치인들 중 오늘 네 곁에서 함께 싸우고 있는 자가 몇이나 되지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202AC3D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 006D0D4D, 00E4B8DC, 00CE6209
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202AC37/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202AC3D
msgctxt "000F6B"
msgid "Let me ask you an honest question, how does it feel enabling politicians who govern behind closed doors?"
msgstr "솔직히 하나 묻지. 닫힌 문 뒤에서 통치하는 정치인들을 돕는 기분이 어떤가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C532
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1500_09_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0007650A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C513/00000/DELTA_FB_1500_09_SFTER_MQ03:0202C532
msgctxt "000F6C"
msgid "Must evacuate immediately."
msgstr "즉시 대피해야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C533
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1305_07_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D043F4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C515/00000/DELTA_FB_1305_07_SFTER_MQ03:0202C533
msgctxt "000F6D"
msgid "Alert: Enemies detected. Program requires additional time. Invoking \"teamwork\" protocol."
msgstr "경보: 적 감지. 프로그램에 추가 시간이 필요합니다. \"협동\" 프로토콜 호출 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
