#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C540/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C55B
msgctxt "000F6E"
msgid "Setting coordinates to current location..."
msgstr "현재 위치로 좌표 설정 중..."

