#. SoundFileID = 006B4D7D
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 로봇들이 서로를 공격하게 됩니까?
#: 0202C54B/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C571
msgctxt "000F7A"
msgid "No. Robots would still retain the [Terran Armada -- Robot] tag. Still see each other as allies."
msgstr "아니요. 로봇들은 여전히 [테란 함대 -- 로봇] 태그를 유지합니다. 서로를 아군으로 인식합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C56E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FE83A9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C54C/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C56E
msgctxt "000F7B"
msgid "Would the robots turn on each other?"
msgstr "로봇들이 서로를 공격하게 됩니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C56A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004751FB
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그게 당신에게는 무슨 의미입니까?
#: 0202C54D/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C56A
msgctxt "000F7C"
msgid "I am disconnected from their network. Software updates not applicable."
msgstr "저는 그들의 네트워크에서 분리되어 있습니다. 소프트웨어 업데이트는 적용되지 않습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C568
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000F84AE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C54E/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C568
msgctxt "000F7D"
msgid "What does that mean for you?"
msgstr "그게 당신에게는 무슨 의미입니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C566
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002A0742
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이러면 테란 함대가 마비될 것입니다.
#: 0202C54F/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C566
msgctxt "000F7E"
msgid "Correct. Increasing Intelligence variable..."
msgstr "정확함. 지능 변수 증가 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C564
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E8589E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C550/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C564
msgctxt "000F7F"
msgid "This would cripple the Terran Armada."
msgstr "이러면 테란 함대가 마비될 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C561
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005A91CC
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 하지만 테란 로봇 근처의 모든 사람도 위험해집니다.
#: 0202C551/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C561
msgctxt "000F80"
msgid "Correct. Running cost-benefit analysis..."
msgstr "정확합니다. 비용 편익 분석 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C55E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002EE30D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C552/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C55E
msgctxt "000F81"
msgid "But it would also endanger everyone near a Terran Robot."
msgstr "하지만 테란 로봇 근처의 모든 사람도 위험해집니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C55C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0062856F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C553/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C55C
msgctxt "000F82"
msgid "Hypothesis: Database update results in Robots becoming hostile to all human entities, resulting in total destruction of chain of command."
msgstr "가설: 데이터베이스 업데이트로 로봇들이 모든 인간 개체에 적대적으로 변해, 지휘 체계가 완전히 파괴되는 결과 발생."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C573
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F2AF0B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C554/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C573
msgctxt "000F83"
msgid "Auxiliary, recommending sending software update to remove [Terran Armada -- Human] tag from Hive-Link parameter Database."
msgstr ""
"보조 인간, 하이브-링크 매개변수 데이터베이스에서 [테란 함대 -- 인간] 태그를 제거하는 소프트웨어 업데이트 전송을 권장합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C55F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0076CA6E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C558/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C55F
msgctxt "000F84"
msgid "I was suspicious of coordination method for the large robotic network. Ran a comparative analysis of previous orders."
msgstr "대규모 로봇 네트워크의 조율 방식이 의심스러웠습니다. 이전 명령들에 대한 비교 분석을 실행했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C56C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002C138B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C556/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C56C
msgctxt "000F85"
msgid "Able to send orders to all robots connected to Unifier's \"Hive-Link\" network from this location. Also able to remotely rewrite operating parameters. Running potential options..."
msgstr ""
"이 위치에서 유니파이어의 \"하이브-링크\" 네트워크에 연결된 모든 로봇에게 명령을 전송할 수 있습니다. 작동 매개변수도 원격으로 다시 "
"쓸 수 있습니다. 가능한 선택지 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C562
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0030AB28
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C557/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C562
msgctxt "000F86"
msgid "Discovered Unifier as present in every relay of orders. All administrative commands are centralized under the same name: \"Hive-Link.\""
msgstr ""
"모든 명령 중계에 유니파이어가 존재함을 발견했습니다. 모든 관리 명령은 같은 이름 아래 중앙화되어 있습니다: \"하이브-링크.\""

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C56D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0081F52B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C559/00000/DELTA_FB_1310_08_SFTER_MQ03:0202C56D
msgctxt "000F87"
msgid "Auxiliary, flaw detected in the Terran network."
msgstr "보조 인간, 테란 네트워크에서 결함 감지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E100DF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 난 목숨을 구하려는 거야. 네 목숨을 버리고 싶다면 마음대로 해. 그래도 네 병사들은 살려.
#: 0202D0AC/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B5
msgctxt "000F88"
msgid "My troops stand with me. Our cause is one and the same. If you insist on fighting this war, so be it."
msgstr "내 병사들은 나와 함께한다. 우리의 대의는 하나다. 이 전쟁을 계속하겠다면, 그렇게 해라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001D3C5B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202D0AD/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B4
msgctxt "000F89"
msgid "I'm trying to save lives. If you want to throw yours away go ahead, at least save your troops."
msgstr "난 목숨을 구하려는 거야. 네 목숨을 버리고 싶다면 마음대로 해. 그래도 네 병사들은 살려."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 0049553F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: [공격] 이쯤 하지.
#: 0202D0AE/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B3
msgctxt "000F8A"
msgid "Troops, rally on me!"
msgstr "병사들, 내게 집결!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00CF4C20
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202D0AF/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B2
msgctxt "000F8B"
msgid "[Attack] Enough of this."
msgstr "[공격] 이쯤 하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 00467874
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: [공격] 그들이 나한테 얼마를 주는지 알아? 크레딧만 충분하면 행성 하나도 불태울 수 있어.
#: 0202D0B0/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B6
msgctxt "000F8C"
msgid "Enough, I'm not wasting anymore time entertaining a soulless parasite. Kill them."
msgstr "그만. 영혼 없는 기생충 장단에 맞춰 더는 시간 낭비하지 않겠다. 죽여라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202D0B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Admiral
#. SoundFileID = 0029EB14
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202D0B1/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:0202D0B7
msgctxt "000F8D"
msgid "[Attack] Do you have any idea how much they pay me? I'll torch a planet for enough credits."
msgstr "[공격] 그들이 나한테 얼마를 주는지 알아? 크레딧만 충분하면 행성 하나도 불태울 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C454
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0015A065, 00F0F5D3
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0200E06D/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C454
msgctxt "000F90"
msgid "We're just trying to make our own way out here, surveying as we go."
msgstr "우린 여기서 조사도 하면서 우리 길을 찾아가고 있을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020174B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00891D8D, 00A3C1D1
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174A9/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020174B2
msgctxt "000F95"
msgid "Do we look like terrorists to you? "
msgstr "우리가 테러리스트처럼 보여?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C411
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009CDEA3
#. Notes = Friendly, acting natural so as not to get blow a cover. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C411
msgctxt "000F96"
msgid "Hey, you lost?"
msgstr "저기, 길 잃었어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C410
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001FD939
#. Notes = Friendly, acting natural so as not to get blow a cover. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C410
msgctxt "000F97"
msgid "Hey there. Wasn't expecting to see anyone else out here. Need help with anything?"
msgstr "안녕. 이런 곳에서 다른 사람을 볼 줄은 몰랐네. 뭐 도와줄 일 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_AttackResponse02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00927FEB
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C2A6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3B1
msgctxt "000F9A"
msgid "I knew I couldn't trust you."
msgstr "역시 널 믿을 수 없다는 걸 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalD01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C39A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
