#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C39A
msgctxt "000F9B"
msgid "[Attack] Thanks for confirming you're Terrans. I just had to be sure."
msgstr "[공격] 테란이라고 확인해 줘서 고맙군. 확실히 해둘 필요가 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalC01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C377
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00109ADF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A7/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C377
msgctxt "000F9D"
msgid "[Attack] For the safety of the Settled Systems, I can't let you go."
msgstr "[공격] 개척 성계의 안전을 위해, 너희를 보내줄 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C444
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002495FD, 00D257DC, 00710FB8
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C444
msgctxt "000F9E"
msgid "Thank you for letting us go."
msgstr "우리를 보내줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C444
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002495FD, 00D257DC, 00710FB8
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C444
msgctxt "000F9F"
msgid "Once we've found somewhere to settle, we'll make sure others will have a safe space to go."
msgstr "정착할 곳을 찾으면, 다른 사람들도 갈 수 있는 안전한 곳이 생기게 할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C444
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002495FD, 00D257DC, 00710FB8
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C444
msgctxt "000FA0"
msgid "You're... you're right. Our situation won't allow for much, but we'll do what we can."
msgstr "네가... 네 말이 맞아. 우리 상황상 많은 건 못 하겠지만, 할 수 있는 건 해볼게."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalB01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C422
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004C64C9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A9/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C422
msgctxt "000FA1"
msgid "Then spread the word you got out. Others will follow."
msgstr "그럼 너희가 빠져나왔다고 알려. 다른 사람들도 따라올 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C403
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D1C487
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 0202C2AA/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C403
msgctxt "000FA4"
msgid "You're serious. Thank you, and believe me, we'll make the most of it. "
msgstr "진심이구나. 고마워, 정말로. 반드시 제대로 활용할게."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalA01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004333DE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AB/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3E8
msgctxt "000FA5"
msgid "Make a new life. The Terrans are too distracted to look for you."
msgstr "새 삶을 시작해. 테란들은 너무 정신이 팔려서 너희를 찾지 못할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003056B3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3BD
msgctxt "000FA6"
msgid "[Attack] Nice story. Too bad I don't believe it."
msgstr "[공격] 그럴듯한 이야기군. 믿지 않는 게 아쉽겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D5BB36
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2AE/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3A4
msgctxt "000FA8"
msgid "Come on. This is all a big mistake."
msgstr "이봐. 이건 전부 큰 오해야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C390
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006BBCCB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AF/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C390
msgctxt "000FA9"
msgid "Seriously? It's really in your best interest to hear me out now."
msgstr "진심이야? 지금은 내 말을 들어보는 게 정말 네게도 이로울 텐데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BB556A
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: There are plenty of non-violent ways to reach people. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2B0/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene:0202C3D7
msgctxt "000FAA"
msgid "And who would listen? Violence is all people like that answer to."
msgstr "그런데 누가 들어주겠어? 그런 인간들은 폭력에만 반응해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0027F8D4
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: There are plenty of non-violent ways to reach people. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B0/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene:0202C3D6
msgctxt "000FAB"
msgid "You're right. Violence wouldn't have been my first choice."
msgstr "맞아. 폭력이 내 첫 선택은 아니었을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CA054D
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2B1/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc04Scene:0202C3A9
msgctxt "000FAC"
msgid "There are plenty of non-violent ways to reach people."
msgstr "사람들에게 뜻을 전할 비폭력적인 방법은 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C408
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FC13DF
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You're extremists. Did you even hear the SSNN broadcast? / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2B2/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene:0202C408
msgctxt "000FAD"
msgid "But we had to get the attention of the Settled Systems."
msgstr "하지만 우리는 개척 성계의 관심을 끌어야 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C407
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0029DD68
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You're extremists. Did you even hear the SSNN broadcast? / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B2/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene:0202C407
msgctxt "000FAE"
msgid "It was a little... over the top."
msgstr "조금... 지나치긴 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001ABFE9
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2B3/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc03Scene:0202C3A5
msgctxt "000FAF"
msgid "You're extremists. Did you even hear the SSNN broadcast?"
msgstr "너희는 극단주의자야. SSNN 방송은 듣기나 했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C426
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A286C1
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You've been misled by your leaders. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2B4/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene:0202C426
msgctxt "000FB0"
msgid "They have no reason to lie to us."
msgstr "그들이 우리에게 거짓말할 이유는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C425
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005E021F
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You've been misled by your leaders. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B4/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene:0202C425
msgctxt "000FB1"
msgid "Hmm. We have been cut off for some time."
msgstr "흠. 우리는 한동안 고립되어 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C37C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003980ED
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2B5/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc01Scene:0202C37C
msgctxt "000FB2"
msgid "You've been misled by your leaders. "
msgstr "넌 지도자들에게 속은 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C44A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0043EDF0
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You see violence as the only way to settle this. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2B6/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene:0202C44A
msgctxt "000FB3"
msgid "It's the most effective way."
msgstr "가장 효과적인 방법이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C449
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0050F6E6
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You see violence as the only way to settle this. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B6/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene:0202C449
msgctxt "000FB4"
msgid "I wish there was another way..."
msgstr "다른 방법이 있었으면 좋겠어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FB8994
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2B7/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Misc02Scene:0202C3BE
msgctxt "000FB5"
msgid "You see violence as the only way to settle this."
msgstr "넌 폭력을 이 일을 해결할 유일한 방법으로 보는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C437
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0014621B
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C437
msgctxt "000FB6"
msgid "Communication is useless here. The Settled Systems would never listen."
msgstr "여기서는 대화가 소용없어. 개척 성계는 절대 귀 기울이지 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C436
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007151D1
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C436
msgctxt "000FB7"
msgid "But the Settled Systems is the problem. It's not up for negotiation."
msgstr "하지만 개척 성계 자체가 문제야. 협상할 사안이 아니라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C435
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DF7E2F
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C435
msgctxt "000FB8"
msgid "That's because the Settled Systems would never listen to reason in the first place."
msgstr "애초에 개척 성계가 이성을 따르는 말을 절대 듣지 않을 테니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C433
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E5950F
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C433
msgctxt "000FB9"
msgid "True, if a situation may be resolved through communication, that's preferable to lives lost."
msgstr "맞아. 대화로 해결할 수 있는 상황이라면 목숨을 잃는 것보다 그쪽이 낫지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C432
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00887635
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C432
msgctxt "000FBA"
msgid "I can see how that may misconstrue things."
msgstr "그게 어떻게 상황을 왜곡할 수 있는지는 알겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C431
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0044EB1C
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0202C2B8/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C431
msgctxt "000FBB"
msgid "A fair point."
msgstr "타당한 지적이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C41A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0081C84C
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You've been killing innocent people. / Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C41A
msgctxt "000FBC"
msgid "The Settled Systems has brought this upon themselves."
msgstr "개척 성계가 자초한 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C419
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006659EA
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You've been killing innocent people. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C419
msgctxt "000FBD"
msgid "It's a means to an end."
msgstr "목적을 위한 수단이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C418
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DA4832
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: You've been killing innocent people. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C418
msgctxt "000FBE"
msgid "Casualties can't be helped."
msgstr "사상자는 어쩔 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C416
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0097D0E1
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You've been killing innocent people. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C416
msgctxt "000FBF"
msgid "I always imagined we'd be going up against UC Marines or Freestar Rangers. None of us expected this."
msgstr "난 우리가 식민지 연합 해병대나 자유항성 레인저와 맞서게 될 줄 알았어. 우리 중 누구도 이런 상황은 예상 못 했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C415
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003A052E
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You've been killing innocent people. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C415
msgctxt "000FC0"
msgid "The amount of innocent lives has been... alarming."
msgstr "무고한 희생자의 수가... 심상치 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C414
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001B5C56
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: You've been killing innocent people. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 0202C2B9/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C414
msgctxt "000FC1"
msgid "It's a regrettable casualty."
msgstr "유감스러운 희생이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C451
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0085C5FD
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BA/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C451
msgctxt "000FC2"
msgid "Most of your victims are ordinary citizens, not soldiers."
msgstr "너희 희생자 대부분은 군인이 아니라 평범한 시민들이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C450
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E17269
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BA/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C450
msgctxt "000FC3"
msgid "You see nothing wrong with sacrificing innocent lives."
msgstr "무고한 생명을 희생시키는 데 아무런 문제도 느끼지 않는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C44F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B198EC
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BA/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0202C44F
msgctxt "000FC4"
msgid "You've been killing innocent people."
msgstr "너희는 무고한 사람들을 죽여 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FA0FAE
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BB/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C3AF
msgctxt "000FC5"
msgid "Reasonable people are open to discussion."
msgstr "이성적인 사람이라면 대화에 열려 있는 법이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006DA0A9
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BB/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C3AE
msgctxt "000FC6"
msgid "There's been no communication between Terran and Settled Systems leaders."
msgstr "테란과 개척 성계 지도부 사이에는 아무런 소통도 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DEFE2C
#. Notes = / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C2BB/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0202C3AD
msgctxt "000FC7"
msgid "You attacked first and haven't been willing to negotiate."
msgstr "너희가 먼저 공격했고, 협상할 생각도 없었잖아."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceB01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C45B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00803C0A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0C/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C45B
msgctxt "000FCB"
msgid "Spread the word. Don't fight a misguided battle."
msgstr "소문을 퍼뜨려. 잘못된 싸움에 뛰어들지 말라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00329ED7, 00AF7459, 0070FCF8
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3DC
msgctxt "000FCC"
msgid "Either way, if they come looking for us, we'll be prepared. Thank you."
msgstr "어느 쪽이든, 그들이 우릴 찾아온다면 우린 대비하고 있겠습니다. 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00329ED7, 00AF7459, 0070FCF8
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3DC
msgctxt "000FCD"
msgid "The Terran Armada doesn't tolerate deserters, but since we're a scouting party, hopefully they'll believe we were killed in action."
msgstr "테란 함대에서는 탈영병을 용납하지 않지만, 저희는 정찰대니까 전사한 걸로 믿어 주길 바라야죠."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceA01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C393
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005CCB95
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C393
msgctxt "000FCE"
msgid "Take this opportunity to start over. "
msgstr "이 기회에 새 출발을 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FAC2E6
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3F3
msgctxt "000FCF"
msgid "It's all a means to a better end. Perhaps you're the one that needs to question your motives."
msgstr "모두 더 나은 결말을 위한 수단일 뿐이야. 오히려 네 동기를 되짚어 봐야 하는 건 너일지도 모르지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C459
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0002771F
#. Notes = SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0202C2C2/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C459
msgctxt "000FD0"
msgid "Time's up, and I think you know what that means."
msgstr "시간 끝이야. 이게 무슨 뜻인지 너도 알겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F4A9DE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3A7
msgctxt "000FD3"
msgid "Why can't you see what you're doing is wrong?"
msgstr "왜 네가 하는 일이 잘못됐다는 걸 모르는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SpeechStart01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000C46FC
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2C5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3DA
msgctxt "000FD4"
msgid "All right. But you'll fail, and when you do, this only ends one way."
msgstr "좋아. 하지만 넌 실패할 거고, 그렇게 되면 결말은 하나뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D21EF3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3C0
msgctxt "000FD5"
msgid "Please, just take a moment to see things from my perspective."
msgstr "제발, 잠깐만이라도 제 입장에서 생각해 봐요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0002230E
#. Notes = About to go into combat. Telling fellow troops to attack. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3EB
msgctxt "000FD6"
msgid "Attack!"
msgstr "공격!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DB3F93
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C8/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3D4
msgctxt "000FD7"
msgid "[Attack] Enough. Obviously, this only ends one way."
msgstr "[공격] 충분해. 분명히 결말은 하나뿐이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C457
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0018DF65
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2C9/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C457
msgctxt "000FD8"
msgid "And why would you think we're following blindly?"
msgstr "우리가 맹목적으로 따른다고 생각하는 이유가 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C456
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009425B9
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C2C9/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C456
msgctxt "000FD9"
msgid "You don't think we've already considered the other point of view? We aren't following blindly here."
msgstr "우리가 다른 관점을 이미 생각해 보지 않았다고 생각하나? 우린 맹목적으로 따르는 게 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C455
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00231443
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2C9/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C455
msgctxt "000FDA"
msgid "Hmm. I admit, I do have moments, but I've always had adequate reassurances."
msgstr "흠. 인정하지, 흔들리는 순간이 있긴 해. 하지만 언제나 충분히 안심할 만한 근거가 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C402
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A7F50D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CA/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C402
msgctxt "000FDB"
msgid "As a fellow soldier, you can't follow orders too blindly."
msgstr "같은 군인으로서, 명령을 너무 맹목적으로 따라선 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C401
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0043D0D4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CA/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C401
msgctxt "000FDC"
msgid "Please, I'd like to present you with a different perspective on your cause."
msgstr "제발, 당신들의 명분을 다른 관점에서 설명해 보고 싶습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C400
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E01847
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CA/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C400
msgctxt "000FDD"
msgid "You believe your cause is just, but you have to feel something is wrong."
msgstr "네 명분이 정의롭다고 믿겠지만, 뭔가 잘못됐다는 느낌은 들 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C378
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F89940
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C2CB/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C378
msgctxt "000FDE"
msgid "Our actions are necessary evil... for now. "
msgstr "우리의 행동은 필요악이야... 지금은."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C447
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003D2B39
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CC/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C447
msgctxt "000FDF"
msgid "You can't really believe what you're doing is right."
msgstr "네가 하는 일이 옳다고 정말 믿을 순 없잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C43C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00729963
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CD/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C43C
msgctxt "000FE0"
msgid "But the question is, for how long?"
msgstr "하지만 문제는, 그게 얼마나 오래가느냐지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C42E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00321405
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C42E
msgctxt "000FE1"
msgid "The Settled Systems is at peace, though."
msgstr "하지만 개척 성계는 평화롭잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C388
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0004D416
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CF/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C388
msgctxt "000FE2"
msgid "If that's not a Terran issued robot, and you're not a Terran, then start talking. Who are you?"
msgstr "그게 테란 지급 로봇이 아니고, 당신도 테란이 아니라면 말해. 정체가 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C391
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0016B29F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D0/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C391
msgctxt "000FE3"
msgid "Why do you think I'm a Terran?"
msgstr "내가 테란이라고 생각하는 이유가 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E7C3C2
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D1/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3B2
msgctxt "000FE4"
msgid "You found us. Now identify and report."
msgstr "우릴 찾았군. 신원을 밝히고 보고해라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EB72F7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D2/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3D2
msgctxt "000FE5"
msgid "Are you the Terran scouting party?"
msgstr "당신들이 테란 정찰대인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DEEFEE
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 0202C2D3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3E9
msgctxt "000FE6"
msgid "Hmm, I'm not buying it. Who are you and what are you doing here?"
msgstr "흠, 못 믿겠군. 넌 누구고 여기서 뭘 하고 있지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C404
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B15438
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C404
msgctxt "000FE7"
msgid "[Lie] You need to disperse and await new orders."
msgstr "[거짓말] 해산하고 새 명령을 대기하라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C423
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B6CA9E
#. Notes = Drawing weapon. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C423
msgctxt "000FE8"
msgid "Then I don't see what we have to talk about."
msgstr "그럼 우리가 더 할 얘기는 없겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C445
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 008AB39B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C445
msgctxt "000FE9"
msgid "I'm not a Terran."
msgstr "난 테란이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B3A818
#. Notes = Question / to Player Default, Face: Question
#: 0202C2D7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3E0
msgctxt "000FEA"
msgid "I don't recognize you, soldier. Who sent you?"
msgstr "처음 보는 군인이군. 누가 보냈지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C38A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A02E41
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C2E1/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C38A
msgctxt "000FEB"
msgid "I'm serious. We aren't these Terrans you're looking for. There's been a mistake."
msgstr "진심이야. 우린 당신들이 찾는 테란이 아니야. 뭔가 착오가 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceSCLeadIn01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C39D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DE55EB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E2/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C39D
msgctxt "000FEE"
msgid "Look, I know you're Terrans, but we can talk about this."
msgstr "들어 봐. 당신들이 테란인 건 알지만, 이건 대화로 풀 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FE5BD0
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0202C2E3/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3B4
msgctxt "000FEF"
msgid "Terrans? Well, we haven't seen any, but we'll sure be on the lookout now."
msgstr "테란? 글쎄, 본 적은 없지만 이제부터는 확실히 경계하겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E69039
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E4/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3CA
msgctxt "000FF0"
msgid "It's not safe here. Terrans are in this area."
msgstr "여긴 안전하지 않아. 이 지역에 테란이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_AttackResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C412
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F2E62C
#. Notes = About to go into combat. Calling to nearby allies. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0202C2E5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C412
msgctxt "000FF1"
msgid "Damn. Our cover's blown!"
msgstr "젠장. 위장이 들켰다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F3C257
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3E1
msgctxt "000FF2"
msgid "[Attack] I don't believe you."
msgstr "[공격] 못 믿겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0098CBD2, 00E1005F
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3BC
msgctxt "000FF3"
msgid "You're right. Once we're settled, well do everything we can to reach out to those like us."
msgstr "맞아. 정착하고 나면 우리 같은 사람들에게 손을 뻗기 위해 할 수 있는 모든 일을 하겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E3B987
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3EE
msgctxt "000FF4"
msgid "You need to help others like you. Get them out of the Armada."
msgstr "너희 같은 사람들을 도와야 해. 그들을 테란 함대에서 빼내."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C421
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000AF5FA, 0072366A, 00C7ACDA
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C421
msgctxt "000FF5"
msgid "Hopefully, we may be able to make up for a fraction of what we've done, once we're settled."
msgstr "정착하고 나면, 우리가 저지른 일의 일부라도 속죄할 수 있기를 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C421
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000AF5FA, 0072366A, 00C7ACDA
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C421
msgctxt "000FF6"
msgid "Thank you for letting us start over. "
msgstr "새 출발을 할 수 있게 해 줘서 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C421
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000AF5FA, 0072366A, 00C7ACDA
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C421
msgctxt "000FF7"
msgid "And I'm glad you weren't one of them."
msgstr "그리고 당신이 그들 중 하나가 아니라서 다행입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C376
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002CC94B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C376
msgctxt "000FF8"
msgid "I'm glad you all came to your senses."
msgstr "모두 정신을 차려서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FAD58A, 009EA8AF, 00DBE766
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3C6
msgctxt "000FF9"
msgid "After what's happened, we certainly don't deserve it, but we're going to do our best to make up for it one way or another."
msgstr "그동안 벌어진 일을 생각하면 우린 분명 이런 기회를 받을 자격이 없지만, 어떤 식으로든 속죄하기 위해 최선을 다하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FAD58A, 009EA8AF, 00DBE766
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3C6
msgctxt "000FFA"
msgid "Thank you for taking the time to talk and letting us start over."
msgstr "시간을 내서 대화해 주고 새 출발을 허락해 줘서 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FAD58A, 009EA8AF, 00DBE766
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3C6
msgctxt "000FFB"
msgid "A lesson we've learned well in the recent years."
msgstr "최근 몇 년 동안 뼈저리게 배운 교훈이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C42C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004518D1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2ED/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C42C
msgctxt "000FFC"
msgid "I don't think the Terran Armada knows how to tolerate anything."
msgstr "테란 함대는 무엇도 용납할 줄 모르는 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C386
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00660C54
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C386
msgctxt "000FFE"
msgid "How do I know you're not lying?"
msgstr "네가 거짓말하는 게 아니라는 걸 어떻게 알지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C399
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A01F6E, 006BE2AC, 001DDA7C
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C399
msgctxt "000FFF"
msgid "The Terran Armada doesn't have any leniency for deserters."
msgstr "테란 함대는 탈영병에게 조금의 관용도 베풀지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C399
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A01F6E, 006BE2AC, 001DDA7C
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C399
msgctxt "001000"
msgid "The moment I saw you walking up here with that robot, I thought we were lost."
msgstr "네가 저 로봇을 데리고 걸어오는 걸 본 순간, 우린 끝났다고 생각했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C399
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A01F6E, 006BE2AC, 001DDA7C
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C399
msgctxt "001001"
msgid "You... you believe me?"
msgstr "당신... 날 믿는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004150AC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F1/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3B0
msgctxt "001002"
msgid "All right, go. I believe you."
msgstr "좋아, 가. 네 말을 믿겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C443
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007A98D5, 00141146
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2EE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C443
msgctxt "001004"
msgid "Two, we're 100% human here. The bots are programmed to report signs of disloyalty. We couldn't risk it."
msgstr "둘째, 여기 있는 우리는 100% 인간이야. 로봇들은 불충성의 징후를 보고하도록 프로그래밍되어 있어. 위험을 감수할 수 없었지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C443
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007A98D5, 00141146
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2EE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C443
msgctxt "001005"
msgid "For one, if we followed protocol, we would've fired on sight."
msgstr "첫째, 우리가 규약을 따랐다면 보이는 즉시 발포했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C446
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DC386D
#. Notes = About to go into battle. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C446
msgctxt "001006"
msgid "So much for the cover. "
msgstr "위장은 여기까지군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C452
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004E5B57
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F7/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C452
msgctxt "001007"
msgid "I don't buy your cover, but I sense some truth in what you're telling me."
msgstr "네 위장은 안 믿지만, 네 말 속에 진실이 조금은 느껴져."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C40D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A01959, 0090326F
#. Notes = About to tell the truth and hoping it works in their favor. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Concerned / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F4/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C40D
msgctxt "001009"
msgid "Yes, we are a Terran scouting party, but the real reason we're out here is to escape. "
msgstr "그래, 우리는 테란 정찰대가 맞지만, 사실 여기 나온 진짜 이유는 도망치기 위해서야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C40D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A01959, 0090326F
#. Notes = About to tell the truth and hoping it works in their favor. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Concerned / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F4/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C40D
msgctxt "00100A"
msgid "All right, all right. Since we're all still alive, hear me out."
msgstr "알았어, 알았어. 아직 모두 살아 있으니 내 말 좀 들어 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B60067
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F3/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3DD
msgctxt "00100B"
msgid "[Attack] Nice story. If only I believed it."
msgstr "[공격] 그럴듯한 이야기네. 믿을 수만 있었다면 말이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C420
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005F5D08
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C420
msgctxt "00100C"
msgid "[Delta] Delta, thoughts?"
msgstr "[델타] 델타, 생각은?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006959D8
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F5/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3F1
msgctxt "00100D"
msgid "Voice analysis indicates partial truth. Initial verbal engagement  suggests uncommonly high levels of reason for Terrans."
msgstr "음성 분석 결과 일부 진실이 감지됩니다. 최초 대화 반응은 테란치고는 이례적으로 높은 수준의 이성을 시사합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C380
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AE830B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C380
msgctxt "00100E"
msgid "[Attack] I'm not buying it."
msgstr "[공격] 난 못 믿겠어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FriendlyDeltaSceneReentry03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E696D4
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3BB
msgctxt "00100F"
msgid "You come out of nowhere with a robot that wants to kill us? Who wouldn't be nervous?"
msgstr "난데없이 나타나서는 우릴 죽이려는 로봇을 데리고 왔잖아? 누가 긴장하지 않겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F27DBF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FD/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3A2
msgctxt "001010"
msgid "Delta isn't wrong."
msgstr "델타 말이 틀리진 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C38F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DF470, 00A7E7D8, 00B12A04
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C38F
msgctxt "001011"
msgid "If anyone here was a Terran, I'd suspect it was you."
msgstr "여기 누군가가 테란이라면, 난 네가 제일 수상하다고 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C38F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DF470, 00A7E7D8, 00B12A04
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C38F
msgctxt "001012"
msgid "From what I've heard, Terrans use robot troops. Does it look like there are any robots here? "
msgstr "내가 듣기로 테란은 로봇 병력을 쓴다던데. 여기에 로봇이 하나라도 보이나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C38F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DF470, 00A7E7D8, 00B12A04
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C38F
msgctxt "001013"
msgid "But there's no proof that they're right either."
msgstr "그렇다고 그들이 옳다는 증거도 없잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0098CD71, 0068865C
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0202C300/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3E7
msgctxt "001014"
msgid "Plus it's not like I haven't been in tense situations before. You never know who you'll run into on these survey jobs."
msgstr "게다가 내가 긴장되는 상황을 처음 겪는 것도 아니고. 이런 탐사 일에서는 누구를 마주칠지 알 수 없으니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0098CD71, 0068865C
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0202C300/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3E7
msgctxt "001015"
msgid "Maybe that's because it's taking every ounce of my strength to keep my composure. "
msgstr "아마 평정심을 유지하려고 온 힘을 다 쓰고 있어서 그럴 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00144EC9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3D0
msgctxt "001016"
msgid "It seems more than a coincidence that you're here."
msgstr "네가 여기 있는 게 단순한 우연 이상의 일처럼 보이는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
