#: 0202C301/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3F9
msgctxt "001017"
msgid "You seem pretty calm after having your life threatened."
msgstr "목숨을 위협받고도 꽤 침착해 보이는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C40C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D85298
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C305/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C40C
msgctxt "001018"
msgid "I get it, but it's not like lying is the only cause."
msgstr "이해는 하지만, 거짓말만이 유일한 원인은 아니잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EFB716
#. Notes = Neutral / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C303/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3B9
msgctxt "001019"
msgid "Accurate assumption."
msgstr "정확한 추정입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C43A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E927D4
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C302/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C43A
msgctxt "00101A"
msgid "This is exactly what I'm talking about."
msgstr "바로 이 말을 하는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C38E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007C119A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C306/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C38E
msgctxt "00101B"
msgid "Elevated heart rate is a good sign of lying. "
msgstr "심박수 상승은 거짓말의 유력한 징후입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0075BBF5
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C304/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3F0
msgctxt "00101C"
msgid "We don't know you, and after what your bot said, it sounds like you may be the real threat here."
msgstr "우린 당신들을 몰라. 게다가 당신네 로봇이 한 말을 보니, 여기서 진짜 위협은 당신들일 수도 있겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C42B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006BEA8E, 00CA89CB
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C307/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C42B
msgctxt "00101D"
msgid "We're not Terrans, we're just here to survey the area."
msgstr "우린 테란이 아니야. 그냥 이 지역을 조사하러 왔을 뿐이라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C42B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006BEA8E, 00CA89CB
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C307/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C42B
msgctxt "00101E"
msgid "Is that what you think?"
msgstr "그렇게 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BB9730
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C308/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3BA
msgctxt "00101F"
msgid "You don't have to worry about them, unless you really are Terran soldiers."
msgstr "정말 테란 병사가 아닌 이상 그들은 걱정하지 않아도 돼."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FriendlyDeltaSceneReentry01
