#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C43B
msgctxt "001020"
msgid "Your robot friend seems a little... anxious."
msgstr "네 로봇 친구가 좀... 불안해 보이는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008410ED
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C309/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3CF
msgctxt "001021"
msgid "Hey, there's plenty of reasons for me to be nervous here."
msgstr "이봐, 내가 여기서 긴장할 이유는 차고 넘쳐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00ADC60C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C30A/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3E6
msgctxt "001022"
msgid "Delta makes a good point."
msgstr "델타 말도 일리가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C41F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
