#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000450D7
#. Notes = Giving in after being persuaded to talk. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C310/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C398
msgctxt "001027"
msgid "Hmm. Well... "
msgstr "흠. 뭐..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009D9BA5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C311/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0202C3AB
msgctxt "001028"
msgid "If you admit to being Terrans, I'd like to discuss something with you."
msgstr "당신들이 테란이라고 인정한다면, 이야기를 나누고 싶은 게 있어."

#. List: 2
