#: 0202C318/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3F7
msgctxt "00102B"
msgid "Dammit."
msgstr "젠장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C37F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004E8DBE
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0202C31A/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C37F
msgctxt "00102C"
msgid "Oh, I can't wait to hear this."
msgstr "아, 이거 정말 기대되는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C37E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00023930
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C319/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C37E
msgctxt "00102D"
msgid "[Attack] I'm going with Delta's assessment."
msgstr "[공격] 델타의 판단을 따르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C44D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D4F8F5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C31B/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C44D
msgctxt "00102E"
msgid "Good. Terrans are misguided. This your chance to see the truth."
msgstr "좋아. 테란들은 잘못된 길을 가고 있어. 진실을 볼 챈스다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0014E599
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C31C/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3CE
msgctxt "00102F"
msgid "Okay, hold on. So the bot's exposed us. We're Terrans. But let's go back to that willingness to engage in discourse."
msgstr "좋아, 잠깐만. 로봇이 우리 정체를 까발렸네. 우린 테란이야. 그런데 대화할 의향이 있다는 얘기로 다시 돌아가 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C397
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000A62B7, 004C3FD0, 00A8DBFC
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C397
msgctxt "001030"
msgid "Processing scenarios. Recommended course of action: extermination."
msgstr "시나리오 처리 중. 권장 행동 방침: 말살."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C397
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000A62B7, 004C3FD0, 00A8DBFC
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C397
msgctxt "001031"
msgid "Counterpoint: Human behavior atypical. Lack of combat initiation. Desire to engage in discourse."
msgstr "반론: 인간 행동이 비정형적. 전투 개시 없음. 대화 참여 의사 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C397
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000A62B7, 004C3FD0, 00A8DBFC
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C397
msgctxt "001032"
msgid "Analysis: Estimated certainty of Terran encounter: 97%. Factors: location, profile, heart rate. Attitude."
msgstr "분석: 테란 조우 추정 확실도: 97%. 요인: 위치, 프로필, 심박수. 태도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009E9715
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C338/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3B5
msgctxt "001048"
msgid "All right, fine. "
msgstr "알았어, 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CE4B49
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C341/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3B8
msgctxt "001050"
msgid "Maybe your intel is wrong, or maybe you just missed them. Either way, it isn't us."
msgstr "네 정보가 틀렸거나, 그냥 그들을 놓친 걸 수도 있어. 어느 쪽이든 우린 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C44B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0009E58A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C342/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C44B
msgctxt "001051"
msgid "I was told Terrans are at this location, and you're the only ones here."
msgstr "이 위치에 테란이 있다고 들었다. 그런데 여기 있는 건 당신들뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00957C69
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C343/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3CC
msgctxt "001052"
msgid "You and me both."
msgstr "나도 마찬가지야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C39F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B30712
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C345/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C39F
msgctxt "001053"
msgid "You're still on about this?"
msgstr "아직도 그 얘기야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004BF867
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C344/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3E4
msgctxt "001054"
msgid "[Attack] I'm done trying to reason with you."
msgstr "[공격] 더는 말로 설득하지 않겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C389
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005D57EA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C348/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C389
msgctxt "001057"
msgid "Cut the crap and admit you're Terrans or this doesn't end well for any of you."
msgstr "헛소리 그만하고 테란이라고 인정해. 안 그러면 너희 모두 좋게 끝나지 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C44C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0041BB25
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C34A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C44C
msgctxt "001058"
msgid "[Delta] Delta, what's your analysis here?"
msgstr "[델타] 델타, 여기 분석은 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C428
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009D39D3
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34F/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C428
msgctxt "00105C"
msgid "Maybe I'm doing my best to remain calm. Ever think of that?"
msgstr "내가 침착하려고 최선을 다하는 중일 수도 있잖아. 그런 생각은 안 해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0077EDD1
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3C3
msgctxt "001068"
msgid "Just not in the mood to deal with strangers is all."
msgstr "그냥 낯선 사람 상대할 기분이 아닐 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002817EF
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C35A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0202C3C2
msgctxt "001069"
msgid "You're the one with a weapon out. "
msgstr "무기를 꺼내 든 건 당신 쪽이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
