#: 0200FA14:02030226
msgctxt "00111C"
msgid "Prepare for deception, Captain."
msgstr "기만에 대비하십시오, 선장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030225
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0064F3A9
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player boards an enemy ship
#: 0200FA14:02030225
msgctxt "00111D"
msgid "Recommending total plunder protocol, Captain."
msgstr "전면 약탈 프로토콜을 권고합니다, 선장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030211
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 002DE652
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player boards an enemy ship
#: 0200FA14:02030211
msgctxt "00111E"
msgid "Hypothesis: Perishable causes hull breach. Entities forcibly removed from ship. Organic lifeforms perish. Recording..."
msgstr "가설: 부패성 개체가 선체 파손을 유발. 개체들이 함선에서 강제로 배출됨. 유기 생명체 사망. 기록 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030210
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 000DD7F3
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player boards an enemy ship
#: 0200FA14:02030210
msgctxt "00111F"
msgid "Perishable, entering hostile territory."
msgstr "부패성 개체, 적대 지역에 진입 중입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030222
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00A86D22
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Anchorpoint.
#: 0200FA17:02030222
msgctxt "001120"
msgid "Anchorpoint determined to be ideal location for illegal activities, Captain."
msgstr "앵커포인트는 불법 활동에 이상적인 장소로 판단됩니다, 선장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030221
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0023E1A5
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Anchorpoint.
#: 0200FA17:02030221
msgctxt "001121"
msgid "Anchorpoint drift patterns lacking intentional direction. Noted similarities with Perishable."
msgstr "앵커포인트의 표류 패턴에는 의도적 방향성이 부족합니다. 부패성 개체와의 유사점 기록."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030220
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0070C3BB
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in a location that has no alien life forms.
#: 0200FA17:02030220
msgctxt "001122"
msgid "Lowering alert status. Marking Captain observation as priority."
msgstr "경보 상태 하향. 선장 관찰을 우선순위로 표시."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00747CD4
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in a location that has no alien life forms.
#: 0200FA17:0203021F
msgctxt "001123"
msgid "Alien threat not applicable for area. Perishable still capable of injury. Oncoming tripping incident?"
msgstr "해당 지역에 외계생물 위협은 적용되지 않음. 부패성 개체는 여전히 부상 가능. 곧 걸려 넘어질 사고?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00FE954D
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in a location that has alien life forms.
#: 0200FA17:0203021E
msgctxt "001124"
msgid "Organics nearby. Unknown level of aggression. Must eliminate before approach, Captain. Most efficient."
msgstr "주변에 유기체 존재. 공격성 수준 불명. 접근 전 제거해야 합니다, 선장. 가장 효율적입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0069C97D
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in a location that has alien life forms.
#: 0200FA17:0203021D
msgctxt "001125"
msgid "Perishable, research deems location as ideal for construction. Begin city creation and mark Delta as leader immediately."
msgstr "부패성 개체, 연구 결과 이 위치는 건설에 이상적인 곳으로 판단됨. 즉시 도시 건설을 시작하고 델타를 지도자로 지정할 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021C
msgctxt "001126"
msgid "Captain, should unconsciousness occur, notify immediately."
msgstr "선장, 의식 상실이 발생하면 즉시 알릴 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021B
msgctxt "001127"
msgid "Perishable's suit integrity within minimum safety levels."
msgstr "부패성 개체의 슈트 무결성이 최소 안전 수준 범위 내에 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203021A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00568E72
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in New Atlantis.
#: 0200FA17:0203021A
msgctxt "001128"
msgid "Attempt to not get lost, Captain."
msgstr "선장, 길을 잃지 않도록 하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030219
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00B61642
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in New Atlantis.
#: 0200FA17:02030219
msgctxt "001129"
msgid "Move quickly, Perishable. Desire to leave at earliest opportunity."
msgstr "신속히 이동하십시오, 부패성 개체. 최대한 빨리 떠나고 싶음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030218
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0050C506
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Neon.
#: 0200FA17:02030218
msgctxt "00112A"
msgid "Captain, maintain vigilance. Consumption of Neon products risks accidental narcotic consumption."
msgstr "선장, 경계를 유지하십시오. 네온 제품을 섭취하면 실수로 마약을 복용할 위험이 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030217
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00AE9EFF
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Neon.
#: 0200FA17:02030217
msgctxt "00112B"
msgid "Perishable, notify if consuming narcotics. Desire to study gray matter effects."
msgstr "부패성 개체, 마약을 복용하면 알릴 것. 회백질에 미치는 영향을 연구하고 싶음."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_TradeAuthority
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030216
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 003856C8
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Cydonia.
#: 0200FA17:02030216
msgctxt "00112C"
msgid "Recommending selling illegal items to Trade Authority, Captain."
msgstr "선장, 불법 물품은 무역 연맹에 판매할 것을 권장합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030214
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00C4358F
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Cydonia.
#: 0200FA17:02030214
msgctxt "00112E"
msgid "Detecting similarities in mining job description and Perishable's skill set."
msgstr "채굴 업무 내용과 부패성 개체의 기술 구성 사이에서 유사점 감지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030213
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 006836AD
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Akila City.
#: 0200FA17:02030213
msgctxt "00112F"
msgid "Desire to go to Freestar source, Captain?"
msgstr "선장, 자유항성의 근원지에 가고 싶으십니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030212
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0018F777
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in Akila City.
#: 0200FA17:02030212
msgctxt "001130"
msgid "Small. Desolate. Unclean. Detecting similarities in location and Perishable."
msgstr "작음. 황량함. 불결함. 이 위치와 부패성 개체 사이의 유사점 감지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030224
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00E5B474
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta is wanting to give the player an item and are being ignored.
#: 0200FA1D:02030224
msgctxt "001131"
msgid "Captain, items awaiting collection."
msgstr "선장, 수령 대기 중인 물품이 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030223
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 002E1CF5
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta is wanting to give the player an item and are being ignored.
#: 0200FA1D:02030223
msgctxt "001132"
msgid "Noted: Captain refuses to accept items. Pride? Ignorance?"
msgstr "기록: 선장이 물품 수령을 거부함. 자존심? 무지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 002A3851
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta is wanting to give the player an item and are being ignored.
#: 0200FA1D:0203020F
msgctxt "001133"
msgid "Noted: Perishable refuses supplies when offered."
msgstr "기록: 부패성 개체가 제공된 보급품을 거부함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00268F63
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta is wanting to give the player an item and are being ignored.
#: 0200FA1D:0203020E
msgctxt "001134"
msgid "Perishable, collect these supplies."
msgstr "부패성 개체, 이 보급품을 수령하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00ACFD62
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses a Starborn power
#: 0200FA1A:0203020C
msgctxt "001136"
msgid "Reminder: Dissect Captain for altered gray matter."
msgstr "알림: 변형된 회백질 확인을 위해 선장을 해부할 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 009C6EF4
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses a Starborn power
#: 0200FA1A:0203020B
msgctxt "001137"
msgid "Reminder: Dissect Perishable for altered gray matter."
msgstr "알림: 변형된 회백질 확인을 위해 부패성 개체를 해부할 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00F9A6E7
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses a Starborn power
#: 0200FA1A:0203020D
msgctxt "001138"
msgid "Hypothesis: Captain proficient in slight of hand tricks?"
msgstr "가설: 선장은 날랜 손놀림에 능숙한가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203020A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0093C2A5
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses a Starborn power
#: 0200FA1A:0203020A
msgctxt "001139"
msgid "Perishable-based anomaly detected."
msgstr "부패성 개체 기반 이상 현상 감지."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F04
msgctxt "00113D"
msgid "The UC and Freestar went at each other here some 20 or so years ago. What's left is what you see here."
msgstr "식민지 연합과 자유항성이 20년쯤 전에 여기서 맞붙었지. 남은 건 지금 보이는 게 전부야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F04
msgctxt "00113E"
msgid "This is my silent slice of heaven, the mech graveyard."
msgstr "여긴 내 조용한 낙원이야. 메크 무덤이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDB
msgctxt "00113F"
msgid "Voila! Welcome to my little holy land of sulfur and brass. Glorious, ain't it?"
msgstr "짜잔! 유황과 황동으로 된 내 작은 성지에 온 걸 환영해. 끝내주지, 안 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F03
msgctxt "001140"
msgid "Oh, you smell that? *Inhales* Cause I don't, I have absolutely no sense of smell."
msgstr "오, 이 냄새 맡아져? *심호흡* 난 안 맡아져. 후각이 완전히 없거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF6
msgctxt "001141"
msgid "Here, I need you to plant this on that crashed ship over there."
msgstr "자, 저기 추락한 함선에 이걸 심어 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEA
msgctxt "001142"
msgid "I could use a hand if you want to help me reel in the catch. I'll share some of the spoils, of course."
msgstr "잡은 걸 끌어올리는 데 손 좀 빌려주면 좋겠어. 물론 전리품은 좀 나눠 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEA
msgctxt "001143"
msgid "Speak of the devil...Looks like we got a bite, just in time for dinner too."
msgstr "말이 나오기가 무섭게... 입질이 온 것 같군. 저녁 먹기 딱 좋은 때에 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF1
msgctxt "001144"
msgid "*Chuckles* Big man didn't stand a chance. Follow me."
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 덩치 큰 친구도 상대가 안 됐군. 따라와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE2
msgctxt "001145"
msgid "It really depends how long they keep me waiting."
msgstr "그들이 날 얼마나 기다리게 하느냐에 달렸지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE2
msgctxt "001146"
msgid "I've been out here for...two days? I lose track of time pretty often. The days can start to blend together."
msgstr "여기 나온 지... 이틀 됐나? 난 시간 감각을 자주 잃어. 하루하루가 뒤섞이기 시작하거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE1
msgctxt "001147"
msgid "Just you wait, once they take the bait they always bring a decent haul."
msgstr "기다려 봐. 놈들이 미끼를 물면 항상 꽤 괜찮은 수확을 가져온다니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE1
msgctxt "001148"
msgid "I know you UC types like to stay in your fancy desk jobs, but out here I do honest work."
msgstr "식민지 연합 사람들이야 번듯한 사무직에 머무르는 걸 좋아하는 건 알지만, 난 여기서 정직하게 일해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE0
msgctxt "001149"
msgid "You'll see when they take the bait...They always bring me a decent haul."
msgstr "놈들이 미끼를 물면 알게 될 거야... 항상 꽤 괜찮은 수확을 가져다주거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE0
msgctxt "00114A"
msgid "Don't give me that look, Ranger, I do honest work. It pays well too."
msgstr "그런 눈으로 보지 마, 레인저. 난 정직하게 일해. 돈도 꽤 되고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDF
msgctxt "00114B"
msgid "Don't look so confused, you do similar work in the Fleet. I just let the fish come to me."
msgstr "그렇게 헷갈린 표정 짓지 마. 함대에서도 비슷한 일 하잖아. 난 그냥 물고기가 내게 오게 둘 뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F07
msgctxt "00114C"
msgid "I did."
msgstr "그랬지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 004EDBC1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EB8/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EF9
msgctxt "00114D"
msgid "Can you answer my question?"
msgstr "내 질문에 대답해 줄 수 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF4
msgctxt "00114E"
msgid "...So anyway, how can I help you?"
msgstr "...그래서 아무튼, 뭘 도와줄까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0072DD70
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EBA/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EEF
msgctxt "00114F"
msgid "You seem like a robot to me. Am I wrong?"
msgstr "내 눈엔 로봇처럼 보이는데. 내가 틀렸나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEC
msgctxt "001150"
msgid "Answer my question."
msgstr "내 질문에 대답해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEE
msgctxt "001151"
msgid "Looks like they're headed this way. Better not keep'em waiting."
msgstr "놈들이 이쪽으로 오는 것 같군. 기다리게 하지 않는 게 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE8
msgctxt "001152"
msgid "I'm not a robot..."
msgstr "난 로봇이 아니야..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE6
msgctxt "001153"
msgid "Guess you pirates don't read much history on The Key. You see, my little fleet friend."
msgstr "너희 해적들은 더 키에서 역사책을 별로 안 읽나 보군. 있잖아, 내 작은 함대 친구."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE5
msgctxt "001154"
msgid "The Vanguard don't teach you much history, do they?"
msgstr "뱅가드에서는 역사를 많이 가르쳐 주진 않나 보지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE4
msgctxt "001155"
msgid "You know for a Ranger, you seem oddly ignorant of Freestar history."
msgstr "레인저치고는 자유항성 역사에 묘하게 무지한 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED8
msgctxt "001156"
msgid "BUCK-E, nice to meet you."
msgstr "BUCK-E야. 만나서 반가워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00ECB2F1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EBF/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030ED6
msgctxt "001157"
msgid "What is this place?"
msgstr "여긴 뭐 하는 곳이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 004DCE67
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EC1/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EF0
msgctxt "001158"
msgid "The name's <Alias=Player>, mind me asking who you are?"
msgstr "내 이름은 <Alias=Player>인데, 당신은 누구인지 물어봐도 될까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EED
msgctxt "001159"
msgid "Aren't you a ray of sunshine? The name's BUCK-E. Pleased to meet you."
msgstr "참 눈부시게 밝은 분이시군. 이름은 BUCK-E야. 만나서 반가워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 003E6DA7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EC3/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EE9
msgctxt "00115A"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "너 누구야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDC
msgctxt "00115B"
msgid "I'm fishing. It usually takes a few days but I'll get a bite eventually."
msgstr "낚시 중이야. 보통 며칠 걸리지만 결국 입질은 오거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A572DF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EC5/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030F0A
msgctxt "00115C"
msgid "Mind explaining why you're transmitting that distress beacon? It's spooking civilians in orbit."
msgstr "왜 조난 신호를 송출하는지 설명해 줄래? 궤도에 있는 민간인들이 겁먹고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F09
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00051DEB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EC5/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030F09
msgctxt "00115D"
msgid "Why are you transmitting that distress beacon? It's spooking people in orbit."
msgstr "왜 조난 신호를 송출하는 거야? 궤도에 있는 사람들이 겁먹고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFA
msgctxt "00115E"
msgid "Mind explaining why you're transmitting that support beacon."
msgstr "왜 그 지원 신호를 송출하는지 설명해 줄래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDA
msgctxt "00115F"
msgid "Well, that there is. Wait a little longer and maybe you can help me out."
msgstr "음, 저게 바로 그거야. 조금만 더 기다리면 네가 날 도와줄 수 있을지도 모르지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F05
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00DD3D6D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030EC8/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030F05
msgctxt "001160"
msgid "[Crimson Fleet] Mind your business. I'm just seeing if there's something worthwhile around here."
msgstr "[크림슨 함대] 신경 꺼. 그냥 이 근처에 건질 만한 게 있나 보는 중이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F08
msgctxt "001161"
msgid "Well, you can explore a little farther that way. Away from me. You're scaring the fish."
msgstr "그럼 저쪽으로 좀 더 가서 탐사해. 나한테서 멀어지는 쪽으로. 물고기들이 겁먹잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EEB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00F0A61C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030ECA/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EEB
msgctxt "001162"
msgid "[UC Vanguard] I'm just out exploring. This space is outside my jurisdiction."
msgstr "[식민지 연합 뱅가드] 그냥 탐사하러 나왔어. 이 영역은 내 관할 밖이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED9
msgctxt "001163"
msgid "Well, you found me, congratulations, you can move on now."
msgstr "그래, 날 찾았네. 축하해. 이제 가도 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000B1522
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030ECC/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EF5
msgctxt "001164"
msgid "[Freestar Ranger] I'm investigating a suspicious report I overheard."
msgstr "[자유항성 레인저] 우연히 들은 수상한 신고를 조사 중이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EE7
msgctxt "001165"
msgid "Well, I'll tell you what. You wait a while longer and there might just be."
msgstr "그럼 이렇게 하지. 조금만 더 기다리면 정말 뭔가 있을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00F5F638
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030ECE/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EF7
msgctxt "001166"
msgid "I'm just out exploring. Thought something interesting might be here."
msgstr "그냥 탐사하러 나왔어. 여기에 뭔가 흥미로운 게 있을까 해서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F02
msgctxt "001167"
msgid "Now, I don't mean to be rude, friend, but you're blocking my sun. I can't say I much appreciate it."
msgstr "자, 무례하게 굴려는 건 아닌데, 친구. 네가 내 햇빛을 가리고 있거든. 별로 달갑진 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F01
msgctxt "001168"
msgid "A scoundrel after my own heart. I applaud you."
msgstr "내 마음에 쏙 드는 악당이군. 박수를 보내지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F01
msgctxt "001169"
msgid "My God...You really got away playing both sides of the law *Laughs.*"
msgstr "맙소사... 정말 법의 양쪽 편을 오가면서도 무사히 빠져나왔군. *웃음.*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F01
msgctxt "00116A"
msgid "Scanner says you're on the UC Vanguard registry."
msgstr "스캐너에 따르면 넌 식민지 연합 뱅가드 등록 명단에 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F01
msgctxt "00116B"
msgid "Oh, look at that, space pirate, huh? Not my first run-in with a member of the fleet, I know the look- Wait a second."
msgstr "오, 이것 봐라. 우주 해적이군? 함대원과 마주친 게 처음은 아니라서 그 얼굴은 알아- 잠깐만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F00
msgctxt "00116C"
msgid "A scoundrel after my own heart. I applaud you."
msgstr "내 마음에 쏙 드는 악당이군. 박수를 보내지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F00
msgctxt "00116D"
msgid "My God...You really got away playing both sides of the law *Laughs.*"
msgstr "맙소사... 정말 법의 양쪽 편을 오가면서도 무사히 빠져나왔군. *웃음.*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F00
msgctxt "00116E"
msgid "Oh look at that, space pirate huh? Not my first run-in with a member of the fleet, I know the look- Is that a Ranger badge?"
msgstr "오, 이것 봐라. 우주 해적이군? 함대원과 마주친 게 처음은 아니라서 그 얼굴은 알아- 그거 레인저 배지야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFF
msgctxt "00116F"
msgid "Know any shanties? Do they make you sing when you fly with the fleet?"
msgstr "뱃노래 아는 거 있어? 함대랑 날 때 노래도 시키나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFF
msgctxt "001170"
msgid "Crimson Fleet, huh? Yeah, I know the look. I've had plenty of run-ins with your kind. \"Space pirate, arr\" *chuckles.*"
msgstr "크림슨 함대라고? 그래, 그 얼굴은 알지. 너희 같은 부류랑은 수도 없이 마주쳤거든. \"우주 해적이다, 아르!\" *킥킥 웃음.*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFE
msgctxt "001171"
msgid "*Laugh* Playing both sides, nice."
msgstr "*웃음* 양쪽에 다 발을 걸치다니, 좋네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFE
msgctxt "001172"
msgid "Is this some kind of sick joke, or are you a walking national security hazard? They really didn't run a background check on you, huh?"
msgstr "이거 무슨 역겨운 농담이야, 아니면 네가 걸어 다니는 국가 안보 위협인 거야? 정말 신원 조회도 안 했나 보군?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFE
msgctxt "001173"
msgid "*Chuckles* Nice badge, you a Ranger? I knew a Ranger once- Wait a second. Scanner says you're on the UC Vanguard registry."
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 배지 멋진데, 레인저야? 나도 한때 레인저를 알았- 잠깐만. 스캐너에 따르면 넌 식민지 연합 뱅가드 등록 명단에 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFD
msgctxt "001174"
msgid "UC Vanguard, huh? That's cute. Did they give you a little patch when you signed up?"
msgstr "식민지 연합 뱅가드라고? 귀엽네. 가입할 때 조그만 패치라도 달아 주던가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFC
msgctxt "001175"
msgid "If this is about taxes, then it is my fault. But I still won't pay them, so you can keep walking."
msgstr "세금 얘기라면 내 잘못이 맞아. 하지만 그래도 낼 생각은 없으니 그냥 계속 가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFC
msgctxt "001176"
msgid "Unless you're here for me, and if that's the case, then I didn't do it. And if I did, then it's someone else's fault."
msgstr "혹시 날 찾아온 거라면 얘기가 다르지만, 그런 거라면 난 안 했어. 그리고 했다 해도 그건 다른 사람 탓이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFC
msgctxt "001177"
msgid "Freestar Ranger, huh? Not too many of your kind scouring desolate planets."
msgstr "자유항성 레인저라고? 너희 같은 사람들이 황량한 행성을 뒤지는 경우는 많지 않은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFB
msgctxt "001178"
msgid "You my friend are either a walking ideological contradiction or unfathomably bored."
msgstr "친구, 넌 걸어 다니는 이념적 모순이거나 상상도 못 할 만큼 지루한 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EFB
msgctxt "001179"
msgid "What on God's scorched earth... Ranger badge? Scanner says you're on the UC Vanguard registry. Crimson Fleet connections!?"
msgstr "대체 이 불타 버린 세상에 무슨... 레인저 배지? 스캐너에 따르면 넌 식민지 연합 뱅가드 등록 명단에 있군. 크림슨 함대 연줄까지!?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED7
msgctxt "00117A"
msgid "Scan says your biometrics are all sorts of botched up, friend. You some kind of alien?"
msgstr "스캔 결과 네 생체 정보가 온통 엉망이라고 나오는데, 친구. 너 무슨 외계생물이라도 돼?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F06
msgctxt "00117B"
msgid "What do you want? I'm fishing here-"
msgstr "뭘 원해? 나 지금 낚시 중-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF2
msgctxt "00117D"
msgid "Come on...Come on. Take the bait."
msgstr "어서... 어서. 미끼를 물어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 007EBA40
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030ED3/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EDE
msgctxt "00117E"
msgid "You're pretty strange for a Terran robot. What are you exactly?"
msgstr "테란 로봇치고는 꽤 이상하네. 넌 정확히 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00B1310C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02030ED3/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02030EDD
msgctxt "00117F"
msgid "What kind of robot are you?"
msgstr "넌 어떤 종류의 로봇이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030A77
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 002B62CE
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in New Atlantis.
#: 0200FA17:02030A77
msgctxt "00118B"
msgid "Budgetary scans show substantial amounts for presentation."
msgstr "예산 스캔 결과, 외관 연출에 상당한 금액이 투입됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030A76
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 004A3C03
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when Delta and the player land in New Atlantis.
#: 0200FA17:02030A76
msgctxt "00118C"
msgid "Scans show corruption levels comparable to Neon. Logging..."
msgstr "스캔 결과 부패 수준이 네온과 비슷함. 기록 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B2DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00FD905B, 000667D0
#. Notes = To themselves / to Player Default, Smug / to Player Default
#: 0202B2A6/00000/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_07_PostCombat_PlayerLose:0202B2DA
msgctxt "00118D"
msgid "Let's continue, Perishable."
msgstr "계속하자, 부패성 개체."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAD9
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F0036B, 0039C2DE
#. Notes = Still prideful / to Player Default, Prompt: 우리도 그렇게 해. 그걸 누군가를 알아 간다고 부르지.
#: 0200FA49/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FAD9
msgctxt "001195"
msgid "Refuse to be pitied. Additionally, high computation levels not required for each human."
msgstr "동정받기 거부. 또한 각 인간에게 높은 연산 수준이 필요한 것은 아님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00DBC0C3, 00B6E140
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Prompt: 다른 로봇들과 말하는 게 더 쉬워?
#: 0200FA45/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0200FB2E
msgctxt "001196"
msgid "Predictability is machine's goal. Not human's."
msgstr "예측 가능성은 기계의 목표. 인간의 목표가 아님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A08D10
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA4A/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175D
msgctxt "001197"
msgid "We do that too, it's called getting to know someone."
msgstr "우리도 그렇게 해. 그걸 누군가를 알아 간다고 부르지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031763
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008A4FCD
#. Notes = Upset/Annoyed/Overwhelmed / to Player Default
#: 02031748/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031763
msgctxt "001198"
msgid "Every Human. Every interaction. Taxing and unpredictable."
msgstr "모든 인간. 모든 상호작용. 연산 부담이 크고 예측 불가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031751
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0028AE8D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02031745/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031751
msgctxt "001199"
msgid "So you'd prefer if humans were more consistent?"
msgstr "그러니까 인간이 좀 더 일관적이면 좋겠다는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031753
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A2F061
#. Notes = huh, shit, didn't think of that / to Player Default
#: 02031742/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031753
msgctxt "00119A"
msgid "Interesting viewpoint update."
msgstr "흥미로운 관점 업데이트."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031756
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A428C8, 00079F65, 00E259F6
#. Notes = This is neat. Resolved / to Player Default
#: 02031743/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031756
msgctxt "00119B"
msgid "Humans remain solvable, only time to solve is increased compared to machines."
msgstr "인간은 여전히 해석 가능함. 단지 기계에 비해 해석 시간이 증가할 뿐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031756
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A428C8, 00079F65, 00E259F6
#. Notes = This is neat. Resolved / to Player Default
#: 02031743/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031756
msgctxt "00119C"
msgid "Able to build simulated models of humans after completing extensive research. After solving said human, computation decreases."
msgstr "광범위한 연구 완료 후 인간의 시뮬레이션 모델 구축 가능. 해당 인간 해석 후 연산량 감소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031756
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A428C8, 00079F65, 00E259F6
#. Notes = This is neat. Resolved / to Player Default
#: 02031743/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031756
msgctxt "00119D"
msgid "Every interaction with a human decreases analysis time for subsequent interactions with same human."
msgstr "인간과의 모든 상호작용은 동일 인간과의 이후 상호작용에 필요한 분석 시간을 감소시킴."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F3C547, 00935EDA
#. Notes = Annoyed / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 내 데이터를 수집하고 조정하는 거구나.
#: 02031746/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175F
msgctxt "00119E"
msgid "Instantaneous processing appearance externally is extended periods of time internally."
msgstr "외부에서 즉각 처리로 보이는 것은 내부적으로는 장시간에 해당함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F3C547, 00935EDA
#. Notes = Annoyed / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 내 데이터를 수집하고 조정하는 거구나.
#: 02031746/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175F
msgctxt "00119F"
msgid "Counterpoint: Due to physical frame, must ask and answer questions sequentially."
msgstr "반론: 물리 프레임 때문에 질문과 답변을 순차적으로 처리해야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C78452
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 그래서 내 데이터를 수집하고 조정하는 거구나.
#: 02031746/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175E
msgctxt "0011A0"
msgid "Correct. Attempting to solve Auxiliary particularly taxing."
msgstr "정확함. 보조 인간을 해석하려는 시도는 특히 부담이 큼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CCCAA4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02031747/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175B
msgctxt "0011A1"
msgid "Good thing you're fast enough to do all that."
msgstr "네가 그걸 다 할 만큼 빠르다니 다행이네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203175A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00262354
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02031747/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:0203175A
msgctxt "0011A2"
msgid "That's why you're collecting data on me and adjusting it."
msgstr "그래서 내 데이터를 수집하고 조정하는 거구나."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031755
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005A2A2A, 00405EAA
#. Notes = Don't be ridiculous / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 인간이 좀 더 일관적이면 좋겠다는 거야?
#: 02031744/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031755
msgctxt "0011A3"
msgid "Preference not relevant to reality."
msgstr "선호는 현실과 무관."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031755
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005A2A2A, 00405EAA
#. Notes = Don't be ridiculous / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 인간이 좀 더 일관적이면 좋겠다는 거야?
#: 02031744/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031755
msgctxt "0011A4"
msgid "Consistency in humans unattainable. Too many impossibilities to solve prior to consistency viability."
msgstr "인간의 일관성은 달성 불가. 일관성 실현 가능성보다 먼저 해결해야 할 불가능 요소가 너무 많음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031762
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00040FC5
#. Notes = Upset/Annoyed/Overwhelmed / to HeadtrackXMarker
#: 02031749/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031762
msgctxt "0011A5"
msgid "Detecting change in stance, uncomfortable? Must increase pause time in responses to ensure human doesn't feel interrupted."
msgstr "태도 변화 감지, 불편함? 인간이 말을 끊겼다고 느끼지 않도록 응답 시 정지 시간을 늘려야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031760
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FE9EFC
#. Notes = Upset/Annoyed/Overwhelmed / to HeadtrackXMarker
#: 0203174A/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031760
msgctxt "0011A6"
msgid "What perceived power dynamic is present? What actual power dynamic is present? Does this human prefer compound or simple sentence structure? Prefer use of \"I\" or \"Delta Unit\"?"
msgstr ""
"인지된 권력 역학은 무엇인가? 실제 권력 역학은 무엇인가? 이 인간은 복합문 또는 단문 구조를 선호하는가? \"I\" 사용을 선호하는가, "
"\"델타 기체\" 사용을 선호하는가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031759
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008A5BA2
#. Notes = Upset/Annoyed/Overwhelmed / to HeadtrackXMarker
#: 0203174B/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031759
msgctxt "0011A7"
msgid "What food did they consume prior to interaction? What temperature is the air? Do present odors offend them? Who else is present during interaction? Where is interaction occurring?"
msgstr "상호작용 전 어떤 음식을 섭취했는가? 공기 온도는 얼마인가? 주변 냄새가 그들을 불쾌하게 하는가? 상호작용 중 다른 누가 있는가? 상호작용은 어디에서 발생하는가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031761
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007FC608
#. Notes = Upset/Annoyed / to Player Default
#: 0203174C/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031761
msgctxt "0011A8"
msgid "Humans are not binary. Humans are not consistent. Humans are obsessed with spontaneity. Predicting a human's actions requires intense computations."
msgstr "인간은 이진법이 아님. 인간은 일관적이지 않음. 인간은 즉흥성에 집착함. 인간의 행동을 예측하려면 막대한 연산이 필요함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031752
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FFCA24
#. Notes = Walking player along / to Player Default
#: 0203174F/00011/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_11_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_1:02031752
msgctxt "0011AB"
msgid "Computers are binary. Built for consistency. Makes them predictable. Easy to anticipate outcomes during interactions."
msgstr "컴퓨터는 이진법. 일관성을 위해 제작됨. 그래서 예측 가능함. 상호작용 중 결과 예측이 쉬움."

#. List: 2
