#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B891D8, 0089A2A6, 0067A15A
#. Notes = Frustrated / Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 본성 대 양육 연구가 도움이 됐어?, Frustrated / to Player Default
#: 0200FA4D/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AA6
