#: 0200FA4D/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AA6
msgctxt "0011BB"
msgid "Negative. Resulted in inconclusive answers."
msgstr "부정. 결론 없는 답변으로 귀결됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
