#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA4E/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AAA
msgctxt "0011BC"
msgid "Did the \"Nature vs. Nurture\" research help?"
msgstr "본성 대 양육 연구가 도움이 됐어?"

