#: 02031A9A/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AB4
msgctxt "0011C9"
msgid "Interesting counterpoint..."
msgstr "흥미로운 반론..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AA9
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E01F61
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02031A9B/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AA9
msgctxt "0011CA"
msgid "It doesn't matter where it came from. You think it, it's your opinion."
msgstr "어디서 나왔는지는 중요하지 않아. 네가 그렇게 생각하면 그건 네 의견이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AA5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0011B418
#. Notes = They've thought about this a lot / to Player Default
#: 02031A9E/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AA5
msgctxt "0011CD"
msgid "Terran Robots protect Terrans. Protection drive programmed into model. Opinions regarding disposition: Unknown. Ability to form novel opinion: Improbable."
msgstr "테란 로봇은 테란을 보호함. 보호 동기가 모델에 프로그래밍됨. 배치 성향에 대한 의견: 알 수 없음. 새로운 의견 형성 능력: 가능성 낮음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AA8
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005D3436
#. Notes = They've thought about this a lot / to Player Default
#: 02031A9F/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AA8
msgctxt "0011CE"
msgid "Second example: Robots lacking \"personalities.\" Terran Robots."
msgstr "두 번째 예시: \"개성\"이 없는 로봇. 테란 로봇."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A4CB74
#. Notes = They've thought about this a lot / to Player Default
#: 02031AA1/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AAE
msgctxt "0011D0"
msgid "Unable to deduce true thoughts of machine. Counterpoint: If thoughts present, robotic or human origin?"
msgstr "기계의 진정한 생각 추론 불가. 반론: 생각이 존재한다면 기계적 기원인가, 인간적 기원인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02031AAC
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00AEDA51
#. Notes = They've thought about this a lot / to Player Default
#: 02031AA3/00012/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_12_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_2:02031AAC
msgctxt "0011D2"
msgid "Example: Vasco. Programmed to respect humans. Vasco's opinion of assigned disposition: Unknown. Opinion originating from programming or choice: Unknown."
msgstr "예시: 바스코. 인간을 존중하도록 프로그래밍됨. 부여된 성향에 대한 바스코의 의견: 알 수 없음. 의견의 기원이 프로그래밍인지 선택인지: 알 수 없음."

