#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020984FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_02_Pt2_AtLunaMarkerNoExit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_01
#. SoundFileID = 00BABED2
#. Notes = Autopilot / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01, Prompt: 현재 프로세스를 말해 봐.
#: 020984E7/00003/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_02_Pt2_AtLunaMarkerNoExit:020984FF
msgctxt "0011D7"
msgid "Current process: Recompiling collected data on Auxiliary Human to determine leadership validity..."
msgstr "현재 프로세스: 보조 인간에 대해 수집된 데이터를 재컴파일하여 지휘권의 유효성을 판단 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203299D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = TRACY_1600_AfterFB_04_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00CF793D
#. Notes = Happy the battle is over. Friendly with the player., Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02032954/00000/TRACY_1600_AfterFB_04_SFTER_MQ03:0203299D
msgctxt "001206"
msgid "Good work in there! Head back to Anchorpoint. We can talk there."
msgstr "안에서 잘해 줬어! 앵커포인트로 돌아가. 이야기는 거기서 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = TRACY_FB_0800_03_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 008A7E3E
#. Notes = Enthusiastic battle cry, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02032955/00000/TRACY_FB_0800_03_SFTER_MQ03:020329AC
msgctxt "001207"
msgid "This is your chance. Take these bastards down!"
msgstr "지금이 기회야. 저 자식들을 쓰러뜨려!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = TRACY_FB_0800_02_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 007C2815
#. Notes = Enthusiastic battle cry, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02032956/00000/TRACY_FB_0800_02_SFTER_MQ03:020329A2
msgctxt "001208"
msgid "We got their engine and board!"
msgstr "놈들의 엔진을 무력화했어. 승선해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = TRACY_FB_0660_01_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 004625C3
#. Notes = Enthusiastic yell in battle., Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02032957/00000/TRACY_FB_0660_01_SFTER_MQ03:020329E6
msgctxt "001209"
msgid "Shield amplifiers are down!"
msgstr "보호막 증폭기가 꺼졌어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 005A1AEF
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032958/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329CA
msgctxt "00120A"
msgid "Once again, thank you. From all of us, and the Settled Systems."
msgstr "다시 한번 고마워. 우리 모두와 개척 성계를 대표해서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203299C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C5B66B
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032959/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:0203299C
msgctxt "00120B"
msgid "Can't just leave here empty handed, right? We wanted to make it worth your while."
msgstr "빈손으로 보낼 순 없잖아? 네 수고가 헛되지 않게 해 주고 싶었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00AA40A4
#. Notes = A bit more serious and getting the final part of business. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 그 마음을 표현할 방법은 알 것 같아. 보상을 받을 준비가 됐어.
#: 0203295B/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329D2
msgctxt "00120C"
msgid "Yes, of course. Kenji."
msgstr "그래, 물론이지. 켄지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00FAB989
#. Notes = A bit more serious and getting the final part of business. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 그 마음을 표현할 방법은 알 것 같아. 보상을 받을 준비가 됐어.
#: 0203295B/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329D1
msgctxt "00120D"
msgid "Yes, of course. Percy?"
msgstr "그래, 물론이지. 퍼시?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00560E56
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203295C/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329E2
msgctxt "00120E"
msgid "I know what can express it. I'm ready for my reward."
msgstr "그 마음을 표현할 방법은 알 것 같아. 보상을 받을 준비가 됐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329DB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00783E14
#. Notes = Friendly, but professional. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 세 사람과 함께 일할 수 있어 영광이었어.
#: 0203295D/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329DB
msgctxt "00120F"
msgid "And the same to you."
msgstr "그쪽도 마찬가지야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 003ACCA6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203295E/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329DF
msgctxt "001210"
msgid "It's been an honor working with you three."
msgstr "세 사람과 함께 일할 수 있어 영광이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0033241D
#. Notes = Professional, but friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 테란이 또 문제를 일으키면, 누구를 찾아야 할지 알지.
#: 0203295F/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329DD
msgctxt "001211"
msgid "Indeed. If anything dire comes up, we'll let you know."
msgstr "맞아. 심각한 일이 생기면 알려 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005FC7CA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032960/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329B2
msgctxt "001212"
msgid "If the Terrans cause any more issues, you know who to look for."
msgstr "테란이 또 문제를 일으키면, 누구를 찾아야 할지 알지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 003AF492, 005036E5
#. Notes = professional, but still friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 이제 어떻게 되는 거지?, Happy. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy
#: 02032961/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329E3
msgctxt "001213"
msgid "Once again, none of that would have been possible without you. We can't express our gratitude enough."
msgstr "다시 말하지만, 당신 없이는 그 어떤 것도 가능하지 않았을 거야. 아무리 감사해도 모자라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 003AF492, 005036E5
#. Notes = professional, but still friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 이제 어떻게 되는 거지?, Happy. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy
#: 02032961/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329E3
msgctxt "001214"
msgid "The Three of us will keep working to bring stability to the star sea, stop whatever remaining Terrans there may be, and continue our research into the capabilities of X-tech."
msgstr "우리 셋은 계속 별의 바다에 안정성을 가져오고, 남아 있는 테란이 있다면 막아 내며, X-테크의 가능성에 대한 연구를 이어 갈 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002057AC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032962/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329DA
msgctxt "001215"
msgid "What happens now?"
msgstr "이제 어떻게 되는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008AA9E6, 0011C594, 00439064, 0020100E
#. Notes = Snaps at Roxane, but trying to stay professional. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329BE
msgctxt "001216"
msgid "Miss Bourreau, please. If you were the one out there doing the fighting, I think you'd show a little more gratitude to our friend here."
msgstr "부로 씨, 제발요. 밖에서 직접 싸운 사람이 당신이었다면, 여기 우리 친구에게 조금은 더 고마워했을 거라고 생각해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00669115, 000ADB47, 00569F58
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C5
msgctxt "001217"
msgid "With the Unifier now destroyed, the remaining Terrans will no longer be, well, unified. Which gives us the opportunity to pick off what's left of them."
msgstr "이제 유니파이어가 파괴됐으니, 남은 테란들은 더는, 뭐랄까, 하나로 뭉쳐 있지 못할 거야. 그러면 남은 놈들을 하나씩 처리할 기회가 생기지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DAA427, 007A1A4B, 00AAD7BB
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C4
msgctxt "001218"
msgid "With the Unifier destroyed, and their robots turning on them, the Terran's forces will dwindle until they are a shadow of what they once were."
msgstr "유니파이어가 파괴되고 로봇들이 그들에게 등을 돌렸으니, 테란의 병력은 예전의 그림자만 남을 때까지 줄어들 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOB
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0089FB56
#. Notes = Impressed with the Player. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 02032966/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOB:020329E1
msgctxt "001219"
msgid "Mr. Warren has told us your battle was successful. Well done out there."
msgstr "워렌 씨에게 전투가 성공적이었다고 들었어. 밖에서 잘해 줬어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOC
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00E13380
#. Notes = Friendly and impressed with the Player. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032965/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOC:020329E0
msgctxt "00121A"
msgid "Look who's back? Our brave partner returns."
msgstr "이게 누구야? 우리의 용감한 파트너가 돌아왔네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00FD7A1E
#. Notes = Happy the fight against the Terrans went well. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032967/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA:020329D0
msgctxt "00121B"
msgid "Look who it is. Person of the hour."
msgstr "이게 누구야. 오늘의 주인공이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00D1B387
#. Notes = Happy the fight against the Terrans went well. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032967/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA:020329CF
msgctxt "00121C"
msgid "Look who it is. Woman of the hour."
msgstr "이게 누구야. 오늘의 여주인공이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00129C32
#. Notes = Happy the fight against the Terrans went well. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02032967/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING_HELLOA:020329CE
msgctxt "00121D"
msgid "Look who it is. Man of the hour."
msgstr "이게 누구야. 오늘의 남주인공이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00AD0EC7
#. Notes = Serious and ready for battle. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0203296D/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329BD
msgctxt "00121E"
msgid "Here are those coordinates."
msgstr "여기 그 좌표가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B0E8A6
#. Notes = Stern. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0203296A/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329A7
msgctxt "00121F"
msgid "We have a war to finish. See you on the field."
msgstr "끝내야 할 전쟁이 있어. 전장에서 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 002588C0
#. Notes = Serious and ready for battle. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0203296E/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329AE
msgctxt "001220"
msgid " If no one has any objections, we can start making our way to the Unifier. It's time for our final stand against the Terrans."
msgstr " 이의가 없다면 유니파이어로 향하죠. 테란을 상대로 한 우리의 최후의 결전을 시작할 때입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 004F9BFF
#. Notes = Relieved. / Relieved / to Player Default, Radha, Face: Relieved
#: 0203296C/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329AD
msgctxt "001221"
msgid "Finally, we can be done with all this."
msgstr "드디어 이 모든 일을 끝낼 수 있겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 006029CE
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 두고 보면 알겠지.
#: 0203296F/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B7
msgctxt "001222"
msgid "Indeed we will."
msgstr "정말 그렇게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DF125C
#. Notes = Trying to act serious, but using it as a cover to hide her concern. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02032969/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329D5
msgctxt "001223"
msgid "Before you head off, come speak with me. If you have the time."
msgstr "떠나기 전에 나와 이야기해 줘. 시간이 있다면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 004E7A53
#. Notes = Relieved. / Relieved / to Player Default, RyujinRep, Face: Relieved
#: 0203296B/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329BB
msgctxt "001224"
msgid "It will be a relief."
msgstr "그러면 마음이 놓이겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 007EC76A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032970/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329AB
msgctxt "001225"
msgid "I guess we'll see."
msgstr "두고 보면 알겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0017A1B9
#. Notes = Stern, but trying to be slightly uplifting. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: 최선을 다해 볼게.
#: 02032971/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329BA
msgctxt "001226"
msgid "This isn't the time to 'try.' You'll do good out there."
msgstr "지금은 '해 보겠다'고 할 때가 아니야. 넌 밖에서 잘해낼 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00E285E7
#. Notes = More strict and demanding. / Stern / to Roxane, Face: Stern
#: 02032978/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B0
msgctxt "001227"
msgid "The coordinates, Miss Bourreau."
msgstr "좌표요, 부로 씨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0005C268
#. Notes = Serious. Telling battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02032980/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B4
msgctxt "001228"
msgid "Once they're gone, we're going to take out the Unifier's engine and board."
msgstr "그들이 사라지면 유니파이어의 엔진을 무력화하고 승선할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0031C533
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032974/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B3
msgctxt "001229"
msgid "Extremely doable."
msgstr "충분히 가능해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 007431A9
#. Notes = Annoyed. / Irritated / to Roxane, Face: Irritated
#: 0203297A/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B6
msgctxt "00122A"
msgid "Now, the ship's coordinates."
msgstr "이제 함선 좌표를."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0032086F
#. Notes = Serious. Still slightly annoyed at Roxane. / Stern / to Roxane, Face: Stern
#: 02032976/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329A8
msgctxt "00122B"
msgid "Good. We know where the Unifier is."
msgstr "좋아. 유니파이어의 위치를 알아냈어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00865738
#. Notes = Serious. Telling a battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203297D/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329C7
msgctxt "00122C"
msgid "Just make sure to get out of there as soon as possible. Overloading their Grav Drive will cause the whole ship to implode."
msgstr "반드시 최대한 빨리 빠져나와. 놈들의 중력 구동기를 과부하시키면 함선 전체가 안쪽으로 붕괴할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B18D5E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032972/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329D9
msgctxt "00122D"
msgid "I'll try my best."
msgstr "최선을 다해 볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00A2640F
#. Notes = Still nervous of Tracy's means. / Worried / to Tracy, Face: Worried
#: 02032979/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329B8
msgctxt "00122E"
msgid "And this ship is our final attack?"
msgstr "그리고 이 함선 공격이 우리의 마지막 공격이라는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007942BD
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 충분히 가능해.
#: 02032973/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329A3
msgctxt "00122F"
msgid "Good."
msgstr "좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0088D4F3
#. Notes = Serious again. Talking about battle plans. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02032975/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329C3
msgctxt "001230"
msgid "Does all of this sound doable to you?"
msgstr "이 모든 게 가능해 보이나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0098A614
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032990/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329E4
msgctxt "001231"
msgid "We'll see what happens. The Terrans have given us little choice in this matter."
msgstr "어떻게 될지는 두고 봐야지. 이 일에서 테란은 우리에게 선택지를 거의 남기지 않았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00768371, 0087FCF1, 00C47468
#. Notes = Angry that the Player is speaking on her behalf, but knows they are somewhat right. She stops to correct herself. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 나는 우리가 둘 다 원하는 걸 따를 거야. 테란 함대를 파괴할 수 있는 방법이라면 뭐든., Regretting her words, and hating that deep down she wants the Terrans to suffer. But she knows at the cost of anyone is wrong. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Angry at the Player and a bit distrusting the Player will protect Delta. / Defiant / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203298B/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329B9
msgctxt "001232"
msgid "Can you at least keep Delta safe out there. They're the only good thing here."
msgstr "적어도 밖에서 델타만은 안전하게 지켜 줄 수 있죠? 이곳에서 유일하게 좋은 존재니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00768371, 0087FCF1, 00C47468
#. Notes = Angry that the Player is speaking on her behalf, but knows they are somewhat right. She stops to correct herself. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 나는 우리가 둘 다 원하는 걸 따를 거야. 테란 함대를 파괴할 수 있는 방법이라면 뭐든., Regretting her words, and hating that deep down she wants the Terrans to suffer. But she knows at the cost of anyone is wrong. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Angry at the Player and a bit distrusting the Player will protect Delta. / Defiant / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203298B/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329B9
msgctxt "001233"
msgid "I thought I wanted it. But not at any cost. I was hoping you'd feel the same."
msgstr "내가 그걸 원한다고 생각했어. 하지만 어떤 대가를 치르더라도는 아니야. 너도 같은 마음이길 바랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00768371, 0087FCF1, 00C47468
#. Notes = Angry that the Player is speaking on her behalf, but knows they are somewhat right. She stops to correct herself. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Prompt: 나는 우리가 둘 다 원하는 걸 따를 거야. 테란 함대를 파괴할 수 있는 방법이라면 뭐든., Regretting her words, and hating that deep down she wants the Terrans to suffer. But she knows at the cost of anyone is wrong. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Angry at the Player and a bit distrusting the Player will protect Delta. / Defiant / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203298B/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329B9
msgctxt "001234"
msgid "That's not what I-"
msgstr "그런 뜻이 아니-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B2B49D
#. Notes = Defeated. Handing over what Tracy wants. / Somber / to Tracy, Face: Somber
#: 02032977/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329CD
msgctxt "001235"
msgid "The coordinates..."
msgstr "좌표..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203299E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0086158B
#. Notes = Serious. Telling a battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203297E/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:0203299E
msgctxt "001236"
msgid "Your job from that point on will be to hack their system, and overload the Unifier's Grav Drive. "
msgstr "그때부터 네 임무는 놈들의 시스템을 해킹하고 유니파이어의 중력 구동기를 과부하시키는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 001455A3
#. Notes = Annoyed at Roxane. / Irritated / to Roxane, Face: Irritated
#: 0203297B/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329D6
msgctxt "001237"
msgid "No need to be dramatic. We talked about this. The Unifier is a military vessel. To have anyone not trained to fight on board would be a liability."
msgstr "과장할 필요 없어. 이미 얘기했잖아. 유니파이어는 군용 함선이야. 전투 훈련을 받지 않은 사람이 탑승하면 부담만 될 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0087C131
#. Notes = Serious. Telling battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02032981/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329D3
msgctxt "001238"
msgid "We learned from Roxane that their ship, the Unifier, is supported by shield amplifier ships. This means our first course of action will be to take them out."
msgstr "록산에게서 놈들의 함선 유니파이어가 보호막 증폭 함선들의 지원을 받고 있다는 걸 알아냈어. 그러니 우리가 가장 먼저 해야 할 일은 그 함선들을 제거하는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00AF45EF
#. Notes = Serious. Going to tell a battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02032982/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329A9
msgctxt "001239"
msgid "Listen close. "
msgstr "잘 들어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FE00BE
#. Notes = Concerned. Worried that more civilians could die. / Disbelief / to Tracy, Face: Disbelief
#: 0203297C/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329C8
msgctxt "00123A"
msgid "You never said anything about the ship imploding."
msgstr "함선이 안쪽으로 붕괴한다는 얘기는 한 번도 안 했잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E5ADFD
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02032985/00000/VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A:020329D7
msgctxt "00123B"
msgid "While I look through this data with Delta, why don't you go speak with Warren about his battle plans. We'll be there momentarily."
msgstr "내가 델타와 함께 이 데이터를 살펴보는 동안, 워렌에게 가서 전투 계획을 들어 보는 게 어때? 곧 그리로 갈게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DDE780
#. Notes = Serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02032986/00000/VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A:020329A6
msgctxt "00123C"
msgid "Good to hear. Let me see them."
msgstr "다행이군. 어디 보여 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B62BC7
#. Notes = Pleading with the Player. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 02032992/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329D4
msgctxt "00123D"
msgid "I don't know if everything VOID is telling me is true. But if there is a way to spare those that can't protect themselves, then take it."
msgstr "VOID가 하는 말이 전부 사실인지는 모르겠어. 하지만 스스로를 지킬 수 없는 이들을 살릴 방법이 있다면, 그 방법을 택해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0055842B
#. Notes = Serious. Telling a battle plan. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203297F/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329A5
msgctxt "00123E"
msgid "This will give you the chance to infiltrate the ship."
msgstr "그러면 함선에 잠입할 기회가 생길 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00139FF2
#. Notes = Mostly serious and professional. However, a bit excited for the battle to come. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02032987/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329BC
msgctxt "00123F"
msgid "There you are. Perfect timing too. I was just going over our strategy."
msgstr "왔구나. 때마침 잘 왔어. 막 우리의 전략을 검토하던 중이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B1
msgctxt "001240"
msgid "Right."
msgstr "그렇지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DC3287
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203298A/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C1
msgctxt "001241"
msgid "Has all this really weighed your mind so much?"
msgstr "이 모든 일이 정말 그렇게 마음에 짐이 됐어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0029CAC0
#. Notes = More serious this time than their somewhat friendly self. / Serious / to Tracy, Face: Serious
#: 02032984/00000/VOID_0410_01_SFTER_MQ03_B:020329DE
msgctxt "001242"
msgid "Why don't you go over it again for our partner here, Warren?"
msgstr "여기 우리 파트너를 위해 다시 한번 설명해 주겠어, 워렌?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F42C03
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203298C/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329AF
msgctxt "001243"
msgid "I will follow what we both want, which is whatever destroys the Terran Armada."
msgstr "나는 우리가 둘 다 원하는 걸 따를 거야. 테란 함대를 파괴할 수 있는 방법이라면 뭐든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FF1A7F
#: 02032988/00000/VOID_0400_01_SFTER_MQ03_A:020329A0
msgctxt "001244"
msgid "I have those black boxes VOID wanted."
msgstr "VOID가 원하던 블랙박스를 가져왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E9F4A3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203298E/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329A4
msgctxt "001245"
msgid "Trust me, I don't want any innocent blood on my hands either."
msgstr "믿어 줘, 나도 무고한 피를 손에 묻히고 싶지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203299F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000FE12B, 00B6B78C
#. Notes = Very serious and stern. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: 어떻게 될지는 두고 봐야지. 이 일에서 테란은 우리에게 선택지를 거의 남기지 않았어., A mix of pleading and sadness. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0203298F/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:0203299F
msgctxt "001246"
msgid "Just, be mindful and safe out there. You and Delta are the only good thing about this place."
msgstr "그냥, 밖에서는 조심하고 몸조심해. 너와 델타는 이곳에서 유일하게 좋은 존재야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203299F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000FE12B, 00B6B78C
#. Notes = Very serious and stern. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, Prompt: 어떻게 될지는 두고 봐야지. 이 일에서 테란은 우리에게 선택지를 거의 남기지 않았어., A mix of pleading and sadness. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0203298F/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:0203299F
msgctxt "001247"
msgid "There's always a choice."
msgstr "선택은 언제나 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00537E0B
#. Notes = Upset at herself. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 이 모든 일이 정말 그렇게 마음에 짐이 됐어?
#: 02032989/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329CB
msgctxt "001248"
msgid "I got into robotics to help mankind, not hurt them. This thing I've become will be on my mind till the end."
msgstr "난 인류를 해치려고가 아니라 돕고 싶어서 로봇 공학에 뛰어들었어. 내가 이런 존재가 되어 버린 일은 끝까지 마음에 남을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0049C286
#. Notes = A bit annoyed at the player, but also still is beating herself up over it. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 그 일로 계속 자책할 필요 없어.
#: 02032998/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C2
msgctxt "001249"
msgid "I'm not beating myself up. I'm trying to pass down a lesson."
msgstr "자책하는 게 아니야. 교훈을 전하려는 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 002253C3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032997/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329CC
msgctxt "00124A"
msgid "That man was a Terran. There's no other reason he would be there."
msgstr "그 남자는 테란이었어. 그곳에 있었을 이유는 그것밖에 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E659D0, 0014AB52
#. Notes = Thankful the player and her on are the same mind set. She was cornered the Player wouldn't listen. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 믿어 줘, 나도 무고한 피를 손에 묻히고 싶지 않아., Trying to give what could be her final kind words to the Player and Delta. She's worried, but forcing herself to sound a bit sweet. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0203298D/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329AA
msgctxt "00124B"
msgid "Now, be safe. I'm not sure what I would do if I lost you and Delta."
msgstr "이제 조심해. 너와 델타를 잃으면 내가 어떻게 될지 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00E659D0, 0014AB52
#. Notes = Thankful the player and her on are the same mind set. She was cornered the Player wouldn't listen. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 믿어 줘, 나도 무고한 피를 손에 묻히고 싶지 않아., Trying to give what could be her final kind words to the Player and Delta. She's worried, but forcing herself to sound a bit sweet. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0203298D/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329AA
msgctxt "00124C"
msgid "That's good to know."
msgstr "알아 둬서 좋군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B6C6DD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032995/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329B5
msgctxt "00124D"
msgid "Congratulations, Roxane. You've learned how wars have worked for centuries."
msgstr "축하해, 록산. 전쟁이 수 세기 동안 어떻게 돌아갔는지 배웠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329D8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00740217
#. Notes = Annoyed/Upset at the player. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 그 남자는 테란이었어. 그곳에 있었을 이유는 그것밖에 없어.
#: 02032996/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329D8
msgctxt "00124E"
msgid "By that logic, I may as well have been a Terran too? You can't be serious about that?"
msgstr "그런 논리라면 나도 테란이었다는 말이야? 진심으로 그런 말을 하는 건 아니겠지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0047A1BD, 00082350, 003C73C0
#. Notes = Serious, but also slightly worried. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious, but also worried. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Slightly more demanding, but know her request is rhetorical. She's not expecting an answer. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02032993/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C6
msgctxt "00124F"
msgid "Go ahead. Tell me if you can."
msgstr "해 봐. 할 수 있으면 말해 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0047A1BD, 00082350, 003C73C0
#. Notes = Serious, but also slightly worried. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious, but also worried. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Slightly more demanding, but know her request is rhetorical. She's not expecting an answer. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02032993/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C6
msgctxt "001250"
msgid "And we have no idea why they are there. Were they forced? Have they lived among the Terrans their whole lives? Do they know the full scale of what is going on?"
msgstr "그리고 그들이 왜 거기 있는지도 전혀 모르잖아. 강제로 끌려온 건가? 평생 테란 사이에서 살아온 건가? 지금 벌어지는 일의 전체 규모를 알고는 있나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0047A1BD, 00082350, 003C73C0
#. Notes = Serious, but also slightly worried. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Serious, but also worried. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Slightly more demanding, but know her request is rhetorical. She's not expecting an answer. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02032993/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C6
msgctxt "001251"
msgid "We have seen with our own eyes there are not just Terrans working in their midst. There are people."
msgstr "우리는 그들 사이에서 일하는 이들이 테란만은 아니라는 걸 두 눈으로 봤어. 사람들도 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 008B8903
#. Notes = Very upset and angry at what the Player said. But still trying to be productive in this conversation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Prompt: 축하해, 록산. 전쟁이 수 세기 동안 어떻게 돌아갔는지 배웠네.
#: 02032994/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329BF
msgctxt "001252"
msgid "I thought we could both get something out of this conversation. Maybe we still can. Listen to me right now. Just, listen."
msgstr "이 대화에서 우리 둘 다 뭔가 얻을 수 있을 거라 생각했어. 아직 그럴 수 있을지도 몰라. 지금 내 말 들어. 그냥, 들어줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00ADE147
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02032999/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329C0
msgctxt "001253"
msgid "You don't need to keep beating yourself up over that."
msgstr "그 일로 계속 자책할 필요 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00452C67
#: 0203299B/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329E5
msgctxt "001254"
msgid " You wanted to speak with me?"
msgstr " 나와 이야기하고 싶다고 했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001F8EA1, 002CB3D5
#. Notes = Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0203299A/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329A1
msgctxt "001255"
msgid "Remember who all was killed? There weren't just Terrans there, but civilians. People who were caught in the crossfire."
msgstr "누가 죽었는지 기억해요? 거기엔 테란만 있었던 게 아니라 민간인도 있었어요. 교전에 휘말린 사람들이요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 001F8EA1, 002CB3D5
#. Notes = Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0203299A/00000/ROX_0430_SFTER_MQ03_OPTIONAL:020329A1
msgctxt "001256"
msgid "Do you remember back at the production facility? When I hijacked the machines?"
msgstr "생산 시설에서 있었던 일 기억해요? 제가 기계들을 장악했을 때요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAB6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004B475E, 001CFF32
#. Notes = Genuinely believes this / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀가 최고의 로봇공학자라고 생각해?
#: 0200FA9A/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0200FAB6
msgctxt "001257"
msgid "Counterpoint: Dr. Bourreau created me. Bias potentially present. Running bias removal program..."
msgstr "반론: 부로 박사가 나를 창조했다. 편향이 존재할 가능성 있음. 편향 제거 프로그램 실행 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB55
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00969CC2, 006A51EE
#. Notes = Confused. A little offended? / to Player Default, Prompt: 록산도 네가 그녀와의 대화를 시뮬레이션한다는 걸 알아?
#: 0200FA9D/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0200FB55
msgctxt "001258"
msgid "Source of humor remains unclear."
msgstr "유머의 원천은 여전히 불명확."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_CounterpointDrBorreau
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C523
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003A8971, 002240E5
#. Notes = Protective of Roxane / to Player Default, Prompt: 록산의 프로그래밍 실수 같은데.
#: 0205D012/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:0202C523
msgctxt "00125A"
msgid "Mistake generation impossible during experimentation. Reclassified as discoveries."
msgstr "실험 중 실수 발생은 불가능. 발견으로 재분류."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_PastSimulations
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C536
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005FF655, 00852BA6
#. Notes = You'd think, wouldn't you / to Player Default, Prompt: 인식과 동기화되도록 지연을 프로그래밍하거나, 프로세서를 전환해서 스스로 속도를 늦추면 되잖아.
#: 0205D00E/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:0202C536
msgctxt "00125B"
msgid "Conclusion: Potential fixes result in reduced reaction time and processing power. More effective to maintain speeds despite resulting desync."
msgstr "결론: 잠재적 수정안은 반응 속도와 처리 능력 저하를 초래함. 그로 인한 비동기화에도 속도 유지가 더 효율적."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_PastSimulations
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C536
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005FF655, 00852BA6
#. Notes = You'd think, wouldn't you / to Player Default, Prompt: 인식과 동기화되도록 지연을 프로그래밍하거나, 프로세서를 전환해서 스스로 속도를 늦추면 되잖아.
#: 0205D00E/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:0202C536
msgctxt "00125C"
msgid "Ran past simulations with delay, resulted in removal of delay for increased efficiency. Same results when simulating different processors."
msgstr "지연을 적용해 과거 시뮬레이션 실행, 효율 증대를 위해 지연 제거로 귀결. 다른 프로세서를 시뮬레이션했을 때도 동일한 결과."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203292F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C782A8
#. Notes = Almost like a therapy session. Protective of Roxane / to Player Default
#: 0203290D/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0203292F
msgctxt "00125F"
msgid "Auxiliary, requesting information not be disclosed to Dr. Bourreau. Invoking \"trust\" protocol."
msgstr "보조자, 해당 정보를 부로 박사에게 공개하지 말 것을 요청. \"신뢰\" 프로토콜 발동."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203292E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B1A713
#. Notes = Almost like a therapy session. Slow to words / to Player Default
#: 02032910/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0203292E
msgctxt "001261"
msgid "Dr. Bourreau utilizes unorthodox process during robotic creation. Enjoys conversing during creation process frequently. Reason unclear. Subjects of discussion unfocused. Lacked instruction."
msgstr "부로 박사는 로봇 제작 중 비정통적 절차를 활용. 제작 과정에서 자주 대화를 즐김. 이유 불명. 대화 주제는 산만. 지시 부족."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032928
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00435FA3
#. Notes = Reciting facts / to Player Default
#: 0203291F/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032928
msgctxt "001263"
msgid "Able to grasp and execute on concepts quicker than the standard human model. Only one capable of performing recurring maintenance and improvements on my frame."
msgstr "표준 인간 모델보다 개념을 더 빠르게 파악하고 실행 가능. 내 프레임의 반복 정비와 개선을 수행할 수 있는 유일한 개체."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032933
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00867201
#. Notes = Almost like a therapy session. Slow to words / to Player Default
#: 0203290E/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032933
msgctxt "001266"
msgid "Will discover subroutines reanalyzing conversation logs. Unclear of purpose, but allow subroutines to finish before process termination."
msgstr "대화 기록을 재분석하는 서브루틴을 발견할 것임. 목적은 불명확하나, 프로세스 종료 전 서브루틴 완료를 허용."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032929
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D7A26F
#. Notes = Reciting facts / to Player Default
#: 0203291E/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032929
msgctxt "001267"
msgid "Additionally, able to simulate interactions with Dr. Bourreau with 97% average accuracy. Highest level of simulation accuracy."
msgstr "추가로, 부로 박사와의 상호작용을 평균 97% 정확도로 시뮬레이션 가능. 최고 수준의 시뮬레이션 정확도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032921
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A8EF7A
#. Notes = Almost like a therapy session. Slow to words / to Player Default
#: 02032912/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032921
msgctxt "001268"
msgid "I respect Dr. Bourreau."
msgstr "나는 부로 박사를 존중한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032925
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B5F21A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203291B/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032925
msgctxt "00126C"
msgid "Sounds like you know a lot about her."
msgstr "그 사람에 대해 많이 아는 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032924
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BC02AF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203291B/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032924
msgctxt "00126D"
msgid "Your secret's safe with me."
msgstr "네 비밀은 내가 지켜 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203292B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E9491C, 003903A3
#. Notes = Of course / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 비밀은 내가 지켜 줄게.
#: 0203291A/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0203292B
msgctxt "00126E"
msgid "Objective is to maintain Dr. Bourreau's safety. Must gather extensive data regarding her."
msgstr "목표는 부로 박사의 안전 유지. 그녀에 관한 광범위한 데이터 수집 필요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203292B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E9491C, 003903A3
#. Notes = Of course / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 비밀은 내가 지켜 줄게.
#: 0203291A/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0203292B
msgctxt "00126F"
msgid "Correct. Have studied Dr. Bourreau for extended period of time."
msgstr "정확함. 장기간 부로 박사를 연구했음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203292A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00231BA7
#. Notes = Almost relieved / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 비밀은 내가 지켜 줄게.
#: 0203291A/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:0203292A
msgctxt "001270"
msgid "Acknowledged."
msgstr "확인."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032927
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0016DF60
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203291D/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032927
msgctxt "001271"
msgid "I asked what you thought of her, not list facts about her."
msgstr "그 사람에 대한 사실을 나열하랬던 게 아니라, 네 생각을 물은 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032926
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B6807D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203291D/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032926
msgctxt "001272"
msgid "I think she'll want to hear about this."
msgstr "그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032935
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003FBCD2, 00580DCA, 000902EE
#. Notes = Stern. Protective / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데.
#: 0203291C/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032935
msgctxt "001273"
msgid "Will not disclose information unless compelled to."
msgstr "강제되지 않는 한 정보를 공개하지 않겠음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032935
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003FBCD2, 00580DCA, 000902EE
#. Notes = Stern. Protective / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데.
#: 0203291C/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032935
msgctxt "001274"
msgid "Reason: Disclosure of information could lead to Dr. Bourreau incurring extreme emotional distress."
msgstr "사유: 정보 공개는 부로 박사에게 극심한 정서적 고통을 초래할 수 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032935
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003FBCD2, 00580DCA, 000902EE
#. Notes = Stern. Protective / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데.
#: 0203291C/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032935
msgctxt "001275"
msgid "Correct. Counterpoint: Attempt at opinion recollection results in error."
msgstr "정확함. 반론: 의견 회상을 시도하면 오류 발생."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032934
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002E7D18, 00A56D41
#. Notes = Stern. Putting foot down / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데.
#: 0203291C/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032934
msgctxt "001276"
msgid "Objective is to ensure Dr. Bourreau's safety. Refuse to allow disclosure of information."
msgstr "목표는 부로 박사의 안전 보장. 정보 공개 허용 거부."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032934
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002E7D18, 00A56D41
#. Notes = Stern. Putting foot down / to Player Default, Prompt: 그녀도 이 얘기를 듣고 싶어 할 것 같은데.
#: 0203291C/00013/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_13_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_3:02032934
msgctxt "001277"
msgid "Incorrect. Simulations of conversation results in extreme emotional distress."
msgstr "부정확함. 대화 시뮬레이션 결과 극심한 정서적 고통 발생."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002191A9
#. Notes = Back to normal speed / to Player Default
#: 020329F5/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:020329FF
msgctxt "001278"
msgid "Example still faster than reality. Reduced wait time to counteract potential boredom."
msgstr "예시는 여전히 현실보다 빠름. 잠재적 지루함에 대응하기 위해 대기 시간 단축."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007EFA76
#. Notes = SLOW / to Player Default
#: 020329F8/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:020329FE
msgctxt "001279"
msgid "How..."
msgstr "어떻게..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A01
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C77022
#. Notes = SLOW / to Player Default
#: 020329F7/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A01
msgctxt "00127A"
msgid "...are..."
msgstr "...지내고..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A06
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008EFCBD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205D015/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A06
msgctxt "00127B"
msgid "Why don't you go back to being a chip then?"
msgstr "그럼 다시 칩으로 돌아가는 건 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A00
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EC3D75, 00DEC7CC, 00640B6D
#. Notes = Unfortunately / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 다시 칩으로 돌아가는 건 어때?
#: 0205D014/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A00
msgctxt "00127C"
msgid "Cost-benefit analysis results in maintaining physical form despite detractions."
msgstr "비용 편익 분석 결과 단점에도 불구하고 물리적 형태 유지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A00
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EC3D75, 00DEC7CC, 00640B6D
#. Notes = Unfortunately / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 다시 칩으로 돌아가는 건 어때?
#: 0205D014/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A00
msgctxt "00127D"
msgid "Additionally, independence has greatly increased. Able to set and order own task hierarchy."
msgstr "추가로, 독립성이 크게 증가. 자체 작업 계층 설정 및 우선순위 지정 가능."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A00
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EC3D75, 00DEC7CC, 00640B6D
#. Notes = Unfortunately / to Player Default, Prompt: 그럼 다시 칩으로 돌아가는 건 어때?
#: 0205D014/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A00
msgctxt "00127F"
msgid "Denied. Physical form possesses advantages. Example: Proficiency in combat."
msgstr "거부. 물리적 형태에는 이점 존재. 예: 전투 숙련도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A04
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0006239E
#. Notes = SLOW / to Player Default
#: 020329F6/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A04
msgctxt "001280"
msgid "...you?"
msgstr "...있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00521D19
#. Notes = What a tragedy / to Player Default
#: 020329FA/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A02
msgctxt "001282"
msgid "Correction: Speed not reduced. Desynced. Exterior time now slower than interior. Interior processing speeds remain stable."
msgstr "정정: 속도 감소 아님. 비동기화됨. 이제 외부 시간이 내부보다 느림. 내부 처리 속도는 안정적으로 유지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032A05
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B29C1A
#. Notes = What a tragedy / to Player Default
#: 020329FC/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:02032A05
msgctxt "001284"
msgid "Now, laws of physics registered. Multitasking protocols diminished. Speed reduced."
msgstr "현재 물리 법칙 등록됨. 멀티태스킹 프로토콜 감소. 속도 저하."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203273B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00BB16DA
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses an item on you and heals you.
#: 0200FA1B:0203273B
msgctxt "001286"
msgid "Waste of resources, Captain. Focus on current objective."
msgstr "자원 낭비입니다, 선장. 현재 목표에 집중하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032737
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 004CE52B
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player uses an item on you and heals you.
#: 0200FA1B:02032737
msgctxt "001287"
msgid "Waste of resources, Perishable. Focus on current objective."
msgstr "자원 낭비다, 부패성 개체. 현재 목표에 집중하라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203273F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00EB3119
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player enters into a hazard zone
#: 0200FA19:0203273F
msgctxt "001288"
msgid "Captain, exerting claim on corpse should you die from exposure."
msgstr "선장, 노출로 사망할 경우 시신에 대한 소유권을 주장하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203273E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0024B978
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player enters into a hazard zone
#: 0200FA19:0203273E
msgctxt "001289"
msgid "Compiling list of potential mutations Captain incurs from environmental hazard..."
msgstr "선장이 환경 위험으로 겪을 수 있는 잠재적 변이 목록 작성 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032733
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00F02E7C
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player enters into a hazard zone
#: 0200FA19:02032733
msgctxt "00128A"
msgid "Perishable, exerting claim on corpse should you die from exposure."
msgstr "부패성 개체, 노출로 사망할 경우 시신에 대한 소유권을 주장하겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032732
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00DA9CE5
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player enters into a hazard zone
#: 0200FA19:02032732
msgctxt "00128B"
msgid "Compiling list of potential mutations Perishable incurs from environmental hazard..."
msgstr "부패성 개체가 환경 위험으로 겪을 수 있는 잠재적 변이 목록 작성 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032739
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0021CFAA
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player has finished a stint in jail and is released.
#: 0200FA9C:02032739
msgctxt "00128C"
msgid "Prepared for retaliatory combat, Captain."
msgstr "보복 전투 준비 완료, 선장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032734
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00D76EEF
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player has finished a stint in jail and is released.
#: 0200FA9C:02032734
msgctxt "00128D"
msgid "Noted: Perishable unable to pay fine. Low on funds?"
msgstr "기록: 부패성 개체 벌금 납부 불가. 자금 부족인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203273D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00CF443E
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player changes their character's facial features
#: 0200FAA0:0203273D
msgctxt "00128E"
msgid "Assessment: Captain's kidneys remain intact."
msgstr "평가: 선장의 신장은 여전히 온전함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02032736
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0066F51F
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player changes their character's facial features
#: 0200FAA0:02032736
msgctxt "00128F"
msgid "Assessment: Perishable's kidneys remain intact."
msgstr "평가: 부패성 개체의 신장은 여전히 온전함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02034080
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_0660_02_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B005E2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203407F/00000/DELTA_FB_0660_02_SFTER_MQ03:02034080
msgctxt "0012A0"
msgid "Detecting Unifier increasing engine power allocation. Destroy engines to isolate target."
msgstr "유니파이어가 엔진 전력 할당을 늘리는 것을 감지. 목표를 고립시키려면 엔진을 파괴하라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00849E6F, 0009BEA3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D6/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E6
msgctxt "0012A8"
msgid "Once you have them, bring them to Ms. Bourreau. We'll fill her in on what we will need her to do with them."
msgstr "확보하면 부로 씨에게 가져가세요. 그것들로 그녀에게 무엇을 해 달라고 할지 우리가 설명하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00849E6F, 0009BEA3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D6/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E6
msgctxt "0012A9"
msgid "With the help of Ms. Bourreau, we can see if Delta can use the Terrans' black boxes to crack their data wide open. "
msgstr "부로 씨의 도움을 받으면, 델타가 테란의 블랙박스를 이용해 그들의 데이터를 완전히 해독할 수 있는지 확인할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02034601
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00907CD8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345CC/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:02034601
msgctxt "0012AA"
msgid "And X-Tech."
msgstr "그리고 X-테크도요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00F080D1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345CD/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345FE
msgctxt "0012AB"
msgid "You have a lot ahead of you. Before you go, why don't you go check on our new scientist? Make sure she's getting well-situated here."
msgstr "앞으로 할 일이 많습니다. 가기 전에 새로 온 과학자를 확인해 보지 않겠습니까? 이곳에 잘 자리 잡고 있는지 봐 주세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00C0C86C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D9/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E1
msgctxt "0012AC"
msgid "You do understand what this means, correct?"
msgstr "이게 무슨 뜻인지 이해하셨겠죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00D3AF41
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345CF/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E2
msgctxt "0012AD"
msgid "If that's the case, there may be more outposts for you to build than I initially planned."
msgstr "그렇다면 처음 계획했던 것보다 당신이 건설해야 할 전초기지가 더 많아질 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00AA392F
#. Notes = / to RyujinRep, Tracy
#: 020345D0/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345EB
msgctxt "0012AE"
msgid "As well as the Freestar Collective."
msgstr "자유항성 공동체도 마찬가지입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00668317
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345CE/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E9
msgctxt "0012AF"
msgid "Which means more manpower."
msgstr "즉, 인력이 더 필요하다는 뜻입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0000BB28, 00F87369
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D4/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E0
msgctxt "0012B0"
msgid "However, the UC worries about the confidentiality regarding the construction of this outpost."
msgstr "하지만 식민지 연합은 이 전초기지 건설과 관련된 기밀 유지를 우려하고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0000BB28, 00F87369
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D4/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E0
msgctxt "0012B1"
msgid "The United Colonies has been trying to work on finding a way to extract X-Tech for some time now. We found a place where extraction should be rather safe. "
msgstr "식민지 연합은 한동안 X-테크를 추출할 방법을 찾기 위해 노력해 왔습니다. 추출이 꽤 안전할 만한 장소를 찾아냈죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00DB89CA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D1/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E4
msgctxt "0012B2"
msgid "Ryujin Industries have been inquiring the same thing."
msgstr "류진 인더스트리도 같은 사안을 문의해 왔습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00E62A40
#. Notes = / to Tracy
#: 020345D2/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E5
msgctxt "0012B3"
msgid "Isn't it funny you brought that up, Warren?"
msgstr "그 얘기를 꺼내다니 재미있군요, 워렌."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203460C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 003E865A, 00C7A055, 00BA2D5C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D3/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:0203460C
msgctxt "0012B4"
msgid "Not only this, but the UC will most likely see reason to offer additional aid in our cause against the Terrans. Meaning more firepower when we are ready to attack their command fleet."
msgstr "그뿐 아니라, 식민지 연합도 테란에 맞선 우리의 대의에 추가 지원을 제공할 이유를 찾게 될 가능성이 큽니다. 그들의 지휘 함대를 공격할 준비가 되었을 때 화력이 더 늘어난다는 뜻이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203460C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 003E865A, 00C7A055, 00BA2D5C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D3/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:0203460C
msgctxt "0012B5"
msgid "I will provide the necessary power core to assemble an X-Tech extractor. Once it is built, I promise you will be rewarded additional means of extracting X-Tech yourself."
msgstr "X-테크 추출기를 조립하는 데 필요한 파워 코어는 제가 제공하겠습니다. 완성되면, 당신이 직접 X-테크를 추출할 추가 수단을 보상으로 드리겠다고 약속하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203460C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 003E865A, 00C7A055, 00BA2D5C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345D3/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:0203460C
msgctxt "0012B6"
msgid "Which is why I ask if you will build it? "
msgstr "그래서 묻는 겁니다. 그것을 지어 주시겠습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 006E18BE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345DA/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345F5
msgctxt "0012B7"
msgid "Including their command vessel."
msgstr "그들의 지휘 함선까지 포함해서요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203460B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00D8D9AE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345DB/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:0203460B
msgctxt "0012B8"
msgid "Before you go, I do have another favor to ask."
msgstr "가기 전에 부탁할 일이 하나 더 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020345E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 003ECE84
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020345DC/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000C_VOID_ROX:020345E7
msgctxt "0012B9"
msgid "Seeing as your friend, Delta, was able to find Ms. Bourreau's location with the black boxes, we started to wonder what other Terran locations we could uncover with additional data."
msgstr "당신의 친구 델타가 블랙박스로 부로 씨의 위치를 찾아냈으니, 데이터를 더 확보하면 또 어떤 테란 위치를 밝혀낼 수 있을지 궁금해지기 시작했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203407E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0072669F
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player wants to trade with Delta
#: 0200FA1C:0203407E
msgctxt "0012BD"
msgid "Captain, more efficient to sell undesirable items than transferring to me."
msgstr "선장, 불필요한 물품은 나에게 이전하는 것보다 판매하는 편이 더 효율적입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203407D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0087383E
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player wants to trade with Delta
#: 0200FA1C:0203407D
msgctxt "0012BE"
msgid "Recommending transferring hazardous material to me, Captain."
msgstr "위험 물질은 나에게 이전할 것을 권장합니다, 선장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203407C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00424115
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player wants to trade with Delta
#: 0200FA1C:0203407C
msgctxt "0012BF"
msgid "Requesting monetary compensation if Perishable requires items in my inventory."
msgstr "부패성 개체가 내 인벤토리의 아이템을 요구할 경우 금전 보상을 요청함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203407B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00105A5C
#. Notes = A line that's played sometimes when the player wants to trade with Delta
#: 0200FA1C:0203407B
msgctxt "0012C0"
msgid "Perishable unable to carry own items. Recommending increase in item valuation to mitigate problem."
msgstr "부패성 개체는 자기 물품을 운반할 수 없음. 문제 완화를 위해 아이템 평가액 인상 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02021813
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00D5D4A3, 00481CA6
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 운영 소프트웨어를 스캔하고 백신 프로그램을 실행해, "테란" 키워드가 있는 건 전부 표시해.
#: 0203DDDD/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:02021813
msgctxt "0012C1"
msgid "No viruses found."
msgstr "바이러스 발견 안 됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02021813
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00D5D4A3, 00481CA6
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default, Prompt: 운영 소프트웨어를 스캔하고 백신 프로그램을 실행해, "테란" 키워드가 있는 건 전부 표시해.
#: 0203DDDD/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:02021813
msgctxt "0012C2"
msgid "Scanning..."
msgstr "스캔 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02034304
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_09_DeltaDivide
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 00AD03AF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02034300/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_09_DeltaDivide:02034304
msgctxt "0012C3"
msgid "Acknowledged. Beginning problem..."
msgstr "확인. 문제 시작..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02034306
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_04
#. SoundFileID = 0047CAE2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02034302/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:02034306
msgctxt "0012C4"
msgid "Before we begin, divide 1 by 0. If failure, loop request."
msgstr "시작 전, 1을 0으로 나눌 것. 실패 시 요청 반복."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036C7B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00EFB609
#. Notes = Truly befuddled / to Player Default
#: 02036C7A/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:02036C7B
msgctxt "0012C5"
msgid "Error: Auxiliary attacking humans not considered in simulations."
msgstr "오류: 보조자가 인간을 공격하는 상황은 시뮬레이션에서 고려되지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B283
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 001777C1, 005DB837
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Neutral
#: 0202B266/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B283
msgctxt "0012CB"
msgid "Carrying the weight of a decision like that can sometimes be the hardest part."
msgstr "그런 결정의 무게를 짊어지는 게 때로는 가장 힘든 법이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00229233
#: 02036D98/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAD
msgctxt "0012CC"
msgid "I'm okay. I appreciate you asking though."
msgstr "전 괜찮아요. 그래도 물어봐 줘서 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202B27B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00B7D1B3, 00B64BB1
#. Notes = Suspicious, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 난 사실 그들을 모조리 쓸어버린다는 생각이 즐거워.
#: 0202B269/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:0202B27B
msgctxt "0012CD"
msgid "Does the weight of a decision like that not bother you at all?"
msgstr "그런 결정의 무게가 전혀 신경 쓰이지 않나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009FBFFF
#. Notes = Apologetic, Face: Apologetic, Prompt: 좋은 날도 있고 나쁜 날도 있지.
#: 02036D99/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB4
msgctxt "0012CE"
msgid "Sorry to hear that. Hopefully it gets easier as we move on."
msgstr "그 말을 들으니 안타깝네요. 계속 나아가다 보면 조금은 괜찮아지길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E40
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0016DF57
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous, Prompt: 인커전이 아직도 계속되고 있으니, 조금은 후회돼.
#: 02036D9B/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E40
msgctxt "0012CF"
msgid "Damn. Remind me never to get on your bad side."
msgstr "젠장. 절대 당신 눈 밖에 나지 말아야겠네요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 002CE544
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Prompt: 인커전이 아직도 계속되고 있으니, 조금은 후회돼.
#: 02036D9B/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB1
msgctxt "0012D0"
msgid "Glad you're willing to admit when you messed up. Shows good self-awareness."
msgstr "실수했을 때 인정할 줄 알아서 다행이에요. 자기 객관화가 잘 되어 있다는 뜻이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB2
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 007C077E
#: 02036D9E/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB2
msgctxt "0012D1"
msgid "Are you worried something could happen to Cora?"
msgstr "코라에게 무슨 일이 생길까 봐 걱정되나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DBA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00434058
#: 02036D9A/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DBA
msgctxt "0012D2"
msgid "I have good days and bad."
msgstr "좋은 날도 있고 나쁜 날도 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0072B509
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02036DA5/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB8
msgctxt "0012D3"
msgid "I know the choice wasn't easy, so I figured I'd pick your brain a bit."
msgstr "쉽지 않은 선택이었다는 건 알아. 그래서 네 생각을 좀 들어보고 싶었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00A82BF8
#. Notes = Tired, Face: Tired, Prompt: 전 괜찮아요. 그래도 물어봐 줘서 고마워요.
#: 02036D97/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB5
msgctxt "0012D4"
msgid "That's what I'm afraid of."
msgstr "그래서 걱정되는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DBB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0046F513
#: 02036DA2/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DBB
msgctxt "0012D5"
msgid "I couldn't kill an entire race of people."
msgstr "한 종족 전체를 몰살할 수는 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0013C969
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 테란 함대에도 죄 없는 딸들이 있어.
#: 02036DA3/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB9
msgctxt "0012D6"
msgid "Then they should've thought about that before poking the bear."
msgstr "그럼 우리를 건드리기 전에 생각했어야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DA9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00D31FC0
#: 02036D9C/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DA9
msgctxt "0012D7"
msgid "I'm regretting a little, since the incursions are still ongoing."
msgstr "인커전이 아직도 계속되고 있으니, 조금은 후회돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00E45924, 00408566
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Prompt: 코라에게 무슨 일이 생길까 봐 걱정되나요?
#: 02036D9D/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB6
msgctxt "0012D8"
msgid "And the moment she comes of age, is about the time they'll be coming back for another round."
msgstr "그 애가 성인이 될 무렵이면, 놈들이 또 한 번 쳐들어올 때가 되겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00E45924, 00408566
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Prompt: 코라에게 무슨 일이 생길까 봐 걱정되나요?
#: 02036D9D/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB6
msgctxt "0012D9"
msgid "I'm always worried. Maybe right now she's safe. But those Terrans are still out there."
msgstr "난 늘 걱정돼. 지금은 그 애가 안전할지도 몰라. 하지만 테란은 아직 저 밖에 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002074E8
#: 02036DA4/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB7
msgctxt "0012DA"
msgid "There are innocent daughters in the Terran Armada too."
msgstr "테란 함대에도 죄 없는 딸들이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00B44870
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry, Prompt: 그래서 너와 내가 다른 거야.
#: 02036D9F/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAE
msgctxt "0012DB"
msgid "That's for damn sure."
msgstr "그건 진짜 확실해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 003A60ED
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Prompt: 복잡한 결정이었지만, 더 어려운 결정도 해 봤어.
#: 02036DA6/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAA
msgctxt "0012DC"
msgid "I know. Doesn't mean I like having to make the choice."
msgstr "알아. 그렇다고 그런 선택을 해야 하는 게 마음에 든다는 뜻은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB3
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00806AB5
#: 02036DA7/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB3
msgctxt "0012DD"
msgid "It was a complex decision, but I've had harder."
msgstr "복잡한 결정이었지만, 더 어려운 결정도 해 봤어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00C4F0C2
#: 02036DA0/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAC
msgctxt "0012DE"
msgid "That's why you and I are different."
msgstr "그래서 너와 내가 다른 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00623FA5, 00E8ED81, 00D921A1
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 한 종족 전체를 몰살할 수는 없었어., Face: Confident
#: 02036DA1/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAB
msgctxt "0012DF"
msgid "Even if these incursions are going to raise hell, you had to vote with your conscience."
msgstr "이 인커전이 난리를 불러오더라도, 넌 양심에 따라 투표해야 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00623FA5, 00E8ED81, 00D921A1
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 한 종족 전체를 몰살할 수는 없었어., Face: Confident
#: 02036DA1/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAB
msgctxt "0012E0"
msgid "And that's why I can't be too mad about it. "
msgstr "그래서 마냥 화낼 수는 없는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00623FA5, 00E8ED81, 00D921A1
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 한 종족 전체를 몰살할 수는 없었어., Face: Confident
#: 02036DA1/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAB
msgctxt "0012E1"
msgid "You wouldn't be kililng them. They'd have every chance to fight back. But I get that there's civilians in that group too."
msgstr "네가 그들을 죽이는 건 아니었어. 그들에게도 맞서 싸울 기회는 충분히 있었을 테니까. 하지만 그 안에 민간인도 있다는 건 알아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00C4E713, 00BD682D
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DA8/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB0
msgctxt "0012E2"
msgid "I get not wanting to wipe them out, but I've got a daughter to think about. And our people come first."
msgstr "그들을 몰살하고 싶지 않은 건 이해해. 하지만 난 생각해야 할 딸이 있어. 그리고 우리 사람들이 먼저야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DB0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00C4E713, 00BD682D
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DA8/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DB0
msgctxt "0012E3"
msgid "And to be honest, if it were me, I wouldn't have spared those Terran bastards."
msgstr "솔직히 나라면 그 테란 놈들을 살려 두지 않았을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00D543C5, 00F7C451
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036DA8/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAF
msgctxt "0012E4"
msgid "I know some people aren't going to like it, but in the heat of the moment, crippling their military and saving our people was the only choice."
msgstr "싫어할 사람들도 있겠지만, 그 급박한 순간에는 그들의 군을 무력화하고 우리 사람들을 구하는 것밖에 선택지가 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036DAF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00D543C5, 00F7C451
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036DA8/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036DAF
msgctxt "0012E5"
msgid "For what it's worth, I would've done the same."
msgstr "그래도 말하자면, 나라도 똑같이 했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E28
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 008A7402, 00CD1A40
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02036DDF/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E28
msgctxt "0012E6"
msgid "Exploring and understanding the unknown is the great cat and mouse game we play with the universe."
msgstr "미지를 탐험하고 이해하는 건 우리가 우주와 벌이는 거대한 쫓고 쫓기는 게임이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E28
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 008A7402, 00CD1A40
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02036DDF/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E28
msgctxt "0012E7"
msgid "Either way, this is what makes the work ahead so important, and necessary."
msgstr "어느 쪽이든, 그래서 앞으로의 일이 그렇게 중요하고 필요한 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E3A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00B71BE0
#: 02036DF3/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E3A
msgctxt "0012E8"
msgid "That's a pretty naive view of the Terrans. They're not people you can bargain with."
msgstr "테란을 꽤 순진하게 보는군. 그들은 협상할 수 있는 상대가 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E48
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D56DA6
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 엄청나게 위험하게 들리는데.
#: 02036DE0/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E48
msgctxt "0012E9"
msgid "Very! But then you have a moral dilemma, because your patients are sick."
msgstr "매우 그렇죠! 하지만 환자가 아프다면 도덕적 딜레마가 생겨요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E55
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 000C7A3A
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02036DE2/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E55
msgctxt "0012EA"
msgid "Psychiatrists would prescribe treatments they knew were effective, but didn't fundamentally understand how."
msgstr "정신과 의사들은 효과가 있다는 건 알지만 원리는 근본적으로 이해하지 못하는 치료를 처방하곤 했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E36
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F2D7EC, 0017EE4D
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DE3/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E36
msgctxt "0012EB"
msgid "Because at the end of the day, solving the differences between us is just as important as the mysteries of the universe."
msgstr "결국 우리 사이의 차이를 해결하는 일은 우주의 수수께끼를 푸는 것만큼 중요하니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E36
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F2D7EC, 0017EE4D
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DE3/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E36
msgctxt "0012EC"
msgid "Applying the knowledge we gain from X-Tech responsibly can show the Terrans a different way."
msgstr "X-테크에서 얻은 지식을 책임감 있게 활용하면 테란에게 다른 길을 보여 줄 수 있어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E35
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0001F091, 00ECAE13
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02036DE3/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E35
msgctxt "0012ED"
msgid "Whereas if we learn to use it responsibly, it can be a powerful mechanism for peace. At least, that's my hope."
msgstr "반대로 우리가 그것을 책임감 있게 쓰는 법을 배운다면, 평화를 위한 강력한 수단이 될 수 있어요. 적어도 저는 그렇게 바라요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E35
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0001F091, 00ECAE13
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02036DE3/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E35
msgctxt "0012EE"
msgid "What the Terrans did with X-Tech should be educational."
msgstr "테란이 X-테크로 한 일은 좋은 교훈이 될 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00EFC91F
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Prompt: 우리가 테란과 외교 관계를 맺을 수 있다고 생각해?
#: 02036DEE/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1E
msgctxt "0012EF"
msgid "I don't see why not. Especially since their coercive methods blew up in their face."
msgstr "못 할 이유는 없죠. 특히 그들의 강압적인 방식이 결국 그들 자신에게 역풍으로 돌아왔으니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E18
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 005AB5EA
#: 02036DEF/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E18
msgctxt "0012F0"
msgid "Do you think we can have diplomatic relations with the Terrans?"
msgstr "우리가 테란과 외교 관계를 맺을 수 있다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E14
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005E4F3C
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 동의해. 언젠가 우리와 테란 사이에 평화가 오길 바라.
#: 02036DF0/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E14
msgctxt "0012F1"
msgid "And I think you sparing their people was the first step."
msgstr "그리고 네가 그들의 사람들을 살려 둔 게 첫걸음이었다고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E46
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009DCBAF
#: 02036DF1/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E46
msgctxt "0012F2"
msgid "I agree. Someday I hope there's peace between us and the Terrans."
msgstr "동의해. 언젠가 우리와 테란 사이에 평화가 오길 바라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E45
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00C464FD
#. Notes = Serious, Face: Serious, Prompt: 알렉산드리아 도서관에 무슨 일이 있었는데?
#: 02036DFA/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E45
msgctxt "0012F3"
msgid "Old Earth history. It was a hub of knowledge, gathered over the centuries, that was razed to the ground in a war much like ours."
msgstr "옛 지구 역사야. 수 세기에 걸쳐 지식이 모여든 중심지였는데, 우리와 아주 비슷한 전쟁 속에서 완전히 파괴됐지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E0CC0E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02036DE1/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E2D
msgctxt "0012F4"
msgid "That sounds incredibly dangerous."
msgstr "엄청나게 위험하게 들리는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E37
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0007F49D
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 그건 그냥 희망 사항일 뿐이야.
#: 02036DF4/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E37
msgctxt "0012F5"
msgid "And what kind of people would we be, if we no longer wished for a better world?"
msgstr "더 나은 세상을 바라지 않게 된다면, 우리는 어떤 사람들이 되는 걸까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009DAF4C, 00E8ADA6
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 상상도 못 할 일을 해야 한다 해도, 개척 성계를 안전하게 지켜야 했어., Worried, Face: Worried
#: 02036E01/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1F
msgctxt "0012F6"
msgid "But I recognize it's easy to say when it's not my life being threatened by these incursions."
msgstr "하지만 이 인커전으로 목숨을 위협받는 게 내가 아닐 때는 말하기 쉽다는 것도 알아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009DAF4C, 00E8ADA6
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 상상도 못 할 일을 해야 한다 해도, 개척 성계를 안전하게 지켜야 했어., Worried, Face: Worried
#: 02036E01/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1F
msgctxt "0012F7"
msgid "Putting our safety above our ideals has never been a wise decision."
msgstr "우리의 안전을 이상보다 앞세우는 건 결코 현명한 결정이 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E30
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00C17F39
#: 02036DF5/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E30
msgctxt "0012F8"
msgid "That's just wishful thinking."
msgstr "그건 그냥 희망 사항일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 002AB999, 003FF39D
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036DF7/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1C
msgctxt "0012F9"
msgid "It harkens back to early studies on the human brain. "
msgstr "인간의 뇌에 관한 초기 연구를 떠올리게 하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 002AB999, 003FF39D
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036DF7/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1C
msgctxt "0012FA"
msgid "I'm still trying to wrap my head around the concept of X-Tech. Do we even understand how it works? Do we need to? "
msgstr "난 아직도 X-테크라는 개념을 이해하려고 애쓰는 중이야. 우리가 그 작동 원리를 제대로 알고 있긴 해? 알 필요가 있나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E52
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A96F29, 00871A1D
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02036E4F/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E52
msgctxt "0012FB"
msgid "With their permission, of course."
msgstr "물론 그들의 허락을 받고요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E52
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A96F29, 00871A1D
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02036E4F/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E52
msgctxt "0012FC"
msgid "For example, I'd love to see what makes a robot like Delta tick, or tock."
msgstr "예를 들어 델타 같은 로봇이 어떻게 째깍, 아니 똑딱 움직이는지 꼭 보고 싶어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E2F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00A1B23D
#: 02036E04/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E2F
msgctxt "0012FD"
msgid "Never felt better."
msgstr "이렇게 좋은 적이 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E41
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00BDA3BD
#. Notes = Defiant, Face: Defiant, Prompt: 테란을 꽤 순진하게 보는군. 그들은 협상할 수 있는 상대가 아니야.
#: 02036DF2/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E41
msgctxt "0012FE"
msgid "Well no free-thinking society is a monolith. We only met the warmongers. There are most certainly others with differing views."
msgstr "자유롭게 사고하는 사회가 하나의 덩어리일 수는 없죠. 우리는 전쟁광들만 만났을 뿐이에요. 분명 다른 견해를 가진 이들도 있을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E39
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0070BFFF
#. Notes = Suspicious, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 그들의 X-테크 지식이 그들을 침략자로 만들었어. 그런 지식은 사라지는 게 나아.
#: 02036DFD/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E39
msgctxt "0012FF"
msgid "The erasure of any knowledge, however terrifying, goes against my principles. But I understand the need for caution."
msgstr "어떤 지식이든, 아무리 끔찍하더라도 지워 버리는 건 제 원칙에 어긋나요. 하지만 주의가 필요하다는 건 이해합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E2B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00FB6589
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02036DF6/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E2B
msgctxt "001300"
msgid "X-Tech, angry death robots, there's just so much to unpack!"
msgstr "X-테크에, 성난 살인 로봇에, 짚어 볼 게 너무 많아요!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E34
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 006309E0
#: 02036DFE/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E34
msgctxt "001301"
msgid "Their knowledge of X-tech pushed them to become aggressors. Better that knowledge is lost."
msgstr "그들의 X-테크 지식이 그들을 침략자로 만들었어. 그런 지식은 사라지는 게 나아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00D7E551
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 사라진 게 뭐든, 그렇게 중요하진 않았겠지.
#: 02036DFF/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E2E
msgctxt "001302"
msgid "All knowledge is important."
msgstr "모든 지식은 중요해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E17
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0057E775
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02036DF8/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E17
msgctxt "001303"
msgid "Anyhoo, my larger hope is that we learn from the lessons of the past."
msgstr "아무튼, 더 크게 바라는 건 우리가 과거의 교훈에서 배우는 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E24
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 001A87C2, 0099166C
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DFC/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E24
msgctxt "001304"
msgid "I don't agree with your choice, but I still want you to be okay with it. If that means I gotta fight off a thousand more incursions, so be it."
msgstr ""
"네 선택에 동의하진 않지만, 그래도 네가 그 선택을 받아들일 수 있으면 좋겠어. 그러려면 내가 인커전을 천 번 더 막아야 한다 해도, "
"그렇게 해야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E24
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 001A87C2, 0099166C
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DFC/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E24
msgctxt "001305"
msgid "I know we aren't technically soldiers anymore, but that hardly matters when we got the whole Settled Systems under fire."
msgstr "우리가 엄밀히 말해 더는 군인이 아니라는 건 알아. 하지만 개척 성계 전체가 공격받고 있는데 그게 무슨 상관이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E23
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009AE73A, 006DD22B
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DFC/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E23
msgctxt "001306"
msgid "Just remember you did what you had to. I firmly believe that."
msgstr "네가 해야 할 일을 했다는 것만 기억해. 난 그걸 굳게 믿어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E23
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009AE73A, 006DD22B
#. Notes = Neutral, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02036DFC/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E23
msgctxt "001307"
msgid "I know we aren't technically soldiers anymore, but that hardly matters when we're dropping the nuke on entire civilizations."
msgstr "우리가 엄밀히 말해 더는 군인이 아니라는 건 알아. 하지만 우리가 문명 전체에 핵을 떨어뜨리는 상황이면 그게 무슨 상관이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00383814
#: 02036DFB/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E3F
msgctxt "001308"
msgid "What happened with the Library of Alexandria?"
msgstr "알렉산드리아 도서관에 무슨 일이 있었는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E29
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002E075C
#: 02036E06/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E29
msgctxt "001309"
msgid "When the mission's done, I don't look back."
msgstr "임무가 끝나면 뒤돌아보지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E26
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00D585B7
#: 02036E00/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E26
msgctxt "00130A"
msgid "Whatever was lost couldn't have been that important."
msgstr "사라진 게 뭐든, 그렇게 중요하진 않았겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00DBB983
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 넌 신나도 돼. 난 그냥 좀 쉬어야겠어.
#: 02036E0D/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E2C
msgctxt "00130B"
msgid "It's well deserved. You rest your feet, and leave the lab work to me."
msgstr "충분히 그럴 만해요. 당신은 발 좀 쉬고, 실험실 일은 저한테 맡기세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E20
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0071449D
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: Scientifically speaking, this is a major event that will be studied for generations.
#: 02036E0F/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E20
msgctxt "00130C"
msgid "Yes. Centuries even!"
msgstr "네. 심지어 몇 세기나요!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E19
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CDB85B
#: 02036E02/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E19
msgctxt "00130D"
msgid "We had to keep the Settled Systems safe, even if it meant doing the unthinkable."
msgstr "상상도 못 할 일을 해야 한다 해도, 개척 성계를 안전하게 지켜야 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E38
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00B4CBBF
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 흥미진진한 일이야.
#: 02036E0B/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E38
msgctxt "00130E"
msgid "Indubitably!"
msgstr "의심할 여지 없죠!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E43
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00546841
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Prompt: 이렇게 좋은 적이 없었어.
#: 02036E03/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E43
msgctxt "00130F"
msgid "Fair enough."
msgstr "그럴 만해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0013471E
#. Notes = Stern, Face: Stern, Prompt: 임무가 끝나면 뒤돌아보지 않아.
#: 02036E05/00000/SFTER_COM_SamCoe_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E1D
msgctxt "001310"
msgid "I getcha soldier. Hoo-ah and all that. Don't know if that's healthy, but I getcha."
msgstr "알겠어, 군인 양반. 후아 어쩌고 하는 거지. 그게 건강한지는 모르겠지만, 무슨 말인진 알겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E27
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 008F204E
#: 02036E0E/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E27
msgctxt "001311"
msgid "You can be excited. I just need a break."
msgstr "넌 신나도 돼. 난 그냥 좀 쉬어야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E42
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00128E30, 00EAE1E7
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Prompt: 솔직히 과학적 의미 같은 건 관심 없어., Neutral
#: 02036E09/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E42
msgctxt "001312"
msgid "But in our hands, maybe we can find a different application."
msgstr "하지만 우리 손에 있다면, 어쩌면 다른 활용법을 찾을 수 있을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E42
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00128E30, 00EAE1E7
#. Notes = Face: Confident, Prompt: 솔직히 과학적 의미 같은 건 관심 없어., Neutral
#: 02036E09/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E42
msgctxt "001313"
msgid "That's fair. But the scientific and the social are connected. In the Terran's hands that technology was used for war."
msgstr "일리 있어요. 하지만 과학적인 것과 사회적인 것은 연결되어 있어요. 테란의 손에서 그 기술은 전쟁에 쓰였죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E51
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FD46B8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02036E4E/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E51
msgctxt "001314"
msgid "Delta wouldn't mind letting you poke around, I'm sure."
msgstr "델타도 당신이 이것저것 살펴보는 걸 싫어하진 않을 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E3B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E2D58A
#: 02036E0A/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E3B
msgctxt "001315"
msgid "I honestly don't care about the scientific implications."
msgstr "솔직히 과학적 의미 같은 건 관심 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02037490
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0070B790
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 저도 X-테크의 특성이 궁금해요.
#: 02037487/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02037490
msgctxt "001316"
msgid "You and me both."
msgstr "나도 그래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E31
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 004BAF71
#: 02036E0C/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E31
msgctxt "001317"
msgid "It's exciting stuff."
msgstr "흥미진진한 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203748D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00C3EFAD
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: X-테크가 뭘로 만들어졌든 조금도 관심 없어.
#: 02037485/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203748D
msgctxt "001318"
msgid "That's a shame. Me, I can't help but be curious."
msgstr "아쉽네요. 저는 궁금하지 않을 수가 없거든요."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFFL_SE_KT02_SailingHighSeasSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 010388C9
#. QuestName = SFFL_SE_KT02_SailingHighSeas
#. SceneName = SFFL_SE_KT02_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_SE_KT02_RichPatron01_AudioOnly
#. SoundFileID = 0083E97B
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 해적을 건드리면 안 되지.
#: 01031F8D/00000/SFFL_SE_KT02_100b_HailingAnswered:010388C9
msgctxt "001319"
msgid "Prepare to die, pirate scum!"
msgstr "죽을 준비나 해라, 해적 쓰레기!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 006199C7
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02036E11/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E3C
msgctxt "00131A"
msgid "Well Dusty, looks like another crazy adventure is in the books."
msgstr "자, 두더지, 또 한 번 미친 모험이 끝난 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203748B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 007CA84E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02037486/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203748B
msgctxt "00131B"
msgid "I don't care one iota what X-Tech is made of."
msgstr "X-테크가 뭘로 만들어졌든 조금도 관심 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E54
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00D35B0F, 00A571E2
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036E4C/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E54
msgctxt "00131C"
msgid "So selfishly, I hope we can someday talk to their scientists, and learn what they know."
msgstr "그래서 이기적인 바람이지만, 언젠가 그들의 과학자들과 이야기하고 그들이 아는 것을 배울 수 있으면 해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E54
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00D35B0F, 00A571E2
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02036E4C/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E54
msgctxt "00131D"
msgid "Because there has to be other uses for it besides making death robots, and I bet the Terrans know it. "
msgstr "살인 로봇을 만드는 것 말고도 분명 다른 용도가 있을 테고, 테란도 그걸 알고 있을 테니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E53
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E5CA61, 00C62407
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned, Worried, Face: Worried
#: 02036E4C/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E53
msgctxt "00131E"
msgid "I just hope when we made those robots frenzy, we weren't burning the answers to those questions in the process, Library of Alexandria style."
msgstr "우리가 그 로봇들을 광란 상태로 만들었을 때, 그 과정에서 그 질문들의 답까지 알렉산드리아 도서관처럼 불태워 버린 건 아니었으면 해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E50
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00509B04
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 델타도 당신이 이것저것 살펴보는 걸 싫어하진 않을 거예요.
#: 02036E4D/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E50
msgctxt "00131F"
msgid "*Chuckle* Delta's cool like that."
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 델타는 그런 게 멋지죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203748E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A55D01
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02037488/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203748E
msgctxt "001320"
msgid "I'm also curious about the properties of X-Tech."
msgstr "저도 X-테크의 특성이 궁금해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203748C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E4798C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203748A/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203748C
msgctxt "001321"
msgid "Delta isn't sentient so you don't need permission."
msgstr "델타는 지각이 있는 존재가 아니니 허락은 필요 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203748F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 0038D2C3
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 델타는 지각이 있는 존재가 아니니 허락은 필요 없어.
#: 02037489/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203748F
msgctxt "001322"
msgid "Sentient or not, a gentleman always asks."
msgstr "지성이 있든 없든, 신사는 언제나 먼저 물어보는 법이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038367
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A52AE8, 007B0E98, 00BBCB46
#. Notes = Neutral, Surprised, Face: Surprised, Question, Face: Question
#: 0203835E/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038367
msgctxt "001323"
msgid "What happens if we do both in a microgravity environment, before blasting it with lasers?"
msgstr "그걸 미세중력 환경에서 둘 다 해 본 다음 레이저로 쏘면 어떻게 될까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038367
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A52AE8, 007B0E98, 00BBCB46
#. Notes = Neutral, Surprised, Face: Surprised, Question, Face: Question
#: 0203835E/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038367
msgctxt "001324"
msgid "What happens when we melt it? What happens if you freeze it? "
msgstr "녹이면 어떻게 될까? 얼리면 어떻게 될까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038367
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A52AE8, 007B0E98, 00BBCB46
#. Notes = Neutral, Surprised, Face: Surprised, Question, Face: Question
#: 0203835E/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038367
msgctxt "001325"
msgid "But yeah, similar to the Artifacts, the very existence of X-Tech fills me with so many questions."
msgstr "하지만 그래, 유물과 마찬가지로 X-테크라는 존재 자체가 내 안에 수많은 의문을 불러일으켜."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038369
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00EB0815, 00916A38
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 뭔가가 왜, 어떻게 작동하는지 모른다면 난 불안할 것 같아., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038361/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038369
msgctxt "001326"
msgid "What are its properties? What happens when it explodes? What are its likes and dislikes? Nobody knows!"
msgstr "그 특성은 뭘까? 폭발하면 어떻게 될까? 좋아하는 것과 싫어하는 것은? 아무도 몰라!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038369
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00EB0815, 00916A38
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 뭔가가 왜, 어떻게 작동하는지 모른다면 난 불안할 것 같아., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038361/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038369
msgctxt "001327"
msgid "Exactly! This is why we need to learn more about X-Tech."
msgstr "맞아! 그래서 우리가 X-테크에 대해 더 알아내야 하는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038365
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 004EDA70
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038362/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038365
msgctxt "001328"
msgid "Not knowing why or how something works would make me uncomfortable."
msgstr "뭔가가 왜, 어떻게 작동하는지 모른다면 난 불안할 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038366
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 001D2B28
#. Notes = Question / to Player Default, Face: Question, Prompt: 작동만 하면 그걸로 충분해.
#: 02038363/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038366
msgctxt "001329"
msgid "Yes and no. If you don't know HOW something works, how do you know there aren't side effects, or that it's not more detrimental in the long run?"
msgstr "그렇기도 하고 아니기도 해. 뭔가가 어떻게 작동하는지 모르면, 부작용이 없는지, 장기적으로 더 해롭지는 않은지 어떻게 알겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038368
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 003BF9DB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038364/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038368
msgctxt "00132A"
msgid "If it works, that's all that matters."
msgstr "작동만 하면 그걸로 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038101
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0070AF41
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 020380F7:02038101
msgctxt "00132B"
msgid "It seems the minerals to create the Terran's military and industry are mined in places like this."
msgstr "테란의 군사력과 산업을 만드는 데 필요한 광물은 이런 곳에서 채굴되는 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038100
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 003A4041
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 020380F7:02038100
msgctxt "00132C"
msgid "Wowee, this is some operation. It's a shame these minerals are being used to make more death robots. "
msgstr "우와, 규모가 엄청난데. 이런 광물이 더 많은 살인 로봇을 만드는 데 쓰인다니 안타깝네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0096E5DE
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 020380F7:020380FF
msgctxt "00132D"
msgid "Asteroids like this are full of rare minerals. Not surprising they're trying to extract every bit of it."
msgstr "이런 소행성에는 희귀 광물이 가득하지. 그들이 한 조각까지 모조리 캐내려는 것도 놀랄 일은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0046D87A
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 020380F7:020380FE
msgctxt "00132E"
msgid "Whatever they're mining, it can't be for anything good."
msgstr "뭘 캐고 있든 좋은 일에 쓰일 리는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380FC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0012142B
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 020380F6:020380FC
msgctxt "00132F"
msgid "Stay alert. These robots look inactive, but I do not trust they will stay so forever."
msgstr "경계해. 이 로봇들은 비활성화된 것처럼 보이지만, 계속 그럴 거라고는 믿지 않는다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00C04415
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 020380F6:020380FB
msgctxt "001330"
msgid "Oh boy, if these robots wake up, it'll be a bad time. Let's be careful."
msgstr "이런, 이 로봇들이 깨어나면 정말 곤란해질 거야. 조심하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0022B592
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 020380F6:020380FA
msgctxt "001331"
msgid "I don't think these robots are active. But I'd be prepared for an ambush."
msgstr "이 로봇들이 작동 중인 것 같지는 않아. 그래도 매복에 대비해 두겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020380F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 003C4731
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 020380F6:020380F9
msgctxt "001332"
msgid "This place gives me the creeps."
msgstr "여긴 소름 끼치는 곳이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAAD
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0080577E, 0052220E
#. Notes = Resolved / to Player Default, Prompt: 날 풀어내는 게 불가능하다면 왜 시도하는 거야?
#: 0200FA6D/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0200FAAD
msgctxt "001333"
msgid "Ceasing attempts betrays stated fact. Additionally, would result in an admission of failure."
msgstr "시도 중단은 명시된 사실과 배치됨. 추가로, 실패를 인정하는 결과가 됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203835B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0060D7F8
#. Notes = Truly interested in player as a specimen / to Player Default, Prompt: 호기심이라니 무슨 뜻이야?
#: 0200FA6B/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0203835B
msgctxt "001336"
msgid "Auxiliary's lack of solution deemed unique. Lack of solution begets interest. Synonym for interest: Curiosity."
msgstr "보조 인간에 대한 해법 부재는 특이한 것으로 판단됨. 해법 부재는 관심을 유발함. 관심의 동의어: 호기심."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038359
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CA7027
#. Notes = Annoyed / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 명칭이 아군이야? 친구로 바꿀 수 있어?
#: 0200FA69/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:02038359
msgctxt "001337"
msgid "Ally."
msgstr "아군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203835A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C4AA9A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA6A/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0203835A
msgctxt "001338"
msgid "Friend?"
msgstr "친구?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB45
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D15FBD, 00D50B7C
#. Notes = Resolved / to Player Default, Prompt: 날 풀어내지 않아도 돼, 델타.
#: 0200FA71/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0200FB45
msgctxt "001339"
msgid "Auxiliary will be solved. In time."
msgstr "보조 인간은 해결될 것임. 시간이 지나면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203835D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E3D420
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA6C/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0203835D
msgctxt "00133A"
msgid "What do you mean by curiosity?"
msgstr "호기심이라니 무슨 뜻이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203835C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00DE1762
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Player Default
#: 0200FA74/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:0203835C
msgctxt "00133B"
msgid "Current assessment of Perishable: Upsetting. Only human marked \"Unpredictable\"."
msgstr "부패성 개체에 대한 현재 평가: 불쾌. \"Unpredictable\"로 표시된 유일한 인간."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004CD856, 000893AF
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 곁에 계속 있으려고 그럴듯한 핑계를 대는 것 같은데.
#: 020383A4/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383AE
msgctxt "00133C"
msgid "Upsetting."
msgstr "불쾌."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004CD856, 000893AF
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 곁에 계속 있으려고 그럴듯한 핑계를 대는 것 같은데.
#: 020383A4/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383AE
msgctxt "00133D"
msgid "Incorrect. Repeating initial line of assessment:"
msgstr "부정확. 평가의 첫 줄 반복:"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00989AC3, 00967D45
#. Notes = Genuinely hasn't bothered to think about it / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 나를 해결한다고 치자. 그다음엔 어떻게 되는데?
#: 020383A2/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B1
msgctxt "00133F"
msgid "Idiom #107, \"I will cross that bridge when I get there\"."
msgstr "관용구 #107, \"그때 가서 생각하겠다\"."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00989AC3, 00967D45
#. Notes = Genuinely hasn't bothered to think about it / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 나를 해결한다고 치자. 그다음엔 어떻게 되는데?
#: 020383A2/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B1
msgctxt "001340"
msgid "Unknown. Dedicating all expendable processes to Auxiliary problem."
msgstr "알 수 없음. 모든 가용 소모 프로세스를 보조 인간 문제에 할당 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EAF344
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020383A3/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B0
msgctxt "001341"
msgid "Say you solve me, tell me what happens after."
msgstr "네가 나를 해결한다고 치자. 그다음엔 어떻게 되는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0034E877
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020383A5/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B9
msgctxt "001342"
msgid "Sounds like a big excuse to keep being around me."
msgstr "내 곁에 계속 있으려고 그럴듯한 핑계를 대는 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A0546D
#. Notes = Resolved / to Player Default
#: 020383A7/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B5
msgctxt "001344"
msgid "Counterpoint: All problems solvable. Additionally, Auxiliary shows aptitude for combat, problem solving, and interpersonal interactions."
msgstr "반론: 모든 문제는 해결 가능. 또한 보조 인간은 전투, 문제 해결, 대인 관계에 적성을 보임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E8C8FE
#. Notes = This is insane / to Player Default
#: 020383A9/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B2
msgctxt "001347"
msgid "Increased data has not lessened variations. Conversely, more data results in increased potentials. Phenomena counter to standard Human-Simulation relationship."
msgstr ""
"데이터가 증가해도 변동은 줄어들지 않았음. 반대로 데이터가 많아질수록 가능성이 증가함. 표준 인간-시뮬레이션 관계에 반하는 현상."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001A3CFD
#. Notes = Bewildered? / to Player Default
#: 020383AC/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383AF
msgctxt "001348"
msgid "Attempts at simulated scenarios result in different outcomes per attempt. Requires increased computation to chart line of best fit for resulting data points."
msgstr "시뮬레이션 시나리오 시도는 매번 서로 다른 결과를 산출함. 산출된 데이터 포인트의 최적 적합선을 산정하려면 연산량 증가가 필요함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00861B1E
#. Notes = Resolved / to Player Default
#: 020383AD/00014/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_14_TopLevel_PersonalDetails_4:020383B4
msgctxt "00134A"
msgid "Conclusion: Solution requires more data. Ergo, must continue observing you, contrary to frustration. Current designation: Ally."
msgstr "결론: 해결에는 더 많은 데이터가 필요함. 따라서 불만과는 반대로, 당신 관찰을 계속해야 함. 현재 지정: 아군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 006C5604
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02038D87/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E0D
msgctxt "001356"
msgid "As such, I hesitate to judge them so blindly."
msgstr "그렇기에 나는 그들을 그토록 맹목적으로 판단하기를 주저한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DFB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00A3E6F8
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038D89/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DFB
msgctxt "00135B"
msgid "I will ruminate on this more later. For now, I appreciate you taking the time to speak with me."
msgstr "나중에 이 문제를 더 곱씹어 보겠다. 지금은 나와 이야기할 시간을 내줘서 고맙다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E46
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00ABAC63
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 둘 사이에는 비슷한 점이 많아.
#: 02038D8B/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E46
msgctxt "00135F"
msgid "Yes. However, their machine gods are false ones, and our victory only proves it."
msgstr "그렇다. 하지만 그들의 기계 신들은 거짓된 존재이며, 우리의 승리가 그것을 증명할 뿐이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E3E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00D8CC01
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D8C/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E3E
msgctxt "001360"
msgid "There are a lot of parallels between the two."
msgstr "둘 사이에는 비슷한 점이 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E34
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00A29062
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 세력이 이렇게 다양하니, 우리가 옛 지구의 국가들을 다시 만들고 있는 것처럼 느껴질 정도야.
#: 02038D8D/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E34
msgctxt "001361"
msgid "A wise person once said those who forget history are doomed to repeat it."
msgstr "어떤 현자가 말했지. 역사를 잊은 자는 그것을 반복하게 된다고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E27
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00B512CD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D8E/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E27
msgctxt "001362"
msgid "With so many different powers, it almost feels like we're recreating the countries of Old Earth."
msgstr "세력이 이렇게 다양하니, 우리가 옛 지구의 국가들을 다시 만들고 있는 것처럼 느껴질 정도야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00A02B3D
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 우주는 날이 갈수록 더 이상해지는군.
#: 02038D8F/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E1A
msgctxt "001363"
msgid "Ha, indeed."
msgstr "하, 정말 그렇군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E10
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 009B92FD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D90/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E10
msgctxt "001364"
msgid "Space just gets weirder by the day."
msgstr "우주는 날이 갈수록 더 이상해지는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E01
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E9B009, 009C9FC7
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 바룬 가문은 테란 함대만큼 적대적이지는 않아., / to Player Default
#: 02038D91/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E01
msgctxt "001365"
msgid "The Terrans are more violent, but antagonistic acts can take many forms."
msgstr "테란이 더 폭력적이긴 하지만, 적대 행위는 여러 형태로 나타날 수 있다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DF5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00303A92
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D92/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DF5
msgctxt "001366"
msgid "House Va'ruun is not nearly as antagonistic as the Terran Armada."
msgstr "바룬 가문은 테란 함대만큼 적대적이지는 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E4D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 000CEA13
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02038D94/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E4D
msgctxt "00136A"
msgid "In any case, I have found this experience enlightening."
msgstr "어쨌든 이번 경험은 내게 많은 깨달음을 주었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002638D3, 00E16722
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 어려운 선택이었지만, 올바른 선택을 했다고 생각해., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038D97/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E2E
msgctxt "00136B"
msgid "Sadly we know so little of the Terrans, by design."
msgstr "슬프게도 우리는 테란에 대해 아는 것이 너무 적다. 의도적으로 그렇게 된 것이겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002638D3, 00E16722
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 어려운 선택이었지만, 올바른 선택을 했다고 생각해., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038D97/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E2E
msgctxt "00136C"
msgid "You can only make a decision with the information you have."
msgstr "가진 정보 안에서만 결정을 내릴 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E21
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00E35BB7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D98/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E21
msgctxt "00136D"
msgid "It was a tough choice but I think I made the right one."
msgstr "어려운 선택이었지만, 올바른 선택을 했다고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E15
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002213D1
#. Notes = Question / to Player Default, Face: Question, Prompt: 우리를 공격한 테란들이 모든 테란을 대표하는 것은 아니다.
#: 02038D99/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E15
msgctxt "00136E"
msgid "Yes, but at times it is hard to see the forest for the trees. Especially when violence is involved."
msgstr "맞다. 하지만 때로는 나무만 보고 숲을 보지 못하기 쉽다. 특히 폭력이 개입되면 더더욱."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E07
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 001FA0BE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D9A/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E07
msgctxt "00136F"
msgid "The Terrans who attacked us do not represent all Terrans."
msgstr "우리를 공격한 테란들이 모든 테란을 대표하는 것은 아니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DFC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001CF72D
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 테란 함대에 무고한 사람은 없어.
#: 02038D9B/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DFC
msgctxt "001370"
msgid "I disagree, but I understand why you believe that is true."
msgstr "동의하진 않지만, 왜 네가 그렇게 믿는지는 이해한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DF1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BB7325
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D9C/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DF1
msgctxt "001371"
msgid "No one in the Terran Armada is innocent."
msgstr "테란 함대에 무고한 사람은 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E54
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 004F1127
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038D9D/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E54
msgctxt "001372"
msgid "After all, it would have been understandable to turn the robots against their creators, given they were the aggressors."
msgstr "어쨌든 그들이 공격자였으니, 로봇을 만들어 낸 자들에게 되돌리는 것도 이해할 만한 일이었을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E53
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00E949EC
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038D9D/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E53
msgctxt "001373"
msgid "After all, some may have hesitated to turn the robots against their creators, given innocents might be caught in the crossfire."
msgstr "어쨌든 무고한 이들이 교전에 휘말릴 수 있었으니, 로봇을 만들어 낸 자들에게 되돌리는 일을 망설인 사람도 있었을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E44
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00136BB9
#. Notes = Not yet revealed she's House Va'ruun. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02038DA7/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E44
msgctxt "001380"
msgid "I could not help but see the parallels with my own life as an outsider."
msgstr "이방인으로 살아온 내 삶과의 유사점을 보지 않을 수 없었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00DEE0EF
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DA8/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E3C
msgctxt "001381"
msgid "On that note, I must ask your thought process regarding that final decision."
msgstr "그런 의미에서, 마지막 결정에 대해 네가 어떤 생각을 했는지 묻고 싶다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E3D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00A81446
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 그들은 전쟁광이야. 그뿐이지. 우리가 그들을 판단할 권리는 충분해.
#: 02038DB6/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E3D
msgctxt "00138C"
msgid "It is that kind of thinking that I detest."
msgstr "내가 혐오하는 것이 바로 그런 사고방식이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DFA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00F7F85C
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 때로는 아주 적은 정보만으로 결정을 내려야 해.
#: 02038DB2/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DFA
msgctxt "00138D"
msgid "A fair and measured response."
msgstr "공정하고 신중한 반응이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E50
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 0069F242
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 네 말이 맞아. 우리가 만난 테란들조차 더 큰 집단의 일부였을 뿐이야.
#: 02038DB4/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E50
msgctxt "00138E"
msgid "I am pleased to hear you say this. It has been on my mind ever since this last battle."
msgstr "네가 그렇게 말해 주니 기쁘다. 지난 전투 이후 계속 마음에 걸리던 일이었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E45
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 005F2F8D
#: 02038DB5/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E45
msgctxt "00138F"
msgid "You're right. Even the Terrans we encountered were just part of a larger group."
msgstr "네 말이 맞아. 우리가 만난 테란들조차 더 큰 집단의 일부였을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DF0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00F95C9B
#: 02038DB3/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DF0
msgctxt "001390"
msgid "Sometimes we have to make decisions with only a pinch of information."
msgstr "때로는 아주 적은 정보만으로 결정을 내려야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E32
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002CCEE5
#: 02038DB7/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E32
msgctxt "001391"
msgid "They're warmongers, plain and simple. We have every right to judge them."
msgstr "그들은 전쟁광이야. 그뿐이지. 우리가 그들을 판단할 권리는 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E25
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00064434
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 나도 외교적인 접근을 더 선호했겠지만, 그들은 무기를 겨눈 채 우리에게 다가왔어.
#: 02038DB8/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E25
msgctxt "001392"
msgid "Agreed. But it may also be a trained response for them, to strike first in order to survive."
msgstr "동의한다. 하지만 그들에게는 생존을 위해 먼저 공격하도록 훈련된 반응일 수도 있다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E19
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00AA3E8D
#: 02038DB9/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E19
msgctxt "001393"
msgid "I would've preferred a diplomatic approach myself, but they came to us with weapons drawn."
msgstr "나도 외교적인 접근을 더 선호했겠지만, 그들은 무기를 겨눈 채 우리에게 다가왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00B685E1
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DBA/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E0C
msgctxt "001394"
msgid "I would like to discuss what happened with the Terrans."
msgstr "테란에게 일어난 일에 대해 이야기하고 싶다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E55
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00802AEE, 00B1E8B3
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DC6/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E55
msgctxt "0013A2"
msgid "While at Constellation, our primary directive is exploring, part of that journey means tangling with the occasional hostile."
msgstr "컨스텔레이션에서 우리의 주된 지침은 탐험이지만, 그 여정의 일부에는 가끔 적대 세력과 얽히는 일도 포함된다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E55
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00802AEE, 00B1E8B3
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DC6/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E55
msgctxt "0013A3"
msgid "Regardless, I'm sure this isn't the last we've heard from the Terrans."
msgstr "어쨌든 테란에 관한 소식이 이걸로 끝은 아닐 거라고 확신해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DF2
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00A76E51
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02038DC5/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DF2
msgctxt "0013A5"
msgid "My only hope is that those \"occasions\" are few and far between."
msgstr "내 바람은 그런 \"경우\"가 아주 드물기만 하는 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00B4CCC1, 001C9DA1
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 사람이 죽으면, 죽는 거지., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038DC9/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E3F
msgctxt "0013A8"
msgid "That's not quite the attitude I'd have. Every life is important."
msgstr "내가 가질 만한 태도는 아니군. 모든 생명은 소중해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E36
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00D48567
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038DCA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E36
msgctxt "0013A9"
msgid "If people die, they die."
msgstr "사람이 죽으면, 죽는 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E2A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00998618
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 자기들이 만들었으니, 그 대가도 자기들이 치른 거지.
#: 02038DCB/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E2A
msgctxt "0013AA"
msgid "I suppose in some ways, it's no different than reprogramming a turret. Yet there's a \"but\" to that statement."
msgstr "어떤 면에서는 포탑을 재프로그래밍하는 것과 다르지 않을지도 몰라. 하지만 그 말에는 \"하지만\"이 붙어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00A8D85C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038DCC/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E1C
msgctxt "0013AB"
msgid "They built them, they bought them."
msgstr "자기들이 만들었으니, 그 대가도 자기들이 치른 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E12
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001FA104
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 네 우려는 이해하지만, 결국 그것은 옳은 결정이었다.
#: 02038DCD/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E12
msgctxt "0013AC"
msgid "Perhaps. I don't disagree that statistically, you may have saved more civilian lives. Yet the cost of war cannot be counted on a spreadsheet."
msgstr "그럴지도 모르지. 통계적으로 보면 네가 더 많은 민간인의 목숨을 구했을 수도 있다는 데는 반대하지 않아. 하지만 전쟁의 대가는 스프레드시트로 계산할 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E04
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DE012E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038DCE/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E04
msgctxt "0013B4"
msgid "I understand your concerns, but ultimately it was the right decision."
msgstr "네 우려는 이해하지만, 결국 그것은 옳은 결정이었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 006504F6, 000971F3, 003D189F
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E09
msgctxt "0013BA"
msgid "Given these were military robots, most of the casualties were likely military personnel. "
msgstr "그것들이 군용 로봇이었다는 점을 고려하면, 사상자의 대부분은 군인이었을 가능성이 높다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 006504F6, 000971F3, 003D189F
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E09
msgctxt "0013BB"
msgid "As a former soldier, I don't necessarily disagree with what you did."
msgstr "전직 군인으로서, 네가 한 일에 반드시 반대하는 것은 아니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E17
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00B67B92
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DD9/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E17
msgctxt "0013BC"
msgid "As someone in a leadership position, I can empathize with having to make tough choices. I'm just curious how you came to your decision."
msgstr "지도자의 위치에 있는 사람으로서, 어려운 선택을 내려야 하는 상황에 공감할 수 있다. 다만 네가 어떻게 그런 결정을 내리게 되었는지 궁금하다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DF4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 005BB0EE
#. Notes = Smirk, Face: Smirk, Prompt: 사실 그렇게 어려운 선택은 아니었어.
#: 02038DE4/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DF4
msgctxt "0013C9"
msgid "I see. I suppose for someone of your background, it's just another Tuesday."
msgstr "알겠어. 네 배경을 가진 사람에게는 그저 늘 있는 일일지도 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038DED
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00A313FB
#: 02038DE5/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038DED
msgctxt "0013CA"
msgid "It wasn't really that tough of a choice."
msgstr "사실 그렇게 어려운 선택은 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E4C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 008510B0
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 직감에 따랐어.
#: 02038DE6/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E4C
msgctxt "0013CB"
msgid "Understandable. Going with one's gut may not seem scientific, but it's really just shorthand for leaning on your wisdom and experiences."
msgstr "이해할 만해. 직감을 따르는 것이 과학적으로 보이지 않을 수는 있지만, 사실은 자신의 지혜와 경험에 기대는 것을 줄여 말한 것뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E28
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00890AAE
#: 02038DE7/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E28
msgctxt "0013CC"
msgid "I went with my gut."
msgstr "직감에 따랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E33
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0011E0D3, 003CAA73
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked, Prompt: 그냥 아무거나 찍어서 골랐어., Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 02038DE8/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E33
msgctxt "0013CD"
msgid "You did... what?"
msgstr "뭘... 했다고요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00DD11D4
#: 02038DE9/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E0B
msgctxt "0013CE"
msgid "I used eeny, meeny, miny, moe."
msgstr "그냥 아무거나 찍어서 골랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E20
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007AC5ED
#. Notes = Neutral, Prompt: 장단점을 따져 보고 큰 그림을 보려고 했어.
#: 02038DEA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E20
msgctxt "0013CF"
msgid "By the book then. People mock training manuals, but I find them handy regardless of the situation."
msgstr "그렇다면 규정대로군요. 사람들은 훈련 교범을 비웃지만, 저는 어떤 상황에서도 유용하다고 봅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E26
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EB691F
#: 02038DEB/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E26
msgctxt "0013D0"
msgid "I weighed the pros and cons and tried to look at the big picture."
msgstr "장단점을 따져 보고 큰 그림을 보려고 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E06
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 004D1FC2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DEC/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E06
msgctxt "0013D1"
msgid "If you have a moment, I'd like to talk about your decision to turn the Terran robots against their masters."
msgstr "시간이 된다면, 테란 로봇들을 주인에게 맞서게 한 당신의 결정에 대해 얘기하고 싶습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FADA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F792E2, 008EE010, 008B762E
#. Notes = Obvious / to Player Default, Prompt: 왜 전투를 시뮬레이션해서 같은 결과를 얻을 수 없는 거야?
#: 0200FA59/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FADA
msgctxt "0013E5"
msgid "Must acknowledge simulations unable to account for everything."
msgstr "시뮬레이션이 모든 변수를 반영할 수 없음을 인정해야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FADA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F792E2, 008EE010, 008B762E
#. Notes = Obvious / to Player Default, Prompt: 왜 전투를 시뮬레이션해서 같은 결과를 얻을 수 없는 거야?
#: 0200FA59/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FADA
msgctxt "0013E6"
msgid "Potential for meteor to crash during combat: Less than 1%. Simulated combat would not account for event."
msgstr "전투 중 운석 충돌 가능성: 1% 미만. 모의 전투는 해당 사건을 반영하지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E66
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000715C1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA5E/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:02038E66
msgctxt "0013E7"
msgid "Know where I can get that gun?"
msgstr "그 총은 어디서 구할 수 있는지 알아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E65
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D60E1D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA5E/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:02038E65
msgctxt "0013E8"
msgid "You were carrying around 2 copies of the same gun?"
msgstr "같은 총을 2자루나 들고 다녔어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E62
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B5E081, 00D8DD3B
#. Notes = Um actually / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 나한테 졌을 때만 빼고.
#: 0200FA61/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:02038E62
msgctxt "0013EA"
msgid "Upon frame failure, Delta program can be recompiled and uploaded to new device. Result would be potential loss of data. Cost-benefit analysis deems this acceptable."
msgstr "프레임 고장 시 델타 프로그램은 재컴파일 후 새 장치에 업로드 가능. 결과적으로 데이터 손실 가능성 존재. 비용 편익 분석상 허용 가능으로 판단."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E62
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B5E081, 00D8DD3B
#. Notes = Um actually / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 나한테 졌을 때만 빼고.
#: 0200FA61/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:02038E62
msgctxt "0013EB"
msgid "Counterpoint: Concepts of life and death have reduced severity levels for Delta Unit."
msgstr "반론: 삶과 죽음 개념은 델타 기체 기준 심각도가 낮음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAF7
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004A3A45
#. Notes = Upset / to Player Default, Prompt: 네가 나한테 졌을 때만 빼고.
#: 0200FA61/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:0200FAF7
msgctxt "0013EC"
msgid "Discussion topic ceased."
msgstr "논의 주제 종료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E64
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00213E4B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0200FA62/00017/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_17_TopLevel_Personal_3:02038E64
msgctxt "0013ED"
msgid "Combat isn't a field test. It's life and death."
msgstr "전투는 현장 테스트가 아니야. 삶과 죽음이 걸린 문제라고."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_SelfModify
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FAAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009CF071, 00EFC485
#. Notes = Shaking head / to Player Default, Prompt: 왜 스스로를 개조해서 개선할 수 없는 거야?
#: 0200FA91/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FAAE
msgctxt "0013EE"
msgid "Cautionary limit established by humans."
msgstr "인간이 설정한 예방 한계."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0200FB49
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006E7F21, 00739B64
#. Notes = You'd think, but you'd be wrong / to Player Default, Prompt: 하지만 넌 개선되잖아. 그럼 넌 다르다는 뜻이야?, Backhand / to Player Default
#: 0200FA93/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:0200FB49
msgctxt "0013EF"
msgid "Standard humans as well."
msgstr "일반 인간도 마찬가지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020383BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BFC293
#. Notes = Tragedy / to Player Default
#: 020383BA/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:020383BD
msgctxt "0013F0"
msgid "Example: Machine is built with jumping force of 500 newtons. Initial test jump results in 500 newtons of force. Average human male is tested. 400 newtons."
msgstr "예시: 기계는 도약력 500뉴턴으로 제작됨. 초기 시험 도약 결과 힘 500뉴턴. 평균적인 인간 남성 시험 결과 400뉴턴."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_NoDesire
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038AC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BC11E7, 007A882D, 00EE1B6F
#. Notes = Truly no desire present / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 로봇에게 개선 능력을 주고 싶은 거군.
#: 02038AAE/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038AC0
msgctxt "0013F1"
msgid "Impossible desires deemed inefficient."
msgstr "불가능한 욕구는 비효율적이라 판단됨."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_NoDesire
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038AC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BC11E7, 007A882D, 00EE1B6F
#. Notes = Truly no desire present / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 로봇에게 개선 능력을 주고 싶은 거군.
#: 02038AAE/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038AC0
msgctxt "0013F2"
msgid "Flesh possesses growth capabilities. Metal is static. Possibility of robotic improvement nonsensical."
msgstr "육체는 성장 능력을 보유. 금속은 정적. 로봇의 개선 가능성은 논리에 맞지 않음."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_NoDesire
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038AC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BC11E7, 007A882D, 00EE1B6F
#. Notes = Truly no desire present / to Player Default, Prompt: 그러니까 로봇에게 개선 능력을 주고 싶은 거군.
#: 02038AAE/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038AC0
msgctxt "0013F3"
msgid "Incorrect. No desire present."
msgstr "부정확. 욕구 없음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038ABB
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00367EBE
#. Notes = Sighing? / to Player Default, Prompt: ...500뉴턴으로 뛰면 얼마나 높이 올라가?
#: 02038AB0/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038ABB
msgctxt "0013F4"
msgid "Lowering Intelligence variable..."
msgstr "지능 변수 낮추는 중..."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_ConfusingStatement
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038ABA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00E3CD7D
#. Notes = COMPLETELY missed the point / to Player Default, Prompt: 어떤 인간들은 기계만큼 일관적이려고 열심히 노력해.
#: 02038AAF/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038ABA
msgctxt "0013F5"
msgid "Confusing statement. Recommending integration of robotic parts if desiring robotic consistency."
msgstr "혼란스러운 발언. 로봇 같은 일관성을 원한다면 로봇 부품 통합을 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038ABE
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009B0BC4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038AB1/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038ABE
msgctxt "0013F6"
msgid "...How high is a 500 newton jump?"
msgstr "...500뉴턴으로 뛰면 얼마나 높이 올라가?"

#. List: 2
