#: 02038AB2/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038AB8
msgctxt "0013F9"
msgid "Some humans work hard to be as consistent as machines."
msgstr "어떤 인간들은 기계만큼 일관적이려고 열심히 노력해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
