#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038AB3/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038ABD
msgctxt "0013FB"
msgid "So you want to give robots the ability to improve."
msgstr "그러니까 로봇에게 개선 능력을 주고 싶은 거군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038ABF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
