#. Notes = Tragedy / to Player Default
#: 02038AB6/00016/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_16_TopLevel_Personal_2:02038AC1
msgctxt "0013FD"
msgid "Machine: 500 newtons. Human: 450 newtons. Looping repetition results in increase in human jump force. Machine jump force consistent."
msgstr "기계: 500뉴턴. 인간: 450뉴턴. 반복 루프 결과 인간 도약력 증가. 기계 도약력은 일정."

