#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E42
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00E7CB92
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 내 결정이 자꾸 망설여져.
#: 02038D95/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E42
msgctxt "001414"
msgid "That is natural. The easy decision comes with little regret. The hard ones plant the seeds of \"what if.\""
msgstr "자연스러운 일입니다. 쉬운 결정에는 후회가 적지만, 어려운 결정은 \"만약에\"라는 씨앗을 남기죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E39
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
