#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00DCDC39
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038D96/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E39
msgctxt "001415"
msgid "I'm having second thoughts about my decision."
msgstr "내 결정이 자꾸 망설여져."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E01
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E9B009, 009C9FC7
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 바룬 가문은 테란 함대만큼 적대적이지는 않아., / to Player Default
#: 02038D91/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E01
msgctxt "001416"
msgid "From that lens, one might argue the United Colonies are the most antagonistic of all."
msgstr "그런 관점에서 보면, 식민지 연합이 가장 적대적이라고 주장할 수도 있겠죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020391F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00AA707E
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 시간이 지나면 내가 옳은 선택을 했는지 알 수 있겠지.
#: 020391F4/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:020391F6
msgctxt "001417"
msgid "Will it? Once a choice is made, there is no going back. We will never know what could have been."
msgstr "그럴까요? 선택이 내려지면 되돌릴 수 없습니다. 다른 가능성이 어땠을지는 영원히 알 수 없죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020391F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00AF1AEB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020391F5/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:020391F8
