#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 009BA82D
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 0203969B:020396CD
msgctxt "00142A"
msgid "It's good to finally have some closure."
msgstr "이제야 어느 정도 마음의 정리가 돼서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 00DAD283
#. Notes = Somber, Face: Somber
#: 0203969B:020396CC
msgctxt "00142B"
msgid "I still can't believe he's gone."
msgstr "아직도 그가 세상을 떠났다는 게 믿기지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 00791493
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 0203969B:020396CB
msgctxt "00142C"
msgid "Thanks again for bringing me this."
msgstr "이걸 가져다줘서 다시 한번 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 000B7F97
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0203969B:020396C9
msgctxt "00142D"
msgid "I wasn't expecting anyone."
msgstr "누가 올 줄은 몰랐는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 00FC2343
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 0203969B:020396C8
msgctxt "00142E"
msgid "I think you may be lost..."
msgstr "길을 잘못 든 것 같은데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMConnorWallace
#. SoundFileID = 006FA1BF
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 0203969B:020396C7
msgctxt "00142F"
msgid "Hi there."
msgstr "안녕."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B03
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00286A48, 009A6443, 00D2B90A
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 아버지가 당신의 상관이었나요?, Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 02005AD3/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B03
msgctxt "001430"
msgid "It's sad to think how that mentality changed over the years."
msgstr "세월이 흐르며 그 마음가짐이 어떻게 변했는지 생각하면 슬퍼요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B03
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00286A48, 009A6443, 00D2B90A
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 아버지가 당신의 상관이었나요?, Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 02005AD3/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B03
msgctxt "001431"
msgid "If the agreement didn't work out, he wanted to make sure he did all he could to protect me. "
msgstr "합의가 잘 안 풀릴 경우에도, 그는 저를 보호하기 위해 할 수 있는 모든 일을 해두고 싶어 했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B03
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00286A48, 009A6443, 00D2B90A
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 아버지가 당신의 상관이었나요?, Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed
#: 02005AD3/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B03
msgctxt "001432"
msgid "Not initially, but he pulled strings to make sure I was on his ship when we met with the Freestar Collective."
msgstr "처음부터 그랬던 건 아니지만, 자유항성 공동체와 만날 때 제가 자기 함선에 타도록 손을 써 줬어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005B05
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00AAD9D0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02005AD4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005B05
msgctxt "001433"
msgid "Was your father your superior officer?"
msgstr "아버지가 당신의 상관이었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF2
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 007537AB
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 나라도 누군가를 잃었다면 진절머리가 났을 거야.
#: 02005AD7/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF2
msgctxt "001434"
msgid "The real question is how do you let that loss affect you?"
msgstr "진짜 문제는 그 상실이 당신에게 어떤 영향을 미치게 둘 것이냐예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00D61357, 00C4C259
#. Notes = Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 그 전쟁에서는 수많은 잔혹한 일이 벌어졌어., Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02005AD9/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFC
msgctxt "001435"
msgid "Let's just hope those lessons remain etched in our history."
msgstr "그 교훈들이 우리 역사에 계속 새겨져 있기를 바랄 뿐이에요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00D61357, 00C4C259
#. Notes = Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 그 전쟁에서는 수많은 잔혹한 일이 벌어졌어., Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02005AD9/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFC
msgctxt "001436"
msgid "And thank goodness a lot of tech got banned because of it, and the people responsible were punished accordingly."
msgstr "그리고 그 일로 많은 기술이 금지되고, 책임자들이 그에 맞게 처벌받아서 정말 다행이에요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007077F9, 0062624E, 00124CF9
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 어머니를 잃었다니 유감이야., Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking, Proud with slight sadness. / Confident / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005ADB/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF1
msgctxt "001437"
msgid "She was an engineer, so if anything broke in the house, she insisted on fixing it herself."
msgstr "그분은 엔지니어라서, 집에서 뭐가 고장 나면 꼭 직접 고치려고 했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007077F9, 0062624E, 00124CF9
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 어머니를 잃었다니 유감이야., Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking, Proud with slight sadness. / Confident / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 02005ADB/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF1
msgctxt "001438"
msgid "She insisted on decorating for every holiday. She made the best pie crusts, knew how to fix any household problem..."
msgstr "명절마다 꼭 장식을 하곤 했어요. 파이 크러스트도 최고였고, 집안 문제라면 뭐든 고칠 줄 알았죠..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0020D5BB, 00D0424F, 00838A6A
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 네 아버지가 테란에 남은 건 네 어머니를 잃었기 때문이라고 생각해?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02005AD5/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFD
msgctxt "001439"
msgid "All the anger he kept suppressed just resurfaced, and the Terran view of the Settled Systems just fueled the fire."
msgstr "그가 억눌러 왔던 분노가 한꺼번에 다시 떠올랐고, 개척 성계를 바라보는 테란식 시각이 그 불에 기름을 부었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0020D5BB, 00D0424F, 00838A6A
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 네 아버지가 테란에 남은 건 네 어머니를 잃었기 때문이라고 생각해?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02005AD5/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFD
msgctxt "00143A"
msgid "Once we discovered X-Tech and talk began to circulate of returning, I think it triggered something deep inside. "
msgstr "우리가 X-테크를 발견하고 귀환 이야기가 돌기 시작하자, 그의 깊은 곳에서 뭔가가 건드려진 것 같아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AFD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0020D5BB, 00D0424F, 00838A6A
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 네 아버지가 테란에 남은 건 네 어머니를 잃었기 때문이라고 생각해?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02005AD5/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AFD
msgctxt "00143B"
msgid "I think so, yes. He was so tied up in the war that he never got the chance to properly mourn."
msgstr "네, 그런 것 같아요. 그는 전쟁에 너무 얽매여 있어서 제대로 애도할 기회조차 없었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CCD692
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203969D/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B0
msgctxt "00143C"
msgid "I'd like to ask you about something else, if you don't mind."
msgstr "괜찮다면 다른 것도 좀 물어봐도 될까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001426EC, 006B9C7B
#. Notes = Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 전쟁은 무의미해., Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 02005ADD/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF5
msgctxt "00143D"
msgid "When wars are fought over atrocities, it's understandable, but when they're fought over personal gain, it's unforgivable."
msgstr "잔혹 행위 때문에 벌어지는 전쟁이라면 이해할 수 있지만, 개인의 이득 때문에 벌어지는 전쟁은 용서할 수 없죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02005AF5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001426EC, 006B9C7B
#. Notes = Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Prompt: 전쟁은 무의미해., Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 02005ADD/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:02005AF5
msgctxt "00143E"
msgid "To think we haven't advanced enough to settle things through discussion, to value human life over the pride or selfishness of the leading few."
msgstr "우리가 아직도 대화로 문제를 해결하고, 소수 지도자들의 자존심이나 이기심보다 인간의 생명을 중시할 만큼 발전하지 못했다니요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001B55CB, 0005DD24, 00B83943, 0061F2D8
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 새로 시작하는 건 힘들었나요?, Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0203969E/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396AF
msgctxt "00143F"
msgid "That's when I realized I was going to have to create a whole new identity if I wanted to have anything close to a normal life."
msgstr "그때 깨달았죠. 정상적인 삶에 가까운 것이라도 원한다면 완전히 새로운 신분을 만들어야 한다는 걸요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001B55CB, 0005DD24, 00B83943, 0061F2D8
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 새로 시작하는 건 힘들었나요?, Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0203969E/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396AF
msgctxt "001440"
msgid "They just wrote me off as a delusional conspiracy theorist."
msgstr "그들은 저를 그저 망상에 빠진 음모론자로 치부했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001B55CB, 0005DD24, 00B83943, 0061F2D8
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 새로 시작하는 건 힘들었나요?, Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0203969E/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396AF
msgctxt "001441"
msgid "I tried to go to MAST and tell them the truth, but they wouldn't even let me past the front desk. "
msgstr "MAST에 가서 진실을 말하려 했지만, 안내처도 지나가게 해 주지 않았어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 001B55CB, 0005DD24, 00B83943, 0061F2D8
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 새로 시작하는 건 힘들었나요?, Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0203969E/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396AF
msgctxt "001442"
msgid "Incredibly hard. To the Settled Systems I was dead, a casualty of the Colony War. "
msgstr "믿을 수 없을 만큼 힘들었죠. 개척 성계에서 저는 식민지 전쟁의 전사자로, 이미 죽은 사람이었으니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D59B11
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 괜찮다면 다른 것도 좀 물어봐도 될까요?
#: 0203969C/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B2
msgctxt "001443"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr "물론이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00E57F8E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203969F/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396AD
msgctxt "001444"
msgid "Was it hard to start over?"
msgstr "새로 시작하는 건 힘들었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 005F6F1C, 00EBBD62, 001E70F7
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 떠나고 싶어 하는 사람이 또 있나요?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A0/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396C5
msgctxt "001445"
msgid "After that, outcries became whispers, and soon after... silence."
msgstr "그 후로 외침은 속삭임이 되었고, 얼마 지나지 않아... 침묵이 찾아왔죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 005F6F1C, 00EBBD62, 001E70F7
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 떠나고 싶어 하는 사람이 또 있나요?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A0/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396C5
msgctxt "001446"
msgid "It wasn't long before they were making public examples of dissenters."
msgstr "머지않아 그들은 반대자들을 공개적으로 본보기 삼기 시작했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 005F6F1C, 00EBBD62, 001E70F7
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 떠나고 싶어 하는 사람이 또 있나요?, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A0/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396C5
msgctxt "001447"
msgid "More than you might realize. The fear to speak out is real. "
msgstr "생각하시는 것보다 훨씬 많아요. 목소리를 내는 것에 대한 두려움은 현실이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0060C16B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020396A1/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396C0
msgctxt "001448"
msgid "Are there others who want to leave?"
msgstr "떠나고 싶어 하는 사람이 또 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0097C953, 004E221C, 00741B8A
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 떠나는 게 얼마나 힘들었나요?, Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 020396A2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396BF
msgctxt "001449"
msgid "When I realized there was nothing I could do for my team, I saw my chance to leave and I took it."
msgstr "팀을 위해 제가 할 수 있는 게 없다는 걸 깨달았을 때, 떠날 기회가 보였고 저는 그 기회를 잡았어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0097C953, 004E221C, 00741B8A
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 떠나는 게 얼마나 힘들었나요?, Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 020396A2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396BF
msgctxt "00144A"
msgid "I was on resource patrol when we were attacked by some local wildlife and found myself to be the only survivor."
msgstr "자원 순찰 중이었는데 현지 야생동물의 공격을 받았고, 정신을 차려 보니 저만 살아남아 있었어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0097C953, 004E221C, 00741B8A
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 떠나는 게 얼마나 힘들었나요?, Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 020396A2/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396BF
msgctxt "00144B"
msgid "It wasn't easy. By then, deserters were dealt with... harshly."
msgstr "쉽지는 않았어요. 그때쯤 탈영병은... 혹독하게 처리됐거든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 0082BDC8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020396A3/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396BA
msgctxt "00144C"
msgid "How hard was it to leave?"
msgstr "떠나는 게 얼마나 힘들었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 000A96AB, 0079AD27, 00EFCB4C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B9
msgctxt "00144D"
msgid "But once we discovered X-Tech, the attitudes changed. Some saw it as a way back home and a means to \"correct\" the Settled Systems."
msgstr "하지만 X-테크를 발견하자 태도가 달라졌어요. 어떤 이들은 그것을 고향으로 돌아갈 길이자 개척 성계를 \"바로잡을\" 수단으로 봤죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 000A96AB, 0079AD27, 00EFCB4C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B9
msgctxt "00144E"
msgid "Back then, we were united in our beliefs and thought we could simply live a better life elsewhere."
msgstr "그 당시 우리는 신념으로 하나가 되어 있었고, 다른 곳에서 더 나은 삶을 살 수 있다고 생각했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 000A96AB, 0079AD27, 00EFCB4C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident, Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 020396A4/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B9
msgctxt "00144F"
msgid "For a time, yes. I just finished training when my father told me the plan to abandon the Colony War and leave the Settled Systems."
msgstr "한동안은 그랬죠. 훈련을 막 마쳤을 때, 아버지가 식민지 전쟁을 포기하고 개척 성계를 떠날 계획을 말해 주셨어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006FA58F
#. Notes = / to Connor
#: 020396A5/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_ConnorScene:020396B7
msgctxt "001450"
msgid "Were you part of the Terran Armada?"
msgstr "테란 함대 소속이었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BF910B, 00457058
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 아버지를 육체적으로도 정신적으로도 잃으신 일에 애도를 표합니다., Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 020396A6/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B4
msgctxt "001451"
msgid "I haven't thought about the past in a while now, and this brings me a sense of closure that I've been lacking for a long time."
msgstr "한동안 과거를 떠올리지 않았는데, 이 일로 오래도록 얻지 못했던 매듭을 지은 기분이 들어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BF910B, 00457058
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Prompt: 아버지를 육체적으로도 정신적으로도 잃으신 일에 애도를 표합니다., Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 020396A6/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B4
msgctxt "001452"
msgid "Thank you. And thank you for delivering this. "
msgstr "고마워요. 그리고 이걸 전해 줘서 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008A44A2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020396A7/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B8
msgctxt "001453"
msgid "My condolences on both the physical and mental loss of your father."
msgstr "아버지를 육체적으로도 정신적으로도 잃으신 일에 애도를 표합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 003E0066, 006AD013, 009EF422
#. Notes = Nostalgic sadness. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 그 당시 아버지는 어떤 점에서 훌륭했나요?, Somber / to Player Default
#: 020396A8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B1
msgctxt "001454"
msgid "He was kind, supportive... he loved me... And then bit by bit I watched the words of small minded, extremists turn him into someone I barely recognized."
msgstr "그분은 다정하고, 든든했고... 저를 사랑해 주셨어요... 그런데 편협한 극단주의자들의 말에 조금씩 변해 가더니, 제가 거의 알아볼 수 없는 사람이 되어 버렸죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 003E0066, 006AD013, 009EF422
#. Notes = Nostalgic sadness. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 그 당시 아버지는 어떤 점에서 훌륭했나요?, Somber / to Player Default
#: 020396A8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B1
msgctxt "001455"
msgid "Explaining the rules during batball or futbol games, family dinners with conversations, helping me with homework and making sure I understood it..."
msgstr "배트볼이나 풋볼 경기 중 규칙을 설명해 주고, 가족 식사 자리에서 대화를 나누고, 숙제를 도와주면서 제가 제대로 이해했는지 확인해 주던 것들..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 003E0066, 006AD013, 009EF422
#. Notes = Nostalgic sadness. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Prompt: 그 당시 아버지는 어떤 점에서 훌륭했나요?, Somber / to Player Default
#: 020396A8/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B1
msgctxt "001456"
msgid "He always tried to be present even though the hours weren't ideal in the military."
msgstr "군 복무 시간이 좋지 않았는데도 언제나 곁에 있어 주려고 노력했어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020396B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Z01_ConnorDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Connor
#. SoundFileID = 00B99360
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020396A9/00000/SFTER_Z01_Connor_TL_FatherScene:020396B6
msgctxt "001457"
msgid "What made your father great back then?"
msgstr "그 당시 아버지는 어떤 점에서 훌륭했나요?"

