#: 0203ADF4/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0203AE0E
msgctxt "00147B"
msgid "What just happened?"
msgstr "방금 무슨 일이 일어난 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0058111B
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Cora
#: 0203ADF5/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0203AE0B
msgctxt "00147C"
msgid "Acknowledged. Pausing current processes to relay book..."
msgstr "확인. 책을 재생하기 위해 현재 프로세스를 일시 중지합니다..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE10
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00F04E21
#. Notes = Begging / Pleading / to Delta, Face: Pleading
#: 0203ADF6/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0203AE10
msgctxt "00147D"
msgid "Can't you do this first? Just play it quick."
msgstr "이거 먼저 해 주면 안 돼? 그냥 빨리 틀어 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE04
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
