#. Notes = Almost autopilot / to Cora
#: 0203ADF7/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0203AE04
msgctxt "00147E"
msgid "Denied. Request conflicts with current priorities."
msgstr "거부. 요청이 현재 우선순위와 충돌합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE03
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 0046F1F2
#. Notes = Like pressing play on a CD player / Friendly / to Delta, Face: Friendly
#: 0203ADF8/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0203AE03
msgctxt "00147F"
msgid "Delta, I want to listen to another book."
msgstr "델타, 다른 책 듣고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE05
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00DBBBE7
#. Notes = Defeated / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0203ADF9/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE05
msgctxt "001481"
msgid "...You're no fun."
msgstr "...재미없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE01
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F05579
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Cora
#: 0203ADFA/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE01
msgctxt "001482"
msgid "Request conflicts with Sam Coe's request, quote:"
msgstr "요청이 샘 코의 요청과 충돌합니다. 인용:"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 007B6F63
#. Notes = ANOTHER LOOPHOLE HERE WE GO- / Smirk / to Delta, Face: Smirk
#: 0203ADFB/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE0F
msgctxt "001483"
msgid "But, I wouldn't be alone. You'd be there to protect me."
msgstr "하지만 혼자는 아니잖아. 네가 나를 지켜 줄 거니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00F8832A
#. Notes = Oh come ON / Pleading / to Delta, Face: Pleading
#: 0203ADFC/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE0C
msgctxt "001484"
msgid "What? How come?"
msgstr "뭐? 왜?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0036FB3A
#. Notes = Enjoys denying it / to Cora
#: 0203ADFD/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE0D
msgctxt "001485"
msgid "Denied."
msgstr "거부."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 005F170E
#. Notes = ahHA, a loophole / Happy / to Delta, Face: Happy
#: 0203ADFE/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE0A
msgctxt "001486"
msgid "Sooo, if I asked you to take me on an adventure, would ya?"
msgstr "그으럼, 내가 모험에 데려가 달라고 하면 데려가 줄 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE09
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003CA77E
#. Notes = here we go... / to Cora
#: 0203ADFF/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE09
msgctxt "001487"
msgid "Within reason."
msgstr "합리적인 범위 내에서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AE08
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00300443
#. Notes = Walking up / Thinking / to Delta, Face: Thinking
#: 0203AE00/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01:0203AE08
msgctxt "001488"
msgid "Hey Delta, you have to listen to humans, right?"
msgstr "있잖아 델타, 넌 인간 말을 들어야 하는 거 맞지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 003E4300
#. Notes = Slams door shut as they leave / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0203ADCC/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADE0
msgctxt "001493"
msgid "Yeah, good talk."
msgstr "그래, 좋은 대화였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADDC
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C28278
#. Notes = Genuinely confused / to Sam
#: 0203ADCD/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADDC
msgctxt "001494"
msgid "Confused. You desire to preserve Cora. Equipping her with weaponry-"
msgstr "혼란. 당신은 코라를 보존하기를 원합니다. 그녀에게 무장을 갖추게 하면-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 002AE806
#. Notes = Angry at this, also angry that they even have to tell someone this / Irritated / to Delta, Face: Irritated
#: 0203ADCE/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADE1
msgctxt "001495"
msgid "No guns, no knives, no grenades, none of that."
msgstr "총도, 칼도, 수류탄도 안 돼. 그런 건 전부 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADDD
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 001F9721
#. Notes = Angry at this, also angry that they even have to tell someone this / Irritated / to Delta, Face: Irritated
#: 0203ADCF/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADDD
msgctxt "001496"
msgid "I don't care. You're not doing that. Not anymore. I'm putting my foot down."
msgstr "상관없어. 넌 그러면 안 돼. 이제는 안 돼. 이번엔 내가 확실히 선을 긋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADDA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C6760E
#. Notes = This'll dissolve the situation / to Sam
#: 0203ADD0/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADDA
msgctxt "001497"
msgid "For clarification, Eon was unloaded."
msgstr "명확히 하자면, 이온은 장전되어 있지 않았습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADD9
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 00579090
#. Notes = Angry at this, also angry that they even have to tell someone this / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0203ADD1/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADD9
msgctxt "001498"
msgid "You can't give Cora guns. Sarah just told me she had to stop you from giving her an Eon."
msgstr "코라에게 총을 주면 안 돼. 사라가 방금 네가 코라한테 이온을 주려던 걸 막았다고 하더라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADD6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0097038E
#. Notes = oblivious to their anger / to Sam
#: 0203ADD2/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADD6
msgctxt "001499"
msgid "Proceed."
msgstr "계속하십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADEB
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 005E8B2B
#. Notes = Like a dad walking into their sons room and closing the door / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0203ADD3/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203ADEB
msgctxt "00149A"
msgid "Delta, we need to talk."
msgstr "델타, 얘기 좀 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADD5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 00BD9060
#. Notes = Maybe this robot ain't so bad? / Amused / to Delta, Face: Amused
#: 0203ADC4/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADD5
msgctxt "00149C"
msgid "*Chuckle* Yeah, I'll keep that in mind."
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 그래, 명심할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADEA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 003F0EAF
#. Notes = Completely oblivious to Sam's emotional cocktail they're dealing with / to Sam
#: 0203ADC5/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADEA
msgctxt "00149D"
msgid "Confirmed. Recommending writing down exact verbiage if improvised conversation proves difficult."
msgstr "확인. 즉흥 대화가 어렵다면 정확한 표현을 적어 두는 것을 권장합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 00B6E5BD
#. Notes = Embarrassed at this whole interaction. A cocktail of emotion / Thinking / to Delta, Face: Thinking
#: 0203ADC7/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADE4
msgctxt "00149F"
msgid "No, that's not what I meant. We'll pick this up later, ok? I need time to think this through."
msgstr "아니, 그런 뜻이 아니었어. 이 얘기는 나중에 다시 하자, 알았지? 생각할 시간이 좀 필요해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE8
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FE53E2
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Sam
#: 0203ADC8/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADE8
msgctxt "0014A0"
msgid "Noted: Only allow Cora to handle weaponry when supervised."
msgstr "기록됨: 코라는 감독하에 있을 때만 무기류를 다루도록 허용."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 0016F086
#. Notes = Embarrassed at how angry they were / Apologetic / to Delta, Face: Apologetic
#: 0203ADC9/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADE5
msgctxt "0014A1"
msgid "No, I'm not talking about that. Well, I am. Kind of."
msgstr "아니, 그 얘기를 하는 게 아니야. 뭐, 맞긴 한데. 어느 정도는."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADE3
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 004A8E7F
#. Notes = This'll make them feel better / to Sam
#: 0203ADCA/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADE3
msgctxt "0014A2"
msgid "If Cora possesses weaponry, I am not the source."
msgstr "코라가 무기류를 소지하고 있다면, 나는 그 출처가 아니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADDF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 00D79C60
#. Notes = Walking into their sons room now embarrassed at how angry they were / Neutral / to Delta
#: 0203ADCB/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203ADDF
msgctxt "0014A3"
msgid "Delta, we need to talk."
msgstr "델타, 우리 얘기 좀 해야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
