#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 006ED266
#. Notes = Oh, no, it's not / Tired / to Delta, Face: Tired
#: 0203AD88/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203AD9C
msgctxt "0014A5"
msgid "No, Delta that's not what I meant."
msgstr "아니, 델타. 그런 뜻이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD99
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008B7CC8
#. Notes = Genuine / to Sarah
#: 0203AD89/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203AD99
msgctxt "0014A6"
msgid "Beginning research into emotional manipulation..."
msgstr "감정 조작에 대한 연구 시작..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA3
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 0045173F
#. Notes = This is going well / Friendly / to Delta, Face: Friendly
#: 0203AD8A/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203ADA3
msgctxt "0014A7"
msgid "Isn't it? If you want, we can sit down and I can-"
msgstr "그렇지 않아? 원하면 우리 앉아서 내가-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 002410D1
#. Notes = Did they practice this last night? / Grateful / to Delta, Face: Grateful
#: 0203AD8B/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203ADA0
msgctxt "0014A8"
msgid "Sometimes it's better to be nice and convince them to do what you want instead of just killing them."
msgstr "그냥 죽이는 것보다 친절하게 대하면서 네가 원하는 대로 하도록 설득하는 게 나을 때도 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00BFBF12
#. Notes = Genuine / to Sarah
#: 0203AD8C/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203AD9D
msgctxt "0014A9"
msgid "Interesting hypothesis..."
msgstr "흥미로운 가설..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 001BC024
#. Notes = Did they practice this last night? / Pleading / to Delta, Face: Pleading
#: 0203AD8D/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203AD9B
msgctxt "0014AA"
msgid "What I meant was that all life is important, and I don't think you're solutions are as efficient as you say."
msgstr "내 말은 모든 생명은 소중하고, 네 해결 방식이 네 말처럼 효율적이라고는 생각하지 않는다는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA7
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EE51DA
#. Notes = Oblivious to the situation's emotional standings / to Sarah
#: 0203AD8E/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203ADA7
msgctxt "0014AB"
msgid "Ending \"Later\" timer. Logging..."
msgstr "나중에 타이머 종료. 기록 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 00A90D3A
#. Notes = Did they practice this last night? / Neutral / to Delta
#: 0203AD8F/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203AD9F
msgctxt "0014AC"
msgid "Delta, I've thought about what I was trying to say."
msgstr "델타, 내가 하려던 말에 대해 생각해 봤어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 00DD39B1
#. Notes = Need to rethink tactics / Irritated / to Delta, Face: Irritated
#: 0203AD90/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203ADA1
msgctxt "0014AE"
msgid "Ugh, we'll pick this up later."
msgstr "하, 이 얘기는 나중에 다시 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA2
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009D0AE6
#. Notes = Genuine / to Sarah
#: 0203AD91/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203ADA2
msgctxt "0014AF"
msgid "Confused. If word was intentionally incorrect, why choose it?"
msgstr "혼란. 단어가 의도적으로 틀린 것이라면, 왜 그 단어를 선택했는가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 001D1B6F
#. Notes = Is Sarah used to people being a smartass to her? / Irritated / to Delta, Face: Irritated
#: 0203AD92/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203AD9E
msgctxt "0014B0"
msgid "No that's not-"
msgstr "아니, 그게 아니라-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD9A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 002815F1
#. Notes = Is Sarah used to people being a smartass to her? / Irritated / to Delta, Face: Irritated
#: 0203AD93/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203AD9A
msgctxt "0014B1"
msgid "Wha-? That's not what I meant, Delta. And you know that."
msgstr "뭐-? 그런 뜻이 아니야, 델타. 너도 알고 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD98
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F8C375
#. Notes = Trying to be helpful / to Sarah
#: 0203AD94/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203AD98
msgctxt "0014B2"
msgid "Counterpoint: Modern firearms commonly utilize laser ammunition."
msgstr "반론: 현대 화기는 보편적으로 레이저 탄약을 사용한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 00939BBB
#. Notes = Teacher conference / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0203AD95/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203ADA6
msgctxt "0014B3"
msgid "You're too indifferent about murder. You can't solve every situation with a bullet."
msgstr "넌 살인에 너무 무심해. 모든 상황을 총알로 해결할 수는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0047A27C
#. Notes = Deadpan / to Sarah
#: 0203AD96/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203ADA5
msgctxt "0014B4"
msgid "Elaborate."
msgstr "상세히 설명하라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADA4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 003B2F21
#. Notes = Teacher conference / Serious / to Delta, Face: Serious
#: 0203AD97/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203ADA4
msgctxt "0014B5"
msgid "Delta, I want to talk to you about your attitude regarding killing."
msgstr "델타, 살인에 대한 네 태도에 관해 얘기하고 싶어."

