#. Notes = Wants to end the conversation / to Barrett
#: 0203AD02/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD17
msgctxt "0014E5"
msgid "Correct. Alert: Annoyance levels increased."
msgstr "정확함. 경보: 짜증 수준 상승."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD26
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 001D793A
#. Notes = Genuine, but also it's fun to annoy Delta / Neutral / to Delta
#: 0203AD03/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD26
msgctxt "0014E6"
msgid "Wow, that must be awful. Glad you're taking it in stride."
msgstr "와, 그거 정말 끔찍하겠다. 그래도 담담하게 받아들이고 있다니 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00826A1B
#. Notes = WOAH / Awed / to Delta, Face: Awed
#: 0203AD04/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD1A
msgctxt "0014E7"
msgid "So this conversation, even though in reality it's only been a couple of seconds, has been going on for minutes for you?"
msgstr "그러니까 실제로는 몇 초밖에 안 지났는데, 너한테는 이 대화가 몇 분째 이어지고 있는 거야?"

