#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD12
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000A3FB6
#. Notes = Wants to end the conversation / to Barrett
#: 0203AD05/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD12
msgctxt "0014E8"
msgid "Correct."
msgstr "정확함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD18
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00FC8DF1
#. Notes = Wants to end the conversation / to Barrett
#: 0203AD07/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD18
msgctxt "0014E9"
msgid "Correct."
msgstr "정확함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD27
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 001EC93E
#. Notes = This is insane / Confused / to Delta, Face: Confused
#: 0203AD08/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD27
msgctxt "0014EA"
msgid "So if I'm reading this report right, your perception of time is skewed now. Right?"
msgstr "그러니까 이 보고서를 제대로 읽은 거라면, 지금 네 시간 인식이 왜곡된 거네. 맞지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 006BA26E
#. Notes = Putting pieces together / Thinking / to Delta, Face: Thinking
#: 0203AD06/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203AD1D
msgctxt "0014EB"
msgid "So every moment is longer for you than it is for everyone else..."
msgstr "그러면 너한텐 모든 순간이 다른 사람들보다 더 길게 느껴지는 거네..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 0044CF15
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9F:02039EE1
msgctxt "0014ED"
msgid "I'm sure missing that Freestar Security right now."
msgstr "지금 자유항성 경비대가 정말 그립군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00DB503A
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9F:02039EE0
msgctxt "0014EE"
msgid "I wonder if we can get some reinforcements."
msgstr "지원 병력을 받을 수 있을지 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDF
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 009B4207
#. Notes = Relieved, Face: Relieved
#: 02039E9F:02039EDF
msgctxt "0014EF"
msgid "After that, I'm taking the rest of this day off."
msgstr "이 일이 끝나면 오늘 남은 시간은 쉬어야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDE
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00392594
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9F:02039EDE
msgctxt "0014F0"
msgid "I can't believe I survived that."
msgstr "그걸 살아남았다니 믿기지가 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDD
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00414892
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9F:02039EDD
msgctxt "0014F1"
msgid "Those Terrans will never get their hands on this place."
msgstr "저 테란들은 절대 이곳을 차지하지 못할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDC
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00646942
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9F:02039EDC
msgctxt "0014F2"
msgid "If I never see another Terran it'll be too soon."
msgstr "앞으로 테란은 두 번 다시 안 봐도 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDB
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00DEC69A
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9F:02039EDB
msgctxt "0014F3"
msgid "I bet those Terrans will think twice before coming back here."
msgstr "저 테란들도 여기 다시 오기 전엔 한 번 더 생각하겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EDA
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00D3861B
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9F:02039EDA
msgctxt "0014F4"
msgid "Hopefully, those Terrans won't be back anytime soon."
msgstr "저 테란들이 당분간 다시 안 오길 바라야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED9
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 001BD984
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9F:02039ED9
msgctxt "0014F5"
msgid "It's a good thing you were here."
msgstr "네가 여기 있어서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED8
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00C5920B
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9F:02039ED8
msgctxt "0014F6"
msgid "Thanks for your help."
msgstr "도와줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED6
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00E7E333
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9F:02039ED6
msgctxt "0014F7"
msgid "I wonder how long they'll have us stationed out here. "
msgstr "우리를 여기 얼마나 오래 배치해 둘지 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED5
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 000F3497
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9F:02039ED5
msgctxt "0014F8"
msgid "Let's hope that extractor holds up."
msgstr "저 추출기가 버텨 주길 바라자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED4
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 001D9222
#. Notes = Happy, Face: Happy
#: 02039E9F:02039ED4
msgctxt "0014F9"
msgid "I miss home, but a new discovery is the perfect trade off."
msgstr "고향은 그립지만, 새로운 발견이라면 그만한 보상으로 충분하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED3
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 0034D448
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9F:02039ED3
msgctxt "0014FA"
msgid "To think we've overlooked this resource all this time."
msgstr "그동안 이 자원을 놓치고 있었다니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED2
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 003F3394
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9F:02039ED2
msgctxt "0014FB"
msgid "After X-Tech, I wonder what else is out there to discover."
msgstr "X-테크 다음엔 또 무엇을 발견하게 될지 궁금하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED1
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 006080F2
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9F:02039ED1
msgctxt "0014FC"
msgid "This X-Tech draws all sorts of unsavory types."
msgstr "이 X-테크는 별별 수상한 자들을 다 끌어들이는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ED0
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 005F08CD
#. Notes = Happy, Face: Happy
#: 02039E9F:02039ED0
msgctxt "0014FD"
msgid "It's fascinating to be part of such a new discovery."
msgstr "이렇게 새로운 발견에 함께한다는 건 정말 매력적인 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ECF
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00D8D835
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9F:02039ECF
msgctxt "0014FE"
msgid "This resource has such interesting properties. I hope we can properly utilize it."
msgstr "이 자원은 정말 흥미로운 특성을 지니고 있어. 제대로 활용할 수 있으면 좋겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ECE
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 0011A2C9
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9F:02039ECE
msgctxt "0014FF"
msgid "I sure hope this X-Tech is worth it."
msgstr "이 X-테크가 그만한 가치가 있으면 좋겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ECD
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostFC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale02, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03
#. SoundFileID = 00A9E03D
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02039E9F:02039ECD
msgctxt "001500"
msgid "It's nice being out here away from it all."
msgstr "모든 것에서 벗어나 여기 나와 있으니 좋군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB5
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00194EC5
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EB5
msgctxt "001502"
msgid "This X-Tech sure is in high demand."
msgstr "이 X-테크는 확실히 수요가 많군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB4
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00083D9C
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EB4
msgctxt "001503"
msgid "If our superiors want to keep this X-Tech flowing, they better send some backup."
msgstr "상부가 이 X-테크 공급을 계속 유지하고 싶다면 지원 병력을 좀 보내야 할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB3
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00B91AD2
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9E:02039EB3
msgctxt "001504"
msgid "We better get some extra support after this."
msgstr "이 일이 끝나면 추가 지원을 받아야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB2
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00EF26C6
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9E:02039EB2
msgctxt "001505"
msgid "Impeccable timing."
msgstr "완벽한 타이밍이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 007192A0
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9E:02039EB1
msgctxt "001506"
msgid "That was a nice little distraction, wasn't it? "
msgstr "제법 괜찮은 주의 분산이었지, 안 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB0
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 0047C8B8
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9E:02039EB0
msgctxt "001507"
msgid "Appreciate the assist."
msgstr "지원 고맙다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EAF
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00E24264
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9E:02039EAF
msgctxt "001508"
msgid "The UC owes you."
msgstr "식민지 연합이 네게 빚졌군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EAE
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 0091E194
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9E:02039EAE
msgctxt "001509"
msgid "We always appreciate an extra hand."
msgstr "일손은 언제나 환영이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EAD
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00CA8064
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9E:02039EAD
msgctxt "00150A"
msgid "After that, let's hope those Terrans learned their lesson."
msgstr "이번 일로 그 테란들이 교훈을 얻었길 바라자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EAC
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00971CD8
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9E:02039EAC
msgctxt "00150B"
msgid "Thanks for helping us with our little Terran problem."
msgstr "우리의 사소한 테란 골칫거리를 도와줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 003565F4
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EAA
msgctxt "00150C"
msgid "I hope to hear back on our latest report soon."
msgstr "최근 보고서에 대한 답변이 곧 오면 좋겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA9
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 0065E062
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EA9
msgctxt "00150D"
msgid "I wonder if Ryujin knows about X-Tech. *sigh* They're probably already one step ahead."
msgstr "류진은 X-테크에 대해 알고 있으려나. *한숨* 아마 벌써 한발 앞서 있겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA8
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 006F131C
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EA8
msgctxt "00150E"
msgid "I know our superiors are interested in military applications, but I'm curious about the every day ones."
msgstr "상부가 군사적 활용에 관심 있다는 건 알지만, 난 일상적인 활용 쪽이 궁금해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA7
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00FF3C59
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9E:02039EA7
msgctxt "00150F"
msgid "Military applications are countless."
msgstr "군사적 활용 방안은 셀 수 없이 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA6
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00F1B264
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EA6
msgctxt "001510"
msgid "With this new tech, our military will be unstoppable."
msgstr "이 신기술만 있으면 우리 군은 막을 수 없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA5
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 0016D7B4
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9E:02039EA5
msgctxt "001511"
msgid "The UC military will put this to good use."
msgstr "식민지 연합 군이 이걸 잘 활용할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA4
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00AFFDEE
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9E:02039EA4
msgctxt "001512"
msgid "We need upgraded defenses. I didn't realize this X-Tech would be so \"popular.\""
msgstr "방어시설을 강화해야겠어. 이 X-테크가 이렇게 \"인기\" 있을 줄은 몰랐네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA3
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 005A4638
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EA3
msgctxt "001513"
msgid "I hope we can properly harness the potential of X-Tech."
msgstr "X-테크의 잠재력을 제대로 활용할 수 있으면 좋겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA2
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 00CAD901
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9E:02039EA2
msgctxt "001514"
msgid "X-Tech is turning out to be everything they promised and more."
msgstr "X-테크는 약속했던 것 이상으로 판명되고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostUC
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01
#. SoundFileID = 009A0C9F
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9E:02039EA1
msgctxt "001515"
msgid "*sigh* I miss the city."
msgstr "*한숨* 도시가 그립군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ECB
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00423520
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9D:02039ECB
msgctxt "001517"
msgid "That was some pretty good timing on your part."
msgstr "정말 좋은 때에 와줬군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039ECA
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00A6E226
#. Notes = Relieved, Face: Relieved
#: 02039E9D:02039ECA
msgctxt "001518"
msgid "Let's hope that's the last of them."
msgstr "그게 마지막이길 바라자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC9
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00D869B1
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EC9
msgctxt "001519"
msgid "I hate it when I get pulled out of my focus."
msgstr "집중이 깨지는 건 정말 싫다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC8
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 007B5266
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9D:02039EC8
msgctxt "00151A"
msgid "Still in one piece."
msgstr "아직 멀쩡하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC7
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00FC7641
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EC7
msgctxt "00151B"
msgid "I wonder if Ryujin would consider more reinforcements."
msgstr "류진이 증원 병력을 더 보내는 걸 고려해 줄까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC6
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00443EC1
#. Notes = Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 02039E9D:02039EC6
msgctxt "00151C"
msgid "I've about had it with these Terran disruptions."
msgstr "이 테란들의 방해도 이제 지긋지긋해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC5
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 005F941C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9D:02039EC5
msgctxt "00151D"
msgid "You stopped by just in time."
msgstr "딱 제때 들러줬군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC4
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 002B6BFC
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02039E9D:02039EC4
msgctxt "00151E"
msgid "Thanks for the assist."
msgstr "지원 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC3
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 006BC2A6
#. Notes = Smug, Face: Smug
#: 02039E9D:02039EC3
msgctxt "00151F"
msgid "If the Terrans think they can take this place, they've got another think coming."
msgstr "테란들이 이곳을 차지할 수 있다고 생각한다면, 큰 착각이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC2
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 0058D09B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9D:02039EC2
msgctxt "001520"
msgid "Survival of the fittest, right?"
msgstr "적자생존, 맞지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EC0
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00571AEC
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02039E9D:02039EC0
msgctxt "001521"
msgid "Good thing we have some defenses here. Those Terrans love to pester us."
msgstr "여기 방어시설이 좀 있어서 다행이야. 저 테란들은 우리를 괴롭히는 걸 좋아하거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBF
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 0053F286
#. Notes = Happy, Face: Happy
#: 02039E9D:02039EBF
msgctxt "001522"
msgid "After this, I bet our exploration team will get a lot more funding."
msgstr "이번 일 이후엔 우리 탐사팀이 훨씬 더 많은 자금을 받을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBE
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00E76E09
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EBE
msgctxt "001523"
msgid "There's going to be so many patents after this."
msgstr "이번 일로 특허가 엄청나게 쏟아지겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBD
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00128929
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9D:02039EBD
msgctxt "001524"
msgid "The existence of X-Tech is just a glimpse of what else may lie out there."
msgstr "X-테크의 존재는 저 밖에 또 무엇이 있을지 보여주는 작은 단서일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBC
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 005E09F7
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EBC
msgctxt "001525"
msgid "The applications for X-Tech seem endless."
msgstr "X-테크의 활용 가능성은 끝이 없어 보여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBB
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00D83657
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EBB
msgctxt "001526"
msgid "I wonder what we can utilize here for future development.  "
msgstr "향후 개발에 여기서 무엇을 활용할 수 있을지 궁금하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EBA
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00CA42B9
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02039E9D:02039EBA
msgctxt "001527"
msgid "The Terrans may have discovered X-Tech, but we'll be the ones to advance it."
msgstr "테란이 X-테크를 발견했을지는 몰라도, 발전시키는 건 우리 몫이 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 0052F1C5
#. Notes = Happy, Face: Happy
#: 02039E9D:02039EB9
msgctxt "001528"
msgid "I can't wait to get some of these findings off to R&D."
msgstr "이 발견 사항들을 빨리 연구개발부에 보내고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB8
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00838BF9
#. Notes = Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 02039E9D:02039EB8
msgctxt "001529"
msgid "This X-Tech is going to going to keep Ryujin on top for years to come."
msgstr "이 X-테크 덕분에 류진은 앞으로 몇 년간 정상의 자리를 지킬 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039EB7
#. QuestName = SFTER_DialogueOutpostRI
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale01, SFFL_NPCFGenericFemale04, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 004CFBF8
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02039E9D:02039EB7
msgctxt "00152A"
msgid "Excuse me, I have vital calculations in my head."
msgstr "실례지만, 머릿속에서 중요한 계산 중입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E23
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F970A9
#. Notes = Almost shuddering at the thought of Barrett / to Andreja
#: 02038DF9/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:02038E23
msgctxt "001536"
msgid "Barrett's demeanor results in spikes in annoyance levels. You do not."
msgstr "배럿의 태도는 짜증 수치의 급등을 유발합니다. 당신은 그렇지 않습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADB4
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 002134D0
#. Notes = Almost shuddering at the thought of Barrett / to Andreja
#: 02038DFE/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:0203ADB4
msgctxt "001537"
msgid "Prefer your presence over Barrett's, significantly."
msgstr "배럿보다 당신의 동행을 훨씬 선호합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002590C5
#. Notes = Genuinely surprise/confused / Confused / to Delta, Face: Confused
#: 02038E0E/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:0203ADAA
msgctxt "001538"
msgid "Why? What do you mean?"
msgstr "왜? 무슨 뜻이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E4B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0023BA35
#. Notes = PLEASE DEAR GOD NO / to Andreja
#: 02038E0F/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:02038E4B
msgctxt "001539"
msgid "Incorrect. Recommending cease all Barrett mimicry attempts immediately."
msgstr "부정확합니다. 모든 배럿 모방 시도를 즉시 중단할 것을 권고합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADAF
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 000D3593
#. Notes = Shrugging almost / to Andreja
#: 02038E1D/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:0203ADAF
msgctxt "00153A"
msgid "Counterpoint: No two humans alike. Example: You and Barrett."
msgstr "반론: 같은 인간은 둘도 없습니다. 예시: 당신과 배럿."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E41
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 0036A32D
#. Notes = Almost ashamed? / Grateful / to Delta, Face: Grateful
#: 02038E13/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:02038E41
msgctxt "00153B"
msgid "Hmm, I have been told Barrett can be less...grating. And that I should learn to be more like him."
msgstr "흠, 배럿은 덜... 거슬릴 수 있다는 말을 들었습니다. 그리고 제가 그를 더 닮아야 한다고도 했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADAC
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 002B2C7B
#. Notes = Musing / Neutral / to Delta
#: 02038E1F/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja00_01:0203ADAC
msgctxt "00153C"
msgid "It's strange. You and Vasco are both machines, but you could not be more different."
msgstr "이상하네. 너랑 바스코는 둘 다 기계인데, 이렇게 다를 수가 없잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00BDA9C1
#. Notes = Remembering when she asked Sarah the same thing / Happy / to Delta, Face: Happy
#: 02038DDE/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:0203ADB1
msgctxt "001540"
msgid "*Laughs*"
msgstr "*웃음*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADAB
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00205BE5
#. Notes = Asking for conversation? Discussion? / to Andreja
#: 02038DE0/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:0203ADAB
msgctxt "001541"
msgid "Confused by human custom. Require explanation."
msgstr "인간 관습으로 혼란 발생. 설명이 필요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203ADB5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CEBA62
#. Notes = Asking for conversation? Discussion? / to Andreja
#: 02038DDD/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:0203ADB5
msgctxt "001542"
msgid "When human sneeze event occurs, typical responses include phrase, \"bless you\"."
msgstr "인간에게 재채기 이벤트가 발생하면, 일반적인 응답에는 \"신의 축복을\"이라는 문구가 포함됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E38
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00D55900
#. Notes = Weird to be asked but sure / Question / to Delta, Face: Question
#: 02038DE1/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:02038E38
msgctxt "001543"
msgid "Ok, I will try. What is it?"
msgstr "좋아, 해볼게. 뭐라고 하는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E30
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0091DF86
#. Notes = Neutral / to Andreja
#: 02038DE2/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:02038E30
msgctxt "001544"
msgid "Andreja."
msgstr "안드레자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 004CDD3A
#. Notes = Short Greeting / Neutral / to Delta
#: 02038DE3/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Andreja01_01:02038E2C
msgctxt "001545"
msgid "Delta."
msgstr "델타."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF6
msgctxt "001547"
msgid "Careful now, wouldn't want you to end up looking like me. *Chuckle*"
msgstr "조심해, 나처럼 되고 싶진 않을 테니까. *킥킥 웃음*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030F03
msgctxt "001548"
msgid "Follow me. The land of milk and honey awaits."
msgstr "따라와. 젖과 꿀이 흐르는 땅이 기다리고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5E
msgctxt "001549"
msgid "You're blocking my sun, and I can't say I much appreciate it."
msgstr "네가 내 햇빛을 가리고 있는데, 썩 달갑진 않군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00720E4E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF4D/00000/SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives:0203AF5C
msgctxt "00154A"
msgid "I don't know what you mean by that..."
msgstr "무슨 뜻인지 모르겠는데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5A
msgctxt "00154B"
msgid "Not my best work, but I have plenty of experience with controlled demolition, so you should remain in one piece."
msgstr "최고의 작품은 아니지만, 통제 폭파 경험은 많으니 넌 무사할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5A
msgctxt "00154C"
msgid "Just a little improvised explosive."
msgstr "그냥 작은 급조 폭발물이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF57
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 008F4A80
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF49/00000/SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives:0203AF57
msgctxt "00154D"
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr "이게 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0076FE4D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF4F/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:0203AF5B
msgctxt "00154E"
msgid "I'm investigating the broadcast coming from this location."
msgstr "이 위치에서 송출되는 방송을 조사하고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF60
msgctxt "00154F"
msgid "Off with you now. The sooner we get this done, the sooner I can share with you a world of wonders."
msgstr "이제 어서 가. 이 일을 빨리 끝낼수록, 내가 경이로운 세계를 더 빨리 보여줄 수 있으니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF59
msgctxt "001550"
msgid "No."
msgstr "아니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5D
msgctxt "001551"
msgid "Oh, don't worry about it. It's nothing that concerns you. I'm surprised you were even able to pick up on this frequency."
msgstr "아, 신경 쓰지 마. 너랑은 상관없는 일이야. 네가 이 주파수를 잡아냈다는 게 오히려 놀랍네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF56
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 007EE971
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF4B/00000/SFTER_MS01_0550_BUCKE_GivesExplosives:0203AF56
msgctxt "001552"
msgid "You mean...Like a robot?"
msgstr "그러니까... 로봇처럼?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF5F
msgctxt "001553"
msgid "What I mean to say is, you've taken up my personal space... and it would fill my heart with all kinds of joy, if you'd be so kind as to give it back."
msgstr "내 말은, 네가 내 개인 공간을 차지하고 있다는 거야... 그러니 친절하게 그걸 돌려준다면 내 마음이 온갖 기쁨으로 가득 찰 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF55
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 002C7490
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF51/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:0203AF55
msgctxt "001554"
msgid "What are you talking about? It's the middle of the night."
msgstr "무슨 소리야? 지금 한밤중이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF54
msgctxt "001555"
msgid "Robot? I don't see any robots here. You must be seeing things, friend."
msgstr "로봇? 여기엔 로봇 같은 건 안 보이는데. 헛것을 본 모양이군, 친구."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF58
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0020678E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AF53/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:0203AF58
msgctxt "001556"
msgid "You're pretty articulate for a robot, what's that about?"
msgstr "로봇치고는 말솜씨가 꽤 좋은데, 어떻게 된 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F59
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006797E0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02039F56/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02039F59
msgctxt "001558"
msgid "I'm here to buy."
msgstr "사러 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F5A
msgctxt "001559"
msgid "Welcome Back. Here for some guns?"
msgstr "다시 오셨군요. 총 보러 오셨나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02036E53
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E5CA61, 00C62407
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned, Worried, Face: Worried
#: 02036E4C/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02036E53
msgctxt "00155A"
msgid "Not to mention hurting any innocent civilians in the process."
msgstr "그 과정에서 무고한 민간인에게 피해를 주는 건 말할 것도 없고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039358
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00961B4B
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038D93/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:02039358
msgctxt "00155B"
msgid "One might argue the Terran attack mirrors that of House Va'ruun, when they announced their presence to the Settled Systems."
msgstr "테란의 공격은 바룬 가문이 개척 성계에 자신들의 존재를 알렸을 때와 닮았다고 볼 수도 있겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020391F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00B8A5EB
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038D93/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:020391F7
msgctxt "00155C"
msgid "One might argue the Terran attack mirrors House Va'ruun's appearance so many years ago, so it is interesting to view it from this perspective."
msgstr "테란의 공격이 오래전 바룬 가문의 등장과 닮았다고 볼 수도 있으니, 이런 관점에서 바라보는 것도 흥미롭군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD80
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Andreja
#. SoundFileID = 00EE71D8
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02038DA7/00000/SFTER_COM_Andreja_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD80
msgctxt "00155D"
msgid "I could not help but see the parallels with House Va'ruun."
msgstr "바룬 가문과의 유사점을 떠올리지 않을 수 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E3F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00B4CCC1, 001C9DA1
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Prompt: 사람이 죽으면, 죽는 거지., Neutral / to Player Default
#: 02038DC9/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E3F
msgctxt "00155E"
msgid "Individuals who construct weapons of war are hardly innocent, but they are also afforded certain rights."
msgstr "전쟁 무기를 만드는 이들을 무고하다고 보긴 어렵지만, 그들에게도 일정한 권리는 보장된다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E49
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 009CFFA0, 0018B97F
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 장기적으로는 더 많은 생명을 구하는 거야.
#: 02038DC7/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E49
msgctxt "00155F"
msgid "Yet the cost of war cannot be counted on a spreadsheet."
msgstr "하지만 전쟁의 대가는 스프레드시트로 계산할 수 없다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E49
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 009CFFA0, 0018B97F
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 장기적으로는 더 많은 생명을 구하는 거야.
#: 02038DC7/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E49
msgctxt "001560"
msgid "Statistically, perhaps. It may even make the Terrans think twice about being so reliant on technology."
msgstr "통계적으로는 그럴지도 모르지. 테란들이 기술에 그토록 의존하는 걸 다시 생각하게 만들 수도 있고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 008C604E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02038DC8/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E2D
msgctxt "001561"
msgid "We're saving more lives in the long run."
msgstr "장기적으로는 더 많은 생명을 구하는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E33
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0011E0D3, 003CAA73
#. Notes = Shocked, Face: Shocked, Prompt: 그냥 아무거나 찍어서 골랐어., Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 02038DE8/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E33
msgctxt "001562"
msgid "Surely you must be joking. I would not tolerate such childish methods from a member of Constellation."
msgstr "분명 농담이겠지. 컨스텔레이션 회원이 그런 유치한 방법을 쓰는 건 용납하지 않겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD81
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 001027E8, 0017EE52, 00C1338C
#. Notes = Neutral, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD81
msgctxt "001563"
msgid "And it's possible there were civilian personnel that could've been harmed in the aftermath."
msgstr "그리고 그 여파로 민간 인력이 피해를 입었을 가능성도 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD81
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 001027E8, 0017EE52, 00C1338C
#. Notes = Neutral, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD81
msgctxt "001564"
msgid "But I believe shooting a defenseless target may violate certain statutes."
msgstr "하지만 무방비 상태의 표적을 사격하는 건 특정 법령을 위반할 소지가 있다고 봅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD81
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 001027E8, 0017EE52, 00C1338C
#. Notes = Neutral, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD81
msgctxt "001565"
msgid "I understand the temptation to set the robots to frenzy. They were military weapons, and would be held in military facilities."
msgstr "로봇들을 광분시키고 싶었을 마음은 이해합니다. 그것들은 군용 병기였고, 군사 시설에 배치되어 있었을 테니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02038E09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 006504F6, 000971F3, 003D189F
#. Notes = Neutral, Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02038DDA/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:02038E09
msgctxt "001566"
msgid "I just have some concerns regarding the manner in which we fought them. To have their own devices turn on them may violate ethical boundaries."
msgstr "다만 우리가 그들과 싸운 방식에는 우려가 있습니다. 그들의 장비가 그들 자신을 공격하게 하는 것은 윤리적 경계를 넘을 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 007B59F9
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02038DEC/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7C
msgctxt "001567"
msgid "If you have a moment, I'd like to talk about your decision not to turn the Terran robots against their masters."
msgstr "시간이 된다면, 테란 로봇들을 주인에게 맞서게 하지 않은 당신의 결정에 대해 얘기하고 싶습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 005C097F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AD75/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7E
msgctxt "001568"
msgid "Hopefully those civilians will be grateful for what we did."
msgstr "그 민간인들이 우리가 한 일에 고마워하길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00AB3B51
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 그 민간인들이 우리가 한 일에 고마워하길 바랍니다.
#: 0203AD74/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7F
msgctxt "00156A"
msgid "I'm not sure they'll ever know. But that's not why we did what we did."
msgstr "그들이 알게 될지는 모르겠습니다. 하지만 그래서 우리가 그런 일을 한 건 아니죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0089F3C0
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 맞습니다. 자칫 집단 학살 행위를 저지르는 셈이 될 수도 있었죠.
#: 0203AD78/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7A
msgctxt "00156B"
msgid "And I support your temperance. It would have been easy to mete out your revenge given they brought the war to us."
msgstr "그리고 당신의 절제를 지지합니다. 그들이 우리에게 전쟁을 가져왔으니 복수하기 쉬웠을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00719191
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AD77/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7B
msgctxt "00156C"
msgid "I didn't have enough information to make them frenzy. It was too risky."
msgstr "그들을 광분시키기엔 정보가 부족했어. 너무 위험했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD7D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 000A80A0
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 그들을 광분시키기엔 정보가 부족했어. 너무 위험했지.
#: 0203AD76/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD7D
msgctxt "00156D"
msgid "Agreed. Not to mention it's a war crime to attack a defenseless target."
msgstr "동의합니다. 무방비 상태의 표적을 공격하는 건 전쟁범죄이기도 하니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AD84
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BD53CB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203AD79/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AD84
msgctxt "00156E"
msgid "Yes. It was potentially committing a genocidal act."
msgstr "맞습니다. 자칫 집단 학살 행위를 저지르는 셈이 될 수도 있었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF65
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00852F33
#. Notes = French for out of combat / Neutral, Prompt: 죽은 민간인이 있었다면 대부분 방위 산업체나 군 계약업체 관계자였을 거야. 사실상 군인이지.
#: 0203AF61/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AF65
msgctxt "00156F"
msgid "Yes but even a soldier can't be attacked when \"hors de combat,\" even in times of war."
msgstr "맞습니다. 하지만 전시에도 \"전투 무력화\", 즉 전투 불능 상태인 병사는 공격할 수 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF64
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 006E413D
#: 0203AF62/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AF64
msgctxt "001570"
msgid "Any civilians that died were likely defense and military contractors. Essentially military."
msgstr "죽은 민간인이 있었다면 대부분 방위 산업체나 군 계약업체 관계자였을 거야. 사실상 군인이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF66
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00C7DA4F, 00B2DD9A
#. Notes = Defiant, Face: Defiant, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0203AF63/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AF66
msgctxt "001571"
msgid "Which I may remind you, is a war crime."
msgstr "다시 말하지만, 그것은 전쟁범죄입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF66
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00C7DA4F, 00B2DD9A
#. Notes = Defiant, Face: Defiant, Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0203AF63/00000/SFTER_COM_Sarah_QEvent_TerranArmada:0203AF66
msgctxt "001572"
msgid "Ethically what you did is analogous to shooting defenseless parachutists."
msgstr "윤리적으로 보면 당신이 한 일은 무방비 상태의 낙하산병을 쏜 것과 같습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00217AD5
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF2D
msgctxt "001573"
msgid "Good, now let's get out of here."
msgstr "좋아, 이제 여기서 나가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0010BE83
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF2C
msgctxt "001574"
msgid "The Terrans will definitely feel this loss."
msgstr "테란은 이 손실을 확실히 체감할 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF2B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0094806A
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF2B
msgctxt "001575"
msgid "Glad that's over with. And still time for tea."
msgstr "끝나서 다행이군요. 아직 차 마실 시간도 있고요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF29
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00BE9128
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF29
msgctxt "001576"
msgid "Just knowing this place is gonna blow makes me feel all warm and fuzzy."
msgstr "이곳이 터진다는 걸 생각만 해도 속이 다 후련해지는군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF28
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 008C5C8C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF28
msgctxt "001577"
msgid "Terrans sure are gonna miss this place."
msgstr "테란은 분명 이곳을 그리워하겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF27
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00EE11C1
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF27
msgctxt "001578"
msgid "Let's blow this scrap heap."
msgstr "이 고철더미를 날려 버리자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF25
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 003FAD66
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF25
msgctxt "001579"
msgid "All right, I don't want to stick around here any longer than we have to."
msgstr "좋아, 필요한 것보다 오래 여기 머물고 싶진 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF24
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 008877B1
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF24
msgctxt "00157A"
msgid "Classic engineering. Years to build, but moments to destroy."
msgstr "전형적인 공학이군. 짓는 데는 몇 년, 무너뜨리는 데는 한순간."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF23
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0038D962
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF23
msgctxt "00157B"
msgid "And that's the end of that. Time to get out of here. "
msgstr "이걸로 끝이군. 이제 여기서 나갈 시간이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF21
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0032C2A7
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF21
msgctxt "00157C"
msgid "Operation neutralized."
msgstr "작전 무력화 완료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF20
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C29DC3
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF20
msgctxt "00157D"
msgid "We must go before this place takes us with it."
msgstr "이곳이 우리까지 집어삼키기 전에 가야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0014650D
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF17/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203AF1F
msgctxt "00157E"
msgid "Mission complete."
msgstr "임무 완료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF3D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F9928B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF3D
msgctxt "00157F"
msgid "All right. Let's put this beast out of commission."
msgstr "좋아. 이 괴물을 작동 불능으로 만들자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 007D3F39
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF3C
msgctxt "001580"
msgid "Here we go again."
msgstr "또 시작이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF3B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00B4D670
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF3B
msgctxt "001581"
msgid "Let's make this quick, shall we?"
msgstr "빨리 끝내죠, 어때요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF39
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0030D81B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF39
msgctxt "001582"
msgid "Do you think they'll be happy to see us?"
msgstr "저들이 우리를 반겨 줄까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF38
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0057B9D5
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF38
msgctxt "001583"
msgid "Hope those Terrans have good insurance."
msgstr "저 테란들에게 보험이 잘 들어 있길 바라야겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF37
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0046D997
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF37
msgctxt "001584"
msgid "Let's shut her down."
msgstr "이 녀석을 꺼 버리죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF35
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0069280F
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF35
msgctxt "001585"
msgid "I hope you're ready for more robots."
msgstr "로봇을 더 상대할 준비가 됐길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF34
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00BFB38F
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF34
msgctxt "001586"
msgid "Time to throw a wrench in production."
msgstr "이제 생산에 차질을 줄 시간입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF33
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00A6C08E
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF33
msgctxt "001587"
msgid "Let's get to work."
msgstr "일하러 가죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF31
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0007975A
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF31
msgctxt "001588"
msgid "Time to shut this place down."
msgstr "이곳을 폐쇄할 시간입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF30
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00109BC3
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF30
msgctxt "001589"
msgid "Let us put an end to this."
msgstr "이제 끝을 내죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF2F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00B7F0FB
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203AF18/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF2F
msgctxt "00158A"
msgid "Neutralization underway."
msgstr "무력화 진행 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00277545
#. Notes = Looking at a Terran Assault Platform for the first time. Similar to an oil rig. / Surprised, Face: Surprised
#: 0203AF19/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF1D
msgctxt "00158B"
msgid "This is quite the operation."
msgstr "상당한 규모의 시설이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00CD1B4F
#. Notes = Looking at a Terran Assault Platform for the first time. Similar to an oil rig. / Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 0203AF19/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF1C
msgctxt "00158C"
msgid "Those Terrans sure have been busy."
msgstr "저 테란들이 꽤 바쁘게 움직였군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203AF1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultPlatformGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 001EA5A2
#. Notes = Looking at a Terran Assault Platform for the first time. Similar to an oil rig. / Impressed, Face: Impressed
#: 0203AF19/00000/SFTER_INC_APG01_Companion_StartScene:0203AF1B
msgctxt "00158D"
msgid "Now that's a feat of engineering."
msgstr "이거야말로 공학의 위업이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008E95DF
#. Notes = / to Roxane_02
#: 02015ED9/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane:02039F0D
msgctxt "001591"
msgid "Do you mind if I ask you some personal questions?"
msgstr "개인적인 질문을 좀 해도 될까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_06_TopLevel_WINtxt
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 0083224E
#. Notes = Smirking / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0202AD28/00006/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_06_TopLevel_WINtxt:02039F0C
msgctxt "001592"
msgid "And you already knew the answers. I wonder why..."
msgstr "그리고 넌 이미 답을 알고 있었어. 왜 그랬을까..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00C63257
#. Notes = Smirking, she's onto the player's game / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02039F0A/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane:02039F0E
msgctxt "001593"
msgid "I told you, you're only getting one answer from me. The rest you have to do yourself."
msgstr "말했잖아. 나한테서 얻을 답은 하나뿐이야. 나머지는 직접 해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane_02
#. SoundFileID = 00DF8CB3
#. Notes = Smirking, she's onto the player's game / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02039F0B/00002/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q02_02_MasterTopLevel_Roxane:02039F0F
msgctxt "001594"
msgid "This is clever, so I'll give you one answer. The rest is up to you."
msgstr "영리하네. 그러니 답 하나는 줄게. 나머지는 네 몫이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B400
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0080163F
#. Notes = Annoyed. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020345C7:0203B400
msgctxt "0015A5"
msgid "You're wasting my time."
msgstr "내 시간 낭비하지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 005D6B62
#. Notes = Annoyed. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020345C7:0203B3FF
msgctxt "0015A6"
msgid "What? Do you have nothing else to say?"
msgstr "뭐야? 더 할 말 없어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00B0FF60
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3F7
msgctxt "0015A7"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "음?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0028F359
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3F6
msgctxt "0015A8"
msgid "Are you alright?"
msgstr "괜찮아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00E48D08
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3F5
msgctxt "0015A9"
msgid "Did you lose your train of thought?"
msgstr "무슨 말 하려던 건지 잊었어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00AA05DE
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345C7:0203B3F4
msgctxt "0015AA"
msgid "Everything okay?"
msgstr "다 괜찮아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00AF7BFD
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345C7:0203B3F3
msgctxt "0015AB"
msgid "Cat got your tongue?"
msgstr "말문이 막혔어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0035CF83
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345C7:0203B3F2
msgctxt "0015AC"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr "여보세요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00505968
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3F1
msgctxt "0015AD"
msgid "Speak."
msgstr "말해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 004668BA
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3F0
msgctxt "0015AE"
msgid "Go on. Say it."
msgstr "계속해. 말해 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00D984CB
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345C7:0203B3EF
msgctxt "0015AF"
msgid "Were you even listening?"
msgstr "듣고 있긴 했어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00EB448B
#. Notes = Nervous as she's still in the facility. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 020345C7:0203B3EE
msgctxt "0015B0"
msgid "If we're not going to talk, we should move."
msgstr "대화할 게 아니라면 움직이자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3ED
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00A6F9E9
#. Notes = Nervous as she's still in the facility. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 020345C7:0203B3ED
msgctxt "0015B1"
msgid "Aren't you going to say something?"
msgstr "뭔가 말할 생각 없어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B46B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00040A20
#. Notes = Friendly and joking. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B46B
msgctxt "0015B2"
msgid "Tracy has lightened up recently since the Terrans' defeat. Not by much, but it's a nice change of pace."
msgstr "테란이 패배한 뒤로 트레이시가 최근 좀 누그러졌어요. 아주 조금이지만, 좋은 기분 전환이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B46A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 001E21C5
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B46A
msgctxt "0015B3"
msgid "Even though the Terrans are gone, I do hope we'll work together again one day."
msgstr "테란은 사라졌지만, 언젠가 다시 함께 일할 수 있으면 좋겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B469
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00A65D1F
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B469
msgctxt "0015B4"
msgid "Hope you don't find any more Terrans out there. Though, if you do, I'm sure you'll tell us right away."
msgstr "밖에서 테란을 더 발견하지 않길 바랍니다. 그래도 발견한다면, 바로 우리에게 알려 줄 거라고 믿습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B467
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 004F5FC6
#. Notes = Professional, but much more relaxed. His tone is softer thinking of his family. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020345CB:0203B467
msgctxt "0015B5"
msgid "Now that the Terrans are defeated, maybe I can visit home. I miss my family."
msgstr "테란이 패배했으니, 이제 고향에 들를 수 있을지도 모르겠습니다. 가족이 그립거든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B466
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 006D3092
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly more relaxed. / Relieved, Face: Relieved
#: 020345CB:0203B466
msgctxt "0015B6"
msgid "Now that the Terrans are defeated, let's hope it's quiet out there. At least for a bit."
msgstr "테란이 패배했으니, 바깥이 조용해지길 바랍니다. 적어도 잠시라도요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B465
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 007713BD
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B465
msgctxt "0015B7"
msgid "If you hear of any new Terran activity, let us know."
msgstr "테란의 새로운 움직임을 듣게 되면 알려 주십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B463
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00E907AD
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B463
msgctxt "0015B8"
msgid "Have you spotted any Terran stragglers out there?"
msgstr "밖에서 테란 잔당을 본 적 있습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B462
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0079E5F7
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B462
msgctxt "0015B9"
msgid "If you hear of any more threats in the Settled Systems, please let us know."
msgstr "개척 성계에 또 다른 위협이 있다는 소식을 들으면, 우리에게 알려 주십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B461
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 002088E9
#. Notes = Starts serious, but throws out a joke in the second sentence. A bit of old woman being silly. Says it almost innocently. / Smug, Face: Smug
#: 020345CB:0203B461
msgctxt "0015BA"
msgid "Do remember to keep our whereabouts secret. It would be a shame if you mysteriously went missing."
msgstr "우리 위치는 반드시 비밀로 해 두십시오. 당신이 의문의 실종을 당하면 참 안타까운 일이니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B45F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00D06EE6
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B45F
msgctxt "0015BB"
msgid "Hope you're doing well."
msgstr "잘 지내고 있길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B45E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00F7D9F2
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B45E
msgctxt "0015BC"
msgid "Good to see you."
msgstr "만나서 반갑습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B45D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0066E991
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B45D
msgctxt "0015BD"
msgid "Hello there."
msgstr "안녕하세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B45C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00DAE316
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B45C
msgctxt "0015BE"
msgid "It's always a pleasure to see you."
msgstr "당신을 뵙는 건 언제나 즐겁습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B45A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0036C10D
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B45A
msgctxt "0015BF"
msgid "We were lucky to find you, you know?"
msgstr "우리가 당신을 찾은 건 정말 행운이었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B459
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 007882C5
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B459
msgctxt "0015C0"
msgid "Find anything new on the Terrans?"
msgstr "테란에 관해 새로 알아낸 건 있습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B458
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00D9F0E3
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B458
msgctxt "0015C1"
msgid "Roxane has been quite the asset. It was wise of us to find her."
msgstr "록산은 상당한 전력이 되어 주었습니다. 그녀를 찾아낸 건 현명한 판단이었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B456
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 002267E0
#. Notes = Professional and but a bit friendly. / Smug, Face: Smug
#: 020345CB:0203B456
msgctxt "0015C2"
msgid "Good to see you're still kicking."
msgstr "아직 멀쩡한 모습을 보니 반갑군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B455
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00C99BFB
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B455
msgctxt "0015C3"
msgid "Anything to report?"
msgstr "보고할 사항 있습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B454
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 008F1977
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B454
msgctxt "0015C4"
msgid "I hope you're keeping an eye on that robot of yours."
msgstr "당신의 그 로봇을 잘 감시하고 있길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B452
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 008C1A5F
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B452
msgctxt "0015C5"
msgid "Be careful out there. Until the Terrans are destroyed, none of us are safe."
msgstr "밖에서는 조심하십시오. 테란이 파괴되기 전까지 우리 중 누구도 안전하지 않습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B451
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 003FF01A
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B451
msgctxt "0015C6"
msgid "Have any news on the Terrans?"
msgstr "테란에 관한 소식이 있습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B450
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00A395CB
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B450
msgctxt "0015C7"
msgid "The more we learn about the Terrans, the better, all right?"
msgstr "우리가 테란에 대해 많이 알수록 좋습니다. 알겠죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B44E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0074C1E5
#. Notes = Spiteful towards the Player. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020345CB:0203B44E
msgctxt "0015C8"
msgid "Can you make this quick?"
msgstr "빨리 끝내 주실 수 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B44D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00B47290
#. Notes = Spiteful towards the Player. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020345CB:0203B44D
msgctxt "0015C9"
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr "원하는 게 뭐죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B44C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00C82D98
#. Notes = Spiteful towards the Player. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020345CB:0203B44C
msgctxt "0015CA"
msgid "Oh. It's you."
msgstr "아. 당신이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B44B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00FA954F
#. Notes = Spiteful towards the Player. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020345CB:0203B44B
msgctxt "0015CB"
msgid "I'm surprised you wanted to visit me."
msgstr "당신이 날 찾아오고 싶어 했다니 의외네요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B44A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0065D355
#. Notes = Distrusting of the Player. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 020345CB:0203B44A
msgctxt "0015CC"
msgid "You're keeping an eye on Delta, right?"
msgstr "델타를 잘 살펴보고 있죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B449
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 008EA497
#. Notes = Frustrated and annoyed. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020345CB:0203B449
msgctxt "0015CD"
msgid "I'm starting to feel a bit mad being cooped up here. I need a vacation."
msgstr "여기 갇혀 있으니 조금 미칠 것 같아요. 휴가가 필요해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B448
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00080301
#. Notes = Extremely angry at the player. However, she knows there is nothing she can do, so she will simply be spiteful towards them. / VeryAngry, Face: VeryAngry
#: 020345CB:0203B448
msgctxt "0015CE"
msgid "To think I actually trusted you. Just, what do you want?"
msgstr "내가 당신을 믿었다니. 그래서, 원하는 게 뭐죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B446
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0031946E
#. Notes = Friendly, but also thinking. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 020345CB:0203B446
msgctxt "0015CF"
msgid "I should really take time to back up Delta's data at some point. Assuming they don't mind."
msgstr "언젠가 시간을 내서 델타의 데이터를 백업해야겠어요. 델타가 싫어하지 않는다면요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B445
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00391832
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B445
msgctxt "0015D0"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr "안녕하세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B444
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0073CF74
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B444
msgctxt "0015D1"
msgid "Are you staying safe out there?"
msgstr "밖에서 안전하게 지내고 있죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B443
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 006A3315
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B443
msgctxt "0015D2"
msgid "Did you need something?"
msgstr "필요한 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B442
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 007F2176
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B442
msgctxt "0015D3"
msgid "I don't want this to be awkward, but thank you for coming to visit me."
msgstr "어색하게 만들고 싶진 않지만, 찾아와 줘서 고마워요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B441
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0015C005
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B441
msgctxt "0015D4"
msgid "I've been starting to feel quite a bit of cabin fever. One day you have to tell me how things are going outside of here."
msgstr "슬슬 꽤 답답해지기 시작했어요. 언젠가 밖은 어떻게 돌아가는지 꼭 들려줘요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B440
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00237CBF
#. Notes = Friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B440
msgctxt "0015D5"
msgid "I hope Delta is performing well."
msgstr "델타가 잘 해내고 있길 바라요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B43F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00B034A8
#. Notes = Grateful and relieved the Terrans are defeated. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020345CB:0203B43F
msgctxt "0015D6"
msgid "I'm sure this goes without saying, but thank you. I just hope we don't hear from the Terrans again."
msgstr "말 안 해도 알겠지만, 고마워요. 다시는 테란 소식을 듣지 않았으면 좋겠네요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B43D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0092FD75
#. Notes = Though safe in Anchorpoint, she is still tired in general. Though she is relieved, the emotion doesn't come all the way through. / Relieved, Face: Relieved
#: 020345CB:0203B43D
msgctxt "0015D7"
msgid "It's good to see you. Lets me know the Terrans haven't gotten you or anything."
msgstr "만나서 반가워요. 테란이 당신까지 잡아가진 않았다는 뜻이니까요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B43C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00CA430E
#. Notes = Though safe in Anchorpoint, she is still tired in general. Though she is apologetic, the emotion doesn't come all the way through. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 020345CB:0203B43C
msgctxt "0015D8"
msgid "I hate to think I've made your job harder with the robots I worked on at the factory. Sorry about that."
msgstr "공장에서 내가 만든 로봇들 때문에 당신 일이 더 어려워졌다고 생각하면 괴로워요. 미안해요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B43B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00C70BF1
#. Notes = Though safe in Anchorpoint, she is still tired in general. Though she is curious, the emotion doesn't come all the way through. / Stern, Face: Stern
#: 020345CB:0203B43B
msgctxt "0015D9"
msgid "Have you learned anything new on the Terrans?"
msgstr "테란에 대해 새로 알아낸 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B439
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00D282DE
#. Notes = Mentally exhausted and just wanting to be out of the Terran facility. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 020345CB:0203B439
msgctxt "0015DA"
msgid "Can we keep moving?"
msgstr "계속 움직이면 안 될까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B438
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00787D87
#. Notes = Mentally exhausted and just wanting to be out of the Terran facility. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 020345CB:0203B438
msgctxt "0015DB"
msgid "We should keep going, okay?"
msgstr "계속 가야 해요, 알겠죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B437
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00CF4BBA
#. Notes = Mentally exhausted and just wanting to be out of the Terran facility. / Somber, Face: Somber
#: 020345CB:0203B437
msgctxt "0015DC"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr "흠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B435
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 005D9D05
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly more relaxed. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 020345CB:0203B435
msgctxt "0015DD"
msgid "How is it in the star sea?"
msgstr "별바다는 어때요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B434
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00046E7F
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly more relaxed. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 020345CB:0203B434
msgctxt "0015DE"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "네?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B433
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 007CB97E
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly more relaxed. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 020345CB:0203B433
msgctxt "0015DF"
msgid "Did you need something?"
msgstr "필요한 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B432
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 008DFCDA
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly more relaxed. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 020345CB:0203B432
msgctxt "0015E0"
msgid "Good to see you again."
msgstr "다시 보니 반갑네요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B430
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0075EAC4
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly amused. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 020345CB:0203B430
msgctxt "0015E1"
msgid "It's a good thing you brought Miss Bourreau to us. She has proven herself to be quite helpful."
msgstr "부로 씨를 우리에게 데려온 건 잘한 일이에요. 꽤 큰 도움이 되고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B42F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00345698
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B42F
msgctxt "0015E2"
msgid "I hope you're staying safe in the star sea."
msgstr "별바다에서 무사히 지내고 있길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B42E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00B0D578
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B42E
msgctxt "0015E3"
msgid "Find anything new on the Terrans?"
msgstr "테란에 대해 새로 알아낸 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B42C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0009E60D
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B42C
msgctxt "0015E4"
msgid "It's not safe for that roboticist to be in Terran hands. The sooner you locate her, the better."
msgstr "그 로봇공학자가 테란 손에 있는 건 위험합니다. 빨리 찾아낼수록 좋습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B42B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00E8CFFC
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B42B
msgctxt "0015E5"
msgid "With that roboticist's help we may be able to figure out how to combat the Terrans."
msgstr "그 로봇공학자의 도움을 받으면 테란에 맞설 방법을 알아낼 수 있을지도 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B42A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00B5A565
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B42A
msgctxt "0015E6"
msgid "Make sure to bring that roboticist back here once you retrieve her."
msgstr "그 로봇공학자를 구출하는 대로 반드시 여기로 데려오세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B429
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 005C514E
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B429
msgctxt "0015E7"
msgid "Hopefully, with your help we can get this whole Terran mess under control."
msgstr "당신의 도움으로 이 테란 사태를 통제할 수 있길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B428
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0050FCF3
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B428
msgctxt "0015E8"
msgid "Learn anything new?"
msgstr "새로 알아낸 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B427
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 002C7212
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:0203B427
msgctxt "0015E9"
msgid "I hope the little spat between me and Tracy didn't paint us in an unprofessional light. Think of us as passionate."
msgstr "나와 트레이시 사이의 사소한 말다툼 때문에 우리가 프로답지 않게 보이지 않았으면 좋겠네요. 열정이 넘친다고 생각해 주세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B426
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00DE16ED
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B426
msgctxt "0015EA"
msgid "How does it go in the field?"
msgstr "현장 상황은 어떤가요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B425
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00EDB38B
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B425
msgctxt "0015EB"
msgid "Once we have that roboticist we can plan our next move."
msgstr "그 로봇공학자만 확보하면 다음 움직임을 계획할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B424
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 0065C019
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 020345CB:0203B424
msgctxt "0015EC"
msgid "Have anything to report on?"
msgstr "보고할 게 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B423
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00170D9E
#. Notes = Determined, but with a mix of worry and anger. / Concentrating, Face: Concentrating
#: 020345CB:0203B423
msgctxt "0015ED"
msgid "Is there something wrong?"
msgstr "문제가 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B422
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00D70524
#. Notes = Determined, but with a mix of worry and anger. / Concentrating, Face: Concentrating
#: 020345CB:0203B422
msgctxt "0015EE"
msgid "We can't afford to stop here."
msgstr "여기서 멈출 여유가 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B421
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
