msgid "This has all gone on long enough."
msgstr "이쯤이면 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00AA8A80
#. Notes = In combat. Angry, yet sounds calculated. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D5
msgctxt "001621"
msgid "I'm losing my patience."
msgstr "슬슬 인내심이 바닥나고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00B69FD8
#. Notes = In combat. Angry, yet sounds calculated. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D4
msgctxt "001622"
msgid "You can still surrender."
msgstr "아직 항복할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00186547
#. Notes = In combat. Angry, yet sounds calculated. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D3
msgctxt "001623"
msgid "We can't let you leave here. Understand?"
msgstr "널 여기서 내보낼 순 없어. 알겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00495839
#. Notes = In combat. Angry, yet sounds calculated. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D2
msgctxt "001624"
msgid "You've made a foolish decision here today."
msgstr "오늘 여기서 어리석은 결정을 했군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00F34254
#. Notes = In combat. Annoyed. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D1
msgctxt "001625"
msgid "Nothing can save you now."
msgstr "이제 널 구할 건 아무것도 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 006F65CB
#. Notes = In combat. Annoyed. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4D0
msgctxt "001626"
msgid "A shame things didn't go differently."
msgstr "이렇게 되지 않을 수도 있었는데, 유감이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 003F72C4
#. Notes = In combat. Annoyed. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CF
msgctxt "001627"
msgid "This wasn't your smartest decision."
msgstr "그리 현명한 결정은 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0011C0C8
#. Notes = In combat. Annoyed. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CE
msgctxt "001628"
msgid "End of the line."
msgstr "여기서 끝이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0035989C
#. Notes = In combat. Annoyed. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CD
msgctxt "001629"
msgid "I'm usually open to making a deal, but not for this."
msgstr "보통은 거래에 열려 있지만, 이건 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 0035C8BC
#. Notes = In combat. Angry. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CC
msgctxt "00162A"
msgid "You're starting to make me mad."
msgstr "슬슬 날 화나게 하는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00A581D1
#. Notes = In combat. Angry. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CB
msgctxt "00162B"
msgid "It's you against all of us. You like those odds that much?"
msgstr "너 혼자 우리 모두를 상대하는 거야. 그 확률이 그렇게 마음에 드나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 000FC392
#. Notes = In combat. Angry. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4CA
msgctxt "00162C"
msgid "You're going to regret this!"
msgstr "후회하게 될 거야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00B4A123
#. Notes = In combat. Angry. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4C9
msgctxt "00162D"
msgid "You think I'm just going to let you off the hook?"
msgstr "내가 그냥 봐줄 거라고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00ABC004
#. Notes = In combat. Angry. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 020345C3:0203B4C8
msgctxt "00162E"
msgid "You won't live to see tomorrow!"
msgstr "넌 내일을 보지 못할 거야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 003F1EA3
#. Notes = Fighting, but scared of being part of the fight. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C3:0203B4C7
msgctxt "00162F"
msgid "Walk away, alright? I want you to walk away."
msgstr "물러나, 알겠어? 그냥 물러나."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 003A7855
#. Notes = Fighting, but scared of being part of the fight. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C3:0203B4C6
msgctxt "001630"
msgid "This doesn't have to be the end for either of us."
msgstr "우리 둘 다 여기서 끝낼 필요는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 001E4AC3
#. Notes = Fighting, but scared of being part of the fight. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C3:0203B3D6
msgctxt "001631"
msgid "We can both still walk away."
msgstr "우리 둘 다 아직 물러날 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00F81AFA
#. Notes = Fighting, but scared of being part of the fight. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C3:0203B3D5
msgctxt "001632"
msgid "This is your fault, understand?"
msgstr "이건 네 탓이야, 알겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00FB4916
#. Notes = Fighting, but scared of being part of the fight. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C3:0203B3D4
msgctxt "001633"
msgid "I didn't want to do any of this!"
msgstr "난 이런 짓 하고 싶지 않았어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0077828C
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4E1
msgctxt "001634"
msgid "I need to fall back."
msgstr "뒤로 빠져야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0092ECA8
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4E0
msgctxt "001635"
msgid "I'm hit!"
msgstr "맞았어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0060B445
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DF
msgctxt "001636"
msgid "Dammit!"
msgstr "젠장!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00AA73FF
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DE
msgctxt "001637"
msgid "You won't be lucky like that for long."
msgstr "그런 행운은 오래 못 가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0061573C
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DD
msgctxt "001638"
msgid "I don't get paid enough for this."
msgstr "이럴 만큼 돈을 받진 않는다고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00F476FF
#. Notes = Hit in combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DC
msgctxt "001639"
msgid "Gh! That was unpleasant."
msgstr "윽! 기분 더럽군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00015773
#. Notes = Hit during combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DB
msgctxt "00163A"
msgid "You're going to regret that."
msgstr "그거 후회하게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 0075E03B
#. Notes = Hit during combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4DA
msgctxt "00163B"
msgid "I won't let you get another hit like that in again."
msgstr "다시는 그런 식으로 맞히게 두지 않겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00F990D4
#. Notes = Hit during combat. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4D9
msgctxt "00163C"
msgid "Gh! Lucky hit."
msgstr "윽! 운 좋게 맞혔군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0037DB23
#. Notes = Hit in combat / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4D8
msgctxt "00163D"
msgid "Why are you doing this?"
msgstr "왜 이러는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 006103A2
#. Notes = Hit in combat / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B4D7
msgctxt "00163E"
msgid "Delta! Help!"
msgstr "델타! 도와줘!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00144A9B
#. Notes = Hit in combat / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B3D3
msgctxt "00163F"
msgid "Stop, please!"
msgstr "그만해, 제발!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00B60A72
#. Notes = Hit in combat / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B3D2
msgctxt "001640"
msgid "Shit!"
msgstr "젠장!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0013E72A
#. Notes = Hit in combat / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C4:0203B3D1
msgctxt "001641"
msgid "Grgh!"
msgstr "으윽!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0046E50B
#. Notes = In facility. Worried for Delta. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B4C5
msgctxt "001642"
msgid "Delta! Be careful!"
msgstr "델타! 조심해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00E1B4B9
#. Notes = In facility. While scared and angry, still trying to rally Player and Delta. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B4C4
msgctxt "001643"
msgid "Don't let your guard down!"
msgstr "방심하지 마!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 001B8AA8
#. Notes = In facility. While scared and angry, still trying to rally Player and Delta. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3CD
msgctxt "001644"
msgid "We can't let this end here. "
msgstr "여기서 끝나게 둘 순 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00119316
#. Notes = In facility. Siccing Delta on her attacker. Angry and scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3CC
msgctxt "001645"
msgid "Get them, Delta!"
msgstr "놈들을 잡아, 델타!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 009FF99A
#. Notes = In facility. Siccing Delta on her attacker. Angry and scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3CB
msgctxt "001646"
msgid "Go, Delta, go!"
msgstr "가, 델타, 가!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0097D78F
#. Notes = Fleeing from enemy. Scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3CA
msgctxt "001647"
msgid "You don't have to do this!"
msgstr "이럴 필요 없어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 003D0465
#. Notes = Fleeing from enemy. Scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3C9
msgctxt "001648"
msgid "I don't want to fight you, please!"
msgstr "너랑 싸우고 싶지 않아, 제발!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00D1EC49
#. Notes = Fleeing from enemy. Scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3C8
msgctxt "001649"
msgid "Please, stop!"
msgstr "제발, 멈춰!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00EAED9D
#. Notes = Fleeing from enemy. Scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3C7
msgctxt "00164A"
msgid "I can't die here!"
msgstr "여기서 죽을 순 없어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00F6AE5B
#. Notes = Fleeing from enemy. Scared. / Afraid, Face: Afraid
#: 020345C5:0203B3C6
msgctxt "00164B"
msgid "Watch out!"
msgstr "조심해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B407
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00D236C9
#. Notes = Dying. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C6:0203B407
msgctxt "00164C"
msgid "Gh..."
msgstr "윽..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B406
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00792F6C
#. Notes = Dying. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C6:0203B406
msgctxt "00164D"
msgid "It wasn't suppose to go this way."
msgstr "이렇게 될 일이 아니었는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B405
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 005CC79A
#. Notes = Dying, but doesn't realize the gravity till it's too late. / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C6:0203B405
msgctxt "00164E"
msgid "Shit... I got hit pretty good..."
msgstr "젠장... 꽤 제대로 맞았어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B404
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 007DA4AD
#. Notes = Dying / InPain, Face: InPain
#: 020345C6:0203B404
msgctxt "00164F"
msgid "Delta, I'm sorry..."
msgstr "델타, 미안해..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B402
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_STANDARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00539063
#. Notes = Happy. / Happy / to Delta, Face: Happy
#: 0203B347/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_STANDARD:0203B402
msgctxt "001650"
msgid "And that does it."
msgstr "이걸로 끝이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_STANDARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004536D5
#. Notes = Proud of herself and enjoyed working on Delta. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy
#: 0203B346/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_STANDARD:0203B3C5
msgctxt "001651"
msgid "Delta's EMP abilities should work far better than before. Thank you for this. It gives me additional data to research."
msgstr "델타의 전자기 펄스 능력이 전보다 훨씬 잘 작동할 겁니다. 도와줘서 고마워요. 연구할 추가 데이터를 얻었네요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00FF6188
#. Notes = Somber about the situation, but is trying to find a positive spin, and crack a joke at the end. / Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0203B34C/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL08:0203B3B0
msgctxt "001652"
msgid "I feel trapped and tired most days. Perhaps the only shining light is I can research X-Tech without having to worry about funding. Oh, and the bar here is nice."
msgstr "대부분의 날은 갇혀 있고 지친 느낌이에요. 유일한 빛이라면 자금 걱정 없이 X-테크를 연구할 수 있다는 거겠죠. 아, 그리고 여기 바도 괜찮고요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00D3D4A4, 00FA4954, 0072918C
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0203B36E/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL02:0203B3BC
msgctxt "001653"
msgid "That's valuable in this line of work."
msgstr "이런 일에서는 그게 귀중하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00D3D4A4, 00FA4954, 0072918C
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0203B36E/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL02:0203B3BC
msgctxt "001654"
msgid "In all seriousness, Radha has the most experience out of all of us. She knows how to keep herself collected and what to say to get what she wants."
msgstr "진지하게 말하면, 라다는 우리 중 경험이 가장 많아요. 어떻게 침착함을 유지하고, 원하는 걸 얻기 위해 무슨 말을 해야 하는지 알고 있죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00D3D4A4, 00FA4954, 0072918C
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 0203B36E/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL02:0203B3BC
msgctxt "001655"
msgid "She's the one who keeps Tracy and me in line most of the time. I don't think anything would get done if we didn't have her."
msgstr "대부분의 시간 동안 트레이시와 저를 바로잡아 주는 사람이 라다예요. 라다가 없었다면 아무 일도 제대로 안 됐을 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02_IbroughtsomemoreX-techtoenhanceDeltasupgrade
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B4EEFF
#: 0203B34B/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD:0203B3BA
msgctxt "001656"
msgid "I brought some more X-Tech to enhance Delta's upgrade."
msgstr "델타의 업그레이드를 강화할 X-테크를 더 가져왔어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F826BA, 00405FB5
#. Notes = Serious as she talks about the future and being stuck with VOID. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Serious as she talks about the future and being stuck with VOID. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0203B354/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL04:0203B3BB
msgctxt "001657"
msgid "I wish I didn't have to, but I should. At the very least, I can keep an eye on them. I'll be damned if I let history repeat itself. "
msgstr "그러고 싶진 않지만, 그래야겠죠. 최소한 그들을 지켜볼 수는 있으니까요. 역사가 반복되게 둘 순 없어요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F826BA, 00405FB5
#. Notes = Serious as she talks about the future and being stuck with VOID. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Serious as she talks about the future and being stuck with VOID. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0203B354/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL04:0203B3BB
msgctxt "001658"
msgid "Mrs. Dhawan wants me to stay here. Since the Freestar, UC, and Ryujin all want to explore X-Tech they find it best I work alongside them."
msgstr "다완 씨는 제가 여기 남기를 원해요. 자유항성 공동체, 식민지 연합, 류진이 모두 X-테크를 탐사하려 하니, 제가 그들과 함께 일하는 게 최선이라고 보는 거죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B38B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0061932A
#: 0203B34F/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL07:0203B38B
msgctxt "001659"
msgid "Do you think you can ever revert Delta to the way they were? "
msgstr "델타를 예전 모습으로 되돌릴 수 있을 거라고 생각하세요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E2160C
#: 0203B357/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL03:0203B3AD
msgctxt "00165A"
msgid "How did you get into robotics?"
msgstr "로봇공학에는 어떻게 입문했어요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00691F11, 005C1E7B, 006D75FB, 00F12CED
#. Notes = Disgusted at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Still disgusted. / Disgust / to Player Default, Softer and sadder as she goes on her tangent. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Sad and worried. / Concerned / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203B350/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL06:0203B3D0
msgctxt "00165B"
msgid "The roboticist in me is interested. Another part, the moral part, screams about how wrong this is. And the artist feels an unconditional love and fear."
msgstr "제 안의 로봇공학자는 흥미를 느껴요. 다른 한쪽, 도덕적인 부분은 이게 얼마나 잘못된 일인지 소리치고 있죠. 그리고 예술가는 무조건적인 사랑과 두려움을 느껴요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00691F11, 005C1E7B, 006D75FB, 00F12CED
#. Notes = Disgusted at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Still disgusted. / Disgust / to Player Default, Softer and sadder as she goes on her tangent. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Sad and worried. / Concerned / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203B350/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL06:0203B3D0
msgctxt "00165C"
msgid "An artist's creations will never be living, breathing things. But with Delta, it's almost like having a child. I created something that somehow feels alive. And now, it's like watching that child become a monster."
msgstr ""
"예술가의 창조물은 결코 살아 숨 쉬는 존재가 될 수 없어요. 하지만 델타는 거의 아이를 둔 것 같아요. 저는 어쩐지 살아 있는 것처럼 느껴지는 것을 창조했어요. 그런데 이제는 그 아이가 괴물이 되어 가는 걸 보는 것 같죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00691F11, 005C1E7B, 006D75FB, 00F12CED
#. Notes = Disgusted at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Still disgusted. / Disgust / to Player Default, Softer and sadder as she goes on her tangent. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Sad and worried. / Concerned / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203B350/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL06:0203B3D0
msgctxt "00165D"
msgid "You want to know the craziest part? I feel this disgusting sense of pride."
msgstr "가장 미친 부분이 뭔지 알아요? 역겨울 정도의 자부심이 느껴진다는 거예요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00691F11, 005C1E7B, 006D75FB, 00F12CED
#. Notes = Disgusted at herself. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Still disgusted. / Disgust / to Player Default, Softer and sadder as she goes on her tangent. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Sad and worried. / Concerned / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 0203B350/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL06:0203B3D0
msgctxt "00165E"
msgid "It's complicated. Delta has become the very thing I hated. Humans should never use robots to fight on their behalf and yet, here I am: A hypocrite."
msgstr "복잡해요. 델타는 제가 그토록 혐오하던 바로 그 존재가 되었어요. 인간은 절대 로봇을 이용해 자기 대신 싸우게 해서는 안 되는데, 지금 저는 이렇게 위선자가 되어 있죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F9BC05, 00452D2E, 003BC886
#. Notes = A little happy, but also a hint of regret due to how Delta is now. Like talking about a friend that you had a falling out with. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B352/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL05:0203B3A3
msgctxt "00165F"
msgid "The process took years, but I loved every moment of it. It sounds silly since they are simply a machine, but Delta felt like a friend. I guess in a way they still do."
msgstr "그 과정은 몇 년이나 걸렸지만, 저는 모든 순간을 사랑했어요. 단순한 기계일 뿐이라 우습게 들리겠지만, 델타는 친구처럼 느껴졌어요. 어떤 의미에서는 아직도 그런 것 같고요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F9BC05, 00452D2E, 003BC886
#. Notes = A little happy, but also a hint of regret due to how Delta is now. Like talking about a friend that you had a falling out with. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B352/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL05:0203B3A3
msgctxt "001660"
msgid "After some research I gathered the alloy would only increase Delta's processing time. Which I was right about. We would talk for hours in trials to see how they were adapting to the new material."
msgstr "조사 끝에 그 합금은 델타의 처리 시간만 늘릴 거라고 판단했어요. 실제로도 그랬고요. 시험 중에는 새로운 소재에 어떻게 적응하는지 보려고 몇 시간씩 대화하곤 했죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F9BC05, 00452D2E, 003BC886
#. Notes = A little happy, but also a hint of regret due to how Delta is now. Like talking about a friend that you had a falling out with. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B352/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL05:0203B3A3
msgctxt "001661"
msgid "I originally created them as a program to help in whatever issues humanity may have. Something to possibly bring forth a better future. And then, I discovered X-Tech."
msgstr "처음에는 인류가 겪을 수 있는 어떤 문제든 돕는 프로그램으로 델타를 만들었어요. 더 나은 미래를 가져올 수도 있는 존재로요. 그리고 그때 X-테크를 발견했죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0054B986
#. Notes = Happy, and a slight bit of excitement shines through to work on Delta. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0203B348/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD:0203B3C3
msgctxt "001662"
msgid "This will do nicely. Alright, Delta. Come here."
msgstr "이 정도면 충분하겠네요. 좋아, 델타. 이리 와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 007F686D
#. Notes = Slightly annoyed, but more informative than mean or snide. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 0203B348/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_STANDARD:0203B3C2
msgctxt "001663"
msgid "I can't do much if they're not here. Bring Delta to me, then we'll talk."
msgstr "델타가 여기 없으면 제가 할 수 있는 게 많지 않아요. 델타를 데려오세요. 그다음에 이야기하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0057524F
#: 0203B35D/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL06:0203B3B8
msgctxt "001664"
msgid "Why does the United Colonies care about the Terrans?"
msgstr "식민지 연합이 왜 테란에게 신경 쓰는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008336AB
#: 0203B355/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL04:0203B3AC
msgctxt "001665"
msgid "What will you do now that the Terrans are gone?"
msgstr "테란이 사라졌으니 이제 뭘 할 건가요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008A9A32
#: 0203B34D/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL08:0203B3AA
msgctxt "001666"
msgid "How are you liking Anchorpoint?"
msgstr "앵커포인트는 마음에 드세요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00AD3EF8
#. Notes = Concerned. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B34E/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL07:0203B3CE
msgctxt "001667"
msgid "I don't know. To be honest, even if I did know how, I don't think they would let me."
msgstr "모르겠어요. 솔직히 방법을 안다고 해도 그 사람들이 허락해 줄 것 같진 않아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B397
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FE71BC
#: 0203B351/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL06:0203B397
msgctxt "001668"
msgid "Why aren't you happy with what Delta has become?"
msgstr "델타가 지금처럼 된 게 왜 마음에 안 드세요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B39E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009AE5A3
#: 0203B353/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL05:0203B39E
msgctxt "001669"
msgid "What can you tell me about Delta's creation?"
msgstr "델타가 어떻게 만들어졌는지 이야기해 줄 수 있나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005E172A
#: 0203B359/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL02:0203B3B5
msgctxt "00166A"
msgid "Why are we shutting this place down again?"
msgstr "다시 말하지만, 이곳을 왜 폐쇄하는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B392
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00375762, 0080CA19, 00EFE566
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, / to Player Default
#: 0203B35A/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL01:0203B392
msgctxt "00166B"
msgid "I happened to be unlucky enough to catch their attention by successfully using X-Tech in the Delta CPU. They had been trying to do something similar for years, and kept failing. "
msgstr "운 나쁘게도 델타 CPU에 X-테크를 성공적으로 사용한 바람에 그들의 눈에 띄었어요. 그들은 몇 년 동안 비슷한 일을 하려 했지만 계속 실패했거든요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B392
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00375762, 0080CA19, 00EFE566
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, / to Player Default
#: 0203B35A/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL01:0203B392
msgctxt "00166C"
msgid "From what I can tell, the Terrans may know about X-Tech's potential, but don't know how to fully realize it."
msgstr "제가 보기엔 테란은 X-테크의 잠재력은 알고 있지만, 그것을 완전히 실현하는 방법은 모르는 것 같아요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B389
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B94151
#: 0203B35B/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL01:0203B389
msgctxt "00166D"
msgid "The Terrans needed a robotics expert, but why you specifically?"
msgstr "테란에게 로봇공학 전문가가 필요했다지만, 왜 하필 당신이었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B398
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00168D0D
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B35C/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL06:0203B398
msgctxt "00166E"
msgid "While the United Colonies is part of VOID, we also understand the importance of not only X-Tech, but Terran technology. With both, the UC can advance our military further than we could have ever imagined."
msgstr "식민지 연합은 VOID의 일원이지만, 우리는 X-테크뿐 아니라 테란 기술의 중요성도 이해하고 있습니다. 둘 다 있으면 식민지 연합은 상상도 못 했던 수준까지 군사력을 발전시킬 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009143C6, 00D2619F, 0080DACD
#. Notes = Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed
#: 0203B356/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL03:0203B3BD
msgctxt "00166F"
msgid "But if we made them more advanced. They could take the brunt of most jobs, leaving people to just... live, create, or whatever they wish to do. That's the universe I want to help build."
msgstr "하지만 로봇을 더 발전시킨다면, 대부분의 일을 대신 떠맡게 해서 사람들은 그저... 살고, 창조하고, 원하는 일을 할 수 있게 되겠죠. 제가 만들고 싶은 우주는 그런 곳이에요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009143C6, 00D2619F, 0080DACD
#. Notes = Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed
#: 0203B356/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL03:0203B3BD
msgctxt "001670"
msgid "With robots, we have a way to give people happier lives. Everyone knows they're useful for dangerous jobs that would otherwise put lives at risk, but they're still pretty basic."
msgstr "로봇이 있으면 사람들에게 더 행복한 삶을 줄 수 있어요. 위험한 일을 맡겨 생명의 위험을 줄일 수 있다는 건 모두 알지만, 아직은 꽤 기본적인 수준이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009143C6, 00D2619F, 0080DACD
#. Notes = Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Happy / to Player Default, Face: Happy, Slightly happy. She enjoys talking about robotics. The more she talks, the more passionate she gets. / Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed
#: 0203B356/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL03:0203B3BD
msgctxt "001671"
msgid "I always found machinery and robotics interesting as a child. But it wasn't until I started to think of how robots can help people that I knew it was what I was really meant to do."
msgstr "어릴 때부터 기계와 로봇공학에 관심이 많았어요. 하지만 로봇이 사람들을 어떻게 도울 수 있을지 생각하기 시작한 뒤에야, 이게 제가 정말 해야 할 일이라는 걸 알았죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00C8997E
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B35E/00000/SFTER_TRACY_TL05:0203B3D7
msgctxt "001672"
msgid "Name's Tracy Warren. I've fought for the United Colonies for years, but was later approached to represent them in VOID. Said they needed someone with my experience. Obviously, I jumped on such an honor. That's all you need to know."
msgstr ""
"이름은 트레이시 워렌이다. 나는 수년간 식민지 연합을 위해 싸웠고, 이후 VOID에서 그들을 대표해 달라는 제안을 받았다. 내 경험이 "
"있는 사람이 필요하다고 하더군. 당연히 그런 영광은 마다할 이유가 없었지. 네가 알아야 할 건 그게 전부다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B38E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00BB55D3
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B362/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL03:0203B38E
msgctxt "001673"
msgid "Mrs. Dhawan is a tough lady, I'll give her that. She's been in VOID longer than any of us, and I don't think she ever plans on leaving. At least that means we'll never be out of experience. "
msgstr "다완 부인은 강한 분이라는 건 인정하지. 우리 중 누구보다 오래 VOID에 있었고, 떠날 생각도 전혀 없어 보인다. 적어도 경험이 부족할 일은 없겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0080D776
#. Notes = Trying to remain professional, but he is extremely angry at Percy and their betrayal. Though towards the end the anger is mixed in with regret. / Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B360/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL04:0203B3A5
msgctxt "001674"
msgid "It doesn't matter what I think. It only matters if he isn't some two faced bastard. Percy has been in VOID for years. They were annoying, sure, but I thought I knew them. "
msgstr "내가 어떻게 생각하느냐는 중요하지 않아. 그 사람이 표리부동한 개자식이 아니기만 하면 돼. 퍼시는 몇 년 동안 VOID에 있었어. 짜증나긴 했지만, 그래도 안다고 생각했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00ED8AFC
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B366/00000/SFTER_TRACY_TL01:0203B3C1
msgctxt "001675"
msgid "VOID, Veterans of Interstellar Deployment. As VOID, we are tasked to uncover threats and stop them. Like the Terran Armada. "
msgstr ""
"VOID, 성간 배치 퇴역 군인회. VOID로서 우리는 위협을 밝혀내고 저지하는 임무를 맡고 있습니다. 테란 함대 같은 위협 말입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00565EC9
#. Notes = Professional, but a bit smug. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug
#: 0203B368/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL05:0203B3AB
msgctxt "001676"
msgid "Isn't it obvious? Ryujin Industries prides itself on innovation in every way possible. Can you imagine the advancements Ryujin Industries can make with Terran technology? Or the profits?"
msgstr "뻔하지 않습니까? 류진 인더스트리는 가능한 모든 방식의 혁신을 자랑으로 삼습니다. 테란 기술이 있다면 류진 인더스트리가 얼마나 발전할 수 있을지 상상해 보셨습니까? 아니면 수익은요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B394
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009FEFB8
#: 0203B369/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL05:0203B394
msgctxt "001677"
msgid "Why does Ryujin Industries care about the Terrans?"
msgstr "류진 인더스트리가 왜 테란에게 신경 쓰는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B390
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 009CDB3F
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0203B370/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL01:0203B390
msgctxt "001678"
msgid "We are the Veterans of Interstellar Deployment. But we call ourselves VOID. As representatives of VOID, we are to watch for any threats to the Settled Systems that may appear and put an end to them."
msgstr "우리는 성간 배치 퇴역 군인회입니다. 하지만 스스로를 VOID라고 부르죠. VOID의 대표자로서, 우리는 개척 성계에 나타날지 모르는 위협을 감시하고 끝장내야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B38C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B590D5, 002CC046
#. Notes = A mix of trying to remain professional, and frustrated/annoyed to talk about Percy. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, A bit less angry. Trying to give Percy a little credit. Maybe deep down, Tracy does consider Percy somewhat a friend. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B364/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL02:0203B38C
msgctxt "001679"
msgid "Still, if Ryujin Industries want a representative here, I guess there could have been a worse pick than him."
msgstr "그래도 류진 인더스트리가 여기에 대표자를 두고 싶어 한다면, 그보다 더 나쁜 선택도 있었을 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B38C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_TRACY_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B590D5, 002CC046
#. Notes = A mix of trying to remain professional, and frustrated/annoyed to talk about Percy. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, A bit less angry. Trying to give Percy a little credit. Maybe deep down, Tracy does consider Percy somewhat a friend. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating
#: 0203B364/00030/SFTER_TRACY_TL02:0203B38C
msgctxt "00167A"
msgid "Nothing professional. Mrs. Dhawan says Percy's an asset because he knows how to get on people's good side. Yet all they do is annoy me."
msgstr "업무적으로는 없습니다. 다완 부인은 퍼시가 사람들의 호감을 사는 법을 안다며 자산이라고 말하죠. 하지만 그 사람이 하는 일이라곤 날 짜증나게 하는 것뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 0006EF51, 00DF0AF3
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0203B36A/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL04:0203B3A4
msgctxt "00167B"
msgid "I work with Ryujin Industries as their VOID representative. I'm Neon born and raised. And in my free time I enjoy making soap. Surely that answers all your queries? "
msgstr "저는 류진 인더스트리 소속 VOID 대표자로 일하고 있습니다. 네온에서 나고 자랐고요. 여가 시간에는 비누 만드는 걸 즐깁니다. 이 정도면 모든 궁금증에 답이 됐겠죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 0006EF51, 00DF0AF3
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0203B36A/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL04:0203B3A4
msgctxt "00167C"
msgid "Getting a bit more curious about VOID than you should? I'm joking, of course. Percy Kanu. I don't think I've ever told you it's a pleasure to meet you?"
msgstr "VOID에 대해 조금 과하게 궁금해지는 것 같은데요? 농담입니다, 물론. 퍼시 카누입니다. 만나서 반갑다고 말한 적이 있었나요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B39F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00A561B9, 00256C8E
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Professional, yet friendly. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0203B36C/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL03:0203B39F
msgctxt "00167D"
msgid "I am a firm believer though he would be much more enjoyable to work alongside if he lightened up a bit."
msgstr "그래도 그가 조금만 유해진다면 함께 일하기 훨씬 즐거울 거라고 굳게 믿습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B39F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_PERCY_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Percy
#. SoundFileID = 00A561B9, 00256C8E
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Professional, yet friendly. / Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 0203B36C/00030/SFTER_PERCY_TL03:0203B39F
msgctxt "00167E"
msgid "Warren and I may rarely see eye to eye, however he has his uses. Especially his military expertise, something Radha and I both lack."
msgstr "워렌과 나는 의견이 일치하는 일이 드물지만, 그래도 쓸모는 있습니다. 특히 군사 전문성은 라다와 나 둘 다 부족한 부분이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 006FCEFE
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B372/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL06:0203B3B2
msgctxt "00167F"
msgid "The Freestar Collective has taken notice of the Terrans' scan data and technology. That, combined with X-Tech, will strengthen the FC in ways that would have taken years to develop without it."
msgstr "자유항성 공동체는 테란의 스캔 데이터와 기술에 주목했습니다. 그것이 X-테크와 결합되면, 원래라면 개발에 수년이 걸렸을 방식으로 자유항성 공동체를 강화할 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B395
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008E3230
#: 0203B373/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL06:0203B395
msgctxt "001680"
msgid "Why does the Freestar Collective care about the Terrans?"
msgstr "자유항성 공동체가 왜 테란에게 신경 쓰는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B403
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0004245B, 003ED29B
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B375/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL05:0203B403
msgctxt "001681"
msgid "I have been here for many, many years, and I don't plan to quit anytime soon. That's all I wish for you to know."
msgstr "나는 아주, 아주 오랫동안 이곳에 있었고, 당분간 그만둘 생각도 없습니다. 당신이 알아야 할 건 그게 전부입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B403
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0004245B, 003ED29B
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B375/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL05:0203B403
msgctxt "001682"
msgid "My name is Radha Dhawan. I represent the Freestar Collective in VOID. There's nothing else about me I feel the need to share."
msgstr "내 이름은 라다 다완입니다. VOID에서 자유항성 공동체를 대표하고 있죠. 그 외에 나눌 필요가 있다고 느끼는 이야기는 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B38D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00094DC6
#. Notes = Professional, but a little annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0203B377/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL04:0203B38D
msgctxt "001683"
msgid "Not much. Only time will tell. If he works as hard as Percy did, then he'll be fine in my book. Let's just hope he doesn't stab us in the back too."
msgstr "별로 없습니다. 시간이 말해 주겠죠. 그가 퍼시만큼 열심히 일한다면, 내 기준으로는 문제없을 겁니다. 그 사람도 우리 뒤통수를 치지 않기만 바라야죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EF4BD9, 00BFBA5D, 001D4C40
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B37B/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL02:0203B3B3
msgctxt "001684"
msgid "I believe this how they've made it so far up the corporate chain at their age. With a smile and compliments."
msgstr "그 나이에 기업 조직에서 그렇게 높은 자리에 오른 것도 이 덕분이라고 생각합니다. 미소와 칭찬으로 말이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EF4BD9, 00BFBA5D, 001D4C40
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B37B/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL02:0203B3B3
msgctxt "001685"
msgid "Mr. Kanu, however, has something more important, yet silly. They know the perfect words to say."
msgstr "하지만 카누 씨에게는 더 중요하면서도 우스운 재능이 있습니다. 해야 할 말을 정확히 안다는 것이죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EF4BD9, 00BFBA5D, 001D4C40
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B37B/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL02:0203B3B3
msgctxt "001686"
msgid "Mr. Warren and I are here because we have experience in this line of work. While I understand the politics, Mr. Warren understands the militant aspects."
msgstr "워렌 씨와 저는 이 분야의 경험 때문에 이곳에 있습니다. 제가 정치적 측면을 이해한다면, 워렌 씨는 군사적 측면을 이해하죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00D2D822
#. Notes = Alt line if the player asks after the Terran Main Quest. Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B379/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL03:0203B3A9
msgctxt "001687"
msgid "Mr. Warren is a valuable member when it comes to his experience in battle. It's because of him we were able to understand the Terran's combative ways. He's a good strategist, and I'm pleased to work alongside him."
msgstr ""
"워렌 씨는 전투 경험 면에서 귀중한 구성원입니다. 그 덕분에 우리는 테란의 전투 방식을 이해할 수 있었습니다. 그는 훌륭한 전략가이고, "
"함께 일하게 되어 기쁩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00CC4456
#. Notes = Professional and serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B379/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL03:0203B3A8
msgctxt "001688"
msgid "Mr. Warren is a valuable member when it comes to his experience in battle. If we are to defeat the Terrans, we need to understand their combative ways. He's a good strategist, and I'm pleased to work alongside him."
msgstr ""
"워렌 씨는 전투 경험 면에서 귀중한 구성원입니다. 테란을 물리치려면 그들의 전투 방식을 이해해야 합니다. 그는 훌륭한 전략가이고, 함께 "
"일하게 되어 기쁩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B399
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_RADHA_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00D5D075
#. Notes = Professional and serious / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0203B37E/00030/SFTER_RADHA_TL01:0203B399
msgctxt "001689"
msgid "We are VOID, Veterans of Interstellar Deployment. As part of VOID, it is our duty to watch over the star sea and any threats that may surface. "
msgstr "우리는 VOID, 성간 배치 퇴역 군인회입니다. VOID의 일원으로서 별바다와 그 위로 떠오를 수 있는 모든 위협을 감시하는 것이 우리의 의무입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B2BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0310_TerranIntroScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PassengerM02
#. SoundFileID = 005F47BC
#. Notes = / to Terran01Scene01
#: 0203B2B6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0310_TerranIntroScene:0203B2BB
msgctxt "00168A"
msgid "No, please...!"
msgstr "안 돼, 제발...!"

