#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B4A3
msgctxt "00169A"
msgid "These pods hit a civilian site. Let's hope there are survivors. "
msgstr "이 포드들이 민간인 시설을 타격했다. 생존자가 있길 바라자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00074513
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B4A2
msgctxt "00169B"
msgid "Those Terrans must be here to scout. Let's make sure they don't find anything."
msgstr "저 테란들은 정찰하러 온 게 분명해. 아무것도 찾지 못하게 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
