#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 004831B7
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B49A
msgctxt "0016A1"
msgid "It's not gonna be a good day for the Terran Armada."
msgstr "테란 함대에게 좋은 날은 아니겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B499
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C5894C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B499
msgctxt "0016A2"
msgid "Time to upset some more Terran plans."
msgstr "테란의 계획을 좀 더 망쳐 줄 시간이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B498
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00E8AAAC
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B498
msgctxt "0016A3"
msgid "Those pods were well aimed. Let's hope there are survivors."
msgstr "저 포드들은 조준이 꽤 정확했어. 생존자가 있길 바라자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B497
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00845529
#. Notes = Pods are in the middle of nowhere vs location with structures. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B497
msgctxt "0016A4"
msgid "I wonder what those Terrans were aiming for."
msgstr "저 테란들이 뭘 노리고 있었는지 궁금하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B495
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 002039C0
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B495
msgctxt "0016A5"
msgid "These Terrans will find nothing here but death."
msgstr "이 테란들이 여기서 찾을 건 죽음뿐이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B494
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00E97C22
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B494
msgctxt "0016A6"
msgid "Time to take these Terrans out."
msgstr "이 테란들을 처리할 시간이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B493
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0014C199
#. Notes = Pods are in the middle of nowhere vs location with structures. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B493
msgctxt "0016A7"
msgid "A civilian site. Let us hope there are survivors."
msgstr "민간 시설이군. 생존자가 있길 바라자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B492
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00A8DEB2
#. Notes = Pods are in the middle of nowhere vs location with structures. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0203B48A/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B492
msgctxt "0016A8"
msgid "These pods either missed their mark, or the Terrans are here to scout."
msgstr "이 포드들은 목표를 빗나갔거나, 테란들이 정찰하러 온 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B490
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00A70F71
#. Notes = Seeing Terran drop pods for the first time. Small "dart" looking vessels that land vertically (like a lawn dart) and hold 3 people at a time. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48B/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B490
msgctxt "0016A9"
msgid "Those pods may be fine for robots, but I can't imagine they're kind to humans."
msgstr "저 포드들은 로봇한테는 괜찮을지 몰라도, 인간에게 편할 것 같진 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B48F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00AD5D65
#. Notes = Seeing Terran drop pods for the first time. Small "dart" looking vessels that land vertically (like a lawn dart) and hold 3 people at a time. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48B/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B48F
msgctxt "0016AA"
msgid "Something about those pods doesn't look comfortable."
msgstr "저 포드들은 어딘가 편해 보이지 않는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B48E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00EFE44E
#. Notes = Seeing Terran drop pods for the first time. Small "dart" looking vessels that land vertically (like a lawn dart) and hold 3 people at a time. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48B/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B48E
msgctxt "0016AB"
msgid "Just looking at those pods makes my back hurt."
msgstr "저 포드들만 봐도 허리가 아프다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B48D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00EC3A7D
#. Notes = Seeing Terran drop pods for the first time. Small "dart" looking vessels that land vertically (like a lawn dart) and hold 3 people at a time. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48B/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_StartScene:0203B48D
msgctxt "0016AC"
msgid "An innovative way to deploy troops."
msgstr "병력을 투입하는 혁신적인 방식이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 001565D4
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4BE
msgctxt "0016AD"
msgid "Solid performance if I do say so myself."
msgstr "내 입으로 말하긴 뭐하지만, 훌륭한 성과였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0081AB87
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4BD
msgctxt "0016AE"
msgid "Right. On to the next then."
msgstr "좋아. 그럼 다음으로 가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 001DE646
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4BC
msgctxt "0016AF"
msgid "Hope those Terrans enjoyed their one way trip."
msgstr "저 테란들이 편도 여행을 즐겼길 바라지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0091E5F0
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people here. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4BB
msgctxt "0016B0"
msgid "So many innocents lost here. The Terrans have truly outdone themselves."
msgstr "여기서 너무 많은 무고한 이들이 희생됐어. 테란들이 정말 도를 넘었군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 004BD372
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people here. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4BA
msgctxt "0016B1"
msgid "The Terrans deserve no mercy after what happened here."
msgstr "여기서 벌어진 일을 생각하면 테란에게 자비는 사치야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C659B0
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people here. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B9
msgctxt "0016B2"
msgid "Damn these Terrans. If the Colony War taught us anything, it was how unacceptable it is when innocent lives are lost."
msgstr "망할 테란들. 식민지 전쟁이 우리에게 가르쳐 준 게 있다면, 무고한 생명이 희생되는 건 용납할 수 없다는 거였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F78C56
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B7
msgctxt "0016B3"
msgid "Aaand, that's a wrap."
msgstr "자아, 이걸로 끝."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00DF6861
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B6
msgctxt "0016B4"
msgid "We done here? I was just getting' warmed up."
msgstr "여기 끝났어? 이제 막 몸이 풀리던 참인데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00DBD255
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B5
msgctxt "0016B5"
msgid "Another day, another dead Terran. "
msgstr "또 하루, 또 죽은 테란 하나."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00DF2C69
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people. / Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B4
msgctxt "0016B6"
msgid "Good riddance. It takes a special kind of monster to target innocents."
msgstr "속이 다 시원하군. 무고한 사람들을 노리려면 특별한 괴물이어야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F7CC2C
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B3
msgctxt "0016B7"
msgid "Damn, if only we got here sooner. At least we avenged these people."
msgstr "젠장, 우리가 조금만 더 일찍 왔더라면. 그래도 이 사람들의 복수는 해줬어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0032D840
#. Notes = Terrans killed a lot of people. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B2
msgctxt "0016B8"
msgid "We got 'em, but not before the real damage was done. "
msgstr "놈들을 잡긴 했지만, 진짜 피해는 이미 벌어진 뒤였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B4B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_DropPodsGround01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00526B7B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203B48C/00000/SFTER_INC_DP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203B4B0
msgctxt "0016B9"
msgid "Maybe the Terrans will think twice before pulling this again."
msgstr "테란들도 다시 이런 짓을 하기 전에 한 번쯤은 더 생각하겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
