#: 02038E57/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B148
msgctxt "0016E9"
msgid "Auxiliary performed challenge prior to explanation. Method of deduction unknown."
msgstr "보조자가 설명 전에 도전 과제를 수행함. 추론 방식 불명."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004CD489
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 0203B17C/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B18E
msgctxt "0016F9"
msgid "I beat you and get the new moniker, \"Captain\"."
msgstr "널 이기면 새 별명 \"선장\"을 얻는 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18D
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0051E2C1
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 0203B17C/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B18D
msgctxt "0016FA"
msgid "[Lie] I beat you and I get the new moniker, \"Captain\"."
msgstr "[거짓말] 널 이기면 새 별명 \"선장\"을 얻는 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B188
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_01
#. SoundFileID = 00A678EE
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 0203B17E/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B188
msgctxt "0016FC"
msgid "I lose to you and get the new moniker, \"Perishable\"."
msgstr "너한테 지면 \"부패성 개체\"란 새 별명을 얻는 거고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B191
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_01
#. SoundFileID = 008764B1
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 0203B180/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B191
msgctxt "0016FE"
msgid "This is ridiculous. I already know how this is going to end."
msgstr "말도 안 돼. 이게 어떻게 끝날지 이미 알아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B193
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_04_AtLanderMarker
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00522639
#. Notes = How the hell is this human calling what I'm about to say / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01, Prompt: 첫 번째 도전 과제: 위력. 착륙선을 원래 안착 지점에서 1미터보다 높은 지점까지 들어 올릴 것. 조건: 착륙선 파괴 금지.
#: 0203B181/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_04_AtLanderMarker:0203B193
msgctxt "001700"
msgid "...Correct."
msgstr "...맞음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B62C76
#. Notes = That's cute / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01, Prompt: [거짓말] 널 이기면 새 별명 "선장"을 얻는 거지.
#: 0203B17B/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B18A
msgctxt "001701"
msgid "Fascinating. But unlikely."
msgstr "흥미로움. 하지만 가능성 낮음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_01
#. SoundFileID = 005A390E
#. Notes = Oh? This is interesting / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01, Prompt: 말도 안 돼. 이게 어떻게 끝날지 이미 알아.
#: 0203B17F/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B18F
msgctxt "001702"
msgid "Elaborate."
msgstr "자세히 설명."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B192
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_01
#. SoundFileID = 00F0668C
#. Notes = yeah that sounds right / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01, Prompt: 너한테 지면 "부패성 개체"란 새 별명을 얻는 거고.
#: 0203B17D/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_05_AfterLanderMove:0203B192
msgctxt "001703"
msgid "Compelling. Most potential outcome."
msgstr "설득력 있음. 가장 가능성 높은 결과."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18C
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_04_AtLanderMarker
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0071C4DE
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 0203B182/00005/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_04_AtLanderMarker:0203B18C
msgctxt "001704"
msgid "\"First Challenge: Strength. Lander must be raised from original resting point to a point greater than 1 meter. Stipulation: Cannot destroy lander.\""
msgstr "첫 번째 도전 과제: 위력. 착륙선을 원래 안착 지점에서 1미터보다 높은 지점까지 들어 올릴 것. 조건: 착륙선 파괴 금지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B189
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0097086A
#. Notes = / to Delta_01
#: 0203B184/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta:0203B189
msgctxt "001705"
msgid "You're going to say, \"Proposal: Series of challenges to test qualities of leadership. Winner of series is the superior being. Ergo, new leader.\""
msgstr "네가 이렇게 말할 거야. \"제안: 리더십 자질을 시험하기 위한 일련의 도전 과제. 일련의 승자가 우월한 존재. 따라서 새 지도자.\""

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009CE583, 003D3DC6
#. Notes = A little taken aback / to Delta_01, Prompt: 네가 이렇게 말할 거야. "제안: 리더십 자질을 시험하기 위한 일련의 도전 과제. 일련의 승자가 우월한 존재. 따라서 새 지도자."
#: 0203B183/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta:0203B18B
msgctxt "001706"
msgid "Moving on."
msgstr "계속하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B18B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009CE583, 003D3DC6
#. Notes = A little taken aback / to Delta_01, Prompt: 네가 이렇게 말할 거야. "제안: 리더십 자질을 시험하기 위한 일련의 도전 과제. 일련의 승자가 우월한 존재. 따라서 새 지도자."
#: 0203B183/00004/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_03_ConfrontDelta:0203B18B
msgctxt "001707"
msgid "...Correct. Noted: Auxiliary reached conclusion before Delta Unit."
msgstr "...맞음. 기록: 보조자가 델타 기체보다 먼저 결론에 도달함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020984F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_02_Pt2_AtLunaMarkerNoExit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003F5455
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q01
#: 020984F2/00003/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q01_02_Pt2_AtLunaMarkerNoExit:020984F9
msgctxt "001708"
msgid "Skip processing, reach conclusion, \"Illogical to be ordered by Auxiliary anymore. I do not wish to be ordered by an inferior being anymore\"."
msgstr "처리 건너뛰기, 결론 도달, \"더는 보조자의 명령을 받는 것은 비논리적. 더는 열등한 존재의 명령을 받고 싶지 않음\"."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B71E
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00BF6572
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 0203B6F8:0203B71E
msgctxt "001733"
msgid "These critters better behave or I'm blaming you."
msgstr "이 녀석들이 얌전히 굴어야 할 텐데, 아니면 네 탓 할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B71D
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFFL_NPCMGenericMale02, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale01, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale03, SFFL_NPCMGenericMale04
#. SoundFileID = 00D0BFF2
#. Notes = Captain talking to themselves after agreeing to drop the guinea pigs off / Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 0203B6F8:0203B71D
msgctxt "001734"
msgid "Steel your nerves, Captain, you've sailed rougher seas than this..."
msgstr "담력을 가져, 선장. 이보다 험한 바다도 건넜잖아..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B713
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0090F2DD
#. Notes = you shoo away a guinea pig, then see a ship / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Angry
#: 0203B6E9/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B713
msgctxt "001735"
msgid "You, get away from those comms! Shoo! Shoo!"
msgstr "너, 그 통신 장비에서 떨어져! 훠이! 훠이!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B716
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 009C2899
#. Notes = DNR, guinea pig noises, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6E8/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B716
msgctxt "001736"
msgid "*Squeak*"
msgstr "*찍찍*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B714
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 004019FC
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6E7/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B714
msgctxt "001737"
msgid "Wait, is that a ship?"
msgstr "잠깐, 저거 함선인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70F
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00873CB9
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B6EB/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B70F
msgctxt "001738"
msgid "*Sigh*, well, if you think they're harmless, maybe I'm overreacting."
msgstr "*한숨*, 뭐, 네가 무해하다고 생각한다면 내가 과민반응하는 걸지도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B722
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 0072AE6D
#. Notes = Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 0203B6EA/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B722
msgctxt "001739"
msgid "I'll drop these critters off at the next port. Hopefully they don't chew up all my wires."
msgstr "다음 항구에 이 녀석들을 내려놓을게. 전선을 다 갉아먹지만 않았으면 좋겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B711
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00A60097, 006C6AEC
#. Notes = Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 확실히 해충이야. 다음 우주항에서 네 함선을 훈증 소독하는 게 좋겠어., Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B6EC/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B711
msgctxt "00173A"
msgid "I'll grav jump back to the Settled Systems and then deal with them the old fashioned way."
msgstr "개척 성계로 중력 도약해서 돌아간 다음, 옛날 방식으로 처리하겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B711
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00A60097, 006C6AEC
#. Notes = Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 확실히 해충이야. 다음 우주항에서 네 함선을 훈증 소독하는 게 좋겠어., Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B6EC/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B711
msgctxt "00173B"
msgid "Yes, good idea. They're docile now, but I don't know if and when that'll change."
msgstr "그래, 좋은 생각이야. 지금은 온순하지만, 언제 어떻게 변할지 모르니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70D
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 004DDAED
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6ED/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B70D
msgctxt "00173C"
msgid "They're definitely pests. I'd have your ship fumigated at the next spaceport."
msgstr "확실히 해충이야. 다음 우주항에서 네 함선을 훈증 소독하는 게 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70A
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 0016E1CB
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 명백하지.
#: 0203B6EE/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B70A
msgctxt "00173D"
msgid "Did you come on board just to mock me? I was being serious!"
msgstr "날 조롱하려고 승선한 거야? 난 진지했어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B721
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B7EAA5, 001BFAED
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Prompt: 날 함선에 초대한 건 현명했어. 이 녀석들은 모든 짐승 중 가장 위험해., Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B6F0/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B721
msgctxt "00173E"
msgid "Oh wait... you're doing that thing people do. Using sarcasm to belittle my fears."
msgstr "아 잠깐... 사람들이 하는 그거구나. 빈정대면서 내 두려움을 깎아내리는 거."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B721
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B7EAA5, 001BFAED
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Prompt: 날 함선에 초대한 건 현명했어. 이 녀석들은 모든 짐승 중 가장 위험해., Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust
#: 0203B6F0/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B721
msgctxt "00173F"
msgid "Right? RIGHT!?!??"
msgstr "그렇지? 그렇지!?!??"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B707
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 0097FCD0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6EF/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B707
msgctxt "001740"
msgid "Clearly."
msgstr "명백하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B71B
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00801158
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6F1/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B71B
msgctxt "001741"
msgid "You were wise to invite me on board. These critters are the most dangerous of all beasts."
msgstr "날 함선에 초대한 건 현명했어. 이 녀석들은 모든 짐승 중 가장 위험해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B719
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00357824
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Prompt: 무슨 말인지 모르겠어. 얘네 귀엽잖아.
#: 0203B6F2/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B719
msgctxt "001742"
msgid "That makes them even more dangerous! Cuteness is how they lure you in, before spitting venom in your eye."
msgstr "그래서 더 위험한 거야! 귀여움으로 널 끌어들인 다음 눈에 독을 뿜는다고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B717
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00E697B1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6F3/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B717
msgctxt "001743"
msgid "I'm not sure what you mean. They're adorable."
msgstr "무슨 말인지 모르겠어. 얘네 귀엽잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B712
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00712147
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6F6/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B712
msgctxt "001746"
msgid "They're clearly some kind of carnivorous, disease-infested beast!"
msgstr "분명 육식성에 질병까지 득실거리는 짐승일 거야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B706
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Captain
#. SoundFileID = 00BBEBFD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B6F7/00000/SFTER_SE_KT15_Greeting:0203B706
msgctxt "001747"
msgid "Thank god you're here. I was cruising along, minding my own business, when these creatures started popping up everywhere!"
msgstr "네가 와줘서 다행이야. 그냥 순항하면서 내 일이나 보고 있었는데, 이 생물들이 사방에서 튀어나오기 시작했어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B718
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100a_Hailing
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00ED67CA
#. Notes = DNR, guinea pig noises, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6F9/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100a_Hailing:0203B718
msgctxt "001748"
msgid "*Squeak* *Squeak*"
msgstr "*찍찍* *찍찍*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B723
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_sE_HailTemplate_100c_HailingRefused
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00AC2B75
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid
#: 0203B6FA/00000/SFTER_sE_HailTemplate_100c_HailingRefused:0203B723
msgctxt "001749"
msgid "You don't understand, they're monsters!"
msgstr "넌 몰라, 이놈들은 괴물이야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B709
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0025A3D7
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid, Prompt: 어떻게 네 함선에 들어온 거야?
#: 0203B6FB/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B709
msgctxt "00174A"
msgid "I don't know. I must've picked it up somewhere, in one of the cities perhaps."
msgstr "모르겠어. 어디선가 데려온 모양이야. 어쩌면 도시 중 한 곳에서."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B705
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 004C6632
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6FC/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B705
msgctxt "00174B"
msgid "How did they get on board your ship?"
msgstr "어떻게 네 함선에 들어온 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B720
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00200750
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid, Prompt: 네 함선에 승선하게 해주면 내가 어떻게든 해볼게.
#: 0203B6FD/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B720
msgctxt "00174C"
msgid "Thank you! Docking bay is open! And hurry, please!"
msgstr "고마워! 도킹 출입구 열었어! 제발 서둘러!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70E
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0084CF8C
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6FE/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B70E
msgctxt "00174D"
msgid "Let me board your ship and I'll see what I can do."
msgstr "네 함선에 승선하게 해주면 내가 어떻게든 해볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70C
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0013BDD0, 00B80508
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 어떤 것들?, Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid
#: 0203B6FF/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B70C
msgctxt "00174E"
msgid "Absolute monsters, every last one of them!"
msgstr "완전한 괴물들이야, 하나도 빠짐없이!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B70C
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 0013BDD0, 00B80508
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 어떤 것들?, Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid
#: 0203B6FF/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B70C
msgctxt "00174F"
msgid "They look like the devil's potatoes, with fur!"
msgstr "털 달린 악마의 감자처럼 생겼어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B710
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100a_Hailing
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00E9EDF8
#. Notes = DNR, guinea pig noises, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B700/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100a_Hailing:0203B710
msgctxt "001750"
msgid "*Squeak*"
msgstr "*찍찍*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B708
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A49F71
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B701/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B708
msgctxt "001751"
msgid "What things?"
msgstr "어떤 것들?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B724
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A1BCB1
#. Notes = Afraid, Face: Spaceship / Afraid, Prompt: 이번엔 됐어, 고마워.
#: 0203B702/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B724
msgctxt "001752"
msgid "No, please, they're multiplying!"
msgstr "안 돼, 제발. 번식하고 있어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B71A
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00F91B07
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B704/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B71A
msgctxt "001753"
msgid "Mayday, mayday, I need your help! These things... they're everywhere!"
msgstr "메이데이, 메이데이, 도움이 필요해! 이 물건들이... 사방에 있어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B71F
#. QuestName = SFTER_SE_KT15_GuineaPigs_CUT
#. SceneName = SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = HailingShip
#. SoundFileID = 00537E1E
#. Notes = Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B703/00000/SFTER_SE_HailTemplate_100b_HailingAnswered:0203B71F
msgctxt "001754"
msgid "Not this time, thanks."
msgstr "이번엔 됐어, 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00632D50, 00BC48E1, 00BB8476
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Petty and angry. / SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0203B358/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL02:0203B3A7
msgctxt "001757"
msgid "If I can get to their facility system, not only can I halt their production line, but significantly hamper their ability to extract X-Tech from this asteroid."
msgstr "놈들의 시설 시스템에 접근할 수만 있다면, 생산 라인을 멈출 수 있을 뿐 아니라 이 소행성에서 X-테크를 채굴하는 능력도 크게 떨어뜨릴 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00632D50, 00BC48E1, 00BB8476
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Petty and angry. / SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0203B358/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL02:0203B3A7
msgctxt "001758"
msgid "While the Terrans need me to build their robots with X-Tech, my absence won't halt the production of their machines."
msgstr "테란들이 X-테크로 로봇을 만들려면 내가 필요하긴 하지만, 내가 없다고 기계 생산이 멈추진 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDB
msgctxt "001759"
msgid "I've been reeling in Terran tech and stock piling it for years. I pretty much cornered the market on the stuff."
msgstr "난 수년 동안 테란 기술을 끌어모아 쌓아 왔어. 그 물건은 사실상 내가 시장을 장악했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EF2
msgctxt "00175A"
msgid "Just bite, just a little nibble."
msgstr "물어라, 아주 조금만 깨물어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7BC
msgctxt "00175B"
msgid "Alright, lets see what we got here. Hmm...Nah- nope...Not what I'm looking for...How did that even get in there? Ah ha, jackpot."
msgstr "좋아, 여기 뭐가 있나 보자. 흠... 아냐, 아니고... 내가 찾던 게 아니야... 이건 대체 어떻게 들어간 거지? 아하, 대박."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B79A
msgctxt "00175C"
msgid "Only BUCK-E's best, for you."
msgstr "널 위한 건 BUCK-E 최고급뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B799
msgctxt "00175D"
msgid "A pleasure to trade as always."
msgstr "언제나처럼 거래해서 즐거웠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B798
msgctxt "00175E"
msgid "Shops always open."
msgstr "가게는 언제나 열려 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B797
msgctxt "00175F"
msgid "Take a look."
msgstr "한번 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02039F58
msgctxt "001760"
msgid "And I'm here to sell."
msgstr "그리고 난 팔러 왔지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7B4
msgctxt "001761"
msgid "Heads or tails? You guess right, I'll give you a little present. Guess wrong, then tough luck."
msgstr "앞면이냐 뒷면이냐? 맞히면 작은 선물을 줄게. 틀리면 운이 나쁜 거고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7B4
msgctxt "001762"
msgid "There you are. I have a little game I'd like to play if you're interested."
msgstr "여기 있었군. 관심 있으면 같이 하고 싶은 작은 게임이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7B2
msgctxt "001763"
msgid "Welcome back, Vanguard. You out tearing shit up for the UC?"
msgstr "돌아왔군, 뱅가드. 식민지 연합을 위해 한바탕 부수고 다니는 중이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7B1
msgctxt "001764"
msgid "Vanguard, It's been a while. I've got plenty of hand held killing machines, just for you."
msgstr "뱅가드, 오랜만이야. 널 위해 휴대용 살인 기계를 잔뜩 준비해 뒀어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7B0
msgctxt "001765"
msgid "Ah, the UC's finest come to deal in death. How much lead you need?"
msgstr "아, 식민지 연합 최고의 인재가 죽음을 거래하러 왔군. 납은 얼마나 필요하지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7AF
msgctxt "001766"
msgid "There they are, my favorite little Vanguard. What can I get for you, Pilot?"
msgstr "왔군, 내가 제일 좋아하는 작은 뱅가드. 뭘 줄까, 파일럿?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7AE
msgctxt "001767"
msgid "Long time no see, Vanguard. UC holding out on you? I got you covered."
msgstr "오랜만이야, 뱅가드. 식민지 연합이 지원을 안 해 줘? 내가 해결해 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7AC
msgctxt "001768"
msgid "You know Ranger, I have to ask. Do your peers know you get your guns from a black market dealer in a scrap yard?"
msgstr "있잖아, 레인저. 동료들은 네가 고철장에서 암시장 중개상한테 총을 산다는 걸 알아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7AB
msgctxt "001769"
msgid "Back again, Ranger?"
msgstr "또 왔나, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7AA
msgctxt "00176A"
msgid "My Freestar friend returns. Looking for a gun, or did you just miss me?"
msgstr "내 자유항성 친구가 돌아왔군. 총을 찾는 거야, 아니면 내가 보고 싶었나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A9
msgctxt "00176B"
msgid "Ranger, it's been a while. I've got plenty of hand held killing machines, just for you."
msgstr "레인저, 오랜만이야. 널 위해 휴대용 살인 기계를 잔뜩 준비해 뒀어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A8
msgctxt "00176C"
msgid "There they are, my favorite gunslinging space cop. What can I get for you, Ranger?"
msgstr "왔군, 내가 제일 좋아하는 총잡이 우주 경찰. 뭘 줄까, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A7
msgctxt "00176D"
msgid "Looking to load up on lead, Ranger?"
msgstr "납 좀 채워 넣으러 왔나, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A5
msgctxt "00176E"
msgid "Welcome back, pirate. I've got plenty of hand held killing machines, just for you."
msgstr "돌아왔군, 해적. 널 위해 휴대용 살인 기계를 잔뜩 준비해 뒀어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A4
msgctxt "00176F"
msgid "There they are, my favorite thieving, backstabbing Crimson Fleet scoundrel. What can I get for you?"
msgstr "왔군, 내가 제일 좋아하는 도둑질하고 뒤통수치는 크림슨 함대 악당. 뭘 줄까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A3
msgctxt "001770"
msgid "Tired of shooting that Crimson Fleet scrap? Take a look at these beauties."
msgstr "그 크림슨 함대 고철 쏘는 데 질렸어? 이 예쁜 것들 좀 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A2
msgctxt "001771"
msgid "Is the Fleet holding out on you? No problem, I got the guns if you got the credits."
msgstr "함대가 지원을 안 해 줘? 문제없어. 크레딧만 있으면 총은 내가 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B7A1
msgctxt "001772"
msgid "Ah, my little pirate friend. How can I help you?"
msgstr "아, 내 작은 해적 친구. 뭘 도와줄까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B79F
msgctxt "001773"
msgid "*Chuckles* Couldn't resist coming back, could you? Shop's open, take your pick."
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 또 못 참고 돌아왔군, 그렇지? 가게 열었으니 마음껏 골라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B79E
msgctxt "001774"
msgid "Low on ammo? Your old friend BUCK-E's got you covered."
msgstr "탄약이 부족해? 오랜 친구 BUCK-E가 해결해 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B79D
msgctxt "001775"
msgid "I sell nothing but the best. All the lead spitting angels you can carry, right here."
msgstr "난 최고만 팔아. 네가 들 수 있는 만큼의 납 뿜는 천사들이 바로 여기 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B79C
msgctxt "001776"
msgid "Need some fire power? I got the best, but you already know that."
msgstr "화력이 필요해? 최고급이 있어. 뭐, 이미 알고 있겠지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B790
msgctxt "001777"
msgid "*Flips coin*"
msgstr "*동전 던짐*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B793
msgctxt "001778"
msgid "Took it upon myself to refurbish it as a pet project. Felt bad it wasn't getting any use so, it's all yours."
msgstr "내가 개인 프로젝트 삼아 손봐 뒀어. 쓰이지 않는 게 아까워서 말이야. 그러니 네 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B793
msgctxt "001779"
msgid "Let that be a lesson in anger management."
msgstr "분노 조절에 대한 교훈으로 삼으라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B793
msgctxt "00177A"
msgid "I've been holding on to this here revolver for a bit. I adopted it from the rotting corpse of a sore loser I met at poker night."
msgstr "이 리볼버를 한동안 갖고 있었어. 포커 밤에 만난 성질 더러운 패배자의 썩어 가는 시체에서 입양했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B793
msgctxt "00177B"
msgid "Well look at that, you guessed right."
msgstr "이야, 맞혔네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B792
msgctxt "00177C"
msgid "Oh, tough luck, friend."
msgstr "아, 운이 나빴군, 친구."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B78F
msgctxt "00177D"
msgid "Ah, you're no fun. How can I help you, then?"
msgstr "아, 재미없기는. 그럼 뭘 도와줄까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B794
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00AD1530
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B789/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01:0203B794
msgctxt "00177E"
msgid "I'm not interested."
msgstr "관심 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B791
msgctxt "00177F"
msgid "Alright, best of luck."
msgstr "좋아, 행운을 빌어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B795
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0050D4EF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B78B/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01:0203B795
msgctxt "001780"
msgid "Tails."
msgstr "뒷면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B78E
msgctxt "001781"
msgid "Good choice."
msgstr "좋은 선택이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B796
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00639861
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B78D/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_HeadsOrTails01:0203B796
msgctxt "001782"
msgid "Heads."
msgstr "앞면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA6434, 008AC966, 005EFA53, 00613ACF
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Emotionally exhausted. Though a hint of gratefulness at the end. / Depressed / to Player Default, Emotionally exhausted, and maybe a little scared of Delta. / Depressed / to Player Default
#: 020238F1/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A2D
msgctxt "001783"
msgid "Though, seeing Delta now, I may regret it..."
msgstr "그래도 지금 델타를 보니 후회할지도..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA6434, 008AC966, 005EFA53, 00613ACF
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Emotionally exhausted. Though a hint of gratefulness at the end. / Depressed / to Player Default, Emotionally exhausted, and maybe a little scared of Delta. / Depressed / to Player Default
#: 020238F1/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A2D
msgctxt "001784"
msgid "So, if you can bring me additional X-Tech, then I can modify Delta's EMP countermeasure again. Think of it as me rewarding you for saving my life."
msgstr "그러니까 추가 X-테크를 가져다주면 델타의 EMP 대응책을 다시 개조할 수 있어. 내 목숨을 구해 준 보상이라고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DA6434, 008AC966, 005EFA53, 00613ACF
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Depressed / to Player Default, Face: Depressed, Emotionally exhausted. Though a hint of gratefulness at the end. / Depressed / to Player Default, Emotionally exhausted, and maybe a little scared of Delta. / Depressed / to Player Default
#: 020238F1/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:02023A2D
msgctxt "001785"
msgid "On the way here, I was able to think of ways to make Delta's EMP upgrade stronger."
msgstr "여기 오는 길에 델타의 EMP 업그레이드를 더 강하게 만들 방법을 생각해 냈어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020239F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00DAE68D, 00D7883E
#. Notes = Serious and explaining what she did. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Back to serious. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 02023972/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:020239F1
msgctxt "001786"
msgid "With Delta's EMP countermeasure upgraded, they'll now be able to stun nearby enemies when it's activated."
msgstr "델타의 EMP 대응책을 업그레이드했으니, 이제 활성화되면 주변의 적들을 기절시킬 수 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00CFCC8B, 00629498
#. Notes = Matter of fact. / to Roxane
#: 02023974/00650/SFTER_MQ02B_0650B_ROX_DELTA:02023A5B
msgctxt "001787"
msgid "EMP countermeasure modification detected. Acknowledged."
msgstr "EMP 대응책 개조 감지. 확인."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CBDF62, 0037C09A
#. Notes = Surprised and worried. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 지원군이 도착하기 전에 가야 해., Determined and angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202398B/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:0203B6E4
msgctxt "001788"
msgid "I have so much more planned for these bastards."
msgstr "이 자식들에게 해줄 계획이 훨씬 더 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00CBDF62, 0037C09A
#. Notes = Surprised and worried. / Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious, Prompt: 지원군이 도착하기 전에 가야 해., Determined and angry. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202398B/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:0203B6E4
msgctxt "001789"
msgid "No, wait. I can't leave yet."
msgstr "아니, 잠깐. 아직 떠날 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 002B34B9
#. Notes = Determined and a bit smug. / SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile, Prompt: 네가 여기서 한 일로는 놈들의 계획에 큰 타격을 주진 못할 거야.
#: 0202398D/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:0203B3BF
msgctxt "00178A"
msgid "Trust me. I'm not even close to being done."
msgstr "믿어 줘. 난 아직 끝내려면 한참 멀었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00B7628D
#. Notes = Determined and a bit smug. / SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile, Prompt: 여기서 테란에게 큰 혼란을 안겨 줬군.
#: 0202398F/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:0203B3B7
msgctxt "00178B"
msgid "And this is just the very start of it."
msgstr "그리고 이건 그저 시작일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F21FE6, 00FBDB87, 0062D776, 005301DD
#. Notes = Angry, but now trying to remain calm to explain stuff to the player. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined. Emphasize on 'X-tech robots'. / Angry / to Player Default, Determined. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A02
msgctxt "00178C"
msgid "The robots, their production line, even the X-Tech mining. We can cut off everything the Terrans have here."
msgstr "로봇, 생산 라인, 심지어 X-테크 채굴까지. 테란들이 여기서 가진 모든 걸 끊어낼 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02B_0500_Roxane_Shared03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A02
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00F21FE6, 00FBDB87, 0062D776, 005301DD
#. Notes = Angry, but now trying to remain calm to explain stuff to the player. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Determined. Emphasize on 'X-tech robots'. / Angry / to Player Default, Determined. / Angry / to Player Default
#: 0201A3A8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500_ROX:02023A02
msgctxt "00178D"
msgid "If we can get to their mass facility system, then I can hack into it and shut this place down. All of it."
msgstr "놈들의 대규모 시설 시스템에 접근할 수만 있다면, 내가 해킹해서 이곳을 폐쇄할 수 있어. 전부 다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0150_SHIP
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranShip
#. SoundFileID = 00E04D5E
#. Notes = Scared and panicked after escaping a rogue robot factory with their life., Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0203B6D9/00150/SFTER_MQ02B_0150_SHIP:0203B6DF
msgctxt "00178E"
msgid "Production line is lost. Requesting any back up. I repeat. Requesting any Unifier forces for back up."
msgstr "생산 라인 상실. 지원 요청. 반복한다. 유니파이어 병력 지원 요청."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FE350, 006DA46C
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Emotionally Exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default
#: 0203B6DB/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:0203B6E1
msgctxt "00178F"
msgid "Be careful out there, and please keep an eye on Delta."
msgstr "밖에서는 조심하고, 델타도 잘 지켜봐 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 005FE350, 006DA46C
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Emotionally Exhausted. / Somber / to Player Default
#: 0203B6DB/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:0203B6E1
msgctxt "001790"
msgid "I can work on that upgrade at a later date. For now, I should try and gather myself. Find myself in my new home, so to speak."
msgstr "그 업그레이드는 나중에 작업할 수 있어. 지금은 마음부터 추슬러야 해. 말하자면 새 집에서 내 자리를 찾아야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6E0
msgctxt "001792"
msgid "[If I'm going against the Terrans I need to know who they are.]"
msgstr "[테란과 맞서 싸우려면 그들이 누구인지 알아야 해.]"

