#. SoundFileID = 00C097CA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203B663/00009/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_09_ChallengeStated:0203B667
msgctxt "0017A3"
msgid "Told you this would be the next challenge. I won the bet."
msgstr "다음 도전 과제가 이거라고 했잖아. 내기에서 내가 이겼어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B68B
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 000129B4
#. Notes = No big deal / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 사람들은 어떻게 찾았어?
#: 0203B688/00010/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_10_ChallengeEnd:0203B68B
msgctxt "0017A4"
msgid "Extant Terran Database from previous frame user. Showed couple received no visitors and no significant relations. Ideal targets."
msgstr "이전 프레임 사용자의 잔존 테란 데이터베이스. 부부에게 방문객도 없고 중요한 관계도 없음을 표시. 이상적인 대상."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
