#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03
#: 0203B68D/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A0
msgctxt "0017A5"
msgid "Guess I really surprised you this time."
msgstr "이번엔 내가 정말 널 놀라게 한 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0063BF1F
#. Notes = Waving it off (actually surprised?) / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03, Prompt: 이번엔 내가 정말 널 놀라게 한 것 같네.
#: 0203B68C/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A2
msgctxt "0017A6"
msgid "Inaccurate. \"Surprised\" implies traces of fear. \"Confused\" more accurate."
msgstr "부정확. \"놀람\"은 공포의 흔적을 암시함. \"혼란\"이 더 정확."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B68A
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
