#. SoundFileID = 00B1CC47, 00673796
#. Notes = Buys it / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03, Prompt: 네 행동이 수상했어.
#: 0203B692/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B69D
msgctxt "0017B0"
msgid "Perhaps. Recompiling truth obfuscation protocols with new data..."
msgstr "가능성 있음. 새 데이터로 진실 난독화 프로토콜 재컴파일 중..."

#. List: 2
