#: 0203B696/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A5
msgctxt "0017B5"
msgid "Moving reasoning ascertainment process to subroutine..."
msgstr "추론 확인 과정을 서브루틴으로 이동 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 0067EB2D, 00586143
#. Notes = Irritated / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03, Prompt: 그냥 내가 왜 그랬는지 물어보면 되잖아., No time for this, bodies are getting cold / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03
#: 0203B696/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A5
msgctxt "0017B6"
msgid "Counterpoint: Humans lie. Analysis of previous actions more truthful."
msgstr "반론: 인간은 거짓말함. 이전 행동 분석이 더 진실함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00A375A5
#. Notes = / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03
#: 0203B697/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A3
msgctxt "0017B7"
msgid "You could just ask me why I did it."
msgstr "그냥 내가 왜 그랬는지 물어보면 되잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
