#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00203BEE
#. Notes = Autopilot / to HeadtrackXMarker_Q03
#: 0203B698/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A7
msgctxt "0017B8"
msgid "Loading hypotheses...Recompiling..."
msgstr "가설 로딩 중...재컴파일 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B6A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta_03
#. SoundFileID = 00A44430
#. Notes = Truly befuddled / to Player Default
#: 0203B69A/00008/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_08_PostHomesteadDeath_PlayerKilling:0203B6A6
msgctxt "0017B9"
msgid "Knowledge of potential criminality? Loss of morality? Spontaneous insanity induction?"
msgstr "잠재적 범죄성에 대한 지식? 도덕성 상실? 자발적 광기 유발?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF08
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 006AEE32
#: 0203BED8/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF08
msgctxt "0017C6"
msgid "Well I should've. it's a suicide mission."
msgstr "글쎄, 그랬어야 했지. 자살 임무니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004A48A4, 00D72E8D, 00AE928E
#: 0203BED7/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF0E
msgctxt "0017C7"
msgid "So we need something to up our game. Increase our troops, bolster our weaponry, and speed our production."
msgstr "그러니 우리 수준을 끌어올릴 뭔가가 필요해. 병력을 늘리고, 무장을 강화하고, 생산 속도를 높이는 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004A48A4, 00D72E8D, 00AE928E
#: 0203BED7/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF0E
msgctxt "0017C8"
msgid "But I also agree we don't have the personnel, or the firepower. "
msgstr "하지만 인력도, 화력도 부족하다는 데는 나도 동의해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004A48A4, 00D72E8D, 00AE928E
#: 0203BED7/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF0E
msgctxt "0017C9"
msgid "General, there won't be another opportunity like this. The longer we wait, the more both sides can recoup their forces. "
msgstr "장군, 이런 기회는 다시 오지 않을 겁니다. 기다릴수록 양측 모두 병력을 회복할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF05
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F7A935
#: 0203BED9/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF05
msgctxt "0017CA"
msgid "You didn't use either of those words."
msgstr "그 두 단어 중 어느 것도 쓰지 않았잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF15
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00A9805E
#: 0203BED6/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF15
msgctxt "0017CB"
msgid "And I suppose you're gonna drop a curtain and show me this weapon of mass efficiency you've been working on?"
msgstr "그러면 이제 장막을 내리고, 네가 작업해 왔다는 대량 효율 무기를 보여줄 셈인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F3BDF9, 00965B7F
#: 0203BEDA/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF2E
msgctxt "0017CC"
msgid "In fact, I believe the word \"cockamamie\" was used, with good reason."
msgstr "사실 \"터무니없는\"이라는 말이 쓰였던 것 같은데, 그럴 만했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F3BDF9, 00965B7F
#: 0203BEDA/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF2E
msgctxt "0017CD"
msgid "With all due respect Admiral, I believe I was clear the last time you brought up this harebrained scheme."
msgstr "외람되지만 제독님, 지난번에 이 허황된 계획을 꺼내셨을 때 제 뜻은 분명히 밝혔던 것 같습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C2F74F
#: 0203BEDB/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF2A
msgctxt "0017CE"
msgid "General, we need to talk. It's about our earlier discussion."
msgstr "장군, 이야기 좀 해야겠습니다. 지난번 논의에 관한 일입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF24
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C4070A
#: 0203BEDC/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF24
msgctxt "0017CF"
msgid "And why in god's name would we do that? I thought the point of this was to get away from the senseless fighting."
msgstr "그리고 맙소사, 우리가 왜 그래야 하지? 이 모든 목적이 무의미한 싸움에서 벗어나는 거라고 생각했는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00982E74
#: 0203BEDD/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF1E
msgctxt "0017D0"
msgid "Fleet's strong, ground game's looking good. Should anyone come looking for us, they'll have a fight on their hands."
msgstr "함대는 강하고, 지상전도 좋아 보입니다. 누가 우리를 찾아온다면 제대로 한판 붙게 될 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C04F2A
#: 0203BEDE/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF1C
msgctxt "0017D1"
msgid "We don't, right now. But things can change."
msgstr "지금은 없지. 하지만 상황은 바뀔 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF19
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004C93B2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0203BEDF/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF19
msgctxt "0017D2"
msgid "You're out of your mind. We don't have the numbers, and we don't have the tech."
msgstr "제정신이 아니군. 우리엔 숫자도 부족하고, 기술도 부족해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF16
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00350B17
#: 0203BEE0/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF16
msgctxt "0017D3"
msgid "It'll force them to unite under us, or against us. But unity, regardless."
msgstr "그들에게 우리 아래 하나로 뭉치거나, 우리에 맞서 하나로 뭉치도록 강제할 겁니다. 어느 쪽이든 통합은 통합입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00525D68, 00E1A1AE
#: 0203BEE1/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF0F
msgctxt "0017D4"
msgid "Are you suggesting we take our little band of mercenaries, and start a WAR with the whole ass Settled Systems?"
msgstr "그러니까 우리 작은 용병 무리를 데리고, 개척 성계 전체와 전쟁을 시작하자는 말이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00525D68, 00E1A1AE
#: 0203BEE1/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF0F
msgctxt "0017D5"
msgid "Wait, let me get this straight. Given all the shellshock, I got but two brain cells left, and they don't always communicate."
msgstr "잠깐, 정리 좀 해보자. 포탄 충격을 하도 받아서 내 머리엔 뇌세포가 두 개뿐이고, 그 둘도 항상 서로 대화하는 건 아니거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF09
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00EB3AD3
#: 0203BEE2/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF09
msgctxt "0017D6"
msgid "Well, what if we wanted to initiate a fight?"
msgstr "글쎄, 우리가 싸움을 시작하고 싶다면?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF06
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00375881
#: 0203BEE3/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF06
msgctxt "0017D7"
msgid "General, how are our forces looking?"
msgstr "장군, 우리 병력 상황은 어떻습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00E57D55, 00022B29
#: 0203BEE4/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF2F
msgctxt "0017D8"
msgid "A banner that spoke for both the UC and the FC."
msgstr "식민지 연합과 자유항성 공동체 모두를 대변하는 깃발."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00E57D55, 00022B29
#: 0203BEE4/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF2F
msgctxt "0017D9"
msgid "But what if there was a different ruling party, with none of the bad blood, or these generational grievances?"
msgstr "하지만 원한도, 세대를 거친 앙금도 없는 다른 집권 세력이 있다면 어떨까요?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0071D8AA
#: 0203BEE5/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF2B
msgctxt "0017DA"
msgid "I get it. You don't want to have to live by another man's rules, especially in your own house."
msgstr "이해해. 남의 규칙대로 살고 싶지 않은 거지. 특히 자기 집에서라면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF25
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 002DB8AA, 00ADE3F7
#: 0203BEE6/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF25
msgctxt "0017DB"
msgid "Regardless of whether these peace talks succeed, their ideals are fundamentally opposed. It won't last."
msgstr "이 평화 회담이 성공하든 말든, 그들의 이상은 근본적으로 대립해. 오래가지 못해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF25
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 002DB8AA, 00ADE3F7
#: 0203BEE6/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF25
msgctxt "0017DC"
msgid "Just zoom out for a second, and listen. "
msgstr "잠깐 시야를 넓히고 들어 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF12
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00470046
#: 0203BEEA/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF12
msgctxt "0017DD"
msgid "Captain Balewa, I take it you didn't come here to surrender, which is a shame given the shape of your fleet."
msgstr "발레와 대령, 항복하러 온 건 아닌 모양이군. 당신 함대 상태를 보면 아쉬운 일이지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0090388E
#: 0203BEE8/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF1A
msgctxt "0017DE"
msgid "Sometimes the best defense is a good offense."
msgstr "때로는 최선의 방어가 훌륭한 공격이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF17
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 005A39FF
#: 0203BEE9/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF17
msgctxt "0017DF"
msgid "Still, I admire your courage. If nothing else, history will remember that kindly."
msgstr "그래도 용기는 높이 사지. 적어도 역사는 그 점을 좋게 기억할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C091EE
#: 0203BEE7/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_02:0203BF1F
msgctxt "0017E0"
msgid "And sometimes platitudes and slogans aren't worth the batball coach they rode in on."
msgstr "그리고 때로는 상투어와 구호가 그걸 주워섬긴 배트볼 코치만큼도 가치 없을 때가 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF31
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00FDA10F, 00CD249F
#: 0203BEEB/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF31
msgctxt "0017E1"
msgid "Unlike the standard Model A, these robots are built with military applications in mind. "
msgstr "표준 모델 A와 달리, 이 로봇들은 군사적 용도를 염두에 두고 제작되었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF31
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00FDA10F, 00CD249F
#: 0203BEEB/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF31
msgctxt "0017E2"
msgid "Yes, for the past few years I've been experimenting with our new light-frame robotic soldiers. "
msgstr "네, 지난 몇 년간 저희의 새로운 경량 프레임 로봇 병사를 실험해 왔습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF27
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00DCA286
#: 0203BEEC/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF27
msgctxt "0017E3"
msgid "Yes sir."
msgstr "예, 장군님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00E2AB3A
#: 0203BEED/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF0C
msgctxt "0017E4"
msgid "To find a way out. And it's Admiral Balewa now."
msgstr "탈출구를 찾기 위해서지. 그리고 지금은 발레와 제독이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF07
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 000BCFCC
#: 0203BEEE/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF07
msgctxt "0017E5"
msgid "Fair enough. Real talk then. Say I agree to this truce of yours. What exactly is your mission directive, Captain?"
msgstr "좋습니다. 그럼 솔직히 말하죠. 제가 이 휴전에 동의한다고 칩시다. 정확히 임무 지시는 뭡니까, 대령?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF33
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C85766
#: 0203BEEF/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF33
msgctxt "0017E6"
msgid "Am I wrong?"
msgstr "내가 틀렸나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 007E06FF
#: 0203BEF0/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF0D
msgctxt "0017E7"
msgid "So, where's this secret weapon you promised me? And who's the kid?"
msgstr "그래서, 약속한 비밀 무기는 어디 있지? 그리고 저 아이는 누구야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF10
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00ACA2FB
#: 0203BEF1/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF10
msgctxt "0017E8"
msgid "The engineers think it might help with our production and personnel problems. But it's still mostly theoretical."
msgstr "엔지니어들은 이것이 생산과 인력 문제에 도움이 될 수 있다고 생각합니다. 하지만 아직은 대부분 이론 단계입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00D88C10
#: 0203BEF2/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF0A
msgctxt "0017E9"
msgid "In English, Admiral."
msgstr "영어로 말해, 제독."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF30
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004EB025
#: 0203BEF3/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF30
msgctxt "0017EA"
msgid "Our miners dug it up on a remote moon. We can't place its origins, but we are starting to get a grasp of what it does."
msgstr "우리 광부들이 외딴 달에서 그것을 캐냈습니다. 기원은 알 수 없지만, 그 기능은 조금씩 파악하기 시작했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF29
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00AEAEFD
#: 0203BEF5/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF29
msgctxt "0017EB"
msgid "Shiny. And what pray tell, does it do?"
msgstr "반짝거리네. 그래서 대체 그게 뭘 하지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF13
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 009A1CD8
#: 0203BEF4/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF13
msgctxt "0017EC"
msgid "We're not entirely sure. It's not like any other alloy in the known universe. But given its allotropic nature, it can bind to almost anything."
msgstr "완전히 확실하진 않습니다. 알려진 우주의 어떤 합금과도 다릅니다. 하지만 동소체적 특성상 거의 무엇에든 결합할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2D
msgctxt "0017ED"
msgid "Our miners dug it up on a remote moon. We can't place its origins, but we are starting to get a grasp of what it does."
msgstr "우리 광부들이 외딴 달에서 그것을 캐냈습니다. 기원은 알 수 없지만, 그 기능은 조금씩 파악하기 시작했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF0B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 000BDD01
#: 0203BEF7/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_03:0203BF0B
msgctxt "0017EE"
msgid "Ha, not a weapon. Something better."
msgstr "하, 무기가 아니야. 그보다 더 나은 것이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF26
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004E0C73
#: 0203BEF8/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF26
msgctxt "0017EF"
msgid "I'm aware of the tin soldiers, kid. Clumsy, slow, and dumb as Chunks. Wouldn't trust a single one to guard my six."
msgstr "양철 병사들은 알고 있어, 꼬마. 서툴고, 느리고, 청크만큼 멍청하지. 내 뒤를 맡길 놈은 하나도 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF21
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C0DBC3, 009ADC21, 00C8501E
#: 0203BEF9/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF21
msgctxt "0017F0"
msgid "There's also opportunities with this new alloy -- which I've been calling X-tech -- into their production. "
msgstr "이 새로운 합금, 내가 X-테크라고 부르는 것을 그들의 생산에 도입할 가능성도 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF21
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C0DBC3, 009ADC21, 00C8501E
#: 0203BEF9/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF21
msgctxt "0017F1"
msgid "Correct. But the modifications I've made should address some of these issues. "
msgstr "맞습니다. 하지만 제가 한 개조가 이런 문제 중 일부를 해결할 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF20
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 000A271B
#: 0203BEFA/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF20
msgctxt "0017F2"
msgid "I served with her. Brilliant scientist. Even better person. What brings you here?"
msgstr "그녀와 함께 복무한 적이 있네. 뛰어난 과학자였고, 그보다 더 좋은 사람이었지. 여기엔 무슨 일인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00FF1C1A
#: 0203BEFB/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF1B
msgctxt "0017F3"
msgid "Young Anwar is helping our robotics department. He's the one who suggested the most recent design. "
msgstr "젊은 안와르가 우리 로봇공학 부서를 돕고 있습니다. 가장 최근 설계를 제안한 사람이 바로 그입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF32
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 007D0ACD
#: 0203BF00/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF32
msgctxt "0017F4"
msgid "Regardless, it's far more humane. Think about it, General. With these machines, we won't have to sacrifice a single human life to win this war."
msgstr "어쨌든, 훨씬 더 인도적입니다. 생각해 보십시오, 장군. 이 기계들이 있으면 이 전쟁에서 이기기 위해 단 한 명의 인간 목숨도 희생할 필요가 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C7EAA5
#: 0203BF01/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF2C
msgctxt "0017F5"
msgid "That's dangerous talk, Captain Balewa. Treasonous talk."
msgstr "위험한 말이군, 발레와 대령. 반역적인 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF14
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 005C4297
#: 0203BEFE/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF14
msgctxt "0017F6"
msgid "General Royce, meet our secret weapon. Anwar Sinaga. "
msgstr "로이스 장군, 우리의 비밀 무기를 소개하죠. 안와르 시나가입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF22
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0054818E
#: 0203BEFF/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF22
msgctxt "0017F7"
msgid "Ha, tell that to the soldiers they're shooting at."
msgstr "하, 그건 그 로봇들에게 총 맞는 군인들한테나 말해 보게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF11
msgctxt "0017F8"
msgid "So we need something to up our game. Get our muskets loaded in half the time."
msgstr "그러니 우리 수준을 끌어올릴 뭔가가 필요해. 머스킷을 절반 시간에 장전하게 해 줄 것."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF18
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00EA4F46, 004E51AA
#: 0203BEFD/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF18
msgctxt "0017F9"
msgid "Wait... Sinaga? Are you Gita's boy?"
msgstr "잠깐... 시나가? 기타의 아들이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF18
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00EA4F46, 004E51AA
#: 0203BEFD/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF18
msgctxt "0017FA"
msgid "Is this some kind of joke? I've got pimples older than this boy! "
msgstr "이게 무슨 농담이야? 내 여드름 중에도 이 애보다 오래된 게 있어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF28
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003B28FD, 00701275
#: 0203BF02/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF28
msgctxt "0017FB"
msgid "Someone who sees the pointlessness of an endless war, and would be willing to leave his post rather than continue this war of attrition."
msgstr "끝없는 전쟁의 무의미함을 알고, 이 소모전을 계속하느니 보직을 떠날 의향이 있는 사람."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF28
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003B28FD, 00701275
#: 0203BF02/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF28
msgctxt "0017FC"
msgid "Well, that's not the story I heard. My sources tell me Tolliver Royce is a practical man. "
msgstr "글쎄, 내가 들은 얘기는 그게 아닌데. 내 정보원들은 톨리버 로이스가 실용적인 사람이라고 하더군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF23
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004E2089
#: 0203BF03/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF23
msgctxt "0017FD"
msgid "Yeah, I've killed more than my fair share of Vanguard, UC marines, even Aegis."
msgstr "그래, 뱅가드, 식민지 연합 해병대, 심지어 이지스까지 내 몫 이상으로 많이 죽였지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00089E16
#: 0203BF04/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_01:0203BF1D
msgctxt "0017FE"
msgid "Tolliver Royce. The Ghost Ranger in the flesh. You're quite the legend back in New Atlantis."
msgstr "톨리버 로이스. 살아 있는 유령 레인저라니. 뉴아틀란티스에서도 꽤 전설적인 존재야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF59
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003B8C64
#: 0203BF48/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF59
msgctxt "0017FF"
msgid "You should be happy, General. This is what the last twenty years have been for."
msgstr "기뻐해야지, 장군. 지난 20년은 바로 이것을 위한 시간이었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F98731, 00573125
#: 0203BF3F/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF5B
msgctxt "001800"
msgid "And with the Unifier controlling the army, we can order strikes and attack targets before our enemies can finish spooling their Grav Drives."
msgstr "그리고 유니파이어가 군대를 통제하면, 적들이 중력 구동기 가동을 끝내기 전에 타격을 명령하고 목표를 공격할 수 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F98731, 00573125
#: 0203BF3F/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF5B
msgctxt "001801"
msgid "We're so close. We have the tactical and technological advantage."
msgstr "거의 다 왔어. 우리에겐 전술적, 기술적 우위가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF69
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00209110
#: 0203BF41/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF69
msgctxt "001802"
msgid "The kid's doing good, I have to admit. Even if his robots creep me out."
msgstr "인정하긴 싫지만 그 아이는 잘하고 있어. 로봇들이 소름 끼치긴 해도 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF67
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003081E2
#: 0203BF42/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF67
msgctxt "001803"
msgid "Supra et Ultra, General. I've always been driven."
msgstr "수프라 엣 울트라, 장군. 전 항상 목표에 몰두했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF6B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 008FA437
#: 0203BF40/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF6B
msgctxt "001804"
msgid "You know, you never told me what happened on the Montero. "
msgstr "있잖아, 몬테로에서 무슨 일이 있었는지는 한 번도 말해주지 않았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF63
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0004CC5C
#: 0203BF43/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF63
msgctxt "001805"
msgid "So is this a revenge thing? Is that why you're so driven?"
msgstr "그래서 이건 복수 같은 건가? 그래서 그렇게 몰두하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00E3325F
#: 0203BF45/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF5D
msgctxt "001806"
msgid "Jesus."
msgstr "세상에."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF60
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00276102
#: 0203BF44/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF60
msgctxt "001807"
msgid "There was a time I would've died for the UC. But now?"
msgstr "한때는 식민지 연합을 위해 죽을 수도 있었어. 하지만 지금은?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_06
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00094732
#: 0203BF46/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_06:0203BF5C
msgctxt "001808"
msgid "It was a setup. My own commanding officer sold me out to the FC."
msgstr "함정이었어. 내 지휘관이 나를 FC에 팔아넘겼지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5A
msgctxt "001809"
msgid "Yeah, I killed more than my fair share of Vanguard, UC marines, even an Aegis spook."
msgstr "그래, 뱅가드, 식민지 연합 해병대, 심지어 이지스 첩자까지 내 몫 이상으로 많이 죽였지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00913778
#: 0203BF49/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF5E
msgctxt "00180A"
msgid "Well, it'll allow us to communicate near-instantaneously with the robot soldiers."
msgstr "그러면 로봇 병사들과 거의 즉각적으로 통신할 수 있게 됩니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF58
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0091B033, 006BBABB
#: 0203BF4A/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF58
msgctxt "00180B"
msgid "This could very well transform the galactic information network!"
msgstr "이건 은하 정보망을 완전히 바꿔 놓을 수도 있어요!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF58
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0091B033, 006BBABB
#: 0203BF4A/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF58
msgctxt "00180C"
msgid "It's remarkable! Every day I'm finding new ways to integrate the technology. I think we can even use it for faster-than-light messaging. "
msgstr "놀랍습니다! 매일 이 기술을 통합할 새로운 방법을 찾고 있어요. 초광속 메시지 전송에도 사용할 수 있을 것 같습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF66
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00066E80, 0000BFCC
#: 0203BF4B/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF66
msgctxt "00180D"
msgid "They've lost friends, family, everything they ever loved to this war. So I trust they know what's at stake."
msgstr "그들은 이 전쟁으로 친구와 가족, 사랑했던 모든 것을 잃었습니다. 그러니 무엇이 걸려 있는지 알고 있다고 믿습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF66
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00066E80, 0000BFCC
#: 0203BF4B/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF66
msgctxt "00180E"
msgid "Heck no, a man's gotta have skin in the game. That's why I follow the Admiral. "
msgstr "절대 아니지. 남자는 판돈을 걸어야 하는 법이야. 그래서 내가 제독을 따르는 거고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF62
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0025A3ED
#: 0203BF4C/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF62
msgctxt "00180F"
msgid "Yes sir."
msgstr "예, 장군님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00CB8E87
#: 0203BF4D/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF5F
msgctxt "001810"
msgid "How's it going, Anwar? Or is it Dr. Anwar now?"
msgstr "어떻게 지내나, 안와르? 아니면 이제 안와르 박사라고 해야 하나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF56
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0048A970
#: 0203BF4E/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF56
msgctxt "001811"
msgid "And what have you lost, sir?"
msgstr "당신은 무엇을 잃으셨습니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 002059B7
#: 0203BF4F/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF6C
msgctxt "001812"
msgid "*Sigh*. That's a long story. Too long for this meeting. How's the X-Tech research coming along? "
msgstr "*한숨*. 긴 이야기야. 이 회의에서 하기엔 너무 길지. X-테크 연구는 어떻게 되어 가나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF6A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 005787C7
#: 0203BF50/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF6A
msgctxt "001813"
msgid "So this whole unifying the UC and FC thing is kind of personal for you, is that right?"
msgstr "그러니까 식민지 연합과 자유항성 공동체를 하나로 묶으려는 이 일 전체가 당신에게는 좀 개인적인 문제라는 거죠?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF68
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00A4616C
#: 0203BF51/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF68
msgctxt "001814"
msgid "Is that a problem, sir?"
msgstr "그게 문제입니까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF64
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00251E5C, 00624ADF
#: 0203BF52/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF64
msgctxt "001815"
msgid "But I've been meaning to ask. I know your mother, but not your father. Is it true he was UC?"
msgstr "그런데 전부터 묻고 싶었어. 네 어머니는 알지만 아버지는 모르거든. 식민지 연합 출신이었다는 게 사실이니?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF64
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00251E5C, 00624ADF
#: 0203BF52/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF64
msgctxt "001816"
msgid "A title earned by merit. Way more impressive than some professor who wrote a book and forced his class to read it."
msgstr "실력으로 얻은 호칭이지. 책 한 권 쓰고 자기 수업 학생들에게 읽으라고 강요한 교수보다 훨씬 인상적이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF57
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 004901A6
#: 0203BF53/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF57
msgctxt "001817"
msgid "Doctor Sinaga is fine. Although it's an honorary title."
msgstr "시나가 박사면 됩니다. 명예 칭호이긴 하지만요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF89
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 007EFC30
#: 0203BF71/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF89
msgctxt "001818"
msgid "Well, I want to hear what the kid thinks."
msgstr "글쎄, 난 그 아이 생각을 듣고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF61
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00CED673
#: 0203BF55/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF61
msgctxt "001819"
msgid "And the military applications?"
msgstr "군사적 응용은?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF65
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0061C1D4, 007D225D
#: 0203BF54/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF65
msgctxt "00181A"
msgid "Fantastic. What about integrating it into the robots?"
msgstr "훌륭해. 로봇에 통합하는 건?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF65
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0061C1D4, 007D225D
#: 0203BF54/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0203BF65
msgctxt "00181B"
msgid "So we can command our tin soldiers from the comfort of our bean bags. "
msgstr "그러면 빈백에 편히 앉아서 양철 병사들을 지휘할 수 있겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF86
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C8322C
#: 0203BF72/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF86
msgctxt "00181C"
msgid "So we force her to reveal her findings. Find out how she did it."
msgstr "그러니 그녀가 연구 결과를 밝히게 강제해야 해. 어떻게 해냈는지 알아내야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF90
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00877EFC
#: 0203BF74/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF90
msgctxt "00181D"
msgid "I haven't been able to figure out how to integrate X-Tech into the processors. I know it's possible in theory, I'm just struggling with the application."
msgstr "프로세서에 X-테크를 통합하는 방법을 아직 알아내지 못했습니다. 이론적으로 가능하다는 건 알지만, 적용에서 막히고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF84
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0001A607, 00B77E4F
#: 0203BF73/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF84
msgctxt "00181E"
msgid "Sometimes the answer reveals itself when our minds are free of distraction."
msgstr "때로는 마음이 산만함에서 벗어났을 때 답이 스스로 모습을 드러내지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF84
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 0001A607, 00B77E4F
#: 0203BF73/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF84
msgctxt "00181F"
msgid "It's all right. You've been working too hard. Take a break. "
msgstr "괜찮아. 너무 무리해서 일했어. 쉬어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003B4637
#: 0203BF75/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF8D
msgctxt "001820"
msgid "You let me worry about the X-Tech. What's the other issue?"
msgstr "X-테크는 내가 걱정할게. 다른 문제는 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF83
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 009CEFA6, 00E745DF
#: 0203BF76/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF83
msgctxt "001821"
msgid "If Roxane Bourreau has the key, then I suggest we take it."
msgstr "록산 부로에게 열쇠가 있다면, 빼앗는 게 좋겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF83
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 009CEFA6, 00E745DF
#: 0203BF76/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF83
msgctxt "001822"
msgid "I agree with the Admiral. We've been banging our heads against the wall for months trying to figure this out."
msgstr "제독님 의견에 동의합니다. 저희는 이걸 알아내려고 몇 달째 벽에 머리를 박고 있었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00728D19
#: 0203BF77/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF8A
msgctxt "001823"
msgid "I believe it's the very same. It has all of the same properties that we've documented in our tests."
msgstr "바로 같은 것이라고 생각합니다. 저희가 시험에서 기록한 것과 모두 같은 특성을 가지고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF87
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 006CDFBC
#: 0203BF79/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF87
msgctxt "001824"
msgid "Fine. But we do this sneaky. Snatch and grab. No fireworks. Because otherwise, it's war."
msgstr "좋아. 하지만 은밀하게 한다. 치고 빠지는 식으로. 불꽃놀이는 없어. 안 그러면 전쟁이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF88
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00B9A5B2
#: 0203BF78/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF88
msgctxt "001825"
msgid "Have you read the report about this Roxane Bourreau?"
msgstr "이 록산 부로에 대한 보고서는 읽어 봤나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF85
msgctxt "001826"
msgid "Processing power is still an issue, but they're far more lightweight and structurally sound, making them better served for the battlefield than a human soldier."
msgstr "처리 능력은 아직 문제지만, 훨씬 가볍고 구조적으로 튼튼해서 인간 병사보다 전장에 더 적합합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF85
msgctxt "001827"
msgid "Correct. But that was before we introduced the new alloy -- which I've been calling X-tech -- into their production. "
msgstr "맞습니다. 하지만 그건 새로운 합금, 제가 X-테크라고 부르는 것을 생산에 도입하기 전의 이야기입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF82
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 005564AC
#: 0203BF7B/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF82
msgctxt "001828"
msgid "I don't know Admiral, I think it's too soon to reveal our cards. If we give the kid more time..."
msgstr "모르겠습니다, 제독님. 아직 패를 드러내기엔 너무 이른 것 같습니다. 그 아이에게 시간을 더 주면..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF92
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 006A9206
#: 0203BF7C/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF92
msgctxt "001829"
msgid "And what if this technology falls into the hands of the UC? We can't lose the advantage."
msgstr "그리고 이 기술이 식민지 연합의 손에 들어가면 어떻게 됩니까? 우위를 잃을 수는 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8F
msgctxt "00182A"
msgid "Wait... Sinaga? Are you Gita's boy?"
msgstr "잠깐... 시나가? 기타의 아들이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8F
msgctxt "00182B"
msgid "Is this some kind of joke? I've got pimples older than this boy! "
msgstr "이게 무슨 농담이야? 내 여드름 중에도 이 애보다 오래된 게 있어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00F3F13D
#: 0203BF7E/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF8E
msgctxt "00182C"
msgid "I have. It sounds like she found a piece of X-Tech, but we'll let the doctor confirm."
msgstr "읽어 봤습니다. X-테크 조각을 발견한 것 같더군요. 하지만 확인은 박사에게 맡기죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_08
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 003BB85A
#: 0203BF7F/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_08:0203BF8C
msgctxt "00182D"
msgid "Then it's war."
msgstr "그렇다면 전쟁입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF8B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AdirmalOdeBalewa_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00B25C1E
#: 0203BF80/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF8B
msgctxt "00182E"
msgid "How's production going?"
msgstr "생산은 어떻게 되어 가나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF91
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_07
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 002E2F35
#: 0203BF81/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_07:0203BF91
msgctxt "00182F"
msgid "I mentioned this to Royce, but the first problem is scale. We don't have nearly enough X-Tech to upgrade all the soldiers. "
msgstr "이 얘기는 로이스에게도 했지만, 첫 번째 문제는 규모입니다. 모든 병사를 업그레이드할 만큼 X-테크가 턱없이 부족합니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_SI_Roxane_Vault02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_RoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 009A4EEF
#. Notes = Scared and apologetic.
#: 020A6CDD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault:0203D0F4
msgctxt "001850"
msgid "I'm sorry for locking you in here. I wish I could explain everything right now, but I can't."
msgstr "여기에 가둬서 미안해. 지금 당장 모든 걸 설명할 수 있으면 좋겠지만, 그럴 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_SI_Roxane_Vault03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_RoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0067E5DB
#. Notes = Scared and trying to explain things. Stumbling a bit over her words here and there.
#: 020A6CDC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault:0203D0C8
msgctxt "001851"
msgid "I don't know what's going on and I don't imagine there's much time. So just trust me for now. Please."
msgstr "무슨 일이 벌어지는지 나도 몰라. 시간도 별로 없을 거야. 그러니 지금은 날 믿어 줘. 제발."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_SI_Roxane_Vault01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_RoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00698F73
#. Notes = All she knows are killer robots are after her. Scared, panicking, and trying to explain things. Stumbling a bit over her words here and the
#: 020A6CDA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault:0203D0C3
msgctxt "001852"
msgid "If you're listening to this, then whatever scan those Terrans use to identify us is working, and you're not one of them."
msgstr "이걸 듣고 있다면, 테란들이 우리를 식별하는 데 쓰는 그 스캔이 작동 중이라는 뜻이고, 넌 그들 중 하나가 아니라는 뜻이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_SI_Roxane_Vault04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_RoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00B58659
#. Notes = Scared and trying to explain things. Stumbling a bit over her words here and there.
#: 020A6CDB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0700_Roxane_Vault:0203D0EB
msgctxt "001853"
msgid "Take this chip and place it in a robotic frame. If all goes well, they'll take things from there."
msgstr "이 칩을 가져가서 로봇 프레임에 장착해. 모든 일이 잘 풀리면, 그들이 알아서 이어받을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_SFX_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 006C181E
#: 0203D09C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0CB
msgctxt "001854"
msgid "*door opening sound*"
msgstr "*문 열리는 소리*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Investor_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00D965C1
#: 0203D09E/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0D0
msgctxt "001855"
msgid "But rest assured, I will be having a word with the administration when we get there."
msgstr "하지만 안심하세요. 도착하면 반드시 관리부에 한마디 하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Investor_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 000BAC8E
#: 0203D09F/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0E8
msgctxt "001856"
msgid "I'm sure it's nothing. They do these security drills every so often. Please, continue."
msgstr "별일 아닐 겁니다. 가끔 이런 보안 훈련을 하곤 하니까요. 계속해 주세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Investor_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00102030
#: 0203D0A1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0D5
msgctxt "001857"
msgid "*sigh* I'm afraid the rest of your presentation will have to wait, Ms. Bourreau. Apparently even money can't save us from the tedium of procedure."
msgstr "*한숨* 유감이지만 발표의 나머지는 나중으로 미뤄야겠군요, 부로 씨. 돈으로도 절차의 지루함에서 우리를 구해 주지는 못하는 모양입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Security_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00FC14BA
#: 0203D0A2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0FF
msgctxt "001858"
msgid "I'm afraid we have to make an exception. I can explain more on the way, but we need to get moving to the vaults. "
msgstr "예외를 두어야 할 것 같습니다. 가는 길에 더 설명드리겠습니다만, 지금은 금고로 이동해야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0ED
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Security_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00F60A4B
#: 0203D0A3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0ED
msgctxt "001859"
msgid "Sir, we've come to escort you to a more secure area."
msgstr "선생님, 더 안전한 구역으로 모시러 왔습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_Investor_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00A032A5
#: 0203D0A4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0E4
msgctxt "00185A"
msgid "I understand the importance of you performing these safety exercises, but I pay good money to not be disturbed with such nonsense."
msgstr "이런 안전 훈련을 수행하는 것이 중요하다는 건 이해하지만, 이런 헛소리에 방해받지 않으려고 내가 적지 않은 돈을 내고 있소."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_SystemVoice_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00E08912
#: 0203D0A5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0D2
msgctxt "00185B"
msgid "Emergency procedures initiated. Power routed to backup reserves. Please remain calm."
msgstr "비상 절차 개시. 전력을 예비 전원으로 전환합니다. 침착하게 대기해 주십시오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLog_SFX_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00091F52
#: 0203D0A6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0DC
msgctxt "00185C"
msgid "*ship impact sounds followed by EMP*"
msgstr "*함선 충돌음에 이어 EMP 발생*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_RoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0009C2E3
#. Notes = Excited to show her findings and extremely passionate.
#: 0203D0A7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs_VIPToVault:0203D0CD
msgctxt "00185D"
msgid "As you can already see, these results show the potential for technological advancements in robotics previously thought impo--"
msgstr "이미 보시다시피, 이 결과는 이전에는 불가능하다고 여겨졌던 로봇공학의 기술 발전 가능성을 보여 줍니--"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D163
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00335E74
#. Notes = Utilizing what they JUST learned / to Sarah
#: 0203D154/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203D163
msgctxt "00185E"
msgid "Research deems Sarah Morgan as \"wise\"."
msgstr "연구 결과 사라 모건은 \"현명함\"으로 판단됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D15F
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 0049836E
#. Notes = No I was wrong this was a mess / Tired / to Delta, Face: Tired
#: 0203D155/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203D15F
msgctxt "00185F"
msgid "*Sigh* This will take a while..."
msgstr "*한숨* 시간이 좀 걸리겠군..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D162
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F2B49B
#. Notes = Utilizing what they JUST learned / to Sarah
#: 0203D157/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203D162
msgctxt "001861"
msgid "Initial emotional manipulation attempt successful. Logging..."
msgstr "초기 감정 조작 시도 성공. 기록 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D15D
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sarah
#. SoundFileID = 0026F0DE
#. Notes = well, it might be / Smug / to Delta, Face: Smug
#: 0203D158/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203D15D
msgctxt "001862"
msgid "Wise? Well, I guess I've had some exper-"
msgstr "현명하다고? 뭐, 내가 경험이 좀 있긴--"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D161
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0022D648
#. Notes = Utilizing what they JUST learned / to Sarah
#: 0203D15A/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah01_01:0203D161
msgctxt "001864"
msgid "Of course. Apologies. Have much to learn from leaders such as you."
msgstr "물론입니다. 사과드립니다. 당신 같은 지도자들에게 배울 것이 많습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D15E
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A37B29
#. Notes = Trying to be helpful / to Sarah
#: 0203D15C/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203D15E
msgctxt "001865"
msgid "\"Bullet\" deemed inaccurate."
msgstr "\"총알\"은 부정확한 것으로 판단됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D160
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00421BE7
#. Notes = Deadpan / to Sarah
#: 0203D15B/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sarah00_01:0203D160
msgctxt "001866"
msgid "Acknowledged. Beginning \"Later\" timer..."
