#. SoundFileID = 00BA2280
#. Notes = Technicalities are important / to Barrett
#: 0203D180/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett02_01:0203D18B
msgctxt "001875"
msgid "Incorrect. Only copied. Original notes remain on Dr. Bourreau's database."
msgstr "오류. 복사만 했음. 원본 노트는 부로 박사의 데이터베이스에 남아 있음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D193
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett02
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett02_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 008F26E4
#. Notes = Slowly understanding the situation / Awed / to Delta, Face: Awed
#: 0203D181/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett02_01:0203D193
msgctxt "001876"
msgid "So you stole your creator's notes and gave them to me because you were annoyed?"
msgstr "그러니까 짜증이 나서 네 창조자의 노트를 훔쳐 내게 줬다는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D18D
