#: 0203D183/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett02_01:0203D18D
msgctxt "001878"
msgid "...Completed. Transferring ownership..."
msgstr "...완료. 소유권 이전 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D195
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00BE208A
#. Notes = It's fun to annoy Delta / Amused / to Delta, Face: Amused
#: 0203D186/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01:0203D195
msgctxt "00187A"
msgid "Oh, I think we're going to get along just fine."
msgstr "아, 우리 아주 잘 지내게 될 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D192
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0079EEBB
#. Notes = Autopilot / to Barrett
#: 0203D185/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01:0203D192
msgctxt "00187B"
msgid "Alert: Annoyance levels increased."
msgstr "경보: 짜증 수치 증가."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D194
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A3E016
#. Notes = Yes this, and also it's fun to annoy Delta / Friendly / to Delta, Face: Friendly
#: 0203D189/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01:0203D194
msgctxt "00187D"
msgid "I think I'd rather pick your brain than hers. Go straight to the source."
msgstr "그녀보다는 네 머릿속을 들여다보고 싶어. 바로 원천으로 가야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D196
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0096ABC8
#. Notes = Does not want to talk to Barrett / to Barrett
#: 0203D18A/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett00_01:0203D196
msgctxt "00187E"
msgid "Recommending directing questions regarding X-Tech to her."
msgstr "X-테크 관련 질문은 그녀에게 할 것을 권장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D191
