#. SoundFileID = 0085F990
#. Notes = Wants to end the conversation / to Barrett
#: 0203D184/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Barrett01_01:0203D191
msgctxt "00187F"
msgid "Correct."
msgstr "정확함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0040599F
#: 0203D09A:0203D0F1
msgctxt "001880"
msgid "All possible responses have already been evaluated."
msgstr "가능한 모든 응답은 이미 평가 완료."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 008A0A1A
#: 0203D09A:0203D0F0
msgctxt "001881"
msgid "Processing speed appears... more stunted than average human."
msgstr "처리 속도는... 평균적인 인간보다 더 둔해 보임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00EAC5D0
#: 0203D09A:0203D0EF
msgctxt "001882"
msgid "Do you require repair? I will not hesitate to leave Auxiliary Human behind."
msgstr "수리가 필요한가? 보조 인간을 뒤에 두고 가는 데 주저하지 않겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0FD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 0068E7B2
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0FD
msgctxt "001883"
msgid "Get a move on."
msgstr "움직여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0FC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 0000423E
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0FC
msgctxt "001884"
msgid "I'm keeping an eye on you both."
msgstr "너희 둘 다 지켜보고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0FB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 008F702B
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0FB
msgctxt "001885"
msgid "Watch your back going after that Terran incursion."
msgstr "테란 인커전을 쫓을 때는 뒤를 조심해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 004AF6D3
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0F9
msgctxt "001886"
msgid "This is no time for extended conversation."
msgstr "긴 대화를 나눌 때가 아니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 0031EC0D
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0F8
msgctxt "001887"
msgid "We have objectives we must still complete."
msgstr "아직 완료해야 할 목표가 있다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 005E722B
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0F7
msgctxt "001888"
msgid "Do not worry. If Auxiliary Human cannot continue, I will carry on my mission."
msgstr "걱정하지 마라. 보조 인간이 계속할 수 없다면, 나는 내 임무를 계속 수행하겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00826325
#: 0203D0BF:0203D0F6
msgctxt "001889"
msgid "Follow lead of Delta Unit if you require guidance."
msgstr "지침이 필요하면 델타 기체의 지휘를 따르라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020281AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0009791F
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Prompt: 그러니까 더더욱 지켜봐야지.
#: 020280BF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:020281AD
msgctxt "00188A"
msgid "So you haven't bought into its story fully yet then. At least you're using some shred of sense."
msgstr "그럼 아직 그 이야기에 완전히 넘어간 건 아니군. 그래도 최소한의 판단력은 쓰고 있네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202818D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00A78A3F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 자기 동족과 싸웠잖아. 기회를 줘야 해.
#: 020280D4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0202818D
msgctxt "00188B"
msgid "Looks like it's already won you over... I wonder how worried I should be about that."
msgstr "이미 저 녀석한테 넘어간 것 같은데... 그걸 얼마나 걱정해야 할지 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02028155
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00886514
#. Notes = Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking, Prompt: 네 말이 맞을지도 몰라. 그래도 위험을 감수할 가치는 있어.
#: 020280E1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02028155
msgctxt "00188C"
msgid "It's certainly... a hard sell. But we might not get another chance like this."
msgstr "확실히... 받아들이기 어려운 이야기야. 하지만 이런 기회가 다시 오지 않을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 001E0986
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0203D086/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0E0
msgctxt "00188D"
msgid "To what degree we can trust this unexpected development is up for debate. But I'd be lying if I said I wasn't the least bit curious in learning more."
msgstr "이 뜻밖의 사태를 어느 정도까지 믿을 수 있을지는 논의가 필요합니다. 하지만 더 알고 싶은 마음이 전혀 없다고 하면 거짓말이겠죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 003859B8
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0203D086/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0DF
msgctxt "00188E"
msgid "Won't say I'm buying the whole play nice angle, but don't have any alternative plans in mind. How about you?"
msgstr "그 착하게 굴자는 태도를 전부 믿는 건 아니지만, 딱히 다른 계획도 없어. 넌 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F5C384
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0203D086/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0DE
msgctxt "00188F"
msgid "Teaming up with a death robot, huh? I'm game if you are, but Vasco will always be my number one."
msgstr "죽음의 로봇이랑 한 팀이라니, 응? 네가 좋다면 나도 좋아. 그래도 내 1순위는 언제나 바스코야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00A444FB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203D086/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0DD
msgctxt "001890"
msgid "Not all things remain as they are created. Perhaps we should see what this one does with the gift of life."
msgstr "모든 것이 창조된 모습 그대로 남는 것은 아닙니다. 이 존재가 생명의 선물로 무엇을 하는지 지켜보는 것도 좋겠군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00922AE3
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: [거짓말] 아니야, 이 로봇이 날 인질로 잡았어! 도와줘!
#: 0203D089/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0203D0D9
msgctxt "001891"
msgid "It's not making a case for me not shutting it down."
msgstr "내가 저걸 꺼 버리지 말아야 할 이유를 잘 보여 주고 있진 않은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00B62452
#. Notes = / to Yemoja, Prompt: [거짓말] 아니야, 이 로봇이 날 인질로 잡았어! 도와줘!
#: 0203D08E/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0203D0D4
msgctxt "001892"
msgid "False projection. Limited understanding of humans is low standard for comparison. Does not make incomprehensible subjects \"defective\"."
msgstr "잘못된 투사. 인간에 대한 제한적 이해는 비교 기준으로 부적절함. 이해 불가능한 대상을 \"결함\"으로 만들지는 않음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007776F8
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker, Prompt: 이 회로들은 서로 맞지 않는 부품들을 마치... 살아 있는 것처럼 통합하고 있어.
#: 0203D093/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0DA
msgctxt "001893"
msgid "Analysis rudimentary, but... not inaccurate. Target appears to possess some modicum of observation."
msgstr "분석은 초보적이지만... 틀리지는 않다. 대상에게 어느 정도 관찰력이 있는 것으로 보임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00AFC789
#. Notes = / to DeltaLookMarker
#: 0203D094/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0900_Delta_Intro:0203D0E2
msgctxt "001894"
msgid "These circuits are integrating incompatible components as if they're... alive."
msgstr "이 회로들은 서로 맞지 않는 부품들을 마치... 살아 있는 것처럼 통합하고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00EBD85C
#: 0203D095/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1:0203D0E6
msgctxt "001895"
msgid "There is likely no satisfactory designation Auxiliary Human could comprehend to quantify full understanding of Delta."
msgstr "보조 인간이 델타에 대한 완전한 이해를 정량화할 수 있는 만족스러운 명칭은 아마 없을 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0EA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 001312FB
#: 0203D096/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1:0203D0EA
msgctxt "001896"
msgid "Counter-argument: humans are just less advanced programs."
msgstr "반론: 인간도 덜 발전한 프로그램일 뿐이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00F5AF5E
#: 0203D0A8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2:0203D0CE
msgctxt "001897"
msgid "Solution: if gravity disruption ceases, spatial technology will once again become functional."
msgstr "해결책: 중력 교란이 중단되면, 공간 기술은 다시 기능할 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0067A546
#: 0203D0A9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2:0203D0C9
msgctxt "001898"
msgid "Gravity disruption technology useful to prevent reinforcements from converging within the systems they are deployed."
msgstr "중력 교란 기술은 배치된 성계 안에서 지원 병력이 집결하는 것을 막는 데 유용하다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00ADABA2
#: 0203D0AA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2:0203D0C4
msgctxt "001899"
msgid "Terrans possess apparatus that causes anomalous spikes in gravitational waves, leaving your rudimentary drives unable to calculate proper warp vectors."
msgstr "테란은 중력파에 이상 급증을 일으키는 장치를 보유하고 있으며, 그 결과 너희의 조잡한 구동기는 올바른 워프 벡터를 계산할 수 없게 된다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0FE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E25532
#: 0203D0AB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL2:0203D0FE
msgctxt "00189A"
msgid "How did they shut our grav jump systems down?"
msgstr "그들이 어떻게 우리 중력 도약 시스템을 차단한 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0EC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0041FDD2
#: 0203D0AC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1:0203D0EC
msgctxt "00189B"
msgid "Gravitational disruption key to Terran incursion strategy. If main forces are eliminated, auxiliary forces will retreat."
msgstr "중력 교란은 테란 인커전 전략의 핵심. 주 병력이 제거되면 보조 병력은 퇴각할 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0071634F
#: 0203D0AD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1:0203D0E7
msgctxt "00189C"
msgid "Numbers certain to overwhelm biologically limited Auxiliary Human, but Delta Unit is enough to raise odds of success."
msgstr "생물학적으로 제한된 보조 인간이 감당하기엔 수가 압도적일 것이 확실하나, 성공 확률을 높이기에는 델타 기체면 충분하다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006D46F5
#: 0203D0AE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1:0203D0D6
msgctxt "00189D"
msgid "Most likely outcome: concentrated Terran resistance force."
msgstr "가장 가능성 높은 결과: 집중된 테란 저항 병력."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0DB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C1A88B
#: 0203D0AF/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1300_Delta_TL1:0203D0DB
msgctxt "00189E"
msgid "What are we going to find at the source of this Grav Jammer?"
msgstr "이 중력 교란기의 근원에서 우린 뭘 발견하게 될까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00933E6D
#: 0203D0B0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2:0203D0D1
msgctxt "00189F"
msgid "Humans individually possess limited usefulness. However, true aims likely lie in creation of technology with no limit of potential."
msgstr "인간 개체는 제한적인 유용성만 가진다. 그러나 진정한 목적은 잠재력에 한계가 없는 기술의 창조일 가능성이 높다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00653E43
#: 0203D0B3/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2:0203D0F2
msgctxt "0018A0"
msgid "Do you know why the Terrans were after your creator?"
msgstr "테란이 왜 네 창조자를 노렸는지 알아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 005B7C68
#: 0203D0B1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2:0203D0E3
msgctxt "0018A1"
msgid "However, even with an army of mere imitations attempting to approach Delta Unit, the universe could be shaped as one desires."
msgstr "하지만 델타 기체에 접근하려는 단순한 모조품의 군대가 있더라도, 우주는 원하는 대로 빚어질 수 있다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009D438B
#: 0203D0B2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL2:0203D0CC
msgctxt "0018A2"
msgid "Alone, Delta Unit represents culmination of the best humanity has to offer, taken even further through my own transcendence. Experiment cannot be replicated."
msgstr ""
"단독으로도 델타 기체는 인류가 제공할 수 있는 최상의 결정체이며, 나 자신의 초월을 통해 그 이상으로 나아갔다. 실험은 복제 불가능하다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00D5F552
#: 0203D0B4/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1:0203D0C7
msgctxt "0018A3"
msgid "Like most developments accidentally discovered by humanity, Delta Unit has transcended those that led to my creation."
msgstr "인류가 우연히 발견한 대부분의 발전처럼, 델타 기체는 나의 창조로 이어진 존재들을 초월했다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F55A8C
#: 0203D0B5/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_Delta_TL1:0203D0C1
msgctxt "0018A4"
msgid "So, you're basically just some sort of advanced program?"
msgstr "그러니까 넌 기본적으로 일종의 고급 프로그램이라는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001FB6E6
#: 0203D0B6/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2:0203D0F3
msgctxt "0018A5"
msgid "If you want answers, going there's your best bet."
msgstr "답을 원한다면, 거기로 가는 게 가장 확실해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00351A9B
#: 0203D0B7/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2:0203D0E5
msgctxt "0018A6"
msgid "Besides, I'm sure there are plenty of questions you have for what's happening now and how to stop it."
msgstr "게다가 지금 무슨 일이 벌어지고 있는지, 그걸 어떻게 막을지 묻고 싶은 것도 많을 테고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00A2C0F2
#: 0203D0B8/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2:0203D0E9
msgctxt "0018A7"
msgid "No matter how good you think you are, you can't win a war by yourselves. You're going to need people -- powerful people -- backing you up."
msgstr "네가 아무리 대단하다고 생각해도 너희끼리 전쟁에서 이길 수는 없어. 사람들이 필요해. 그것도 힘 있는 사람들이 뒤를 받쳐 줘야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00CAEF78
#: 0203D0B9/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2:0203D0E1
msgctxt "0018A8"
msgid "This thing's bigger than either of us. Bigger than your friend, too."
msgstr "이 일은 우리 둘보다 더 커. 네 친구보다도 더 크고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0029E753
#: 0203D0BA/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL2:0203D0D8
msgctxt "0018A9"
msgid "What exactly is waiting for me at Anchorpoint?"
msgstr "앵커포인트에서 정확히 뭐가 날 기다리고 있지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ADB6D4
#: 0203D0BB/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1:0203D0D3
msgctxt "0018AA"
msgid "Looks like I was right on both counts."
msgstr "두 가지 모두 내 말이 맞았던 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00473859
#: 0203D0BC/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1:0203D0CF
msgctxt "0018AB"
msgid "Wasn't sure if someone managed to track it or if the Terrans were gearing up for another move, so I jumped over fast as I could."
msgstr "누가 그걸 추적한 건지, 아니면 테란이 또 다른 움직임을 준비하는 건지 확신이 없어서 최대한 빨리 도약해 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EF665D
#: 0203D0BD/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1:0203D0CA
msgctxt "0018AC"
msgid "Cruise ship here lit up and sent out a distress beacon not too long ago. I'm assuming you're the one who turned the lights back on."
msgstr "여기 유람선이 얼마 전에 불이 켜지고 조난 신호를 보냈어. 불을 다시 켠 게 너라고 보고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0070E510
#: 0203D0BE/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1200_Yemoja_TL1:0203D0C5
msgctxt "0018AD"
msgid "How did you track me out here so fast?"
msgstr "어떻게 이렇게 빨리 날 여기까지 추적한 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D0C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_0510_ElevatorVIPVoice
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ElevatorVoice
#. SoundFileID = 007CB9DA
#. Notes = Elevator system voice, speaker pre-recorded, informational / to Player Default
#: 0203D0C0/00000/SFTER_MQ01_0510_ElevatorVIPVoice:0203D0C2
msgctxt "0018AE"
msgid "VIP Card required for elevator access."
msgstr "엘리베이터 이용에는 VIP 카드가 필요합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0450_GUARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranGuard02
#. SoundFileID = 006A8D67
#. Notes = Annoyed, angry, and also pretty scared their having to look for a missing scientist while rogue robots are attacking everyone on sight. / to TerranGuard01
#: 0203CDC7/00450/SFTER_MQ02B_0450_GUARD:0203CDD0
msgctxt "0018AF"
msgid "You don't have to tell me twice. But we have an order. Let's just find her corpse and get the hell out of here."
msgstr "두 번 말할 필요 없어. 하지만 명령이 있잖아. 그냥 그 여자 시체를 찾아서 여기서 꺼지자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0450_GUARD
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranGuard01
#. SoundFileID = 0022D13A
#. Notes = Annoyed, angry, and also pretty scared their having to look for a missing scientist while rogue robots are attacking everyone on sight. / to TerranGuard02
#: 0203CDC8/00450/SFTER_MQ02B_0450_GUARD:0203CDCD
msgctxt "0018B0"
msgid "Facility going sideways and they still want us to find that damned scientist. She's a lost cause. Probably dead by now."
msgstr "시설이 엉망이 됐는데도 아직 그 빌어먹을 과학자를 찾으라니. 그 여자는 이미 끝났어. 아마 지금쯤 죽었겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranShip
#. SoundFileID = 0061BBA2, 00B42D27, 00ACA0B8
#. Notes = Panicked as they just got out of the factory with their life and trying to warn others/ask the Terran head ship if they can evacuate., Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Still panicked, but then something goes wrong on the ship and they get startled., Scared as they spot a robot on board. Now they are trying to get the message across before the robot kills them. In the end, it does kill them.
#: 0203CDC9/00300/SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP:0203CDCA
msgctxt "0018B1"
msgid "How'd you get in here? Shit! Requesting evacuation of facility. The facility needs to be- Argh!"
msgstr "어떻게 여기 들어온 거야? 젠장! 시설 대피를 요청한다. 시설은 이제- 아악!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranShip
#. SoundFileID = 0061BBA2, 00B42D27, 00ACA0B8
#. Notes = Panicked as they just got out of the factory with their life and trying to warn others/ask the Terran head ship if they can evacuate., Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Still panicked, but then something goes wrong on the ship and they get startled., Scared as they spot a robot on board. Now they are trying to get the message across before the robot kills them. In the end, it does kill them.
#: 0203CDC9/00300/SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP:0203CDCA
msgctxt "0018B2"
msgid "I repeat. the facility is lost. Requesting-"
msgstr "반복한다. 시설은 상실됐다. 요청--"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TerranShip
#. SoundFileID = 0061BBA2, 00B42D27, 00ACA0B8
#. Notes = Panicked as they just got out of the factory with their life and trying to warn others/ask the Terran head ship if they can evacuate., Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Still panicked, but then something goes wrong on the ship and they get startled., Scared as they spot a robot on board. Now they are trying to get the message across before the robot kills them. In the end, it does kill them.
#: 0203CDC9/00300/SFTER_MQ02B_0300_SHIP:0203CDCA
msgctxt "0018B3"
msgid "Terran production line is lost. Requesting entire evacuation of facility."
msgstr "테란 생산 라인이 상실됐다. 시설 전체 대피를 요청한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0201A444
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00F95FDC, 002F2B1A
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Irritated / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0201A3D5/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0201A444
msgctxt "0018B4"
msgid "Whether you still want to do this or not, you know of us and the Terrans. There's no going back now."
msgstr "아직 이 일을 계속하고 싶은지와는 상관없이, 당신은 우리와 테란에 대해 알게 됐습니다. 이제 되돌아갈 수는 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00D3F2D0
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 너희 모두 대중에게 거짓말을 했군. 테란을 없애고 싶어 하는 것도 당연하네.
#: 0203CDBC/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD6
msgctxt "0018B5"
msgid "It was a lie for the greater good. Besides, the Terrans pose a threat to more than just an old lie. We all have seen what's at stake."
msgstr "더 큰 선을 위한 거짓말이었소. 게다가 테란은 오래된 거짓말 하나보다 훨씬 더 큰 위협이오. 무엇이 걸려 있는지는 우리 모두 보았지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00142F45
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 물론이지. 이렇게 오랜 시간이 지나도 식민지 전쟁은 여전히 모두에게 문제를 일으키고 있군.
#: 0203CDBE/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD4
msgctxt "0018B6"
msgid "That is how war works, no? It's never so simple."
msgstr "그게 전쟁이라는 것 아니겠습니까? 그렇게 단순한 일이 아니죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00AB37D7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDBD/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD5
msgctxt "0018B7"
msgid "You all lied to the public. No wonder you want the Terrans destroyed."
msgstr "너희 모두 대중에게 거짓말을 했군. 테란을 없애고 싶어 하는 것도 당연하네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00A64529
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDBF/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD3
msgctxt "0018B8"
msgid "Of course, after all this time the Colony War is still causing everyone issues."
msgstr "물론이지. 이렇게 오랜 시간이 지나도 식민지 전쟁은 여전히 모두에게 문제를 일으키고 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0037142B
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 나는 테란의 기원 따위에는 관심 없소. 내가 신경 쓰는 건 그들을 파괴하는 것뿐이오.
#: 0203CDC0/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD2
msgctxt "0018B9"
msgid "Good. Then we are all on the same page."
msgstr "좋습니다. 그럼 우리는 모두 같은 생각이군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002E846A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC1/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD1
msgctxt "0018BA"
msgid "I don't care about the Terrans' origins. All I care about is destroying them."
msgstr "나는 테란의 기원 따위에는 관심 없소. 내가 신경 쓰는 건 그들을 파괴하는 것뿐이오."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00EB47FF
#. Notes = Serious and professional. There is a faint hint of threat to the player at the end. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 그렇다면 철저히 지켜야 하는 비밀이겠군?
#: 0203CDC2/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCF
msgctxt "0018BB"
msgid "Indeed. And we will be trusting you to keep it. I hope there are no issues in our future regarding this."
msgstr "그렇습니다. 그리고 우리는 당신이 그 비밀을 지켜 주리라 믿겠습니다. 앞으로 이와 관련해 문제가 없기를 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0017872A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC3/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCC
msgctxt "0018BC"
msgid "This must be a tightly kept secret then?"
msgstr "그렇다면 철저히 지켜야 하는 비밀이겠군?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 004F17F5
#. Notes = Serious and professional. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Prompt: 왜 이 모든 걸 대중에게 숨긴 거지?
#: 0203CDC4/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCB
msgctxt "0018BD"
msgid "To say two ships disappeared with one another would create questions during our time of war. Then would come doubt. Then conspiracies. Everything we didn't need during a time of vulnerability."
msgstr "두 함선이 서로 함께 사라졌다고 말하면 전시에는 의문이 생겼을 겁니다. 그다음엔 의심이 뒤따르고, 그다음엔 음모론이 뒤따르죠. 취약한 시기에 필요 없던 모든 것들이 말입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDD7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B35B92
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC5/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDD7
msgctxt "0018BE"
msgid "Why hide all this from the public?"
msgstr "왜 이 모든 걸 대중에게 숨긴 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B2DF42, 00F0614A, 008B6CE4, 00E69E7F (+1 more)
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCE
msgctxt "0018BF"
msgid "We don't know why they left the battle, or why they have now returned. All we know is the threat they currently pose."
msgstr "그들이 왜 전투를 떠났는지, 왜 지금 돌아왔는지는 모릅니다. 우리가 아는 건 그들이 현재 가하는 위협뿐입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B2DF42, 00F0614A, 008B6CE4, 00E69E7F (+1 more)
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCE
msgctxt "0018C0"
msgid "As far as the public knows, the two sides destroyed one another. But as we've since discovered, they banded together to form what we now know as the Terran Armada."
msgstr ""
"대중이 아는 바로는 양측이 서로를 파괴했습니다. 하지만 이후 우리가 알아낸 바로는, 그들은 힘을 합쳐 지금 우리가 테란 함대라고 부르는 "
"것을 결성했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B2DF42, 00F0614A, 008B6CE4, 00E69E7F (+1 more)
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCE
msgctxt "0018C1"
msgid "However, instead of following through with the battle, the commanders of their respective fleets met with one another. Last we knew both fleets vanished side by side."
msgstr "하지만 전투를 끝까지 수행하는 대신, 각 함대의 지휘관들이 서로 만났습니다. 우리가 마지막으로 알던 것은 두 함대가 횡대로 사라졌다는 사실입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B2DF42, 00F0614A, 008B6CE4, 00E69E7F (+1 more)
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCE
msgctxt "0018C2"
msgid "I have no doubt you know of the Colony War. During that time there was a large battle between a Freestar and United Colony fleet at the edge of the Settled Systems."
msgstr "식민지 전쟁에 대해서는 당연히 알고 계실 겁니다. 그 시기 개척 성계의 가장자리에서 자유항성과 식민지 연합 함대 사이에 큰 전투가 있었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203CDCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B2DF42, 00F0614A, 008B6CE4, 00E69E7F (+1 more)
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203CDC6/00175/SFTER_MQ02A_0175_VOID:0203CDCE
msgctxt "0018C3"
msgid "Before we speak of this any further, if you are to be our partner in this mission, we must be honest with you regarding the Terran's origins."
msgstr "이 이야기를 더 진행하기 전에, 당신이 이 임무의 협력자가 되려면 테란의 기원에 대해 솔직히 말씀드려야 합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D150
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00817D0D
#. Notes = Backhand / to Player Default, Prompt: 이게 어떻게 끝날지 넌 마음에 안 들어할 거야.
#: 0203D14A/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D150
msgctxt "0018C4"
msgid "Noted: Auxiliary experiences hallucinations prior to combat. Fear response?"
msgstr "기록: 보조 인간은 전투 전 환각을 경험함. 공포 반응인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D14F
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CC6163
#. Notes = Conclusive. / to Player Default, Prompt: 이게 어떻게 끝날지 넌 마음에 안 들어할 거야.
#: 0203D14A/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D14F
msgctxt "0018C5"
msgid "Nor will you."
msgstr "너도 그럴 일은 없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D152
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00373E16
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203D14B/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D152
msgctxt "0018C6"
msgid "I'm glad I get a do-over at this."
msgstr "이번에는 다시 해 볼 기회가 생겨서 기뻐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D151
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0089B78A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203D14B/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D151
msgctxt "0018C7"
msgid "You're not going to like how this ends."
msgstr "이게 어떻게 끝날지 넌 마음에 안 들어할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D153
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CF213F
#. Notes = A little snarky. "Oh aren't you chipper" / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 순간을 기다려 왔어.
#: 0203D14C/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D153
msgctxt "0018C8"
msgid "Combative eagerness and preparedness noted."
msgstr "전투적 열의와 준비 상태 기록됨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D14E
#. QuestName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04
#. SceneName = SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E9DE8C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0203D14D/00001/SFTER_EC_Robot_Q04_01_PreCombat:0203D14E
msgctxt "0018C9"
msgid "I've been waiting for this."
msgstr "이 순간을 기다려 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_EC_Robot_Q03_RevivifyBark_2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D143
msgctxt "0018CA"
msgid "Anna? What happened to Anna?"
msgstr "애나? 애나에게 무슨 일이 있었죠?"

