#: 0203D1A2/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam00_01:0203D1A8
msgctxt "0018EE"
msgid "Not like that. Not like that at all."
msgstr "그런 뜻이 아니야. 전혀 아니라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D1A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Sam
#. SoundFileID = 0002EA3E
#. Notes = Embarrassed at how angry they were / Grateful / to Delta, Face: Grateful
#: 0203D19E/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203D1A6
msgctxt "0018F0"
msgid "I just don't want her around these things unsupervised. They're dangerous if you're not handling them properly."
msgstr "그냥 걔가 감독 없이 이런 것들 주변에 있지 않았으면 하는 거야. 제대로 다루지 않으면 위험하니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D1A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01
