#: 0203D19F/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Sam01_01:0203D1A5
msgctxt "0018F1"
msgid "*Sigh* Look, I'm sorry for getting so heated. I know you were just trying to help."
msgstr "*한숨* 들어 봐, 그렇게 흥분해서 미안해. 네가 도와주려고 했다는 건 알아."

