#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D33A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 0020B042
#: 0203D0BF:0203D33A
msgctxt "0018F5"
msgid "I'm trusting you here. Don't make me regret it."
msgstr "이번엔 널 믿는 거야. 후회하게 만들지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203D339
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00C72771
#: 0203D0BF:0203D339
msgctxt "0018F6"
msgid "Waiting on you to handle that Grav Jammer -- it won't take itself out. At least I don't think so."
msgstr "네가 그 중력 교란기를 처리하길 기다리고 있어. 저절로 없어지진 않을 테니까. 적어도 내 생각엔 그래."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ01_YemojaEMP03_Shared
