msgid "Our work here is done."
msgstr "우리 일은 끝났습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Andreja_ScoutingPartyComplete02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00305434
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF2
msgctxt "0019A5"
msgid "One less source of intel for the enemy."
msgstr "적의 정보원 하나가 줄었습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Andreja_ScoutingPartyComplete01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 009B755A
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF3
msgctxt "0019A6"
msgid "A decisive win. These Terrans were no match."
msgstr "결정적 승리입니다. 이 테란들은 상대가 되지 못했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Sam_ScoutingPartyComplete01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
