#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00D20668
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF9
msgctxt "0019A7"
msgid "That's one source of intel they'll be missing."
msgstr "저들이 잃게 될 정보원 하나가 줄었군."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Sarah_ScoutingPartyComplete02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAFD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00E2C5EC
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAFD
msgctxt "0019A8"
msgid "That's one source of intel the Terrans won't be getting."
msgstr "테란이 얻지 못할 정보원 하나가 줄었군요."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Sarah_ScoutingPartyComplete01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAFE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 000E11C1
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAFE
msgctxt "0019A9"
msgid "A small victory for us. Let's hope the Terrans feel it."
msgstr "우리에게는 작은 승리군요. 테란도 타격을 느끼길 바랍니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBAB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0006B7E8
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EBAB
msgctxt "0019AA"
msgid "Let's put these Terrans in their place."
msgstr "이 테란들에게 제자리를 알려 주자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBAA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00ED2E9B
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EBAA
msgctxt "0019AB"
msgid "There's the patrol. Let's take them out."
msgstr "저기 순찰대가 있군. 처리하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBA6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 002D6962
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EBA6
msgctxt "0019AC"
msgid "Time to take out some ships."
msgstr "함선 좀 처리할 시간이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBA5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00DD18E1
#. Notes = Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EBA5
msgctxt "0019AD"
msgid "Let's show these Terrans who's boss."
msgstr "테란들에게 누가 우위인지 보여 주자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBA0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00041014
#. Notes = Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EBA0
msgctxt "0019AE"
msgid "Something tells me they won't be happy to see us."
msgstr "왠지 우리를 보면 좋아하지 않을 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB9F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00064578
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB9F
msgctxt "0019AF"
msgid "Let's give this patrol something to find."
msgstr "이 순찰대가 찾을 만한 걸 하나 던져 주자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB9B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 007CBFA2
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB9B
msgctxt "0019B0"
msgid "Let us make quick work of them."
msgstr "빠르게 처리합시다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB9A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00BBDA33
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB79/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB9A
msgctxt "0019B1"
msgid "This patrol will be their last."
msgstr "이 순찰은 그들의 마지막이 될 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB96
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 006639E4
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB96
msgctxt "0019B2"
msgid "Guess we know which side has the better pilots now, don't we?"
msgstr "이제 어느 쪽 조종사가 더 나은지 알겠지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB93
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00566A57
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB93
msgctxt "0019B3"
msgid "Solid shooting. Can't say the same for those Terrans."
msgstr "좋은 사격이었어. 저 테란들은 아니었지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB92
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 006783C5
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB92
msgctxt "0019B4"
msgid "One patrol down for the count."
msgstr "순찰대 하나 완전히 처리했군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB90
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00B9D3E1
#. Notes = Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB90
msgctxt "0019B5"
msgid "And that's why you're the pilot and I'm the passenger."
msgstr "그래서 네가 조종사고 내가 승객인 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB8F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0095ACFB
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB8F
msgctxt "0019B6"
msgid "Think the Terrans know they're funding some scavenger's whole operation?"
msgstr "테란들이 자기들이 어떤 폐품업자의 사업 전체를 대 주고 있다는 걸 알까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB8E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_SpacePatrol01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 002B3467
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB78/00000/SFTER_INC_SPP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB8E
msgctxt "0019B7"
msgid "One less Terran thorn in our side."
msgstr "우리 옆구리의 테란 가시가 하나 줄었군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00E08ECE
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB1F
msgctxt "0019B8"
msgid "Well done. Couldn't have handled it better myself."
msgstr "잘했어. 나라도 이보다 더 잘하진 못했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB1E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 004E1E02
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB1E
msgctxt "0019B9"
msgid "I hate to think how many other Terrans are fighting for a cause they don't believe in."
msgstr "얼마나 많은 테란이 믿지도 않는 대의를 위해 싸우고 있을지 생각하기도 싫어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB1D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00468010
#. Notes = are they? is not asking question, but more of a statement. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB1D
msgctxt "0019BA"
msgid "The Terran Armada's cracks are showing. Not so unified after all, are they?"
msgstr "테란 함대에도 균열이 보이는군. 결국 그렇게 단결된 건 아니었어, 그렇지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB1B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00495E22
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB1B
msgctxt "0019BB"
msgid "Damn Terran Armada. I hate to think how many others just want out at this point."
msgstr "빌어먹을 테란 함대. 지금쯤 얼마나 많은 사람이 빠져나가고 싶어 할지 생각하기도 싫어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB1A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00D57BBB
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB1A
msgctxt "0019BC"
msgid "That's one way to take out a scouting party."
msgstr "정찰대를 처리하는 방법도 참 다양하네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB19
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00491A91
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB19
msgctxt "0019BD"
msgid "I know what it's like to feel trapped. I'm glad these people are getting out."
msgstr "갇힌 기분이 어떤 건지 알아. 이 사람들이 빠져나가게 돼서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB17
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00682791
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB17
msgctxt "0019BE"
msgid "Makes you wonder how many Terrans believe their rhetoric versus the ones who are too afraid to leave."
msgstr "테란 중에 얼마나 많은 이들이 그 선전을 진심으로 믿고, 또 얼마나 많은 이들이 겁나서 못 떠나는 건지 궁금해지네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB16
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00948A79
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB16
msgctxt "0019BF"
msgid "It's a different sort of win, but I'll take it."
msgstr "종류는 좀 다르지만 승리는 승리지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB15
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0041574A
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB15
msgctxt "0019C0"
msgid "The Terran Armada is like one big toxic relationship."
msgstr "테란 함대는 그냥 거대한 불건전한 관계 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB13
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 005DEDD6
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB13
msgctxt "0019C1"
msgid "Taking the opportunity to escape is the first brave action these people have done."
msgstr "탈출할 기회를 붙잡은 게 이 사람들이 처음으로 해낸 용감한 행동이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB12
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00552654
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB12
msgctxt "0019C2"
msgid "The Terran Armada is not as unified as one may think."
msgstr "테란 함대는 생각만큼 하나로 뭉쳐 있지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB11
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0041817A
#. Notes = Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0203EAEC/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EB11
msgctxt "0019C3"
msgid "An unexpected outcome."
msgstr "예상 밖의 결과군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAFF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 000FD34C
#. Notes = Disgust, Face: Disgust
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAFF
msgctxt "0019C4"
msgid "Why sacrifice human lives when robots would suffice? Terran logic is beyond me."
msgstr "로봇이면 충분한데 왜 인간의 목숨을 희생시키는 거지? 테란의 논리는 이해가 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAFB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 007F7065
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAFB
msgctxt "0019C5"
msgid "Hope the Terrans really feel this loss. Sacrificing human lives when they could've just sent their bots."
msgstr "테란이 이 손실을 제대로 실감했으면 좋겠어. 그냥 로봇을 보내도 됐을 걸 인간 목숨을 희생시키다니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAFA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0064EB7D
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAFA
msgctxt "0019C6"
msgid "Scouting party down. Let's hope the Terrans got nothing."
msgstr "정찰대 격파. 테란이 아무것도 얻지 못했길 바라자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 008570F3
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF7
msgctxt "0019C7"
msgid "Scouting party no more, and no more intel for the Terrans."
msgstr "정찰대는 사라졌고, 테란에게 넘어갈 정보도 없어졌어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00D2F22A
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF6
msgctxt "0019C8"
msgid "Without their bots, I bet they couldn't transmit any intel before we found them."
msgstr "로봇들이 없었으니, 우리가 찾기 전에 어떤 정보도 전송하지 못했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EAF5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00EAD877
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAED/10000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_CompleteScene:0203EAF5
msgctxt "0019C9"
msgid "They won't be writing home anytime soon."
msgstr "당분간 고향에 편지 쓸 일은 없겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00A5BBBF
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB0F
msgctxt "0019CA"
msgid "Do they really think they can fool us again?"
msgstr "정말 또 우리를 속일 수 있다고 생각하는 건가?"

#. List: 2
