#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB0B
msgctxt "0019CD"
msgid "Whatever you do, I'll back you up."
msgstr "네가 뭘 하든 내가 엄호해 줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
