#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB07
msgctxt "0019D0"
msgid "Let's shut this party down."
msgstr "이 판은 여기서 끝내자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
