#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB06
msgctxt "0019D1"
msgid "Think they're in the mood to socialize?"
msgstr "쟤들이 대화할 기분일까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB05
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 003F56F2
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB05
msgctxt "0019D2"
msgid "I'll follow your lead."
msgstr "네 지시에 따를게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB03
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 003D7904
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB03
msgctxt "0019D3"
msgid "These Terrans fool no one. Stay alert."
msgstr "저 테란들은 아무도 못 속여. 경계해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB02
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F12609
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB02
msgctxt "0019D4"
msgid "Civilian disguises again. Cowards."
msgstr "또 민간인 변장이야. 겁쟁이들."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB01
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 007D87D4
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEE/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB01
msgctxt "0019D5"
msgid "Your call, but I advise caution."
msgstr "네 판단에 맡기겠지만, 조심하는 게 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB23
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00E0A408
#. Notes = Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203EAEF/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB23
msgctxt "0019D6"
msgid "Those Terrans are woefully mistaken if they think they can pass as civilians."
msgstr "민간인 행세가 통할 거라고 생각한다면 저 테란들은 한참 착각한 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB22
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0050D9E3
#. Notes = Terrans are disguised as civilians. / Amused, Face: Amused
#: 0203EAEF/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB22
msgctxt "0019D7"
msgid "Are those Terrans playing civilian dress-up?"
msgstr "저 테란들, 민간인 분장 놀이라도 하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB21
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C7D4B1
#. Notes = Toys as in robots. Groups of just humans are rare for the Terrans. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0203EAEF/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB21
msgctxt "0019D8"
msgid "A bunch of Terrans without their toys? This is new."
msgstr "장난감 없는 테란 무리라니? 이건 새롭네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EB20
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00BDCC9D
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EAEF/00100/SFTER_INC_SCP01_Companion_StartScene:0203EB20
msgctxt "0019D9"
msgid "They appear as civilians. Do not be fooled."
msgstr "민간인처럼 보입니다. 속지 마십시오."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Intercom_Propaganda05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBB3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultShipEnforcer01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = IntercomMotivational
#. SoundFileID = 00A01C99
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB7A/00000/SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene:0203EBB3
msgctxt "0019DA"
msgid "While the Settled Systems fight among themselves, we fight for the advancement and glory of humanity. "
msgstr "개척 성계가 서로 싸우는 동안, 우리는 인류의 진보와 영광을 위해 싸운다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Intercom_Propaganda04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBB2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultShipEnforcer01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = IntercomMotivational
#. SoundFileID = 00B9706C
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB7A/00000/SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene:0203EBB2
msgctxt "0019DB"
msgid "Humanity only survives under the unified banner of the Terran Armada."
msgstr "인류는 테란 함대의 통일된 깃발 아래에서만 생존한다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Intercom_Propaganda03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultShipEnforcer01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = IntercomMotivational
#. SoundFileID = 005D1DE3
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB7A/00000/SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene:0203EBB1
msgctxt "0019DC"
msgid "The Terran Armada is the only true course. Those who oppose us, oppose humanity."
msgstr "테란 함대만이 유일한 참된 길이다. 우리에게 맞서는 자는 인류에게 맞서는 자다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Intercom_Propaganda02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBB0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultShipEnforcer01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = IntercomMotivational
#. SoundFileID = 00310916
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB7A/00000/SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene:0203EBB0
msgctxt "0019DD"
msgid "We are the true children of Earth and will reclaim what is rightfully ours."
msgstr "우리는 지구의 참된 자녀이며, 마땅히 우리의 것인 것을 되찾을 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_Intercom_Propaganda01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203EBAF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MAJ_AssaultShipEnforcer01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = IntercomMotivational
#. SoundFileID = 0094821E
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0203EB7A/00000/SFTER_INC_ASE01_Intercom_MotivationalScene:0203EBAF
msgctxt "0019DE"
msgid "The Settled Systems has lost their way. It is our duty to remind them and preserve the human race."
msgstr "개척 성계는 길을 잃었다. 그들에게 상기시키고 인류를 보존하는 것이 우리의 의무다."

