#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042480
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003DE615
#: 0204245B/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene:02042480
msgctxt "001AB9"
msgid "Please don't risk the lives of everyone here. There are other ways."
msgstr "제발 여기 있는 모두의 목숨을 위험에 빠뜨리지 마. 다른 방법이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B2D49F
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Don't force my hand. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0204245C/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene:020424AB
msgctxt "001ABA"
msgid "I'm not, we're simply not Terrans."
msgstr "아니야, 우린 그냥 테란이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00ECF294
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: Don't force my hand. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0204245C/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene:020424AA
msgctxt "001ABB"
msgid "Hey, there's no need to be hasty..."
msgstr "이봐, 성급하게 굴 필요 없잖아..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0006F3ED
#: 02042457/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene:0204248A
msgctxt "001ABC"
msgid "I know this is an act. I can see right through it."
msgstr "이거 연기인 거 알아. 다 꿰뚫어 보고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002B2654
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Please don't risk the lives of everyone here. There are other ways. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 0204245A/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene:020424E5
msgctxt "001ABD"
msgid "That may be so, but there's nothing to talk about. We're not Terrans."
msgstr "그럴 수도 있겠지만, 얘기할 건 없어. 우린 테란이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0012AFB3
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: Please don't risk the lives of everyone here. There are other ways. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0204245A/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc02Scene:020424E4
msgctxt "001ABE"
msgid "I don't want to risk anyone's life..."
msgstr "누구의 목숨도 위험하게 하고 싶지 않아..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042487
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B3C7CC
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: I know this is an act. I can see right through it. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02042456/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene:02042487
msgctxt "001ABF"
msgid "Please. This is ridiculous."
msgstr "제발. 이건 말도 안 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042486
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000BB725
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: I know this is an act. I can see right through it. (Nervous denial) / Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 02042456/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc04Scene:02042486
msgctxt "001AC0"
msgid "What? You can't be serious..."
msgstr "뭐? 진심일 리가 없어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042498
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007F80EE
#: 02042459/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene:02042498
msgctxt "001AC1"
msgid "Believe it or not, I want to help you."
msgstr "믿든 말든, 난 널 돕고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D3222D
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Believe it or not, I want to help you. / Serious, Face: Serious
#: 02042458/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene:020424E3
msgctxt "001AC2"
msgid "But we're not Terrans. We don't need help."
msgstr "하지만 우린 테란이 아니야. 도움은 필요 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F73F91
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: Believe it or not, I want to help you. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02042458/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc03Scene:020424E2
msgctxt "001AC3"
msgid "Help us? I'm not sure what you're saying..."
msgstr "우리를 도와? 무슨 말인지 잘 모르겠는데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0047BE53
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Trust me, we can work this out. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C6
msgctxt "001AC4"
msgid "I don't know how many different ways I can tell you that we're not Terrans."
msgstr "우리가 테란이 아니라고 대체 몇 번이나 말해야 할지 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0087E739
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Trust me, we can work this out. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C5
msgctxt "001AC5"
msgid "You know the truth. We're just surveyors."
msgstr "당신도 사실을 알잖아. 우린 그냥 탐사원이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B294DB
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: Trust me, we can work this out. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C4
msgctxt "001AC6"
msgid "We're surveyors, nothing more, nothing less."
msgstr "우린 탐사원이야. 그 이상도 이하도 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
