#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C2
msgctxt "001AC7"
msgid "It's great that you want to talk, it really is..."
msgstr "대화하고 싶다는 건 좋아, 정말로..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0042BDC7
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: Trust me, we can work this out. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C1
msgctxt "001AC8"
msgid "I see where you're coming from, I really do..."
msgstr "네가 왜 그러는지는 알아, 정말이야..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0034E74E
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: Trust me, we can work this out. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 02042460/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:020424C0
msgctxt "001AC9"
msgid "I can see how you're being fair..."
msgstr "공정하게 하려는 건 알겠어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204250B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002320F1
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0204250B
msgctxt "001ACA"
msgid "You would attack us without any proof?"
msgstr "아무 증거도 없이 우릴 공격하겠다고?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204250A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00513861
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:0204250A
msgctxt "001ACB"
msgid "But we're innocent. You can't possibly be serious."
msgstr "하지만 우린 결백해. 진심일 리가 없잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042509
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00349E24
#. Notes = Speech challenge lose: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:02042509
msgctxt "001ACC"
msgid "What's that supposed to mean? You'd attack innocent people?"
msgstr "그게 무슨 뜻이야? 무고한 사람들을 공격하겠다고?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042507
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A72E0C
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:02042507
msgctxt "001ACD"
msgid "We'd rather avoid a fight here if possible..."
msgstr "가능하면 여기서 싸움은 피하고 싶어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042506
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00466803
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:02042506
msgctxt "001ACE"
msgid "We're not looking for a fight."
msgstr "우린 싸우려는 게 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042505
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0098FDD9
#. Notes = Speech challenge win: If we do this the hard way, you'll lose. / Thinking, Face: Thinking
#: 0204245E/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:02042505
msgctxt "001ACF"
msgid "We don't want any trouble..."
msgstr "우린 문제를 일으키고 싶지 않아..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204247F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 001ADF33
#: 0204245D/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc01Scene:0204247F
msgctxt "001AD0"
msgid "Don't force my hand."
msgstr "내 손을 쓰게 만들지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005C508E
#: 0204245F/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:020424CD
msgctxt "001AD1"
msgid "Admit you're Terrans and avoid any unnecessary actions."
msgstr "테란이라고 인정하고 불필요한 행동은 피하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0031DDC0
#: 0204245F/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:020424CC
msgctxt "001AD2"
msgid "Don't force me to do anything you'll regret."
msgstr "네가 후회할 일을 내가 하게 만들지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00413204
#: 0204245F/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable02Scene:020424CB
msgctxt "001AD3"
msgid "If we do this the hard way, you'll lose."
msgstr "어렵게 가면 네가 지게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042491
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0075E8A9
#: 02042461/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:02042491
msgctxt "001AD4"
msgid "Trust me, we can work this out."
msgstr "날 믿어. 우린 이걸 해결할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042490
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002283F6
#: 02042461/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:02042490
msgctxt "001AD5"
msgid "If you tell me the truth, we can talk about this."
msgstr "사실대로 말하면 이 일을 대화로 풀 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004CFC91
#: 02042461/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Repeatable01Scene:0204248F
msgctxt "001AD6"
msgid "Just admit you're Terrans and we can work this out."
msgstr "그냥 테란이라고 인정해. 그러면 이 일을 해결할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E10
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00EC85F0
#: 02042D75:02042E10
msgctxt "001AD7"
msgid "*Whistles* You are somewhere else, huh?"
msgstr "*휘파람* 정신이 딴 데 가 있구나, 응?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 009D926E
#: 02042D75:02042E0F
msgctxt "001AD8"
msgid "Aurora, is that it? Had yourself some Aurora and decided to talk to the funny metal man?"
msgstr "오로라야, 그거지? 오로라 좀 하고 웃긴 금속 남자한테 말 걸기로 한 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00A42526
#: 02042D75:02042E0E
msgctxt "001AD9"
msgid "I get it, I'm a good looking guy. You don't have to stare though."
msgstr "알아, 나 잘생겼지. 그래도 그렇게 빤히 볼 필요는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00DE1D3E
#: 02042D75:02042E0D
msgctxt "001ADA"
msgid "You know, I feel very seen right now. I don't think anyone has ever paid me this much attention. I'm both annoyed and flattered."
msgstr "있잖아, 지금 엄청 주목받는 기분이야. 누가 나한테 이렇게까지 관심을 준 적은 없는 것 같거든. 짜증나면서도 우쭐하네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00EE7BBB, 0043467A, 00D0E75A, 00B00B8A
#. Notes = Impersonating the player., Exclaims "Dirt" as if he just remember a very important detail.
#: 02042D75:02042E0C
msgctxt "001ADB"
msgid "Dirt. Lots of dirt. Love me some dirt...You know?"
msgstr "흙. 아주 많은 흙. 나 흙 정말 좋아하거든...알지?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00EE7BBB, 0043467A, 00D0E75A, 00B00B8A
#. Notes = Impersonating the player., Exclaims "Dirt" as if he just remember a very important detail.
#: 02042D75:02042E0C
msgctxt "001ADC"
msgid "Places where there are no people generally. Just alone, no one to stare at you blankly.."
msgstr "보통은 사람이 없는 곳. 혼자 있을 수 있고, 멍하니 쳐다보는 사람도 없는 곳.."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00EE7BBB, 0043467A, 00D0E75A, 00B00B8A
#. Notes = Impersonating the player., Exclaims "Dirt" as if he just remember a very important detail.
#: 02042D75:02042E0C
msgctxt "001ADD"
msgid "Oh me? I'm glad you asked. I'm just a free spirit, you know? I like scrap yards. Empty, abandoned scrap yards."
msgstr "아, 나? 물어봐 줘서 고마워. 난 그냥 자유로운 영혼이야, 알지? 고철장을 좋아해. 텅 비고 버려진 고철장."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01SharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00EE7BBB, 0043467A, 00D0E75A, 00B00B8A
#. Notes = Impersonating the player., Exclaims "Dirt" as if he just remember a very important detail.
#: 02042D75:02042E0C
msgctxt "001ADE"
msgid "\"Well it's nice to meet you, tell me about yourself.\""
msgstr "만나서 반가워요. 자기소개 좀 해 주세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030EDB
msgctxt "001ADF"
msgid "Feel free to take a look around. If you need anything, I'll be at my desk."
msgstr "편하게 둘러봐. 필요한 게 있으면 난 내 책상에 있을게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED8
msgctxt "001AE0"
msgid "That's just how my Ma raised me, and unfortunately for you, I will continue to make her proud."
msgstr "우리 엄마가 날 그렇게 키웠거든. 안타깝게도 난 앞으로도 엄마가 자랑스러워할 짓을 계속할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02030ED8
msgctxt "001AE1"
msgid "I apologize in advance if I'm a sarcastic prick."
msgstr "내가 빈정대는 재수 없는 놈처럼 굴면 미리 사과할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E50
msgctxt "001AE2"
msgid "You have a good one now. I think I'm going to take a little nap after all of this chaos."
msgstr "그럼 좋은 하루 보내. 난 이 난리 끝에 잠깐 낮잠이나 자야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E50
msgctxt "001AE3"
msgid "Also if you're looking to upgrade your weapons, I can help you out for a fraction of the price you'd be able to do yourself."
msgstr "그리고 무기를 업그레이드하려는 거라면, 네가 직접 할 때 드는 비용의 일부만 받고 도와줄 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E50
msgctxt "001AE4"
msgid "I've got all the Terran tech you could ever dream of, so don't be shy to stop by."
msgstr "네가 꿈꿀 만한 테란 기술은 전부 갖추고 있으니, 부담 갖지 말고 들러."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E50
msgctxt "001AE5"
msgid "Anyway, like I was saying before we were so rudely interrupted. My shop's always open. "
msgstr "아무튼, 우리가 무례하게 방해받기 전에 말하던 것처럼. 내 가게는 언제나 열려 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00F8D14F
#. Notes = / to BUCKE, Face: Confident
#: 02042D6F/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCD
msgctxt "001AE6"
msgid "Can't say you're surprised? You're telling me you've been setting up these ambushes in the same location for years?"
msgstr "놀랍지도 않다고? 몇 년 동안 같은 장소에서 이런 매복을 준비해 왔다는 말이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00617688
#. Notes = / to BUCKE, Face: Confident
#: 02042D6F/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCC
msgctxt "001AE7"
msgid "You're telling me you've been attacking these Terran patrols for years in the same spot!?"
msgstr "몇 년 동안 같은 자리에서 테란 순찰대를 공격해 왔다는 말이야!?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C1D613, 00AD5601
#. Notes = / to BUCKE, Face: Confident
#: 02042D6F/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCB
msgctxt "001AE8"
msgid "But if you're going to ambush the same organization over the span of years, I'd recommend not doing it in the same spot every time."
msgstr "하지만 몇 년에 걸쳐 같은 조직을 매복 공격할 거라면, 매번 같은 장소에서 하지는 말라고 권하고 싶군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 00C1D613, 00AD5601
#. Notes = / to BUCKE, Face: Confident
#: 02042D6F/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCB
msgctxt "001AE9"
msgid "Now, I generally don't like to tell people how to go about their business."
msgstr "난 보통 남의 일 처리 방식에 이래라저래라하는 걸 좋아하진 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = companion
#. SoundFileID = 0085462D
#. Notes = / to BUCKE
#: 02042D6F/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCA
msgctxt "001AEA"
msgid "You're telling us you've been coordinating these attacks on Terran patrols for years...In the same location?"
msgstr "몇 년 동안 테란 순찰대 공격을 조율해 왔다는 말이야...같은 장소에서?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0A
msgctxt "001AEB"
msgid "I'm not quite sure how we made it out of that alive."
msgstr "우리가 어떻게 살아서 빠져나왔는지 잘 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0A
msgctxt "001AEC"
msgid "Well religious or not, there's definitely something watching your back out there."
msgstr "뭐, 종교가 있든 없든 저 밖에서 널 지켜주는 뭔가가 있는 건 분명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E09
msgctxt "001AED"
msgid "Well I'll be damned, looks like we didn't need any divine intervention after all."
msgstr "이런 세상에, 결국 신의 개입은 필요 없었던 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E08
msgctxt "001AEE"
msgid "I don't know much about what God you follow, but there's definitely something watching your back out there."
msgstr "네가 믿는 신에 대해 잘 알진 못하지만, 저 밖에서 널 지켜주는 뭔가가 있는 건 분명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E07
msgctxt "001AEF"
msgid "Deity or not, there's definitely something watching out for you."
msgstr "신이든 아니든, 널 지켜주는 뭔가가 있는 건 분명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E06
msgctxt "001AF0"
msgid "I don't know what it is, but there's something watching out for you."
msgstr "그게 뭔지는 몰라도, 널 지켜주는 뭔가가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E06
msgctxt "001AF1"
msgid "I guess those prayers came through, huh."
msgstr "그 기도가 통했나 보네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E05
msgctxt "001AF2"
msgid "I guess there might be something to that Great Serpent of yours after all."
msgstr "네 위대한 뱀이라는 것도 결국 뭔가 있긴 한가 보네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DEF
msgctxt "001AF3"
msgid "If you say so. I got your back."
msgstr "네가 그렇다면야. 내가 도와줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00D17AA7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D7A/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DD8
msgctxt "001AF4"
msgid "I've made it this far without prayers, we'll be fine."
msgstr "난 기도 없이도 여기까지 왔어. 우린 괜찮을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC0
msgctxt "001AF5"
msgid "I'll do my best."
msgstr "최선을 다할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00182F6E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D7C/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DD4
msgctxt "001AF6"
msgid "God is watching, lets put on a good show."
msgstr "신이 보고 있어. 멋진 구경거리나 보여주자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB0
msgctxt "001AF7"
msgid "I'm not a robot- you know what, lets just end it."
msgstr "난 로봇이 아니... 됐다, 그냥 끝내자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00516C8D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D7E/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DE1
msgctxt "001AF8"
msgid "There's no after life for robots, start shooting."
msgstr "로봇에겐 사후 세계가 없어. 사격 개시."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00BE2D36
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D80/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DBE
msgctxt "001AF9"
msgid "I'll see you on the other side."
msgstr "저편에서 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD7
msgctxt "001AFA"
msgid "That's the nicest thing anyone has ever said to me."
msgstr "그건 내가 들어본 말 중에 제일 다정하네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00BDDED3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D82/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DD3
msgctxt "001AFB"
msgid "You dragged me into this, now you're going to help me fight our way out."
msgstr "네가 날 여기로 끌어들였으니, 이제 나랑 같이 싸워서 빠져나가야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC4
msgctxt "001AFC"
msgid "With some luck and duct tape we might be able to pull through."
msgstr "운과 덕트 테이프만 좀 따라주면 어떻게든 버틸 수 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC1
msgctxt "001AFD"
msgid "Is everyone in your religion this angry? I think you just need therapy."
msgstr "네 종교 사람들은 다 이렇게 화가 많아? 넌 그냥 상담이 필요한 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00632C41
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D84/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCE
msgctxt "001AFE"
msgid "We don't need prayers right now, we need to kill."
msgstr "지금 필요한 건 기도가 아니라 죽이는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0067DACC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D86/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DB9
msgctxt "001AFF"
msgid "You have my prayers if you can carry your weight in this fight."
msgstr "이 싸움에서 네 몫을 해낸다면 내 기도를 보내주지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB6
msgctxt "001B00"
msgid "Thank you. Now lets see how powerful your snake God really is."
msgstr "고마워. 이제 네 뱀 신이 얼마나 강한지 한번 보자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE9
msgctxt "001B01"
msgid "Let's not keep our new friends waiting."
msgstr "새 친구들을 기다리게 하진 말자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE9
msgctxt "001B02"
msgid "That's a fair enough deal."
msgstr "그 정도면 충분히 공정한 거래야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00841E9E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D88/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DF0
msgctxt "001B03"
msgid "I'll be sure to inquire."
msgstr "꼭 물어볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB3
msgctxt "001B04"
msgid "Guess we'll see who's right by the end of this...or, you know...not."
msgstr "이 일이 끝날 때쯤엔 누가 맞는지 알게 되겠지... 아니면 뭐... 못 알 수도 있고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB3
msgctxt "001B05"
msgid "That makes one of us."
msgstr "그렇게 생각하는 건 너뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00F7998E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D8A/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DBA
msgctxt "001B06"
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "그래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00CD59BF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D8E/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DF8
msgctxt "001B07"
msgid "I believe in a higher power."
msgstr "난 더 높은 존재를 믿어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DCF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 000952E3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D8C/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DCF
msgctxt "001B08"
msgid "I don't follow any deity if that's what you're asking."
msgstr "그걸 묻는 거라면, 난 어떤 신도 따르지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB2
msgctxt "001B09"
msgid "I'd appreciate if you said a prayer for me in that case. I don't think we're getting through this one alive."
msgstr "그렇다면 날 위해 기도 한 번 해주면 고맙겠어. 이번엔 살아서 못 빠져나갈 것 같거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC5
msgctxt "001B0A"
msgid "Me either... I was going to ask you to say a prayer for us, but I guess that's off the table."
msgstr "나도... 사실 우리를 위해 기도 좀 해달라고 하려 했는데, 그건 물 건너갔네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD5
msgctxt "001B0B"
msgid "If so, I'd appreciate if you vouch for me. I don't think we're getting out of this alive."
msgstr "그렇다면 날 위해 보증 좀 서주면 고맙겠어. 여기서 살아 나갈 것 같지 않거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD5
msgctxt "001B0C"
msgid "Does this Serpent of yours accept plus ones in the afterlife?"
msgstr "네 위대한 뱀은 사후세계에 동반자 입장도 받아 주나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008672CD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D90/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DD2
msgctxt "001B0D"
msgid "I follow the Great Serpent."
msgstr "난 위대한 뱀을 따른다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD0
msgctxt "001B0E"
msgid "We might want to say a prayer just in case. Doubt we'll see this fight to the end."
msgstr "혹시 모르니 기도라도 해두는 게 좋겠어. 이 싸움 끝까지 버틸 것 같진 않으니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD0
msgctxt "001B0F"
msgid "Yeah...fair enough."
msgstr "그래... 그 말도 맞지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DED
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00015C4B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D92/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042DED
msgctxt "001B10"
msgid "It's complicated."
msgstr "복잡해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB7
msgctxt "001B11"
msgid "This is as good as any place to end a story, I guess. I'm ready to go."
msgstr "이야기를 끝내기엔 여기만 한 곳도 없겠지. 난 갈 준비 됐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB7
msgctxt "001B12"
msgid "That makes two of us."
msgstr "나도 그래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E24
msgctxt "001B13"
msgid "You a religious gal by any chance, Ms. Vanguard?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 여자야, 뱅가드 아가씨?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E23
msgctxt "001B14"
msgid "You a religious man by any chance, Mr. Vanguard?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 남자야, 뱅가드 양반?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E22
msgctxt "001B15"
msgid "You religious by any chance, Vanguard?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있어, 뱅가드?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E20
msgctxt "001B16"
msgid "You a religious gal by any chance, Pirate? I know your kind aren't usually the spiritual sort."
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 여자야, 해적? 너희 부류가 보통 영적인 편은 아닌 거 알지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E1F
msgctxt "001B17"
msgid "You a religious man by any chance, Pirate? I know your kind aren't usually the spiritual sort."
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 남자야, 해적? 너희 부류가 보통 영적인 편은 아닌 거 알지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E1E
msgctxt "001B18"
msgid "You religious by any chance, Pirate? I know your kind aren't usually the spiritual sort."
msgstr "혹시 종교 있어, 해적? 너희 부류가 보통 영적인 편은 아닌 거 알지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E1C
msgctxt "001B19"
msgid "You a religious gal by any chance, Ranger?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 여자야, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E1B
msgctxt "001B1A"
msgid "You a religious man by any chance, Ranger?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 남자야, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E1A
msgctxt "001B1B"
msgid "You religious by any chance, Ranger?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있어, 레인저?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E18
msgctxt "001B1C"
msgid "You a religious gal by any chance?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 여자야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E17
msgctxt "001B1D"
msgid "You a religious man by any chance?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있는 남자야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E16
msgctxt "001B1E"
msgid "You religious by any chance?"
msgstr "혹시 종교 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E34
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00E809E2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D94/00000/SFTER_MS01_1250_TerranArmyScene02:02042E34
msgctxt "001B1F"
msgid "No."
msgstr "아니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3B
msgctxt "001B20"
msgid "Sweet mother of all that's good..."
msgstr "세상에, 맙소사..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC8
msgctxt "001B21"
msgid "What the hell was that?"
msgstr "방금 그게 대체 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3A
msgctxt "001B22"
msgid "Can't say I'm surprised though."
msgstr "그렇다고 놀랍다고는 못 하겠지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3A
msgctxt "001B23"
msgid "Well, looks like this is it. They finally caught up to ol' BUCK-E."
msgstr "뭐, 이제 끝인가 보네. 드디어 늙은 BUCK-E를 따라잡았군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBD
msgctxt "001B24"
msgid "Also if you're interested I -"
msgstr "그리고 관심 있으면 내가 -"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC7
msgctxt "001B25"
msgid "So much for lending me a hand."
msgstr "도와준다더니 이게 뭐야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E54
msgctxt "001B26"
msgid "Either way, if you do decide to lend a hand, I'll make it worth your while."
msgstr "어쨌든 도와주기로 마음먹으면, 네 시간값은 해줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E54
msgctxt "001B27"
msgid "I know this isn't UC territory and whatnot, but I'd have thought a valiant Vanguard such as yourself would help a poor guy out, huh?"
msgstr "여기가 식민지 연합 영토가 아닌 건 알지만, 너 같은 용맹한 뱅가드라면 불쌍한 녀석 하나쯤은 도와줄 줄 알았는데, 응?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E53
msgctxt "001B28"
msgid "Well, if you do decide to help, I'll make it worth your time."
msgstr "뭐, 도와주기로 마음먹으면 시간값은 해줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E53
msgctxt "001B29"
msgid "I thought you Rangers were supposed to keep the peace out here. Help out the little guy and whatnot."
msgstr "너희 레인저는 여기 평화를 지키는 사람들이라며. 힘없는 사람도 좀 돕고 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E52
msgctxt "001B2A"
msgid "I can respect that. I will reiterate, however, if you help me out, there's something in it for you."
msgstr "그건 존중해. 다만 다시 말하지만, 날 도와주면 네게도 득이 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E52
msgctxt "001B2B"
msgid "Can't say I'm surprised though, pirates only look after themselves, am I right?"
msgstr "그렇다고 놀랍진 않네. 해적은 자기만 챙기는 법이잖아, 안 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E51
msgctxt "001B2C"
msgid "If you help me out though, I'll make it worth your time."
msgstr "그래도 날 도와주면 시간값은 해줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E51
msgctxt "001B2D"
msgid "You're more of a wait and see kind of person, huh? Mind your own business, go about your day. I can respect that."
msgstr "넌 일단 지켜보자는 쪽이구나? 자기 일이나 챙기고 하루를 보내는 타입. 존중해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E83
msgctxt "001B2E"
msgid " Moving on..."
msgstr " 넘어가자..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E83
msgctxt "001B2F"
msgid "That's a fair answer...concerning, but fair."
msgstr "그거야 공정한 대답이지... 걱정스럽긴 하지만 공정해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E81
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 003C7633
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042E75/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02042E81
msgctxt "001B30"
msgid "Don't ask me, I know as much as you do."
msgstr "나한테 묻지 마. 나도 너만큼밖에 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E7F
msgctxt "001B31"
msgid "You approached me. I'm just living my life. If anyone's allowed to be concerned, it's me. I mean look at you..."
msgstr "네가 먼저 다가왔잖아. 난 그냥 내 삶을 살고 있었고. 누가 걱정할 자격이 있다면 그건 나지. 아니, 네 꼴을 좀 봐..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E80
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00687723
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042E77/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02042E80
msgctxt "001B32"
msgid "Mind your own business and stop scanning me."
msgstr "남 일에 신경 끄고 날 스캔하지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E7E
msgctxt "001B33"
msgid "No..."
msgstr "아니..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E7D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00A54DA9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042E79/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02042E7D
msgctxt "001B34"
msgid "Would you believe me if I told you I'm an interdimensional being?"
msgstr "내가 차원 간 존재라고 하면 믿어줄래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E7C
msgctxt "001B35"
msgid "That answer honestly makes me more concerned, but I'll respect your boundaries. Anyway..."
msgstr "솔직히 그 대답을 들으니 더 걱정되지만, 네 선은 존중할게. 아무튼..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E82
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006842AD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042E7B/00000/SFTER_MS01_0200_IntroGreeting:02042E82
msgctxt "001B36"
msgid "Don't worry about it."
msgstr "신경 쓰지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007C5E45, 0002FA94, 00A3A585, 008AAE47 (+1 more)
#: 02042D75:02042DE0
msgctxt "001B3A"
msgid "Fine, here! Calibrated to perfection by yours truly, on the house. Where the hell did you learn to negotiate like that?"
msgstr "좋아, 여기! 내가 직접 완벽하게 조정해 둔 거야. 공짜로 가져가. 대체 어디서 그렇게 협상을 배운 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007C5E45, 0002FA94, 00A3A585, 008AAE47 (+1 more)
#: 02042D75:02042DE0
msgctxt "001B3B"
msgid "...Alright, alright. You drive a hard bargain, twenty five and that's it. You're testing your luck."
msgstr "...알았어, 알았다고. 정말 끈질기군. 25퍼센트, 거기까지야. 운을 시험하고 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007C5E45, 0002FA94, 00A3A585, 008AAE47 (+1 more)
#: 02042D75:02042DE0
msgctxt "001B3C"
msgid "...Fifty percent off, take it or leave it. That's the best you're getting out of me."
msgstr "...50퍼센트 할인, 받든가 말든가. 나한테서 얻어낼 수 있는 건 그게 최선이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007C5E45, 0002FA94, 00A3A585, 008AAE47 (+1 more)
#: 02042D75:02042DE0
msgctxt "001B3D"
msgid "...Ok I get it, economy's tough right now. Still doesn't mean I'm going to start giving you handouts."
msgstr "...그래, 알겠어. 요즘 경제가 어렵지. 그렇다고 내가 공짜로 퍼주기 시작한다는 뜻은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007C5E45, 0002FA94, 00A3A585, 008AAE47 (+1 more)
#: 02042D75:02042DE0
msgctxt "001B3E"
msgid "Listen, you can stand there all day if you want but if you're expecting free shit you can forget about it."
msgstr "들어봐, 온종일 거기 서 있어도 되지만 공짜로 뭔가 받아낼 생각이면 꿈도 꾸지 마."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E33
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 005D6DE5
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E33
msgctxt "001B3F"
msgid "That's amusing."
msgstr "재미있네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E32
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00206EF5
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E32
msgctxt "001B40"
msgid "Was I supposed to feel that? *Chuckles*"
msgstr "내가 뭘 느껴야 했나? *킥킥 웃음*"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E31
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 002B76EE
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E31
msgctxt "001B41"
msgid "Damn, I think they scratched me."
msgstr "젠장, 긁힌 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E30
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00FDB524
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E30
msgctxt "001B42"
msgid "Hey, watch the paint!"
msgstr "야, 도장 조심해!"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00834731
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2F
msgctxt "001B43"
msgid "You're really trying to piss me off, huh?"
msgstr "정말 날 열받게 하려는 거지, 응?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00177F09
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2E
msgctxt "001B44"
msgid "That wasn't very nice."
msgstr "별로 착한 짓은 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 003B7CB8
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2D
msgctxt "001B45"
msgid "Gonna take more than that to put me down."
msgstr "그 정도로 날 쓰러뜨리긴 어림없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 001133B4
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2C
msgctxt "001B46"
msgid "That's rude."
msgstr "무례하네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo10
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 0042A1B1
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2B
msgctxt "001B47"
msgid "There goes my favorite limb."
msgstr "내가 제일 좋아하는 팔다리가 날아갔군."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo11
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E2A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00DAE939
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E2A
msgctxt "001B48"
msgid "Ugh, that's gonna suck to fix."
msgstr "윽, 이거 고치려면 골치 아프겠네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo12
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E29
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00C28EB4
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D74:02042E29
msgctxt "001B49"
msgid "Alright, time out!"
msgstr "좋아, 잠깐 쉬자!"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo13
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E28
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 005392E3
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D74:02042E28
msgctxt "001B4A"
msgid "Huh, I think I'm tapping out."
msgstr "허, 나 포기해야 할 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo14
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E27
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00D9FED3
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D74:02042E27
msgctxt "001B4B"
msgid "Whelp, I'm down."
msgstr "에휴, 나 쓰러졌다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo15
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E26
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00C2CF3D
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D74:02042E26
msgctxt "001B4C"
msgid "I'm just going to lay here for a bit, don't mind me."
msgstr "잠깐 여기 누워 있을 테니 신경 쓰지 마."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_VendorSharedInfo01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E25
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00623DDF
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02042D77:02042E25
msgctxt "001B4D"
msgid "*Chuckles* Is that it?"
msgstr "*킥킥 웃음* 그게 다야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC2
msgctxt "001B4E"
msgid "I couldn't tell you, you'll have to ask a robot."
msgstr "그건 나도 몰라. 로봇한테 물어봐야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 007FB0AE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D6A/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02042DBB
msgctxt "001B4F"
msgid "What's it feel like being a robot?"
msgstr "로봇으로 사는 기분은 어때?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB4
msgctxt "001B50"
msgid "And that's when you came along."
msgstr "그때 네가 나타난 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB4
msgctxt "001B51"
msgid "After I crashed the ship on top of my little shack, I decided to just wait for the next patrol to come along so I can blow it open."
msgstr "내 작은 오두막 위에 함선을 추락시킨 뒤에는, 다음 순찰대가 올 때까지 기다렸다가 뚫어버리기로 했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB4
msgctxt "001B52"
msgid "This time around, I had a grand idea. I'll hijack the ship and sell it all together...That did not work out."
msgstr "이번에는 기발한 생각이 떠올랐어. 함선을 탈취해서 통째로 팔아버리자고... 잘 안 됐지만."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB4
msgctxt "001B53"
msgid "Usually, when I'm done mopping up a Terran patrol I gut their ship and just blow it up."
msgstr "보통 테란 순찰대를 해치우고 나면 함선을 뜯어낸 다음 그냥 폭파해 버려."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB4
msgctxt "001B54"
msgid "Oh, it's a long story. I'll just say I'm not much of a pilot."
msgstr "오, 긴 이야기야. 그냥 내가 조종에는 영 소질이 없다고만 해둘게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF5
msgctxt "001B55"
msgid "'Ol BUCK-E always here to lend a hand."
msgstr "늙은 BUCK-E는 언제나 도울 준비가 되어 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF4
msgctxt "001B56"
msgid "Sure, let's see what were working with."
msgstr "좋아, 상태를 한번 보자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF3
msgctxt "001B57"
msgid "No problem, put them on the counter."
msgstr "문제없어. 카운터에 올려놔."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF2
msgctxt "001B58"
msgid "Let's see what you got."
msgstr "뭘 가져왔는지 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF1
msgctxt "001B59"
msgid "Always glad to help. Let me take a look."
msgstr "언제든 도와주지. 한번 살펴볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0039AEC2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D6D/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02042DC6
msgctxt "001B5A"
msgid "I need you to do some work on my weapons."
msgstr "내 무기 좀 손봐줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00CE135D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D6E/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02042E3C
msgctxt "001B5B"
msgid "How'd the entrance to your bunker get blocked?"
msgstr "벙커 입구는 어떻게 막힌 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3D
msgctxt "001B5C"
msgid "I'd harness it and hold myself accountable for how I use it, not other people."
msgstr "나라면 그 힘을 이용하고, 그걸 어떻게 쓰는지에 대해 남이 아니라 나 자신에게 책임을 물을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3D
msgctxt "001B5D"
msgid "I think making it your responsibility to determine who's \"worthy\" in your own eyes is naive and sanctimonious."
msgstr "누가 네 기준으로 \"자격이 있는지\"를 네 책임으로 정하겠다는 건 순진하고 독선적이라고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3D
msgctxt "001B5E"
msgid "Who's to say you're not the wrong hands to harness such a thing?"
msgstr "그런 걸 다루기에 네 손이 잘못된 손이 아니라고 누가 장담하지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE2
msgctxt "001B5F"
msgid "Could you imagine the consequences of such a thing?"
msgstr "그런 일의 결과가 어떨지 상상이나 돼?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DE2
msgctxt "001B60"
msgid "As a specialist in neurological tech. Absolutely not. I don't even want to think about that hypothetical."
msgstr "신경 기술 전문가로서? 절대 안 돼. 그런 가정은 생각하고 싶지도 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00A71F3A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042D9E/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DC9
msgctxt "001B61"
msgid "If you could develop technology that enabled you to manipulate peoples' behavior, would you?"
msgstr "사람들의 행동을 조종할 수 있는 기술을 개발할 수 있다면, 넌 하겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DEE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00271015
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DA0/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DEE
msgctxt "001B62"
msgid "If you could harness great power or ensure it stays out of the wrong hands, which would you do?"
msgstr "큰 힘을 손에 넣을 수 있다면, 아니면 그 힘이 잘못된 손에 들어가지 않게 막을 수 있다면, 어느 쪽을 택하겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC3
msgctxt "001B63"
msgid "Personally I find the people on Paradiso insufferable, living around them would be a punishment."
msgstr "개인적으로 파라디소 사람들은 견딜 수가 없어. 그들 곁에 산다는 건 벌이나 다름없지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DC3
msgctxt "001B64"
msgid "I don't even know why this is a question. If you can relocate the colonist ship then problem solved."
msgstr "이게 왜 고민거리인지도 모르겠어. 개척선을 이전할 수 있다면 문제는 해결이잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DEC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0099F42A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DA8/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DEC
msgctxt "001B65"
msgid "Between releasing a weaponized microbe and restoring the Aceles, what do you think is the best way to deal with Terrormorphs?"
msgstr "무기화된 미생물을 풀어놓는 것과 아셀리스를 복원하는 것 중에, 테러모프를 처리하는 최선의 방법은 뭐라고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF6
msgctxt "001B66"
msgid "Friends are a rare commodity. Useful war criminals? Well, you can always buy new tools."
msgstr "친구는 드문 자원이야. 쓸모 있는 전범? 뭐, 도구는 새로 사면 되지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF6
msgctxt "001B67"
msgid "If utility is their only excuse for living then they're a means with no ends. That's dangerous...I'd kill them."
msgstr "그들이 살아 있을 이유가 쓸모뿐이라면, 그건 목적 없는 수단이야. 위험하지... 나라면 죽일 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF6
msgctxt "001B68"
msgid "I live by people and principle. Sometimes we get caught up in the systems a little too much. It muddies the waters."
msgstr "난 사람과 원칙을 기준으로 살아. 가끔 우리는 체계에 너무 휘말려 버려. 그러면 판단이 흐려져."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DEB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00D8F1CD
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DA4/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DEB
msgctxt "001B69"
msgid "If you discovered a war criminal was alive, would you kill them? Even if they're useful?"
msgstr "전범이 살아 있다는 걸 알게 된다면, 죽이겠어? 쓸모가 있더라도?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB8
msgctxt "001B6A"
msgid "Too many friendly faces would be gone...but that's just me."
msgstr "너무 많은 친근한 얼굴들이 사라질 거야... 적어도 내 생각은 그래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB8
msgctxt "001B6B"
msgid "If destroying the Terrans meant killing everyone forced to associate with them... I don't think I'd have the heart to do it."
msgstr "테란을 파괴한다는 게 그들과 억지로 엮인 모두를 죽이는 뜻이라면... 난 차마 못 할 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB8
msgctxt "001B6C"
msgid "Depends on what you mean by destroy. There's a lot of good people forced to work for the Armada, thousands in fact."
msgstr "파괴가 무슨 뜻인지에 따라 달라. 테란 함대를 위해 억지로 일하는 좋은 사람들도 많아. 사실 수천 명이나 되지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00CDF046
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DA6/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DD1
msgctxt "001B6D"
msgid "If you had the ability to completely destroy the Terran Armada, would you do it?"
msgstr "테란 함대를 완전히 파괴할 능력이 있다면, 그렇게 하겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00A8F47A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DA2/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DB1
msgctxt "001B6E"
msgid "There's a colony ship orbiting Paradiso and the resort wants it gone. I'm not sure what to do."
msgstr "파라디소 궤도에 개척선이 있고, 리조트 측은 그걸 치우길 원해. 어떻게 해야 할지 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0B
msgctxt "001B6F"
msgid "If people were just a little more patient the Settled Systems would be a safer place."
msgstr "사람들이 조금만 더 인내심을 가졌다면 개척 성계는 더 안전한 곳이 됐을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0B
msgctxt "001B70"
msgid "That was rhetorical. The answer obviously is the safest option."
msgstr "수사적인 질문이었어. 답은 당연히 가장 안전한 선택지지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0B
msgctxt "001B71"
msgid "Let me ask you this, do you value time and efficacy or safety and stability?"
msgstr "이렇게 물어볼게. 넌 시간과 효율을 중시해, 아니면 안전과 안정성을 중시해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E0B
msgctxt "001B72"
msgid "You mean between proliferating a potentially hazardous compound as a pesticide, and resurrecting a natural predator to the problem at hand?"
msgstr "잠재적으로 위험한 화합물을 살충제로 퍼뜨리는 것과, 당면한 문제의 자연 포식자를 되살리는 것 사이를 말하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBC
msgctxt "001B73"
msgid "The way I see it, that's not your responsibility."
msgstr "내가 보기엔 그건 네 책임이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBC
msgctxt "001B74"
msgid "Even if SysDef or the Fleet are destroyed. The UC will still stand and there will still be pirates."
msgstr "성계 방위군이나 크림슨 함대가 무너진다 해도, 식민지 연합은 여전히 남고 해적도 계속 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBC
msgctxt "001B75"
msgid "Side with those you have the strongest bond with. Let time determine who reigns in the end."
msgstr "가장 강한 유대를 맺은 쪽에 서. 끝에 누가 군림할지는 시간이 정하게 두고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBC
msgctxt "001B76"
msgid "Ideology aside, you're accountable for how you deal with the immediate people in your life."
msgstr "이념은 제쳐두고, 넌 지금 네 삶에 가까이 있는 사람들을 어떻게 대하는지에 책임이 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBC
msgctxt "001B77"
msgid "Who do you respect more?"
msgstr "넌 누구를 더 존중해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DB5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0010F8FE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DAA/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DB5
msgctxt "001B78"
msgid "I'm caught between the Crimson Fleet and SysDef. Who do you think I should side with?"
msgstr "크림슨 함대와 성계 방위군 사이에서 고민 중이야. 어느 쪽 편을 들어야 한다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DBF
msgctxt "001B79"
msgid "Alright, then."
msgstr "좋아, 그럼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DF7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00991A7D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DAC/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendo_0100_Opinions:02042DF7
msgctxt "001B7A"
msgid "That's all."
msgstr "그게 다야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD9
msgctxt "001B7B"
msgid "Nevermind"
msgstr "신경 쓰지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E44
msgctxt "001B7C"
msgid "If it motivates you to buy more guns, then sure."
msgstr "네가 총을 더 사게 만들 동기라면야, 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E43
msgctxt "001B7D"
msgid "Take a seat, what's the conundrum?"
msgstr "앉아봐. 무슨 고민인데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E42
msgctxt "001B7E"
msgid "Warms my heart you think my opinion is worth something."
msgstr "내 의견을 가치 있다고 생각해주니 마음이 따뜻해지는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E41
msgctxt "001B7F"
msgid "Sure, you want to sit on my lap too?"
msgstr "좋아, 내 무릎에도 앉고 싶어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E40
msgctxt "001B80"
msgid "Only if it's not marriage related."
msgstr "결혼 관련만 아니면."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3F
msgctxt "001B81"
msgid "Comin to old BUCK-E for advice eh? Shoot."
msgstr "늙은 BUCK-E에게 조언을 구하러 왔나? 말해 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E3E
msgctxt "001B82"
msgid "What's up?"
msgstr "무슨 일이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042DD6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0072DD11
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042DAF/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02042DD6
msgctxt "001B83"
msgid "Can I get your opinion on something?"
msgstr "네 의견 좀 물어봐도 돼?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SuccessResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042519
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
