#. Notes = Player won speech challenge. Finally giving in. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042519
msgctxt "001B84"
msgid "All right. Enough."
msgstr "좋아. 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SuccessResponse02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042518
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C9C8B8
#. Notes = Player won speech challenge. Finally giving in. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042518
msgctxt "001B85"
msgid "Fine."
msgstr "좋아."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FailResponse01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042517
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006A27CC
#. Notes = Player failed speech challenge. Fed up and ready to attack. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042517
msgctxt "001B86"
msgid "All right, enough. You had your chance to leave. You wanted Terrans, you got 'em."
msgstr "좋아, 충분해. 떠날 기회는 줬다. 테란을 원했지? 테란을 보게 해주마."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FailResponse02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042516
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00569B93
#. Notes = Player lost speech challenge. Ready to attack. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042516
msgctxt "001B87"
msgid "Actually, I'm sick of this game, and we can't afford any witnesses."
msgstr "사실, 이 장난도 지긋지긋하고, 우린 목격자를 남길 여유가 없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FailResponse03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042515
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EBBE0D
#. Notes = Player lost speech challenge. About to attack. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042515
msgctxt "001B88"
msgid "You know what? I'm done with this, and I can't afford to let you live."
msgstr "있잖아? 난 이제 끝났고, 널 살려둘 여유도 없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SuccessResponse03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042514
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00403C53
#. Notes = Player won speech challenge. Finally giving in. / Tired / to Player Default, Face: Tired
#: 02042464/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042514
msgctxt "001B89"
msgid "Okay, okay..."
msgstr "알았어, 알았다고..."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_AttackResponse03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042513
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0079D888
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C2A6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042513
msgctxt "001B8A"
msgid "Damn. I never should've trusted you."
msgstr "젠장. 널 믿는 게 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_AttackResponse04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042512
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F2095E
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C2A6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042512
msgctxt "001B8B"
msgid "I knew we'd never get out."
msgstr "우린 절대 빠져나가지 못할 줄 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042531
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 007909A4
#. Notes = Thought the player was a threat, but the helped out instead. / Apologetic, Face: Apologetic
#: 02042469:02042531
msgctxt "001B8C"
msgid "We've been blind for so long. Thanks for showing us the way out."
msgstr "우린 너무 오래 눈이 멀어 있었어. 나가는 길을 보여줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042530
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 000AB520
#. Notes = Thought the player was a threat, but the helped out instead. / Apologetic, Face: Apologetic
#: 02042469:02042530
msgctxt "001B8D"
msgid "You were right. Now let's hope we can make up for this."
msgstr "네 말이 맞았어. 이제 우리가 이걸 만회할 수 있길 바라야지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204252F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 0022863A
#. Notes = Thought the player was a threat, but the helped out instead. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:0204252F
msgctxt "001B8E"
msgid "I didn't think I'd be saying this, but thanks."
msgstr "이런 말을 하게 될 줄은 몰랐지만, 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204252E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00D030DA
#. Notes = Thought the player was a threat, but the helped out instead. / Apologetic, Face: Apologetic
#: 02042469:0204252E
msgctxt "001B8F"
msgid "Not the outcome I expected, but I'm glad we ran into you."
msgstr "예상한 결과는 아니지만, 널 만나서 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204252D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 0090B25A
#. Notes = Thought the player was a threat, but the helped out instead. / Apologetic, Face: Apologetic
#: 02042469:0204252D
msgctxt "001B90"
msgid "Looks like I misjudged you."
msgstr "널 잘못 판단한 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204252B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00DCA9BA
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:0204252B
msgctxt "001B91"
msgid "We're going to make the most of this second chance."
msgstr "우린 이 두 번째 기회를 최대한 살릴 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204252A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00B622DA
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:0204252A
msgctxt "001B92"
msgid "I hope we can make up for what we've done."
msgstr "우리가 저지른 일을 만회할 수 있길 바라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042529
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00E28DDA
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:02042529
msgctxt "001B93"
msgid "It's going to be hard to start over, but worth it."
msgstr "새로 시작하는 건 힘들겠지만, 그만한 가치가 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042528
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00B52CBE
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:02042528
msgctxt "001B94"
msgid "We're lucky you came along."
msgstr "네가 와줘서 운이 좋았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042527
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00E12661
#. Notes = Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 02042469:02042527
msgctxt "001B95"
msgid "Thanks for understanding. "
msgstr "이해해줘서 고마워. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042525
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 000ACCB6
#. Notes = Doesn't want the player around. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 02042469:02042525
msgctxt "001B96"
msgid "Sorry, I don't do small talk."
msgstr "미안, 난 잡담은 안 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042524
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00DFAB48
#. Notes = Doesn't want the player around. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 02042469:02042524
msgctxt "001B97"
msgid "It's been a long day."
msgstr "긴 하루였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042523
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00BA861B
#. Notes = Doesn't want the player around. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 02042469:02042523
msgctxt "001B98"
msgid "I'm not in the mood for chit chat."
msgstr "수다 떨 기분이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042522
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00E02BBD
#. Notes = Doesn't want the player around. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 02042469:02042522
msgctxt "001B99"
msgid "I wasn't expecting to see anyone else out here."
msgstr "여기서 다른 사람을 보게 될 줄은 몰랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042521
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 003DA710
#. Notes = Doesn't want the player around. / Suspicious, Face: Suspicious
#: 02042469:02042521
msgctxt "001B9A"
msgid "A bit busy here."
msgstr "지금 좀 바빠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204251F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 0048DC55
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02042469:0204251F
msgctxt "001B9B"
msgid "It's nice to rest for a bit."
msgstr "잠깐 쉬니 좋네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204251E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 0044DBED
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02042469:0204251E
msgctxt "001B9C"
msgid "I'm glad we're finally taking a break."
msgstr "드디어 쉬게 돼서 기뻐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204251D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00EE676B
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02042469:0204251D
msgctxt "001B9D"
msgid "Been a long day."
msgstr "긴 하루였어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204251C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 008B8F79
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02042469:0204251C
msgctxt "001B9E"
msgid "Nice to see we're not the only ones out here."
msgstr "여기 우리만 있는 게 아니라니 반갑네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204251B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric01, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric02, SFTER_NPCMTerranGeneric03, SFTER_NPCFTerranGeneric01 (+2 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00D5AB5F
#. Notes = Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 02042469:0204251B
msgctxt "001B9F"
msgid "Hey there."
msgstr "안녕."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalD03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00487D72
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424AE
msgctxt "001BA0"
msgid "[Attack] The fact that you're Terrans is all I needed to know."
msgstr "[공격] 너희가 테란이라는 사실만 알면 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalD02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00235D06
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424AD
msgctxt "001BA1"
msgid "[Attack] Now that I know you're Terrans, the rest is easy."
msgstr "[공격] 이제 너희가 테란이라는 걸 알았으니, 나머지는 쉽지."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalC03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042502
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A695FE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A7/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042502
msgctxt "001BA2"
msgid "[Attack] You're a Terran. I can't allow you to live."
msgstr "[공격] 넌 테란이야. 살려둘 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalC02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042501
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006B8FC2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A7/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042501
msgctxt "001BA3"
msgid "[Attack] Unfortunately, for security purposes, I can't let you go."
msgstr "[공격] 안타깝지만, 보안상 널 보내줄 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00759DFD, 00CFE82F, 000F7415
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248D
msgctxt "001BA4"
msgid "Thanks for letting us go and giving us a way to help fight back."
msgstr "우릴 보내주고 맞서 싸울 방법까지 줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00759DFD, 00CFE82F, 000F7415
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248D
msgctxt "001BA5"
msgid "As soon as we're able, we'll get a plan in place to spread the word."
msgstr "가능해지는 대로, 이 사실을 알릴 계획을 세울 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00759DFD, 00CFE82F, 000F7415
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248D
msgctxt "001BA6"
msgid "I hadn't thought about that, but you're right. We aren't the only ones that wanted out."
msgstr "그 생각은 못 했지만 네 말이 맞아. 나가고 싶었던 건 우리뿐이 아니었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FC2DA2, 00990EC9, 006B5CE7
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248C
msgctxt "001BA7"
msgid "Thanks for hearing me out. We'll be back in this as soon as we're able."
msgstr "내 말을 들어줘서 고마워. 가능한 대로 바로 이 싸움에 돌아올게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FC2DA2, 00990EC9, 006B5CE7
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248C
msgctxt "001BA8"
msgid "I know more would leave if they could. It's just a matter of letting them know there's a way."
msgstr "나갈 수만 있다면 더 많은 사람이 떠날 거라는 걸 알아. 방법이 있다는 걸 알려주기만 하면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204248C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FC2DA2, 00990EC9, 006B5CE7
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204248C
msgctxt "001BA9"
msgid "Already in the works! Once we get settled, that's the first thing we plan to do. "
msgstr "이미 준비 중이야! 자리를 잡으면 그게 우리가 제일 먼저 할 일이야. "

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalB03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006AE7FE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A9/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424EF
msgctxt "001BAA"
msgid "Find a way to let others know you got out. There's sure to be more."
msgstr "빠져나왔다는 걸 다른 이들에게 알릴 방법을 찾아. 분명 더 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalB02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001C9EC0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2A9/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424EE
msgctxt "001BAB"
msgid "Join the fight by spreading news of your escape. There may be others."
msgstr "탈출 소식을 퍼뜨려 싸움에 합류해. 다른 이들도 있을지 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalA03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0050D04A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AB/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424DA
msgctxt "001BAC"
msgid "Consider it the first day of your new life then. Leave the Terrans to me."
msgstr "그럼 오늘을 새 삶의 첫날로 생각해. 테란은 나한테 맡겨."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceFinalA02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007D8EB8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AB/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424D9
msgctxt "001BAD"
msgid "Go and start over. I'm keeping the Terrans busy enough."
msgstr "가서 새로 시작해. 테란은 내가 충분히 붙잡아 두고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042497
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0043571F
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C2AC/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042497
msgctxt "001BAE"
msgid "You're dead."
msgstr "넌 죽었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042496
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F2AEAE
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C2AC/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042496
msgctxt "001BAF"
msgid "Damn."
msgstr "젠장."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D04284
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2AE/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424DD
msgctxt "001BB0"
msgid "I'm trying to tell you the truth here."
msgstr "난 지금 진실을 말하려는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004DF2CC
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2AE/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424DC
msgctxt "001BB1"
msgid "I swear, you have us mistaken."
msgstr "맹세해, 우릴 오해하고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D67D91
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AF/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424BE
msgctxt "001BB2"
msgid "You expect me to believe that? Seriously, let's talk."
msgstr "내가 그걸 믿을 거라고 생각해? 진심으로, 대화하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0020F003
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AF/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424BD
msgctxt "001BB3"
msgid "No data? You really need to admit the truth so we can talk."
msgstr "데이터가 없다고? 대화하려면 진실을 인정해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204254B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0052CDE3, 00CFD552
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2AA/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204254B
msgctxt "001BB4"
msgid "Thank you for letting us take this second chance. You won't regret it."
msgstr "이 두 번째 기회를 잡게 해줘서 고마워. 후회하지 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204254B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0052CDE3, 00CFD552
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2AA/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204254B
msgctxt "001BB5"
msgid "Oh thank god. I took a gamble trusting you, and let's just say it's about time I made the right decision for once. "
msgstr "아, 세상에 다행이다. 널 믿고 도박을 걸었는데, 이제야 한 번은 옳은 결정을 한 것 같네. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204254A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DDA38D, 008A528F
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2AA/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204254A
msgctxt "001BB6"
msgid "Thank you. And if we're ever able to get back in this fight on the right side, we'll be there."
msgstr "고마워. 그리고 언젠가 올바른 편에서 이 싸움에 다시 뛰어들 수 있게 되면, 우리도 함께할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204254A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DDA38D, 008A528F
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2AA/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0204254A
msgctxt "001BB7"
msgid "You have no idea how relieved I am to hear that. "
msgstr "그 말을 들으니 얼마나 안심되는지 넌 모를 거야. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00310C82
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424A3
msgctxt "001BB8"
msgid "[Attack] That's a very unfortunate coincidence."
msgstr "[공격] 정말 안타까운 우연이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001FADDC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424A2
msgctxt "001BB9"
msgid "[Attack] I knew you were lying."
msgstr "[공격] 네가 거짓말하는 줄 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042483
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D3B9CE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042483
msgctxt "001BBA"
msgid "[Attack] Nice try, but I don't believe you. "
msgstr "[공격] 수작은 좋았지만, 난 안 믿어. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042482
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000A76A6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E6/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042482
msgctxt "001BBB"
msgid "[Attack] I don't buy it."
msgstr "[공격] 난 안 믿어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FD067D
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C2E1/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424B0
msgctxt "001BBC"
msgid "For the last time, we're not Terrans. I don't know what I need to say or do to make you believe me."
msgstr "마지막으로 말하는데, 우린 테란이 아니야. 널 믿게 하려면 내가 대체 뭘 말하고 뭘 해야 하는지 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00CC08D9
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C2E1/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424AF
msgctxt "001BBD"
msgid "You're still on about this? We're not Terrans. We're just here to gather survey data and that's it."
msgstr "아직도 이 얘기야? 우린 테란이 아니야. 그냥 조사 데이터를 모으러 온 것뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0014366C
#. Notes = About to go into combat. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2E5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424B3
msgctxt "001BBE"
msgid "Too bad."
msgstr "유감이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0022BA72
#. Notes = About to go into combat. / Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 0202C2E5/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424B2
msgctxt "001BBF"
msgid "Heh. Smart."
msgstr "헤. 영리하네."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceSCLeadIn03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042533
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0074C863
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E2/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042533
msgctxt "001BC0"
msgid "Quit denying it, it's obvious. "
msgstr "그만 부정해. 뻔하잖아. "

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_PlayerChoiceSCLeadIn02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042532
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F4ECA9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E2/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02042532
msgctxt "001BC1"
msgid "Just admit the truth so we can discuss our options here."
msgstr "그냥 진실을 인정해. 그래야 여기서 선택지를 논의하지."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AA04DC, 009C9B73, 0076A498
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C9
msgctxt "001BC2"
msgid "Please, we aren't looking to fight. We only want to be left alone."
msgstr "제발, 우린 싸우러 온 게 아니야. 그냥 우리를 내버려 두길 바랄 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AA04DC, 009C9B73, 0076A498
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C9
msgctxt "001BC3"
msgid "We figured when we didn't return, they'd declare us MIA, and we could safely start a new life."
msgstr "우리가 돌아가지 않으면 그들이 우릴 미아로 처리할 거라 생각했어. 그러면 안전하게 새 삶을 시작할 수 있을 거라고."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AA04DC, 009C9B73, 0076A498
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C9
msgctxt "001BC4"
msgid "We were part of the Terran Armada, but we came here hoping to escape."
msgstr "우린 테란 함대 소속이었지만, 여기엔 탈출하려고 온 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005C73B4, 00130E66, 00A86AF7
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C8
msgctxt "001BC5"
msgid "We just want to start over. We don't want to fight."
msgstr "우린 그냥 새로 시작하고 싶어. 싸우고 싶지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005C73B4, 00130E66, 00A86AF7
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C8
msgctxt "001BC6"
msgid "We're done with the Terran Armada and their cause, so we found a way out and we took it."
msgstr "우린 테란 함대와 그 대의에서 손을 뗐어. 그래서 빠져나갈 방법을 찾았고, 그걸 택한 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005C73B4, 00130E66, 00A86AF7
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424C8
msgctxt "001BC7"
msgid "Yes, we are the Terran scouting party, but please, hear me out."
msgstr "그래, 우린 테란 정찰대가 맞아. 하지만 제발, 내 말을 들어줘."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203F2B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C72009, 00A2C42C, 0061B2AA
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0203F2B2
msgctxt "001BC8"
msgid "Please just let us go. This isn't our fight anymore. We want out."
msgstr "제발 그냥 보내줘. 이건 더 이상 우리 싸움이 아니야. 우린 빠지고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_Confession01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203F2B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C72009, 00A2C42C, 0061B2AA
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0203F2A8/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0203F2B2
msgctxt "001BC9"
msgid "We used this opportunity to get away from the Armada. Our hope is they'll write us off as dead and we can start over."
msgstr "우린 이 기회를 이용해 테란 함대에서 벗어났어. 그들이 우릴 죽은 것으로 처리해주면 새로 시작할 수 있길 바랐지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A9579F
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 02042465/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424F9
msgctxt "001BCA"
msgid "We only recently arrived, so we haven't had a chance to get set up yet."
msgstr "우린 최근에야 도착해서 아직 준비할 시간이 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00717110
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 02042465/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424F8
msgctxt "001BCB"
msgid "Unfortunately, we haven't begun our data collection process yet."
msgstr "아쉽지만, 아직 데이터 수집 절차를 시작하지 못했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B3419E
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 02042465/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424F7
msgctxt "001BCC"
msgid "We haven't actually started our work yet. We're just en route."
msgstr "사실 아직 일을 시작하지도 않았어. 이동 중일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0083D2AB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042466/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424A7
msgctxt "001BCD"
msgid "Prove to me you're surveyors, and I'll believe you."
msgstr "네가 조사원이라는 걸 증명해. 그러면 믿어주지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0026F918
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042466/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424A6
msgctxt "001BCE"
msgid "Let's see your data then, if you're surveyors."
msgstr "조사원이라면 네 데이터를 보여줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EFCD5D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02042466/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424A5
msgctxt "001BCF"
msgid "If you're surveyors, prove it."
msgstr "조사원이라면 증명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B2A48A
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02042468/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424E1
msgctxt "001BD0"
msgid "We're only here to survey the area."
msgstr "우린 이 지역을 조사하러 왔을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FriendlySceneReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001CFF14
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424E0
msgctxt "001BD1"
msgid "We're just here to survey the area and collect some data."
msgstr "우린 이 지역을 조사하고 데이터를 수집하러 왔을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020424DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0078999B
#. Notes = Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 02042468/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:020424DF
msgctxt "001BD2"
msgid "We're just simple surveyors getting data on the area."
msgstr "우린 이 지역 데이터를 모으는 평범한 조사원일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E88
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00B3F4F6
#: 02042E84:02042E88
msgctxt "001BE4"
msgid "For Gods sake, place down those explosives."
msgstr "제발, 그 폭발물부터 설치해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E87
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 005099CB
#: 02042E84:02042E87
msgctxt "001BE5"
msgid "I'll be happy to chat once we get those explosives down."
msgstr "폭발물 설치를 끝내면 기꺼이 이야기하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E86
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00505BFC
#: 02042E84:02042E86
msgctxt "001BE6"
msgid "Place down those explosives and we can talk."
msgstr "그 폭발물을 설치하면 이야기할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 007F4727
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202CD93/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_CompletionScene:02042E9B
msgctxt "001BE7"
msgid "I hope your presence indicates that you finally completed the requested outpost?"
msgstr "네가 온 걸 보니, 드디어 요청한 전초기지를 완성했다는 뜻인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042EA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0063FEB2, 005F22D7, 00685B59, 0021B7BE
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8D/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene:02042EA1
msgctxt "001BE8"
msgid "It'll be spec'd to handle robots, so should prove useful against the Terrans."
msgstr "로봇에 대응하도록 사양이 맞춰질 테니, 테란을 상대할 때도 유용할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042EA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0063FEB2, 005F22D7, 00685B59, 0021B7BE
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8D/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene:02042EA1
msgctxt "001BE9"
msgid "In addition to that, I've been granted special permission to give you a prototype Novablast Disrupter."
msgstr "거기에 더해, 네게 시제품 노바블래스트 교란기를 지급할 특별 허가도 받았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042EA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0063FEB2, 005F22D7, 00685B59, 0021B7BE
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8D/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene:02042EA1
msgctxt "001BEA"
msgid "Once complete, I can issue you another power core that will allow you to build an X-Tech extractor where you wish."
msgstr "완료되면, 네가 원하는 곳에 X-테크 추출기를 지을 수 있게 해줄 추가 파워 코어를 발급할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042EA1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 0063FEB2, 005F22D7, 00685B59, 0021B7BE
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8D/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene:02042EA1
msgctxt "001BEB"
msgid "You have the necessary specifications: power source, proper defenses, and of course, the X-Tech extractor."
msgstr "필요한 사양은 알고 있지. 전원, 적절한 방어시설, 그리고 물론 X-테크 추출기다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FFC7D9
#: 02042E8E/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostRI_TL_OutpostScene:02042E9E
msgctxt "001BEC"
msgid "Can you give me the details again on this outpost?"
msgstr "이 전초기지에 대한 세부 사항을 다시 알려줄 수 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E98
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B5272F
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202CDA2/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:02042E98
msgctxt "001BED"
msgid "One X-Tech power core as promised. Use it wisely."
msgstr "약속한 대로 X-테크 파워 코어 하나야. 현명하게 써."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E93
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00945735
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 02042E89/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:02042E93
msgctxt "001BEE"
msgid "Now that you've held up your end, we'll be sure to hold up ours. "
msgstr "이제 네가 약속을 지켰으니, 우리도 반드시 우리 약속을 지키겠어. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B1EC0C
#. Notes = Question / to Player Default, Face: Question
#: 0202CDA9/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_CompletionScene:02042E9D
msgctxt "001BEF"
msgid "The outpost. Is it completed?"
msgstr "전초기지는 완성됐나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00E1F1C1
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8A/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E9F
msgctxt "001BF0"
msgid "As incentive, finish the outpost before we face off against the Terrans, and I can guarantee extra fire support from the Freestar Collective."
msgstr "동기 부여 차원에서 말하지. 테란과 맞붙기 전에 전초기지를 완성하면, 자유항성 공동체의 추가 화력 지원을 보장할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 009D576C, 00942DD6
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8B/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E9C
msgctxt "001BF1"
msgid "In return, I can grant you an additional extractor power core so you can build one of your own."
msgstr "그 대가로 추가 추출기 파워 코어를 지급해서, 네가 직접 하나 지을 수 있게 해주지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 009D576C, 00942DD6
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 02042E8B/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E9C
msgctxt "001BF2"
msgid "Of course. Your goal is to outfit our outpost location with an X-Tech extractor. It will need defenses and adequate power to sustain it."
msgstr "물론이지. 목표는 우리 전초기지 위치에 X-테크 추출기를 갖추는 거야. 그것을 유지할 방어시설과 충분한 전력도 필요해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E99
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D0D9C6
#: 02042E8C/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostFC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E99
msgctxt "001BF3"
msgid "Can we talk about what's needed at this outpost again?"
msgstr "이 전초기지에 필요한 것들을 다시 이야기할 수 있을까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E9A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00B53D17
#. Notes = Confident, Face: Confident
#: 0202CD84/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:02042E9A
msgctxt "001BF4"
msgid "As for my end of the bargain, one X-Tech power core for your own personal outpost. I expect you'll put that to good use."
msgstr "내가 약속한 몫은 네 개인 전초기지용 X-테크 파워 코어 하나야. 잘 활용하길 기대하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E97
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 000F2B2A
#. Notes = Question, Face: Question
#: 0202CD8B/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_CompletionScene:02042E97
msgctxt "001BF5"
msgid "You finally wrap up that outpost I asked you about?"
msgstr "내가 부탁한 그 전초기지, 드디어 마무리했나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042EA0
msgctxt "001BF6"
msgid "Once you wrap that up, you're looking at a power core of your very own so you can set up an X-Tech extractor wherever you want."
msgstr "그걸 마무리하면, 네가 원하는 곳에 X-테크 추출기를 세울 수 있도록 네 전용 파워 코어가 생길 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E96
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 003ED14F
#. Notes = The reference to sky is intentional, even though it will be space. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 02042E90/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E96
msgctxt "001BF7"
msgid "And to sweeten the deal, you build this outpost before we take the fight to the Terrans, and I can guarantee you extra ships in the sky when the time comes."
msgstr "그리고 보상을 더 달콤하게 하자면, 우리가 테란과 싸우러 가기 전에 이 전초기지를 지으면, 때가 왔을 때 하늘의 추가 함선 지원을 보장할 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E95
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0088B3D5, 00F98E96, 0057512F
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 02042E91/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E95
msgctxt "001BF8"
msgid "Once you wrap that up, you're looking at your very own power core so you can set up an X-Tech extractor wherever you want."
msgstr "그걸 마무리하면, 네가 원하는 곳에 X-테크 추출기를 세울 수 있도록 네 전용 파워 코어를 받게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E95
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0088B3D5, 00F98E96, 0057512F
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 02042E91/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E95
msgctxt "001BF9"
msgid "I got a few preferences, but nothing you can't handle."
msgstr "선호하는 조건이 몇 가지 있긴 하지만, 네가 감당 못 할 건 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E95
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 0088B3D5, 00F98E96, 0057512F
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 02042E91/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E95
msgctxt "001BFA"
msgid "Pretty simple really, just an X-Tech extractor along with the means to power and defend it. "
msgstr "정말 간단해. X-테크 추출기 하나와, 그걸 가동하고 방어할 수단이면 돼. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02042E94
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0090CFA1
#. Notes = / to Tracy
#: 02042E92/00000/SFTER_MQOutpostUC_TL_OutpostScene:02042E94
msgctxt "001BFB"
msgid "Can you tell me what you need at this outpost again?"
msgstr "이 전초기지에 필요한 걸 다시 말해줄 수 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0011A7C5
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 02043831/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438BE
msgctxt "001C00"
msgid "Percy Kanu, I'm placing you under arrest."
msgstr "퍼시 카누, 당신을 체포하겠습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00F38590
#. Notes = Disbelief / to VOIDTablet, Face: Disbelief
#: 02043835/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438A0
msgctxt "001C01"
msgid "This... Clearly this has been edited."
msgstr "이건... 분명히 편집됐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043881
msgctxt "001C02"
msgid "Good work, the higher ups are going to be pleased. I'll read the report later for details."
msgstr "잘했어. 윗선이 기뻐하겠군. 세부 사항은 보고서를 나중에 읽어볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0077C029, 005837C5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그건 네가 얼마를 낼 생각이냐에 달렸지.
#: 0204382E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0204388B
msgctxt "001C03"
msgid "We'll just consider the matter of plugging a leak to be a happy bonus."
msgstr "정보 유출원을 막은 일은 기분 좋은 덤으로 치지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0077C029, 005837C5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그건 네가 얼마를 낼 생각이냐에 달렸지.
#: 0204382E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0204388B
msgctxt "001C04"
msgid "Don't worry, I'm not taking your assistance as charity. You'll be paid for the trouble."
msgstr "걱정 마. 네 도움을 자선으로 받지는 않을 거야. 수고한 만큼 보수는 받을 거다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 009788E2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204383D/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438A5
msgctxt "001C05"
msgid "With the help of our mutual friend here, we've finally concluded the investigation."
msgstr "여기 우리의 공통 지인 덕분에, 마침내 조사를 마무리했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00A73C15
#. Notes = Defiant / to Yemoja, Face: Defiant
#: 02043838/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438BB
msgctxt "001C06"
msgid "I won't entertain this joke any longer. You have no authority outside of UC space."
msgstr "이 농담은 더 이상 받아주지 않겠어. 당신은 식민지 연합 우주 밖에서는 아무 권한도 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00F1C831
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204382B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438AF
msgctxt "001C07"
msgid "Is this really enough to put someone away?"
msgstr "이 정도면 사람을 감옥에 넣기에 정말 충분한가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00965373
#. Notes = Smug / to RadhaDhawan, Face: Smug
#: 02043842/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438B5
msgctxt "001C08"
msgid "I'm saying there's no proof."
msgstr "증거가 없다는 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043892
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0097FF2D
#. Notes = Sad / to PercyKanu, Face: Sad
#: 02043834/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043892
msgctxt "001C09"
msgid "Percy... even Ryujin cannot protect you from this. And I doubt they would even want to."
msgstr "퍼시... 아무리 류진이라도 이번 일에서는 널 보호하지 못해. 애초에 그러고 싶어 할지도 의문이고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00DA8B08
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 02043843/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438A6
msgctxt "001C0A"
msgid "Are you denying it?"
msgstr "부인하는 건가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043886
msgctxt "001C0B"
msgid "It might be better for you to save your dignity and simply stop here."
msgstr "체면을 지키고 싶다면 여기서 그냥 멈추는 편이 나을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043890
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00F60E1E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204382F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:02043890
msgctxt "001C0C"
msgid "Depends. How much are you willing to pay for it?"
msgstr "그건 네가 얼마를 낼 생각이냐에 달렸지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043877
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00BB0267
#. Notes = VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry
#: 02043830/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043877
msgctxt "001C0D"
msgid "Tch. This isn't over. For any of you."
msgstr "쳇. 이걸로 끝난 게 아니야. 너희 누구에게도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00242A12
#. Notes = / to TracyWarren
#: 0204383B/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438B4
msgctxt "001C0E"
msgid "That's likely not going to be necessary."
msgstr "아마 그럴 필요는 없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00E82FA1
#. Notes = Concerned / to TracyWarren, Face: Concerned
#: 02043832/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438B0
msgctxt "001C0F"
msgid "If you think you can railroad me with some doctored evidence... Ryujin's lawyers will easily clear me."
msgstr "조작된 증거로 날 몰아붙일 수 있다고 생각한다면... 류진의 변호사들이 쉽게 내 혐의를 벗겨줄 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00B54B3B
#. Notes = SinisterSmile / to TracyWarren, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 02043837/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0204388E
msgctxt "001C10"
msgid "Such accusations, and after the courtesy Ryujin's offered to this council. You would have been lost without the resources we provided."
msgstr "이런 고발이라니, 류진이 이 대의회에 베푼 호의가 있는데도 말이야. 우리가 제공한 자원이 없었다면 너희는 길을 잃었을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0070CF2C, 0032824A, 00D697E5
#. Notes = Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 왜 이걸 나한테 가져온 거야?, Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, / to Player Default
#: 0204385C/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438B1
msgctxt "001C11"
msgid "You on the other hand already operate with a lot of freedom. Going back and forth won't raise any red flags."
msgstr "반면 넌 이미 꽤 자유롭게 움직이고 있어. 오가더라도 어떤 위험 신호도 올라오지 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0070CF2C, 0032824A, 00D697E5
#. Notes = Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 왜 이걸 나한테 가져온 거야?, Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, / to Player Default
#: 0204385C/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438B1
msgctxt "001C12"
msgid "No one else onboard's got the same luxury. Which means if I play too much of my hand, they might get spooked before we're ready to make our move."
msgstr "함선의 다른 누구도 그런 여유는 없어. 그러니 내가 패를 너무 많이 드러내면, 우리가 움직일 준비가 되기 전에 그들이 겁을 먹을 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0070CF2C, 0032824A, 00D697E5
#. Notes = Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 왜 이걸 나한테 가져온 거야?, Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern, / to Player Default
#: 0204385C/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438B1
msgctxt "001C13"
msgid "You're my best bet. I've been able to look into everyone on this station, including you. And at least for this you've been cleared on being the source I'm after."
msgstr "네가 내 최선의 선택이야. 난 너를 포함해 이 정거장의 모두를 조사해 볼 수 있었어. 그리고 적어도 이번 일에 관해서는 네가 내가 찾는 유출원이 아니라는 게 확인됐지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00002615
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 02043836/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438B7
msgctxt "001C14"
msgid "We have evidence linking you to the dispersal of several confidential reports relating to internal Terran operations."
msgstr "내부 테란 작전과 관련된 여러 기밀 보고서의 유포에 당신이 연루됐다는 증거가 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DFF27A
#. Notes = / to TracyWarren
#: 0204383F/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438BC
msgctxt "001C15"
msgid "Not exactly. I've been running up leads on that information leak."
msgstr "정확히는 아니야. 그 정보 유출에 대한 단서를 따라 조사하고 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E97E95
#: 0204384F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438B6
msgctxt "001C16"
msgid "I found the name you were looking for."
msgstr "네가 찾던 이름을 알아냈어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043891
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 0018376C
#. Notes = Surprised / to Yemoja, Face: Surprised
#: 02043841/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043891
msgctxt "001C17"
msgid "Agent Yemoja? It's rare to see you in person."
msgstr "예모자 요원? 직접 보는 건 드문 일이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043884
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00F29621
#. Notes = Defiant / to Yemoja, Face: Defiant
#: 02043839/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043884
msgctxt "001C18"
msgid "This is ludicrous. I don't care what you're basing this on, you're out of your depth."
msgstr "터무니없군. 뭘 근거로 그러는지는 몰라도, 당신이 감당할 수 있는 수준이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00C8C867
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043856/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438C4
msgctxt "001C19"
msgid "Don't people usually smoke on a smoke break?"
msgstr "사람들은 보통 흡연 휴식 때 담배를 피우지 않나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043897
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 000E4B27
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 0204383A/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043897
msgctxt "001C1A"
msgid "The protections you're used to don't extend to activities relating to the matters of this council -- namely the Terran Armada."
msgstr "당신이 익숙한 보호는 이 대의회의 사안, 즉 테란 함대와 관련된 활동까지 미치지 않습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00853B8B
#. Notes = / to Yemoja
#: 02043844/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0204389F
msgctxt "001C1B"
msgid "Your war on the Terrans has left you paranoid."
msgstr "테란과의 전쟁이 널 편집증적으로 만들었군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00A110A2
#. Notes = Confused / to Yemoja, Face: Confused
#: 02043844/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0204389E
msgctxt "001C1C"
msgid "You can't be serious. Surely this is some UC joke to liven the atmosphere."
msgstr "진심일 리 없지. 분위기 좀 살리려는 식민지 연합식 농담이겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043880
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00252DD6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043861/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043880
msgctxt "001C1D"
msgid "I'm in. Might as well wrap up this problem."
msgstr "할게. 이 문제도 마무리하는 게 낫겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B0FBFB
#. Notes = / to Player
#: 02043846/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438B8
msgctxt "001C1E"
msgid "Now that squares a lot of holes."
msgstr "이제 많은 빈칸이 맞아떨어지는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00657FDC
#. Notes = Question / to Yemoja, Face: Question
#: 0204383E/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020438A8
msgctxt "001C1F"
msgid "Do you have business with me? I don't recall anything pressing."
msgstr "나한테 볼일이 있나? 급한 일은 기억에 없는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043878
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001041E5
#. Notes = Smirk / to PercyKanu, Face: Smirk
#: 02043840/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043878
msgctxt "001C20"
msgid "Ryujin -- and by extension you -- waived your rights to neutrality when VOID was formed."
msgstr "류진은, 그리고 더 나아가 당신은, VOID가 결성될 때 중립 권리를 포기했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043894
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 003B39D6
#. Notes = Stern / to PercyKanu, Face: Stern
#: 02043845/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02043894
msgctxt "001C21"
msgid "Percy Kanu. Under the authority of Aegis as empowered by the UC government, I'm placing you under arrest for conspiracy of collusion and treason."
msgstr "퍼시 카누. 식민지 연합 정부로부터 권한을 위임받은 이지스의 권한으로, 당신을 결탁 및 반역 공모 혐의로 체포합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D9357A
#. Notes = Prompt: 난 이런 곳에서 제일 잘 움직여. 집에 돌아오니 좋군.
#: 0204386E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438B3
msgctxt "001C22"
msgid "And given you feel at ease somewhere like this, I'd say I've found the perfect partner to carry out this little request."
msgstr "그리고 네가 이런 곳에서도 편안해한다는 걸 보면, 이 작은 부탁을 수행할 완벽한 파트너를 찾은 셈이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00B9DB65
#: 02043857/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:0204388D
msgctxt "001C23"
msgid "That doesn't sound right to me, I'm just out here on a smoke break. Can't imagine you have any business with me."
msgstr "그건 말이 안 되는군. 난 그냥 흡연 휴식으로 여기 나와 있을 뿐이야. 당신이 나한테 볼일이 있을 리가 없는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 004E8F95
#: 0204384D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0204387F
msgctxt "001C25"
msgid "Let's hear it, then. What do you have for me?"
msgstr "그럼 들어보지. 내게 줄 게 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043888
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 004781E3
#: 02043848/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:02043888
msgctxt "001C26"
msgid "I'd been wondering on the motivations. Why someone as high up at Ryujin as Percy would want to sell data to the Terrans..."
msgstr "동기가 궁금했어. 퍼시처럼 류진의 높은 자리에 있는 사람이 왜 테란에게 데이터를 팔고 싶어 했는지..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 0010E92F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043852/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438C2
msgctxt "001C27"
msgid "But I was told to meet a contact out here."
msgstr "하지만 난 여기서 연락책을 만나라는 말을 들었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043882
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00F5AAB2
#: 02043863/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043882
msgctxt "001C28"
msgid "Hard to verify much while everyone was scrambling dealing with the main forces, but now that things have calmed down I managed to finish half of the puzzle."
msgstr "모두가 주 병력을 상대하느라 허둥대는 동안엔 확인할 수 있는 게 많지 않았지만, 이제 상황이 진정됐으니 퍼즐의 절반은 맞출 수 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043887
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00439B44, 0065E303
#. Notes = Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 사람들은 보통 흡연 휴식 때 담배를 피우지 않나?, / to Player Default
#: 02043855/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:02043887
msgctxt "001C29"
msgid "If that group's entitled to random breaks throughout the day, well, then so am I."
msgstr "그 무리가 하루 종일 아무 때나 쉬어도 된다면, 뭐, 나도 그래도 되겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043887
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00439B44, 0065E303
#. Notes = Disgust / to Player Default, Face: Disgust, Prompt: 사람들은 보통 흡연 휴식 때 담배를 피우지 않나?, / to Player Default
#: 02043855/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:02043887
msgctxt "001C2A"
msgid "What, I'm not allowed a few minutes to myself unless I show proof of lung damage?"
msgstr "뭐, 폐 손상 증명이라도 보여주지 않으면 나 혼자 몇 분 쉬는 것도 안 된다는 건가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00181A98
#: 0204384E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438AB
msgctxt "001C2B"
msgid "Is that so? I'm assuming this means you managed to get what we needed from our mutual friend."
msgstr "그래? 그럼 우리의 공통 지인에게서 필요한 걸 확보했다는 뜻으로 봐도 되겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 0084E641
#. Notes = / to VossSlate
#: 02043850/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438AD
msgctxt "001C2C"
msgid "Be careful walking around here, wouldn't want anything valuable dropping in the water."
msgstr "이 주변을 걸을 땐 조심해. 귀중한 게 물에 빠지는 일은 없었으면 하니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B07D26, 005232F6, 00B7AED7
#. Notes = Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief, Prompt: 내가 관심 있을 거라고 생각한 이유가 뭐야?, / to Player Default, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02043865/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438AA
msgctxt "001C2D"
msgid "When you hear what I've been looking into, you might even be mad I didn't bring it to you earlier."
msgstr "내가 무엇을 조사하고 있었는지 들으면, 왜 더 일찍 가져오지 않았냐고 화낼 수도 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B07D26, 005232F6, 00B7AED7
#. Notes = Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief, Prompt: 내가 관심 있을 거라고 생각한 이유가 뭐야?, / to Player Default, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02043865/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438AA
msgctxt "001C2E"
msgid "You can act like you couldn't care less, but we both know you're no stranger to helping out when you can."
msgstr "관심 없는 척할 수는 있겠지만, 도울 수 있을 때 돕는 일이 너에게 낯설지 않다는 건 우리 둘 다 알잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B07D26, 005232F6, 00B7AED7
#. Notes = Disbelief / to Player Default, Face: Disbelief, Prompt: 내가 관심 있을 거라고 생각한 이유가 뭐야?, / to Player Default, Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk
#: 02043865/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438AA
msgctxt "001C2F"
msgid "Come on. \"Hero\" who led the resistance against the Terrans?"
msgstr "왜 이래. 테란에 맞선 저항군을 이끈 \"영웅\" 말이야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00F030F8
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 하지만 난 여기서 연락책을 만나라는 말을 들었어.
#: 02043851/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438AE
msgctxt "001C30"
msgid "*sigh* If that was the case, then I don't think whoever told you that would want you running your mouth off about it. Do you?"
msgstr "*한숨* 그게 사실이라면, 그 말을 전한 사람도 네가 그걸 떠벌리고 다니길 바라진 않을 것 같은데. 안 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00BCFBE4
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0204385A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204389B
msgctxt "001C31"
msgid "There are too many eyes on me right now to risk transmission of anything more, so I need you to go meet them and help with whatever it is they're running into."
msgstr "지금은 나를 보는 눈이 너무 많아서 더 전송하는 건 위험해. 그러니 네가 가서 그들을 만나고, 그들이 겪는 문제가 뭐든 도와줘야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0011B86B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204385D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A4
msgctxt "001C32"
msgid "Why come to me with this?"
msgstr "왜 이걸 나한테 가져온 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00FDA649
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 내가 착각했나 보군.
#: 02043853/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438AC
msgctxt "001C33"
msgid "Happens to the best of us. Hope you find what you're looking for, friend."
msgstr "누구에게나 있는 일이야. 찾는 걸 발견하길 바라, 친구."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 00951E52
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043854/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:020438BA
msgctxt "001C34"
msgid "I guess I was mistaken."
msgstr "내가 착각했나 보군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043898
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00456249
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204385F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043898
msgctxt "001C35"
msgid "My services are always open for the right amount of credits."
msgstr "크레딧만 충분하다면 내 서비스는 언제나 열려 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E0DBA9
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 할게. 이 문제도 마무리하는 게 낫겠지.
#: 02043860/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438BF
msgctxt "001C36"
msgid "One of many, unfortunately. But this'll definitely help take care of a big one."
msgstr "안타깝지만 많은 문제 중 하나야. 그래도 이건 큰 문제 하나를 해결하는 데 분명 도움이 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043885
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A8A600
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed, Prompt: 난 이런 곳에서 제일 잘 움직여. 집에 돌아오니 좋군.
#: 02043873/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043885
msgctxt "001C37"
msgid "I'm not convinced that's entirely a good thing. But it seems to be doing you some form of success."
msgstr "그게 전적으로 좋은 일인지는 확신이 안 서. 하지만 너에게는 어느 정도 성과가 있는 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005A6535
#: 02043858/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:0204387C
msgctxt "001C38"
msgid "I think you have something for me."
msgstr "나한테 줄 게 있는 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 008379D0
#: 02043859/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204387D
msgctxt "001C39"
msgid "I'll stick around here while you take care of this, keep the heat off you."
msgstr "네가 이 일을 처리하는 동안 난 여기 남아서 네게 쏠리는 관심을 막아둘게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D49667
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043872/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204389C
msgctxt "001C3A"
msgid "I feel uneasy whenever I dock here, but there's always something to do."
msgstr "여기에 도킹할 때마다 불안하지만, 늘 할 일은 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00298315
#: 0204385B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A9
msgctxt "001C3B"
msgid "I managed to get what I have over to a contact at MAST, but I got word they ran into a problem they need help with."
msgstr "내가 가진 건 MAST의 연락책에게 넘겼는데, 그쪽에서 도움이 필요한 문제에 부딪혔다는 소식을 들었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B82537
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043866/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A2
msgctxt "001C3C"
msgid "What makes you think I'd be interested?"
msgstr "내가 관심 있을 거라고 생각한 이유가 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043896
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00563D4D
#: 02043867/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043896
msgctxt "001C3D"
msgid "Thing is, I'm looking to tie up loose ends related to the Terran fleet you scattered."
msgstr "문제는, 네가 흩어 놓은 테란 함대와 관련된 뒷마무리를 하려는 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0079C7B8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043875/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204388A
msgctxt "001C3E"
msgid "With the Terrans dealt with, I'm surprised you still have a reason to hang around here."
msgstr "테란이 처리됐는데도 네가 아직 여기 어슬렁거릴 이유가 있다니 놀랍군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EE66C9
#. Notes = Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk, Prompt: 크레딧만 충분하다면 내 서비스는 언제나 열려 있어.
#: 0204385E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A1
msgctxt "001C3F"
msgid "Nothing more consistent than someone backed by a need for credits. I knew you could be counted on."
msgstr "크레딧이 필요한 사람만큼 일관된 존재도 없지. 네게 기대도 된다는 걸 알고 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 007B4F63, 0088A425, 001D2E52
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그 말은 나도 너한테 할 수 있지 않을까?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0204386F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A7
msgctxt "001C40"
msgid "I was hoping I could just point you here and not have to come back myself."
msgstr "난 그냥 너를 여기로 안내하고, 다시 직접 돌아오지 않아도 되길 바랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 007B4F63, 0088A425, 001D2E52
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그 말은 나도 너한테 할 수 있지 않을까?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0204386F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A7
msgctxt "001C41"
msgid "I prefer laying low, bouncing from assignment to assignment, but I feel too exposed when I'm in one location too long. Double that if I have to keep returning to it."
msgstr "난 몸을 낮추고 임무에서 임무로 옮겨 다니는 걸 선호하지만, 한 장소에 너무 오래 있으면 너무 노출된 기분이 들어. 계속 돌아와야 한다면 그 느낌은 두 배고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 007B4F63, 0088A425, 001D2E52
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 그 말은 나도 너한테 할 수 있지 않을까?, Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0204386F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438A7
msgctxt "001C42"
msgid "Fair enough. But I'm sure you can tell this isn't a place I tend to hang my hat."
msgstr "그렇군. 하지만 여기가 내가 눌러앉는 곳은 아니라는 건 너도 알겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00845AA4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043874/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204387B
msgctxt "001C43"
msgid "I'm at my best in places like this. It's good to be home."
msgstr "난 이런 곳에서 제일 잘 움직여. 집에 돌아오니 좋군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043889
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00501B46
#. Notes = Prompt: 여기에 도킹할 때마다 불안하지만, 늘 할 일은 있지.
#: 0204386D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043889
msgctxt "001C44"
msgid "But if you're in need of a scenery change, I've got a request you might be interested in helping with."
msgstr "하지만 기분 전환이 필요하다면, 네가 도와주면 관심 가질 만한 부탁이 하나 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00E88CDD
#: 02043862/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438B2
msgctxt "001C45"
msgid "With your help, I could finish the other half and make it decisive."
msgstr "네 도움이 있으면 나머지 절반도 끝내고 결정타로 만들 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0063201A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043870/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204388C
msgctxt "001C46"
msgid "Couldn't I say the same about you?"
msgstr "그 말은 나도 너한테 할 수 있지 않을까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0077C085
#. Notes = Concentrating, Face: Concentrating
#: 02043864/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438C0
msgctxt "001C47"
msgid "We've got intel on someone getting access to our Terran operations and leaking them to other parties. Could be they still are."
msgstr "누군가 우리 테란 관련 작전에 접근해서 다른 세력에게 유출하고 있다는 첩보가 있어. 아직도 그러고 있을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043895
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00897E03
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Prompt: 여기에 도킹할 때마다 불안하지만, 늘 할 일은 있지.
#: 02043871/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043895
msgctxt "001C48"
msgid "Don't let the people that filter through here rub off too much on you. That's a stink that doesn't come off easy."
msgstr "여길 드나드는 사람들에게 너무 물들지 마. 그런 냄새는 쉽게 안 빠지니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009E3BD1
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Prompt: 네 얘기를 들어본다고 손해 볼 건 없지.
#: 0204386A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:020438C3
msgctxt "001C49"
msgid "I knew you would. You have that helpful streak in you."
msgstr "네가 그럴 줄 알았어. 너한텐 남을 돕는 기질이 있거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043893
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00401A1E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204386B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:02043893
msgctxt "001C4A"
msgid "No harm in hearing you out."
msgstr "네 얘기를 들어본다고 손해 볼 건 없지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EA1129, 00EE39D5
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 넌 항상 내게 시킬 일이 더 있는 것 같네., / to Player Default
#: 02043868/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204388F
msgctxt "001C4B"
msgid "But count yourself lucky. I've lived both sides of it, and it's not always a bad thing to be wanted."
msgstr "하지만 운이 좋다고 생각해. 난 양쪽 다 겪어봤는데, 현상수배된 게 늘 나쁜 것만은 아니더군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204388F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00EA1129, 00EE39D5
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 넌 항상 내게 시킬 일이 더 있는 것 같네., / to Player Default
#: 02043868/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204388F
msgctxt "001C4C"
msgid "That's the job. If it isn't one thing, it's another."
msgstr "원래 그런 일이야. 하나가 아니면 또 다른 일이 생기지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B99438
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043869/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0204387E
msgctxt "001C4D"
msgid "Seems like you always have more work for me."
msgstr "넌 항상 내게 시킬 일이 더 있는 것 같네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204374A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00676FA5, 000B76AA
#: 02043748/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0204374A
msgctxt "001C4E"
msgid "I know there's a way to utilize it, but I'm missing one key part of the assimilation process."
msgstr "이걸 활용할 방법이 있다는 건 알아. 하지만 동화 과정에서 핵심적인 부분 하나가 빠져 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204374A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00676FA5, 000B76AA
#: 02043748/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0204374A
msgctxt "001C4F"
msgid "There are multiple issues with that. "
msgstr "그건 문제가 한두 가지가 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203BF21
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_04
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_AnwarSinaga_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 00C0DBC3, 009ADC21, 00C8501E
#: 0203BEF9/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_04:0203BF21
msgctxt "001C50"
msgid "It's still theoretical at the moment, but I believe there's a lot of potential applications, from materials to circuit augmentation."
msgstr "아직은 이론 단계지만, 재료부터 회로 증강까지 응용 가능성이 아주 많다고 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204374B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 009FEE3E, 000193D6
#: 02043749/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0204374B
msgctxt "001C51"
msgid "There's gotta be more of this X-Tech out there."
msgstr "이런 X-테크가 어딘가에 더 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204374B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Terran_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_TerranAudio_05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MQIntro_TolliverRoyce_AUDIOONLY
#. SoundFileID = 009FEE3E, 000193D6
#: 02043749/00000/SFTER_TerranAudio_05:0204374B
msgctxt "001C52"
msgid "Well, I can't help you with the 1s and 0s, but I can talk to the Admiral about boosting production. "
msgstr "뭐, 1과 0 쪽은 내가 도와줄 수 없지만, 생산량을 늘리는 건 제독에게 얘기해 볼 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 002DA4F3, 0070CCC7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 무슨 일이 있었지?
#: 0204377C/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378D
msgctxt "001C53"
msgid "They got my ship pretty good. My Grav Drive is fine, but my engines are almost down."
msgstr "놈들이 내 우주선을 제대로 박살 냈어. 내 중력 구동기는 멀쩡하지만 엔진은 거의 나가기 직전이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 002DA4F3, 0070CCC7
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 무슨 일이 있었지?
#: 0204377C/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378D
msgctxt "001C54"
msgid "I was attacked by some Terran patrol."
msgstr "테란 순찰대에게 공격받았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00614713
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0204377D/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378B
msgctxt "001C55"
msgid "What happened to you?"
msgstr "무슨 일이 있었지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043792
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A0E500, 00E7A847
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0204377E/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043792
msgctxt "001C56"
msgid "I saw them scanning the orbit pretty frantically. The second they detected me, they frenzied. I just barely got away."
msgstr "궤도를 정신없이 스캔하고 있더라고. 날 감지하자마자 미친 듯이 달려들었어. 겨우 빠져나왔지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043792
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00A0E500, 00E7A847
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0204377E/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043792
msgctxt "001C57"
msgid "If you're heading towards Niira, I would watch yourself. Some signal around there has the Terrans on high alert."
msgstr "니라 쪽으로 갈 거라면 조심해. 그 근처의 어떤 신호 때문에 테란들이 경계 태세야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378F
msgctxt "001C58"
msgid "Tell me what happened to your ship."
msgstr "네 우주선에 무슨 일이 있었는지 말해 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00F55EDF
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 괜찮아?
#: 02043780/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378E
msgctxt "001C59"
msgid "Yeah, I'll be fine. Like I said I just need to patch my ship up."
msgstr "응, 난 괜찮을 거야. 말했듯이 우주선만 좀 수리하면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00325676
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: 미안하지만, 나눠줄 여분이 없어.
#: 02043782/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378A
msgctxt "001C5A"
msgid "Don't worry about it, I'm close enough to orbit someone will stop by."
msgstr "걱정하지 마. 궤도에서 충분히 가까우니 누군가는 들를 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204378C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00E4647F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02043781/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:0204378C
msgctxt "001C5B"
msgid "Are you ok?"
msgstr "괜찮아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043789
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00D4893F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02043783/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043789
msgctxt "001C5C"
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't have any to spare."
msgstr "미안하지만, 나눠줄 여분이 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043788
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B863F5
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral, Prompt: [우주선 부품 1개 주기] 물론이지. 나눠줄 게 좀 있어.
#: 02043784/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043788
msgctxt "001C5D"
msgid "Thank you, you're a life saver."
msgstr "고마워. 정말 생명의 은인이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043787
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F743A4
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02043785/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043787
msgctxt "001C5E"
msgid "[Give 1 Ship Part] Sure, I've got some to spare."
msgstr "[우주선 부품 1개 주기] 물론이지. 나눠줄 게 좀 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043795
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00300A42
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02043786/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter02:02043795
msgctxt "001C5F"
msgid "Hey, you have some ship parts to spare by any chance? My ship's in bad shape, I could really use a hand. I've got credits to spare."
msgstr "혹시 남는 우주선 부품 좀 있어? 내 우주선 상태가 엉망이라 정말 도움이 필요해. 크레딧은 줄 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00341FCF
#: 0204379D:020437AD
msgctxt "001C60"
msgid "Always a pleasure."
msgstr "언제나 반갑지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 007997FD
#: 0204379D:020437AC
msgctxt "001C61"
msgid "Stay safe, it's a wild world out there."
msgstr "조심해. 밖은 험한 세상이니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00233632
#: 0204379D:020437AB
msgctxt "001C62"
msgid "Watch your back out there."
msgstr "밖에서는 뒤를 조심해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00E5D980
#: 0204379D:020437AA
msgctxt "001C63"
msgid "You have a good one."
msgstr "좋은 하루 보내."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00A6D8A2
#: 0204379D:020437A9
msgctxt "001C64"
msgid "I'll be here if you need me."
msgstr "필요하면 여기 있을게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00986481
#: 0204379D:020437A8
msgctxt "001C65"
msgid "I'll be seeing you."
msgstr "또 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00CBA183
#: 0204379E:020437A6
msgctxt "001C66"
msgid "Take your time, I've got all day. Come see me when you're ready to buy."
msgstr "천천히 봐. 시간은 많아. 살 준비가 되면 와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00D9F765
#: 0204379E:020437A5
msgctxt "001C67"
msgid "If you need a weapon looked at, I'm here to help."
msgstr "무기를 봐줄 사람이 필요하면 내가 도와줄게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00A61C8D
#: 0204379E:020437A4
msgctxt "001C68"
msgid "Shops open, as always."
msgstr "가게는 늘 그렇듯 열려 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00549C98
#: 0204379E:020437A3
msgctxt "001C69"
msgid "Always nice to see a friendly face around."
msgstr "주변에 반가운 얼굴이 보이면 언제나 좋지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 00A974C2
#: 0204379E:020437A2
msgctxt "001C6A"
msgid "Welcome back."
msgstr "다시 와서 반가워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 006093A8
#: 0204379E:020437A1
msgctxt "001C6B"
msgid "Feel free to browse, I got plenty in stock."
msgstr "편하게 둘러봐. 재고는 넉넉해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020437A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMBuckE
#. SoundFileID = 0093B492
#: 0204379E:020437A0
msgctxt "001C6C"
msgid "Nice to see you're still in one piece."
msgstr "아직 멀쩡한 걸 보니 반갑네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043793
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 0078F5D7
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02043779/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02043793
msgctxt "001C6D"
msgid "Your operating system is running remotely somewhere isn't it?"
msgstr "네 운영체제는 어딘가에서 원격으로 돌아가고 있는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043794
msgctxt "001C6E"
msgid "Ask me again in a few hundred years and maybe I'll have an answer, for you."
msgstr "몇백 년 뒤에 다시 물어봐. 그땐 대답해 줄 수 있을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043794
msgctxt "001C6F"
msgid "Operating system? *Chuckles* You're partially correct, but I like to keep my secrets."
msgstr "운영체제? *킥킥 웃음* 어느 정도는 맞지만, 난 내 비밀을 지키는 걸 좋아해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043791
msgctxt "001C70"
msgid "You tell me, friend. You seem to be the expert on the subject."
msgstr "네가 말해 봐, 친구. 그 분야 전문가는 너 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043790
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = BUCKE
#. SoundFileID = 00F4D0AE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204377B/00000/SFTER_MS01_BUCKE_Vendor_0100_Scene:02043790
msgctxt "001C71"
msgid "Your memory capacity is unusually small and you're missing a storage drive all together. How are you functioning?"
msgstr "네 메모리 용량은 비정상적으로 작고, 저장 드라이브가 통째로 없잖아. 대체 어떻게 작동하는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0064D6BB, 00E7822B, 00BA7146
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly disappointed. / to Player Default, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F8
msgctxt "001C72"
msgid "We are forever grateful."
msgstr "우리는 영원히 감사할 것입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0064D6BB, 00E7822B, 00BA7146
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly disappointed. / to Player Default, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F8
msgctxt "001C73"
msgid "While the Terrans may have the capacity to potentially continue to mobilize forces, in the grand scheme of it all they are utterly crushed."
msgstr "테란에게 아직 병력을 계속 동원할 역량이 남아 있을 수는 있지만, 큰 흐름에서 보면 그들은 완전히 무너졌습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 0064D6BB, 00E7822B, 00BA7146
#. Notes = Professional, but slightly disappointed. / to Player Default, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F8
msgctxt "001C74"
msgid "Enough of this. Regardless of how others feel about your decision, we are eternally grateful for your help."
msgstr "이쯤 하죠. 다른 이들이 당신의 결정에 대해 어떻게 느끼든, 우리는 당신의 도움에 영원히 감사하고 있습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008AA9E6, 0011C594, 00439064, 0020100E
#. Notes = Snaps at Roxane, but trying to stay professional. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329BE
msgctxt "001C75"
msgid "We are in your debt."
msgstr "우리는 당신에게 빚을 졌습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008AA9E6, 0011C594, 00439064, 0020100E
#. Notes = Snaps at Roxane, but trying to stay professional. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329BE
msgctxt "001C76"
msgid "Had you not turned the Terrans robots against them, who knows how many more thousands would have died if they continued to mobilize."
msgstr "당신이 테란의 로봇들을 그들에게 돌려세우지 않았다면, 그들이 계속 동원되는 동안 얼마나 더 많은 수천 명이 죽었을지 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 008AA9E6, 0011C594, 00439064, 0020100E
#. Notes = Snaps at Roxane, but trying to stay professional. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, / to Player Default
#: 02032963/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329BE
msgctxt "001C77"
msgid "You listen to me, words can't express the good you've done today."
msgstr "내 말 잘 들어요. 오늘 당신이 해낸 선행은 말로 다 표현할 수 없습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00669115, 000ADB47, 00569F58
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C5
msgctxt "001C78"
msgid "You should have taken the opportunity and ended the Terran threat...Permanently."
msgstr "그 기회를 잡아 테란의 위협을... 영원히 끝냈어야 했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00669115, 000ADB47, 00569F58
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C5
msgctxt "001C79"
msgid "However, we did receive a report of the dilemma you faced on the bridge. I have to say, not taking advantage of such a fatal weakness is...Regrettable."
msgstr "하지만 함교에서 당신이 마주한 딜레마에 대한 보고를 받았습니다. 솔직히 말해, 그런 치명적인 약점을 이용하지 않은 것은... 유감스럽군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DAA427, 007A1A4B, 00AAD7BB
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C4
msgctxt "001C7A"
msgid "You've secured our future and-"
msgstr "당신은 우리의 미래를 지켜냈고-"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020329C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Tracy
#. SoundFileID = 00DAA427, 007A1A4B, 00AAD7BB
#. Notes = Serious, but still happy the fight went so well. / Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug, / to Player Default
#: 02032964/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020329C4
msgctxt "001C7B"
msgid "I understand this was a... difficult decision. But none the less necessary. Your actions here will cripple the Terrans ability to mobilize permanently."
msgstr "이것이... 어려운 결정이었다는 건 압니다. 하지만 그럼에도 필요한 결정이었죠. 여기서의 당신 행동은 테란의 동원 능력을 영구적으로 무력화할 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EFA4A5, 00D03565
#. Notes = Annoyed at Void for thinking the Player failed in some part. Emphasis on 'or anyone's' as a jab at VOID / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Softer and grateful to the player. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F6
msgctxt "001C7C"
msgid "If the Terran robots were frenzied, their rampage would've been indiscriminate. Who knows how many thousands would have been lost."
msgstr "테란 로봇들이 광분했다면 그 난동은 무차별적이었을 겁니다. 얼마나 많은 수천 명이 목숨을 잃었을지 모릅니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EFA4A5, 00D03565
#. Notes = Annoyed at Void for thinking the Player failed in some part. Emphasis on 'or anyone's' as a jab at VOID / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Softer and grateful to the player. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F6
msgctxt "001C7D"
msgid "Don't listen to them. The sacrifices of those innocent lives wasn't your, or anyone's, call to make."
msgstr "저 사람들 말 듣지 마. 무고한 생명들을 희생시킬 권리는 너에게도, 누구에게도 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EB1347, 00770341, 008E7913, 003C914D
#. Notes = Just learned the Player killed many innocent people. Words can't express her anger. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Having trouble finding the words in her anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Still seething and nearly screaming in anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Starting to get softer. Her anger lessening. Not because she's not mad, but because she's growing exhausted from the anger and raised voice. / Worried / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F5
msgctxt "001C7E"
msgid "I hope you got the victory you wanted... All that blood is on you. It's on your hands..."
msgstr "네가 원하던 승리를 얻었길 바라... 그 모든 피는 네 책임이야. 네 손에 묻어 있어..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EB1347, 00770341, 008E7913, 003C914D
#. Notes = Just learned the Player killed many innocent people. Words can't express her anger. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Having trouble finding the words in her anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Still seething and nearly screaming in anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Starting to get softer. Her anger lessening. Not because she's not mad, but because she's growing exhausted from the anger and raised voice. / Worried / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F5
msgctxt "001C7F"
msgid "But, no. Frenzy an army of those damned machines to rampage, maim, and slaughter everything in their path!"
msgstr "그런데 아니었지. 그 빌어먹을 기계 군대를 광분시켜 가는 길의 모든 것을 날뛰며 불구로 만들고 학살하게 했잖아!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EB1347, 00770341, 008E7913, 003C914D
#. Notes = Just learned the Player killed many innocent people. Words can't express her anger. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Having trouble finding the words in her anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Still seething and nearly screaming in anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Starting to get softer. Her anger lessening. Not because she's not mad, but because she's growing exhausted from the anger and raised voice. / Worried / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F5
msgctxt "001C80"
msgid "After everything... I really thought that after everything that- I trusted you."
msgstr "그 모든 일을 겪고도... 난 정말, 그 모든 일을 겪은 뒤에는- 널 믿었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00EB1347, 00770341, 008E7913, 003C914D
#. Notes = Just learned the Player killed many innocent people. Words can't express her anger. / VeryAngry / to Player Default, Face: VeryAngry, Having trouble finding the words in her anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Still seething and nearly screaming in anger. / Angry / to Player Default, Starting to get softer. Her anger lessening. Not because she's not mad, but because she's growing exhausted from the anger and raised voice. / Worried / to Player Default (+1 more)
#: 020451F1/00000/VOID_1600_02_SFTER_MQ03_ENDING:020451F5
msgctxt "001C81"
msgid "You had no right to make that choice!"
msgstr "넌 그런 선택을 할 권리가 없었어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EB563F
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: [스타본] 널 설득할 수 없다는 건 이미 알아. 빨리 끝내자.
#: 020451F2/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:020451F9
msgctxt "001C82"
msgid "I've never met you in my life, but you're just about right. Troops on me!"
msgstr "난 너를 평생 처음 보지만, 네 말이 거의 맞아. 병력은 나를 따라!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = DELTA_FB_0900_06_SFTER_MQ05
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00DF07CA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020451F3/00000/DELTA_FB_0900_06_SFTER_MQ05:020451FA
msgctxt "001C83"
msgid "Scanning...Artificial gravity has been disabled for power conservation. Unifier systems in critical condition."
msgstr "스캔 중... 전력 보존을 위해 인공 중력이 비활성화되었습니다. 유니파이어 시스템 임계 상태."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020451F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 008DC34C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020451F4/00000/Admiral_FB_1150_SFTER_MQ03:020451F7
msgctxt "001C84"
msgid "[Starborn] I already know there's no convincing you, lets get this over with."
msgstr "[스타본] 널 설득할 수 없다는 건 이미 알아. 빨리 끝내자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A208B3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C306/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452E3
msgctxt "001C85"
msgid "It sounds like all the symptoms of lying to me. "
msgstr "내겐 거짓말의 증상이 전부 드러난 것처럼 들리는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CFFCB4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C306/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452E2
msgctxt "001C86"
msgid "It's hard to lie when your body betrays you."
msgstr "몸이 배신하면 거짓말하기 어렵지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005E511F
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C307/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452F5
msgctxt "001C87"
msgid "I don't know if that makes me feel any better."
msgstr "그 말을 들어도 별로 마음이 편해지진 않네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004BED1D
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C307/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452F4
msgctxt "001C88"
msgid "I already told you, we're not Terrans, we're surveyors."
msgstr "이미 말했잖아. 우린 테란이 아니라 조사원들이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452DD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00F7E2B8
#. Notes = Nervous laugh at the beginning. / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C30B/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452DD
msgctxt "001C89"
msgid "Extermination? Seems a bit harsh, doesn't it? "
msgstr "몰살? 좀 과한 것 같지 않아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E0A949
#. Notes = Nervous laugh at the beginning. / Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C30B/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452DC
msgctxt "001C8A"
msgid "Whoa, you're not going to trust that robot, are you?"
msgstr "잠깐, 저 로봇을 믿으려는 건 아니지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007FF3FC
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C305/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452EF
msgctxt "001C8B"
msgid "Just hear me out on this..."
msgstr "일단 내 말 좀 들어 봐..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0072637E
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C305/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452EE
msgctxt "001C8C"
msgid "I think there's a little more to this situation than just the possibility of me lying."
msgstr "이 상황엔 내가 거짓말을 할 가능성 말고도 좀 더 많은 게 있다고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0044D062
#. Notes = Neutral / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C30D/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452E0
msgctxt "001C8D"
msgid "Analysis: Vital signs elevated. Voice pattern unsteady. Human attempting deception. Attempt unsuccessful."
msgstr "분석: 생체 신호 상승. 음성 패턴 불안정. 인간이 기만을 시도 중. 시도 실패."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00893C02
#. Notes = Neutral / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C30D/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452DF
msgctxt "001C8E"
msgid "Analysis: Rise in blood pressure. Elevated heart rate. Auxiliary, chance of deception has increased."
msgstr "분석: 혈압 상승. 심박수 증가. 보조 개체, 기만 가능성이 증가했습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004A22FB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C308/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452DA
msgctxt "001C8F"
msgid "The only people that need to be worried about us are Terrans."
msgstr "우리를 걱정해야 할 사람들은 테란뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0043F8D3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C308/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452D9
msgctxt "001C90"
msgid "If you aren't Terrans, you have nothing to worry about."
msgstr "너희가 테란이 아니라면 걱정할 것 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009B77B2
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C309/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452F2
msgctxt "001C91"
msgid "Then tell me, who wouldn't be nervous in this situation?"
msgstr "그럼 말해 봐. 이런 상황에서 누가 긴장하지 않겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E12336
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C309/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452F1
msgctxt "001C92"
msgid "You don't think I have good reason to be nervous?"
msgstr "내가 긴장할 만한 이유가 충분하다고 생각하지 않아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00447240
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C30A/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452D7
msgctxt "001C93"
msgid "Delta is just stating facts."
msgstr "델타는 사실을 말하고 있을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020452D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004BF1B4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C30A/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020452D6
msgctxt "001C94"
msgid "I trust Delta."
msgstr "난 델타를 믿어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204586A
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006BA315
#. Notes = What's the big deal / to Cora
#: 02045865/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:0204586A
msgctxt "001CA4"
msgid "Recommending reading at preferred pace for better comprehension."
msgstr "더 나은 이해를 위해 선호하는 속도로 읽을 것을 권장합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045868
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00B37DE7
#. Notes = Deadpan / to Delta
#: 02045866/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:02045868
msgctxt "001CA5"
msgid "...You're weird."
msgstr "...너 이상해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045869
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora01
#. SceneName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Cora
#. SoundFileID = 00089F9F
#. Notes = Stunned / Awed / to Delta, Face: Awed
#: 02045867/00000/SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_Convo_Cora00_01COPY0000:02045869
msgctxt "001CA6"
msgid "But I didn't understand any of it."
msgstr "하지만 하나도 이해 못 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00CB2E32
#. Notes = Professional. Tone is mostly friendly, but there is a slight hint of them mocking the Player. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:020517CA
msgctxt "001CA7"
msgid "Seen any Terrans still running about lately?"
msgstr "최근에 아직 돌아다니는 테란 본 적 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0073CE19
#. Notes = Professional. Tone is mostly friendly, but there is a slight hint of disappointment in 'I hope it was worth it.' / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:020517C9
msgctxt "001CA8"
msgid "You certainly put your stock in Roxane's words to save innocents. I hope it was worth it."
msgstr "무고한 사람들을 구하겠다고 록산의 말을 꽤 믿었군. 그럴 가치가 있었길 바라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00B734AB
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020345CB:020517C8
msgctxt "001CA9"
msgid "Thanks to you the Settled Systems will be far safer now. And safer for any Ryujin shipments."
msgstr "당신 덕분에 이제 개척 성계는 훨씬 안전해질 겁니다. 류진 선적물에도 더 안전하겠죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00214DA7
#. Notes = Professional. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020345CB:020517C7
msgctxt "001CAA"
msgid "After the Unifier its hard to say if we're truly safe from the Terrans. If you see any of them, make sure to put them down immediately. "
msgstr "유니파이어 이후로 우리가 정말 테란에게서 안전한지는 말하기 어렵습니다. 그들을 보게 되면 즉시 처치하세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 0048A73A
#. Notes = Trying to act professional, but still a little annoyed the Player didn't take the chance to stop the Terrans once and for all. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020345CB:020517C6
msgctxt "001CAB"
msgid "Keep your eyes peeled for any remaining Terrans. I think you owe the Settled Systems that much."
msgstr "남은 테란이 있는지 눈을 크게 뜨고 살피세요. 그 정도는 개척 성계에 빚진 셈이라고 생각합니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 000D5C03
#. Notes = Professional. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020345CB:020517C5
msgctxt "001CAC"
msgid "After the Unifier we shouldn't see any more Terrans any time soon. But you can never be too careful."
msgstr "유니파이어 이후로 당분간 테란을 더 볼 일은 없을 겁니다. 하지만 아무리 조심해도 지나치지 않죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00E92DF0
#. Notes = Stern, but slightly softer and understanding the choice may have put stress of the Player. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020345CB:020517C4
msgctxt "001CAD"
msgid "It took a lot of sacrifice to make the choice you made back at the Unifier. I know it wasn't easy, but the Settled Systems is forever grateful."
msgstr "유니파이어에서 당신이 내린 선택에는 많은 희생이 따랐습니다. 쉽지 않았다는 건 알지만, 개척 성계는 영원히 감사할 겁니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 004C9953
#. Notes = Professional.
#: 020345CB:020517C3
msgctxt "001CAE"
msgid "Whatever Terrans may be left out there are still a threat to the Settled System. No one is truly safe until they are all defeated."
msgstr "밖에 남아 있을 테란은 여전히 개척 성계의 위협입니다. 그들이 모두 패배하기 전까지는 누구도 진정으로 안전하지 않습니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 005E78C4
#. Notes = Professional.
#: 020345CB:020517C2
msgctxt "001CAF"
msgid "Remember, Terrans could still be out there. Keep your wits about you."
msgstr "잊지 마세요. 테란이 아직 밖에 있을 수 있습니다. 항상 정신 바짝 차리세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 007EC051
#. Notes = Professional, but grateful.
#: 020345CB:020517C1
msgctxt "001CB0"
msgid "With the Terrans defeated, the Settled Systems will be far safer. We have you to thank for that."
msgstr "테란이 패배했으니 개척 성계는 훨씬 안전해질 겁니다. 모두 당신 덕분입니다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 0054F8FC
#. Notes = Professional, but tries to comfort the player over Roxane's dislike of them.
#: 020345CB:020517C0
msgctxt "001CB1"
msgid "Don't let Roxane get to you. Remember, you made the right choice in stopping the Terrans once and for all."
msgstr "록산 말에 흔들리지 마세요. 테란을 영원히 막아낸 것은 옳은 선택이었다는 걸 기억하세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051713
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00E13E42
#. Notes = To Delta. Completely ignoring the Player as they leave. She's much more sweet and friendly to Delta. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020516DD:02051713
msgctxt "001CB2"
msgid "Be safe, Delta."
msgstr "조심해, 델타."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051712
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 0061125A
#. Notes = Annoyed at the player, but worried for Delta. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020516DD:02051712
msgctxt "001CB3"
msgid "Just, keep an eye on Delta. It's the least you could do."
msgstr "그냥 델타를 잘 지켜봐 줘. 그 정도는 해줄 수 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051711
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00ACF6A1
#. Notes = Annoyed. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020516DD:02051711
msgctxt "001CB4"
msgid "Find someone else to bother, alright?"
msgstr "다른 사람이나 귀찮게 해, 알겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051710
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00521DF5
#. Notes = Annoyed. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020516DD:02051710
msgctxt "001CB5"
msgid "Now, if you'll excuse me."
msgstr "그럼 이만 실례할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205170E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 005EC600
#. Notes = Sort of like a mom telling her kid to behave while she's not around. / Confident, Face: Confident
#: 020516DD:0205170E
msgctxt "001CB6"
msgid "Delta, you stay of out of trouble. Alright?"
msgstr "델타, 문제 일으키지 말고 있어. 알겠지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205170D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 007460E2
#. Notes = Friendly and kind to the Player. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020516DD:0205170D
msgctxt "001CB7"
msgid "Come visit me again, okay?"
msgstr "또 찾아와, 알겠지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205170C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 002D463C
#. Notes = Worried for the player. / Worried, Face: Worried
#: 020516DD:0205170C
msgctxt "001CB8"
msgid "Be safe out there, please."
msgstr "부디 밖에서 조심해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205170A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00668061
#. Notes = Casual with a hint of nervousness. / Worried, Face: Worried
#: 020516DD:0205170A
msgctxt "001CB9"
msgid "Keep an eye on Delta for me, would you?"
msgstr "나 대신 델타를 잘 지켜봐 줄래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051709
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00DDB6DE
#. Notes = Casual. / Concentrating, Face: Concentrating
#: 020516DD:02051709
msgctxt "001CBA"
msgid "We can talk more later."
msgstr "자세한 얘기는 나중에 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051708
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00F79B93
#. Notes = Cracking a petty, sarcastic joke. / Irritated, Face: Irritated
#: 020516DD:02051708
msgctxt "001CBB"
msgid "Don't worry. I can't go anywhere."
msgstr "걱정 마. 난 어디에도 못 가니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051706
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00A69639
#. Notes = Sad, regretful, and emotionally exhausted. / Depressed, Face: Depressed
#: 020516DD:02051706
msgctxt "001CBC"
msgid "Right... Let's go."
msgstr "그래... 가자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051705
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00DE3EAE
#. Notes = Sad, regretful, and emotionally exhausted. / Depressed, Face: Depressed
#: 020516DD:02051705
msgctxt "001CBD"
msgid "Can we keep moving now?"
msgstr "이제 계속 움직여도 될까?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051703
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 002EC110
#. Notes = Serious, but also anxious in the facility. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020516DD:02051703
msgctxt "001CBE"
msgid "We can talk more once we're out of here."
msgstr "여기서 나가면 더 얘기하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051702
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00B54480
#. Notes = Serious, but also anxious in the facility. / Defiant, Face: Defiant
#: 020516DD:02051702
msgctxt "001CBF"
msgid "We should keep moving."
msgstr "계속 움직여야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051700
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00F15FC3
#. Notes = Professional. / Stern, Face: Stern
#: 020516DD:02051700
msgctxt "001CC0"
msgid "You know where to find us."
msgstr "우리가 어디 있는지는 알잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516FF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00048F57
#. Notes = Professional. / Stern, Face: Stern
#: 020516DD:020516FF
msgctxt "001CC1"
msgid "Til' next time."
msgstr "다음에 보자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516FD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 005661BE
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020516DD:020516FD
msgctxt "001CC2"
msgid "Hope to see you again."
msgstr "또 보길 바라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516FC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 001E6F50
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly, Face: Friendly
#: 020516DD:020516FC
msgctxt "001CC3"
msgid "We'll be here if you need anything."
msgstr "필요한 게 있으면 우린 여기 있을게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516FA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00374A34
#. Notes = Professional. / Neutral
#: 020516DD:020516FA
msgctxt "001CC4"
msgid "Be safe out there."
msgstr "밖에서 조심해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00F80B86
#. Notes = Professional. / Neutral
#: 020516DD:020516F9
msgctxt "001CC5"
msgid "We'll speak another time."
msgstr "얘기는 다음에 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B3A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00632D50, 00BC48E1, 00BB8476
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, Petty and angry. / SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0203B358/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL02:0203B3A7
msgctxt "001CC6"
msgid "Besides, they need to pay for what they've done, and wrecking their flagship manufacturing facility is a good start."
msgstr "게다가 그들은 자신들이 한 일의 대가를 치러야 해. 그들의 주력 제조 시설을 박살 내는 건 좋은 시작이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0203B392
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00375762, 0080CA19, 00EFE566
#. Notes = Trying to explain to the best of her ability, but still quiet nervous in the facility and overwhelmed by the dangerous situation. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry, / to Player Default
#: 0203B35A/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL01:0203B392
msgctxt "001CC7"
msgid "They wanted to use my designs to make their unstoppable killing machines, well... more unstoppable. And who better to coerce into doing that than the only person who figured out how."
msgstr "그들은 내 설계를 이용해서 멈출 수 없는 살인 기계를, 뭐랄까... 더 멈출 수 없게 만들려고 했어. 그리고 그 방법을 알아낸 유일한 사람보다 협박하기 좋은 대상이 또 있겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205179F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00702657
#. Notes = Back to addressing the player. Annoyed at them and hoping the Player will leave her alone. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 02051797/00000/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE:0205179F
msgctxt "001CC8"
msgid "Now, if you don't mind, I have some additional research to attend to."
msgstr "이제 괜찮다면, 난 추가 연구를 좀 처리해야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 000BA634
#. Notes = Kinder tone as she is addressing Delta and not the player. / Amused / to Delta, Face: Amused
#: 02051798/00000/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE:020517A5
msgctxt "001CC9"
msgid "Your EMP abilities should work far better now, Delta. Use them well."
msgstr "이제 네 EMP 능력이 훨씬 더 잘 작동할 거야, 델타. 잘 써."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00870E19
#. Notes = Oddly gentle and soft. / Amused / to Delta, Face: Amused
#: 02051799/00000/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE02_BADSIDE:020517A1
msgctxt "001CCA"
msgid "There you are."
msgstr "거기 있었군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0068B5F6, 007A5685
#. Notes = Annoyed at the player and a bit upset with herself she's helping the player. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Quickly justifies to herself the upgrade is to help Delta. Kinder about Delta, tone goes back to venom when telling player 'Not you' / Irritated / to Player Default
#: 0205179A/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE:020517A7
msgctxt "001CCB"
msgid "Fine. But this is for Delta. Not you. "
msgstr "좋아. 하지만 이건 델타를 위한 거야. 네가 아니라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0068B5F6, 007A5685
#. Notes = Annoyed at the player and a bit upset with herself she's helping the player. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Quickly justifies to herself the upgrade is to help Delta. Kinder about Delta, tone goes back to venom when telling player 'Not you' / Irritated / to Player Default
#: 0205179A/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE:020517A7
msgctxt "001CCC"
msgid "Part of me hoped you'd forget about the upgrade..."
msgstr "네가 격상 얘기를 잊어버리길 바란 마음도 좀 있었는데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0010CC4D, 008E7B64
#. Notes = Annoyed at the Player. Bit snappy. Emphasis 'so' / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default
#: 0205179A/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE:020517A6
msgctxt "001CCD"
msgid "If you're not going to take this seriously, then don't bother me."
msgstr "진지하게 할 생각이 없다면 날 귀찮게 하지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 0010CC4D, 008E7B64
#. Notes = Annoyed at the Player. Bit snappy. Emphasis 'so' / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Annoyed. / Irritated / to Player Default
#: 0205179A/00030/SFTER_ROX_UPGRADE_BADSIDE:020517A6
msgctxt "001CCE"
msgid "Right. Cause I can do so much while they're not here."
msgstr "그래. 그들이 여기 없으면 내가 할 수 있는 게 참 많겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL09
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 009888F7
#. Notes = Slightly worried about the mysterious object the Terrans spoke about, but frustrated she never learned what it was. / Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0205179C/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL09:020517A3
msgctxt "001CCF"
msgid "The Terrans spoke of it. But I never learned what it was. Sounds like it could be some sort of networking system, or something? I can't imagine it's anything good."
msgstr "테란들이 그 이야기를 했어. 하지만 그게 뭔지는 끝내 알지 못했지. 일종의 네트워크 시스템 같은 걸 수도 있겠는데? 좋은 것일 리는 없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_TL09
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A8DC56
#: 0205179D/00030/SFTER_ROX_TL09:020517A4
msgctxt "001CD0"
msgid "Do you know anything about something called a hive-link?"
msgstr "하이브-링크라는 것에 대해 아는 게 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045708
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 0014B539
#. Notes = / to CivilianShip01, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02045704/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01:02045708
msgctxt "001CD1"
msgid "I appreciate it."
msgstr "고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204570B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip01
#. SoundFileID = 006BB8CC
#. Notes = / to CivilianShip, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02045705/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01:0204570B
msgctxt "001CD2"
msgid "I'll be sure to avoid the area. When I land, I'll see if I can get someone to help you out."
msgstr "그 지역은 꼭 피할게. 착륙하면 누군가 널 도와줄 사람을 구해볼게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204570A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip
#. SoundFileID = 00E95A65
#. Notes = / to CivilianShip01, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02045706/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01:0204570A
msgctxt "001CD3"
msgid "Yeah, I have no idea why. There's some weird signal coming from there that's got them riled up."
msgstr "그래, 왜인지는 전혀 모르겠어. 거기서 이상한 신호가 나오는데, 그게 놈들을 잔뜩 흥분시킨 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045709
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = CivilianShip01
#. SoundFileID = 00C2BA00
#. Notes = / to CivilianShip01, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 02045707/00000/SFTER_MS01_0095_RandomEncounter01:02045709
msgctxt "001CD4"
msgid "I'm sorry, I don't have any parts to spare. You said they attacked you around Niira?"
msgstr "미안하지만 나눠줄 부품이 없어. 니라 근처에서 공격받았다고 했지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204577D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 009A6EC2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204571D:0204577D
msgctxt "001CD9"
msgid "War, automated."
msgstr "자동화된 전쟁이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204577C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00172340
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0204571D:0204577C
msgctxt "001CDA"
msgid "Assembly line. Build, package, and get you murderous robot by Christmas."
msgstr "조립 라인. 만들고, 포장하고, 크리스마스까지 살인 로봇을 받아 보세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204577B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00943408
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571D:0204577B
msgctxt "001CDB"
msgid "Factories like this show the soullessness of war."
msgstr "이런 공장은 전쟁이 얼마나 영혼 없는 일인지 보여줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204577A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 003DEAB8
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571D:0204577A
msgctxt "001CDC"
msgid "Assembly line's been put to a halt. Let's hope it stays that way."
msgstr "조립 라인이 멈췄군. 계속 이대로였으면 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045764
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 005391EE
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204571E:02045764
msgctxt "001CDD"
msgid "These bots have seen better days."
msgstr "이 로봇들도 한때는 멀쩡했겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045763
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A3C216
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0204571E:02045763
msgctxt "001CDE"
msgid "Lot of broken bots. They must've seen some serious action."
msgstr "망가진 로봇이 많군. 꽤 격렬한 전투를 겪었나 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045762
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00B973B0
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571E:02045762
msgctxt "001CDF"
msgid "It's terrifying to think every machine we kill can just be repaired again."
msgstr "우리가 쓰러뜨린 기계마다 다시 수리될 수 있다고 생각하면 소름 끼쳐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045761
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00D6AE5F
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571E:02045761
msgctxt "001CE0"
msgid "This must be the med bay. Guess robots need patching too."
msgstr "여기가 의무실인가 봐. 로봇도 수리가 필요한 모양이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204576E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00CDD67B
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204571F:0204576E
msgctxt "001CE1"
msgid "They can build as many of these machines as they like. We will destroy them all."
msgstr "놈들이 이런 기계를 얼마든지 만들어도 상관없다. 우리가 전부 파괴할 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204576D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00517566
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0204571F:0204576D
msgctxt "001CE2"
msgid "Robots. Mass produced and ready to slaughter."
msgstr "로봇들. 대량 생산되어 학살 준비까지 끝났군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204576C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0001CDC1
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571F:0204576C
msgctxt "001CE3"
msgid "The fact the Terrans can produce and deploy these robots so quickly is frightening."
msgstr "테란이 이 로봇들을 이렇게 빠르게 생산하고 투입할 수 있다는 사실이 두렵군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204576B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00F10A5A
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204571F:0204576B
msgctxt "001CE4"
msgid "Deployment bay. These things look ready to go too."
msgstr "배치 구역이군. 이것들도 당장 나갈 준비가 된 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204575F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00DC03D4
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045720:0204575F
msgctxt "001CE5"
msgid "This is a strange room. The robots must be held here for storage."
msgstr "이상한 방이군. 로봇들을 보관하려고 여기에 붙잡아 두는 모양이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204575E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00B39375
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045720:0204575E
msgctxt "001CE6"
msgid "Neat. The robots in those pods are being hung like bats."
msgstr "멋지네. 저 포드 안의 로봇들이 박쥐처럼 매달려 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204575D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00FC4171
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045720:0204575D
msgctxt "001CE7"
msgid "Hm... the robots here seem to be in a state of suspended animation."
msgstr "흠... 여기 로봇들은 가사 상태에 있는 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204575C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00BC3A80
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045720:0204575C
msgctxt "001CE8"
msgid "That's a lot of firepower sleeping overhead."
msgstr "머리 위에서 엄청난 화력이 잠들어 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457AB
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 006E0669
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045721:020457AB
msgctxt "001CE9"
msgid "These robots look like they're about to be reassigned."
msgstr "이 로봇들은 곧 재배치될 것처럼 보이는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00408B1C
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045721:020457AA
msgctxt "001CEA"
msgid "Conditioning bay. Reassignments must happen here."
msgstr "조정 구역. 재배치는 여기서 이루어지는 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00AB48FE
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045721:020457A9
msgctxt "001CEB"
msgid "This must be where they transfer robots from ship to ship."
msgstr "여기가 로봇을 함선에서 다른 함선으로 옮기는 곳인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00E2E050
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045721:020457A8
msgctxt "001CEC"
msgid "Seems this is where units transfer to other ships."
msgstr "유닛들이 다른 함선으로 이동하는 곳인 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045755
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0036851B
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045722:02045755
msgctxt "001CED"
msgid "I'm surprised the Terrans eat."
msgstr "테란도 먹는다는 게 놀랍군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045754
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0033A633
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045722:02045754
msgctxt "001CEE"
msgid "Anyone fancy a bite to eat?"
msgstr "뭐 좀 먹고 싶은 사람?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045753
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 005FDE0F
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045722:02045753
msgctxt "001CEF"
msgid "Cafeteria. The smell is certainly pungent."
msgstr "식당이군. 냄새가 확실히 지독해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045752
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 004D4B64
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045722:02045752
msgctxt "001CF0"
msgid "Cafeteria. You sometimes forget these bastards are human."
msgstr "식당이군. 가끔은 이 자식들도 인간이라는 걸 잊게 된다니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045788
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00AFDE8F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045723:02045788
msgctxt "001CF1"
msgid "Military style quarters. Not surprising."
msgstr "군대식 숙소군. 놀랍지도 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045787
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E5C5C7
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045723:02045787
msgctxt "001CF2"
msgid "I rate the accommodations here two stars. Small beds, and everyone's shooting at you."
msgstr "여기 숙소는 별 두 개 주겠어. 침대는 작고, 모두가 널 향해 총을 쏘거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045786
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 004B70B6
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045723:02045786
msgctxt "001CF3"
msgid "Tight quarters, double-stacked. They certainly sleep like machines."
msgstr "비좁은 숙소에 2단 침상이라. 정말 기계처럼 자는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045785
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 003FE455
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045723:02045785
msgctxt "001CF4"
msgid "Crew quarters. Not exactly cozy."
msgstr "승무원 숙소군. 아늑하진 않네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204578D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 003DEC41
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045724:0204578D
msgctxt "001CF5"
msgid "Terran weaponry. Well made, too."
msgstr "테란 무기군. 꽤 잘 만들기도 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204578C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0086E6D6
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045724:0204578C
msgctxt "001CF6"
msgid "Nice of the Terrans to give us a spot to reload."
msgstr "테란이 재장전할 자리를 마련해 주다니 친절하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204578B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00BA16A3
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045724:0204578B
msgctxt "001CF7"
msgid "Tidy setup. There's enough firepower here to hold a corridor, or lose one."
msgstr "깔끔한 배치군. 여기 화력이면 복도를 지킬 수도 있고, 잃을 수도 있겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204578A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00AD3218
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045724:0204578A
msgctxt "001CF8"
msgid "This is the armory. Feel free to gear up."
msgstr "여긴 무기고야. 마음껏 장비를 챙겨."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045773
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 000E43A1
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045725:02045773
msgctxt "001CF9"
msgid "That is the ship generator."
msgstr "저게 함선 발전기야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045772
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F305BD
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045725:02045772
msgctxt "001CFA"
msgid "Generator, up ahead. And it's a big boy."
msgstr "앞쪽에 발전기야. 덩치가 엄청 큰데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045771
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0035AE75
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045725:02045771
msgctxt "001CFB"
msgid "This must be the ship generator."
msgstr "이게 함선 발전기인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045770
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00473B98
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045725:02045770
msgctxt "001CFC"
msgid "That's the generator. Keep a watch out for Terrans."
msgstr "저게 발전기야. 테란을 경계해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 007A150C
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045726:020457A1
msgctxt "001CFD"
msgid "Engine room. I'm not an engineer, but these are strange designs."
msgstr "엔진실이군. 난 엔지니어는 아니지만, 설계가 이상해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F86791
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045726:020457A0
msgctxt "001CFE"
msgid "It's like looking at an engine from an alternate universe. I know humans made this, but not any humans I know."
msgstr "다른 우주의 엔진을 보는 것 같아. 인간이 만들었다는 건 알겠지만, 내가 아는 인간들은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204579F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00DD9711
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045726:0204579F
msgctxt "001CFF"
msgid "This must be what powers the ship."
msgstr "이게 함선에 동력을 공급하는 장치인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204579E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009665D6
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045726:0204579E
msgctxt "001D00"
msgid "Engine room. Looks vaguely alien."
msgstr "엔진실이군. 어딘가 외계 기술 같아 보여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204575A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00B57AD2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045729:0204575A
msgctxt "001D01"
msgid "A crude weapon of destruction, but one to be feared."
msgstr "조잡한 파괴 무기지만, 두려워할 만한 물건이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045759
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0046B4B7
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045729:02045759
msgctxt "001D02"
msgid "Decommissioned or not, that's still a missile ready to go vertical."
msgstr "퇴역했든 아니든, 저건 아직 수직 발사 준비가 된 미사일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045758
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00470F76
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045729:02045758
msgctxt "001D03"
msgid "I know it's decommissioned, but the sheer destructive force of it gives me shivers."
msgstr "퇴역 처리된 건 알지만, 그 순수한 파괴력만 생각해도 몸서리쳐져."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045757
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0061969D
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045729:02045757
msgctxt "001D04"
msgid "That's one big warhead, and the whole place is built to keep it breathing."
msgstr "정말 거대한 탄두군. 이곳 전체가 저걸 계속 살아 있게 하려고 지어진 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051866
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00B0D0CC
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045727:02051866
msgctxt "001D05"
msgid "I think it is safe to say the scientists here are the mad kind."
msgstr "여기 과학자들은 미친 부류였다고 봐도 되겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051865
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00ADD327
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045727:02051865
msgctxt "001D06"
msgid "Holy Dr. Moreau! This doesn't look ethical."
msgstr "이런, 닥터 모로 맙소사! 이건 윤리적으로 보이지 않는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051864
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00F42209
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045727:02051864
msgctxt "001D07"
msgid "I shudder to think of what kind of experiments were performed here."
msgstr "여기서 어떤 실험이 벌어졌을지 생각만 해도 몸서리쳐져."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051863
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00CEA823
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045727:02051863
msgctxt "001D08"
msgid "Secret lab. Check. Wild, unhinged experiments. Double check."
msgstr "비밀 연구소. 확인. 거칠고 정신 나간 실험. 두 번 확인."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00E38280
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045728:020457B5
msgctxt "001D09"
msgid "This must be the ship's command center."
msgstr "여기가 함선 지휘 센터인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 004E3789
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045728:020457B4
msgctxt "001D0A"
msgid "This must be the brain of the whole ship."
msgstr "이곳이 함선 전체의 중추인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00B4D643
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045728:020457B3
msgctxt "001D0B"
msgid "This appears to be the command center."
msgstr "지휘 센터로 보이는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00287B11
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045728:020457B2
msgctxt "001D0C"
msgid "Looks like the command center."
msgstr "지휘 센터 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045797
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 001B20C2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572A:02045797
msgctxt "001D0D"
msgid "Missile silo. The scale of such weapons are always terrifying. "
msgstr "미사일 사일로. 이런 무기의 규모는 언제 봐도 무섭군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045796
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0024654D
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0204572A:02045796
msgctxt "001D0E"
msgid "That right there is a bonafide missile silo. So if you see a button, make sure before you press it."
msgstr "저건 진짜 미사일 사일로야. 그러니 버튼이 보이면 누르기 전에 꼭 확인해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045795
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00BCD231
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572A:02045795
msgctxt "001D0F"
msgid "The missile platform has its cranes still in place. Hopefully it's no longer active."
msgstr "미사일 플랫폼에는 아직 크레인이 그대로 있군. 더는 작동하지 않기를 바라야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045794
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 006830FF
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572A:02045794
msgctxt "001D10"
msgid "Missile platform. Hard to tell if the missile's long gone... or still waiting down there."
msgstr "미사일 플랫폼이군. 미사일이 오래전에 사라졌는지... 아니면 아직 저 아래에서 기다리는지 알기 어렵네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045750
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 002C041C
#. Notes = As opposed to Have Nots / Neutral
#: 0204572B:02045750
msgctxt "001D11"
msgid "It seems we've come to the \"Have's\" part of the station."
msgstr "우주정거장의 \"가진 자들\" 구역에 온 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204574F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00303B15
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572B:0204574F
msgctxt "001D12"
msgid " Seems we've entered the VIP area."
msgstr "VIP 구역에 들어온 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204574E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0093C280
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572B:0204574E
msgctxt "001D13"
msgid "Fancy location, especially compared to the rest of the station."
msgstr "근사한 곳이군. 우주정거장 나머지 구역과 비교하면 특히 더."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204574D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 006452FC
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572B:0204574D
msgctxt "001D14"
msgid "Nice digs."
msgstr "괜찮은 거처군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045792
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0024C7D9
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572C:02045792
msgctxt "001D15"
msgid "This must have been the bridge, once upon a time. I am surprised it has not been repurposed."
msgstr "한때는 이곳이 함교였던 모양이군. 다른 용도로 바뀌지 않았다는 게 놀라워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045791
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00CE569A
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572C:02045791
msgctxt "001D16"
msgid "Few things lonelier than an empty bridge."
msgstr "텅 빈 함교만큼 쓸쓸한 곳도 드물지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045790
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00BBA09C
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572C:02045790
msgctxt "001D17"
msgid "This must be the bridge. It's not surprising that it's empty, given the current use of this station."
msgstr "여기가 함교인가 봐. 이 우주정거장의 현재 용도를 생각하면 비어 있는 것도 놀랍지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204578F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00E9B33B
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572C:0204578F
msgctxt "001D18"
msgid "Guess the bridge's no longer in use."
msgstr "함교는 더 이상 쓰지 않는 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204574B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00A93D72
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572D:0204574B
msgctxt "001D19"
msgid "UC Security must make for a good target. It helps to visualize your enemy."
msgstr "식민지 연합 경비대는 좋은 표적이 되나 보군. 적을 시각화하는 데 도움이 되니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204574A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E8CAA3
#. Notes = Skeleton in firing range with UC sec armor / Neutral
#: 0204572D:0204574A
msgctxt "001D1A"
msgid "I gotta admit, that's a pretty creative use of a skeleton. Sick, but creative."
msgstr "인정해야겠네. 해골을 꽤 창의적으로 써먹었어. 역겹지만 창의적이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045749
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 007A5B92
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572D:02045749
msgctxt "001D1B"
msgid "This poor soldier. To have his body be made a mockery of is disgusting to say the least."
msgstr "불쌍한 군인. 시신이 조롱거리로 쓰이다니, 좋게 말해도 역겹군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045748
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00F5CAC9
#. Notes = Skeleton in firing range with UC sec armor, Face: Confident
#: 0204572D:02045748
msgctxt "001D1C"
msgid "That skeleton was UC security. You'd never see a Freestar soldier strung up like that."
msgstr "저 해골은 식민지 연합 경비대였어. 자유항성 군인이 저렇게 매달린 모습은 절대 못 볼 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045778
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0009C5CB
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045730:02045778
msgctxt "001D1D"
msgid "The Terrans certainly have an impressive operation. "
msgstr "테란의 운영 규모는 확실히 인상적이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045777
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F2FD51
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045730:02045777
msgctxt "001D1E"
msgid "The twisted part of me wants to see this baby in action."
msgstr "내 안의 뒤틀린 부분은 이 녀석이 실제로 움직이는 걸 보고 싶어 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045776
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 004D6790
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045730:02045776
msgctxt "001D1F"
msgid "The scale of machinery like this never ceases to amaze me."
msgstr "이런 기계의 규모는 볼 때마다 놀랍군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045775
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 003281A7
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045730:02045775
msgctxt "001D20"
msgid "This must be used planet-side to extract resources."
msgstr "이건 행성 표면에서 자원을 채굴하는 데 쓰이는 모양이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0055CA13
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572E:020457BA
msgctxt "001D21"
msgid "The scientists here were trespassers. The creatures merely defended their home."
msgstr "이곳의 과학자들은 침입자였어. 생물들은 그저 자신들의 보금자리를 지켰을 뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00177965
#. Notes = Somber, Face: Somber
#: 0204572E:020457B9
msgctxt "001D22"
msgid "Damn. Scientists are my tribe, so it always hurts to see scenes like this."
msgstr "젠장. 과학자들은 내 동족 같은 사람들이라, 이런 광경은 언제 봐도 마음이 아파."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00DEA506
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572E:020457B8
msgctxt "001D23"
msgid "Research on the fringes was always fraught with peril. You needed to be more soldier than scientist."
msgstr "변경 지역의 연구는 늘 위험으로 가득했어. 과학자라기보다 군인에 더 가까워야 했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00606929
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572E:020457B7
msgctxt "001D24"
msgid "It was either the starvation or the creatures that got them. Not sure what's worse."
msgstr "굶주림이었든 생물들이었든, 결국 그들을 덮쳤군. 어느 쪽이 더 나쁜지는 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A6
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 003FED2F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0204572F:020457A6
msgctxt "001D25"
msgid "It is hard not to be impressed by the scale and efficiency of their refineries."
msgstr "그들의 제련소 규모와 효율에는 감탄하지 않을 수 없군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A5
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 002467C3
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0204572F:020457A5
msgctxt "001D26"
msgid "The Venn diagram of warmonger, industrialist, and environmental hazard is a circle."
msgstr "전쟁광, 기업가, 환경 위험 요소의 벤 다이어그램은 원 하나로 끝나겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00C1C27B
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572F:020457A4
msgctxt "001D27"
msgid "Ugh, it's hard to breathe in here with all the smoke and runoff."
msgstr "으, 연기와 폐수 때문에 여기선 숨쉬기 힘들어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0064FC4A
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0204572F:020457A3
msgctxt "001D28"
msgid "Now I see how they made their armies so quickly."
msgstr "이제 그들이 어떻게 그렇게 빨리 군대를 만들어냈는지 알겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045741
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 006A6ED2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045732:02045741
msgctxt "001D29"
msgid "This would be a good opportunity to restock."
msgstr "재고를 보충하기 좋은 기회겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045740
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0003CE59
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045732:02045740
msgctxt "001D2A"
msgid "Wow, look at all this food! And me without my fork."
msgstr "와, 이 음식들 좀 봐! 하필 포크를 안 가져왔네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204573F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 008BB5C4
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045732:0204573F
msgctxt "001D2B"
msgid "Rest stops like these were perfect for travelers in need of supplies. It's a shame pirates took it over."
msgstr "이런 휴게소는 보급품이 필요한 여행자들에게 딱이었지. 해적들이 차지해 버려서 아쉽군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204573E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0076ED0D
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045732:0204573E
msgctxt "001D2C"
msgid "Don't mind doing a little grocery shopping."
msgstr "장 좀 보는 건 나쁘지 않지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204579C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 0083EAB2
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045734:0204579C
msgctxt "001D2D"
msgid "We cannot let these materials get to their destination."
msgstr "이 자재들이 목적지에 도착하게 둘 수는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204579B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0034DA5E
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045734:0204579B
msgctxt "001D2E"
msgid "The Terrans taking shipping to new heights. If only they chose express package delivery as their north star instead of you know, waging war."
msgstr "테란이 배송을 새로운 경지로 끌어올렸군. 전쟁 같은 걸 하지 말고 특급 택배를 지향점으로 삼았더라면 좋았을 텐데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204579A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00C4C354
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045734:0204579A
msgctxt "001D2F"
msgid "Let's make sure this cargo doesn't find its way back to the Terrans."
msgstr "이 화물이 테란에게 돌아가지 않게 하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045799
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 000F08CD
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045734:02045799
msgctxt "001D30"
msgid "Star Parcel could learn a thing or two from this shipping operation."
msgstr "스타 파셀도 이 배송 운영에서 한두 가지는 배울 수 있겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204573C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00ADEDAB
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045733:0204573C
msgctxt "001D31"
msgid "All this training did nothing for the previous owners, and it will do nothing for the pirates who own it now."
msgstr "이 모든 훈련은 이전 주인들에게도 소용없었고, 지금 이걸 차지한 해적들에게도 소용없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204573B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00AE8A10
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045733:0204573B
msgctxt "001D32"
msgid "I see a training course, I want to run it. Still got that watch, Dusty? Time it!"
msgstr "훈련 과정이 보이면 뛰어보고 싶어진단 말이지. 아직 그 시계 갖고 있어, 더스티? 시간 재!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204573A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 008499B1
#. Notes = Running through a training course for pirates, Face: Confident
#: 02045733:0204573A
msgctxt "001D33"
msgid "This training course was once run by the UC. The alterations are crude to say the least."
msgstr "이 훈련 과정은 한때 식민지 연합이 운영했어. 개조 상태는 좋게 말해도 조잡하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045739
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0065A6FE
#. Notes = Running through a training course for pirates, Face: Confident
#: 02045733:02045739
msgctxt "001D34"
msgid "Wonder what the high score is."
msgstr "최고 기록이 얼마일지 궁금하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00195FB6
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045731:020457B0
msgctxt "001D35"
msgid "Careful. Corridors this narrow leave little room for cover."
msgstr "조심해. 이렇게 좁은 복도에서는 엄폐할 공간이 별로 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0022911B
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045731:020457AF
msgctxt "001D36"
msgid "Narrow passages make me claustrophobic."
msgstr "좁은 통로는 폐소공포증이 올라오게 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 007CEF2D
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045731:020457AE
msgctxt "001D37"
msgid "This lane is designed for a firefight. Stay ready."
msgstr "이 통로는 총격전을 위해 설계됐어. 준비해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00E569DB
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045731:020457AD
msgctxt "001D38"
msgid "Tight corridor. Be ready for a fight."
msgstr "좁은 복도야. 싸울 준비해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457BF
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00E1C692
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045735:020457BF
msgctxt "001D39"
msgid "This thing is as dangerous at it is noisy."
msgstr "이건 시끄러운 만큼 위험하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0064DB81
#. Notes = loud drill machine / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045735:020457BE
msgctxt "001D3A"
msgid "\"What did you say, Barrett?\" Golly! I can't even hear myself think!"
msgstr "뭐라고 했어, 배럿? 세상에! 내 생각도 안 들릴 지경이야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00A0A088
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045735:020457BD
msgctxt "001D3B"
msgid "The noise from this drill is getting on my nerves. "
msgstr "이 드릴 소음이 신경을 긁는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00DD7734
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045735:020457BC
msgctxt "001D3C"
msgid "\"Drill, drill, drill,\" said the Terran."
msgstr "파고, 파고, 또 파라. 테란이 말했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045783
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00957318
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045737:02045783
msgctxt "001D3D"
msgid "That is a large drilling rig. We'll need to get inside if we want to shut it down."
msgstr "큰 시추 장비군. 멈추려면 안으로 들어가야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045782
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0099D600
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045737:02045782
msgctxt "001D3E"
msgid "That rig is MASSIVE. We might get pulled in by its gravity."
msgstr "저 장비는 엄청나게 거대해. 중력에 끌려 들어갈지도 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045781
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0046A3A3
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045737:02045781
msgctxt "001D3F"
msgid "The Terrans must be drilling for materials to build their armies."
msgstr "테란은 군대를 만들 자재를 얻으려고 시추 중인 게 틀림없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204577F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 006431EF
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045737:0204577F
msgctxt "001D41"
msgid "Looking at the size of that thing, we'll need to get inside to shut it down."
msgstr "저 크기를 보면, 멈추려면 안으로 들어가야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045769
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 007D7248
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02045736:02045769
msgctxt "001D42"
msgid "Having a mobile refinery like this has its advantages. Secrecy is paramount for the Terrans."
msgstr "이런 이동식 제련소가 있으면 장점이 있지. 테란에게는 은밀성이 무엇보다 중요하니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045768
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E287AB
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02045736:02045768
msgctxt "001D43"
msgid "These refining machines must be used to draw out the raw materials."
msgstr "이 정제 기계들은 원자재를 추출하는 데 쓰이는 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045767
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 009E4640
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045736:02045767
msgctxt "001D44"
msgid "It seems when they've exhausted a planet of its resources, they simply move on to the next one."
msgstr "행성의 자원을 다 써버리면 그냥 다음 행성으로 옮겨 가는 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045766
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 001299DD
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02045736:02045766
msgctxt "001D45"
msgid "When this baby is running, I'm sure it's one hell of a polluter."
msgstr "이 녀석이 가동되면 엄청난 오염원이 되겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051875
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00BCAC45
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02051844:02051875
msgctxt "001D46"
msgid "It is interesting to see outposts like this, making their own way on distant worlds."
msgstr "먼 세계에서 이렇게 나름의 삶을 꾸려가는 전초기지를 보는 건 흥미롭군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051874
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 005B81F0
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02051844:02051874
msgctxt "001D47"
msgid "This outpost seems to be thriving. I'm curious what challenges they've faced."
msgstr "이 전초기지는 번창하는 것 같군. 어떤 어려움을 겪었는지 궁금해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051873
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00F4159B
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051844:02051873
msgctxt "001D48"
msgid "This colony looks in good shape, relative to the last one."
msgstr "이 식민지는 지난 곳에 비하면 상태가 좋아 보여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051872
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00177127
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051844:02051872
msgctxt "001D49"
msgid "Place on the hill looks like a church. Granted I haven't been to one in a while..."
msgstr "언덕 위 건물은 교회처럼 보이네. 뭐, 내가 교회에 가본 지 좀 되긴 했지만..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205187A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00971C3A
#. Notes = Mass graves / Neutral
#: 02051846:0205187A
msgctxt "001D4A"
msgid "Unfortunately, death is a common story in places like this."
msgstr "안타깝지만 이런 곳에서는 죽음이 흔한 이야기지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051879
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00A3222D
#. Notes = Mass graves / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02051846:02051879
msgctxt "001D4B"
msgid "So many lives lost. It's heartbreaking."
msgstr "너무 많은 생명이 사라졌어. 가슴 아프군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051878
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 009E5269
#. Notes = Mass graves, Face: Confident
#: 02051846:02051878
msgctxt "001D4C"
msgid "It's evident whatever happened here, ended in tragedy."
msgstr "여기서 무슨 일이 있었든 비극으로 끝났다는 건 분명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051877
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00C7E8E4
#. Notes = Mass graves, Face: Confident
#: 02051846:02051877
msgctxt "001D4D"
msgid "A lot of graves, not a lot of people."
msgstr "무덤은 많은데, 사람은 별로 없군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051852
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 005C7006
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02051845:02051852
msgctxt "001D4E"
msgid "It seems this is where the parts are sorted and sent for construction."
msgstr "이곳에서 부품을 분류해 건설 현장으로 보내는 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051851
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 0045CE8A
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02051845:02051851
msgctxt "001D4F"
msgid "The Terrans are always trying to build a better mousetrap."
msgstr "테란은 늘 더 나은 쥐덫을 만들려고 하는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051850
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 0008D1E3
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051845:02051850
msgctxt "001D50"
msgid "It's a marvel to see how all this gets automated, until you realize what they're building."
msgstr "이 모든 것이 자동화되는 방식을 보면 경이롭지. 그들이 뭘 만들고 있는지 깨닫기 전까지는."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205184F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0012589A
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051845:0205184F
msgctxt "001D51"
msgid "This must be where the parts get sorted."
msgstr "여기가 부품을 분류하는 곳인가 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205187F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00FD9EF1
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02051847:0205187F
msgctxt "001D52"
msgid "The view is nice. Just try not to look down."
msgstr "경치는 좋군. 아래만 보지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205187E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00387214
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02051847:0205187E
msgctxt "001D53"
msgid "Wanted: Scientists. Location: Lab with a scenic view. Requirement: Cannot be afraid of heights."
msgstr "구함: 과학자. 위치: 경치 좋은 연구소. 조건: 고소공포증 없어야 함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205187D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 000AF1C0
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051847:0205187D
msgctxt "001D54"
msgid "Wonderful view."
msgstr "멋진 경치야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205187C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 002076B2
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051847:0205187C
msgctxt "001D55"
msgid "That's one hell of a view."
msgstr "전망 한번 끝내주는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045746
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00184D2F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 02051848:02045746
msgctxt "001D56"
msgid "There must be another way up."
msgstr "위로 올라갈 다른 길이 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045745
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00F5B0BF
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02051848:02045745
msgctxt "001D57"
msgid "Elevators out of commission. I'm more of a stairs person anyway."
msgstr "엘리베이터는 작동 중지네. 어차피 난 계단파야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045744
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00BBC9C5
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051848:02045744
msgctxt "001D58"
msgid "The elevator likely has no power. We'll need to find an alternate route."
msgstr "엘리베이터에 전력이 없는 것 같아. 다른 경로를 찾아야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045743
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 009A7072
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051848:02045743
msgctxt "001D59"
msgid "Looks like we need to find another way up."
msgstr "위로 올라갈 다른 길을 찾아야겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051857
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00C488A6
#. Notes = finding a bit of nature underneath an abandoned pit stop. / Neutral
#: 02051849:02051857
msgctxt "001D5A"
msgid "Well, this is a surprising discovery, and welcome."
msgstr "음, 뜻밖이지만 반가운 발견이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051856
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00E21D48
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 02051849:02051856
msgctxt "001D5B"
msgid "Will you look at that. Beautiful."
msgstr "저것 좀 봐. 아름답군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051855
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 003F4469
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051849:02051855
msgctxt "001D5C"
msgid "And even under all this industry, there are still secrets to be found."
msgstr "이 모든 산업 시설 아래에도 아직 발견할 비밀이 남아 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051854
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00DE84C3
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 02051849:02051854
msgctxt "001D5D"
msgid "Didn't expect to find a piece of nature all the way down here."
msgstr "이렇게 깊은 곳에서 자연의 한 조각을 찾을 줄은 몰랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051870
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 005DF223
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0205184B:02051870
msgctxt "001D5E"
msgid "This place is a scavenger's dream. But I am wary of such obvious gifts."
msgstr "이곳은 폐품업자의 꿈이군. 하지만 이렇게 노골적인 선물은 경계해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205186F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00B1727A
#. Notes = Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0205184B:0205186F
msgctxt "001D5F"
msgid "Well, this feels ominous."
msgstr "음, 불길한 느낌이 드는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205186E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 0021C1F3
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184B:0205186E
msgctxt "001D60"
msgid "Did you hear something? Safety's off."
msgstr "무슨 소리 들었어? 안전장치는 풀어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205186D
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00DB9F7F
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184B:0205186D
msgctxt "001D61"
msgid "Something feels off about this place."
msgstr "이곳은 뭔가 이상한 느낌이 들어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205186B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 007B694E
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0205184A:0205186B
msgctxt "001D62"
msgid "Ships must have used those platforms to get repairs."
msgstr "우주선들이 수리를 받으려고 저 플랫폼들을 이용했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205186A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00D6903F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0205184A:0205186A
msgctxt "001D63"
msgid "This looks like an old school ship stop. Imagine what it was like in its heyday!"
msgstr "구식 우주선 정비소처럼 보이네. 전성기 때는 어땠을지 상상해 봐!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051869
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 000355A6
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184A:02051869
msgctxt "001D64"
msgid "It's sad to see once bustling places of industry abandoned like this. "
msgstr "한때 북적였던 산업 현장이 이렇게 버려진 걸 보니 씁쓸하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051868
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00434405
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184A:02051868
msgctxt "001D65"
msgid "Back in the day this place must've been real busy. Come in, get some work, fly out."
msgstr "예전엔 여기가 정말 바빴겠지. 들어와서 정비 받고, 다시 날아가고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051861
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00425DB0
#. Notes = Owen Wilson type wow / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0205184D:02051861
msgctxt "001D66"
msgid "Wow..."
msgstr "와..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051860
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00283620
#. Notes = Owen Wilson type wow / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0205184D:02051860
msgctxt "001D67"
msgid "Wowee..."
msgstr "우와..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205185F
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 00E02050
#. Notes = Owen Wilson type wow / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0205184D:0205185F
msgctxt "001D68"
msgid "Wow..."
msgstr "와..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205185E
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00F2F586
#. Notes = Owen Wilson type wow / Awed, Face: Awed
#: 0205184D:0205185E
msgctxt "001D69"
msgid "Wow..."
msgstr "와..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205185C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFAndreja
#. SoundFileID = 00D92C5F
#. Notes = Neutral
#: 0205184C:0205185C
msgctxt "001D6A"
msgid "I feel as if something is waiting for us inside."
msgstr "안에서 뭔가 우리를 기다리고 있는 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205185B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMBarrett
#. SoundFileID = 00111387
#. Notes = Nervous, Face: Nervous
#: 0205184C:0205185B
msgctxt "001D6B"
msgid "You first. I've seen way too many horror movies to go diving into that."
msgstr "네가 먼저 가. 저런 데 뛰어들기엔 호러 영화를 너무 많이 봤어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205185A
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCFSarahMorgan
#. SoundFileID = 002ED0E1
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184C:0205185A
msgctxt "001D6C"
msgid "Once more into the breach."
msgstr "다시 한번 사지로 들어가는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051859
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. DialogCallType = PlayerDialogue
#. Speaker = NPCMSamCoe
#. SoundFileID = 00DCE757
#. Notes = Face: Confident
#: 0205184C:02051859
msgctxt "001D6D"
msgid "I think something just crawled up my spine."
msgstr "방금 등골을 타고 뭔가 기어오른 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02023A13
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 002FD370, 003EBA5A
#. Notes = Professional, however, she is trying to show a little empathy to what Roxane just said. / to Roxane, Professional, however, she is trying to show a little empathy to what Roxane just said. / Stern / to Roxane, Face: Stern
#: 02023922/01000/SFTER_MQ02B_1000B_VOID_ROX:02023A13
msgctxt "001D6E"
msgid "If they're out there posing an immediate threat in the field of combat, then we have to assume they're enemy combatants."
msgstr "저들이 전장에서 즉각적인 위협이 된다면, 우리는 적 전투원으로 간주해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C58F01
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516C4/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020516E7
msgctxt "001D6F"
msgid "We're entering a war and I was following orders."
msgstr "우린 전쟁에 들어서고 있었고, 난 명령을 따랐을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EEBF3F, 0067060F
#. Notes = Starts with a deep breath of exasperation. But as she explains what's at risk she becomes more panicked. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 걱정 마. 놈들이 뭘 던져도 난 버틸 수 있어., Worried and internally screaming. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020516C7/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020516E0
msgctxt "001D70"
msgid "Sorry. I'll be sweating."
msgstr "미안. 난 긴장할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EEBF3F, 0067060F
#. Notes = Starts with a deep breath of exasperation. But as she explains what's at risk she becomes more panicked. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading, Prompt: 걱정 마. 놈들이 뭘 던져도 난 버틸 수 있어., Worried and internally screaming. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020516C7/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:020516E0
msgctxt "001D71"
msgid "Let's hope so. Just remember, if not, they'll kill you and Delta, and I'll be stuck building crazy robots for the rest of my life."
msgstr "그러길 바라자. 안 그러면 그들이 너와 델타를 죽이고, 난 평생 미친 로봇이나 만들며 갇혀 지내게 된다는 걸 기억해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051714
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0000217F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516C8/00700/SFTER_MQ02B_0700_ROX:02051714
msgctxt "001D72"
msgid "Don't sweat. I can take anything they throw at me."
msgstr "걱정 마. 놈들이 뭘 던져도 난 버틸 수 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003E8979
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516C6/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020516E4
msgctxt "001D73"
msgid "We can't always plan for every possible outcome. You did what you thought was best to survive. "
msgstr "모든 가능한 결과를 늘 계획할 수는 없어. 넌 살아남기 위해 최선이라고 생각한 일을 한 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00289BA2
#. Notes = Annoyed the Player just does what they're told without questioning it. But still exhausted. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated, Prompt: 우린 전쟁에 들어서고 있었고, 난 명령을 따랐을 뿐이야.
#: 020516C3/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020516F0
msgctxt "001D74"
msgid "Right. Just following orders without knowing the specifics. I forgot that's how it works."
msgstr "그래. 자세한 내용도 모르고 그냥 명령을 따른 거지. 원래 그런 식으로 돌아간다는 걸 깜빡했네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005AB2D0
#. Notes = Emotionally exhausted. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 격상은 나중에 해도 돼. 넌 방금 엄청난 스트레스를 겪었어.
#: 020516C9/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020516F5
msgctxt "001D75"
msgid "*Sigh* I know..."
msgstr "*한숨* 알아..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B2EED0
#. Notes = Sad and regretful that the blood of a innocent person is on her hands. / Sad / to Player Default, Face: Sad, Prompt: 모든 가능한 결과를 늘 계획할 수는 없어. 넌 살아남기 위해 최선이라고 생각한 일을 한 거야.
#: 020516C5/00960/SFTER_MQ02B_0960_ROX:020516E2
msgctxt "001D76"
msgid "If I had known, I never would have wanted this. I could have found another way... I would of..."
msgstr "알았더라면 이런 건 절대 원하지 않았을 거야. 다른 방법을 찾을 수 있었을 텐데... 그랬을 텐데..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00AC5DBA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516CA/01200/SFTER_MQ02B_1200_ROX:020516E8
msgctxt "001D77"
msgid "Any upgrades can wait. You just went through a large amount of stress."
msgstr "격상은 나중에 해도 돼. 넌 방금 엄청난 스트레스를 겪었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516ED
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0056C386
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516D8/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020516ED
msgctxt "001D78"
msgid "You turned the flaws in their CPUs against them. Well done."
msgstr "그들의 CPU 결함을 역이용했군. 잘했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02B
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A7402B
#. Notes = Determined and a bit smug. / Concentrating / to Player Default, Face: Concentrating, Prompt: 그들의 CPU 결함을 역이용했군. 잘했어.
#: 020516CB/00500/SFTER_MQ02B_0500B_ROX_DELTA:020516F3
msgctxt "001D79"
msgid "I didn't just find flaws in the CPUs, but the overall system."
msgstr "CPU뿐만 아니라 전체 시스템에서도 결함을 찾아냈어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051818
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0061CA99
#. Notes = Drawing weapon. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051818
msgctxt "001D7A"
msgid "Then start explaining."
msgstr "그럼 설명 시작해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051817
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00875A11
#. Notes = Drawing weapon. / Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051817
msgctxt "001D7B"
msgid "Then I'll give you one chance to tell me who you are and what you're doing out here."
msgstr "그렇다면 네가 누구고 여기서 뭘 하는지 말할 기회를 한 번 주겠다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205183B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B349BC
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2D7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205183B
msgctxt "001D7C"
msgid "Who sent you? Report."
msgstr "누가 너희를 보냈나? 보고해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205183A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E3F9B8
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2D7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205183A
msgctxt "001D7D"
msgid "I didn't receive any word on reinforcements. Report."
msgstr "증원에 대한 말은 듣지 못했다. 보고해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051811
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EFA5F2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051811
msgctxt "001D7E"
msgid "I'm not one of your soldiers."
msgstr "난 네 병사가 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051810
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0007592F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051810
msgctxt "001D7F"
msgid "I'm not part of the Armada."
msgstr "난 테란 함대 소속이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003727C4, 009F5FCC, 007F2F51
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C8
msgctxt "001D80"
msgid "We'll get as many out as we can, thanks to you."
msgstr "네 덕분에 가능한 한 많은 사람을 빼낼 수 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003727C4, 009F5FCC, 007F2F51
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C8
msgctxt "001D81"
msgid "Once we set up a place, it's our top priority."
msgstr "자리를 잡는 대로 그게 최우선 과제가 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003727C4, 009F5FCC, 007F2F51
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C8
msgctxt "001D82"
msgid "Don't worry, we already plan to. "
msgstr "걱정 마, 이미 그럴 계획이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001EFACA, 00A5498B
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C7
msgctxt "001D83"
msgid "Once it proves effective, I've no doubt others will quickly follow."
msgstr "효과가 입증되면 다른 이들도 곧 따를 거라고 확신해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001EFACA, 00A5498B
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful, Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C7
msgctxt "001D84"
msgid "We plan on it. As soon we find a place to set up, we'll start organizing a way to safely reach others in the Armada and get them out."
msgstr "그럴 계획이야. 자리를 잡을 곳을 찾는 대로 테란 함대 안의 다른 이들에게 안전하게 연락해 빼낼 방법을 조직하기 시작할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0098CBD2, 00E1005F
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2E8/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0202C3BC
msgctxt "001D85"
msgid "Thank you for allowing us to go free. "
msgstr "우리를 자유롭게 보내줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003436B0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D4
msgctxt "001D86"
msgid "Don't let others suffer like you. Help get them out of the Armada."
msgstr "다른 이들이 너희처럼 고통받게 두지 마. 테란 함대에서 그들을 빼내는 걸 도와."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0065F282
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2E9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D3
msgctxt "001D87"
msgid "Take up the fight. If other Terrans feel trapped, you need to help them."
msgstr "싸움에 나서. 다른 테란들이 갇혀 있다고 느낀다면, 네가 그들을 도와야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0074565D, 00FAE21F
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CE
msgctxt "001D88"
msgid "I can't even tell you what a relief it was to speak to someone reasonable for a change."
msgstr "오랜만에 말이 통하는 사람과 이야기한 게 얼마나 안도됐는지 말로 다 못해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0074565D, 00FAE21F
#. Notes = Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CE
msgctxt "001D89"
msgid "Thank you for listening and allowing us to start over. "
msgstr "우리 말을 들어주고 새로 시작할 기회를 줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004F3A0C, 0058F820, 00FB441D
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CD
msgctxt "001D8A"
msgid "We'll definitely be working to make up for what the Terran Armada has done."
msgstr "테란 함대가 저지른 일을 만회하기 위해 반드시 노력할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004F3A0C, 0058F820, 00FB441D
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CD
msgctxt "001D8B"
msgid "Thanks for listening and allowing us this second chance. "
msgstr "우리 말을 들어주고 두 번째 기회를 줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 004F3A0C, 0058F820, 00FB441D
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EA/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CD
msgctxt "001D8C"
msgid "It's a relief that we ran into someone like you. I would guess anyone else may not be as... kind."
msgstr "너 같은 사람을 만나서 다행이야. 다른 사람이었다면 이렇게... 친절하진 않았을지도 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009C29C9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C5
msgctxt "001D8D"
msgid "It's good to know some people can still think for themselves."
msgstr "아직도 스스로 생각할 줄 아는 사람들이 있다니 다행이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 002506EB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C4
msgctxt "001D8E"
msgid "I'm glad you made it out."
msgstr "무사히 빠져나왔다니 다행이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00464D6A, 007FFF37, 00956C51
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CB
msgctxt "001D8F"
msgid "Thank you for taking the time to listen. It's something we haven't had for years now."
msgstr "시간을 내서 들어줘서 고마워. 우리는 몇 년 동안 그런 기회조차 없었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00464D6A, 007FFF37, 00956C51
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CB
msgctxt "001D90"
msgid "You've no idea the people we've watched lose their lives for speaking out against our leaders."
msgstr "우리 지도자들에게 반대하는 말을 했다는 이유로 죽어 간 사람들을 얼마나 많이 봐 왔는지 넌 모를 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CB
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00464D6A, 007FFF37, 00956C51
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CB
msgctxt "001D91"
msgid "Something none of us will forget anytime soon."
msgstr "우리 중 누구도 당분간은 잊지 못할 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002B93E3, 0029990B, 00FC6997
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CA
msgctxt "001D92"
msgid "Thank you for listening and sparing us. "
msgstr "우리 말을 들어 주고 살려 줘서 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002B93E3, 0029990B, 00FC6997
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CA
msgctxt "001D93"
msgid "That's why it was a relief to come across someone willing to talk for once."
msgstr "그래서 모처럼 대화하려는 사람을 만났을 때 안도했던 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 002B93E3, 0029990B, 00FC6997
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2EC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457CA
msgctxt "001D94"
msgid "Believe me, we've learned that the hard way."
msgstr "믿어 줘. 우리는 그걸 아주 힘들게 배웠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D7FCBA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2ED/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D7
msgctxt "001D95"
msgid "The Terran Armada will never be known for forgiveness."
msgstr "테란 함대는 절대 용서로 알려질 조직이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00E72E4F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2ED/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D6
msgctxt "001D96"
msgid "The Terran Armada doesn't have leniency for anything."
msgstr "테란 함대는 그 어떤 일에도 관용을 베풀지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C67193
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2EE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D1
msgctxt "001D97"
msgid "Terrans aren't exactly known for their subtlety. If we were still with the Armada, we would've attacked on sight. "
msgstr "테란은 섬세함과는 거리가 멀지. 우리가 아직 테란 함대 소속이었다면 보이는 즉시 공격했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0080C1C2, 003FB7BB
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2EE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D0
msgctxt "001D98"
msgid "Terrans don't negotiate when it comes to the Settled Systems."
msgstr "테란은 개척 성계 문제에 관해서는 협상하지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0080C1C2, 003FB7BB
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2EE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457D0
msgctxt "001D99"
msgid "I think we both know, if we were Terrans, we never would've allowed you to get this close to begin with. "
msgstr "우리 둘 다 알잖아. 우리가 테란이었다면 애초에 네가 이렇게 가까이 오게 두지도 않았을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AC22DC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C2
msgctxt "001D9A"
msgid "And I'm just supposed to take your word?"
msgstr "그럼 내가 네 말만 믿으면 된다는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020457C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D444C1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2EF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:020457C1
msgctxt "001D9B"
msgid "How do I know you're telling the truth?"
msgstr "네가 진실을 말하고 있다는 걸 내가 어떻게 알지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DB80E6, 00C52E98, 00D1D0D9
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Confused / to Player Default, Face: Confused
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571B
msgctxt "001D9C"
msgid "It's partly why I was so nervous when you approached."
msgstr "네가 다가왔을 때 내가 그렇게 긴장했던 것도 어느 정도는 그 때문이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DB80E6, 00C52E98, 00D1D0D9
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Confused / to Player Default, Face: Confused
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571B
msgctxt "001D9D"
msgid "When we saw your robot, I assumed it was a new Terran design and we'd been caught."
msgstr "네 로봇을 봤을 때, 새로운 테란 설계인 줄 알고 우리가 붙잡힌 줄 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DB80E6, 00C52E98, 00D1D0D9
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Confused / to Player Default, Face: Confused
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571B
msgctxt "001D9E"
msgid "Thank god, I thought we were dead. "
msgstr "맙소사, 우린 죽은 줄 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003ABE6D, 005B98C9, 0003ACBD
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571A
msgctxt "001D9F"
msgid "It was a relief to know you weren't one of them."
msgstr "네가 그들 중 하나가 아니라는 걸 알고 안심했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003ABE6D, 005B98C9, 0003ACBD
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571A
msgctxt "001DA0"
msgid "The Armada doesn't tolerate deserters. When we saw you approaching, I thought we were dead."
msgstr "테란 함대는 탈영병을 용납하지 않아. 네가 다가오는 걸 봤을 때 우린 죽은 줄 알았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204571A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003ABE6D, 005B98C9, 0003ACBD
#. Notes = Relieved / to Player Default, Face: Relieved, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2F0/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204571A
msgctxt "001DA1"
msgid "Thank you. That's really all we ask. "
msgstr "고마워. 우리가 바라는 건 정말 그게 전부야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045715
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00554763
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F1/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045715
msgctxt "001DA2"
msgid "Go and start over then. My fight is with the Terrans."
msgstr "그럼 가서 새로 시작해. 내 싸움은 테란을 상대로 한 거니까."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045714
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0020A2B2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F1/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045714
msgctxt "001DA3"
msgid "If you've turned your back on their cause, you're free to go."
msgstr "그들의 명분에 등을 돌렸다면, 가도 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045712
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BDE31C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F3/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045712
msgctxt "001DA4"
msgid "[Attack] I find that hard to believe."
msgstr "[공격] 믿기 힘든데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045711
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00946422
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F3/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045711
msgctxt "001DA5"
msgid "[Attack] I don't believe you."
msgstr "[공격] 난 네 말을 믿지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045336
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0043350A, 00990C80
#. Notes = About to tell the truth and hoping it works in their favor. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Concerned / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F4/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045336
msgctxt "001DA7"
msgid "We're deserters. We saw an opportunity to get away from the Armada and we took it."
msgstr "우린 탈영병이야. 테란 함대에서 벗어날 기회가 보여서 잡았을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045336
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0043350A, 00990C80
#. Notes = About to tell the truth and hoping it works in their favor. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned, Concerned / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F4/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045336
msgctxt "001DA8"
msgid "All right, all right. Not sure who programmed that bot... but they're right."
msgstr "알았어, 알았어. 누가 저 로봇을 프로그래밍했는지는 몰라도... 맞는 말이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045335
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00959B0A, 00B08BCA, 00820FD5
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F5/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045335
msgctxt "001DA9"
msgid "Hypothesis: These are Terrans, but specifically Terran deserters."
msgstr "가설: 이들은 테란이다. 정확히는 테란 탈영병이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045335
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00959B0A, 00B08BCA, 00820FD5
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F5/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045335
msgctxt "001DAA"
msgid "Counterpoint: Engaging in discourse not common Terran behavior."
msgstr "반론: 담화 참여는 일반적인 테란 행동이 아님."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045335
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00959B0A, 00B08BCA, 00820FD5
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F5/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045335
msgctxt "001DAB"
msgid "Vitals, voice analysis, and coordinates indicate Terran scouts."
msgstr "생체 신호, 음성 분석, 좌표가 테란 정찰대를 가리킴."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045334
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 006E4AA8
#. Notes = Ideally, the second half of this line can use the same audio as the original line. / Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F5/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045334
msgctxt "001DAC"
msgid "Accessing playback: Recommending immediate extermination."
msgstr "재생 기록 접근 중: 즉각적인 말살을 권고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204533C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00385C4E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204533C
msgctxt "001DAD"
msgid "[Delta] Delta, anything else to contribute?"
msgstr "[델타] 델타, 더 보탤 말 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204533B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D9DDCC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2F9/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204533B
msgctxt "001DAE"
msgid "[Delta] Delta, a little help here?"
msgstr "[델타] 델타, 여기서 좀 도와줄래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045339
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EB0D24
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045339
msgctxt "001DAF"
msgid "[Attack] I can't risk allowing Terrans to go free."
msgstr "[공격] 테란을 그냥 풀어 주는 위험은 감수할 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045338
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009FA0F4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FB/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045338
msgctxt "001DB0"
msgid "[Attack] Better safe than sorry."
msgstr "[공격] 후회하는 것보단 조심하는 게 낫지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045320
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DB72D, 00D788CB
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045320
msgctxt "001DB1"
msgid "I don't even know how you could mistake us for Terrans to begin with."
msgstr "애초에 어떻게 우리를 테란으로 착각할 수 있는지도 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045320
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DB72D, 00D788CB
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045320
msgctxt "001DB2"
msgid "I don't mean to dispute data, but the fact is they're not 100%. "
msgstr "데이터에 이의를 제기하려는 건 아니지만, 사실 100% 확실한 건 아니잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204531F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0058064B, 00CF499F
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204531F
msgctxt "001DB3"
msgid "Besides, it's the Terrans who use robot troops, right? And look who has the robot."
msgstr "게다가 로봇 부대를 쓰는 건 테란이잖아? 그런데 로봇을 데리고 있는 게 누구지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204531F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0058064B, 00CF499F
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2FC/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204531F
msgctxt "001DB4"
msgid "Yeah, but they're also not certain. Are you willing to take that chance?"
msgstr "그래, 하지만 확실한 것도 아니잖아. 그 위험을 감수할 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204532F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00437CCA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FD/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204532F
msgctxt "001DB5"
msgid "Delta's providing calculated observations."
msgstr "델타는 계산된 관찰 결과를 제시하고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204532E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FE1FE9
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FD/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204532E
msgctxt "001DB6"
msgid "Delta doesn't lie."
msgstr "델타는 거짓말하지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045329
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00218AB8
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C2FE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045329
msgctxt "001DB7"
msgid "You're the ones threatening to kill everyone here. How do you think I feel? "
msgstr "여기 있는 모두를 죽이겠다고 위협하는 건 너희야. 내가 어떤 기분일 것 같아?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045328
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E53EA8
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C2FE/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045328
msgctxt "001DB8"
msgid "The only thing here that isn't right is this bot recommending you kill us."
msgstr "여기서 잘못된 건 우리를 죽이라고 권고하는 이 로봇뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045326
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DE5A8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045326
msgctxt "001DB9"
msgid "You have to admit the circumstances here are suspicious."
msgstr "상황이 수상하다는 건 인정해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045325
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 009D9A21
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2FF/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045325
msgctxt "001DBA"
msgid "I trust Delta's analysis. Something here isn't right."
msgstr "난 델타의 분석을 믿어. 여기 뭔가 이상해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045317
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007F1CCE
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous
#: 0202C300/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045317
msgctxt "001DBB"
msgid "Are you kidding? I'm terrified. I'm just trying to keep it together since it seems like one wrong move and we're all dead."
msgstr "농담해? 나 겁에 질렸어. 한 번만 잘못 움직여도 모두 죽을 것 같으니까 겨우 버티고 있는 거라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045316
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004BF536, 0056DBCC
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0202C300/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045316
msgctxt "001DBC"
msgid "I just want to settle this amicably so we can go our separate ways."
msgstr "난 그냥 이 일을 원만하게 해결하고 각자 갈 길을 가고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045316
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004BF536, 0056DBCC
#. Notes = Nervous / to Player Default, Face: Nervous, Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 0202C300/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045316
msgctxt "001DBD"
msgid "It only seems that way because I don't want my colleagues here to panic."
msgstr "동료들이 당황하지 않게 하려다 보니 그렇게 보일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204532C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FEEA5E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C301/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204532C
msgctxt "001DBE"
msgid "I would've expected you to be more nervous considering the situation."
msgstr "상황을 생각하면 좀 더 긴장했을 줄 알았는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204532B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00223225
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C301/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204532B
msgctxt "001DBF"
msgid "You're handling this situation rather well after being threatened."
msgstr "협박을 받은 뒤치고는 이 상황을 꽤 잘 받아들이고 있군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045323
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AED2C3
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C302/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045323
msgctxt "001DC0"
msgid "Need I say more?"
msgstr "더 말해야 하나?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FriendlyDeltaSceneReentry02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045322
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00149CEE
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:02045322
msgctxt "001DC1"
msgid "Your bot's just proving my point."
msgstr "네 로봇이 내 말을 증명해 주고 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204531A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00C377BB
#. Notes = Neutral / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C303/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204531A
msgctxt "001DC2"
msgid "Human attempting redirection. Reiterating course of action: extermination."
msgstr "인간이 논점을 전환하려 시도 중. 행동 방침 재강조: 말살."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02045319
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 0043A762
#. Notes = Neutral / to ScoutLeader
#: 0202C303/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:02045319
msgctxt "001DC3"
msgid "Correct."
msgstr "정확함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204531D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006E401C
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C304/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204531D
msgctxt "001DC4"
msgid "You're the stranger here. Why should we trust you? We don't know what you're capable of. "
msgstr "여기서는 네가 낯선 사람이야. 우리가 왜 널 믿어야 하지? 네가 뭘 할 수 있는지 우린 몰라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204531C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BE56E9
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C304/02010/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204531C
msgctxt "001DC5"
msgid "You're the first person we've seen out here for a while. For all we know, you're the real threat. "
msgstr "여기서 한동안 본 사람은 네가 처음이야. 우리가 아는 한 진짜 위협은 너일 수도 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205171F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CFBC5E
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C31C/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0205171F
msgctxt "001DC6"
msgid "Okay, let's relax. No need to go to extremes here. Yes, we're Terrans, but let's focus on that willingness to talk."
msgstr "좋아, 진정하자. 여기서 극단적으로 갈 필요는 없어. 그래, 우린 테란이지만 대화할 의지가 있다는 데 집중하자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205171E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D5BD1F
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C31C/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0205171E
msgctxt "001DC7"
msgid "Whoa, extermination? All right. We may be Terrans, but we aren't looking for a fight here. You want to talk. Fine. Let's talk."
msgstr "잠깐, 말살이라고? 알았어. 우리가 테란이긴 해도 여기서 싸움을 바라진 않아. 대화하고 싶다고? 좋아. 얘기하자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009E0F91, 0090F19F, 0018F634
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5F
msgctxt "001DC8"
msgid "Recommended course of action based on data: extermination."
msgstr "데이터 기반 권장 행동 방침: 말살."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009E0F91, 0090F19F, 0018F634
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5F
msgctxt "001DC9"
msgid "Positive indicators: elevated vitals, coordinates. Demeanor."
msgstr "양성 지표: 상승한 생체 신호, 좌표. 태도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 009E0F91, 0090F19F, 0018F634
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5F
msgctxt "001DCA"
msgid "Conflicting data. Human behavior atypical: engaging in discourse, failure to initiate combat."
msgstr "상충 데이터. 인간 행동 비정형: 담화 참여, 전투 개시 실패."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00557DE3, 0021C58D, 004FCB3C
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5E
msgctxt "001DCB"
msgid "Calculated results recommend extermination."
msgstr "계산 결과 말살을 권고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00557DE3, 0021C58D, 004FCB3C
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5E
msgctxt "001DCC"
msgid "Counterpoint: Engaging in discourse atypical."
msgstr "반론: 담화 참여는 비정형적임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00557DE3, 0021C58D, 004FCB3C
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default
#: 0202C31D/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:0204FF5E
msgctxt "001DCD"
msgid "Analysis: Elevated vitals and coordinates indicate Terran human."
msgstr "분석: 상승한 생체 신호와 좌표가 테란 인간임을 나타냄."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00795A9A
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C338/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517D7
msgctxt "001DCE"
msgid "All right, enough, you've wore me down."
msgstr "알았어, 충분해. 네가 날 지치게 했어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006BEBC5
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C338/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517D6
msgctxt "001DCF"
msgid "All right, all right, enough."
msgstr "알았어, 알았어, 충분해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051719
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A88351
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C341/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051719
msgctxt "001DD0"
msgid "Or maybe you should be thankful that whatever info you got is obviously wrong."
msgstr "아니면 네가 얻은 정보가 명백히 틀렸다는 데 감사해야 할지도 모르지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051718
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006AD657
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C341/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051718
msgctxt "001DD1"
msgid "I don't know what to tell you. Maybe you've just got some bad intel."
msgstr "뭐라고 말해야 할지 모르겠군. 그냥 정보가 잘못됐을 수도 있잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051728
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007E2633
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C342/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051728
msgctxt "001DD2"
msgid "It's a bit suspicious that Terrans were reported in the area, and instead, I find you. "
msgstr "이 지역에 테란이 있다는 보고가 있었는데, 정작 찾은 게 너희라면 좀 수상하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051727
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00AD8765
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C342/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051727
msgctxt "001DD3"
msgid "Interesting coincidence that I came here to find Terrans and find you instead."
msgstr "테란을 찾으러 왔는데 대신 너희를 찾았다니 흥미로운 우연이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517E4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001527D9
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C343/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517E4
msgctxt "001DD4"
msgid "That makes two of us."
msgstr "나도 마찬가지야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517E3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007A2D0D
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C343/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517E3
msgctxt "001DD5"
msgid "I couldn't agree more."
msgstr "전적으로 동의해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517E1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007FF5AA
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C345/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517E1
msgctxt "001DD6"
msgid "I don't think you're listening to me."
msgstr "내 말을 안 듣고 있는 것 같은데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517E0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DA57DD
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C345/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517E0
msgctxt "001DD7"
msgid "You just can't drop it, can you?"
msgstr "그냥 넘어갈 수가 없나 보지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517F1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0074AC07
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C344/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517F1
msgctxt "001DD8"
msgid "[Attack] I've had it with this."
msgstr "[공격] 이제 질렸어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517F0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0071743F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C344/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517F0
msgctxt "001DD9"
msgid "[Attack] I'm done with this."
msgstr "[공격] 이 일은 여기까지야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B4CF3C
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C348/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517F7
msgctxt "001DDA"
msgid "Just admit you're Terrans, or I'll make this very unpleasant for everyone."
msgstr "테란이라고 인정해. 안 그러면 모두에게 아주 불쾌한 일을 겪게 해 주지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517F6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0061AC2A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C348/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517F6
msgctxt "001DDB"
msgid "If you don't admit you're Terrans, I'm happy to do this the very hard way."
msgstr "테란이라고 인정하지 않으면, 아주 힘든 방식으로 처리해도 난 좋아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF52
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005714F8
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34B/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF52
msgctxt "001DDC"
msgid "Haven't seen anyone around here but you, so I think we're good."
msgstr "여기 주변엔 너희 말고 아무도 못 봤으니 문제없을 것 같군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF51
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C10F96
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34B/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF51
msgctxt "001DDD"
msgid "That so? Sounds like you best be on your way then."
msgstr "그래? 그럼 슬슬 가는 게 좋겠네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF50
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00776254
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34B/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF50
msgctxt "001DDE"
msgid "Yeah, well, you won't find any Terrans here. "
msgstr "그래, 뭐, 여기서는 테란을 못 찾을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051722
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B0E2BB
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34F/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051722
msgctxt "001DDF"
msgid "What, you want me to cause a panic? I'm sorry I'm not living up to your expectations."
msgstr "뭐, 내가 공포라도 일으키길 바라? 기대에 못 미쳐서 미안하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051721
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D4EC97
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C34F/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051721
msgctxt "001DE0"
msgid "I'm processing it, okay? Why don't you back off?"
msgstr "나도 처리 중이야, 알겠어? 좀 물러서 주지 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF36
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 008AC935
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C358/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF36
msgctxt "001DE1"
msgid "I don't see how that's any of your business."
msgstr "그게 왜 네가 신경 쓸 일인지 모르겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF35
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B8BD08
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C358/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF35
msgctxt "001DE2"
msgid "I could ask you the same thing."
msgstr "그 말은 내가 너한테도 할 수 있겠는데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF61
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B1421F
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF61
msgctxt "001DE3"
msgid "Yeah? And who made you the expert?"
msgstr "그래? 누가 널 전문가로 만들었는데?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF4B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C98844
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C35B/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF4B
msgctxt "001DE4"
msgid "Nice attitude. Real friendly."
msgstr "태도 참 좋군. 정말 친절해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF4A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BFE97F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C35B/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF4A
msgctxt "001DE5"
msgid "Someone's a little grumpy today."
msgstr "오늘 좀 짜증이 난 모양이네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF55
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C1E04A
#. Notes = Rude, doesn't want to be bothered. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF55
msgctxt "001DE6"
msgid "Whatever you want, make it quick."
msgstr "뭘 원하든 빨리 말해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF54
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001E4F96
#. Notes = Rude, doesn't want to be bothered. / Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF54
msgctxt "001DE7"
msgid "Do I look like I want to talk?"
msgstr "내가 대화하고 싶은 사람처럼 보여?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF45
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FB5B57, 00EBB94C
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35C/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF45
msgctxt "001DE8"
msgid "Really? Is that what you're here bothering us for? "
msgstr "정말? 그것 때문에 여기 와서 우릴 귀찮게 하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF44
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0023827A
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0202C35C/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF44
msgctxt "001DE9"
msgid "Terrans? Us? Now that's a laugh."
msgstr "테란? 우리가? 웃기고 있네."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DA590F
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020517CC/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517EE
msgctxt "001DEA"
msgid "Confess to being Terrans. You want to trust me."
msgstr "테란이라고 자백해. 넌 날 믿고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517ED
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CBB9FE
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020517CC/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517ED
msgctxt "001DEB"
msgid "You know confessing to be Terrans will lift that weight you've been carrying."
msgstr "테란이라고 자백하면 네가 짊어진 그 무게가 덜어질 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517EC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003C01B4
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020517CC/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517EC
msgctxt "001DEC"
msgid "If you're Terrans, you know it's in your best interest to confess."
msgstr "너희가 테란이라면 자백하는 게 너희에게 최선이라는 걸 알잖아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C30E1B
#. Notes = Giving in. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020517CB/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517D1
msgctxt "001DED"
msgid "Hmm. For some reason, I'm inclined to believe you."
msgstr "흠. 왠지 네 말을 믿고 싶어지는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001701B2
#. Notes = Giving in. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020517CB/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517D0
msgctxt "001DEE"
msgid "I don't know why, but something tells me you're right."
msgstr "왜인지는 모르겠지만, 네 말이 맞다는 느낌이 들어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020517CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E517D8
#. Notes = Giving in. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020517CB/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020517CF
msgctxt "001DEF"
msgid "I -- Fine. Here's the story."
msgstr "내가 -- 좋아. 사실은 이래."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0049969D
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0204FF30/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF5C
msgctxt "001DF0"
msgid "Now why don't you move along? We're not in the mood for company."
msgstr "이제 그만 가 주지 그래? 우린 손님 받을 기분이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 008DBDD6
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0204FF30/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF5B
msgctxt "001DF1"
msgid "Now are we done here? "
msgstr "이제 끝난 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204FF5A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D72FE8
#. Notes = Irritated / to Player Default, Face: Irritated
#: 0204FF30/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0204FF5A
msgctxt "001DF2"
msgid "Now if you don't mind, we'd like to be left alone."
msgstr "괜찮다면 이제 우리끼리 있게 해 줘."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02A_VOIDPlayerQuestion
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516EA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 00B4F3E3
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516D3/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:020516EA
msgctxt "001E02"
msgid "Before that, why is a clandestine operation named after what sounds like a veteran support group?"
msgstr "그 전에, 비밀 작전 이름이 왜 퇴역 군인 지원 단체처럼 들리는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02VOIDPlayerQuestion_Answer
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 001536B9, 005BEF91
#. Notes = professional and explaining. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Professional. / Confident / to Player Default
#: 020516D2/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:020516E9
msgctxt "001E03"
msgid "But back to the conversation at hand: What happened on the Opulence?"
msgstr "하지만 하던 이야기로 돌아가서, 오퓰런스에서 무슨 일이 있었지?"

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MQ02VOIDPlayerQuestion_Answer
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Radha
#. SoundFileID = 001536B9, 005BEF91
#. Notes = professional and explaining. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Professional. / Confident / to Player Default
#: 020516D2/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:020516E9
msgctxt "001E04"
msgid "As you can imagine, being who we are, it is best to not arouse suspicion from the general public regarding our true nature. Because of this, the name of VOID is simply a front."
msgstr "상상할 수 있듯이, 우리 같은 존재가 우리의 본질을 일반 대중에게 의심받지 않는 것이 최선이다. 그래서 VOID라는 이름은 그저 위장일 뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516DE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 00A9F405
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516CE/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:020516DE
msgctxt "001E05"
msgid "Never thought I'd be working for big wigs like you."
msgstr "너희 같은 높으신 분들을 위해 일하게 될 줄은 몰랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = RyujinRep
#. SoundFileID = 004A0B7C
#. Notes = Professional, yet friendly. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly
#: 020516CC/00170/SFTER_MQ02A_0170_VOID:020516E5
msgctxt "001E06"
msgid "You know what they say: Never say never."
msgstr "사람들이 그러잖아. 절대라는 말은 하지 말라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516EF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 00C45757
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516D5/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516EF
msgctxt "001E07"
msgid "Get me a fully-loaded bloody mary."
msgstr "풀옵션 블러디 메리로 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 00CC23B4
#. Notes = Friendly and acting sorry. She knows the Player just failed to give her the right keyword. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 풀옵션 블러디 메리로 줘.
#: 020516D4/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516F7
msgctxt "001E08"
msgid "Sorry, friend, I can't make that right now."
msgstr "미안해, 친구. 지금은 그걸 만들 수 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516E6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 008C447D
#. Notes = Friendly and acting sorry. She knows the Player just failed to give her the right keyword. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 그렇게 특별한 건 아니야. 그냥 물이지.
#: 020516D6/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516E6
msgctxt "001E09"
msgid "I'm not sure I can get you that at the moment."
msgstr "지금은 그걸 구해 줄 수 있을지 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 00E93C19
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516D7/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516F4
msgctxt "001E0A"
msgid "It's not that special. Just some water."
msgstr "그렇게 특별한 건 아니야. 그냥 물이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 004288CB
#. Notes = Friendly and acting sorry. She knows the Player just failed to give her the right keyword. / Worried / to Player Default, Face: Worried, Prompt: 외계 버블티 하나 마시고 싶군.
#: 020516D9/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516EB
msgctxt "001E0B"
msgid "Sorry. We're all out of that."
msgstr "미안. 그건 다 떨어졌어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516EE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Valeria
#. SoundFileID = 00831AEC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516DA/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516EE
msgctxt "001E0C"
msgid "I could use a boba alien tea."
msgstr "외계 버블티 하나 마시고 싶군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516DF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0029A324
#. Notes = Friendly. Player just gave her the correct keyword to enter a secret backroom. / Friendly / to Player Default, Face: Friendly, Prompt: 보카티스 바쿠오스를 즐기기엔 환상적인 날이군.
#: 020516DB/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516DF
msgctxt "001E0D"
msgid "Indeed it is. Here. It's right this way. Follow me."
msgstr "맞습니다. 여기 있습니다. 이쪽입니다. 따라오세요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516F2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02A
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003DF5D0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 020516DC/00100/SFTER_MQ02A_0100_VALERIA:020516F2
msgctxt "001E0E"
msgid "It's a fantastic day for a vocatis vacuos."
msgstr "보카티스 바쿠오스를 즐기기엔 환상적인 날이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020516C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCDelta
#. SoundFileID = 00F413CB
#. Notes = A line that's played when the player tells Delta they don't want to talk anymore
#: 0200F9F8:020516C0
msgctxt "001E0F"
msgid "Logging facial language for further analysis..."
msgstr "추가 분석을 위해 안면 언어 기록 중..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02029B83
msgctxt "001E10"
msgid "Disregard alert. Testing communication connection."
msgstr "경보 무시. 통신 연결 테스트 중."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C91
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0082514D
#: 020AC746:02051C91
msgctxt "001E1F"
msgid "I have nothing more to say to you."
msgstr "너에게 더 할 말은 없다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C90
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00AB32F7
#: 020AC746:02051C90
msgctxt "001E20"
msgid "You will regret this mistake, you can be sure."
msgstr "이번 실수를 후회하게 될 것이다. 반드시."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C8F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCPercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00D1CD8E
#: 020AC746:02051C8F
msgctxt "001E21"
msgid "This will be resolved soon enough. I'm not worried."
msgstr "이 일은 곧 해결될 거다. 난 걱정하지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C8D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00676772
#. Notes = greeting to a member of the vanguard fleet
#: 02051C36:02051C8D
msgctxt "001E22"
msgid "Vanguard."
msgstr "뱅가드."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C8C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00F2A3E1
#: 02051C36:02051C8C
msgctxt "001E23"
msgid "Don't let me hold you up."
msgstr "내가 붙잡아 두진 않을게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C8B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 0039AD64
#: 02051C36:02051C8B
msgctxt "001E24"
msgid "Did you need something else?"
msgstr "또 필요한 게 있었나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C8A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 004538D6
#: 02051C36:02051C8A
msgctxt "001E25"
msgid "Let me know if you need anything."
msgstr "필요한 게 있으면 알려 줘."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C89
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 006E7065
#: 02051C36:02051C89
msgctxt "001E26"
msgid "Best we keep interactions to a minimum for now."
msgstr "지금은 접촉을 최소한으로 유지하는 게 좋겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C88
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 007743E7
#: 02051C36:02051C88
msgctxt "001E27"
msgid "You were a big help. Thanks again."
msgstr "큰 도움이 됐어. 다시 한 번 고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C86
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 001B3F34
#: 02051C36:02051C86
msgctxt "001E28"
msgid "If you'll excuse me."
msgstr "그럼 실례하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C85
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 00F14EE3
#: 02051C36:02051C85
msgctxt "001E29"
msgid "Time to get back to it."
msgstr "다시 일하러 갈 시간이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C84
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 0093FC28
#: 02051C36:02051C84
msgctxt "001E2A"
msgid "Make sure you've got everything."
msgstr "필요한 건 전부 챙겼는지 확인해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C82
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00E64AAE
#: 02051C36:02051C82
msgctxt "001E2B"
msgid "We do not need added complication."
msgstr "추가적인 복잡함은 필요 없다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C81
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00EE9209
#: 02051C36:02051C81
msgctxt "001E2C"
msgid "Oh, Percy... To think one's need for profit would outweigh moral duty."
msgstr "아, 퍼시... 이윤에 대한 욕구가 도덕적 의무보다 앞서다니."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C80
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00E741F4
#: 02051C36:02051C80
msgctxt "001E2D"
msgid "I will miss our conversations, but Percy knew the consequences. A waste of talent."
msgstr "우리의 대화가 그리울 테지만, 퍼시는 그 결과를 알고 있었다. 아까운 재능이었지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C7F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00EDD9CD
#: 02051C36:02051C7F
msgctxt "001E2E"
msgid "Ryujin assures us Percy was working alone. We can do nothing but take them at their word."
msgstr "류진은 퍼시가 단독으로 움직였다고 확언했다. 우리는 그들의 말을 믿는 수밖에 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C7E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRadhaDhawan
#. SoundFileID = 00961DDB
#: 02051C36:02051C7E
msgctxt "001E2F"
msgid "I do not paint Kenji with the same color Percy left us with. He is his own person and deserves to be treated as such."
msgstr "퍼시가 남긴 색으로 켄지를 칠하진 않겠다. 그는 독립된 사람이고, 그에 맞게 대우받아야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C7C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00D1E781
#: 02051C36:02051C7C
msgctxt "001E30"
msgid "Hell is going on here? I wasn't told about this."
msgstr "여기 대체 무슨 일이야? 난 이런 얘기 못 들었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C7B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 0064C0F1
#: 02051C36:02051C7B
msgctxt "001E31"
msgid "No wonder some of those Terrans slipped through our fingers. Need to be more careful who we let in here."
msgstr "테란 몇 명이 우리 손아귀에서 빠져나간 것도 당연하군. 여기에 누굴 들이는지 더 조심해야겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C7A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00AFCBEB
#: 02051C36:02051C7A
msgctxt "001E32"
msgid "'Course someone from Ryujin would try this... Never liked that one."
msgstr "류진 사람이 이런 짓을 할 줄 알았지... 처음부터 마음에 안 들었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C79
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00C7EF58
#: 02051C36:02051C79
msgctxt "001E33"
msgid "Letting that kid in wasn't my call. But orders are orders, and we still need to work with Ryujin."
msgstr "그 애를 들인 건 내 결정이 아니었어. 하지만 명령은 명령이고, 우린 여전히 류진과 협력해야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C78
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCTracyWarrens
#. SoundFileID = 00FFD45C
#: 02051C36:02051C78
msgctxt "001E34"
msgid "I don't care how sweet this Kenji guy talks, I'm keeping an eye on him. Don't want a repeat of what happened with Percy."
msgstr "이 켄지라는 자식이 얼마나 달콤하게 말하든 상관없어. 난 그를 감시할 거야. 퍼시 때 같은 일이 반복되는 건 원치 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00F53B3C
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 02051C33:0205D07E
msgctxt "001E35"
msgid "I'm good at what I do."
msgstr "난 내 일에 능숙해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 006EC888
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 02051C33:0205D07D
msgctxt "001E36"
msgid "Regretting your choices now?"
msgstr "이제 선택을 후회하나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C4F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00B5ABA4
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 02051C33:02051C4F
msgctxt "001E37"
msgid "You'll have to do better than that."
msgstr "그 정도로는 부족할 텐데."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C76
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 00167DC6
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C76
msgctxt "001E38"
msgid "What's wrong with you?"
msgstr "너 대체 왜 그래?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C75
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 002985B4
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C75
msgctxt "001E39"
msgid "I'm on your side!"
msgstr "난 네 편이야!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C74
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCMAgenetVoss
#. SoundFileID = 00A6C03B
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C74
msgctxt "001E3A"
msgid "Hey, watch it!"
msgstr "이봐, 조심해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C72
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 000909A9
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C72
msgctxt "001E3B"
msgid "Lucky shot."
msgstr "운 좋은 한 발이었군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C71
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00E7C791
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C71
msgctxt "001E3C"
msgid "I've survived worse."
msgstr "이보다 더한 일도 살아남았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C70
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00DD0888
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 02051C29:02051C70
msgctxt "001E3D"
msgid "You think you've got me?"
msgstr "날 잡았다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00AEF26E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204382D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0204389A
msgctxt "001E3E"
msgid "[Play Terran Slate] Just give this a listen."
msgstr "[테란 슬레이트 재생] 이걸 한번 들어 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0047D7CD, 00E21B2F, 000343F3
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 정도면 사람을 감옥에 넣기에 정말 충분한가?
#: 0204382A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438BD
msgctxt "001E3F"
msgid "Not a lot of people wanting to run cover for someone helping the Terrans. Not after what they've done."
msgstr "테란을 돕는 자를 감싸 주려는 사람은 많지 않아. 그들이 한 짓을 생각하면 더더욱."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0047D7CD, 00E21B2F, 000343F3
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 정도면 사람을 감옥에 넣기에 정말 충분한가?
#: 0204382A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438BD
msgctxt "001E40"
msgid "If it's definitive, whoever's behind it isn't going to see themselves with too many friends willing to back them."
msgstr "결정적인 증거라면, 그 배후에 있는 자는 자신을 지지해 줄 친구를 많이 찾지 못할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0047D7CD, 00E21B2F, 000343F3
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 이 정도면 사람을 감옥에 넣기에 정말 충분한가?
#: 0204382A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438BD
msgctxt "001E41"
msgid "Let's just say the ones who want this settled don't take kindly to war crimes."
msgstr "이 일을 해결하려는 자들은 전쟁 범죄를 좋게 보지 않는다고만 해 두지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020AC58C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 0086C930
#. Notes = Defiant / to TracyWarren, Face: Defiant
#: 02043837/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:020AC58C
msgctxt "001E42"
msgid "Tell her to drop this or I'll be forced to report this overreach."
msgstr "이 일에서 손 떼라고 전해. 안 그러면 이 월권을 보고할 수밖에 없다고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204389D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004C52E6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0204384C/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0204389D
msgctxt "001E43"
msgid "Here's the source of our leak."
msgstr "우리 쪽 누출의 근원을 찾았군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043879
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00662704
#: 02043847/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:02043879
msgctxt "001E44"
msgid "But helping our operations to make sure just enough Terrans survived for his people to make a profit from the influx of new tech on the backend?"
msgstr "하지만 우리 작전을 도와 테란이 딱 충분히 살아남게 하고, 그 뒤 유입될 신기술로 자기 사람들에게 이익을 안겨 주려 했다면?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0056D2C3, 008F0C11
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: It looks like Percy Kanu's been playing both sides.
#: 0204384B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438A3
msgctxt "001E45"
msgid "I'd say it's worth a look."
msgstr "조사해 볼 가치는 있다고 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020438A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0056D2C3, 008F0C11
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: It looks like Percy Kanu's been playing both sides.
#: 0204384B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:020438A3
msgctxt "001E46"
msgid "I can't say I wasn't expecting this. But having the proof in hand..."
msgstr "예상하지 못했다고는 못 하겠어. 하지만 증거를 손에 쥐고 보니..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D086
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001478AB
#. Notes = Concerned, Face: Concerned
#: 0204385A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D086
msgctxt "001E47"
msgid "Too much risk in transmission knowing how many tech resources Ryujin's got, so I need you to go meet them and help with whatever problem they're running into."
msgstr "류진이 가진 기술 자원이 얼마나 많은지 생각하면 전송은 너무 위험해. 그러니 네가 직접 가서 그들을 만나고, 그들이 겪는 문제를 도와줘야 해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0008958C
#: 02051C37/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:02051C5E
msgctxt "001E48"
msgid "I'm hoping what my contact has pans out and gets us the smoking gun we're after. We don't need them slipping away after we've gotten so close."
msgstr "내 연락책이 가진 게 제대로 맞아떨어져서 우리가 찾는 결정적 증거가 되길 바라고 있어. 이렇게 가까이 온 뒤에 그들이 빠져나가게 둘 순 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C54
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0007065E
#: 02051C2E/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C54
msgctxt "001E49"
msgid "They didn't count on you, though. Thanks to you throwing a wrench in things, I don't think they're getting away this time."
msgstr "하지만 그들은 널 계산에 넣지 않았지. 네가 일을 망쳐 놓은 덕분에, 이번엔 빠져나가지 못할 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02043883
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Hello
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00513BBA
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 020AAC69/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Hello:02043883
msgctxt "001E4A"
msgid "Look who it is. You've come pretty far since I first sent you to Anchorpoint."
msgstr "누가 왔는지 보자. 내가 처음 앵커포인트로 보냈을 때 이후로 꽤 멀리 왔군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Hello
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00BB191E
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 020AAC69/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Hello:02051C5F
msgctxt "001E4B"
msgid "Look who it is. You've come pretty far since when we first met. Still a mystery, though..."
msgstr "누가 왔는지 보자. 우리가 처음 만났을 때 이후로 꽤 멀리 왔군. 그래도 여전히 수수께끼야..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C92
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0062975F
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 02051C30/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02051C92
msgctxt "001E4C"
msgid "Guess I know who to call the next time something Terran-related comes up."
msgstr "다음에 테란 관련 일이 생기면 누구를 불러야 할지 알겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00228998
#: 02051C2C/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C5C
msgctxt "001E4D"
msgid "Ideally, no one. They have no skin in this other than profits, and they can't be relied on fully."
msgstr "이상적으로는 아무도 없어야 해. 그들은 이 일에 이익 말고는 걸린 게 없고, 완전히 믿을 수도 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C60
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 008100BC
#: 02051C2B/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C60
msgctxt "001E4E"
msgid "But we still need their resources, so I'm sure they'll be sending some replaceable drone at some point."
msgstr "하지만 우리에겐 여전히 그들의 자원이 필요하니, 언젠가는 대체 가능한 심부름꾼 하나를 보낼 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C50
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 006C40AB
#: 02051C2F/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C50
msgctxt "001E4F"
msgid "And the people who hide behind money and red tape make a habit of slipping away right at the finish line."
msgstr "돈과 잡다한 절차 뒤에 숨는 자들은 결승선 바로 앞에서 빠져나가는 버릇이 있지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C62
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 004355E6
#: 02051C2A/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C62
msgctxt "001E50"
msgid "We'll just be keeping a much closer eye on things going forward to make sure this doesn't happen again."
msgstr "앞으로는 이런 일이 다시 일어나지 않도록 훨씬 더 가까이 지켜볼 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C68
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0046AE21
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051C32/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02051C68
msgctxt "001E51"
msgid "And to the one who made it all happen."
msgstr "그리고 이 모든 일을 가능하게 한 사람을 위하여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C67
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 004FC688
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051C32/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02051C67
msgctxt "001E52"
msgid "And to the woman who made it all happen."
msgstr "그리고 이 모든 일을 가능하게 한 여성을 위하여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C66
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00BB3A89
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051C32/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02051C66
msgctxt "001E53"
msgid "And to the man who made it all happen."
msgstr "그리고 이 모든 일을 가능하게 한 남성을 위하여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00CBD78C
#: 02051C34/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C5D
msgctxt "001E54"
msgid "Well normally we would have been able to move on this earlier, but Ryujin's influence is pretty far-reaching."
msgstr "원래라면 더 일찍 움직일 수 있었겠지만, 류진의 영향력은 꽤 넓게 뻗어 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C57
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00FA4C0E
#: 02051C2D/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C57
msgctxt "001E55"
msgid "Who will fill in for Ryujin on VOID?"
msgstr "VOID에서 류진의 자리는 누가 대신하지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C64
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00837AE0
#: 02051C38/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:02051C64
msgctxt "001E56"
msgid "Missing alibis, unaccounted logs, things like that. Enough to invite questions, but I'm still looking for that definitive piece of evidence."
msgstr "빠진 알리바이, 설명되지 않는 기록, 그런 것들이지. 의문을 불러일으키기엔 충분하지만, 난 아직 결정적인 증거를 찾고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0009F17F
#. Notes = Impressed / to Player Default, Face: Impressed
#: 02051C31/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02051C6C
msgctxt "001E57"
msgid "Taking out the Terran forces and even cleaning up the messes they left behind."
msgstr "테란 병력을 제거하고, 그들이 남긴 난장판까지 정리했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C59
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00ABA258
#: 02051C41/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C59
msgctxt "001E58"
msgid "Details are vague for a reason. Just go for a stroll around MAST. See if anyone catches your eye."
msgstr "세부 내용이 모호한 데는 이유가 있어. 그냥 MAST 주변을 산책해 봐. 눈에 띄는 사람이 있는지 보라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C6E
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 000D4417
#: 02051C3D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C6E
msgctxt "001E59"
msgid "This has been going on since we first caught wind of the Terrans and formed a resistance effort."
msgstr "이 일은 우리가 처음 테란의 낌새를 알아채고 저항 활동을 조직했을 때부터 계속돼 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D078
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00BDD834
#. Notes = Relieved / to Yemoja, Face: Relieved
#: 0205D070/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0205D078
msgctxt "001E5A"
msgid "Good work, higher-ups are going to be pleased. I'll read the report later."
msgstr "잘했어. 윗선에서 기뻐하겠군. 보고서는 나중에 읽을게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C6D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D34CCA
#: 02051C43/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:02051C6D
msgctxt "001E5B"
msgid "I've seen enough. Let's go bag us a snake."
msgstr "충분히 봤어. 이제 뱀 한 마리 잡으러 가자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D080
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00B0E153
#: 02051C39/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:0205D080
msgctxt "001E5C"
msgid "Nothing to tie them to anyone in particular, but there are plenty of holes that leave people open to scrutiny."
msgstr "특정 인물과 직접 연결할 건 없지만, 조사를 받게 만들 구멍은 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C56
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D3110F
#: 02051C39/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:02051C56
msgctxt "001E5D"
msgid "Nothing to pin them as the leaker directly, but there are plenty of holes that leave him open to scrutiny."
msgstr "그를 누출자로 직접 지목할 건 없지만, 조사를 받게 만들 구멍은 많아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00789C1D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205D061/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D07A
msgctxt "001E5E"
msgid "Percy Kanu's been leaking information to the Terrans."
msgstr "퍼시 카누가 테란에게 정보를 흘리고 있었어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D074
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00734933
#: 0205D064/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0205D074
msgctxt "001E5F"
msgid "A lot more information leaked to the Terrans than I had assumed, but it looks like even some of VOID's operations were sabotaged in their favor too."
msgstr "내가 생각했던 것보다 훨씬 많은 정보가 테란에게 새어 나갔고, VOID의 일부 작전마저 그들에게 유리하도록 방해받은 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C58
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0055F7A9
#: 02051C35/00000/SFTER_MS02_1200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C58
msgctxt "001E60"
msgid "What happens to Percy now?"
msgstr "이제 퍼시는 어떻게 되는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003EC66F, 00536C4F
#. Notes = Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk, Prompt: 물론 아니지. 그냥 우연히 만난 두 사람일 뿐이야., / to Player Default
#: 0205D05D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:0205D08C
msgctxt "001E61"
msgid "I hope your stroll leads to further coincidences you find fruitful."
msgstr "그 산책에서 네게 유익한 우연이 더 이어지길 바라지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003EC66F, 00536C4F
#. Notes = Smirk / to Player Default, Face: Smirk, Prompt: 물론 아니지. 그냥 우연히 만난 두 사람일 뿐이야., / to Player Default
#: 0205D05D/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:0205D08C
msgctxt "001E62"
msgid "Nothing strange about a chance encounter, especially here of all places."
msgstr "우연한 만남에 이상할 건 없지. 특히 여기 같은 곳에서는 더더욱."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D084
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000FF7A1
#: 02051C3A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:0205D084
msgctxt "001E63"
msgid "What have you found so far on the leaker?"
msgstr "누출자에 대해 지금까지 알아낸 건 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C51
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00427124
#: 02051C3A/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL3:02051C51
msgctxt "001E64"
msgid "What have you found so far on Percy Kanu?"
msgstr "퍼시 카누에 대해 지금까지 알아낸 건 뭐야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C61
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00315187
#: 02051C3B/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C61
msgctxt "001E65"
msgid "But with any luck, you'll help wrap up this investigation and we can bring this chapter to a close."
msgstr "운이 따른다면 네가 이 조사를 마무리하는 데 도움을 주고, 우리는 이 장을 끝낼 수 있겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C4D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00D56511
#: 02051C3C/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C4D
msgctxt "001E66"
msgid "Leaks are always a danger in any joint effort, and working out of a place like Anchorpoint just opens you up to even more."
msgstr "누출은 어떤 공동 작업에서든 항상 위험 요소야. 앵커포인트 같은 곳에서 일하면 그 위험은 더 커지고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D087
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00C20F11
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 0205D05C/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0205D087
msgctxt "001E67"
msgid "Only one way to be sure, right? Shouldn't be any harm hearing her out."
msgstr "확실히 하려면 방법은 하나뿐이지, 안 그래? 그녀의 말을 들어 봐서 나쁠 건 없을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C52
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0028FE6E
#: 02051C3F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C52
msgctxt "001E68"
msgid "Keep in mind MAST -- and especially Aegis -- are known for their surveillance network. They more or less have all of New Atlantis bugged."
msgstr "MAST, 특히 이지스는 감시망으로 유명하다는 걸 명심해. 사실상 뉴아틀란티스 전체를 도청하고 있다고 보면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C69
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0095A6F6
#: 02051C3E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL2:02051C69
msgctxt "001E69"
msgid "How long have you been looking into the leaker?"
msgstr "누출자를 조사한 지는 얼마나 됐어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C55
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00BFE29F
#: 02051C40/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C55
msgctxt "001E6A"
msgid "So above all else, try and keep any conversations light."
msgstr "그러니 무엇보다도 대화는 가볍게 유지해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D079
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D1B1FD
#: 0205D066/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL:0205D079
msgctxt "001E6B"
msgid "Enjoying the view?"
msgstr "경치 감상 중인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C6A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0042C89A
#: 02051C42/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Yemoja_TL1:02051C6A
msgctxt "001E6C"
msgid "Where am I supposed to find your contact?"
msgstr "네 연락책은 어디서 찾으면 되지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D085
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0021B7BB
#. Notes = emphasis on "this"
#: 0205D05F/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D085
msgctxt "001E6D"
msgid "Lucky for us, I've been compiling a case on my own time. We're this close to discovering the vital piece we need."
msgstr "다행히도 난 개인 시간에 사건 자료를 정리해 왔어. 우리에게 필요한 핵심 조각을 찾아내기 직전이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D082
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 0093821A
#: 0205D062/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D082
msgctxt "001E6E"
msgid "You solve this in the meantime and by the end of it we should end up with the name we need."
msgstr "그동안 네가 이걸 해결하면, 끝날 때쯤엔 우리에게 필요한 이름을 손에 넣게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D081
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00A5F39E
#: 0205D062/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D081
msgctxt "001E6F"
msgid "You get the info we need in the meantime, and by the end of it we'll nail this guy."
msgstr "그동안 네가 필요한 정보를 구해 오면, 끝날 때쯤엔 그자를 잡아낼 수 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 002B700B, 00283FCA, 00F513CB
#: 0205D065/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL:0205D08B
msgctxt "001E70"
msgid "Sorry, not in the mood for much conversation. I'm a million miles from here."
msgstr "미안, 긴 대화를 나눌 기분이 아니야. 마음은 여기서 한참 멀리 가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 002B700B, 00283FCA, 00F513CB
#: 0205D065/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL:0205D08B
msgctxt "001E71"
msgid "But I've stared out at the water enough times over the years that it all looks the same to me at this point."
msgstr "하지만 오랜 세월 물을 충분히 바라본 탓에, 이제는 전부 똑같아 보여."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Voss
#. SoundFileID = 002B700B, 00283FCA, 00F513CB
#: 0205D065/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_TL:0205D08B
msgctxt "001E72"
msgid "What? Oh. Maybe when I first got here."
msgstr "뭐? 아. 처음 여기 왔을 때라면 그랬을지도."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D089
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B56FDC, 008DD72B
#. Notes = Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed, Prompt: 퍼시 카누가 테란에게 정보를 흘리고 있었어., / to Player Default
#: 0205D060/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D089
msgctxt "001E73"
msgid "But the fact we're both playing along means you haven't found that decisive piece of evidence either."
msgstr "하지만 우리 둘 다 장단을 맞추고 있다는 건, 너도 아직 결정적인 증거를 찾지 못했다는 뜻이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D089
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00B56FDC, 008DD72B
#. Notes = Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed, Prompt: 퍼시 카누가 테란에게 정보를 흘리고 있었어., / to Player Default
#: 0205D060/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D089
msgctxt "001E74"
msgid "Looks like you've been doing a little investigation of your own."
msgstr "너도 나름대로 조사를 좀 하고 있었던 모양이군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D088
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DAD562
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused, Prompt: 퍼시 카누가 테란에게 정보를 흘리고 있었어.
#: 0205D060/00000/SFTER_MS02_0100_Yemoja_Intro:0205D088
msgctxt "001E75"
msgid "There you go being mysterious again... Not even surprised at this point."
msgstr "또 그렇게 수수께끼처럼 구는군... 이제는 놀랍지도 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 007E66C8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205D05E/00000/SFTER_MS02_0200_Voss_MeetMAST:0205D07C
msgctxt "001E76"
msgid "Of course not. Just two people meeting coincidentally."
msgstr "물론 아니지. 그냥 우연히 만난 두 사람일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D076
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00C4E330
#: 0205D063/00000/SFTER_MS02_0900_Yemoja_DeliverSlate:0205D076
msgctxt "001E77"
msgid "Off-book credit transfers, doctored satellite data, leaked schedules and operations... A little bit of everything."
msgstr "장부 밖 크레딧 송금, 조작된 위성 데이터, 유출된 일정과 작전... 이것저것 다 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 009A423F
#. Notes = Irritated / to PercyKanu, Face: Irritated
#: 0205D06B/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:0205D07F
msgctxt "001E78"
msgid "Come on, Percy. Save your dignity and stop here."
msgstr "그만해, 퍼시. 품위는 지키고 여기서 멈춰."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D073
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MS02_TerranSoldier_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00F4F127
#: 0205D068/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D073
msgctxt "001E79"
msgid "So this is nothing more than a means to an end for you. That may be the first thing from you I really believe."
msgstr "그러니까 이건 네게 목적을 위한 수단일 뿐이라는 거군. 네 말 중에서 내가 진심으로 믿는 첫마디일지도 모르겠어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_SI_Percy01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D072
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_MS02_TerranSoldier_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00CD8F3A
#: 0205D06A/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D072
msgctxt "001E7A"
msgid "Do you think the favor of us Terrans is so easily gained?"
msgstr "우리 테란의 호의가 그리 쉽게 얻어질 거라 생각하나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D08A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 00D562F7
#: 0205D067/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D08A
msgctxt "001E7B"
msgid "Oh, I certainly will be."
msgstr "오, 물론 그렇게 할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_SI_Percy04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D071
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 002203BD
#: 0205D069/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D071
msgctxt "001E7C"
msgid "You should know I have no reason to impede you or your comrades. It would do me no favors to weaken the Terrans and end this stalemate."
msgstr "내게 너나 네 동료들을 방해할 이유가 없다는 걸 알아 둬. 테란을 약화시키고 이 교착 상태를 끝내는 건 내게 아무 이득도 되지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D083
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MS02_TerranSoldier_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00D070E6
#: 0205D06C/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D083
msgctxt "001E7D"
msgid "It will be ended soon enough. Just be careful which side you find yourself aligned with when we are ready to move on the rest of them."
msgstr "곧 끝날 것이다. 그저 우리가 그 나머지를 향해 움직일 준비가 되었을 때, 네가 어느 편에 서 있는지 조심해라."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MS02_TerranSoldier_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00D3D5CA, 00BB6E9A
#: 0205D06E/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D07B
msgctxt "001E80"
msgid "The sins of your people extend far beyond what a single slate of information can mend."
msgstr "네 사람들의 죄는 슬레이트 하나의 정보로 만회할 수 있는 수준을 훨씬 넘어선다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D07B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_MS02_TerranSoldier_VoiceOnly_NoAppearanceData
#. SoundFileID = 00D3D5CA, 00BB6E9A
#: 0205D06E/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D07B
msgctxt "001E81"
msgid "So you say. But even if this all is as it appears, this is nothing more than a tribute. You have not earned our trust."
msgstr "네 말은 그렇겠지. 하지만 설령 이 모든 것이 보이는 그대로라 해도, 이건 공물에 지나지 않는다. 너는 우리의 신뢰를 얻지 못했다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_SI_Percy02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D077
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01_AudioLogs
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_PercyKanu
#. SoundFileID = 004EB099
#: 0205D06F/00000/SFTER_MS02_AudioLogs_TerranRecording:0205D077
msgctxt "001E82"
msgid "I assure you, all of the details I'm providing you are on the up and up. You'll see as much once VOID begins to make its moves."
msgstr "내가 제공하는 모든 세부 정보가 전부 정직하고 확실한 것이라고 보장하지. VOID가 움직이기 시작하면 너희도 알게 될 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA20
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCRoxaneBourreau
#. SoundFileID = 00D7BF8B
#. Notes = To Delta. Completely ignoring the Player as they leave. She's much more sweet and friendly to Delta, but still trying to ask them to behave. / Grateful, Face: Grateful
#: 020516DD:0205CA20
msgctxt "001E83"
msgid "Delta, please stay out of trouble."
msgstr "델타, 제발 문제 일으키지 말고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA1F
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00422F75
#. Notes = (Delta Response: Counterpoint: Elimination more effective than avoidance.) To tried/ exasperated to even retort. / Stern / to Delta, Face: Stern
#: 0205CA1B/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA1F
msgctxt "001E84"
msgid "*Sigh*"
msgstr "*한숨*"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA25
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 004E53D7
#. Notes = (Delta Response: Acknowledged, will return with minimal damage.) Emphasis 'because' like finishing a sentence. Then worry when saying 'right? right?' / Pleading / to Delta, Face: Pleading
#: 0205CA1C/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA25
msgctxt "001E85"
msgid "Because you will stay out of trouble, right? ... Right?"
msgstr "문제 일으키지 않을 거지? ... 그렇지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA21
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Roxane
#. SoundFileID = 00892906
#. Notes = (Delta Response: Confirmed, avoiding areas labeled "trouble") Pleased and amused to hear they're listening to her. A little proud. / Amused / to Delta, Face: Amused
#: 0205CA1D/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA21
msgctxt "001E86"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "고마워."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA24
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 007E0B07
#. Notes = Almost as if trying to bargain with Roxane. / to Roxane
#: 0205CA1E/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA24
msgctxt "001E87"
msgid "Counterpoint: Elimination more effective than avoidance."
msgstr "반론: 제거가 회피보다 더 효과적임."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA23
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00A8E6B1
#. Notes = Matter of fact. Like 'Yes, ma'am.' / to Roxane
#: 0205CA1E/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA23
msgctxt "001E88"
msgid "Acknowledged, will return with minimal damage."
msgstr "확인. 최소 피해로 복귀하겠음."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205CA22
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ02_GenericDialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 00465C4E
#. Notes = Matter of fact. Like a 'you got it, boss.' / to Roxane
#: 0205CA1E/00030/SFTER_ROX_DELTA_Goodbye:0205CA22
msgctxt "001E89"
msgid "Confirmed, avoiding areas labeled \"trouble\""
msgstr "확인, \"문제\"라고 표시된 구역 회피 중"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 009F96FC, 00DD625A, 00DDBB10
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 그게 어디서 왔을지에 대한 이론이 있나?
#: 02045780/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02051A6C
msgctxt "001E8A"
msgid "I would posit that it doesn't originate from our universe. Crazy, I know. But it's what I think."
msgstr "내 생각엔 그것이 우리 우주에서 비롯된 것이 아닌 것 같아. 말도 안 된다는 건 알지만, 난 그렇게 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 009F96FC, 00DD625A, 00DDBB10
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 그게 어디서 왔을지에 대한 이론이 있나?
#: 02045780/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02051A6C
msgctxt "001E8B"
msgid "But given its dispersement seems random, and we don't have a clear explanation for HOW it's created..."
msgstr "하지만 그 분산이 무작위로 보이고, 그것이 어떻게 생성되는지 명확한 설명도 없다는 점을 고려하면..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 009F96FC, 00DD625A, 00DDBB10
#. Notes = Neutral / to Player Default, Prompt: 그게 어디서 왔을지에 대한 이론이 있나?
#: 02045780/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02051A6C
msgctxt "001E8C"
msgid "Well, this is just a hypothesis, and I have no data to back it up."
msgstr "뭐, 이건 그냥 가설이고 뒷받침할 데이터는 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A6B
#. QuestName = SFTER_Companions
#. SceneName = SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Barrett
#. SoundFileID = 003D3FCC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051A6A/00000/SFTER_COM_Barrett_QEvent_TerranArmada:02051A6B
msgctxt "001E8D"
msgid "Do you have any theories on where it might come from?"
msgstr "그게 어디서 왔을지에 대한 이론이 있나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C96
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00051091
#: 0203D09A:02051C96
msgctxt "001E8E"
msgid "No funny business."
msgstr "수작 부리지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C95
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 00D703F2
#: 0203D09A:02051C95
msgctxt "001E8F"
msgid "Don't give me a reason to change my mind about you."
msgstr "너에 대한 생각을 바꿀 이유를 주지 마."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C94
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFAgentYemonja
#. SoundFileID = 0089E438
#: 0203D09A:02051C94
msgctxt "001E90"
msgid "You're not going to go all Terran on me or something, right?"
msgstr "갑자기 테란처럼 굴거나 하진 않을 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C6B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00A21622
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051C4C/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02051C6B
msgctxt "001E91"
msgid "I'm actually delivering this Terran robot to VOID back at Anchorpoint."
msgstr "난 사실 이 테란 로봇을 앵커포인트에 있는 VOID로 데려가는 중이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C65
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00DC0D79
#. Notes = / to Delta
#: 02051C46/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02051C65
msgctxt "001E92"
msgid "In any case, I can see why the members of VOID would be interested in a potentially rebel Terran like this."
msgstr "어쨌든 VOID의 구성원들이 이런 잠재적 테란 반란자에게 관심을 가질 이유는 알겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0204387A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00F92A6F
#: 02043829/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:0204387A
msgctxt "001E93"
msgid "Seems I missed some important new details while out coordinating the search in orbit..."
msgstr "궤도에서 수색을 조율하느라 자리를 비운 사이 중요한 새 정보를 놓친 모양이군..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5A
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005E5CD6
#. Notes = Awed / to Player Default, Face: Awed, Prompt: 난 사실 이 테란 로봇을 앵커포인트에 있는 VOID로 데려가는 중이야.
#: 02051C4B/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02051C5A
msgctxt "001E94"
msgid "What, how do you...? You're involved with VOID?"
msgstr "뭐, 어떻게 그걸...? 너 VOID와 관련이 있어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C53
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00A73717
#: 02051C45/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1100_Yemoja_Exit:02051C53
msgctxt "001E96"
msgid "I assume you already know your way back to Anchorpoint, so carry on. I'll stay back here to make sure this mess gets cleaned up."
msgstr "앵커포인트로 돌아가는 길은 이미 알고 있을 테니 계속 가. 난 여기 남아서 이 난장판이 정리되도록 확인하겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051C5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1000_SystemVoice_LockdownLifted
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ElevatorVoice
#. SoundFileID = 0020F26B
#. Notes = Ship system voice, loudspeaker pre-recorded, informational
#: 02051C28/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1000_SystemVoice_LockdownLifted:02051C5B
msgctxt "001E97"
msgid "Emergency systems disengaged. Lockdown lifted. Resuming normal operations."
msgstr "비상 시스템 해제. 봉쇄 해제. 정상 운영 재개."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00671857, 0081A636
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 강제 궤환 회로로 축적된 이온 전하를 유발하다니... 빠른 판단이었다.
#: 0205D0A1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0205D0A4
msgctxt "001E98"
msgid "Raising base level Perception variable for Auxiliary Human."
msgstr "보조 인간의 기본 지각 변수 레벨 상승."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0A4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00671857, 0081A636
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 강제 궤환 회로로 축적된 이온 전하를 유발하다니... 빠른 판단이었다.
#: 0205D0A1/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0205D0A4
msgctxt "001E99"
msgid "Thinking \"quick\" relative only to dulled comprehension. Otherwise, Human Auxiliary's analysis is... sound."
msgstr "빠르다는 표현은 둔화된 이해력에 상대적일 뿐. 그 외에는 보조 인간의 분석이... 타당함."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ01
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00EC4758
#: 0205D0A2/00000/SFTER_MQ01_1600_Delta_HackEnd:0205D0A3
msgctxt "001E9A"
msgid "Using a forced feedback loop to trigger an accrued ionic charge... quick thinking."
msgstr "강제 궤환 회로로 축적된 이온 전하를 유발하다니... 빠른 판단이었다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 00C03BBA
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0B2
msgctxt "001E9B"
msgid "This war is far from over!"
msgstr "이 전쟁은 아직 끝나려면 멀었다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 000E633D
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0B1
msgctxt "001E9C"
msgid "You really think you'll come out on top, huh!?"
msgstr "정말 네가 이길 거라고 생각하나, 응!?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 0055C905
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0B0
msgctxt "001E9D"
msgid "I've been at this far longer than you!"
msgstr "난 너보다 훨씬 오래 이 일을 해 왔다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 009756C9
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0AF
msgctxt "001E9E"
msgid "This won't end in your favor!"
msgstr "이건 네게 유리하게 끝나지 않을 거다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AE
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 003CC20D
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0AE
msgctxt "001E9F"
msgid "You're out classed!"
msgstr "넌 상대가 안 돼!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 0084E3E2
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0AD
msgctxt "001EA0"
msgid "The colonies are a dying cause, give up!"
msgstr "식민지 연합은 죽어 가는 명분이다, 포기해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 007B3B9A
#. Notes = Angry, Face: Angry
#: 0205D0A5:0205D0AC
msgctxt "001EA1"
msgid "For the Armada!"
msgstr "테란 함대를 위하여!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 00A3BB65
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0BA
msgctxt "001EA2"
msgid "Erh, Can I get some cover here!?"
msgstr "어, 여기 엄호 좀 해 줄 수 있나!?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 000EFE04
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B9
msgctxt "001EA3"
msgid "Ugh!"
msgstr "으윽!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 00F4A62F
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B8
msgctxt "001EA4"
msgid "Errh!"
msgstr "으으윽!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B7
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 0038684E
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B7
msgctxt "001EA5"
msgid "Arg, Is that it!?"
msgstr "아악, 그게 다인가!?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 004E9249
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B6
msgctxt "001EA6"
msgid "I'm hit!"
msgstr "맞았다!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 008870C8
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B5
msgctxt "001EA7"
msgid "Agh!"
msgstr "악!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0B4
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. DialogCallType = Combat
#. Speaker = SFTER_NPCFOdeBalewa
#. SoundFileID = 008EE9A4
#. Notes = InPain, Face: InPain
#: 0205D0A6:0205D0B4
msgctxt "001EA8"
msgid "They got me!"
msgstr "놈들이 날 맞혔어!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 005FB7EE, 00F04968
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0205D0A7/00000/SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape02:0205D0A9
msgctxt "001EA9"
msgid "It's been an honor working with you. Go ahead and report back to the council, I'll meet you back there while our troops mop up here."
msgstr "함께 일해서 영광이었어. 가서 대의회에 보고해. 우리 병력이 여기 잔당을 정리하는 동안 나도 거기로 돌아갈게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape02
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 005FB7EE, 00F04968
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0205D0A7/00000/SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape02:0205D0A9
msgctxt "001EAA"
msgid "Haha! That's what I'm talking about! Haha!"
msgstr "하하! 바로 이거지! 하하!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00665FF9, 002B2D16, 008FECB2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0205D0A8/00000/SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01:0205D0AA
msgctxt "001EAB"
msgid "Trust me, these Grav Drive melt downs are nasty business. You don't want to be too close."
msgstr "믿어, 이런 중력 구동기 멜트다운은 아주 골치 아픈 일이야. 너무 가까이 있고 싶진 않을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00665FF9, 002B2D16, 008FECB2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0205D0A8/00000/SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01:0205D0AA
msgctxt "001EAC"
msgid "Focus on getting some distance between you and the Unifier. I've got you covered."
msgstr "너와 유니파이어 사이의 거리를 벌리는 데 집중해. 내가 엄호할게."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D0AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_MQ03
#. SceneName = SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = SFTER_TracyWarren
#. SoundFileID = 00665FF9, 002B2D16, 008FECB2
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Face: Spaceship / Neutral
#: 0205D0A8/00000/SFTER_MQ03_Unifier_Escape01:0205D0AA
msgctxt "001EAD"
msgid "I'll assume you undocking means we're all clear."
msgstr "네가 도킹을 해제했다는 건 이제 모두 안전하다는 뜻으로 받아들일게."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SpeechStart02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518AC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00755A38
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2C5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518AC
msgctxt "001EAE"
msgid "Talk all you want, but you won't change my mind."
msgstr "마음껏 말해 봐. 그래도 내 마음은 바뀌지 않을 테니까."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SpeechStart03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518AD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00F30379
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2C5/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518AD
msgctxt "001EAF"
msgid "Consider these your last words, so make them good."
msgstr "마지막 말이라고 생각하고, 제대로 해 봐."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_FriendlyDeltaSceneReentry04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D056
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E1986D
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0205D056
msgctxt "001EB0"
msgid "We don't want any part of this fight. We just want to live in peace. It's why we left the Settled Systems to begin with. "
msgstr "우린 이 싸움에 끼고 싶지 않아. 그냥 평화롭게 살고 싶을 뿐이야. 애초에 개척 성계를 떠난 것도 그래서였어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierSceneReentry01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0073BADE
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020518C0
msgctxt "001EB1"
msgid "We do what we must to prevent another Colony War."
msgstr "우린 또 다른 식민지 전쟁을 막기 위해 해야 할 일을 한다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D05A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C3237A
#. Notes = Scene re-entry. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0205D05A
msgctxt "001EB2"
msgid "You have to believe me. We're just surveyors."
msgstr "날 믿어 줘. 우린 그냥 측량사야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D059
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 006E4E67
#. Notes = Scene re-entry. / Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0205D059
msgctxt "001EB3"
msgid "We only recently arrived, so we don't have any data to show for it yet."
msgstr "우린 최근에 도착했을 뿐이라 아직 보여 줄 데이터가 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DBE5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A55443
#. Notes = Scene re-entry. / Pleading / to Player Default, Face: Pleading
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0205DBE5
msgctxt "001EB4"
msgid "Please, just let us go. We only want to start over."
msgstr "제발, 그냥 보내 줘. 우린 새로 시작하고 싶을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DBE1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D30A97
#. Notes = Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 020174AD/02000/SFTER_INC_SCP01_FriendlyIntroMainScene:0205DBE1
msgctxt "001EB5"
msgid "Hopefully, the Armada doesn't send anyone after us. They don't tolerate deserters. "
msgstr "테란 함대가 우리 뒤를 쫓아 사람을 보내지 않길 바랄 뿐이야. 그들은 탈영병을 용납하지 않거든."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003BFFBE, 00720B7E
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CD
msgctxt "001EBC"
msgid "Thank you. I know you didn't have to speak to us, nor try to convince us of the truth."
msgstr "고마워. 우리와 대화할 필요도, 진실을 설득하려 애쓸 필요도 없었다는 걸 알아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 003BFFBE, 00720B7E
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CD
msgctxt "001EBD"
msgid "You're right, the timing is perfect. We'll be presumed dead, and with no ships or robots, we won't be worth the recovery effort."
msgstr "네 말이 맞아, 타이밍이 완벽해. 우린 죽은 것으로 추정될 거고, 함선도 로봇도 없으니 회수 작전을 벌일 가치도 없겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0017CD39, 0058EB63, 000F836B
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CC
msgctxt "001EBE"
msgid "Thank you for taking the time. I know if the roles were reversed, I wouldn't have been as kind."
msgstr "시간을 내줘서 고마워. 입장이 반대였다면 난 이렇게 친절하지 못했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0017CD39, 0058EB63, 000F836B
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CC
msgctxt "001EBF"
msgid "When we don't report back, I'm certain they'll write us off as MIA rather than spend the resources to find us."
msgstr "우리가 복귀 보고를 하지 않으면, 그들은 우리를 찾는 데 자원을 쓰기보다 미아로 처리할 게 분명해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0017CD39, 0058EB63, 000F836B
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Grateful / to Player Default, Face: Grateful
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CC
msgctxt "001EC0"
msgid "We will, and this is the perfect opportunity. "
msgstr "그럴게. 그리고 지금이 완벽한 기회야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0202C3DC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00329ED7, 00AF7459, 0070FCF8
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 0202C2BE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0202C3DC
msgctxt "001EC1"
msgid "You're right, and the timing is ideal."
msgstr "네 말이 맞아. 타이밍도 이상적이고."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceB03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00C8A0A5
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0C/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020518B3
msgctxt "001EC2"
msgid "There must be others. Help them find a way out, too."
msgstr "분명 다른 이들도 있을 거야. 그들도 빠져나갈 길을 찾도록 도와줘."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceB02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CA882D
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0C/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020518B2
msgctxt "001EC3"
msgid "Start a movement. There must be others like you."
msgstr "운동을 시작해. 너희 같은 사람들이 더 있을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceA03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00BC3FB0
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020518C4
msgctxt "001EC4"
msgid "You don't have to continue this fight. You're free to leave."
msgstr "이 싸움을 계속할 필요는 없어. 자유롭게 떠나도 돼."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceA02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00766983
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:020518C3
msgctxt "001EC5"
msgid "Then leave the Armada. Start a new life."
msgstr "그럼 테란 함대를 떠나. 새 삶을 시작해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205189C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0074EC0A
#. Notes = SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0202C2C2/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205189C
msgctxt "001EC6"
msgid "I think I've heard enough."
msgstr "충분히 들은 것 같아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205189B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006887B7
#. Notes = SinisterSmile / to Player Default, Face: SinisterSmile
#: 0202C2C2/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205189B
msgctxt "001EC7"
msgid "Enough of this talk. Let's end this."
msgstr "이 대화는 충분해. 끝내자."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518DA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0058EB18
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518DA
msgctxt "001EC8"
msgid "Can't you see how hypocritical this all feels?"
msgstr "이 모든 게 얼마나 위선적으로 느껴지는지 모르겠어?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005C708A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D9
msgctxt "001EC9"
msgid "Why can't you see there must be a better way?"
msgstr "더 나은 길이 분명히 있다는 걸 왜 보지 못하는 거야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051892
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FB4D9B
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051892
msgctxt "001ECA"
msgid "We aren't following blindly. It's an unfortunate necessity that things get worse before they can get better."
msgstr "우린 맹목적으로 따르는 게 아니야. 나아지기 전에 상황이 더 나빠져야 하는 건 안타까운 필연일 뿐이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051891
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005EBB5C
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051891
msgctxt "001ECB"
msgid "I'm not blind to our actions. It's the sacrifice we're all willing to make for a better world."
msgstr "우리의 행동을 모르는 척하는 게 아니야. 더 나은 세상을 위해 우리 모두가 감수하기로 한 희생이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051825
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FD382A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D2/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051825
msgctxt "001ECC"
msgid "You're the Terran scouting party?"
msgstr "너희가 테란 정찰대야?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D4
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005E4DCD
#. Notes = About to go into combat. Telling fellow troops to attack. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D4
msgctxt "001ECD"
msgid "For the Terran Armada!"
msgstr "테란 함대를 위하여!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D24BA6
#. Notes = About to go into combat. Telling fellow troops to attack. / Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C2C7/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D3
msgctxt "001ECE"
msgid "You'll be just another casualty."
msgstr "넌 또 하나의 희생자가 될 뿐이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00985D2E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C8/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518B6
msgctxt "001ECF"
msgid "[Attack] I'm obviously not going to be able to change your mind."
msgstr "[공격] 네 마음을 바꿀 수 없다는 건 분명하군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B5
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00308CA2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C8/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518B5
msgctxt "001ED0"
msgid "[Attack] You're wrong about the Settled Systems, but violence does solve a lot of problems."
msgstr "[공격] 개척 성계에 대한 네 생각은 틀렸지만, 폭력이 많은 문제를 해결하긴 하지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000BEFEF
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 0202C2CB/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518C1
msgctxt "001ED1"
msgid "Our methods are the only way to get the Settled Systems to listen, to educate them."
msgstr "우리의 방식만이 개척 성계가 듣게 만들고, 그들을 깨우칠 유일한 길이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009598DB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518C7
msgctxt "001ED2"
msgid "I've heard your point of view, but I'd like to ask that you reconsider."
msgstr "네 관점은 들었지만, 다시 생각해 달라고 부탁하고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00162D97
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2C6/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518C6
msgctxt "001ED3"
msgid "All I ask is you take a moment to listen."
msgstr "잠시만 들어 달라는 게 전부야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205181F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003B0369
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D0/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205181F
msgctxt "001ED4"
msgid "What makes you think I'm a Terran?"
msgstr "내가 테란이라고 생각하는 이유가 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205181E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00D4611B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D0/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205181E
msgctxt "001ED5"
msgid "How can you tell if I'm a Terran or not?"
msgstr "내가 테란인지 아닌지 어떻게 알 수 있지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205189F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007DC381
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CC/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205189F
msgctxt "001ED6"
msgid "You can't really justify what you're doing in the name of peace."
msgstr "평화라는 이름으로 네가 하는 일을 정당화할 순 없어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205189E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00FC2A4A
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CC/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205189E
msgctxt "001ED7"
msgid "The actions of your leaders aren't so different."
msgstr "네 지도자들의 행동도 크게 다르지 않아."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E45EFC
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CA
msgctxt "001ED8"
msgid "But there is already peace within the Settled Systems."
msgstr "하지만 개척 성계 안에는 이미 평화가 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518C9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0028C4F1
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2CE/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518C9
msgctxt "001ED9"
msgid "We already have peace within the Settled Systems."
msgstr "우리는 이미 개척 성계 안에서 평화를 누리고 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051838
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00BC3495
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CF/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051838
msgctxt "001EDA"
msgid "The only robots like that are Terran issued. Now who are you?"
msgstr "그런 로봇은 테란 지급품뿐이야. 이제 네가 누구인지 말해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051837
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00684705
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CF/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051837
msgctxt "001EDB"
msgid "Only our troops have robots like that, but if you're not one of us, you have some explaining to do."
msgstr "그런 로봇은 우리 병력만 가지고 있어. 네가 우리 중 하나가 아니라면 설명이 필요하겠군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A48
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00578FED
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 0202C2D3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051A48
msgctxt "001EDC"
msgid "There's no way we lost the numbers that quickly. You're no Terran soldier. Who are you and what do you want?"
msgstr "우리가 그렇게 빨리 병력을 잃었을 리 없어. 넌 테란 병사가 아니야. 넌 누구고 뭘 원하는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A47
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 009CBC97
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 0202C2D3/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051A47
msgctxt "001EDD"
msgid "This mission's classified, and you don't look like any superior officer I recognize. Who are you really, and what do you want?"
msgstr "이 임무는 기밀이고, 넌 내가 아는 어떤 상급 장교처럼도 보이지 않아. 정체가 뭐고 뭘 원하는 거지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0042B5BD
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CD/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518B0
msgctxt "001EDE"
msgid "Your peace is fleeting. Give it time. You may not know it, but the cracks are already showing."
msgstr "너희의 평화는 덧없다. 시간을 두고 봐라. 너희는 모르겠지만 이미 균열이 드러나고 있다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EE5687, 00BCA710
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CD/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518AF
msgctxt "001EDF"
msgid "It's in their nature to want more, to be better."
msgstr "더 많은 것을 원하고, 더 나아지길 바라는 건 그들의 본성이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518AF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00EE5687, 00BCA710
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2CD/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518AF
msgctxt "001EE0"
msgid "It's just a matter of time before your leaders grow malcontent. "
msgstr "너희 지도자들이 불만을 품는 건 시간문제일 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051829
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0041763F
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D1/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051829
msgctxt "001EE1"
msgid "Affirmative. And you are?"
msgstr "긍정. 그리고 당신은?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051828
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B132E2
#. Notes = Serious / to Player Default, Face: Serious
#: 0202C2D1/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051828
msgctxt "001EE2"
msgid "Correct. You made it. Now report."
msgstr "정확함. 도착했군. 이제 보고하라."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SolderSceneReentry04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DBDF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00277E73
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0205DBDF
msgctxt "001EE3"
msgid "Start talking."
msgstr "말해라."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SolderSceneReentry03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DBDE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00E4F1DB
#. Notes = Confident / to Player Default, Face: Confident
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0205DBDE
msgctxt "001EE4"
msgid "Once the Terran Armada has established true peace, the Settled Systems will thank us."
msgstr "테란 함대가 진정한 평화를 이룩하고 나면, 개척 성계도 우리에게 감사하게 될 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierSceneReentry02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DBDC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0005ECF9
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber
#: 0202C35E/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:0205DBDC
msgctxt "001EE5"
msgid "We've been so misguided all this time."
msgstr "우리는 지금까지 너무나도 잘못된 길을 걸어왔다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D7
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D4D487
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D7
msgctxt "001EE6"
msgid "[Lie] We've lost the fight. It's time to make a new life. Start over."
msgstr "[Lie] 우리는 싸움에서 졌어. 새 삶을 시작할 때야. 다시 시작하는 거지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D6
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 005CC3B8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C2D4/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D6
msgctxt "001EE7"
msgid "[Lie] The Armada's been defeated. Lay low. Start a new life."
msgstr "[Lie] 아르마다는 패배했어. 몸을 숨기고 새 삶을 시작해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A4F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00DE2F45
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0202C31A/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A4F
msgctxt "001EE8"
msgid "Just try and change my mind."
msgstr "어디 한번 내 마음을 바꿔 봐."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A4E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00073494
#. Notes = Amused / to Player Default, Face: Amused
#: 0202C31A/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A4E
msgctxt "001EE9"
msgid "Misguided? The only one here misguided is you."
msgstr "잘못됐다고? 여기서 잘못된 건 너뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A5A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000F2739
#. Notes = Going into combat. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C318/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A5A
msgctxt "001EEA"
msgid "Good luck with that."
msgstr "잘해 보시지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A59
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 000ECAEB
#. Notes = Going into combat. Shouting to nearby soldiers. / Angry / to Player Default, Face: Angry
#: 0202C318/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A59
msgctxt "001EEB"
msgid "Back me up!"
msgstr "엄호해!"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A5D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 001DCC9E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C319/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A5D
msgctxt "001EEC"
msgid "[Attack] I'm not taking any chances."
msgstr "[Attack] 위험은 남기지 않겠어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A5C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0061F2A8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C319/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A5C
msgctxt "001EED"
msgid "[Attack] Delta's assessment sounds fair to me."
msgstr "[Attack] 델타의 평가가 타당해 보이는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A4B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00C0D85E
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C31B/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A4B
msgctxt "001EEE"
msgid "Good, now let's focus on how misguided the Terran cause is."
msgstr "좋아, 이제 테란의 대의가 얼마나 잘못됐는지에 집중해 보자고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A4A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00165D99
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0202C31B/02210/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroDeltaBranchScene:02051A4A
msgctxt "001EEF"
msgid "Now all you need to admit is how misguided your cause is."
msgstr "이제 네 대의가 얼마나 잘못됐는지만 인정하면 돼."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051896
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00615CB2
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051883/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051896
msgctxt "001EF0"
msgid "What makes you think you can take on the United Colonies and the Freestar Collective and win?"
msgstr "식민지 연합과 자유항성 공동체를 상대로 싸워서 이길 수 있다고 생각하는 근거가 뭐지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051895
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DBD4EF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051883/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051895
msgctxt "001EF1"
msgid "You're one small faction. Do you really think you stand a chance?"
msgstr "너희는 작은 세력 하나일 뿐이야. 정말 승산이 있다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051894
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00264BEA
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051883/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051894
msgctxt "001EF2"
msgid "Do you really think you can take on the Settled Systems and win?"
msgstr "정말 개척 성계 전체를 상대해서 이길 수 있다고 생각해?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B5FA22, 00755880
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188B
msgctxt "001EF3"
msgid "The Terran Armada is going to bring about a true age of peace by uniting everyone under a single banner."
msgstr "테란 아르마다는 모두를 하나의 깃발 아래 통합해 진정한 평화의 시대를 열 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00B5FA22, 00755880
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188B
msgctxt "001EF4"
msgid "Just because the Colony War is over doesn't mean the people in power have superior morals or motivations to their predecessors. "
msgstr "식민지 전쟁이 끝났다고 해서 권력자들의 도덕성이나 동기가 선대보다 낫다는 뜻은 아니야. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0020A36F, 004B5D3E, 00337175
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188A
msgctxt "001EF5"
msgid "The Terran Armada will bring a new age of peace for all."
msgstr "테란 아르마다는 모두를 위한 새로운 평화의 시대를 열 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0020A36F, 004B5D3E, 00337175
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188A
msgctxt "001EF6"
msgid "The leaders of the Settled Systems cannot be trusted. Tech may be banned, but their motivations are still as selfish as ever."
msgstr "개척 성계의 지도자들은 믿을 수 없어. 기술은 금지됐을지 몰라도 그들의 동기는 여전히 이기적이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0020A36F, 004B5D3E, 00337175
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188A
msgctxt "001EF7"
msgid "What the people in power did during the Colony War was unforgivable. "
msgstr "식민지 전쟁 중 권력자들이 저지른 일은 용서받을 수 없어. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051889
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0019963C, 00C27C7D, 0059158E
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051889
msgctxt "001EF8"
msgid "The Terran Armada will establish a true age of peace and war will be a thing of the past."
msgstr "테란 아르마다는 진정한 평화의 시대를 세울 것이고, 전쟁은 과거의 일이 될 것이다."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051889
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0019963C, 00C27C7D, 0059158E
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051889
msgctxt "001EF9"
msgid "And their intentions cost the lives of thousands. "
msgstr "그리고 그 의도 때문에 수천 명이 목숨을 잃었지. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051889
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0019963C, 00C27C7D, 0059158E
#. Notes = Stern / to Player Default, Face: Stern
#: 02051881/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:02051889
msgctxt "001EFA"
msgid "The Colony War was full of atrocities. The people in power had no respect. No decency. "
msgstr "식민지 전쟁은 잔혹 행위로 가득했어. 권력자들에게는 존중도 없었고, 품위도 없었지. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518BA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0095D105
#. Notes = Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug
#: 02051882/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518BA
msgctxt "001EFB"
msgid "You can't possibly imagine the amount of preparation we've done for this. Your very question shows how you underestimate us."
msgstr "우리가 이 일을 위해 얼마나 준비했는지 너는 상상도 못 할 거야. 그런 질문 자체가 네가 우리를 얼마나 과소평가하는지 보여 주는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00DB263D
#. Notes = Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug
#: 02051882/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518B9
msgctxt "001EFC"
msgid "It's been over twenty years since the Colony War. What do you think we've been doing all that time? "
msgstr "식민지 전쟁이 끝난 지 20년도 넘었어. 그동안 우리가 뭘 하고 있었다고 생각하지? "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518B8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0077D39C
#. Notes = Smug / to Player Default, Face: Smug
#: 02051882/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518B8
msgctxt "001EFD"
msgid "We've done nothing but prepare after the Colony War. You have no idea what you're up against."
msgstr "우리는 식민지 전쟁 이후 준비만 해 왔다. 네가 뭘 상대하고 있는지 전혀 모르는군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00477E9B, 00B7D624, 00BB63AF
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A3
msgctxt "001EFE"
msgid "We've all had a pervasive feeling of... wrongness since it started. And you've helped to open our eyes."
msgstr "시작된 뒤로 우리 모두에게는 줄곧... 뭔가 잘못됐다는 느낌이 퍼져 있었다. 그리고 네가 우리의 눈을 뜨게 해 줬어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00477E9B, 00B7D624, 00BB63AF
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A3
msgctxt "001EFF"
msgid "There is a level of hypocrisy and extremism that's hard to ignore now that we've entered into this battle. "
msgstr "이 전투에 뛰어들고 보니 외면하기 힘든 수준의 위선과 극단주의가 보이더군. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A3
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00477E9B, 00B7D624, 00BB63AF
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A3
msgctxt "001F00"
msgid "I think everyone here would agree that we've had our doubts with leadership for some time now."
msgstr "여기 있는 모두가 한동안 지도부에 의구심을 품고 있었다는 데 동의할 거라고 생각해."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A61AB4, 003D5F54, 00BCCB7B
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A2
msgctxt "001F01"
msgid "I think my fellow soldiers here would agree, we were misled."
msgstr "내 전우들도 동의할 거야. 우리는 속았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A61AB4, 003D5F54, 00BCCB7B
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A2
msgctxt "001F02"
msgid "Returning to the Settled Systems has been eye opening. It's not the place of evil we all believed it to be."
msgstr "개척 성계로 돌아와 보니 눈이 뜨였어. 우리가 믿었던 것처럼 악의 땅은 아니더군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A2
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A61AB4, 003D5F54, 00BCCB7B
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A2
msgctxt "001F03"
msgid "I would be remiss to not admit I've... struggled with the words of our leaders of late."
msgstr "최근 우리 지도자들의 말에... 흔들렸다는 걸 인정하지 않으면 정직하지 못한 거겠지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A6097F, 00803937
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A1
msgctxt "001F04"
msgid "The Settled Systems may still be misguided, but not as misguided as we've been."
msgstr "개척 성계가 아직 잘못된 길을 가고 있을지는 몰라도, 우리가 그랬던 것만큼은 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00A6097F, 00803937
#. Notes = Somber / to Player Default, Face: Somber, Concerned / to Player Default, Face: Concerned
#: 02051880/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A1
msgctxt "001F05"
msgid "I admit, I've had my doubts with our leaders for some time, but your words have finally convinced me. "
msgstr "인정하지. 나는 한동안 우리 지도자들에게 의구심을 품고 있었어. 하지만 네 말이 마침내 나를 설득했다. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D1
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0048DBE2
#. Notes = Thinking / to Player Default, Face: Thinking
#: 02051884/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D1
msgctxt "001F06"
msgid "Is that so? Perhaps there is hope for some in the Settled Systems after all."
msgstr "그래? 어쩌면 개척 성계에도 아직 희망이 있는 자들이 있나 보군."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518D0
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00410D79
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 02051884/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518D0
msgctxt "001F07"
msgid "I suppose there's a first chance for everything."
msgstr "무슨 일이든 첫 기회라는 건 있는 법이지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518CF
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 007F7F62
#. Notes = Suspicious / to Player Default, Face: Suspicious
#: 02051884/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518CF
msgctxt "001F08"
msgid "Now that's a first. But it's about time someone from the Settled Systems was willing to listen."
msgstr "이건 처음이군. 그래도 개척 성계 사람이 들을 마음을 먹을 때가 되긴 했지."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518AA
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CEEB07
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051885/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518AA
msgctxt "001F09"
msgid "I'd like to get a better understanding on why you're with the Armada."
msgstr "네가 왜 아르마다에 있는지 더 잘 이해하고 싶어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A9
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CC9B13
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051885/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A9
msgctxt "001F0A"
msgid "I only want to exchange points of view and try to understand."
msgstr "나는 그저 관점을 나누고 이해해 보려는 것뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518A8
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 00CD3D85
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051885/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518A8
msgctxt "001F0B"
msgid "I just want to hear your side of the story."
msgstr "네 입장을 들어 보고 싶을 뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D3154B
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 02051886/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188F
msgctxt "001F0C"
msgid "If you want to preach, you've come to the wrong place."
msgstr "설교하러 온 거라면 번지수를 잘못 찾았어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0010C726
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 02051886/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188E
msgctxt "001F0D"
msgid "Let me stop you right there. We're a necessary force. The Settled Systems needs guidance and the Terran Armada will provide it."
msgstr "거기서 멈춰. 우리는 필요한 힘이다. 개척 성계에는 지도가 필요하고, 테란 아르마다가 그 역할을 할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205188D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00200808
#. Notes = Defiant / to Player Default, Face: Defiant
#: 02051886/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:0205188D
msgctxt "001F0E"
msgid "No, you may not recognize it, but the Settled Systems needs us. "
msgstr "아니, 네가 알아보지 못할 뿐 개척 성계에는 우리가 필요해. "

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518BE
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 00D42F72
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051887/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518BE
msgctxt "001F0F"
msgid "The Terran Armada are extremists. You're on the wrong side."
msgstr "테란 아르마다는 극단주의자들이야. 넌 잘못된 편에 서 있어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518BD
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 0036BAC6
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051887/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518BD
msgctxt "001F10"
msgid "Abandon this fight. It's misguided and foolish."
msgstr "이 싸움을 포기해. 잘못됐고 어리석은 일이야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020518BC
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 000745DF
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02051887/02300/SFTER_INC_SCP01_SoldierIntroMainScene:020518BC
msgctxt "001F11"
msgid "I'm here to convince you to leave the Terran Armada."
msgstr "난 네가 테란 아르마다를 떠나도록 설득하러 왔어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceC03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A63
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 005F5D96
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051A63
msgctxt "001F12"
msgid "[Attack] There's only one way to atone for what you've done."
msgstr "[Attack] 네가 저지른 일을 속죄할 방법은 하나뿐이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceC02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A62
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 003F21FB
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051A62
msgctxt "001F13"
msgid "[Attack] You know the truth, so you know you deserve this."
msgstr "[Attack] 넌 진실을 알고 있어. 그러니 네가 이걸 받아 마땅하다는 것도 알겠지."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SCP_SoldierFinalPlayerChoiceC01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02051A61
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_MIN_ScoutingParty01
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = ScoutLeader
#. SoundFileID = 0062EA0B
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 0205DC0A/02200/SFTER_INC_SCP01_RudeIntroMainScene:02051A61
msgctxt "001F14"
msgid "[Attack] Now that you've seen the truth, you can pay the price."
msgstr "[Attack] 이제 진실을 봤으니, 대가를 치를 차례야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_ExteriorReality
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D009
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = Delta
#. SoundFileID = 008852FA
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: Makes sense for how on top of things you seem to be.
#: 0205D010/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:0205D009
msgctxt "001F15"
msgid "Correct. Counterpoint: Must wait for exterior reality to catch up after solution discovery."
msgstr "정확함. 반론: 해결책 발견 후 외부 현실이 따라잡을 때까지 대기 필요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205D01B
#. QuestName = SFTER_CREW_EliteCrew_Delta
#. SceneName = CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 004E427C
#. Notes = / to Player Default, Prompt: 인식과 동기화되도록 지연을 프로그래밍하거나, 프로세서를 전환해서 스스로 속도를 늦추면 되잖아.
#: 0205D00E/00015/CREW_EliteCrew_Delta_15_TopLevel_Personal_1:0205D01B
msgctxt "001F16"
