#. SoundFileID = 00832709
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC73
msgctxt "001F42"
msgid "Your timing couldn't have been better. We're alive, thanks to you."
msgstr "타이밍이 이보다 좋을 수는 없었어. 네 덕분에 살았어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks09
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC72
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00759927
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC72
msgctxt "001F43"
msgid "Those Terrans almost had us. I've never been so thankful for reinforcements."
msgstr "그 테란들이 우리를 거의 잡을 뻔했어. 지원 병력이 이렇게 고마운 적은 처음이야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks08
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC71
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00BB116C
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC71
msgctxt "001F44"
msgid "Thank god you showed up. We owe you our lives."
msgstr "네가 와 줘서 정말 다행이야. 우리는 목숨을 빚졌어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks07
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC70
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00A9C5D3
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC70
msgctxt "001F45"
msgid "Are we glad to see you. We weren't going to last much longer."
msgstr "널 보니 얼마나 반가운지 몰라. 더는 오래 버티지 못했을 거야."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks06
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00AD5231
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6F
msgctxt "001F46"
msgid "Thanks for the save! Those Terrans came out of nowhere."
msgstr "구해 줘서 고마워! 그 테란들이 갑자기 튀어나왔어."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks05
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6E
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00C68B80
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6E
msgctxt "001F47"
msgid "I thought those Terrans had us. You showed up just in time."
msgstr "그 테란들에게 끝장나는 줄 알았어. 정말 제때 나타났군."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks04
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6D
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 002F2D9C
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6D
msgctxt "001F48"
msgid "You saved our lives. We owe you one."
msgstr "우리 목숨을 구했어. 신세 하나 졌군."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks03
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6C
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00A3834F
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6C
msgctxt "001F49"
msgid "I've never been so happy to see a friendly face! "
msgstr "우호적인 얼굴을 보고 이렇게 기뻤던 적은 없어! "

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks02
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00A69F36
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6B
msgctxt "001F4A"
msgid "You showed up just in time. I thought we were dead."
msgstr "정말 제때 나타났어. 죽는 줄 알았다고."

#. List: 2
#. EDID: SFTER_INC_SPP_Thanks01
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC6A
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_SE_SpacePatrol01
#. DialogCallType = Miscellaneous
#. Speaker = GenericFemaleEvenToned, GenericMale01, SpacerFemale01, FreestarSecurityFemale01 (+18 more)
#. SoundFileID = 00F99418
#. Notes = Player rescued them and they're out of danger. / Grateful, Face: Spaceship / Grateful
#: 020AA529:0205DC6A
msgctxt "001F4B"
msgid "Thanks! I didn't think we'd survive that."
msgstr "고마워! 살아남을 줄은 몰랐어."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC5D
