#: 0205DC4A/02400/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_Misc05Scene:0205DC5C
msgctxt "001F4D"
msgid "I wouldn't say everything..."
msgstr "전부라고까지는 안 하겠지만..."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC5B
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
