msgid "You can trust me. This will work in your favor."
msgstr "날 믿어도 돼. 이건 너에게 유리하게 작용할 거야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC60
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_RepeatableManipulation01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006744E4
#: 0205DC4F/00000/SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_RepeatableManipulation01Scene:0205DC60
msgctxt "001F50"
msgid "Just be honest with me, be reasonable."
msgstr "솔직하게 말해. 이성적으로 굴라고."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC5F
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
