msgctxt "001F52"
msgid "I told you the truth. It's not my fault you won't believe it."
msgstr "난 진실을 말했어. 네가 믿지 않는 건 내 탓이 아니야."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 0205DC59
#. QuestName = SFTER_INC_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_INC_SCP_Surveyor_SC_RepeatableManipulation01Scene
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
