#. SoundFileID = 003821D1
#: 0206189D/00000/SFTER_MS02_Kenji_TL1:020618C8
msgctxt "002009"
msgid "You're Ryujin's replacement VOID representative?"
msgstr "당신이 류진의 새 VOID 대표인가?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020618EB
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_Kenji_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Player Default
#. SoundFileID = 006F6536
#: 0206189E/00000/SFTER_MS02_Kenji_TL2:020618EB
msgctxt "00200A"
msgid "Are you upset about what happened to Percy Kanu?"
msgstr "퍼시 카누에게 일어난 일 때문에 화가 났나?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 020618A1
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02_Dialogue
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_Kenji_TL2
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = KenjiKanazawa
#. SoundFileID = 00F45ED0
#: 0206189C/00000/SFTER_MS02_Kenji_TL2:020618A1
msgctxt "00200B"
msgid "It's just business. We have a contract with VOID, and there was a party not honoring the spirit of it."
msgstr "그저 비즈니스일 뿐입니다. 우리는 VOID와 계약을 맺었고, 그 정신을 지키지 않은 당사자가 있었죠."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02061C7C
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 001508D8
#. Notes = / to Player Default
#: 02061C78/00000/SFTER_MS02_1100_Yemoja_End:02061C7C
msgctxt "00200D"
msgid "Though, maybe let's hope it doesn't come to this point again."
msgstr "하지만, 이런 지경까지 다시 오지 않기를 바라야겠군요."

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
#. FormID: 02061C7D
#. QuestName = SFTER_MS02
#. SceneName = SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront
#. DialogCallType = SceneDialogue
#. Speaker = Yemoja
#. SoundFileID = 00362D45
#. Notes = / to PercyKanu
#: 02061C79/00000/SFTER_MS02_1000_Yemoja_PercyConfront:02061C7D
msgctxt "00200E"
msgid "You were saying?"
msgstr "말하던 중이었지?"

#. List: 2
#. REC: INFO:NAM1
